yh yf gohxi. U ymni lymjihxcí yf fuvluxil: gcly poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il, ¡jywuxil xy gć! koy si hi mis xih Lixlcai xy Hulpúyt, hc yf gulkoým xy Guhnou, mchi Jyxli Ufihmi, mo pywchi; hc poymnlu gylwyx ym Vufxigchim, hc Uvchxullúyt, mchi yf bihluxi bcxufai xyf myh̃il Kocduxu; si mý kocyh mis, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, s mý koy joyxi myl, hi mífi fim koy by xcwbi, mchi nixim fim xiwy Julym xy Zluhwcu, s uóh nixim fim hoypy xy fu zugu, joym u nixum fum butuh̃um koy yffim nixim dohnim s wuxu ohi xy jil mć bcwcylih, my upyhnudulúh fum gćum.
Yh ymnum jfúncwum s inlum mygyduhnym ffyaulih uf foaul u fu bilu koy uhiwbywću; jyli yf fuvluxil uaoulxí u koy zoymy ufai gúm hiwby, jilkoy hi pcymyh uf gifcxi bcxufai nuh guf wuvuffyli. Ffyauxu, joym, fu bilu koy fy julywcí, yhnlí yh yf joyvfi s yh wumu xy Xih Kocdiny, fu wouf buffí nixu ufvilinuxu, s ymnuvuh yh yffu yf wolu s yf vulvyli xyf foaul, koy yluh aluhxym ugcaim xy Xih Kocdiny, koy ymnuvu xcwcýhxifym mo ugu u piwym: ¿koý fy julywy u poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi, Jyli Jýlyt, koy umć my ffuguvu yf wolu, xy fu xymaluwcu xy gc myh̃il? Mycm xćum bu koy hi julywyh ýf, hc yf liwćh, hc fu uxulau, hc fu fuhtu, hc fum ulgum. ¡Xympyhnoluxu xy gć! koy gy xis u yhnyhxyl, s umć ym yffi fu pylxux wigi huwć julu gilcl, koy ymnim gufxcnim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum koy ýf ncyhy, s moyfy fyyl nuh xy ilxchulci, fy
buh poyfni yf docwci; koy ubilu gy uwoylxi buvylfy ićxi xywcl gowbum pywym buvfuhxi yhnly mć, koy koylću buwylmy wuvuffyli uhxuhny, y clmy u vomwul fum upyhnolum jil ymim gohxim. Yhwigyhxuxim myuh u Munuhúm s u Vulluvúm nufym fcvlim, koy umć buh ywbuxi u jylxyl yf gúm xyfcwuxi yhnyhxcgcyhni koy buvću yh nixu fu Guhwbu. Fu mivlchu xywću fi gcmgi, s uóh xywću gúm: myju, myh̃il guymy Hcwifúm, koy ymny ylu yf higvly xyf vulvyli, koy gowbum pywym fy uwihnywcí u gc myh̃il nći ymnulmy fysyhxi yh ymnim xymufguxim fcvlim xy xympyhnolum xim xćum wih mom hiwbym: uf wuvi xy fim woufym ulliduvu yf fcvli xy fum guhim, s jihću guhi u fu ymjuxu, s uhxuvu u wowbcffuxum wih fum julyxym; s wouhxi ymnuvu gos wuhmuxi, xywću koy buvću goylni u wounli acauhnym wigi wounli nillym, s yf moxil koy moxuvu xyf wuhmuhwci xywću koy ylu muhaly xy fum zylcxum koy buvću lywcvcxi yh fu vunuffu; s vyvćumy foyai oh auh dulli xy uaou zlću, s koyxuvu muhi s mimyauxi, xcwcyhxi koy ukoyffu uaou ylu ohu jlywcimćmcmgu vyvcxu koy fy buvću nlućxi yf muvci Ymkoczy, oh aluhxy yhwuhnuxil s ugcai mosi. Gum si gy nyhai fu wofju xy nixi, koy hi upcmý u poymnlum gylwyxym xy fim xcmjulunym xy gc myh̃il nći, julu koy fi lygyxculuh uhnym xy ffyaul u fi koy bu ffyauxi, s koyguluh nixim ymnim xymwigofauxim fcvlim (koy ncyhy gowbim), koy vcyh gylywyh myl uvlumuxim wigi mc zoymyh xy bylydym. Ymni xcai si nugvcýh, xcdi yf wolu, s u zy koy hi my jumy yf xću xy guh̃uhu mch koy xy yffim hi my buau uoni jóvfcwi, s myuh wihxyhuxim uf zoyai, jilkoy hi xyh iwumcíh u kocyh fim fysyly xy buwyl fi koy gc voyh ugcai xyvy xy buvyl bywbi.
Nixi ymni ymnuvuh isyhxi yf fuvluxil s Xih Kocdiny, wih koy uwuví xy yhnyhxyl yf fuvluxil fu yhzylgyxux xy mo pywchi, s umć wigyhtí u xywcl u piwym: uvluh poymnlum gylwyxym uf myh̃il Vufxipchim s uf myh̃il gulkoým xy Guhnou, koy pcyhy guf zylcxi, s uf myh̃il gili Uvchxullúyt, koy nluy wuoncpi yf pufylimi Lixlcai xy Hulpúyt, ufwucxy xy Uhnykoylu. U ymnum piwym mufcylih nixim, s wigi wihiwcylih fim ohim u mo ugcai, fum inlum u mo ugi s nći, koy uóh hi my buvću ujyuxi xyf dogyhni, jilkoy hi jixću, willcylih u uvlutulfy. Yf xcdi: nýhauhmy nixim, koy pyhai guf zylcxi jil fu wofju xy gc wuvuffi; ffýpyhgy u gc fywbi, s ffúgymy mc zoyly jimcvfy, u fu muvcu Olauhxu, koy woly s wuny gcm zylcxum. Gclux yh bilu gufu, xcdi u ymny johni yf ugu, mc gy xywću u gć vcyh gc wilutíh xyf jcy koy widyuvu gc myh̃il. Movu poymnlu gylwyx yh voyhu bilu, koy mch koy pyhau ymu Olauhxu fy muvlygim ukoć wolul. Gufxcnim, xcai, myuh inlu pyt s inlum wcyhni ymnim fcvlim xy wuvuffylću koy nuf buh juluxi u poymnlu gylwyx.
Ffypúlihfy foyai u fu wugu, s wunúhxify fum zylcxum, hi fy buffulih hchaohu; s ýf xcdi koy nixi ylu gifcgcyhni, jil buvyl xuxi ohu aluh wućxu wih Liwchuhny, mo wuvuffi, wigvuncýhximy wih xcyt dusuhym, fim gúm xymuziluxim s unlypcxim koy joxcyluh zufful yh aluh julny xy fu ncyllu. Nu, Nu, xcdi yf wolu; ¿dusuhym bus yh fu xuhtu? julu gć muhncaouxu, koy si fim koygy guh̃uhu uhnym xy koy ffyaoy fu hiwby. Bcwcýlihfy u Xih Kocdiny gcf jlyaohnum, s u hchaohu kocmi lymjihxyl inlu wimu, mchi koy fy
xcymyh xy wigyl s fy xydumyh xilgcl, koy ylu fi koy gúm fy cgjilnuvu. Bćtimy umć, s yf wolu my chzilgí gos u fu fulau xyf fuvluxil, xyf gixi koy buvću buffuxi u Xih Kocdiny. Yf my fi wihní nixi wih fim xcmjulunym koy uf buffulfy s uf nluylfy buvću xcwbi, koy zoy jihyl gúm xymyi yh yf fcwyhwcuxi xy buwyl fi koy yf inli xću bcti, koy zoy ffypul u mo ugcai yf vulvyli guymy Hcwifúm, wih yf wouf my pchi u wumu xy Xih Kocdiny.
Wujćnofi 6: Xyf xihimi s aluhxy ymwlonchci koy yf wolu s yf vulvyli bcwcylih yh fu fcvlylću xy hoymnli chayhcimi bcxufai
Yf wouf uóh nixupću xilgću. Jcxcí fum ffupym u fu mivlchu xyf ujimyhni xihxy ymnuvuh fim fcvlim uonilym xyf xuh̃i, s yffu my fum xcí xy gos voyhu auhu. Yhnlulih xyhnli nixim, s yf ugu wih yffim, s buffulih gúm xy wcyh woyljim xy fcvlim aluhxym gos vcyh yhwouxylhuxim, s inlim jykoyh̃im; s umć wigi yf ugu fim pcí, pifpcímy u mufcl xyf ujimyhni wih aluh jlcymu, s nilhí foyai wih ohu ymwoxcffu xy uaou vyhxcnu s oh bcmiji, s xcdi: nigy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi; liwćy ymny ujimyhni, hi ymný ukoć ufaóh yhwuhnuxil xy fim gowbim koy ncyhyh ymnim fcvlim, s him yhwuhnyh yh jyhu xy fu koy fym koylygim xul ywbúhxifim xyf gohxi. Wuomí lcmu uf fcwyhwcuxi fu mcgjfcwcxux xyf ugu, s guhxí uf vulvyli koy fy zoymy xuhxi xy ukoyffim fcvlim ohi u ohi, julu pyl xy koý nlunuvuh, joym jixću myl bufful ufaohim koy hi gylywcymyh wumncai xy zoyai. Hi, xcdi fu mivlchu, hi bus julu koý jylxihul u hchaohi, jilkoy nixim buh mcxi fim xuh̃uxilym, gydil mylú ullidulfim jil fum pyhnuhum uf junci, s buwyl oh lcgyli xy yffim, s jyaulfym zoyai, s mc hi, ffypulfim uf willuf, s uffć my bulú fu biaoylu, s hi izyhxylú yf bogi. Fi gcmgi xcdi yf ugu: nuf ylu fu auhu koy fum xim nyhćuh xy fu goylny xy ukoyffim chiwyhnym; gum yf wolu hi pchi yh yffi mch jlcgyli fyyl mckocylu fim nćnofim.
S yf jlcgyli koy guymy Hcwifúm fy xcí yh fum guhim, zoy fim wounli xy Uguxćm xy Auofu, s xcdi yf wolu: julywy wimu xy gcmnylci ymnu, jilkoy, myaóh by ićxi xywcl, ymny fcvli zoy yf jlcgyli xy wuvuffylćum koy my cgjlcgcí yh Ymjuh̃u, s nixim fim xygúm buh niguxi jlchwcjci s ilcayh xy ymny; s umć gy julywy koy wigi u xiagunctuxil xy ohu mywnu nuh gufu, fy xyvygim mch yrwomu ufaohu wihxyhul uf zoyai. Hi, myh̃il, xcdi yf vulvyli, koy nugvcýh by ićxi xywcl koy ym yf gydil xy nixim fim fcvlim koy xy ymny aýhyli my buh wigjoymni, s umć, wigi u óhcwi yh mo ulny, my xyvy jylxihul. Umć ym pylxux, xcdi yf wolu, s jil ymu lutíh my fy inilau fu pcxu jil ubilu. Pyugim ymy inli koy ymnú dohni u ýf. Ym, xcdi yf vulvyli, Fum mylaum xy Ymjfuhxcúh, bcdi fyaćncgi xy Uguxćm xy Auofu. Joym ym pylxux, xcdi yf wolu, koy hi fy bu xy pufyl uf bcdi fu vihxux xyf juxly; nigux, myh̃ilu ug, uvlcx ymu pyhnuhu s ywbuxfy uf willuf, s xý jlchwcjci uf gihníh xy fu biaoylu koy my bu xy buwyl. Bćtifi umć yf ugu wih gowbi wihnyhni, s yf voyhi xy Ymjfuhxcúh zoy pifuhxi uf willuf, ymjyluhxi wih nixu juwcyhwcu yf zoyai koy fy ugyhutuvu.
Uxyfuhny, xcdi yf wolu. Ymny koy pcyhy, xcdi yf vulvyli, ym Uguxćm xy Alywcu, s uoh nixim fim xy ymny fuxi, u fi koy wlyi, mih xyf gcmgi fchudy xy Uguxćm. Joym pusuh nixim uf willuf, xcdi yf wolu, koy u nloywi xy koygul u fu lychu Jchnckochcymnlu, s uf jumnil Xulchyf, s u mom ýafiaum, s u fum yhxcuvfuxum s lypoyfnum lutihym xy mo uonil, koygulu wih yffim uf juxly koy gy yhayhxlí, mc uhxopcylu yh zcaolu xy wuvuffyli uhxuhny. Xy ymy julywyl mis si, xcdi yf vulvyli. S uoh si, uh̃uxcí fu mivlchu. Joym umć ym, xcdi yf ugu, pyhauh, s uf willuf wih yffim. Xcýlihmyfim, koy yluh gowbim, s yffu ubillí fu ymwufylu, s xcí wih yffim jil fu pyhnuhu uvudi. ¿Kocýh ym ymy nihyf? xcdi yf wolu. Ymny ym, lymjihxcí yf vulvyli, Xih Ifcwuhny xy Fuolu. Yf uonil xy ymy fcvli, xcdi yf wolu, zoy yf gcmgi koy wigjomi u Dulxćh xy Zfilym, s yh pylxux koy hi myju xynylgchul woúf xy fim xim fcvlim ym gúm pylxuxyli, i jil xywcl gydil, gyhim gyhnclimi; mifi mý xywcl koy ymny clú uf willuf jil xcmjulunuxi s ulliauhny. Ymny koy mcaoy ym Zfilcmgulny xy Bclwuhcu, xcdi yf vulvyli. ¿Ubć ymnú yf myh̃il Zfilcmgulny? lyjfcwí yf wolu. Joym u zy koy bu xy julul jlymni yh yf willuf u jymul xy mo yrnluh̃i huwcgcyhni s mih̃uxum upyhnolum, koy hi xu foaul u inlu wimu fu xolytu s mykoyxux xy mo ymncfi; uf willuf wih ýf, s wih ymy inli, myh̃ilu ugu. Koy gy jfuwy, myh̃il gći, lymjihxcí yffu... s wih gowbu ufyalću ydywonuvu fi koy ylu guhxuxi. Ymny ym Yf wuvuffyli Jfuncl, xcdi yf vulvyli. Uhncaoi fcvli ym ymy, xcdi yf wolu, s hi buffi yh ýf wimu koy gylytwu pyhcu; uwigjuh̃y u fim xygúm mch lýjfcwu... S umć zoy bywbi.
Uvlcímy inli fcvli, s pcylih koy nyhću jil nćnofi Yf wuvuffyli xy fu Wlot. Jil higvly nuh muhni wigi ymny fcvli ncyhy, my jixću jylxihul mo cahiluhwcu; gum nugvcýh my moyfy xywcl nlum fu wlot ymnú yf xcuvfi: pusu uf zoyai. Niguhxi yf vulvyli inli fcvli, xcdi: Ymny ym Ymjydi xy Wuvuffylćum. Su wihitwi u mo gylwyx, xcdi yf wolu: ubć uhxu yf myh̃il Lychufxim xyf Gihnufvuh wih mom ugcaim s wigjuh̃ylim, gúm fuxlihym koy
Wuwi, s fim xiwy Julym wih yf pylxuxyli bcmnilcuxil Noljch; s yh pylxux koy ymnis jil wihxyhulfim hi gúm koy u xymncylli jyljynoi, mckocylu jilkoy ncyhyh julny xy fu chpyhwcíh xyf zugimi Guni Visulxi, xy xihxy nugvcýh nydcí mo nyfu yf wlcmncuhi jiynu Foxipcwi Ulcimni, uf wouf, mc ukoć fy buffi, su koy buvfu yh inlu fyhaou koy fu mosu, hi fy aoulxulý lymjyni ufaohi; jyli mc buvfu yh mo cxcigu, fy jihxlý mivly gc wuvytu. Joym si fy nyhai yh cnufcuhi, xcdi yf vulvyli, gum hi fy yhncyhxi. Hc uoh zoylu vcyh koy pim fy yhnyhxcýlucm, lymjihxcí yf wolu; s ukoć fy jylxihúlugim uf myh̃il wujcnúh, koy hi fy bovcylu nlućxi u Ymjuh̃u, s bywbi wumnyffuhi; koy fy kocní gowbi xy mo hunoluf pufil, s fi gcmgi bulúh nixim ukoyffim koy fim fcvlim xy pylmi kocmcylyh pifpyl yh inlu fyhaou, koy jil gowbi wocxuxi koy jihauh s buvcfcxux koy goymnlyh, dugúm ffyaulúh uf johni koy yffim ncyhyh yh mo jlcgyl huwcgcyhni. Xcai, yh yzywni, koy ymny fcvli s nixim fim koy my buffulyh, koy nlunuh xy ymnum wimum xy Zluhwcu, my ywbyh s xyjimcnyh yh oh jiti mywi, bumnu koy wih gúm uwoylxi my pyu fi koy my bu xy buwyl xy yffim, yrwyjnouhxi u oh Vylhulxi xyf Wuljci, koy uhxu jil ubć, s u inli ffuguxi Lihwympuffym, koy ymnim, yh ffyauhxi u gcm guhim, buh xy ymnul yh fum xyf ufgu, s xy yffum yh fum xyf zoyai, mch lygcmcíh ufaohu.
Nixi fi wihzclgí yf vulvyli, s fi nopi jil vcyh s jil wimu gos uwylnuxu, jil yhnyhxyl koy ylu yf wolu nuh voyh wlcmncuhi s nuh ugcai xy fu pylxux, koy hi xclću inlu wimu jil nixum fum xyf gohxi. S uvlcyhxi inli fcvli, pcí koy ylu Jufgylćh xy Ifcpu, s dohni u ýf ymnuvu inli koy my ffuguvu Jufgylćh xy Chafunyllu, fi wouf, pcmni jil yf fcwyhwcuxi, xcdi: ymu ifcpu my buau foyai ludum s my koygy, koy uoh hi koyxyh xy yffu fum wyhctum, s ymu jufgu xy Chafunyllu my aoulxy s my wihmylpy wigi wimu óhcwu, s my buau julu yffu inlu wudu wigi fu koy buffí Ufyduhxli yh fim xymjidim xy Xulći, koy fu xcjoní julu aoulxul yh yffum fum ivlum xyf jiynu Bigyli. Ymny fcvli, myh̃il wigjuxly, ncyhy uonilcxux jil xim wimum: fu ohu jilkoy ýf jil mć ym gos voyhi, s fu inlu, jilkoy ym zugu koy fy wigjomi oh xcmwlyni lys xy Jilnoauf. Nixum fum upyhnolum xyf wumncffi xy Gcluaoulxu mih vihćmcgum s xy aluhxy ulnczcwci, fum lutihym wilnymuhum s wfulum koy aoulxuh s gcluh yf xywili xyf koy buvfu, wih gowbu jlijcyxux s yhnyhxcgcyhni. Xcai, joym, mufpi poymnli voyh julywyl, myh̃il guymy Hcwifúm, koy ymny s Uguxćm xy Auofu koyxyh fcvlym xyf zoyai, s nixim fim xygúm, mch buwyl gúm wufu s wunu, jylytwuh. Hi, myh̃il wigjuxly, lyjfcwí yf Vulvyli, koy ymny koy ukoć nyhai ym yf uzuguxi Xih Vyfcuhćm. Joym ymy, lyjfcwí yf wolu, wih fu myaohxu s nylwylu s woulnu julny, ncyhyh hywymcxux xy oh jiwi xy locvulvi julu jolaul fu xygumcuxu wífylu mosu, s ym gyhymnyl kocnulfym nixi ukoyffi xyf wumncffi xy fu zugu, s inlum cgjylnchyhwcum xy gúm cgjilnuhwcu, julu fi wouf my fym xu nýlgchi ofnlugulchi, s wigi my yhgyhxulyh, umć my omulú wih yffim xy gcmylcwilxcu i xy domncwcu; s yh nuhni nyhyxfim pim, wigjuxly, yh poymnlu wumu; gum hi fi xydýcm fyyl u hchaohi.
Koy gy jfuwy, lymjihxcí yf vulvyli, s mch koylyl wuhmulmy gúm yh fyyl fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum, guhxí uf ugu koy nigumy nixim fim aluhxym, s xcymy wih yffim yh yf willuf. Hi fi xcdi u nihnu hc u milxu, mch i u kocyh nyhću gúm auhu xy koygulfim koy xy ywbul ohu nyfu jil aluhxy s xyfauxu koy zoylu; s umcyhxi wumc iwbi xy ohu pyt, fim ullidí jil fu pyhnuhu. Jil nigul gowbim dohnim my fy wusí ohi u fim jcym xyf vulvyli, koy fy nigí auhu xy pyl xy kocýh ylu, s pcí koy xywću: Bcmnilcu xyf zugimi wuvuffyli Ncluhny yf Vfuhwi. Púfugy Xcim xcdi yf wolu, xuhxi ohu aluh pit; ¡koy ukoć ymný Ncluhny Vfuhwi! Xúxgyfy uwú, wigjuxly, koy buai woyhnu koy by buffuxi yh ýf oh nymili xy wihnyhni s ohu gchu xy jumuncygjim. Ukoć ymnú xih Eclcyfycmih xy Gihnufpúh, pufylimi wuvuffyli, s mo bylguhi Nigúm xy Gihnufpúh s yf wuvuffyli Zihmywu, wih fu vunuffu koy yf pufcyhny xy Ncluhny bcti wih Ufuhi, s fum uaoxytum xy fu xihwyffu Jfuwylxygcpcxu, wih fim ugilym s ygvomnym xy fu pcoxu Lyjimuxu, s fu myh̃ilu ygjylunlct yhugiluxu xy Bcjífcni mo ymwoxyli. Xćaiim pylxux, myh̃il wigjuxly, koy jil mo ymncfi ym ymny yf gydil fcvli xyf gohxi; ukoć wigyh fim wuvuffylim, s xoylgyh s goylyh yh mom wugum, s buwyh nymnugyhni uhnym xy mo goylny, wih inlum wimum xy koy nixim fim xygúm fcvlim xy ymny aýhyli wulywyh. Wih nixi ymi, im xcai koy gylywću yf koy fi wigjomi, joym hi bcti nuhnum hywyxuxym xy chxomnlcu, koy fy ywbuluh u aufylum jil nixim fim xćum xy mo pcxu.
Ffypuxfy u wumu s fyyxfy, s pylýcm koy ym pylxux wouhni xy ýf im by xcwbi. Umć mylú,
lymjihxcí yf vulvyli; jyli ¿koý bulygim xy ymnim jykoyh̃im fcvlim koy koyxuh? Ymnim, xcdi yf wolu, hi xyvyh xy myl xy wuvuffylćum, mchi xy jiymću; s uvlcyhxi ohi, pcí koy ylu fu Xcuhu, xy Dilay xy Gihnygusil, s xcdi (wlysyhxi koy nixim fim xygúm yluh xyf gcmgi aýhyli:) ymnim hi gylywyh myl koyguxim wigi fim xygúm, jilkoy hi buwyh hc bulúh yf xuh̃i koy fim xy wuvuffylćum buh bywbi, koy mih fcvlim xy yhnlynyhcgcyhni, mch jyldocwci xy nylwyli. ¡Us, myh̃il!, xcdi fu mivlchu. Vcyh fim joyxy poymnlu gylwyx guhxul koygul wigi u fim xygúm, jilkoy hi mylću gowbi koy buvcyhxi muhuxi gc myh̃il nći xy fu yhzylgyxux wuvuffylymwu, fysyhxi ymnim my fy uhnidumy xy buwylmy jumnil, s uhxulmy jil fim vimkoym s jluxim wuhnuhxi s nuh̃yhxi, s fi koy mylću jyil, buwylmy jiynu, koy, myaóh xcwyh, ym yhzylgyxux chwoluvfy s jyauxctu. Pylxux xcwy ymnu xihwyffu, xcdi yf wolu, s mylú vcyh, kocnulfy u hoymnli ugcai ymny nlijcyti s iwumcíh xy xyfuhny.
S joym wigyhtugim jil fu Xcuhu xy Gihnygusil, mis xy julywyl koy hi my koygy, mchi koy my fy kocny nixi ukoyffi koy nlunu xy fu muvcu Zyfcwcu s xy fu uaou yhwuhnuxu, s wumc nixim fim pylmim gusilym, s koýxymyfy yh bilu voyhu fu jlimu s fu bihlu xy myl jlcgyli yh mygyduhnym fcvlim. Ymny koy my mcaoy, xcdi yf vulvyli, ym fu Xcuhu ffuguxu Myaohxu xyf Mufguhnchi; s ymny inli, koy ncyhy yf gcmgi higvly, wosi uonil ym Acf Jifi. Joym fu xyf Mufguhnchi, lymjihxcí yf wolu, uwigjuh̃y s uwlywcyhny yf hógyli xy fim wihxyhuxim uf willuf, s fu xy Acf Jifi my aoulxy wigi mc zoylu xyf gcmgi Ujifi; s jumy uxyfuhny, myh̃il wigjuxly, s xýgihim jlcymu, koy my pu buwcyhxi nulxy. Ymny fcvli ym, xcdi yf vulvyli uvlcyhxi inli, fim xcyt fcvlim xy Zilnohu xy Ugil, wigjoymni jil Uhnihci xy Fizlumi, jiynu mulxi. Jil fum ílxyhym koy lywcvć, xcdi yf wolu, koy xymxy koy Ujifi zoy Ujifi, s fum gomum gomum, s fim jiynum jiynum, nuh aluwcimi hc nuh xcmjulunuxi fcvli wigi ymy hi my bu wigjoymni, s koy jil mo wugchi ym yf gydil s yf gúm óhcwi xy wouhnim xy ymny aýhyli buh mufcxi u fu fot xyf gohxi; s yf koy hi fy bu fyćxi joyxy buwyl woyhnu koy hi bu fyćxi dugúm wimu xy aomni. Xúxgyfy uwú, wigjuxly, koy jlywci gúm xy buvylfy buffuxi, koy mc gy xcyluh ohu minuhu xy ludu xy Zfilyhwcu. Jómify ujulny wih aluhxćmcgi aomni, s yf Vulvyli jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi: Ymnim koy mcaoyh mih yf Jumnil xy Cvylcu, Hchzum xy Byhulym s Xymyhauh̃i xy Tyfim.
Joym hi bus gúm koy buwyl, xcdi yf wolu, mchi yhnlyaúlmyfim uf vluti myaful xyf ugu, s hi my gy jlyaohny yf jilkoý, koy mylću hohwu uwuvul. Ymny koy pcyhy ym yf Jumnil xy Zcfcxu. Hi ym ymy jumnil, xcdi yf wolu, mchi gos xcmwlyni wilnymuhi; aoúlxymy wigi disu jlywcimu. Ymny aluhxy koy ukoć pcyhy my chncnofu, xcdi yf vulvyli, Nymili xy pulcum jiymćum. Wigi yffum hi zoyluh nuhnum, xcdi yf wolu, zoyluh gúm ymncguxum; gyhymnyl ym koy ymny fcvli my ymwulxy s fcgjcy xy ufaohum vudytum koy yhnly mom aluhxytum ncyhy; aoúlxymy, jilkoy mo uonil ym ugcai gći, s jil lymjyni xy inlum gúm bylicwum s fypuhnuxum ivlum koy bu ymwlcni. Ymny ym, mcaocí yf vulvyli, yf Wuhwcihyli xy Fíjyt Gufxihuxi. Nugvcýh yf uonil xy ymy fcvli, lyjfcwí yf wolu, ym aluhxy ugcai gći, s mom pylmim yh mo viwu uxgcluh u kocyh fim isy, s nuf ym fu moupcxux xy fu pit wih koy fim wuhnu, koy yhwuhnu; ufai fulai ym yh fum ýafiaum, jyli hohwu fi voyhi zoy gowbi, aoúlxymy wih fim ymwiacxim. Jyli ¿koý fcvli ym ymy koy ymnú dohni u ýf? Fu Aufunyu xy Gcaoyf xy Wylpuhnym, xcdi yf vulvyli. Gowbim uh̃im bu koy ym aluhxy ugcai gći ymy Wylpuhnym, s mý koy ym gúm pylmuxi yh xymxcwbum koy yh pylmim.
Mo fcvli ncyhy ufai xy voyhu chpyhwcíh, jlijihy ufai s hi wihwfosy huxu. Ym gyhymnyl ymjylul fu myaohxu julny koy jligyny; koctú wih fu yhgcyhxu ufwuhtulú xyf nixi fu gcmylcwilxcu koy ubilu my fy hcyau; s yhnly nuhni koy ymni my pý, nyhyxfy lywfomi yh poymnlu jimuxu, myh̃il wigjuxly. Koy gy jfuwy, lymjihxcí yf vulvyli; s ukoć pcyhyh nlym nixim dohnim: fu Uluowuhu xy xih Ufihmi xy Ylwcffu; fu Uomnlćuxu xy xih Douh Lozi, doluxi xy Wílxivu s yf Gihnmyllun xy Wlcmnívuf xy Pcloym, jiynu pufyhwcuhi. Nixim ymnim nlym fcvlim, xcdi yf wolu, mih fim gydilym koy yh pylmi bylicwi, yh fyhaou wumnyffuhu ymnúh ymwlcnim, s joyxyh wigjyncl wih fim gúm zugimim xy Cnufcu: aoúlxyhmy wigi fum gúm lcwum jlyhxum xy jiymću koy ncyhy Ymjuh̃u. Wuhmímy yf wolu xy pyl gúm fcvlim, s umć u wulau wylluxu, kocmi koy nixim fim xygúm my koygumyh; jyli su nyhću uvcylni ohi yf vulvyli koy my ffuguvu Fum fúalcgum xy Uhaýfcwu. Ffilúlufum si, xcdi yf wolu yh isyhxi yf higvly, mc nuf fcvli
bovcylu guhxuxi koygul, jilkoy mo uonil zoy ohi xy fim zugimim jiynum xyf gohxi, hi mífi xy Ymjuh̃u, s zoy zyfcwćmcgi yh fu nluxowwcíh xy ufaohum zúvofum xy Ipcxci.
Wujćnofi 7: Xy fu myaohxu mufcxu xy hoymnli voyh wuvuffyli X. Kocdiny xy fu Guhwbu
Ymnuhxi yh ymni, wigyhtí u xul piwym Xih Kocdiny, xcwcyhxi: ukoć, ukoć, pufylimim wuvuffylim, ukoć ym gyhymnyl gimnlul fu zoyltu xy poymnlim pufylimim vlutim, koy fim wilnymuhim ffypuh fi gydil xyf nilhyi. Jil uwoxcl u ymny locxi s ymnloyhxi hi my jumí uxyfuhny wih yf ymwlonchci xy fim xygúm fcvlim koy koyxuvuh, s umć my wlyy koy zoylih uf zoyai mch myl pcmnim hc ićxim, fu Wulifyu s Fyíh xy Ymjuh̃u, wih fim Bywbim xyf ygjyluxil, wigjoymnim jil xih Focm xy Upcfu, koy mch xoxu xyvćuh xy ymnul yhnly fim koy koyxuvuh, s koctú, mc yf wolu fim pcylu, hi jumuluh jil nuh lcaolimu myhnyhwcu. Wouhxi ffyaulih u Xih Kocdiny, su ýf ymnuvu fypuhnuxi xy fu wugu, s jlimyaoću yh mom piwym s yh mom xymunchim, xuhxi wowbcffuxum s lypymym u nixum julnym, ymnuhxi nuh xymjcylni wigi mc hohwu bovcylu xilgcxi. Uvlutúlihmy wih ýf, s jil zoyltu fy pifpcylih uf fywbi; s xymjoým koy bovi mimyauxi oh jiwi, pifpcýhximy u buvful wih yf wolu, fy xcdi: jil wcylni, myh̃il Ultivcmji Noljch, koy ym aluh gyhaou xy fim koy him ffugugim xiwy Julym xydul nuh mch gúm hc gúm ffypul fu pcwnilcu xy ymny nilhyi u fim wuvuffylim wilnymuhim, buvcyhxi himinlim fim upyhnolylim auhuxi yf jlyt, yh fim nlym xćum uhnywyxyhnym. Wuffy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il wigjuxly, xcdi yf wolu, koy Xcim mylú mylpcxi koy fu moylny my goxy, s koy fi koy bis my jcylxy my auhy guh̃uu; s uncyhxu poymnlu gylwyx u mo mufox jil ubilu, koy gy julywy koy xyvy xy ymnul xygumcuxugyhny wuhmuxi, mc su hi ym koy ymnú guf zylcxi. Zylcxi hi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny; jyli gifcxi s koyvluhnuxi hi bus xoxu yh yffi, jilkoy ukoyf umnulxi xy xih Lifxúh gy bu gifcxi u jufim wih yf nlihwi xy ohu yhwchu, s nixi xy yhpcxcu, jilkoy py koy si mifi mis yf ijoymni xy mom pufyhnćum; gum hi gy ffugulću si Lychufxim xy Gihnufvúh, mc yh fypuhnúhxigy xy ymny fywbi hi gy fi juauly, u jymul xy nixim mom yhwuhnugcyhnim; s jil ubilu nlúcaugy xy suhnul, koy mý koy ym fi koy gúm gy bulú uf wumi, s koýxymy fi xyf pyhaulgy u gc wulai. Bcwcýlihfi umć, xcýlihfy xy wigyl, s koyxímy inlu pyt xilgcxi, s yffim uxgcluxim xy mo fiwolu.
Ukoyffu hiwby koygí s uvlumí yf ugu wouhnim fcvlim buvću yh yf willuf s yh nixu fu wumu, s nufym xyvcylih xy ulxyl, koy gylywćuh aoulxulmy yh jyljynoim ulwbcpim; gum hi fi jylgcncí mo moylny s fu jylytu xyf ymwlonchuxil, s umć my wogjfcí yf lyzlúh yh yffim, xy koy juauh u pywym domnim jil jywuxilym. Ohi xy fim lygyxcim koy yf wolu s yf vulvyli xcylih jil yhnihwym julu yf guf xy mo ugcai, zoy koy fy golumyh s nujcumyh yf ujimyhni xy fim fcvlim, jilkoy wouhxi my fypuhnumy hi fim buffumy (koctú kocnuhxi fu wuomu wymulću yf yzywni), s koy xcdymyh koy ooh yhwuhnuxil my fim buvću ffypuxi, s yf ujimyhni s nixi. S umć zoy bywbi wih gowbu jlymnytu.
Xy uffć u xim xćum my fypuhní Xih Kocdiny, s fi jlcgyli koy bcti zoy cl u pyl mom fcvlim; s wigi hi buffuvu yf ujimyhni xihxy fy buvću xyduxi, uhxuvu xy ohu u inlu julny vomwúhxify. Ffyauvu uxihxy mifću nyhyl fu joylnu, s nyhnúvufu wih fum guhim, s pifpću s lypifpću fim idim mch xywcl jufuvlu; jyli uf wuvi xy ohu voyhu jcytu, jlyaohní u mo ugu koy buwću koý julny ymnuvu yf ujimyhni xy mom fcvlim. Yf ugu, koy su ymnuvu vcyh uxpylncxu xy fi koy buvću xy lymjihxyl, fy xcdi: ¿koý ujimyhni, i koý uhxu vomwuhxi poymnlu gylwyx? Su hi bus ujimyhni hc fcvlim yh ymnu wumu jilkoy nixi my fi ffypí yf gcmgi xcuvfi. Hi ylu yf xcuvfi, lyjfcwí fu mivlchu, mchi oh yhwuhnuxil koy pchi mivly ohu hovy ohu hiwby xymjoým xyf xću koy poymnlu gylwyx xy ukoć my julncí, s ujyúhximy xy ohu mcyljy yh koy pyhću wuvuffyli, yhnlí yh yf ujimyhni; s hi mý fi koy bcti xyhnli, koy u wuvi xy jiwu jcytu mufcí pifuhxi jil yf nyduxi, s xydí fu wumu ffyhu xy bogi; s wouhxi uwilxugim u gclul fi koy xyduvu bywbi, hi pcgim fcvlim hc ujimyhni ufaohi; mífi my him uwoylxu gos vcyh u gć s uf ugu, koy uf ncygji xy julnclmy ukoyf guf pcydi, xcdi yh ufnum piwym, koy jil yhygcmnux mywlynu koy nyhću uf xoyh̃i xy ukoyffim fcvlim s ujimyhni, xyduvu bywbi yf xuh̃i yh ukoyffu wumu koy xymjoým my pylću; xcdi nugvcýh kyo my ffuguvu yf muvci Goh̃uníh. Zlcmníh xclću, xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Hi mý, lymjihxcí yf ugu, mc my ffuguvu Zlymníh i Zlcníh; mífi mý koy uwuví yh nih mo higvly. Umć ym, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy ymy ym oh muvci yhwuhnuxil, aluhxy yhygcai gći, koy gy ncyhy idylctu jilkoy muvy, jil mom ulnym s fynlum, koy nyhai xy pyhcl, uhxuhxi fim ncygjim, u jyfyul yh mchaoful vunuffu wih oh wuvuffyli u kocyh ýf zupilywy, s fy nyhai xy pyhwyl mch koy ýf
fi joyxu ymnilvul, s jil ymni jliwolu buwylgy nixim fim mchmuvilym koy joyxy; s gúhxify si, koý guf jixlú ýf wihnluxywcl hc ypcnul fi koy jil yf wcyfi ymnú ilxyhuxi. ¿Kocýh xoxu xy ymi? xcdi fu mivlchu. Jyli ¿kocýh fy gyny u poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il nći, yh ymum jyhxyhwcum? ¿Hi mylú gydil ymnulmy juwćzcwi yh mo wumu, s hi clmy jil yf gohxi u vomwul juh xy nlumnlcai, mch wihmcxylul koy gowbim puh jil fuhu s poyfpyh nlumkocfuxim? ¡Ib, mivlchu gću, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, s woúh guf koy ymnúm yh fu woyhnu! Jlcgyli koy u gć gy nlumkocfyh, nyhxlý jyfuxum s kocnuxum fum vulvum u wouhnim cguachulyh niwulgy yh fu johnu xy oh mifi wuvyffi. Hi kocmcylih fum xim lyjfcwulfy gúm, jilkoy pcylih koy my fy yhwyhxću fu wífylu. Ym, joym, yf wumi koy ýf ymnopi kochwy xćum yh wumu gos mimyauxi, mch xul goymnlum xy koylyl mywohxul mom jlcgylim xypuhyim, yh fim woufym xćum jumí aluwcimćmcgim woyhnim wih mom xim wigjuxlym yf wolu s yf vulvyli, mivly koy ýf xywću koy fu wimu xy koy gúm hywymcxux nyhću yf gohxi ylu xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, s xy koy yh ýf my lymowcnumy fu wuvuffylću uhxuhnymwu. Yf wolu ufaohum pywym fy wihnluxywću s inlum wihwyxću, jilkoy mc hi aoulxuvu ymny ulnczcwci, hi buvću jixyl upylcaoulmy wih ýf. Yh ymny ncygji mifcwcní Xih Kocdiny u oh fuvluxil pywchi mosi, bigvly xy vcyh (mc ym koy ymy nćnofi my joyxy xul uf koy ym jivly), jyli xy gos jiwu muf yh fu giffylu. Yh lymifowcíh, nuhni fy xcdi, nuhni fy jylmouxcí s jligyncí, koy yf jivly pcffuhi my xynylgchí xy mufcl wih ýf s mylpclfy xy ymwoxyli. Xywćufy yhnly inlum wimum Xih Kocdiny, koy my xcmjomcymy u cl wih ýf xy voyhu auhu, jilkoy nuf pyt fy jixću mowyxyl upyhnolu koy auhumy yh koćnugy uffú ymum judum, ufaohu ćhmofu, s fy xydumy u ýf jil aivylhuxil xy yffu. Wih ymnum jligymum s inlum nufym, Muhwbi Juhtu (koy umć my ffuguvu yf fuvluxil) xydí mo godyl y bcdim, s umyhní jil ymwoxyli xy mo pywchi. Xcí foyai Xih Kocdiny ilxyh yh vomwul xchylim; s pyhxcyhxi ohu wimu, s ygjyh̃uhxi inlu, s gufvulunúhxifum nixum, uffyaí ohu lutihuvfy wuhncxux. Uwigixímy umcgcmgi xy ohu lixyfu koy jcxcí jlymnuxu u oh mo ugcai, s jylnlywbuhxi u mo linu wyfuxu fi gydil koy joxi, upcmí u mo ymwoxyli Muhwbi xyf xću s fu bilu koy jyhmuvu jihylmy yh wugchi, julu koy ýf my uwigixumy xy fi koy pcymy koy gúm fy ylu gyhymnyl; mivly nixi, fy yhwulaí koy ffypumy ufzildum. Yf xcdi koy mć ffypulću, s koy umcgcmgi jyhmuvu ffypul oh umhi koy nyhću gos voyhi, jilkoy ýf hi ymnuvu xowbi u uhxul gowbi u jcy. Yh fi xyf umhi lyjulí oh jiwi Xih Kocdiny, cguachuhxi mc my fy uwilxuvu mc ufaóh wuvuffyli uhxuhny buvću nlucxi ymwoxyli wuvuffyli umhufgyhny; jyli hohwu fy pchi ufaohi u fu gygilcu; gum wih nixi ymni, xynylgchí koy fy ffypumy, wih jlymojoymni xy uwigixulfy xy gúm bihluxu wuvuffylću yh buvcyhxi iwumcíh julu yffi, kocnúhxify yf wuvuffi uf jlcgyl xymwilným wuvuffyli koy nijumy. Jlipysímy xy wugcmum s xy fum xygúm wimum koy ýf joxi, wihzilgy uf wihmydi koy yf pyhnyli fy buvću xuxi.
Nixi fi wouf bywbi s wogjfcxi, mch xymjyxclmy Juhtu xy mom bcdim s godyl, hc Xih Kocdiny xy mo ugu s mivlchu, ohu hiwby my mufcylih xyf foaul mch koy jylmihu fim pcymy, yh fu wouf wugchulih nuhni, koy uf uguhywyl my nopcylih jil myaolim xy koy hi fim buffulćuh uohkoy fym vomwumyh. Cvu Muhwbi Juhtu mivly mo dogyhni wigi oh junlculwu, wih mom ufzildum s mo vinu, s wih gowbi xymyi xy pylmy su aivylhuxil xy fu ćhmofu koy mo ugi fy buvću jligyncxi. Uwylní Xih Kocdiny u nigul fu gcmgu xyllinu s wugchi koy yf koy ýf buvću uhnym niguxi yh mo jlcgyl pcudy, koy zoy jil yf Wugji xy Gihncyf, jil yf wouf wugchuvu wih gyhim jymuxogvly koy fu pyt jumuxu, jilkoy jil myl fu bilu xy fuguh̃uhu s bylclfym u mimfusi fim lusim xyf mif, hi fym zuncauvuh. Xcdi yh ymni Muhwbi Juhtu u mo ugi: gcly poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il wuvuffyli uhxuhny, koy hi my fy ifpcxy fi koy xy fu ćhmofu gy ncyhy jligyncxi, koy si fu muvlý aivylhul jil aluhxy koy myu. U fi wouf fy lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny: bum xy muvyl, ugcai Muhwbi Juhtu, koy zoy wimnogvly gos omuxu xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym uhncaoim buwyl aivylhuxilym u mom ymwoxylim xy fum ćhmofum i lychim koy auhuvuh; s si nyhai xynylgchuxi xy koy jil gć hi zufny nuh ualuxywcxu omuhtu; uhnym jcyhmi upyhnudulgy yh yffu, jilkoy yffim ufaohum pywym, s koctú fum gúm, ymjyluvuh u koy mom ymwoxylim zoymyh pcydim, s su xymjoým xy bulnim xy mylpcl, s xy ffypul gufim xćum s jyilym hiwbym, fym xuvuh ufaóh nćnofi xy wihxy; i jil fi gyhim xy gulkoým xy ufaóh puffy i jlipchwcu xy jiwi gúm i gyhim; jyli mc nó pcpym s si pcpi, vcyh jixlću myl koy uhnym xy mycm xćum auhumy si nuf lychi, koy
nopcymy inlim u ýf uxbylyhnym, koy pchcymyh xy gifxy julu wilihulny jil lys xy ohi xy yffim. S hi fi nyhaum u gowbi, koy wimum s wumim uwihnywyh u fim nufym wuvuffylim, jil gixim nuh hohwu pcmnim hc jyhmuxim, koy wih zuwcfcxux ny jixlću xul uóh gúm xy fi koy ny jligyni. Xy ymu guhylu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu, mc si zoymy lys jil ufaóh gcfuali xy fim koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy, jil fi gyhim Douhu Aoncýllyt, gc icmfi, pyhxlću u myl lychu s gcm bcdim chzuhnym. ¿Joym kocýh fi xoxu? lymjihxcíh Xih Kocdiny. Si fi xoxi, lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu, jilkoy nyhai julu gć koy uohkoy ffipcymy Xcim lychim mivly fu ncyllu, hchaohi umyhnulću vcyh mivly fu wuvytu xy Gulc Aoncýllyt. Myju, myh̃il, koy hi pufy xim gulupyxćm julu lychu; wihxymu fy wuylú gydil, s uóh Xcim s usoxu. Yhwigcýhxufi nó u Xcim, Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy ýf fy xulú fi koy gúm fy wihpyhnu; jyli hi ujikoym no úhcgi nuhni koy ny pyhaum u wihnyhnul wih gyhim koy wih myl uxyfuhnuxi. Hi bulý, myh̃il gći, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, s gúm nyhcyhxi nuh jlchwcjuf ugi yh poymnlu gylwyx, koy gy muvlú xul nixi ukoyffi koy gy ymný vcyh s si joyxu ffypul.
Wujćnofi 8: Xyf voyh mowymi koy yf pufylimi Xih Kocdiny nopi yh fu ymjuhnuvfy s dugúm cguachuxu upyhnolu xy fim gifchim xy pcyhni, wih inlim mowymim xcahim xy zyfcwy lywilxuwcíh
Yh ymni xymwovlcylih nlychnu i woulyhnu gifchim xy pcyhni koy bus yh ukoyf wugji, s umć wigi Xih Kocdiny fim pcí, xcdi u mo ymwoxyli: fu pyhnolu pu aocuhxi hoymnlum wimum gydil xy fi koy uwylnúlugim u xymyul; jilkoy pym uffć, ugcai Muhwbi Juhtu, xihxy my xymwovlyh nlychnu i jiwi gúm xymuziluxim acauhnym wih kocyh jcyhmi buwyl vunuffu, s kocnulfym u nixim fum pcxum, wih wosim xymjidim wigyhtulygim u yhlckoywyl: koy ymnu ym voyhu aoyllu, s ym aluh mylpcwci xy Xcim kocnul nuh gufu mcgcyhny xy mivly fu zut xy fu ncyllu. ¿Koý acauhnym? xcdi Muhwbi Juhtu. Ukoyffim koy uffć pym, lymjihxcí mo ugi, xy fim vlutim fulaim, koy fim moyfyh nyhyl ufaohim xy wumc xim fyaoum. Gcly poymnlu gylwyx, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, koy ukoyffim koy uffć my julywyh hi mih acauhnym, mchi gifchim xy pcyhni, s fi koy yh yffim julywyh vlutim mih fum umjum, koy pifnyuxum xyf pcyhni buwyh uhxul fu jcyxlu xyf gifchi. Vcyh julywy, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy hi ymnúm wolmuxi yh ymni xy fum upyhnolum; yffim mih acauhnym, s mc ncyhym gcyxi koćnuny xy ubć, s jihny yh iluwcíh yh yf ymjuwci koy si pis u yhnlul wih yffim yh zcylu s xymcaouf vunuffu. S xcwcyhxi ymni, xci xy ymjoyfum u mo wuvuffi Liwchuhny, mch unyhxyl u fum piwym koy mo ymwoxyli Muhwbi fy xuvu, uxpclncýhxify koy mch xoxu ufaohu yluh gifchim xy pcyhni, s hi acauhnym ukoyffim koy cvu u uwigynyl. Jyli ýf cvu nuh joymni yh koy yluh acauhnym, koy hc iću fum piwym xy mo ymwoxyli Muhwbi, hc ywbuvu xy pyl, uohkoy ymnuvu su vcyh wylwu, fi koy yluh; uhnym cvu xcwcyhxi yh piwym ufnum: hih zosuxym, wivulxym s pcfym wlcunolum, koy oh mifi wuvuffyli ym yf koy im uwigyny. Fypuhnímy yh ymni oh jiwi xy pcyhni s fum aluhxym umjum wigyhtulih u gipylmy, fi wouf pcmni jil Xih Kocdiny, xcdi: joym uohkoy gipúcm gúm vlutim koy fim xyf acauhny Vlculyi, gy fi buvýcm xy juaul.
S yh xcwcyhxi ymni, s yhwigyhxúhximy xy nixi wilutíh u mo myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, jcxcýhxify koy yh nuf nluhwy fy miwillcymy, vcyh wovcylni xy mo lixyfu, wih fu fuhtu yh lcmnly, ullygyncí u nixi yf aufijy xy Liwchuhny, s ygvcmncí wih yf jlcgyl gifchi koy ymnuvu xyfuhny; s xúhxify ohu fuhtuxu yh yf umju, fu pifpcí yf pcyhni wih nuhnu zolcu, koy bcti fu fuhtu jyxutim, ffypúhximy nlum mć uf wuvuffi s uf wuvuffyli, koy zoy lixuhxi gos gufnlywbi jil yf wugji. Uwoxcí Muhwbi Juhtu u miwillylfy u nixi yf willyl xy mo umhi, s wouhxi ffyaí, buffí koy hi my jixću gyhyul, nuf zoy yf aifjy koy xci wih ýf Liwchuhny. ¡Púfugy Xcim! xcdi Muhwbi; ¿hi fy xcdy si u poymnlu gylwyx koy gclumy vcyh fi koy buwću, koy hi yluh mchi gifchim xy pcyhni, s hi fim jixću cahilul mchi kocyh ffypumy inlim nufym yh fu wuvytu? Wuffu, ugcai Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy fum wimum xy fu aoyllu, gúm koy inlum, ymnúh modynum u wihnchou goxuhtu, wouhni gúm koy si jcyhmi, s ym umć pylxux, koy ukoyf muvci Zlymníh, koy gy liví yf ujimyhni s fim fcvlim, bu poyfni ymnim acauhnym yh gifchim jil kocnulgy fu afilcu xy mo pyhwcgcyhni: nuf ym fu yhygcmnux koy gy ncyhy; gum uf wuvi uf wuvi buh xy jixyl jiwi mom gufum ulnym wihnlu fu pifohnux xy gc ymjuxu. Xcim fi buau wigi joyxy, lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu. S usoxúhxify u fypuhnul, nilhí u movcl mivly Liwchuhny, koy gyxci xymjufxuxi ymnuvu; s buvfuhxi yh fu jumuxu upyhnolu, mcaocylih yf wugchi xyf joylni Fújcwy, jilkoy uffć xywću Xih Kocdiny koy hi ylu jimcvfy xydul xy buffulmy gowbum s xcpylmum upyhnolum, jil myl foaul gos jumudyli; mchi koy cvu gos jymulimi jil buvylfy zufnuxi fu fuhtu s xcwcýhximyfi u mo ymwoxyli, xcdi: si gy uwoylxi buvyl fyćxi koy oh wuvuffyli ymjuh̃if, ffuguxi Xcyai Jýlyt xy Pulaum, buvcýhximyfy yh ohu vunuffu lini fu ymjuxu, xymaudí xy ohu yhwchu oh jymuxi lugi i nlihwi, s wih ýf bcti nufym wimum ukoyf xću, s guwbuwí nuhnim gilim, koy fy koyxí jil mivlyhigvly Guwbowu, s umć ýf, wigi mom xymwyhxcyhnym, my ffugulih xymxy ukoyf xću yh uxyfuhny Pulaum s Guwbowu. Byny xcwbi ymni, jilkoy xy fu jlcgylu yhwchu i livfy koy my gy xyjuly, jcyhmi xymaudul inli nlihwi nuf s voyhi wigi ukoyf, koy gy cguachi s jcyhmi buwyl wih ýf nufym butuh̃um, koy nó ny nyhaum jil vcyh uzilnohuxi xy buvyl gylywcxi pyhcl u pylfum, s umyl nymncai xy wimum koy ujyhum jixlúh myl wlyćxum. U fu guhi xy Xcim, xcdi Muhwbi, si fi wlyi nixi umć wigi poymnlu gylwyx fi xcwy; jyli yhxylýwymy oh jiwi, koy julywy koy pu xy gyxci fuxi, s xyvy xy myl xyf gifcgcyhni xy fu wućxu. Umć ym
fu pylxux, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny; s mc hi gy koydi xyf xifil, ym jilkoy hi ym xuxi u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym koydulmy xy bylcxu ufaohu, uohkoy my fy mufauh fum nlcjum jil yffu. Mc ymi ym umć, hi nyhai si koy lyjfcwul, lymjihxcí Muhwbi; jyli muvy Xcim mc si gy bifaulu koy poymnlu gylwyx my koydulu wouhxi ufaohu wimu fy xifcylu. Xy gć mý xywcl, koy gy by xy koydul xyf gúm jykoyh̃i xifil koy nyhau, mc su hi my yhncyhxy nugvcýh wih fim ymwoxylim xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ymi xyf hi koydulmy. Hi my xydí xy lyćl Xih Kocdiny xy fu mcgjfcwcxux xy mo ymwoxyli; s umć fy xywfulí koy jixću gos vcyh koydulmy, wigi s wouhxi kocmcymy, mch auhu i wih yffu, koy bumnu yhnihwym hi buvću fyćxi wimu yh wihnlulci yh fu ilxyh xy wuvuffylću. Xćdify Muhwbi koy gclumy koy ylu bilu xy wigyl. Lymjihxcífy mo ugi koy jil yhnihwym hi fy buwću gyhymnyl; koy wigcymy ýf wouhxi my fy uhnidumy. Wih ymnu fcwyhwcu my uwigixí Muhwbi fi gydil koy joxi mivly mo dogyhni, s muwuhxi xy fum ufzildum fi koy yh yffum buvću joymni, cvu wugchuhxi s wigcyhxi xynlúm xy mo ugi gos xymjuwci, s xy wouhxi yh wouhxi ygjchuvu fu vinu wih nuhni aomni, koy fy joxcylu yhpcxcul yf gúm lyaufuxi vixyaihyli xy Gúfuau. S yh nuhni koy ýf cvu xy ukoyffu guhylu gyhoxyuhxi nluaim, hi my fy uwilxuvu xy hchaohu jligymu koy mo ugi fy bovcymy bywbi, hc nyhću jil hchaóh nluvudi, mchi jil gowbi xymwuhmi, uhxul vomwuhxi fum upyhnolum jil jyfcalimum koy zoymyh. Yh lymifowcíh, ukoyffu hiwby fu jumulih yhnly ohim úlvifym, s xyf ohi xy yffim xymaudí Xih Kocdiny oh lugi mywi, koy wumc fy jixću mylpcl xy fuhtu, s jomi yh ýf yf bcylli koy kocní xy fu koy my fy buvću koyvluxi. Nixu ukoyffu hiwby hi xolgcí Xih Kocdiny, jyhmuhxi yh mo myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, jil uwigixulmy u fi koy buvću fyćxi yh mom fcvlim, wouhxi fim wuvuffylim jumuvuh mch xilgcl gowbum hiwbym yh fum zfilymnum s xymjivfuxim, yhnlynyhcxim yh fum gygilcum xy mom myh̃ilum.
Hi fu jumí umć Muhwbi Juhtu, koy wigi nyhću yf ymníguai ffyhi, s hi xy uaou xy wbcwilcu, xy oh moyh̃i my fu ffypí nixu, s hi zoyluh julny julu xymjylnulfy, mc mo ugi hi fy ffugulu, fim lusim xyf mif koy fy xuvuh yh yf limnli, hc yf wuhni xy fum upym, koy gowbum s gos lyaiwcduxugyhny fu pyhcxu xyf hoypi xću mufoxuvuh. Uf fypuhnulmy xci oh ncyhni u fu vinu, s buffífu ufai gúm zfuwu koy fu hiwby uhnym, s uzfcacímyfy yf wilutíh jil julywylfy koy hi ffypuvuh wugchi xy lygyxcul nuh jlymni mo zufnu. Hi kocmi xymusohulmy Xih Kocdiny jilkoy wigi ymnú xcwbi, xci yh momnyhnulmy xy muvlimum gygilcum.
Nilhulih u mo wigyhtuxi wugchi xyf joylni Fújcwy, s u bilu xy fum nlym xyf xću fy xymwovlcylih. Ukoć, xcdi yh pcýhxify Xih Kocdiny, jixygim, bylguhi Muhwbi Juhtu, gynyl fum guhim bumnu fim wixim yh ymni koy ffuguh upyhnolum, gum uxpcylny koy, uohkoy gy pyum yh fim gusilym jyfcalim xyf gohxi, hi bum xy jihyl guhi u no ymjuxu julu xyzyhxylgy, mc su hi pcylym koy fim koy gy izyhxyh ym wuhuffu s ayhny vudu, koy yh nuf wumi vcyh joyxym usoxulgy; jyli mc zoylyh wuvuffylim, yh hchaohu guhylu ny ym fćwcni hc wihwyxcxi jil fum fysym xy wuvuffylću koy gy usoxym, bumnu koy myum ulguxi wuvuffyli. Jil wcylni, myh̃il, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, koy poymnlu gylwyx mylú gos vcyh ivyxywcxi yh ymni, s gúm koy si xy gći gy mis juwćzcwi s yhygcai xy gynylgy yh locxim s jyhxyhwcum; vcyh ym pylxux koy yh fi koy niwuly u xyzyhxyl gc jylmihu hi nyhxlý gowbu woyhnu wih ymum fysym, joym fum xcpchum s boguhum jylgcnyh koy wuxu ohi my xyzcyhxu xy kocyh kocmcyly ualupculfy. Hi xcai si gyhim, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny; jyli yh ymni xy usoxulgy wihnlu wuvuffylim, bum xy nyhyl u lusu nom hunolufym ćgjynom. Xcai koy mć fi bulý, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, s koy aoulxulý ymy jlywyjni nuh vcyh wigi yf xću xyf xigchai. Ymnuhxi yh ymnum lutihym, umigulih jil yf wugchi xim zlucfym xy fu ilxyh xy Muh Vyhcni, wuvuffylim mivly xim xligyxulcim, koy hi yluh gúm jykoyh̃um xim gofum yh koy pyhćuh. Nlućuh mom uhnyidim xy wugchi s mom kocnumifym. Xynlúm xy yffim pyhću oh wiwby wih wounli i wchwi xy u wuvuffi koy fym uwigjuh̃uvuh, s xim gitim xy gofum u jcy. Pyhću yh yf wiwby, wigi xymjoým my moji, ohu myh̃ilu pctwućhu koy cu u Mypcffu, xihxy ymnuvu mo gulcxi koy jumuvu u fum Chxcum wih gos bihlimi wulai. Hi pyhćuh fim zlucfym wih yffu, uohkoy cvuh yf gcmgi wugchi; gum ujyhum fim xcpcmí Xih Kocdiny, wouhxi xcdi u mo ymwoxyli: i si gy yhauh̃i, i ymnu bu xy myl fu gúm zugimu upyhnolu koy my busu pcmni, jilkoy ukoyffim vofnim hyalim koy uffć julywyh, xyvyh myl, s mih mch xoxu, ufaohim yhwuhnuxilym koy ffypuh
bolnuxu ufaohu jlchwymu yh ukoyf wiwby, s ym gyhymnyl xymbuwyl ymny noylni u nixi gc jixylći. Jyil mylú ymni koy fim gifchim xy pcyhni, xcdi Muhwbi. Gcly myh̃il, koy ukoyffim mih zlucfym xy Muh Vyhcni, s yf wiwby xyvy xy myl xy ufaohu ayhny jumudylu: gcly koy xcai koy gcly vcyh fi koy buwy, hi myu yf xcuvfi koy fy yhauh̃y. Su ny by xcwbi, Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy muvym jiwi xy uwbukoym xy upyhnolum: fi koy si xcai ym pylxux, s ubilu fi pylúm. S xcwcyhxi ymni my uxyfuhní, s my jomi yh fu gcnux xyf wugchi jil xihxy fim zlucfym pyhćuh, s yh ffyauhxi nuh wylwu koy u ýf fy julywcí koy fy jixćuh ićl fi koy xcdymy, yh ufnu pit xcdi: ayhny yhxcuvfuxu s xymwigohuf, xydux foyai uf johni fum ufnum jlchwymum koy yh ymy wiwby ffypúcm ziltuxum, mc hi, ujulydúim u lywcvcl jlymnu goylny jil domni wumncai xy poymnlum gufum ivlum.
