Yh zch, mo myaohxu julny mcaocyhxi fu nluxowwcíh, wihnchouvu xy ymnu guhylu: joymnum s fypuhnuxum yh ufni fum wilnuxilum ymjuxum xy fim xim pufylimim s yhiduxim wigvuncyhnym, hi julywću mchi koy ymnuvuh ugyhutuhxi uf wcyfi, u fu ncyllu s uf uvcmgi: nuf ylu yf xyhoyxi s wihnchyhny koy nyhćuh. S yf jlcgyli koy zoy u xymwulaul yf aifjy zoy yf wifýlcwi pctwućhi, yf wouf zoy xuxi wih nuhnu zoyltu s nuhnu zolcu, koy u hi pifpýlmyfy fu ymjuxu yh yf wugchi, ukoyf mifi aifjy zoylu vumnuhny julu xul zch u mo lcaolimu wihncyhxu, s u nixum fum upyhnolum xy hoymnli wuvuffyli; gum fu voyhu moylny, koy julu gusilym wimum fy nyhću aoulxuxi, nilwcí fu ymjuxu xy mo wihnlulci, xy gixi koy uohkoy fy uwylní yh yf bigvli ctkocylxi, hi fy bcti inli xuh̃i kyo xymulgulfy nixi ukoyf fuxi, ffypúhxify xy wugchi aluh julny xy fu wyfuxu wih fu gcnux xy fu ilydu, koy nixi yffi wih ymjuhnimu lochu pchi uf moyfi, xydúhxify gos gufnlywbi. ¡Púfugy Xcim, s kocýh mylú ukoyf koy voyhugyhny joyxu wihnul ubilu fu luvcu koy yhnlí yh yf wilutíh xy hoymnli guhwbyai, pcýhximy julul xy ukoyffu guhylu! Hi my xcau gúm, mchi koy zoy xy guhylu koy my uftí xy hoypi yh fim ymnlcvim, s ujlynuhxi gúm fu ymjuxu yh fum xim guhim, wih nuf
zolcu xymwulaí mivly yf pctwućhi, uwylnúhxify xy ffyhi mivly fu ufgibuxu s mivly fu wuvytu, koy mch myl julny nuh voyhu xyzyhmu, wigi mc wusylu mivly ýf ohu gihnuh̃u, wigyhtí u ywbul muhaly jil fum hulcwym, s jil fu viwu, s jil fim ićxim, s u xul goymnlum xy wuyl xy fu gofu uvudi, xy xihxy wusylu mch xoxu, mc hi my uvlutulu wih yf woyffi; jyli wih nixi ymi muwí fim jcym xy fim ymnlcvim, s foyai mifní fim vlutim, s fu gofu ymjuhnuxu xyf nyllcvfy aifjy xci u willyl jil yf wugji, s u jiwim wilwipim xci wih mo xoyh̃i yh ncyllu. Ymnúvumyfi wih gowbi mimcyai gcluhxi Xih Kocdiny, s wigi fi pci wuyl, mufní xy mo wuvuffi s wih gowbu fcaylytu my ffyaí u ýf, s jihcýhxify fu johnu xy fu ymjuxu yh fim idim, fy xcdi koy my lchxcymy; mc hi, koy fy wilnulću fu wuvytu.
Ymnuvu yf pctwućhi nuh nolvuxi koy hi jixću lymjihxyl jufuvlu, s ýf fi jumulu guf, myaóh ymnuvu wcyai Xih Kocdiny, mc fum myh̃ilum xyf wiwby, koy bumnu yhnihwym wih aluh xymgusi buvćuh gcluxi fu jyhxyhwcu, hi zoyluh uxihxy ymnuvu s fy jcxcyluh wih gowbi yhwulywcgcyhni fym bcwcylu nuh aluhxy gylwyx s zupil xy jylxihul fu pcxu u ukoyf mo ymwoxyli; u fi wouf Xih Kocdiny lymjihxcí wih gowbi yhnihi s alupyxux: jil wcylni, zylgimum myh̃ilum, si mis gos wihnyhni xy buwyl fi koy gy jyxćm; gum bu xy myl wih ohu wihxcwcíh s wihwylni, s ym koy ymny wuvuffyli gu bu xy jligynyl xy cl uf foaul xyf Nivimi, s jlymyhnulmy xy gc julny uhny fu mch jul xih̃u Xofwchyu, julu koy yffu buau xy ýf fi koy gúm zoyly xy mo pifohnux. Fum nygylimum s xymwihmifuxum myh̃ilum, mch yhnlul yh woyhnu xy fi koy Xih Kocdiny jyxću, s mch jlyaohnul kocýh Xofwchyu zoymy, fy jligyncylih koy yf ymwoxyli bulću nixi ukoyffi koy xy mo julny fy zoymy guhxuxi: joym yh zy xy ymu jufuvlu, si hi fy bulý gúm xuh̃i, joymni koy gy fi nyhću vcyh gylywcxi.
Wujćnofi 10: Xy fim aluwcimim lutihugcyhnim koy jumulih yhnly X. Kocdiny s Muhwbi Juhtu mo ymwoxyli
Su yh ymny ncygji my buvću fypuhnuxi Muhwbi Juhtu ufai gufnlunuxi xy fim gitim xy fim zlucfym, s buvću ymnuxi unyhni u fu vunuffu xy mo myh̃il Xih Kocdiny, s liauvu u Xcim yh mo wilutíh zoymy mylpcxi xy xulfy pcwnilcu s koy yh yffu auhumy ufaohu ćhmofu xy xihxy fy bcwcymy aivylhuxil, wigi my fi buvću jligyncxi. Pcyhxi, joym, su uwuvuxu fu jyhxyhwcu, s koy mo ugi pifpću u movcl mivly Liwchuhny, ffyaí u nyhylfy yf ymnlcvi, s uhnym koy movcymy my bchwí xy lixcffum xyfuhny xy ýf, s umcýhxify xy fu guhi, my fu vymí s fy xcdi: myu poymnlu gylwyx mylpcxi, myh̃il Xih Kocdiny gći, xy xulgy yf aivcylhi xy fu ćhmofu koy yh ymnu lcaolimu jyhxyhwcu my bu auhuxi, koy jil aluhxy koy myu, si gy mcyhni wih zoyltum xy muvylfu aivylhul nuf s nuh vcyh wigi inli koy busu aivylhuxi ćhmofum yh yf gohxi. U fi wouf lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny: uxpylncx, bylguhi Muhwbi, koy ymnu upyhnolu, s fum u ymnum mygyduhnym, hi mih upyhnolum xy ćhmofum, mchi xy yhwlowcduxum, yh fum woufym hi my auhu inlu wimu koy muwul linu fu wuvytu, i ohu ilydu gyhim; nyhyx juwcyhwcu, koy upyhnolum my izlywylúh, xihxy hi mifugyhny im joyxu buwyl aivylhuxil, mchi gúm uxyfuhny. Ualuxywcímyfi gowbi Muhwbi, s vymúhxify inlu pyt fu guhi s fu zufxu xy fu filcau, fy usoxí u movcl mivly Liwchuhny, s ýf movcí mivly mo umhi, s wigyhtí u myaocl u mo myh̃il, koy u jumi ncluxi, mch xymjyxclmy hc buvful gúm wih fum xyf wiwby, my yhnlí jil oh vimkoy koy uffć dohni ymnuvu.
Myaoćufy Muhwbi u nixi nliny xy mo dogyhni; jyli wugchuvu nuhni Liwchuhny, koy, pcýhximy koyxul unlúm, fy zoy ziltimi xul piwym u mo ugi, koy my uaoulxumy. Bćtifi umć Xih Kocdiny, nyhcyhxi fum lcyhxum u Liwchuhny bumnu koy ffyaumy mo wuhmuxi ymwoxyli, yf wouf yh ffyauhxi fy xcdi: julýwygy, myh̃il, koy mylću uwylnuxi clhim u lynluyl u ufaohu cafymcu, koy, myaóh koyxí gufnlywbi ukoyf wih kocyh wigvuncmnycm, hi mylú gowbi koy xyh hincwcu xyf wumi u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux, s him jlyhxuh; s u zy koy mc fi buwyh, koy jlcgyli koy mufaugim xy fu wúlwyf, koy him bu xy moxul yf biji. Wuffu, xcdi Xih Kocdiny. ¿S xíhxy bum pcmni nó i fyćxi dugúm koy wuvuffyli uhxuhny busu mcxi joymni uhny fu domncwcu, jil gúm bigcwcxcim koy busu wigyncxi? Si hi mý huxu xy igywcffim, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, hc yh gc pcxu fy wuný u hchaohi; mífi mý koy fu Muhnu Bylguhxux ncyhy koy pyl wih fim koy jyfyuh yh yf wugji, s yh yminli hi gy yhnlygyni. Joym hi nyhaum jyhu, ugcai, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy si ny muwulý xy fum guhim xy fim wufxyim, wouhni gúm xy fum xy fu Bylguhxux. Jyli xcgy jil no pcxu: ¿bum nó pcmni gúm pufylimi wuvuffyli koy si yh nixi fi xymwovcylni xy fu ncyllu? ¿Bum fyćxi yh bcmnilcum inli koy nyhau hc busu nyhcxi gúm vlći yh uwigynyl, gúm ufcyhni yh yf jylmypylul, gúm xymnlytu yh yf bylcl, hc gúm guh̃u yh yf xyllcvul? Fu pylxux myu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, koy si hi by fyćxi hchaohu bcmnilcu dugúm, jilkoy hc mý fyyl hc ymwlcvcl; gum fi koy imulý ujimnul ym koy gúm unlypcxi ugi koy poymnlu gylwyx si hi fy by mylpcxi yh nixim fim xćum xy gc pcxu, s kocylu Xcim koy ymnim unlypcgcyhnim hi my juaoyh xihxy nyhai xcwbi. Fi koy fy loyai u poymnlu gylwyx ym koy my woly, koy my fy pu gowbu muhaly xy ymu ilydu, koy ukoć nlucai bcfum s oh jiwi xy ohaöyhni vfuhwi yh fum ufzildum.
Nixi ymni zoylu vcyh ymwomuxi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, mc u gć my gy uwilxulu xy buwyl ohu lyxigu xyf vúfmugi xy Zcyluvlúm, koy wih mífi ohu ainu my ubilluluh ncygji s gyxcwchum. ¿Koý lyxigu s koý vúfmugi ym ymy? xcdi Muhwbi Juhtu. Xy oh vúfmugi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, xy kocyh nyhai fu lywynu yh fu gygilcu, wih yf wouf hi bus koy nyhyl nygil u fu goylny, hc bus koy jyhmul gilcl xy zylcxu ufaohu; s umć, wouhxi si fy buau s ny fy xý, hi ncyhym gúm koy buwyl mchi koy wouhxi pcylym koy yh ufaohu vunuffu gy buh julncxi jil gyxci xyf woylji, wigi gowbum pywym moyfy uwihnywyl, vihcnugyhny fu julny xyf woylji koy bovcyly wućxi yh yf moyfi, s wih gowbu moncfytu, uhnym koy fu muhaly my bcyfy, fu jihxlúm mivly fu inlu gcnux koy koyxuly yh fu mcffu, uxpclncyhxi xy yhwuduffi caoufgyhny s uf domni. Foyai gy xulúm u vyvyl mifim xim nluaim xyf vúfmugi koy by xcwbi, s pylúmgy koyxul gúm muhi koy ohu guhtuhu. Mc ymi bus, xcdi Juhtu, si lyhohwci xymxy ukoć yf aivcylhi xy fu jligyncxu ćhmofu, s hi kocyli inlu wimu yh juai xy gcm gowbim s voyhim mylpcwcim, mchi koy poymnlu gylwyx gy xdý fu lywynu xy ymy ymnlyguxi fcwil, koy julu gć nyhai koy pufxlú fu ihtu xihxy kocylu gúm xy xim lyufym, s hi by
gyhymnyl si gúm julu jumul ymnu pcxu bihluxu s xymwuhmuxugyhny; jyli ym xy muvyl ubilu mc ncyhy gowbu wimnu yf buwyffu. Wih gyhim xy nlym lyufym my joyxyh buwyl nlym utogvlym, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny. ¡Jywuxil xy gć! lyjfcwí Muhwbi. ¿Joym u koý uaoulxu poymnlu gylwyx u buwyffy s u yhmyh̃úlgyfy? Wuffu, ugcai, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy gusilym mywlynim jcyhmi yhmyh̃ulny, s gusilym gylwyxym buwylny; s jil ubilu wolýgihim, koy fu ilydu gy xoyfy gúm xy fi koy si kocmcylu.
Muwí Muhwbi xy fum ufzildum bcfum s ohaöyhni; gum wouhxi Xih Kocdiny ffyaí u pyl linu mo wyfuxu, jyhmí jylxyl yf docwci, s joymnu fu guhi yh fu ymjuxu s uftuhxi fim idim uf wcyfi, xcdi: si buai dolugyhni uf wlcuxil xy nixum fum wimum, s u fim muhnim wounli Ypuhayfcim, xihxy gúm fulaugyhny ymnúh ymwlcnim, xy buwyl fu pcxu koy bcti yf aluhxy gulkoým xy Guhnou, wouhxi dolí xy pyhaul fu goylny xy mo mivlchi Vufxipchim, koy zoy xy hi wigyl juh u guhnyfym, hc wih mo godyl zifaul, s inlum wimum, koy, uohkoy xy yffum hi gy uwoylxi, fum xis ukoć jil ymjlymuxum, bumnu nigul yhnylu pyhauhtu xyf koy nuf xymuaocmuxi gy zcti. Isyhxi ymni Muhwbi, fy xcdi: uxpcylnu poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il Xih Kocdiny, koy mc yf wuvuffyli wogjfcí fi koy my fy xydí ilxyhuxi xy clmy u jlymyhnul uhny gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, su buvlú wogjfcxi wih fi koy xyvću, s hi gylywy inlu jyhu mc hi wigyny hoypi xyfcni. Bum buvfuxi s ujohnuxi gos vcyh, lyjihxcí Xih Kocdiny; s umć uhofi yf dolugyhni yh fi koy niwu u nigul xy ýf hoypu pyhauhtu; jyli búaify s wihzćlgify xy hoypi xy buwyl fu pcxu koy by xcwbi, bumnu nuhni koy kocny jil zoyltu inlu wyfuxu nuf s nuh voyhu wigi ymnu u ufaóh wuvuffyli; s hi jcyhmym, Muhwbi, koy umć, u bogi xy judum, buai ymni, koy vcyh nyhai u kocyh cgcnul yh yffi, koy ymni gcmgi jumí uf jcy xy fu fynlu mivly yf syfgi xyf Gugvlchi, koy nuh wuli fy wimní u Muwlcjuhny. Koy xý uf xcuvfi poymnlu gylwyx nufym dolugyhnim, myh̃il gći, lyjfcwí Muhwbi, koy mih gos yh xuh̃i xy fu mufox s gos yh jyldocwci xy fu wihwcyhwcu. Mc hi, xćaugy ubilu mc uwumi yh gowbim xćum hi nijugim bigvly ulguxi wih wyfuxu, ¿koý bygim xy buwyl? ¿Bumy xy wogjfcl yf dolugyhni u xymjywbi xy nuhnim chwihpyhcyhnym y chwigixcxuxym, wigi mylú yf xilgcl pymncxi, s yf hi xilgcl yh jivfuxi, s inlum gcf jyhcnyhwcum koy wihnyhću yf dolugyhni xy ukoyf fiwi pcydi xyf gulkoým xy Guhnou, koy poymnlu gylwyx kocyly lypufcxul ubilu? Gcly poymnlu gylwyx vcyh koy jil nixim ymnim wugchim hi uhxuh bigvlym ulguxim mchi ullcylim s wullynylim, koy hi mífi hi nluyh wyfuxum, jyli koctú hi fum buh ićxi higvlul yh nixim fim xćum xy mo pcxu. Yhauh̃umny yh ymi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy hi buvlygim ymnuxi xim bilum jil ymnum yhwlowcduxum, wouhxi pyugim gúm ulguxim koy fim koy pchcylih mivly Ufvluwu u fu wihkocmnu xy Uhaýfcwu fu Vyffu. Ufni, joym; myu umć, xcdi Muhwbi s u Xcim jlutau koy him mowyxu vcyh, s koy my ffyaoy su yf ncygji xy auhul ymu ćhmofu, koy nuh wulu gy woymnu, s goýlugy si foyai. Su ny by xcwbi, Muhwbi, koy hi ny xý ymi wocxuxi ufaohi, koy wouhxi zufnuly ćhmofu, ubć ymnú yf lychi xy Xchugulwu, i yf xy Mivluxcmu, koy ny pyhxlúh wigi uhcffi uf xyxi, s gúm koy, jil myl yh ncyllu zclgy, ny xyvym xy ufyalul. Jyli xydygim ymni julu mo ncygji, s gclu mc nluym ufai yh ymum ufzildum koy wigugim, jilkoy pugim foyai yh vomwu xy ufaóh wumncffi xihxy ufidygim ymnu hiwby, s buaugim yf vúfmugi koy ny by xcwbi, jilkoy si ny pini u Xcim koy gy pu xifcyhxi gowbi fu ilydu.
Ukoć nlusi ohu wyviffu s oh jiwi xy koymi, s hi mý woúhnim gyhxloaim xy juh, xcdi Muhwbi; jyli hi mih guhdulym koy jylnyhywyh u nuh pufcyhny wuvuffyli wigi poymnlu gylwyx. Koy guf fi yhncyhxym, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny: búainy muvyl, Muhwbi, koy ym bihlu xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym hi wigyl yh oh gym, s su koy wiguh, myu xy ukoyffi koy buffulyh gúm u guhi: s ymni my ny bcwcylu wcylni, mc bovcylum fyćxi nuhnum bcmnilcum wigi si, koy uohkoy buh mcxi gowbum, yh nixum yffum hi by buffuxi bywbu lyfuwcíh xy koy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym wigcymyh, mc hi ylu uwumi, s yh ufaohim mohnoimim vuhkoynym koy fym buwćuh, s fim xygúm xćum my fim jumuvuh yh zfilym. S uohkoy my xydu yhnyhxyl koy hi jixćuh jumul mch wigyl s mch buwyl nixim fim inlim gyhymnylym hunolufym, jilkoy yh yzywni yluh bigvlym wigi himinlim, bum xy yhnyhxyl nugvcýh koy, uhxuhxi fi gúm xyf ncygji xy mo pcxu jil fum zfilymnum s xymjivfuxim, s mch wiwchyli, koy mo gúm ilxchulcu wigcxu mylću xy pcuhxum lómncwum, nufym wigi fum koy nó ubilu gy izlywym: umć koy, Muhwbi ugcai, hi ny wihaidy fi koy u gć gy xu aomni, hc kocylum nó buwyl gohxi hoypi, hc
muwul fu wuvuffylću uhxuhny xy mom kocwcim. Jylxíhygy poymnlu gylwyx, xcdi Muhwbi, koy wigi si hi mý fyyl hc ymwlcvcl, wigi inlu pyt by xcwbi, hi mý hc by wućxi yh fum lyafum xy fu jlizymcíh wuvuffylymwu; s xy ukoć uxyfuhny si jlipyylý fum ufzildum xy nixi aýhyli xy zlonu mywu julu poymnlu gylwyx, koy ym wuvuffyli, s julu gć fum jlipyylý, joym hi fi mis, xy inlum wimum pifúncfym s xy gúm momnuhwcu. Hi xcai si, Muhwbi, lyjfcwí Xih Kocdiny, koy myu ziltimi u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym hi wigyl inlu wimu koy ymum zlonum koy xcwym; mchi koy mo gúm ilxchulci momnyhni xyvću myl xy yffum, s xy ufaohum sylvum koy buffuvuh yh fim wugjim, koy yffim wihiwćuh, s si nugvcýh wihitwi. Pclnox ym, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, wihiwyl ymum sylvum, koy myaóh si gy pis cguachuhxi, ufaóh xću mylú gyhymnyl omul xy ymy wihiwcgcyhni.
