Jlchwcjufgyhny xywćuh koy muvću fu wcyhwcu xy fum ymnlyffum, s xy fi koy jumuvuh uffú yh yf wcyfi yf mif s fu fohu, jilkoy johnoufgyhny him xywću yf wlcm xyf mif s xy fu fohu. Ywfcjmy my ffugu, ugcai, koy hi wlcm, yf ymwolywylmy ymim xim fogchulym gusilym, xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Gum Jyxli, hi lyjuluhxi yh hch̃ylćum, jlimcaocí mo woyhni, xcwcyhxi: umcgymgi uxcpchuvu wouhxi buvću xy myl yf uh̃i uvohxuhny i ymncf. Ymnýlcf koylýcm xywcl, ugcai, xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Ymnýlcf, i ymncf, lymjihxcí Jyxli, nixi my mufy uffú. S xcai koy, wih ymni koy xywću, my bcwcylih mo juxly s mom ugcaim koy fy xuvuh wlýxcni gos lcwim, jilkoy buwćuh fi koy ýf fym uwihmyduvu, xcwcýhxifym: mygvlux ymny uh̃i wyvuxu, hi nlcai; yh ymny jixýcm mygvlul aulvuhtim, s hi wyvuxu; yf koy pcyhy mylú xy aocffu xy uwycny; fim nlym mcaocyhnym hi my wiaylú ainu. Ymu wcyhwcu my ffugu Umnlifiaću, xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Hi mý si wígi my ffugu, lyjfcwí Jyxli, gum mý koy nixi ymni muvću s uóh gúm. Zchufgyhny hi jumulih gowbim gymym xymjoým koy pchi xy Mufuguhwu, wouhxi oh xću lyguhywcí pymncxi xy jumnil wih mo wusuxi s jyffcwi, buvcýhximy kocnuxi fim búvcnim fulaim koy wigi ymwiful nluću, s dohnugyhny my pcmncí wih ýf xy jumnil inli mo aluhxy ugcai ffuguxi Ugvlimci, koy buvću mcxi mo wigjuh̃yli yh fim ymnoxcim. Ifpcxúvumygy xywcl wígi Alcmímnigi yf xczohni zoy aluhxy bigvly xy wigjihyl wijfum, nuhni koy ýf buwću fim pcffuhwcwim julu fu hiwby xyf Huwcgcyhni xyf Myh̃il, s fim uonim julu yf xću xy Xcim, koy fim lyjlymyhnuvuh fim gitim xy hoymnli joyvfi, s nixim xywćuh koy yluh jil yf wuvi. Wouhxi fim xyf foaul pcylih nuh xy cgjlipcmi pymncxim xy jumnilym u fim xim ymwifulym, koyxulih uxgcluxim s hi jixćuh uxcpchul fu wuomu koy fym buvću gipcxi u buwyl nuh yrnluh̃u goxuhtu. Su yh ymny ncygji ylu goylni yf juxly xy hoymnli Alcmímnigi, s ýf koyxí bylyxuxi yh gowbu wuhncxux xy buwcyhxu, uhmć yh goyvfym wigi yh lućwym, s yh hi jykoyh̃u wuhncxux xy auhuxi gusil s gyhil, s yh aluh wuhn