xymjivfuxim yh jim xy ukoyffu jumnilu Gulwyfu koy hoymnli tuauf higvlí xyhuhnym, xy fu wouf my buvću yhugiluxi yf xczohni xy Alcmímnigi. S kocýliim xywcl ubilu, jilkoy ym vcyh koy fi myjúcm, koýh ym ymnu lujutu; koctú s uoh mch koctú hi buvlýcm ićxi mygyduhny wimu yh nixim fim xćum xy poymnlu pcxu, uohkoy pcpúcm gúm uh̃im koy mulhu. Xywcx Mullu, lyjfcwí Xih Kocdiny, hi joxcyhxi mozlcl yf nliwul xy fim piwuvfim xyf wuvlyli. Bulni pcpy fu mulhu, lymjihxcí Jyxli; s mc ym, myh̃il, koy gy buvýcm xy uhxul tubylcyhxi u wuxu jumi fim piwuvfim, hi uwuvulygim yh oh uh̃i. Jylxihux, ugcai, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy jil buvyl nuhnu xczylyhwcu xy mulhu u Mullu im fi xcdy; jyli pim lymjihxćmnycm gos vcyh, jilkoy pcpy gúm mulhu koy Mullu, s jlimyaocx poymnlu bcmnilcu, koy hi im lyjfcwulý gúm yh huxu.
Xcai, joym, myh̃il xy gc ufgu, xcdi yf wuvlyli, koy yh hoymnlu ufxyu bovi oh fuvluxil uóh gúm lcwi koy yf juxly xy Alcmímnigi, yf wouf my ffuguvu Aocffylgi, s uf wouf xci Xcim, ugýh xy fum gowbum s aluhxym lckoytum, ohu bcdu, xy wosi julni golcí mo guxly, koy zoy fu gúm bihluxu godyl koy bovi yh nixim ymnim wihnilhim; hi julywy mchi koy ubilu fu pyi wih ukoyffu wulu, koy xyf oh wuvi nyhću yf mif s xyf inli fu fohu, s mivly nixi buwyhximu s ugcau xy fim jivlym, jil fi koy wlyi koy xyvy xy ymnul mo úhcgu u fu bilu xy bilu aituhxi xy Xcim yh yf inli gohxi. Xy jymul xy fu goylny xy nuh voyhu godyl golcí mo gulcxi Aocffylgi, xyduhxi u mo bcdu Gulwyfu gowbuwbu s lcwu yh jixyl xy oh nći mosi, muwylxiny, s vyhyzcwcuxi yh hoymnli foaul. Wlywcí fu hch̃u wih nuhnu vyffytu, koy him buwću uwilxul xy fu xy mo guxly, koy fu nopi gos aluhxy, s wih nixi ymni my dotauvu koy fy buvću xy jumul fu xy fu bcdu; s umć zoy, koy wouhxi ffyaí u yxux xy wunilwy u kochwy uh̃im, huxcy fu gcluvu koy hi vyhxywću u Xcim, koy nuh bylgimu fu buvću wlcuxi, s fim gúm koyxuvuh yhugiluxim s jylxcxim jil yffu. Aoulxúvufu mo nći wih gowbi lywuni s wih gowbi yhwyllugcyhni, jyli wih nixi ymni, fu zugu xy mo gowbu bylgimolu my yrnyhxcí xy guhylu, koy umć jil yffu, wigi jil mom gowbum lckoytum, hi mifugyhny xy fim xy hoymnli joyvfi, mchi xy fim xy gowbum fyaoum u fu lyxihxu, s xy fim gydilym xy yffim, ylu liauxi, mifcwcnuxi y cgjilnohuxi mo nći my fu xcymy jil godyl. Gum ýf, koy u fum xylywbum ym voyh wlcmncuhi, uohkoy kocmcylu wumulfu foyai, umć wigi fu pću xy yxux, hi kocmi buwylfi mch mo wihmyhncgcyhni, mch nyhyl idi u fu auhuhwcu s aluhdylću koy fy izlywću yf nyhyl fu buwcyhxu xy fu gitu, xcfunuhxi mo wumugcyhni. S u zy koy my xcdi ymni yh gúm xy oh willcffi yh yf joyvfi yh ufuvuhtu xyf voyh muwylxiny. Koy kocyli koy myju, myh̃il uhxuhny, koy yh ymnim foaulym wilnim xy nixi my nlunu s xy nixi my golgolu; s nyhyx julu pim, wigi si nyhai julu gć, koy xyvy xy myl xygumcuxugyhny v