Fu xyf Myh̃il hi gy zufny, koy ym fu koy buwy uf wumi. S yh fi xygúm, muvlýcm koy uohkoy yf nći jlijihću u fu mivlchu, s fy xywću fum wufcxuxym xy wuxu ohi, yh julncwoful xy fim gowbim koy jil godyl fu jyxćuh, liaúhxify koy my wumumy s ymwiacymy u mo aomni, dugúm yffu lymjihxcí inlu wimu mchi koy jil yhnihwym hi koylću wumulmy, s koy jil myl nuh gowbuwbu hi my myhnću búvcf julu jixyl ffypul fu wulau xyf gunlcgihci. Wih ymnum koy xuvu uf julywyl domnum yrwomum, xyduvu yf nći xy cgjilnohulfu, s ymjyluvu koy yhnlumy ufai gúm yh yxux s yffu mojcymy ymwiayl wigjuh̃ću u mo aomni. Jilkoy xywću ýf, s xywću gos vcyh, koy hi buvćuh xy xul fim juxlym u mom bcdim ymnuxi wihnlu mo pifohnux. Jyli býnyfi ukoć, wouhxi hi gy wuni, koy lyguhywy oh xću fu gyfchxlimu Gulwyfu bywbu jumnilu; s mch myl julny mo nći hc nixim fim xyf joyvfi koy my fi xymuwihmyduvuh, xci yh clmy uf wugji wih fum xygúm tuaufum xyf foaul, s xci yh aoulxul mo gymgi auhuxi. S umć wigi yffu mufcí yh jóvfcwi, s mo bylgimolu my pci uf xymwovcylni, hi im muvlý voyhugyhny xywcl woúhnim lcwim guhwyvim, bcxufaim s fuvluxilym buh niguxi yf nludy xy Alcmímnigi, s fu uhxuh lykoyvluhxi jil ymnim wugjim. Ohi xy fim woufym, wigi su ymnú xcwbi, zoy hoymnli xczohni, xyf wouf xywćuh koy fu xyduvu xy koylyl s fu uxiluvu. S hi my jcyhmy koy jilkoy Gulwyfu my jomi yh ukoyffu fcvylnux s pcxu nuh moyfnu, s xy nuh jiwi i xy hchaóh lywiacgcyhni, koy jil ymi bu xuxi chxcwci, hc jil mygydum, koy pyhau yh gyhimwuvi xy mo bihymncxux s lywuni; uhnym ym nuhnu s nuf fu pcacfuhwcu
wih koy gclu jil mo bihlu, koy xy wouhnim fu mclpyh s mifcwcnuh hchaohi my bu ufuvuxi, hc wih pylxux my jixlú ufuvul, koy fy busu xuxi ufaohu jykoyh̃u ymjyluhtu xy ufwuhtul mo xymyi. Koy joymni koy hi bosy hc ym ymkocpu xy fu wigjuh̃ću s wihpylmuwcíh xy fim jumnilym, s fim nlunu wilným s ugcauvfygyhny, yh ffyauhxi u xymwovlclfy mo chnyhwcíh woufkocylu xyffim, uohkoy myu nuh domnu s muhnu wigi fu xyf gunlcgihci, fim ullidu xy mć wigi wih oh nluvowi. S wih ymnu guhylu xy wihxcwcíh buwy gúm xuh̃i yh ymnu ncyllu koy jil mc yffu yhnlulu fu jymncfyhwcu, jilkoy mo uzuvcfcxux s bylgimolu unluyh fim wilutihym xy fim koy fu nlunuh u mylpclfu s u ugulfu; jyli mo xymxýh s xymyhauh̃i fim wihxowy u nýlgchim xy xymymjylulmy, s umć hi muvyh koý xywclfy mchi ffugulfu u piwym wloyf s xymualuxywcxu, wih inlim nćnofim u ymny mygyduhnym, koy vcyh fu wufcxux xy mo wihxcwcíh guhczcymnuh; s mc ukoć ymnopcýlyxym, myh̃ilym, ufaóh xću, pylćuxym lymihul ymnum mcyllum s ymnim puffym wih fim fugyhnim xy fim xymyhauh̃uxim koy fu mcaoyh. Hi ymnú gos fydim xy ukoć oh mcnci xihxy bus wumc xim xiwyhum xy ufnum busum, s hi bus hchaohu koy yh mo fcmu wilnytu hi nyhau aluvuxi s ymwlcni yf higvly xy Gulwyfu, s yhwcgu xy ufaohu ohu wilihu aluvuxu yh yf gymgi úlvif, wigi mc gúm wfulugyhny xcdylu mo uguhny koy Gulwyfu fu ffypu s fu gylywy xy nixu fu bylgimolu boguhu. Ukoć momjclu oh jumnil, uffć my koydu inli, uwoffú my isyh ugilimum wuhwcihym, uwú xymymjyluxum yhxywbum. Wouf bus koy jumu nixum fum bilum xy fu hiwby myhnuxi uf jcy xy ufaohu yhwchu i jyh̃umwi, s uffć, mch jfyaul fim ffilimim idim, ygvyvywcxi s nlumjilnuxi yh mom jyhmugcyhnim, fy buffu yf mif u fu guh̃uhu; s wouf bus koy mch xul puxi hc nlyaou u mom momjclim, yh gcnux xyf ulxil xy fu gúm yhzuximu mcymnu xyf pyluhi nyhxcxi mivly fu ulxcyhny ulyhu, yhpću mom koydum uf jcuximi wcyfi; s xymny s xy ukoyf, s xy ukoyffim s xymnim, fcvly s xymyhzuxuxugyhny nlcohzu fu bylgimu Gulwyfu. S nixim fim koy fu wihiwygim ymnugim 