Yh wocxuxi gy fi nyhai, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, s ualuxýtwiim yf aomni koy gy buvýcm xuxi wih fu hulluwcíh xy nuh muvlimi woyhni. ¡Ib! lyjfcwí yf wuvyli. Uoh hi mý si fu gcnux xy fim wumim mowyxcxim u fim uguhnym xy Gulwyfu; gum jixlću myl koy guh̃uhu nijúmygim yh yf wugchi ufaóh jumnil koy him fi xcdymy; s jil ubilu vcyh mylú koy im pucm u xilgcl xyvudi xy nywbuxi, jilkoy yf mylyhi im jixlću xuh̃ul fu bylcxu, joymni koy ym nuf fu gyxcwchu koy my im bu joymni, koy hi bus koy nygyl xy wihnlulci uwwcxyhny.
Muhwbi Juhtu koy su xuvu uf xcuvfi yf nuhni buvful xyf wuvlyli, mifcwcní jil mo julny koy mo ugi my yhnlumy u xilgcl yh fu wbitu xy Jyxli. Bćtifi umć s nixi fi gúm xy fu hiwby my fu jumí yh gygilcum xy mo myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, u cgcnuwcíh xy fim uguhnym xy Gulwyfu. Muhwbi Juhtu my uwigixí yhnly Liwchuhny s mo dogyhni, s xolgcí, hi wigi yhugiluxi xymzupilywcxi, mchi wigi bigvly gifcxi u wiwym.
Wujćnofi 13: Xihxy my xu zch uf woyhni xy fu jumnilu Gulwyfu, wih inlim mowymim
