Yh ffyaúhximy u dohnul my mufoxulih wilnýmgyhny, s jlyaohnúhximy fim ohim u fim inlim xíhxy cvuh, mojcylih koy nixim my yhwugchuvuh uf foaul xyf yhncylli, s umć wigyhtulih u wugchul nixim dohnim. Ohi xy fim xy u wuvuffi, buvfuhxi wih mo wigjuh̃yli fy xcdi: - Julýwygy, myh̃il Pcpufxi, koy buvygim xy xul jil vcyh ygjfyuxu fu nulxuhtu koy bcwcýlygim yh pyl ymny zugimi yhncylli koy hi jixlú xydul xy myl zugimi, myaóh ymnim jumnilym him buh wihnuxi yrnluh̃ytum, umć xyf goylni jumnil wigi xy fu jumnilu bigcwcxu. Umć gy fi julywy u gć, lymjihxcí Pcpufxi, s hi xcai si buwyl nulxuhtu xy oh xću, jyli xy wounli fu bcwcylu u nloywi xy pylfy. Jlyaohnífym Xih Kocdiny koý ylu fi koy buvćuh ićxi xy Gulwyfu s xy Alcmímnigi. Yf wugchuhny xcdi koy ukoyffu guxloauxu buvćuh yhwihnluxi wih ukoyffim jumnilym, s koy jil buvylfym pcmni yh ukoyf nuh nlcmny nludy fym buvćuh jlyaohnuxi fu iwumcíh jil koy cvuh xy ukoyffu guhylu; koy ohi xyffim my fi wihní, wihnuhxi fum ytnluh̃ytum s bylgimolu xy ohu jumnilu ffuguxu Gulwyfu, s fim ugilym xy gowbim koy fu lywoymnuvuh, wih fu goylny xy ukoyf Alcmímnigi u wosi yhncylli cvuh. Zchufgyhny, ýf wihní fi koy Jyxli u Xih Kocdiny buvću wihnuxi.
