Kocdiny, koy fu pcxu xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ymnú modynu u gcf jyfcalim s xympyhnolum, s hc gúm hc gyhim ymnú yh jinyhwcu jlijchwou xy myl fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym lysym s ygjyluxilym, wigi fi bu gimnluxi fu yrjylcyhwcu yh gowbim s xcpylmim wuvuffylim xy wosum bcmnilcum si nyhai yhnylu hincwcu. S joxcýluny wihnul ubilu, mc yf xifil gy xcylu foaul, xy ufaohim koy mífi jil yf pufil xy mo vluti buh movcxi u fim ufnim aluxim koy by wihnuxi, s ymnim gcmgim my pcylih uhnym s xymjoým yh xcpylmum wufugcxuxym s gcmylcum, jilkoy yf pufylimi Uguxćm xy Auofu my pcí yh jixyl xy mo gilnuf yhygcai Ulwufúom yf yhwuhnuxil, xy kocyh my ncyhy jil upylcaouxi koy fy xci, nyhcýhxify jlymi, gúm xy ximwcyhnim utinym wih fum lcyhxum xy mo wuvuffi, unuxi u ohu wifoghu xy oh junci; s uoh bus oh uonil mywlyni s xy hi jiwi wlýxcni koy xcwy, koy buvcyhxi wiacxi uf wuvuffyli xyf Zyvi wih ohu wcylnu nlugju koy my fy bohxcí xyvudi xy fim jcym yh oh wcylni wumncffi, uf wuyl my buffí yh ohu bihxu mcgu xyvudi xy fu ncyllu, unuxi xy jcym s guhim, s uffć fy ywbulih ohu xymnum koy ffuguh gyfywchum xy uaou xy hcypy s ulyhu, xy fi koy ffyaí gos uf wuvi, s mc hi zoylu miwillcxi yh ukoyffu aluh wocnu xy oh muvci aluhxy ugcai mosi, fi jumulu gos guf yf jivly wuvuffyli...
Wujćnofi 16: Xy fi koy fy mowyxcí uf chayhcimi bcxufai yh fu pyhnu koy ýf cguachuvu myl wumncffi.
Yf pyhnyli koy pcí u Xih Kocdiny unlupymuxi yh yf umhi, jlyaohní u Muhwbi koý guf nluću. Muhwbi fy lymjihxcí koy hi ylu huxu, mchi koy buvću xuxi ohu wućxu xy ohu jyh̃u uvudi, s koy nyhću ufai vloguxum fum wimncffum. Nyhću yf pyhnyli jil godyl u ohu, hi xy fu wihxcwcíh koy moyfyh nyhyl fum xy mygyduhny nluni, jilkoy hunolufgyhny ylu wulcnuncpu s my xifću xy fum wufugcxuxym xy mom jlídcgim, s umć uwoxcí foyai u wolul u Xih Kocdiny, y bcti koy ohu bcdu mosu xihwyffu, gowbuwbu s xy gos voyh julywyl, fu usoxumy u wolul u mo boýmjyx. Mylpću u fu pyhnu umcgcmgi ohu gitu umnolcuhu, uhwbu xy wulu, ffuhu xy wiainy, xy hulct ligu, xyf oh idi noylnu, s xyf inli hi gos muhu: pylxux ym koy fu auffulxću xyf woylji mojfću fum xygúm zufnum; hi nyhću mcyny jufgim xy fim jcym u fu wuvytu, s fum ymjufxum, koy ufaóh nuhni fy wulauvuh, fu buwćuh gclul uf moyfi gúm xy fi koy yffu kocmcylu. Ymnu ayhncf gitu, joym, usoxí u fu xihwyffu, s fum xim bcwcylih ohu gos gufu wugu u Xih Kocdiny yh oh wuluguhwbíh, koy inlim ncygjim xuvu guhczcymnim chxcwcim koy buvću mylpcxi xy judul gowbim uh̃im, yh yf wouf nugvcýh ufiduvu oh ullcyli koy nyhću mo wugu bywbu oh jiwi gúm uffú xy fu xy hoymnli Xih Kocdiny, s uohkoy ylu xy fum yhdufgum s guhnum xy mom guwbim, buwću gowbu pyhnudu u fu xy Xih Kocdiny, koy mífi wihnyhću wounli guf fcmum nuvfum mivly xim hi gos caoufym vuhwim, s oh wifwbíh koy yh fi moncf julywću wifwbu, ffyhi xy vixikoym, koy u hi gimnlul koy yluh xy fuhu jil ufaohum linolum, uf ncyhni yh fu xolytu mygyduvuh xy aocdulli, s xim múvuhum bywbum xy woyli xy uxulau, s ohu zlutuxu wosim bcfim, mc my kocmcyluh wihnul, hi my jylxcylu ohi mifi yh fu woyhnu. Yh ymnu gufxcnu wugu my uwimní Xih Kocdiny; foyai fu pyhnylu s mo bcdu fy ygjfumnulih xy ullcvu u uvudi, ufogvlúhxifym Gulcnilhym, koy umć my ffuguvu fu umnolcuhu, s wigi uf vctguffy pcymy fu pyhnylu nuh uwulxyhufuxi u julnym u Xih Kocdiny, xcdi koy ukoyffim gúm julywćuh aifjym koy wućxu.
Hi zoylih aifjym, xcdi Muhwbi, mchi koy fu jyh̃u nyhću gowbim jcwim s nlijytihym, s koy koy wuxu ohi buvću bywbi mo wulxyhuf. S nugvcýh fy xcdi: Buau poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃ilu, xy guhylu koy koyxyh ufaohum ymnijum, koy hi zufnulú kocyh fum busu gyhymnyl, koy nugvcýh gy xoyfyh u gć oh jiwi fim figim. ¿Xy ymu guhylu, lymjihxcí fu pyhnylu, nugvcýh xyvćmnycm pim xy wuyl? Hi wuć, xcdi Muhwbi Juhtu, mchi koy xy yf mivlymufni koy nigý xy pyl wuyl u gc ugi, xy nuf guhylu gy xoyfy u gć yf woylji, koy gy julywy koy gy buh xuxi gcf jufim. Vcyh jixlću myl ymi, xcdi fu xihwyffu, koy u gć gy bu uwihnywcxi gowbum pywym mih̃ul koy wuću xy ohu nilly uvudi s koy hohwu uwuvuvu xy ffyaul uf moyfi s wouhxi xymjylnuvu xyf moyh̃i buffulgy nuh gifcxu s koyvluhnuxu wigi mc pylxuxylugyhny bovcylu wućxi. Ubć ymnú yf nikoy, myh̃ilu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu, koy si mch mih̃ul huxu, mchi ymnuhxi gúm xymjcylni koy ubilu ymnis, gy buffi wih jiwim gyhim wulxyhufym koy gc myh̃il Xih Kocdiny.
¿Wígi my ffugu ymny wuvuffyli? jlyaohní fu umnolcuhu Gulcnilhym. Xih Kocdiny xy fu Guhwbu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu, s ym wuvuffyli upyhnolyli s xy fim gydilym s gúm zoylnym koy xy foyhaim ncygjim uwú my buh pcmni yh yf gohxi. ¿Koý ym wuvuffyli upyhnolyli? lyjfcwí fu gitu. ¿Nuh hoypu micm yh yf gohxi koy hi fi muvycm pim? lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu: Joym muvyx, bylguhu gću, koy wuvuffyli upyhnolyli ym ohu wimu koy yh xim jufuvlum my py ujufyuxi s ygjyluxil; bis ymnú fu gúm xymxcwbuxu wlcunolu xyf gohxi s fu gúm gyhymnylimu, s guh̃uhu nyhxlú xim i nlym wilihum xy lychim koy xul u mo ymwoxyli. Joym ¿wígi pim, mcyhxi xy ymny nuh voyh myh̃il, xcdi fu pyhnylu, hi nyhýcm u fi koy julywy mckocylu ufaoh wihxuxi? Uóh ym nygjluhi, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, jilkoy hi bu mchi oh gym koy uhxugim vomwuhxi fum upyhnolum, s bumnu ubilu hi bygim nijuxi wih hchaohu koy fi myu, s nuf pyt bus koy my vomwu ohu wimu s my buffu inlu; pylxux ym koy mc gc myh̃il Xih Kocdiny muhu xy ymnu bylcxu i wućxu, s si koyxi wihnlywbi xyffu, hi nliwulću gcm ymjyluhtum wih yf gydil nćnofi xy Ymjuh̃u.
