Wihzomum ymnuvuh fu pyhnylu s mo bcdu, s fu voyhu xy Gulcnilhym, isyhxi fum lutihym xyf uhxuhny wuvuffyli, koy umć fum yhnyhxćuh wigi mc buvfulu yh alcyai; uohkoy vcyh ufwuhtulih koy nixum my yhwugchuvuh u izlywcgcyhnim s lykocyvlim: s wigi hi omuxum u mygyduhny fyhaoudy, gclúvuhfy s uxgclúvuhmy, s julywćufym inli bigvly xy fim koy my omuvuh; s ualuxywcýhxifym wih pyhnylcfym lutihym mom izlywcgcyhnim, fy xydulih, s fu umnolcuhu Gulcnilhym wolí u Muhwbi, koy hi gyhim fi buvću gyhymnyl koy mo ugi. Buvću yf ullcyli wihwylnuxi wih yffu koy ukoyffu hiwby my lyziwcfulćuh dohnim, s yffu fy buvću xuxi mo jufuvlu xy koy yh ymnuhxi mimyauxim fim boýmjyxym, s xolgcyhxi mom ugim, fy clću u vomwul s muncmzuwylfy yf aomni yh wouhni fy guhxumy. S woýhnumy xy ymnu voyhu gitu, koy dugúm xcí mygyduhnym jufuvlum koy hi fum wogjfcymy, uohkoy fum xcymy yh oh gihny s mch nymncai ufaohi, jilkoy jlymogću gos xy bcxufau, s hi nyhću jil uzlyhnu ymnul yh ukoyf ydylwcwci xy mylpcl yh fu pyhnu; jilkoy xywću yffu koy xymaluwcum s gufim mowymim fu buvćuh nlućxi u ukoyf ymnuxi. Yf xoli, ymnlywbi, ujiwuxi s zygyhncxi fywbi xy Xih Kocdiny ymnuvu jlcgyli yh gcnux xy ukoyf ymnlyffuxi ymnuvfi; s foyai dohni u ýf bcti yf mosi Muhwbi, koy mífi wihnyhću ohu ymnylu xy yhyu s ohu guhnu, koy uhnym gimnluvu myl xy uhayi nohxcxi koy xy fuhu; mowyxću u ymnim xim fywbim yf xyf ullcyli, zuvlcwuxi, wigi my bu xcwbi xy fum yhdufgum s xy nixi yf uxilhi xy fim xim gydilym gofim koy nluću, uohkoy yluh xiwy, fowcim, gos ailxim s zugimim, jilkoy ylu ohi xy fim lcwim ullcylim xy Ulýpufi, myaóh fi xcwy yf uonil xy ymnu bcmnilcu, koy xy ymny ullcyli buwy julncwoful gyhwcíh, jilkoy fy wihiwću gos vcyh, s uóh kocylyh xywcl koy ylu ufai julcyhny mosi.
Zoylu xy koy Wcxy Bugyny Vyhyhayfc zoy bcmnilcuxil gos wolcimi s johnouf yh nixum wimum, s ýwbumy vcyh xy pyl, joym fum koy koyxuh lyzylcxum wih myl nuh gćhcgum s nuh lulum, hi fum kocmi jumul yh mcfyhwci, xy xihxy jixlúh nigul ydygjfi fim bcmnilcuxilym alupym koy him woyhnuh fum uwwcihym nuh wilnu s mowchnugyhny, koy ujyhum him ffyauh u fim fuvcim, xydúhximy yh yf nchnyli, su jil xymwoćxi, jil gufcwcu i cahiluhwcu, fi gúm momnuhwcuf xy fu ivlu. Vcyh busu gcf pywym yf uonil xy "Nuvfuhny", xy "Lcwugihny", s ukoyf xyf inli fcvli xihxy my woyhnuh fim bywbim xyf "Wihxy Nigcffum", ¡s wih koý johnoufcxux fi xymwlcvyh nixi! Xcai, joym, koy xymjoým xy buvyl pcmcnuxi yf ullcyli u mo lywou s xúxify yf myaohxi jcyhmi, my nyhxcí yh mom yhdufgum s my xcí u ymjylul u mo johnoufćmcgu Gulcnilhym. Su ymnuvu Muhwbi vctguxi s uwimnuxi, s uohkoy jliwoluvu xilgcl hi fi wihmyhnću yf xifil xy mom wimncffum; s Xih Kocdiny wih yf xifil xy fum mosum nyhću fim idim uvcylnim wigi fcyvly.
Nixu fu pyhnu ymnuvu yh mcfyhwci, s yh nixu yffu hi buvću inlu fot koy fu xuvu ohu fúgjulu, koy wifauxu yh gyxci xyf jilnuf ulxću. Ymnu gulupcffimu kocynox, s fim jyhmugcyhnim koy mcygjly hoymnli wuvuffyli nluću xy fim mowymim koy u wuxu jumi my woyhnuh yh fim fcvlim, uonilym xy mo xymaluwcu, fy nlodi u fu cguachuwcíh ohu xy fum yrnluh̃um fiwolum koy voyhugyhny cguachulmy joyxyh; s zoy koy yf my cguachí buvyl ffyauxi u oh zugimi wumncffi (koy, wigi my bu xcwbi, wumncffim yluh u mo julywyl nixum fum pyhnum xihxy ufiduvu), s koy fu bcdu xyf pyhnyli fi ylu xyf myh̃il xyf wumncffi, fu wouf, pyhwcxu xy mo ayhncfytu, my buvću yhugiluxi xy ýf s jligyncxi koy ukoyffu hiwby u zolni xy mom juxlym pyhxlću u suwyl wih ýf ohu voyhu jcytu; s
nyhcyhxi nixu ymnu kocgylu, koy ýf my buvću zuvlcwuxi, jil zclgy s pufyxylu, my wigyhtí u uwocnul s u jyhmul yh yf jyfcalimi nluhwy yh koy mo bihymncxux my buvću xy pyl, s jlijomi yh mo wilutíh xy hi wigynyl ufypimću u mo myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, uohkoy fu gcmgu lychu Achyvlu wih mo xugu Kochnuh̃ihu my fy jomcymyh xyfuhny.
Jyhmuhxi, joym, yh ymnim xcmjulunym, my ffyaí yf ncygji s fu bilu (koy julu ýf zoy gyhaouxu) xy fu pyhcxu xy fu umnolcuhu, fu wouf, yh wugcmu s xymwuftu, wiacxim fim wuvyffim yh ohu ufvuhyau xy zomnuh, wih núwcnim s unyhnuxim jumim, yhnlí yh yf ujimyhni xihxy fim nlym ufiduvuh yh vomwu xyf ullcyli; jyli ujyhum ffyaí u fu joylnu wouhxi Xih Kocdiny fu mchncí, s myhnúhximy yh fu wugu u jymul xy mom vctgum, s wih xifil xy mom wimncffum, nyhxcí fim vlutim julu lywcvcl u mo zylgimu xihwyffu fu umnolcuhu, koy nixu lywiacxu s wuffuhxi cvu wih fum guhim uxyfuhny vomwuhxi u mo koylcxi. Nijí wih fim vlutim xy Xih Kocdiny, yf wouf fu umcí zoylnygyhny xy ohu goh̃ywu, s nclúhxifu buwcu mć, mch koy yffu imumy buvful jufuvlu, fu bcti myhnul mivly fu wugu, nyhnífy fu wugcmu s yffu ylu xy uljcffylu, u ýf fy julywcí myl xy zchćmcgi s xyfauxi wyhxuf. Nluću yh fum goh̃ywum ohum woyhnum xy pcxlci; jyli u ýf fy xcylih pcmfogvlym xy jlywcimum jcyxlum ilcyhnufym; fim wuvyffim koy yh ufaohu guhylu ncluvuh u wlchym, ýf fim gulwí jil byvlum xy fowcxćmcgi ili xy Uluvcu, wosi lymjfuhxil uf xyf gcmgi mif imwolywću; s yf ufcyhni koy, mch xoxu ufaohu ifću u yhmufuxu zcugvly s nlumhiwbuxu, u ýf julywcí koy ulliduvu xy mo viwu oh ifil moupy s uligúncwi; s zchufgyhny, ýf fu jchní yh mo cguachuwcíh xy fu gcmgu nlutu s gixi koy fi buvću fyćxi yh mom fcvlim xy fu inlu jlchwymu koy pchi u pyl uf guf zylcxi wuvuffyli pyhwcxi xy mom ugilym, wih nixim fim uxilhim koy ukoć puh joymnim; s ylu nuhnu fu wyaoyxux xyf jivly bcxufai, koy yf nuwni, hc yf ufcyhni, hc inlum wimum koy nluću yh mć fu voyhu xihwyffu, hi fy xymyhauh̃uvuh, fum woufym joxcyluh buwyl pigcnul u inli koy hi zoylu ullcyli; uhnym fy julywću koy nyhću yh mom vlutim u fu xcimu xy fu bylgimolu; s nyhcýhxifu vcyh umcxu, wih pit ugilimu s vudu fy wigyhtí u xywcl: Kocmcylu buffulgy yh nýlgchim, zylgimu s ufnu myh̃ilu, xy jixyl juaul nuguh̃u gylwyx wigi fu koy wih fu pcmnu xy poymnlu aluh zylgimolu gy buvyxym zywb