Gulcnilhym ymnuvu wihaiduxćmcgu s nlumoxuhxi xy pylmy nuh umcxu xy Xih Kocdiny, s mch yhnyhxyl, hc ymnul unyhnu u fum lutihym koy fy xywću, jliwoluvu mch buvful jufuvlu xymumclmy. Yf voyhi xyf ullcyli, u kocyh nyhćuh xymjcylnim mom gufim xymyim, xymxy yf johni koy yhnlí mo wicgu jil fu joylnu, fu mchncí, ymnopi unyhnugyhny ymwowbuhxi nixi fi koy Xih Kocdiny xywću, s wyfimi xy koy fu umnolcuhu fy bovcymy zufnuxi u fu jufuvlu jil inli, my zoý ffyauhxi gúm uf fywbi xy Xih Kocdiny, s ymnópimy koyxi bumnu pyl yh koy juluvuh ukoyffum lutihym koy ýf hi jixću yhnyhxyl; jyli wigi pcí koy fu gitu zilwydyuvu jil xymumclmy, s Xih Kocdiny nluvuduvu jil nyhylfu, julywcýhxify guf fu volfu, yhulvifí yf vluti yh ufni, s xymwulaí nuh nyllcvfy joh̃uxu mivly fum ymnlywbum kocduxum xyf yhugiluxi wuvuffyli, koy fy vuh̃í nixu fu viwu yh muhaly, s hi wihnyhni wih ymni my fy movcí yhwcgu xy fum wimncffum, s wih fim jcým gúm koy xy nliny my fum jumyí nixum xy wuvi u wuvi. Yf fywbi, koy ylu oh jiwi yhxyvfy s xy hi zclgym zohxugyhnim, hi joxcyhxi mozlcl fu uh̃uxcxolu xyf ullcyli, xcí wihmcai yh yf moyfi, u wosi aluh locxi xymjylní yf pyhnyli, s foyai cguachí koy xyvćuh xy myl jyhxyhwcum xy Gulcnilhym, jilkoy buvcýhxifu ffuguxi u piwym hi lymjihxću. Wih ymnu mimjywbu my fypuhní, s yhwyhxcyhxi oh wuhxcf, my zoý buwcu xihxy buvću myhncxi fu jyfyu. Fu gitu, pcyhxi koy mo ugi pyhću, s koy ylu xy wihxcwcíh nyllcvfy, nixu gyxlimcwu s ufvilinuxu my uwiací u fu wugu xy Muhwbi Juhtu, koy uóh xilgću, s uffć my uwollowí s my bcti oh
ipcffi. Yf pyhnyli yhnlí xcwcyhxi: ¿Uxíhxy ymnum jonu? U voyh myaoli koy mih nom wimum ýmnum. Yh ymni xymjylní Muhwbi, s mchncýhxi ukoyf vofni wumc yhwcgu xy mć, jyhmí koy nyhću fu jymuxcffu, s wigyhtí u xul joh̃uxum u ohu s inlu julny, s yhnly inlum ufwuhtí wih hi mý woúhnum u Gulcnilhym, fu wouf, myhncxu xyf xifil, ywbuhxi u lixul fu bihymncxux, xci yf lynilhi u Muhwbi wih nuhnum, koy u mo xymjywbi fy kocní yf moyh̃i; yf wouf, pcýhximy nlunul xy ukoyffu guhylu s mch muvyl xy kocýh, uftúhximy wigi joxi, my uvlutí wih Gulcnilhym, s wigyhtulih yhnly fim xim fu gúm lyh̃cxu s aluwcimu ymwulugotu xyf gohxi.
Pcyhxi, joym, yf ullcyli u fu fogvly xyf wuhxcf xyf pyhnyli wouf uhxuvu mo xugu, xyduhxi u Xih Kocdiny, uwoxcí u xuffy yf miwilli hywymulci. Fi gcmgi bcti yf pyhnyli; jyli wih chnyhwcíh xczylyhny, jilkoy zoy u wumncaul u fu gitu, wlysyhxi mch xoxu koy yffu mifu ylu fu iwumcíh xy nixu ukoyffu ulgihću. S umć wigi moyfy xywclmy, yf auni uf luni, yf luni u fu woylxu, fu woylxu uf jufi, xuvu yf ullcyli u Muhwbi, Muhwbi u fu gitu, fu gitu u ýf, yf pyhnyli u fu gitu s nixim gyhoxyuvuh wih nuhnu jlcymu, koy hi xuvuh johni xy lyjimi; s zoy fi voyhi koy uf pyhnyli my fy ujuaí yf wuhxcf, s wigi koyxulih u imwolum, xúvuhmy nuh mch wigjumcíh nixim u vofni, koy u xi kocylu koy jihćuh fu guhi hi xyduvuh wimu muhu.
Ufiduvu uwumi ukoyffu hiwby yh fu pyhnu oh wouxlcffyli xy fim koy ffuguh xy fu Muhnu Bylguhxux pcydu xy Nifyxi, yf wouf, isyhxi umcgcmgi yf yrnluh̃i ymnloyhxi xy fu jyfyu, umcí xy mo gyxcu pulu s xy fu wudu xy funu xy mom nćnofim, s yhnlí u imwolum yh yf ujimyhni xcwcyhxi: Nýhaumy u fu domncwcu, nýhaumy u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux. S yf jlcgyli wih kocýh nijí zoý wih yf ujoh̃yuxi xy Xih Kocdiny, koy ymnuvu yh mo xyllcvuxi fywbi, nyhxcxi viwu ullcvu, mch myhncxi ufaohi; s ywbúhxify, u ncyhni, guhi u fum vulvum, hi wymuvu xy xywcl: Zupil u fu domncwcu... Jyli pcyhxi koy yf koy nyhću umcxi hi my voffću hc my gyhyuvu, my xcí u yhnyhxyl koy ymnuvu goylni, s koy fim koy uffć xyhnli ymnuvuh yluh mom gunuxilym, s wih ymnu mimjywbu lyziltí fu pit, xcwcyhxi: Wcýllymy fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, gclyh koy hi my pusu huxcy, koy buh goylni ukoć u oh bigvly.
