Wujćnofi 17: Xihxy my jlimcaoyh fim chhogyluvfym nluvudim koy yf vlupi Xih Kocdiny s mo voyh ymwoxyli Muhwbi Juhtu jumulih yh fu pyhnu, koy jil mo guf jyhmí koy ylu wumncffi
Buvću su poyfni yh ymny ncygji xy mo julumcmgi Xih Kocdiny, s wih yf gcmgi nihi xy pit koy yf xću uhnym buvću ffuguxi u mo ymwoxyli wouhxi ymnuvu nyhxcxi yh yf puf xy fum ymnuwum, fy wigyhtí u ffugul xcwcyhxi: ¿Muhwbi ugcai, xoylgym? ¿Xoylgym, ugcai Muhwbi? Koý nyhai xy xilgcl, jymcu u gć, lymjihxcí Muhwbi ffyhi xy jymuxogvly s xy xymjywbi, koy hi julywy mchi koy nixim fim xcuvfim buh uhxuxi wihgcai ymnu hiwby. Joýxymfi wlyyl umć mch xoxu, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy i si mý jiwi, i ymny wumncffi ym yhwuhnuxi, jilkoy bum xy muvyl... gum ymni koy ubilu kocyli xywclny, bumgy xy dolul koy fi nyhxlum mywlyni bumnu xymjoým xy gc goylny. Mć doli, lymjihxcí Muhwbi.
Xćaifi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy mis yhygcai xy koy my kocny fu bihlu u huxcy. Xcai koy mć doli, nilhí u xywcl Muhwbi, koy fi wuffulý bumnu xymjoým xy fim xćum xy poymnlu gylwyx, s jfyau u Xcim koy fi joyxu xymwovlcl guh̃uhu. ¿Nuh gufum ivlum ny buai, Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy gy koyllćum pyl goylni wih nuhnu vlypyxux? Hi ym jil ymi, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, mchi koy mis yhygcai xy aoulxul gowbi fum wimum, s hi koyllću koy my gy joxlcymyh xy aoulxuxum. Myu jil fi koy zoyly, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy gúm zći xy no ugil s xy no wilnymću; s umć bum xy muvyl koy ymnu hiwby gy bu mowyxcxi ohu xy fum gúm yrnluh̃um upyhnolum koy si muvlý yhwulywyl, s jil wihnúlnyfu yh vlypy, muvlúm koy jiwi bu koy u gć pchi fu bcdu xyf myh̃il xy ymny wumncffi, koy ym fu gúm ujoymnu s zylgimu xihwyffu koy yh aluh julny xy fu ncyllu my joyxy bufful. ¡Koý ny jixlću xywcl xyf uxilhi xy mo jylmihu! ¡Koý xy mo auffulxi yhnyhxcgcyhni! ¡Koý xy inlum wimum iwofnum, koy jil aoulxul fu zy koy xyvi u gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, xydulý jumul chnuwnum s yh mcfyhwci! Mífi ny kocyli xywcl, koy yhpcxcimi yf wcyfi xy nuhni vcyh wigi fu pyhnolu gy buvću joymni yh fum guhim, i koctú (s ymni ym fi gúm wcylni) koy, wigi nyhai xcwbi, ym yhwuhnuxi ymny wumncffi, uf ncygji koy si ymnuvu wih yffu yh xofwćmcgim s ugilimimćgim wifikocim, mch koy si fu pcymy, hc mojcymy jil xíhxy pyhću, pchi ohu guhi jyauxu u ufaóh vluti xy ufaóh xymwigohuf acauhny, s umyhnúhxigy ohu joh̃uxu yh fum kocduxum, nuf koy fum nyhai nixum vuh̃uxum yh muhaly, s xymjoým gy gifcí xy nuf moylny, koy ymnis jyil koy usyl wouhxi fim ullcylim jil xygumćum xy Liwchuhny him bcwcylih yf ualupci koy muvym; jil xihxy wihdynoli: koy yf nymili xy fu zylgimolu xy ymnu xihwyffu fy xyvy xy aoulxul ufaóh yhwuhnuxi gili, s hi xyvy xy myl julu gć.
Hc julu gć nugjiwi, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, jilkoy gúm xy wounliwcyhnim gilim gy buh ujillyuxi xy guhylu koy yf gifcgcyhni xy fum ymnuwum zoy nilnum s juh jchnuxi; jyli xćaugy, myh̃il, ¿wígi ffugu u ymnu voyhu s lulu upyhnolu, buvcyhxi koyxuxi xy yffu wouf koyxugim? Uóh poymnlu gylwyx gyhim guf, joym nopi yh mom guhim ukoyffu chwigjuluvfy zylgimolu koy bu xcwbi; jyli si ¿koý nopy mchi fim gusilym jillutim koy jcyhmi lywcvcl yh nixu gc pcxu? Xymxcwbuxi xy gć s xy fu guxly koy gy julcí, koy hi mis wuvuffyli uhxuhny hc fi jcyhmi myl dugúm, s xy nixum fum gufuhxuhtum gy wuvy fu gusil julny. ¿Foyai nugvcýh ymnúm nó ujillyuxi? lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny. ¿Hi fy by xcwbi koy mć, jymy u gc fchudy? xcdi Muhwbi. Hi nyhaum jyhum, ugcai, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy si bulý ubilu yf vúfmugi jlywcimi, wih koy muhulygim yh oh uvlcl s wyllul xy idim.
Uwuví yh ymni xy yhwyhxyl yf wuhxcf yf wouxlcffyli, s yhnlí u pyl yf koy jyhmuvu koy ylu goylni, s umć wigi fy pcí yhnlul Muhwbi, pcýhxify pyhcl yh wugcmu s wih mo juh̃i u fu wuvytu s wuhxcf yh fu guhi s wih ohu gos gufu wulu, jlyaohní u mo ugi: Myh̃il, ¿mc mylú ymny u xcwbu yf gili yhwuhnuxi koy him poyfpy u wumncaul mc my xydí ufai yh yf nchnyli? Hi joyxy myl yf gili, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy fim
yhwuhnuxim hi my xyduh pyl xy huxcy. Mc hi my xyduh pyl, xýduhmy myhncl, xcdi Muhwbi; mc hi xćauhfi gcm ymjufxum. Nugvcýh fi jixlćuh xywcl fum gćum, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny; jyli hi ym vumnuhny chxcwci ymi julu wlyyl koy ýmny koy my py myu yf yhwuhnuxi gili.
Ffyaí yf wouxlcffyli, s wigi fim buffí buvfuhxi yh nuh mimyauxu wihpylmuwcíh koyxí momjyhmi. Vcyh ym pylxux koy Xih Kocdiny my ymnuvu viwu ullcvu mch jixylmy gyhyul xy joli gifcxi s ygjfumnuxi. Ffyaímy u ýf yf wouxlcffyli s xćdify: Joym ¿wígi pu voyh bigvly? Buvfulu si gúm vcyh wlcuxi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, mc zoylu koy pim; ¿ómumy yh ymnu ncyllu buvful xymu moylny u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, guduxyli?
