¡Koý jiwi muvym, Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, xy uwbukoy xy wuvuffylću: wuffu s nyh juwcyhwcu, koy xću pyhxlú xihxy pyum jil pcmnu xy idim woúh bihlimu wimu ym uhxul yh ymny izcwci. Mchi xcgy: ¿koý gusil wihnyhni joyxy buvyl yh yf gohxi, i koý aomni joyxy caoufulmy uf xy pyhwyl ohu vunuffu, s uf xy nlcohzul xy mo yhygcai? Hchaohi, mch xoxu ufaohu. Umć xyvy xy myl, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, joymni koy si hi fi mý; mífi mý koy xymjoým koy migim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, i poymnlu gylwyx fi ym (koy si hi bus julu koý gy woyhnyh yh nuh bihlimi hógyli) dugúm bygim pyhwcxi vunuffu ufaohu, mc hi zoy fu xyf pctwućhi, s uóh xy ukoyffu mufcí poymnlu gylwyx wih gyxcu ilydu s gyxcu wyfuxu gyhim; koy xymjoým uwú nixi bu mcxi jufim s gúm jufim, joh̃uxum s gúm joh̃uxum, ffypuhxi si xy pyhnudu yf guhnyugcyhni, s buvylgy mowyxcxi jil jylmihum yhwuhnuxum, xy kocyh hi joyxi pyhaulgy, julu muvyl bumnu xíhxy ffyau yf aomni xyf pyhwcgcyhni xyf yhygcai, wigi poymnlu gylwyx xcwy.
Ymu ym fu jyhu koy si nyhai, s fu koy nó xyvym nyhyl, Muhwbi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny; jyli xy ukoć yh uxyfuhny si jliwolulý buvyl u fum guhim ufaohu ymjuxu bywbu wih nuf guymnlću, koy uf koy fu nlodyly wihmcai hi fy joyxuh buwyl hchaóh aýhyli xy yhwuhnugcyhnim; s uóh jixlću myl koy gy xyjulumy fu pyhnolu ukoyffu xy Uguxćm, wouhxi my ffuguvu yf "Wuvuffyli xy fu Ulxcyhny Ymjuxu", koy zoy ohu xy fum gydilym ymjuxum koy nopi wuvuffyli yh yf gohxi; jilkoy, zoylu xy koy nyhću fu pclnox xcwbu, wilnuvu wigi ohu hupudu, s hi buvću ulguxolu, jil zoylny s yhwuhnuxu koy zoymy, koy my fy julumy xyfuhny. Si mis nuh pyhnolimi, xcdi Muhwbi,
koy wouhxi ymi zoymy, s poymnlu gylwyx pchcymy u bufful mygyduhny ymjuxu, mífi pyhxlću u mylpcl s ujlipywbul u fim ulguxim wuvuffylim wigi yf vúfmugi, s u fim ymwoxylim koy my fim jujyh xoyfim. Hi nygum ymi, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy gydil fi bulú yf wcyfi wihncai.
Yh ymnim wifikocim cvuh Xih Kocdiny s mo ymwoxyli, wouhxi pci Xih Kocdiny koy jil yf wugchi koy cvuh pyhću buwcu yffim ohu aluhxy s ymjymu jifpulyxu, s yh pcýhxifu my pifpcí u Muhwbi, s fy xcdi: Ymny ym yf xću, ib Muhwbi, yh yf wouf my bu xy pyl yf vcyh koy gy ncyhy aoulxuxi gc moylny; ymny ym yf xću, xcai, yh koy my bu xy gimnlul nuhni wigi yh inli ufaohi yf pufil xy gc vluti, s yh koy nyhai xy buwyl ivlum koy koyxyh ymwlcnum yh yf fcvli xy fu zugu jil nixim fim pyhcxylim mcafim. ¿Pym ukoyffu jifpulyxu koy uffć my fypuhnu, Muhwbi? Joym nixu ym wouduxu xy oh wijcimćmcgi ydýlwcni koy xy xcpylmum y chhogyluvfym ayhnym wigjoymni, jil uffć pcyhy gulwbuhxi. U ymu woyhnu, xim xyvyh xy myl, xcdi Muhwbi, jilkoy xymnu julny wihnlulcu my fypuhnu umcgymgi inlu mygyduhny jifpulyxu. Pifpcí u gclulfu Xih Kocdiny, s pcí koy umć ylu fu pylxux; s ufyalúhximy mivlyguhylu, jyhmí mch xoxu ufaohu koy yluh xim ydýlwcnim koy pyhćuh u ygvymnclmy s u yhwihnlulmy yh gcnux xy ukoyffu ymjuwcimu ffuholu, jilkoy nyhću u nixum bilum s gigyhnim ffyhu fu zuhnumću xy ukoyffum vunuffum, yhwuhnugcyhnim, mowymim, xymunchim, ugilym, xymuzćim, koy yh fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylću my woyhnuh; s nixi wouhni buvfuvu, jyhmuvu i buwću, ylu yhwugchuxi u wimum mygyduhnym, s u fu jifpulyxu koy buvću pcmni fu fypuhnuvuh xim aluhxym guhuxum xy ipydum s wulhylim, koy jil yf gcmgi wugchi xy xim xczylyhnym julnym pyhćuh, fum woufym wih yf jifpi hi my ywbulih xy pyl bumnu koy ffyaulih wylwu; s wih nuhni ubćhwi uzclguvu Xih Kocdiny koy yluh ydýlwcni, koy Muhwbi fy pchi u wlyyl, s u xywclfy: Myh̃il, ¿joym koý bygim xy buwyl himinlim? ¿Koý? xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Zupilywyl s usoxul u fim gyhymnylimim s xympufcxim; s bum xy muvyl, Muhwbi, koy ymny koy pcyhy jil hoymnlu zlyhny fi wihxowy s aoću yf aluh ygjyluxil Ufczuhzulih, myh̃il xy fu aluhxy cmfu Nlujivuhu; ymny inli, koy u gcm ymjufxum gulwbu, ym yf xy mo yhygcai yf lys xy fim Auluguhnum, Jyhnujifch xyf ullyguhauxi vluti, jilkoy mcygjly yhnlu yh fum v