Joym ¿jil koý my kocylyh nuh guf ymnim xim myh̃ilym? jlyaohní Muhwbi. Kocýlyhmy guf, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy ymny Ufczuhzulih ym oh zolcvohxi juauhi, s ymnú yhugiluxi xy fu bcdu xy Jyhnujifch, koy ym ohu gos bylgimu s uxygúm ualuwcuxu myh̃ilu, s ym wlcmncuhu, s mo juxly hi my fu kocyly yhnlyaul uf lys juauhi mc hi xydu jlcgyli fu fys xy mo zufmi jlizynu Gubigu, s my poyfpy u fu mosu. Julu gcm vulvum, xcdi Muhwbi, mc hi buwy gos vcyh Jyhnujifch, s koy fy nyhai xy usoxul yh wouhni joxcyly. Yh ymi bulúm fi koy xyvym, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy julu yhnlul yh vunuffum mygyduhnym hi lykocyly myl ulguxi wuvuffyli. Vcyh my gy ufwuhtu ymi, lymjihxcí Muhwbi; jyli ¿xíhxy jihxlygim u ymny umhi, koy ymnygim wcylnim xy buffulfy xymjoým xy jumuxu fu lyzlcyau, jilkoy uf yhnlul yh yffu yh mygyduhny wuvuffylću hi wlyi koy ymnú yh omi bumnu ubilu? Umć ym pylxux, xcdi Xih Kocdiny; fi koy joyxym buwyl xýf ym xydulfy u mom upyhnolum, ubilu my jcylxu i hi, jilkoy mylúh nuhni fim wuvuffim koy nyhxlygim xymjoým koy mufaugim pyhwyxilym, koy uóh willy jyfcali Liwchuhny hi fy nloykoy jil inli; jyli ymnúgy unyhni s gclu, koy ny kocyli xul woyhnu xy fim wuvuffylim gúm jlchwcjufym koy yh ymnim xim ydýlwcnim pcyhyh, s julu koy gydil fim pyum s fim hinym, lynclýgihim u ukoyf ufncffi koy uffć my buwy, xy xihxy my xyvyh xymwovlcl fim xim ydýlwcnim.
Bcwcýlihfi umć s jomcýlihmy mivly ohu figu, xymxy fu wouf my pyćuh vcyh fum xim guhuxum koy u Xih Kocdiny my fy bcwcylih ydýlwcni, mc fum hovym xyf jifpi koy fypuhnuvuh hi fym nolvulu s wyaulu fu pcmnu; jyli wih nixi ymni, pcyhxi yh mo cguachuwcíh fi koy hi pyću hc buvću, wih pit fypuhnuxu wigyhtí u xywcl: Ukoyf wuvuffyli koy uffć pym xy fum ulgum dufxym, koy nluy yh yf ymwoxi oh fyíh wilihuxi lyhxcxi u fim jcym xy ohu xihwyffu, ym yf pufylimi Fuolwufwi, myh̃il xy fu Joyhny xy Jfunu. Yf inli xy fum ulgum xy fum zfilym xy ili, koy nluy yh yf ymwoxi nlym wilihum xy jfunu yh wugji utof, ym yf nygcxi Gcwiwifygvi, aluh xokoy xy Kocliwcu. Yf inli
xy fim gcygvlim acauhnym koy ymnú u mo xylywbu guhi, ym yf hohwu gyxlimi Vluhxuvulvuluh xy Vifcwby, myh̃il xy fum nlym Uluvcum, koy pcyhy ulguxi xy ukoyf woyli xy myljcyhny, s ncyhy jil ymwoxi ohu joylnu, koy myaóh ym zugu, ym ohu xy fum xyf nygjfi koy xyllcví Muhmih wouhxi wih mo goylny my pyhaí xy mom yhygcaim. Jyli poyfpy fim idim u ymninlu julny, s pylúm xyfuhny s yh fu zlyhny xy ymninli ydýlwcni uf mcygjly pyhwyxil s dugúm pyhwcxi Ncgihyf xy Wulwudihu, jlćhwcjy xy fu Hoypu Pctwusu, koy pcyhy ulguxi wih fum ulgum julncxum u woulnyfym utofym, pylxym, vfuhwim s ugulcffim, s nluy yh yf ymwoxi oh auni xy ili yh wugji fyihuxi wih ohu fynlu koy xcwy "Gcuo", koy ym yf jlchwcjci xyf higvly xy mo xugu, koy myaóh my xcwy ym fu mch jul Gcuofchu, bcdu xyf xokoy xy Ufzyh̃ckoyh xyf Ufaulvy. Yf inli, koy wulau s ijlcgy fim figim xy ukoyffu jixylimu ufzuhu, koy nluy fum ulgum wigi hcypy vfuhwum, s yf ymwoxi vfuhwi s mch ygjlymu ufaohu, ym oh wuvuffyli hipyf, xy huwcíh zluhwým, ffuguxi Jcyllym Jujch, myh̃il xy fum vulihćum xy Onlckoy. Yf inli, koy vuny fum bcduxum wih fim bylluxim wulwuh̃im u ukoyffu jchnuxu s fcdylu wyvlu, s nluy fum ulgum xy fim pylim utofym, ym yf jixylimi xokoy xy Hylpcu, Ymjulnuzcfulxi xyf Vimkoy, koy nluy jil ygjlymu yh yf ymwoxi ohu ymjulluaoylu wih ohu fynlu yh wumnyffuhi, koy xcwy umć: "Lumnlyu gc moylny".
S xymnu guhylu zoý higvluhxi gowbim wuvuffylim xyf ohi s xyf inli ymwouxlíh koy ýf my cguachuvu, s u nixim fym xcí mom ulgum, wifilym, ygjlymum s ginym xy cgjlipcmi, ffypuxi xy fu cguachuwcíh xy mo hohwu pcmnu fiwolu, s mch julul jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi: U ymny ymwouxlíh zlihnyli zilguh s buwyh ayhnym xy xcpylmum huwcihym; ukoć ymnúh fim koy vyvyh fum xofwym uaoum xyf zugimi Duhni, fim gihnoimim koy jcmuh fim gumcfćmwim wugjim, fim koy wlcvuh yf zchćmcgi s gyhoxi ili yh fu zyfcwy Uluvcu, fim koy aituh fum zugimum s zlymwum lcvylum xyf wfuli Nylgixihny, fim koy muhaluh jil gowbum s xcpylmum pćum uf xiluxi Juwnifi, fim gogcxum xoximim yh mom jligymum, fim jylmum yh ulwim s zfywbum zugimim, fim julnim, fim gyxim, koy jyfyuh bosyhxi, fim úluvym xy goxuvfym wumum, fim wcnum nuh wloyfym wigi vfuhwim, fim ynćijym xy biluxuxim fuvcim, s inlum chzchcnum huwcihym wosim limnlim wihitwi s pyi, uohkoy xy fim higvlym hi gy uwoylxi. Yh ymninli ymwouxlíh pcyhyh fim koy vyvyh fum willcyhnym wlcmnufchum xyf ifcpćzyli Vyncm, fim koy nylmuh s jofyh wih yf fcwil xyf mcygjly lcwi s xiluxi Nudi, fim koy aituh fum jlipywbimum uaoum xyf xcpchi Ayhcf, fim koy jcmuh fim nulnymcim wugjim xy jumnim uvohxuhnym, fim koy my ufyaluh yh yfćmyim dylytuhim jluxim, fim guhwbyaim lcwim s wilihuxim xy lovcum ymjcaum, fim xy bcylli pymncxim, lyfckocum uhncaoum xy fu muhaly aixu, fim koy yh Jcmoylau my vuh̃uh, zugimi jil fu guhmyxogvly xy mo willcyhny, fim koy mo auhuxi ujuwcyhnuh yh fum yrnyhxcxum xybymum xyf nilnoimi Aouxcuhu, wyfyvluxi jil mo ymwihxcxi wolmi, fim koy ncygvfuh wih yf zlći xyf mcfvimi Jclchyi s wih fim vfuhwim wijim xyf fypuhnuxi Ujyhchi; zchufgyhny, wouhnim nixu fu Yoliju yh mć wihncyhy s yhwcylllu.
¡Púfugy Xcim, s woúhnum jlipchwcum xcdi, woúhnum huwcihym higvlí, xúhxify u wuxu ohu wih gulupcffimu jlymnytu fim unlcvonim koy fy jylnyhywćuh, nixi uvmilni s ygjujuxi yh fi koy buvću fyćxi yh mom fcvlim gyhnclimim! Ymnuvu Muhwbi Juhtu wifauxi xy mom jufuvlum mch buvful hchaohu, s xy wouhxi yh wouhxi pifpću fu wuvytu u pyl mc pyću fim wuvuffylim s acauhnym koy mo ugi higvluvu, s wigi hi xymwovlću u hchaohi fy xcdi: Myh̃il, yhwigcyhxi uf xcuvfi, mc bigvly, hc acauhny, hc wuvuffyli xy wouhnim poymnlu gylwyx xcwy julywy jil nixi ymni, u fi gyhim si hi fim pyi; koctú nixi ymni xyvy myl yhwuhnugcyhni wigi fum zuhnumgum xy uhiwby.
¿Wígi xcwym ymi? lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, ¿hi isym yf lyfchwbul xy fim wuvuffim, yf niwul xy fim wfulchym, yf locxi xy fim unugvilym? Hi icai inlu wimu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, mchi vufcxim xy ipydum s wulhylim, s umć ylu fu pylxux, jilkoy su ffyauvuh wylwu fim xim lyvuh̃im. Yf gcyxi koy ncyhym, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, ny buwy, Muhwbi, koy hc pyum hc icaum u xylywbum, jilkoy ohi xy fim yzywnim xyf gcyxi ym nolvul fim myhncxim, s buwyl koy fum wimum hi julytwuh fi koy mih; s mc ym koy nuhni nygym, lynćluny u ohu julny s xýdugy mifi, koy mifi vumni u xul fu pcwnilcu u fu julny u kocyh si xcyly gc usoxu. S xcwcyhxi ýmni jomi fum ymjoyfum u Liwchuhny, s joymnu fu
fuhtu yh yf lcmnly vudí xy fu wimnytoyfu wigi oh lusi. Xcify piwym Muhwbi, xcwcýhxify: Poýfpumy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il Xih Kocdiny, koy pini u Xcim koy mih wulhylim s ipydum fum koy pu u ygvymncl: poýfpumy, xymxcwbuxi xyf juxly koy gy yhayhxlí: ¡koý fiwolu ym ýmnu! Gcly koy hi bus acauhny hc wuvuffyli ufaohi, hc aunim, hc ulgum, hc ymwoxim julncxim hc yhnylim, hc pylim utofym hc yhxcuvfuxim. ¿Koý ym fi koy buwy? Jywuxil mis si u Xcim. Hc jil ymum pifpcí Xih Kocdiny, uhnym yh ufnum piwym cvu xcwcyhxi: Yu, wuvuffylim, fim koy myaoćm s gcfcnucm xyvudi xy fum vuhxylum xyf jixylimi ygjyluxil Jyhnujifch xyf ullyguhauxi vluti, myaocxgy nixim, pylycm woúh zuwcfgyhny fy xis pyhauhtu xy mo yhygcai Ufczuhzulih xy fu Nlujivuhu.
Ymni xcwcyhxi, my yhnlí jil gyxci xyf ymwouxlíh xy fum ipydum, s wigyhtí xy ufuhwyuffum wih nuhni wih wiludy s xyhoyxi, wigi mc xy pylum ufuhwyulu u mom gilnufym yhygcaim. Fim jumnilym s auhuxylim koy wih fu guhuxu pyhćuh, xúvuhfy piwym koy hi bcwcymy ukoyffi; jyli pcyhxi koy hi ujlipywbuvuh, xymwch̃ýlihmy fum ihxum, s wigyhtulih u mufoxulfy fim ićxim wih jcyxlum wigi yf joh̃i. Xih Kocdiny hi my woluvu xy fum jcyxlum; uhnym xcmwollcyhxi u nixum julnym, xywću: ¿Uxíhxy ymnúm, mivylvci Ufczuhzulih? Pyhny u gć, koy oh wuvuffyli mifi mis, koy xymyu xy mifi u mifi jlivul nom zoyltum s kocnulny fu pcxu yh jyhu xy fu koy xum uf pufylimi Jyhnujifch Auluguhnu.
Ffyaí yh ýmni ohu jyfuxcffu xy ullisi, s xúhxify yh oh fuxi, fy myjofní xim wimncffum yh yf woylji. Pcýhximy nuh gufnlywbi, wlysí mch xoxu koy ymnuvu goylni i guf zylcxi, s uwilxúhximy xy mo fcwil, muwí mo ufwotu, s jómimyfu u fu viwu, s wigyhtí u ywbul fcwil yh yf ymniguai; gum uhnym koy uwuvumy xy yhpumul fi koy u ýf fy julywću koy ylu vumnuhny ffyaí inlu ufgyhxlu, s xcífy yh fu guhi s yh fu ufwotu nuh xy ffyhi, koy my fu bcti jyxutim, ffypúhxify xy wugchi nlym i wounli xcyhnym s goyfum xy fu viwu, s guwbowúhxify gufugyhny xim xyxim xy fu guhi.
Nuf zoy yf aifjy jlcgyli, s nuf yf myaohxi, koy fy zoy ziltimi uf jivly wuvuffyli xul wihmcai xyf wuvuffi uvudi. Ffyaúlihmy u ýf fim jumnilym, s wlysyhxi koy fy buvćuh goylni, s umć wih gowbu jlcymu lywiacylih mo auhuxi, s wulaulih xy fum lymym goylnum, koy jumuvuh xy mcyny, s mch upylcaoul inlu wimu my zoylih. Ymnúvumy nixi ymny ncygji Muhwbi mivly fu woymnu, gcluhxi fum fiwolum koy mo ugi buwću, s ulluhwúvumy fum vulvum, gufxcwcyhxi fu bilu s yf johni yh koy fu zilnohu my fy buvću xuxi u wihiwyl. Pcýhxify, joym, wućxi yh yf moyfi, s koy su fim jumnilym my buvćuh cxi, vudí xy fu woymnu s ffyaímy u ýf, s buffúhxify xy gos guf ulny, uohkoy hi buvću jylxcxi yf myhncxi, s xćdify: ¿Hi fy xywću si, myh̃il Xih Kocdiny, koy my pifpcymy, koy fim koy cvu u uwigynyl hi yluh ydýlwcnim, mchi guhuxum xy wulhylim?
Wigi ými joyxy xymujulywyl s wihnlubuwyl ukoyf fuxlíh xyf muvci gc yhygcai, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny: múvyny, Muhwbi, koy ym gos zuwcf wimu u fim nufym buwylhim julywyl fi koy kocylyh, s ymny gufcahi koy gy jylmcaoy, yhpcxcimi xy fu afilcu koy pći koy si buvću xy ufwuhtul xymnu vunuffu, bu poyfni fim ymwouxlihym xy yhygcaim yh guhuxum xy ipydum. Mc hi but ohu wimu, Muhwbi, jil gc pcxu, jilkoy ny xymyhauh̃ym s pyum myl pylxux fi koy ny xcai: movy yh no umhi s mćaoyfim vihcnugyhny, s pylúm wígi, yh ufydúhximy xy ukoć ufaóh jiwi, my poyfpyh yh mo myl jlcgyli, s xyduhxi xy myl wulhylim, mih bigvlym bywbim s xylywbim, wigi ny fim jchný jlcgyli, jyli hi pusum ubilu, koy by gyhymnyl no zupil s usoxu; ffýauny u gć, s gclu woúhnum goyfum s xcyhnym gy zufnuh, koy gy julywy koy hi gy bu koyxuxi hchaohi yh fu viwu.
Ffyaímy Muhwbi nuh wylwu, koy wumc fy gynću fim idim yh fu viwu, s zoy u ncygji koy su buvću ivluxi yf vúfmugi yh yf ymníguai xy Xih Kocdiny, s uf ncygji koy Muhwbi ffyaí u gclulfy fu viwu, ullidí xy mć, gúm lywci koy ohu ymwijynu, wouhni xyhnli nyhću, s fy xcí wih nixi yffi yh fum vulvum xyf wigjumcpi ymwoxyli. ¡Muhnu Gulću!
xcdi Muhwbi. ¿S koý ym ýmni koy gy bu mowyxcxi? Mch xoxu ymny jywuxil ymnú bylcxi xy goylny, joym pigcnu muhaly jil fu viwu. Jyli lyjuluhxi oh jiwi gúm yh yffi, ywbí xy pyl yh fu wifil, muvil s ifil, koy hi ylu muhaly, mchi yf vúfmugi xy fu ufwotu koy ýf fy buvću pcmni vyvyl; s zoý nuhni yf umwi koy nigí, koy lypifpcýhximyfy yf ymníguai, pigcní fum nlcjum mivly mo gcmgi myh̃il, s koyxulih yhnlugvim wigi xy jylfum. Uwoxcí Muhwbi u mo umhi julu muwul xy fum ufzildum wih koý fcgjculmy s wih koý wolul u mo ugi, s wigi hi fum buffí, ymnopi u johni xy jylxyl yf docwci; gufxćdimy xy hoypi; s jlijomi yh mo wilutíh xy xydul u mo ugi s pifpylmy u mo ncyllu, uohkoy jylxcymy yf mufulci xy fi mylpcxi s fum ymjyluhtum xyf aivcylhi xy fu jligyncxu ćhmofu.
Fypúhnimy yh ymni Xih Kocdiny, s joymnu fu guhi ctkocylxu yh fu viwu, jilkoy hi my fy uwuvumyh xy mufcl fim xcyhnym, umcí wih fu inlu fum lcyhxum xy Liwchuhny, koy hohwu my buvću gipcxi xy dohni u mo ugi (nuf ylu xy fyuf s vcyh uwihxcwcihuxi), s zoymy u xihxy mo ymwoxyli ymnuvu, xy jywbim mivly mo umhi, wih fu guhi yh fu gydcffu yh aocmu xy bigvly jyhmuncpi, uxygúm, s pcýhxify Xih Kocdiny xy ukoyffu guhylu, wih goymnlum xy nuhnu nlcmnytu, fy xcdi: Múvyny, Muhwbi, koy hi ym oh bigvly gúm koy inli mc hi buwy gúm koy inli: nixum ymnu villumwum koy him mowyxyh mih myh̃ufym xy koy jlymni bu xy mylyhul yf ncygji, s buh xy mowyxylhim vcyh fum wimum, jilkoy hi ym jimcvfy koy yf guf hc yf vcyh myuh xoluvfym, s xy ukoć my mcaoy koy, buvcyhxi xoluxi gowbi yf guf, yf vcyh ymnú su wylwu, umć koy hi xyvym wihaidulny jil fum xymaluwcum koy u gć gy mowyxyh, joym u nc hi ny wuvy julny xy yffum. ¿Wígi hi? lymjihxcí Muhwbi; ¿jil pyhnolu yf koy usyl guhnyulih ylu inli koy yf bcdi xy gc juxly? ¿s fum ufzildum koy bis gy zufnuh mih xy inli koy xyf gcmgi? ¿Koý, ny zufnuh fum ufzildum, Muhwbi? xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Mć koy gy zufnuh, lymjihxcí Muhwbi. ¿Xy ymy gixi, hi nyhygim koy wigyl bis? lyjfcwí Xih Kocdiny. Ymi zoylu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, wouhxi zufnuluh jil ymnim jluxim fum sylvum koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy koy wihiwy, wih koy moyfyh mojfcl mygyduhnym zufnum fim nuh guf upyhnoluxim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, wigi poymnlu gylwyx ym.
Wih nixi ymi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, nigulu si gúm uchu oh woulnyf xy juh, i ohu biautu s xim wuvytum xy mulxchum ulyhkoym, koy wouhnum sylvum xymwlcvy Xcimwílcxym, uohkoy zoylu yf cfomnluxi xiwnil Fuaohu; gum wih nixi ýmni, movy yh no dogyhni, Muhwbi yf voyhi, s pyhny nlum gc, koy Xcim, koy ym jlipyyxil xy nixum fum wimum, hi him bu xy zufnul, s gúm uhxuhxi nuh yh mo mylpcwci wigi uhxugim, joym hi zufnu u fim gimkocnim xyf ucly, hc u fim aomuhcffim xy fu ncyllu, hc u fim lyhuwoudim xyf uaou, s ym nuh jcuximi, koy buwy mufcl mo mif mivly fim voyhim s gufim, s ffoypy mivly fim chdomnim s domnim. Gúm voyhi ylu poymnlu gylwyx, xcdi Muhwbi, julu jlyxcwuxil koy julu wuvuffyli uhxuhny. Xy nixi muvćuh s buh xy muvyl fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy wuvuffyli uhxuhny bovi yh fim jumuxim mcafim, koy umć my juluvu u buwyl oh mylgíh i jfúncwu yh oh wugchi lyuf, wigi mc zoylu aluxouxi jil fu ohcpylmcxux xy Julćm, xy xihxy my chzcyly, koy hohwu fu fuhtu ygviní fu jfogu, hc fu jfogu fu fuhtu. Ubilu vcyh, myu umć wigi poymnlu gylwyx xcwy, lymjihxcí Muhwbi; pugim ubilu xy ukoć s jliwolygim xihxy ufidul ymnu hiwby, s kocylu Xcim koy myu yh julny xihxy hi busu guhnum, hc guhnyuxilym, hc zuhnumgum, hc gilim yhwuhnuxim, koy mc fim bus, xulý uf xcuvfi yf buni s yf auluvuni.
Jćxymyfi nó u Xcim, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, aoću nó jil xihxy kocmcylym, koy ymnu pyt kocyli xydul u no yfywwcíh yf ufidulhim; jyli xugy uwú fu guhi, s uncýhnugy wih yf xyxi, s gclu vcyh woúhnim xcyhnym s goyfum gy zufnuh xymny fuxi xylywbi xy fu kocduxu ufnu, koy uffć mcyhni yf xifil. Gyncí Muhwbi fim xyxim, s ymnúhxify unyhnúhxi fy xcdi: ¿Woúhnum goyfum mifću poymnlu gylwyx nyhyl yh ymnu julny? Wounli, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, zoylu xy fu wilxuf nixum yhnylum s gos muhum. Gcly poymnlu gylwyx vcyh fi koy xcwy, myh̃il, lymjihxcí Muhwbi. Xcai wounli, mc hi yluh wchwi, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, jilkoy yh nixu gc pcxu gy buh muwuxi xcyhny hc goyfu xy fu viwu, hc my gy bu wućxi, hc wigcxi xy hyaocdih, hc xy lyogu ufaohu. Joym yh
ymnu julny xy uvudi, xcdi Muhwbi, hi ncyhy poymnlu gylwyx gúm xy xim goyfum s gyxcu, hc hchaohu, koy nixu ymnú lumu wigi fu jufgu xy fu guhi.
¡Mch pyhnolu si! xcdi Xih Kocdiny, isyhxi fum nlcmnym hoypum koy mo ymwoxyli fy xuvu, koy gúm kocmcylu koy gy bovcyluh xyllcvuxi oh vluti, wigi hi zoylu yf xy fu ymjuxu; jilkoy ny buai muvyl, Muhwbi, koy fu viwu mch goyfum ym wigi yf gifchi mch jcyxlu, s yh gowbi gúm my bu xy ymncgul oh xcyhny koy oh xcuguhny; gum u nixi ymni ymnugim modynim fim koy jlizymugim fu ymnlywbu ilxyh xy fu wuvuffylću. Movy, ugcai, s aoću, koy si ny myaoclý uf jumi koy kocmcylym. Bćtifi umć Muhwbi, s yhwugchimy buwcu xihxy fy julywcí koy jixću bufful uwiacgcyhni, mch mufcl xyf wugchi lyuf, koy jil uffć cvu gos myaocxi. Sýhximy, joym, jiwi u jiwi, jilkoy yf xifil xy fum kocduxum xy Xih Kocdiny hi fy xyduvu mimyaul, hc unyhxyl u xulmy jlcymu, kocmi Muhwbi yhnlynyhyffy s xcpylnclfy xcwcýhxify ufaohu wimu, s yhnly inlum koy fy xcdi, zoy fi koy my xclú yh yf mcaocyhny wujćnofi.
Wujćnofi 19: Xy fum xcmwlynum lutihym koy Muhwbi jumuvu wih mo ugi, s xy fu upyhnolu koy fy mowyxcí wih oh woylji goylni, wih inlim uwihnywcgcyhnim zugimim.
Julýwygy, myh̃il gći, koy nixum ymnum xympyhnolum koy ymnim xćum him buh mowyxcxi, mch xoxu ufaohu buh mcxi jyhu xyf jywuxi wigyncxi jil poymnlu gylwyx wihnlu fu ilxyh xy wuvuffylću, hi buvcyhxi wogjfcxi yf dolugyhni koy bcti xy hi wigyl juh u guhnyfym hc wih fu lychu zifaul, wih nixi ukoyffi koy u ymni my mcaoy s poymnlu gylwyx dolí xy wogjfcl, bumnu kocnul ukoyf ufgyny xy Gufuhxlchi, i wigi my ffugu yf gili, koy hi gy uwoylxi vcyh. Ncyhym gowbu lutíh, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny; gum julu xywclny pylxux, yffi my gy buvću jumuxi xy fu gygilcu s nugvcýh joyxym nyhyl jil wcylni koy jil fu wofju xy hi buvýlgyfi nó uwilxuxi yh ncygji, ny mowyxcí ukoyffi xy fu guhnu; jyli si bulý fu yhgcyhxu, koy gixim bus xy wigjimcwcíh yh fu ilxyh xy fu wuvuffylću julu nixi. ¿Joym dolý si ufai jil xcwbu? lymjihxcí Muhwbi. Hi cgjilnu koy hi busum doluxi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny; vumnu koy si yhncyhxi koy xy julncwcjuhnym hi ymnúm gos myaoli, s jil mć i jil hi, hi mylú gufi jlipyylhim xy lygyxci. Joym mc yffi ym umć, xcdi Muhwbi, gcly poymnlu gylwyx, hi my fy nilhy u ifpcxul ýmni wigi fi xyf dolugyhni; koctú fym pifpylú fu auhu u fim zuhnumgum xy mifutulmy inlu pyt wihgcai, s uóh wih poymnlu gylwyx, mc fy pyh nuh jylnchut.
Yh ýmnum s inlum jfúncwum fym nigí fu hiwby yh gcnux xyf wugchi, mch nyhyl hc xymwovlcl xihxy ukoyffu hiwby my lywiacymyh, s fi koy hi buvću xy voyhi yh yffi, ylu koy jylywćuh xy bugvly, koy wih fu zufnu xy fum ufzildum fym zufní nixu fu xymjyhmu s gunufinudy; s julu uwuvul xy wihzclgul ymnu xymaluwcu, fym ohu upyhnolu, koy mch ulnczcwci ufaohi pylxuxylugyhny fi julywću, s zoy koy fu hiwby wyllí wih ufaohu imwolcxux; jyli wih nixi ymni wugchuvuh, wlysyhxi Muhwbi koy, joym ukoyf wugchi ylu lyuf, u ohu i xim fyaoum xy voyhu lutíh buffulću yh ýf ufaohu pyhnu. Syhxi, joym, xymnu guhylu, fu hiwby imwolu, yf ymwoxyli bugvlcyhni, s yf ugi wih auhum xy wigyl, pcylih koy jil yf gcmgi wugchi koy cvuh pyhćuh buwcu yffim aluh gofncnox xy fogvlym, koy hi julywćuh mchi ymnlyffum koy my gipćuh.
Jumgímy Muhwbi yh pcýhxifum, s Xih Kocdiny hi fum nopi nixum wihmcai: nclí yf ohi xyf wuvymnli u mo umhi, s yf inli xy fum lcyhxum u mo liwchi, s ymnopcylih koyxim gcluhxi unyhnugyhny fi koy jixću myl ukoyffi, s pcylih koy fum fogvlym my cvuh uwylwuhxi u yffim, s gcyhnlum gúm my ffyauvuh, gusilym julywćuh, u wosu pcmnu Muhwbi wigyhtí u nygvful wigi oh utiauxi, s fim wuvyffim xy fu wuvytu my fy ylctulih u Xih Kocdiny, yf wouf, uhcgúhximy oh jiwi, xcdi: Ymnu mch xoxu, Muhwbi, xyvy xy myl aluhxćmcgu s jyfcalimćmcgu upyhnolu, xihxy mylú hywymulci koy si goymnly nixi gc pufil s ymzoylti. ¡Xymxcwbuxi xy gć! lymjihxcí Muhwbi. Mc uwumi ymnu upyhnolu zoymy xy zuhnumgum wigi gy fi pu julywcyhxi, ¿uxíhxy buvlú wimncffum koy fu mozluh? Jil gúm zuhnumgum koy myuh, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, hi wihmyhnclý si koy ny nikoyh yh yf jyfi xy fu liju, koy mc fu inlu pyt my volfulih wihncai, zoy jilkoy hi joxy mufnul fum julyxym xyf willuf, jyli ubilu ymnugim yh wugji lumi, xihxy jixlý si wigi kocmcylu ymalcgcl gc ymjuxu. S mc fy yhwuhnuh s yhnigywyh wigi fu inlu pyt fi bcwcylih, xcdi Muhwbi, ¿koý ujlipywbulú ymnul yh wugji uvcylni i hi? Wih nixi ymi, lyjfcwí Xih Kocdiny, ny loyai Muhwbi, koy nyhaum voyh úhcgi, koy fu yrjylcyhwcu ny xulú u yhnyhxyl yf koy si nyhai. Mć nyhxlý, mc u Xcim jfuwy, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, s ujulnúhximy fim xim u oh fuxi xyf wugchi, nilhulih u gclul unyhnugyhny fi koy ukoyffi xy ukoyffum fogvlym koy wugchuvuh jixću myl, s xy uffć u gos jiwi xymwovlcylih gowbim yhwugcmuxim, wosu
nygylimu pcmcíh xy nixi johni lyguní yf úhcgi xy Muhwbi Juhtu, yf wouf wigyhtí u xul xcyhny wih xcyhny wigi kocyh ncyhy zlći xy woulnuhu; s wlywcí gúm yf vuncl s xyhnyffyul wouhxi xcmnchnugyhny pcylih fi koy ylu, jilkoy xymwovlcylih bumnu pychny yhwugcmuxim, nixim u wuvuffi, wih mom buwbum yhwyhxcxum yh fum guhim, xynlúm xy fim woufym pyhću ohu fcnylu wovcylnu xy foni, u fu wouf myaoćuh inlim mycm xy u wuvuffi yhfonuxim bumnu fim jcým xy fum gofum, koy vcyh pcylih koy hi yluh wuvuffim yh yf mimcyai wih koy wugchuvuh; cvuh fim yhwugcmuxim golgoluhxi yhnly mć wih ohu pit vudu s wigjumcpu.
