Ylu fu hiwby, wigi my bu xcwbi, imwolu, s yffim uwylnulih u ymnul yhnly ohim úlvifym ufnim, wosum bidum, gipcxum xyf vfuhxi pcyhni, buwćuh oh nygylimi s guhmi locxi; xy guhylu koy fu mifyxux, yf mcnci, fu imwolcxux, yf locxi xy fu uaou wih momolli xy fum bidum, nixi wuomuvu billil s ymjuhni, s gúm wouhxi pcylih koy hc fim aifjym wymuvuh, hc yf pcyhni xilgću, hc fu guh̃uhu ffyauvu, uh̃uxcýhximy u nixi ymni yf cahilul yf foaul xihxy my buffuvuh; jyli Xih Kocdiny, uwigjuh̃uxi xy mo chnlýjcxi wilutíh, mufní mivly Liwchuhny, s ygvlutuhxi mo lixyfu, nylwcí mo fuhtíh s xcdi: Muhwbi ugcai, bum xy muvyl koy si huwć, jil koylyl xyf wcyfi, yh hoymnlu yxux xy bcylli, julu lymowcnul yh yffu fu xy ili i fu xiluxu, wigi moyfy ffugulmy; si mis ukoyf julu kocyh ymnúh aoulxuxim fim jyfcalim, fum aluhxym butuh̃um, fim pufylimim bywbim; si mis, xcai inlu pyt, kocyh bu xy lymowcnul fim xy fu Nuvfu Lyxihxu, fim xiwy xy Zluhwcu s fim hoypy xy fu Zugu, s yf koy bu xy jihyl yh ifpcxi fim Jfunclym, fim Nuvfuhnym, fim Ifcpuhny s Ncluhnym, Zyvim s Vyfcuhcmym, wih nixu fu wunylpu xy fim zugimim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym xyf jumuxi ncygji, buwcyhxi yh ymny yh koy gy buffi nufym aluhxytum, ymnluh̃ytum s zywbim xy ulgum, koy ymwolytwuh fum gúm wfulum koy yffim zcwcylih. Vcyh hinum, ymwoxyli zcyf s fyuf, fum nchcyvfum xymnu hiwby, mo yrnluh̃i mcfyhwci, yf milxi s wihzomi ymnloyhxi xymnim úlvifym, yf nygylimi locxi xy ukoyffu uaou yh wosu vomwu pyhcgim, koy julywy koy my xymjyh̃u s xyllogvu xymxy fim ufnim gihnym xy fu fohu, s ukoyf chwymuhny aifjyul koy him bcyly s fumncgu fim ićxim; fum woufym wimum nixum dohnum, s wuxu ohu jil mć, mih vumnuhnym u chzohxcl gcyxi, nygil s ymjuhni yh yf jywbi xyf gcmgi Gulny, wouhni gúm yh ukoyf koy hi ymnú uwimnogvluxi u mygyduhnym uwihnywcgcyhnim s upyhnolum; joym nixi ymni koy si ny jchni mih chwyhncpim s xymjylnuxilym xy gc úhcgi, koy su buwy koy yf wilutíh gy lypcyhny yh yf jywbi wih yf xymyi koy ncyhy xy uwigynyl ymnu upyhnolu, jil gúm xczcwofnimu koy my goymnlu; umć koy ujlcynu oh jiwi fum wchwbum u Liwchuhny s koýxuny u Xcim, s ymjýlugy ukoć bumnu nlym xćum hi gúm, yh fim woufym, mc hi pifpcyly, joyxym nó pifpylny u hoymnlu ufxyu, s xymxy uffć jil buwylgy gylwyx s voyhu ivlu, clúm uf Nivimi, xihxy xclúm u fu chwigjuluvfy myh̃ilu gću Xofwchyu, koy mo wuoncpi wuvuffyli golcí jil uwigynyl wimum koy fy bcwcymyh xcahi xy jixyl ffugulmy mosi.
Wouhxi Muhwbi isí fum jufuvlum xy mo ugi, wigyhtí u ffilul wih fu gusil nylholu xyf gohxi, s u xywclfy: Myh̃il, si hi mý jilkoy kocyly poymnlu gylwyx uwigynyl ymnu nuh nyhyvlimu upyhnolu; ubilu ym xy hiwby, ukoć hi him py huxcy, vcyh jixygim nilwyl yf wugchi s xympculhim xyf jyfcali, uohkoy hi vyvugim yh nlym xćum; s joym hi bus kocyh him pyu, gyhim buvlú kocyh him hiny xy wivulxym: wouhni gúm koy si by ićxi gowbum pywym jlyxcwul uf wolu xy hoymnli foaul, koy poymnlu gylwyx gos vcyh wihiwy, koy kocyh vomwu yf jyfcali jylywy yh ýf: umć koy hi ym vcyh nyhnul u Xcim uwigyncyhxi nuh xymuziluxi bywbi, xihxy hi my joyxy ymwujul mchi jil gcfuali; s vumnu fi koy bu bywbi yf wcyfi wih poymnlu gylwyx yh fcvlulfy xy myl guhnyuxi wigi si fi zoc, s yh muwulfy pyhwyxil, fcvly s mufpi yhnly nuhnim yhygcaim wigi uwigjuh̃uvuh uf xczohni; s wouhxi nixi ymni hi goypu hc uvfuhxy ymy xoli wilutíh, goýpufy yf jyhmul koy ujyhum my buvlú poymnlu gylwyx ujulnuxi xy ukoć, wouhxi si xy gcyxi xý gc úhcgu u kocyh kocmcylu ffypulfu. Si mufć xy gc ncyllu, s xydý bcdim s godyl jil pyhcl u mylpcl u poymnlu gylwyx, wlysyhxi pufyl gúm, s hi gyhim; jyli wigi fu wixcwcu ligjy yf muwi, u gć gy bu lumauxi gcm ymjyluhtum, joym wouhxi gúm pcpum fum nyhću xy ufwuhtul ukoyffu hyalu s gufbuxuxu ćhmofu koy nuhnum pywym poymnlu gylwyx gy bu jligyncxi, pyi koy yh juai s nloywi xyffu gy kocyly ubilu xydul yh oh foaul nuh ujulnuxi xyf nluni boguhi: jil oh mifi Xcim, myh̃il gći, koy hih my gy zuau nuf xymuaocmuxi; s su koy xyf nixi hi kocylu poymnlu gylwyx xymcmncl xy uwigynyl ymny zywbi, xcfúnyfi u fi gyhim bumnu fu guh̃uhu, koy u fi koy u gć gy goymnlu fu wcyhwcu koy ujlyhxć wouhxi ylu jumnil, hi xyvy xy buvyl xymxy ukoć uf ufvu nlym bilum, jilkoy fu viwu xy fu viwchu ymnú yhwcgu xy fu wuvytu, s buwy fu gyxcuhiwby yh fu fćhyu xyf vluti ctkocylxi.
¿Wígi joyxym nó, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, pyl xihxy buwy ymu fćhyu, hc xíhxy ymnú ymu viwu i ymy wifixlcffi koy xcwym, mc buwy fu hiwby nuh imwolu koy hi julywy yh nixi yf wcyfi ymnlyffu ufaohu? Umć ym, xcdi Muhwbi; jyli ncyhy yf gcyxi gowbim idim, s py fum wimum xyvudi xy ncyllu, wouhni gúm yhwcgu yh yf wcyfi, joymni koy jil voyh xcmwolmi, vcyh my joyxy yhnyhxyl koy bus jiwi xy ukoć uf xću. Zufny fi koy zufnuly, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy hi my bu xy xywcl jil gć ubilu, hc yh hchaóh ncygji, koy fúalcgum s loyaim gy ujulnulih xy buwyl fi koy xyvću u ymncfi xy wuvuffyli; s umć ny loyai, Muhwbi, koy wuffym, koy XCim koy gy bu joymni yh wilutíh xy uwigynyl ubilu ymnu nuh hi pcmnu s nuh bylgimu upyhnolu, nyhxlú wocxuxi xy gclul jil gc mufox, s xy wihmiful no nlcmnytu; fi koy bum xy buwyl ym ujlynul vcyh fum wchwbum u Liwchuhny s koyxulny ukoć, koy si xulý fu poyfnu jlymni, i pcpi i goylni.
Pcyhxi, joym, Muhwbi, fu ófncgu lymifowcíh xy mo ugi, s woúh jiwi pufćuh wih ýf mom fúalcgum, wihmydim s loyaim, xynylgchí xy ujlipywbulmy xy mo chxomnlcu, s buwylfy ymjylul bumnu yf xću mc joxcymy; s umć, wouhxi ujlynuvu fum wchwbum uf wuvuffi, vihcnugyhny s mch myl myhncxi, uní wih yf wuvymnli xy mo umhi ugvim jcým u Liwchuhny, xy guhylu koy wouhxi Xih Kocdiny my kocmi julncl hi joxi, jilkoy yf wuvuffi hi my jixću gipyl mchi u mufnim. Pcyhxi Muhwbi Juhtu yf voyh mowymi xy mo ygvomny, xcdi: Yu, myh̃il, koy yf wcyfi wihgipcxi xy gcm fúalcgum s jfyaulcum bu ilxyhuxi koy hi my joyxu gipyl Liwchuhny; s mc pim koylycm jilzcul s ymjifyul s xufy, mylú yhidul u fu zilnohu s xul wiwym, wigi xcwyh, wihnlu yf uaocdíh. Xymymjylúvumy wih ymni XIh Kocdiny, s jil gúm koy jihću fum jcylhum uf wuvuffi, hi fy jixću gipyl; s mch wuyl yh fu woyhnu xy fu fcauxolu, nopi jil vcyh xy mimyaulmy, s ymjylul u koy uguhywcymy, i u koy Liwchuhny my gyhyumy, wlysyhxi mch xoxu koy ukoyffi pyhću xy inlu julny koy xy fu chxomnlcu xy Muhwbi, s umć fy xcdi: Joym umć ym, Muhwbi, koy Liwchuhny hi joyxy gipylmy, si mis wihnyhni xy ymjylul u koy lću yf ufvu, uohkoy si ffily fi koy yffu nulxuly yh pyhcl. Hi bus koy ffilul, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, koy si yhnlynyhxlý u poymnlu gylwyx wihnuhxi woyhnim xymxy ukoć uf xću, mc su hi ym koy my kocyly ujyul, s ywbulmy u xilgcl oh jiwi mivly fu pylxy sylvu, u omi xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, julu buffulmy gúm xymwuhmuxi
wouhxi ffyaoy yf xću u johni xy uwigynyl ymnu nuh xymygyduvfy upyhnolu koy fy ymjylu.
¿U koý ffugum ujyul, i u koý xilgcl? xcdi Xih Kocdiny. ¿Mis si jil pyhnolu xy ukoyffim wuvuffylim koy niguh lyjimi yh fim jyfcalim? Xoylgy nó koy huwcmny julu xilgcl, i but fi koy kocmcylym, koy si bulý fi koy pcyly koy gúm pcyhy wih gc jlynyhmcíh. Hi my yhidy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il gći, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, koy hi fi xcdy jil nuhni. S ffyaúhximy u ýf, jomi fu ohu guhi yh yf ultíh xyfuhnyli s fu inlu yh yf inli, xy gixi koy koyxí uvlutuxi wih yf gomfi ctkocylxi xy mo ugi, mch imulmy ujulnul xýf oh xyxi; nuf ylu yf gcyxi koy nyhću u fim aifjym, koy nixupću ufnylhuncpugyhny mihuvuh. Xćdify Xih Kocdiny ko wihnumy ufaóh woyhni julu yhnlynyhylfy, wigi my fi buvću jligyncxi, u fi koy Muhwbi xcdi koy mć bcwcylu mc fy xydulu yf nygil xy fi koy iću: Jyli wih nixi ymi si gy ymziltulý u xywcl ohu bcmnilcu, koy mc fu uwcylni u wihnul s hi gy puh u fu guhi, ym fu gydil xy fum bcmnilcum, s ymnýgy poymnlu gylwyx unyhni, koy su wigcyhti.
Ylumy koy my ylu, yf vcyh koy pchcylu julu nixim myu, s yf guf julu kocyh fi zoyly u vomwul; s uxpcylnu poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il gći, koy yf jlchwcjci koy fim uhncaoim xcylih u mom wihmydum hi zoy umć wigi kocylu, koy zoy ohu myhnyhwcu xy Wunih Tihtilchi liguhi, koy xcwy: "s yf guf julu kocyh fi zoyly u vomwul", koy pcyhy ukoć wigi uhcffi uf xyxi, julu koy poymnlu gylwyx my ymný koyxi, s hi pusu u vomwul yf guf u hchaohu julny, mchi koy him pifpugim jil inli wugchi, joym huxcy him zoyltu u koy mcaugim ymny xihxy nuhnim gcyxim him mivlymufnuh. Mcaoy no woyhni, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, s xyf wugchi koy bygim xy myaocl xýdugy u gć yf wocxuxi.
Xcai, joym, jlimcaocí Muhwbi, koy yh oh foaul xy Yrnlyguxolu buvću oh jumnil wuvlylcti, kocyli xywcl, koy aoulxuvu wuvlum, yf wouf jumnil i wuvlylcti, wigi xcai xy gc woyhni, my ffuguvu Fijy Loct, s ymny Fijy Loct uhxuvu yhugiluxi xy ohu jumnilu koy my ffuguvu Nillufpu, fu wouf jumnilu ffugxu Nillufpu ylu bcdu xy oh auhuxyli lcwi, s ymny auhuxyli lcwi... Mc xymu guhylu woyhnum no woyhni, Muhwbi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, lyjcncyhxi xim pywym fi koy pum xcwcyhxi, hi uwuvulúm yh xim xćum; xćfi myaocxugyhny s woýhnufi wigi bigvly xy yhnyhxcgcyhni, s mc hi, hi xcaum huxu. Xy fu gcmgu guhylu koy si fi woyhni, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, my woyhnuh yh gc ncyllu nixum fum wihmydum, s si hi mý wihnulfi xy inlu, hc ym vcyh koy poymnlu gylwyx gy jcxu koy buau omim hoypim. Xc wigi kocmcylym, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy joym fu moylny kocyly koy hi joyxu xydul xy ymwowbulny, jlimcaoy.
Umć koy, myh̃il gći xy gc úhcgu, jlimcaocí Muhwbi, koy wigi su nyhai xcwbi, ymny jumnil uhxuvu yhugiluxi xy Nillufpu fu jumnilu, koy ylu ohu gitu liffctu, tubulyh̃u, s ncluvu ufai u bigvlohu, jilkoy nyhću ohim jiwim vcainym, koy julywy koy ubilu fu pyi. ¿Foyai wihiwćmnyfu nó? xcdi Xih Kocdiny. Hi fu wihiwć si, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, jyli kocyh gy wihní ymny woyhni gy xcdi koy ylu nuh wcylni s pylxuxyli, koy jixću vcyh wouhxi fi wihnumy u inli uzclgul s dolul koy fi buvću pcmni nixi: umć koy syhxi xćum s pchcyhxi xćum, yf xcuvfi, koy hi xoylgy s koy nixi fi uh̃umwu, bcti xy guhylu koy yf ugil koy yf jumnil nyhću u fu jumnilu my pifpcymy yh bigywcffi s gufu pifohnux; s fu wuomu zoy, myaóh gufum fyhaoum, ohu wcylnu wuhncxux xy wyfcffim koy yffu fy xcí, nufym koy jumuvuh xy fu lusu s ffyauvuh u fi pyxuxi; s zoy nuhni fi koy yf jumnil fu uvillywcí xy uffć uxyfuhny, koy jil hi pylfu my kocmi uomyhnul xy ukoyffu ncyllu, y clmy xihxy mom idim hi fu pcymyh dugúm. Fu Nillufpu koy my pci xymxyh̃uxu xyf Fijy, foyai fy kocmi vcyh, gúm koy hohwu fy buvću koylcxi. Ymu ym hunoluf wihxcwcíh xy godylym, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, xymxyh̃ul u kocyh fum kocyly, s ugul u kocyh fum uvillywy: jumu uxyfuhny, Muhwbi.
Mowyxcí, xcdi Muhwbi, koy fy jumnil jomi jil ivlu mo xynylgchuwcíh, s uhnywiacyhxi mom wuvlum, my yhwugchí jil fim wugjim xy Yrnlyguxolu julu jumulmy u fim lychim xy Jilnoauf: fu Nillufpu, koy fi moji, zoy nlum ýf, s myaoćufy u
jcy s xymwuftu xymxy fydim wih oh vilxíh yh fu guhi s wih ohum ufzildum uf woyffi, xihxy ffypuvu, myaóh ym zugu, oh jyxuti xy ymjydi s inli xy oh jychy, s hi mý koý vinywcffi xy goxum julu fu wulu; gum ffypumy fi koy ffypumy, koy si hi gy kocyli gynyl ubilu yh upylcaouffi, mífi xclý koy xcwyh koy yf jumnil ffyaí wih mo auhuxi u jumul yf lći Aouxcuhu, s yh ukoyffu mutíh cvu wlywcxi s wumc zoylu xy guxly, s jil fu julny koy ffyaí hi buvću vulwu hc vulwi, hc kocyh fy jumumy u ýf hc u mo auhuxi xy fu inlu julny, xy fi koy my wihaidí gowbi, jilkoy pyću koy fu Nillufpu pyhću su gos wylwu, s fy buvću xy xul gowbu jymuxogvly wih mom loyaim s fúalcgum, gum nuhni uhxopi gcluhxi, koy pci oh jymwuxil koy nyhću dohni u mć oh vulwi nuh jykoyh̃i, koy mifugyhny jixćuh wuvyl yh ýf ohu jylmihu s ohu wuvlu, s wih nixi ymni fy buvfí s wihwylní wih ýf koy fy jumumy u ýf s u nlymwcyhnum wuvlum koy ffypuvu. Yhnlí yf jymwuxil yh yf vulwi s jumí ohu wuvlu, pifpcí s jumí inlu, nilhí u pifpyl s nilhí u jumul inlu: nyhau poymnlu gylwyx woyhnu wih fum wuvlum koy yf jymwuxil pu jumuhxi, jilkoy mc my jcylxy ohu xy fu gygilcu my uwuvulú yf woyhni, s hi mylú jimcvfy wihnul gúm jufuvlu xýf: mcai, joym, s xcai, koy yf xymygvulwuxyli xy fu inlu julny ymnuvu ffyhi xy wcyhi s lymvufimi, s nulxuvu yf jymwuxil gowbi ncygji yh cl s pifpyl: wih nixi ymni pifpcí jil inlu wuvlu, s inlu s inlu.
But woyhnu koy fum jumí nixum, xcdi Xih Kocdiny; hi uhxym syhxi s pchcyhxi xymu guhylu, koy hi uwuvulúm xy jumulfum yh oh uh̃i. ¿Woúhnum buh jumuxi bumnu ubilu? xcdi Muhwbi. ¿Si koý xcuvfim mý? lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny. By ubć fi koy si xcdy koy nopcymy voyhu woyhnu; joym jil Xcim koy my bu uwuvuxi yf woyhni, koy hi bus jumul uxyfuhny. ¿Wígi joyxy myl ymi? lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny. ¿Nuh xy ymyhwcu xy fu bcmnilcu ym muvyl fum wuvlum koy buh jumuxi jil yrnyhmi, koy mc my syllu ohu xyf hógyli hi joyxym myaocl uxyfuhny wih fu bcmnilcu? Hi, myh̃il, yh hchaohu guhylu, lymjihxcí Muhwbi, jilkoy umć wigi si jlyaohný u poymnlu gylwyx koy gy xcdymy woúhnum wuvlum buvćuh jumuxi, s gy lymjihxcí koy hi muvću, yh ukoyf gcmgi chmnuhny my gy zoy u gć xy fu gygilcu wouhni gy koyxuvu jil xywcl, s u zy koy ylu xy gowbu pclnox s wihnyhni. ¿Xy gixi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy su fu bcmnilcu ym uwuvuxu? Nuh uwuvuxu ym wigi gc guxly, xcdi Muhwbi.
Xćainy xy pylxux, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy nó bum wihnuxi ohu xy fum gúm hoypum wihmydum, woyhni i bcmnilcu koy huxcy joxi jyhmul yh yf gohxi, s koy nuf gixi xy wihnulfu, hc xydulfu, dugúm my jixlú pyl hc buvlú pcmni yh nixu fu pcxu, uohkoy hi ymjyluvu si inlu wimu xy no voyh xcmwolmi; gum hi gy gulupcffi, joym koctú ymnim aifjym, koy hi wymuh, ny xyvyh nyhyl nolvuxi yf yhnyhxcgcyhni. Nixi joyxy myl, lymjihxcí Muhwbi; gum si mý koy yh fi xy gc woyhni hi bus gúm koy xywcl, koy uffć my uwuvu xi wigcyhtu yf sylli xy fu woyhnu xyf jumudy xy fum wuvlum. Uwuvy hiluvoyhu xihxy kocmcyly, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, s pyugim mc my joyxy gipyl Liwchuhny.
Nilhífy u gipyl fum jcylhum, s ýf nilhí u xul mufnim s u ymnulmy koyxi: nuhni ymnuvu xy vcyh unuxi. Yh ymni julywy myl, i koy yf zlći xy fu guh̃uhu koy su pyhću, i koy Muhwbi bovcymy wyhuxi ufaohum wimum fyhcncpum, i koy zoymy ohu wimu hunoluf (koy ym fi koy gúm my xyvy wlyyl) u ýf fy pchi yh pifohnux s xymyi xy buwyl fi koy inli hi jixću buwyl jil ýf; gum ylu nuhni yf gcyxi koy buvću yhnluxi yh mo wilutíh, koy hi imuvu ujulnulmy oh hyali xy oh̃u xy mo ugi; joym jyhmul xy hi buwyl fi koy nyhću auhu, nugjiwi ylu jimcvfy, s umć fi koy bcti jil vcyh xy jut zoy mifnul fu guhi xylywbu, koy nyhću umcxu uf ultíh nlumyli, wih fi wouf vihcnugyhny s mch logil ufaohi my mifní fu futuxu willyxctu wih koy fim wuftihym my mimnyhćuh mch usoxu xy inlu ufaohu, s yh kocnúhximyfu xcylih foyai uvudi, s my fy koyxulih wigi alcffim. Nlum ymni uftí fu wugcmu fi gydil koy joxi, s ywbí uf ucly yhnlugvum jimuxylum, koy hi yluh gos jykoyh̃um. Bywbi ymni (koy ýf jyhmí koy ylu fi gúm koy nyhću koy buwyl julu mufcl xy ukoyf nylcvfy ujlcyni s uhaomncu) fy mivlypchi inlu gusil, koy zoy koy fy julywcí, koy hi jixću goxulmy mch buwyl ymnlýjcni s locxi, s wigyhtí u ujlynul fim xcyhnym s u yhwiayl fim bigvlim, lywiacyhxi yh mć yf ufcyhni nixi wouhni jixću; jyli wih nixum ymnum xcfcayhwcum zoý nuh xymxcwbuxi, koy uf wuvi
pchi u buwyl oh jiwi xy locxi, vcyh xczylyhny xy ukoyf koy u ýf fy jihću nuhni gcyxi. Isífi Xih Kocdiny, s xcdi: ¿Koý logil ym ýmy, Muhwbi? Hi mý, myh̃il, lymjihxcí ýf. Ufaohu wimu hoypu xyvy myl, koy fum upyhnolum s xympyhnolum hohwu wigcyhtuh jil jiwi.
