Xy hoypi nilhí u ffilul Muhwbi, isyhxi xy hoypi fum fumncgylum lutihym xy mo voyh myh̃il, s xynylgchí xy hi xydulfy bumnu yf ófncgi nluhwy s zch xy ukoyf hyaiwci.
