Ufvilinímy Liwchuhny wih yf ymnloyhxi xyf uaou s xy fim aifjym, s mimyaúhxify Xih Kocdiny, my zoy ffyaúhxify jiwi u jiwi u fum wumum; yhwigyhxímy xy nixi wilutíh u mo myh̃ilu, mojfcwúhxify koy yh ukoyffu nygylimu dilhuxu s ygjlymu fy zupilywcymy, s xy wugchi my yhwigyhxuvu nugvcýh u Xcim koy hi fy ifpcxumy. Hi my fy kocnuvu Muhwbi xyf fuxi, yf wouf ufulauvu wouhni jixću yf woyffi s fu pcmnu jil yhnly fum jcylhum xy Liwchuhny, jil pyl mc pylću su fi koy nuh momjyhmi s gyxlimi fy nyhću.
