Wouhxi Xih Kocdiny pcí fi koy ylu, yhgoxywcí s jumgímy xy ullcvu uvudi. Gclífy Muhwbi, s pcí koy nyhću fu wuvytu chwfchuxu mivly yf jywbi wih goymnlum xy ymnul willcxi.
