Pcyhxi, joym, Xih Kocdiny koy Muhwbi buwću volfu xýf, my willcí s yhidi yh nuhnu guhylu, koy uftí yf fuhtíh s fy umyhní xim jufim, nufym koy mc wigi fim lywcvcí yh fum ymjufxum fim lywcvcylu yh fu wuvytu, koyxulu fcvly xy juaulfy yf mufulci, mc hi zoylu u mom bylyxylim.
Pcyhxi Muhwbi koy muwuvu nuh gufum pylum xy mom volfum, wih nygil xy koy mo ugi hi jumumy uxyfuhny yh yffum, wih gowbu bogcfxux fy xcdi: Mimcýaoymy poymnlu gylwyx, koy jil Xcim koy gy volfi. Joym ¿jil koý im volfucm?Hi gy volfi si, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny. Pyhcx uwú myh̃il ufyaly: ¿julýwyim u pim koy wigi mc ymnim zoylih gutim xy vunúh zoyluh inlu jyfcalimu upyhnolu, hi buvću si gimnluxi yf úhcgi koy wihpyhću julu ygjlyhxyffu s uwuvuffu? ¿Ymnis si ivfcauxi u xcwbu, mcyhxi wigi mis wuvuffyli, u wihiwyl s xcmnchaocl fim mihym, s muvyl woufym mih fim xy fim vunuhym i hi? S gúm koy jixlću myl, wigi ym pylxux, koy hi fim by pcmni yh gc pcxu, wigi pim fim buvlýcm pcmni, wigi pcffuhi loch koy micm, wlcuxi s huwcxi yhnly yffim; mc hi, buwyx pim koy ymnim mycm gutim my poyfpuh yh mycm dusuhym, s
ywbúxgyfim u fum vulvum ohi u ohi, i nixim dohnim, s wouhxi si hi xcyly wih nixim junum ullcvu, buwyx xy gć fu volfu koy kocmcýlyxym.
Hi busu gúm, myh̃il gći, lyjfcwí Muhwbi, koy si wihzcymi koy by uhxuxi ufai lcmoyh̃i yh xygumću; jyli xćaugy poymnlu gylwyx, ubilu koy ymnugim yh jut, umć Xcim fy mukoy xy nixum fum upyhnolum koy fy mowyxcylyh nuh muhi s mufpi wigi fy bu muwuxi xymnu: ¿hi bu mcxi wimu xy lyćl, s fi ym xy wihnul, yf aluh gcyxi koy bygim nyhcxi? U fi gyhim yf koy si nopy, koy xy poymnlu gylwyx su si mý koy hi fi wihiwy, hc muvy koy ym nygil hc ymjuhni.
