Nuf jixlću willyl yf xuxi, xcdi Xih Kocdiny, koy nixi fi koy xcwym pchcymy u myl pylxux, s jylxihu fi jumuxi, joym ylym xcmwlyni s muvym koy fim jlcgylim gipcgcyhnim hi mih yh guhim xyf bigvly, s ymnú uxpylncxi xy ukoć yh uxyfuhny yh ohu wimu, julu koy ny uvmnyhaum s lyjilnym yh yf buvful xygumcuxi wihgcai, koy yh wouhnim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum by fyćxi, koy mih chzchcnim, dugúm by buffuxi koy hchaóh ymwoxyli buvfumy nuhni wih mo myh̃il wigi nó wih yf nosi, s yh pylxux koy fi nyhai u aluh zufnu nosu s gću: nosu, yh koy gy ymncgum yh jiwi; gću, yh koy hi gy xydi ymncgul yh gúm: mć koy Aufuxch, ymwoxyli xy Uguxćm xy Auofu, wihxy, zoy xy fu Chmofu zclgy, s my fy xýf koy mcygjly buvfuvu u mo myh̃il wih fu aillu yh fu guhi, chwfchuxu fu wuvytu s xivfuxi yf woylji gily nolkoymwi. Joym ¿koý xclygim xy Aumuvuf, ymwoxyli xy xih Aufuil, koy zoy nuh wuffuxi, koy julu xywfululhim fu yrwyfyhwcu xy mo gulupcffimi mcfyhwci, mífi ohu pyt my higvlu mo higvly yh nixu ukoyffu nuh aluhxy wigi gulupcffimu bcmnilcu? Xy nixi fi koy by xcwbi bum xy chzylcl, Muhwbi, koy ym gyhymnyl buwyl xczylyhwcu xy ugi u giti, xy myh̃il u wlcuxi, s xy wuvuffyli u ymwoxyli; umć koy xymxy bis yh uxyfuhny him bygim xy nlunul wih gúm lymjyni, mch xulhim wilxyfydi, jilkoy xy woufkocylu guhylu koy si gy yhidy wih pim bu xy myl guf julu yf wúhnuli. Fum gylwyxym s vyhyzcwcim koy si im by jligyncxi ffyaulúh u mo ncygji, s mc hi ffyaulyh, yf mufulci u fi gyhim hi my bu xy jylxyl, wigi su im by xcwbi. Ymnu vcyh wouhni poymnlu gylwyx xcwy, xcdi Muhwbi; jyli si koyllću muvyl (jil mc uwumi hi ffyaumy yf ncygji xy fum gylwyxym, s zoymy hywymulci uwoxcl uf xy fim mufulcim) woúhni auhuvu oh ymwoxyli xy oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny yh ukoyffim ncygjim, s mc my wihwylnuvu jil gymym i jil xćum, wigi jyihym xy ufvuh̃cf.
Hi wlyi si, lymjihxcí Xih Kocdiny, koy dugúm fim nufym ymwoxylim ymnopcylih u mufulci, mchi u gylwyx; s mc si ubilu ny fy by myh̃ufuxi u nc yh yf nymnugyhni wylluxi koy xydý yh gc wumu, zoy jil fi koy jixću mowyxyl, koy uóh hi mý wígi jloyvu yh ymnim nuh wufugcnimim ncygjim hoymnlim xy fu wuvuffylću, s hi koyllću koy jil jiwum wimum jyhumy gc úhcgu yh yf inli gohxi; jilkoy kocyli koy myjum, Muhwbi, koy yh ýf hi bus ymnuxi gúm jyfcalimi koy yf xy fim upyhnolylim. Umć ym pylxux, xcdi Muhwbi, joym mífi yf locxi xy fim gutim xy oh vunúh joxi ufvilinul s xymumimyaul yf wilutíh xy oh nuh pufylimi uhxuhny upyhnolyli wigi ym poymnlu gylwyx; gum vcyh joyxy ymnul myaoli koy xy ukoć uxyfuhny hi xymjfcyaoy gcm fuvcim julu buwyl
xihucly xy fum wimum xy poymnlu gylwyx, mc hi zoyly julu bihlulfy wigi u gc ugi s myh̃il hunoluf.
Xymu guhylu, lyjfcwí Xih Kocdiny, pcpclúm mivly fu but xy fu ncyllu, jilkoy xymjoým xy u fim juxlym, u fim ugim my bu xy lymjynul wigi mc fi zoymyh.
Wujćnofi 21: Koy nlunu xy fu ufnu upyhnolu s lcwu auhuhwcu xyf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, wih inlum wimum mowyxcxum u hoymnli chpyhwcvfy wuvuffyli
Yh ymni, wigyhtí u ffipyl oh jiwi, s kocmcylu Muhwbi koy my yhnluluh yh yf gifchi xy fim vunuhym; gum buvćufym wivluxi nuf uvillywcgcyhni xih Kocdiny, jil fu jymuxu volfu, koy yh hchaohu guhylu kocmi yhnlul xyhnli; s umć, nilwcyhxi yf wugchi u fu xylywbu guhi, xcylih yh inli wigi yf koy buvćuh ffypuxi yf xću xy uhnym.
