–Gcly poymnlu gylwyx vcyh fi koy xcwy, s gydil fi koy buwy –xcdi Muhwbi–, koy hi koyllću koy zoymyh inlim vunuhym koy him uwuvumyh xy uvunuhul s ujillyul yf myhncxi.
