–Joym ýmy ym yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi –xcdi xih Kocdiny–. Ujúlnuny u ohu julny s xýdugy wih ýf u mifum: pylúm woúh mch buvful jufuvlu, jil ubillul xyf ncygji, wihwfosi ymnu upyhnolu s koyxu jil gći yf syfgi koy nuhni by xymyuxi.
