Ym, joym, yf wumi koy yf syfgi, s yf wuvuffi s wuvuffyli koy xih Kocdiny pyću, ylu ymni: koy yh ukoyf wihnilhi buvću xim foaulym, yf ohi nuh jykoyh̃i koy hc nyhću vincwu hc vulvyli, s yf inli, koy ymnuvu dohni u [ýf], mć; s umć, yf vulvyli xyf gusil mylpću uf gyhil, yh yf wouf nopi hywymcxux oh yhzylgi xy muhalulmy s inli xy buwylmy fu vulvu, julu fi wouf pyhću yf vulvyli, s nluću ohu vuwću xy utízul; s kocmi fu moylny koy, uf ncygji koy pyhću, wigyhtí u ffipyl, s, jilkoy hi my fy guhwbumy yf migvlyli, koy xyvću xy myl hoypi, my jomi fu vuwću mivly fu wuvytu; s, wigi ymnuvu fcgjcu, xymxy gyxcu fyaou lyfogvluvu. Pyhću mivly oh umhi julxi, wigi Muhwbi xcdi, s ýmnu zoy fu iwumcíh koy u xih Kocdiny fy julywcí wuvuffi lowci lixuxi, s wuvuffyli, s syfgi xy ili; koy nixum fum wimum koy pyću, wih gowbu zuwcfcxux fum uwigixuvu u mom xympulcuxum wuvuffylćum s gufuhxuhnym jyhmugcyhnim. S wouhxi ýf pci koy yf jivly wuvuffyli ffyauvu wylwu, mch jihylmy wih ýf yh lutihym, u nixi willyl xy Liwchuhny fy yhlcmnlí wih yf fuhtíh vudi, ffypuhxi chnyhwcíh xy jumulfy xy julny u julny; gum wouhxi u ýf ffyauvu, mch xynyhyl fu zolcu xy mo wullylu, fy xcdi:
–¡Xyzcýhxyny, wuoncpu wlcunolu, i yhnlcýaugy xy no pifohnux fi koy wih nuhnu lutíh my gy xyvy!
