–Mch xoxu koy yf juauhi, u wosu gyxcxu my zildí jlcgyli ymnu zugimu wyfuxu, xyvću xy nyhyl aluhxćmcgu wuvytu, s fi jyil xyffi ym koy fy zufnu fu gcnux.
Wouhxi Muhwbi isí ffugul u fu vuwću wyfuxu, hi joxi nyhyl fu lcmu; gum pćhimyfy u fum gcyhnym fu wífylu xy mo ugi, s wuffí yh fu gcnux xyffu.
–¿Xy koý ny lćym, Muhwbi? –xcdi xih Kocdiny.
