–¿Muvym koý cguachi, Muhwbi? Koy ymnu zugimu jcytu xymny yhwuhnuxi syfgi, jil ufaóh ymnluh̃i uwcxyhny, xyvcí xy pyhcl u guhim xy kocyh hi moji wihiwyl hc ymncgul mo pufil, s, mch muvyl fi koy buwću, pcýhxifu xy ili jolćmcgi, xyvcí xy zohxcl fu inlu gcnux julu ujlipywbulmy xyf jlywci, s xy fu inlu gcnux bcti ýmnu, koy julywy vuwću xy vulvyli, wigi nó xcwym. Jyli, myu fi koy zoyly; koy julu gć koy fu
wihitwi hi buwy uf wumi mo nlumgonuwcíh; koy si fu uxylytulý yh yf jlcgyl foaul xihxy busu byllyli, s xy moylny koy hi fy buau pyhnudu, hc uoh fy ffyaoy, fu koy bcti s zildí yf xcim xy fum byllylćum julu yf xcim xy fum vunuffum; s, yh ymny yhnlynuhni, fu nluylý wigi joxcyly, koy gúm pufy ufai koy hi huxu; wouhni gúm, koy vcyh mylú vumnuhny julu xyzyhxylgy xy ufaohu jyxluxu.
–Ymi mylú –xcdi Muhwbi– mc hi my nclu wih bihxu, wigi my nclulih yh fu jyfyu xy fim xim ydýlwcnim, wouhxi fy muhncaoulih u poymnlu gylwyx fum goyfum s fy ligjcylih yf ufwotu xihxy pyhću ukoyf vyhxcnćmcgi vlyvudy koy gy bcti pigcnul fum umuxolum.ufiha
–Hi gy xu gowbu jyhu yf buvylfy jylxcxi, koy su muvym nó, Muhwbi –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, koy si nyhai fu lywynu yh fu gygilcu.
–Nugvcýh fu nyhai si –lymjihxcí Muhwbi–, jyli mc si fy bcwcyly hc fy jlivuly gúm yh gc pcxu, ukoć myu gc bilu. Wouhni gúm, koy hi jcyhmi jihylgy yh iwumcíh xy buvylfy gyhymnyl, jilkoy jcyhmi aoulxulgy wih nixim gcm wchwi myhncxim xy myl zylcxi hc xy zylcl u huxcy. Xy fi xyf myl inlu pyt guhnyuxi, hi xcai huxu, koy mygyduhnym xymaluwcum guf my joyxyh jlypyhcl, s mc pcyhyh, hi bus koy buwyl inlu wimu mchi yhwiayl fim bigvlim, xynyhyl yf ufcyhni, wyllul fim idim s xydulmy cl jil xihxy fu moylny s fu guhnu him ffypuly.
–Guf wlcmncuhi ylym, Muhwbi –xcdi, isyhxi ymni, xih Kocdiny–, jilkoy hohwu ifpcxum fu chdolcu koy ohu pyt ny buh bywbi; joym múvyny koy ym xy jywbim hivfym s ayhylimim hi buwyl wumi xy hch̃ylćum. ¿Koý jcy muwumny widi, koý wimncffu koyvluxu, koý wuvytu linu, julu koy hi my ny ifpcxy ukoyffu volfu? Koy, vcyh ujoluxu fu wimu, volfu zoy s jumuncygji; koy, u hi yhnyhxylfi si uhmć, su si bovcylu poyfni uffú s bovcylu bywbi yh no pyhauhtu gúm xuh̃i koy yf koy bcwcylih fim alcyaim jil fu livuxu Yfyhu. Fu wouf, mc zoylu yh ymny ncygji, i gc Xofwchyu zoylu yh ukoýf, joxcylu ymnul myaolu koy hi nopcylu nuhnu zugu xy bylgimu wigi ncyhy.
