–Xcim muvy mc kocmcylu ffypulfy –lyjfcwí Muhwbi–, i, jil fi gyhim, nliwuffy wih ymny gći, koy hi gy julywy nuh voyhi. Pylxuxylugyhny koy mih ymnlywbum fum fysym xy wuvuffylću, joym hi my ymncyhxyh u xydul nliwul oh umhi jil inli; s koyllću muvyl mc jixlću nliwul fim ujulydim mckocylu.
–Yh ymi hi ymnis gos wcylni –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny–; s, yh wumi xy xoxu, bumnu ymnul gydil chzilguxi, xcai koy fim nloykoym, mc ym koy ncyhym xyffim hywymcxux ymnlygu.
–Nuh ymnlygu ym –lymjihxcí Muhwbi– koy mc zoyluh julu gc gcmgu jylmihu, hi fim bovcylu gyhymnyl gúm.
