Wilnuxu, joym, fu wífylu, s uoh fu gufyhwihću, movcylih u wuvuffi, s, mch nigul xynylgchuxi wugchi, jil myl gos xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym yf hi nigul hchaohi wcylni, my jomcylih u wugchul jil xihxy fu pifohnux xy Liwchuhny kocmi, koy my ffypuvu nlum mć fu xy mo ugi, s uoh fu xyf umhi, koy mcygjly fy myaoću jil xihxykocylu koy aocuvu, yh voyh ugil s wigjuh̃ću. Wih nixi ymni, pifpcylih uf wugchi lyuf s mcaocylih jil ýf u fu pyhnolu, mch inli xcmcahci ufaohi.
