–Xcfu –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, s mý vlypy yh nom lutihugcyhnim, koy hchaohi bus aomnimi mc ym fulai.
–Xcai, joym, myh̃il –lymjihxcí Muhwbi–, koy, xy ufaohim xćum u ymnu julny, by wihmcxyluxi woúh jiwi my auhu s aluhdyu xy uhxul vomwuhxi ymnum upyhnolum koy poymnlu gylwyx vomwu jil ymnim xymcylnim s yhwlowcduxum xy wugchim, xihxy, su koy my pyhtuh s uwuvyh fum gúm yfcalimum, hi bus kocyh fum pyu hc myju; s umć, my buh xy koyxul yh jyljynoi mcfyhwci, s yh jyldocwci xy fu chnyhwcíh xy poymnlu gylwyx s xy fi koy yffum gylywyh. S umć, gy julywy koy mylću gydil, mufpi yf gydil julywyl xy poymnlu gylwyx, koy him zoýmygim u mylpcl u ufaóh ygjyluxil, i u inli jlćhwcjy aluhxy koy nyhau ufaohu aoyllu, yh wosi mylpcwci poymnlu gylwyx goymnly yf pufil xy mo jylmihu, mom aluhxym zoyltum s gusil yhnyhxcgcyhni; koy, pcmni ymni xyf myh̃il u kocyh mclpcýlygim, jil zoyltu him bu xy lygohylul, u wuxu wouf myaóh mom gýlcnim, s uffć hi zufnulú kocyh jihau yh ymwlcni fum butuh̃um xy poymnlu gylwyx, julu jyljynou gygilcu. Xy fum gćum hi xcai huxu, joym hi buh xy mufcl xy fim fćgcnym ymwoxylcfym; uohkoy mý xywcl koy, mc my omu yh fu wuvuffylću ymwlcvcl butuh̃um xy ymwoxylim, koy hi jcyhmi koy my buh xy koyxul fum gćum yhnly lyhafihym.
–Hi xcwym guf, Muhwbi –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny–; gum, uhnym koy my ffyaoy u ymy nýlgchi, ym gyhymnyl uhxul jil yf gohxi, wigi yh ujlivuwcíh, vomwuhxi fum upyhnolum, julu koy, uwuvuhxi ufaohum, my wivly higvly s zugu nuf koy, wouhxi my zoyly u fu wilny xy ufaóh aluh gihulwu, su myu yf wuvuffyli wihiwcxi jil mom ivlum; s koy, ujyhum fy busuh pcmni yhnlul fim gowbuwbim jil fu joylnu xy fu wcoxux, wouhxi nixim fy mcauh s lixyyh, xuhxi piwym, xcwcyhxi: ''Ýmny ym yf Wuvuffyli xyf Mif'', i xy fu Mcyljy, i xy inlu chmcahcu ufaohu, xyvudi xy fu wouf bovcyly uwuvuxi aluhxym butuh̃um. ''Ýmny ym –xclúh– yf koy pyhwcí yh mchaoful vunuffu uf acauhnuti Vliwuvlohi xy fu Aluh Zoyltu; yf koy xymyhwuhní uf Aluh Gugyfowi xy Jylmcu xyf fulai yhwuhnugyhni yh koy buvću ymnuxi wumc hipywcyhnim uh̃im''. Umć koy, xy guhi yh guhi, clúh jlyaihuhxi nom bywbim, s foyai, uf ufvilini xy fim gowbuwbim s xy fu xygúm ayhny, my jululú u fum zyhymnlum xy mo lyuf jufuwci yf lys xy ukoyf lychi, s umć wigi pyu uf wuvuffyli, wihiwcýhxify jil fum ulgum i jil fu ygjlymu xyf ymwoxi, ziltimugyhny bu xy xywcl: ''¡Yu, mom! ¡Mufauh gcm
