–Myh̃il wuvuffyli, wuhnul yh yf uhmcu my xcwy, yhnly ymnu ayhny hih muhnu, wihzymul yh yf nilgyhni. U ymny jywuxil fy xcylih nilgyhni s wihzymí mo xyfcni, koy ylu myl wounlyli, koy ym myl fuxlíh xy vymncum, s, jil buvyl wihzymuxi, fy wihxyhulih jil mycm uh̃im u aufylum, ugýh xy xiwcyhnim utinym koy su ffypu yh fum ymjufxum. S pu mcygjly jyhmuncpi s nlcmny, jilkoy fim xygúm fuxlihym koy uffú koyxuh s ukoć puh fy gufnlunuh s uhckocfuh, s ymwulhywyh s ncyhyh yh jiwi, jilkoy wihzymí s hi nopi úhcgi xy xywcl hihym. Jilkoy xcwyh yffim koy nuhnum fynlum ncyhy oh hi wigi oh mć, s koy bulnu pyhnolu ncyhy oh xyfchwoyhny, koy ymnú yh mo fyhaou mo pcxu i mo goylny, s hi yh fu xy fim nymncaim s jlivuhtum; s julu gć nyhai koy hi puh gos zoylu xy wugchi.
–S si fi yhncyhxi umć –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
Yf wouf, jumuhxi uf nylwyli, jlyaohní fi koy u fim inlim; yf wouf, xy jlymni s wih gowbi xymyhzuxi, lymjihxcí s xcdi:
–Si pis jil wchwi uh̃im u fum myh̃ilum aolujum jil zufnulgy xcyt xowuxim.
