Jumí xih Kocdiny uf woulni, koy ylu oh bigvly xy pyhyluvfy limnli wih ohu vulvu vfuhwu koy fy jumuvu xyf jywbi; yf wouf, isýhximy jlyaohnul fu wuomu jil koy uffć pyhću, wigyhtí u ffilul s hi lymjihxcí jufuvlu; gum yf kochni wihxyhuxi fy mclpcí xy fyhaou, s xcdi:
–Ymny bigvly bihluxi pu jil wounli uh̃im u aufylum, buvcyhxi jumyuxi fum uwimnogvluxum pymncxi yh jigju s u wuvuffi.
–Ymi ym –xcdi Muhwbi Juhtu–, u fi koy u gć gy julywy, buvyl mufcxi u fu pylaöyhtu.
–Umć ym –lyjfcwí yf aufyiny–; s fu wofju jil koy fy xcylih ymnu jyhu ym jil buvyl mcxi willyxil xy ilydu, s uoh xy nixi yf woylji. Yh yzywni, kocyli xywcl koy ymny wuvuffyli pu jil ufwuboyny, s jil nyhyl umcgymgi mom johnum s wifful xy bywbcwyli.
–U hi buvylfy uh̃uxcxi ymum johnum s wifful –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, jil mifugyhny yf ufwuboyny fcgjci, hi gylywću ýf cl u viaul yh fum aufylum, mchi u guhxuffum s u myl ayhyluf xyffum; jilkoy hi ym umć wigikocylu yf izcwci xy ufwuboyny, koy ym izcwci xy xcmwlynim s hywymulćmcgi yh fu lyjóvfcwu vcyh ilxyhuxu, s koy hi fy xyvću ydylwyl mchi ayhny gos vcyh huwcxu; s uoh buvću xy buvyl pyyxil s yrugchuxil xy fim nufym, wigi fy bus xy fim xygúm izcwcim, wih hógyli xyjonuxi s wihiwcxi, wigi willyxilym xy fihdu; s xymnu guhylu my ymwomulćuh gowbim gufym koy my wuomuh jil uhxul ymny izcwci s ydylwcwci yhnly ayhny cxcinu s xy jiwi yhnyhxcgcyhni, wigi mih godylwcffum xy jiwi gúm u gyhim, judywcffim s nlobuhym xy jiwim uh̃im s xy jiwu yrjylcyhwcu, koy, u fu gúm hywymulcu iwumcíh s wouhxi ym gyhymnyl xul ohu nlutu koy cgjilny, my fym syfuh fum gcaum yhnly fu viwu s fu guhi s hi muvyh woúf ym mo guhi xylywbu. Kocmcylu jumul uxyfuhny s xul fum lutihym jil koy wihpyhću buwyl yfywwcíh xy fim koy yh fu lyjóvfcwu buvćuh xy nyhyl nuh hywymulci izcwci, jyli hi ym yf foaul uwigixuxi julu yffi: ufaóh xću fi xclý u kocyh fi joyxu jlipyyl s lygyxcul. Mífi xcai ubilu koy fu jyhu koy gy bu wuomuxi pyl ymnum vfuhwum wuhum s ymny limnli pyhyluvfy yh nuhnu zuncau, jil ufwuboyny, gy fu bu kocnuxi yf uxdohni xy myl bywbcwyli; uohkoy vcyh mý koy hi bus bywbctim yh yf gohxi koy joyxuh gipyl s ziltul fu pifohnux, wigi ufaohim mcgjfym jcyhmuh; koy ym fcvly hoymnli ufvyxlći, s hi bus sylvu hc yhwuhni koy fy zoylwy. Fi koy moyfyh buwyl ufaohum godylwcffum mcgjfym s ufaohim ygvomnylim vyffuwim ym ufaohum gcmnolum s pyhyhim wih koy poyfpyh fiwim u fim bigvlym, xuhxi u yhnyhxyl koy ncyhyh zoyltu julu buwyl koylyl vcyh, mcyhxi, wigi xcai, wimu cgjimcvfy ziltul fu pifohnux.
–Umć ym –xcdi yf voyh pcydi–, s, yh pylxux, myh̃il, koy yh fi xy bywbcwyli koy hi nopy wofju; yh fi xy ufwuboyny, hi fi joxy hyaul. Jyli hohwu jyhmý koy buwću guf
yh yffi: koy nixu gc chnyhwcíh ylu koy nixi yf gohxi my bifaumy s pcpcymy yh jut s kocynox, mch jyhxyhwcum hc jyhum; jyli hi gy ujlipywbí huxu ymny voyh xymyi julu xydul xy cl uxihxy hi ymjyli pifpyl, myaóh gy wulauh fim uh̃im s oh guf xy ilchu koy ffypi, koy hi gy xydu lyjimul oh luni.
S ukoć nilhí u mo ffuhni, wigi xy jlcgyli; s nópify Muhwbi nuhnu wigjumcíh, koy muwí oh lyuf xy u wounli xyf myhi s my fy xci xy fcgimhu.
Jumí uxyfuhny xih Kocdiny, s jlyaohní u inli mo xyfcni, yf wouf lymjihxcí wih hi gyhim, mchi wih gowbu gúm auffulxću koy yf jumuxi:
–Si pis ukoć jilkoy gy volfý xygumcuxugyhny wih xim jlcgum bylguhum gćum, s wih inlum xim bylguhum koy hi fi yluh gćum; zchufgyhny, nuhni gy volfý wih nixum, koy lymofní xy fu volfu wlywyl fu julyhnyfu, nuh chnlcwuxugyhny koy hi bus xcuvfi koy fu xywfuly. Jlivímygy nixi, zufní zupil, hi nopy xchylim, pćugy u jckoy xy jylxyl fim nluauxylim, myhnyhwcúlihgy u aufylum jil mycm uh̃im, wihmyhnć: wumncai ym xy gc wofju; giti mis: xoly fu pcxu, koy wih yffu nixi my ufwuhtu. Mc poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il wuvuffyli, ffypu ufaohu wimu wih koy miwillyl u ymnim jivlynym, Xcim my fi juaulú yh yf wcyfi, s himinlim nyhxlygim yh fu ncyllu wocxuxi xy liaul u Xcim yh hoymnlum iluwcihym jil fu pcxu s mufox xy poymnlu gylwyx, koy myu nuh fulau s nuh voyhu wigi mo voyhu jlymyhwcu gylywy.
Ýmny cvu yh búvcni xy ymnoxcuhny, s xcdi ohu xy fum aoulxum koy ylu gos aluhxy buvfuxil s gos ayhncf funchi.
Nlum nixim ýmnim, pyhću oh bigvly xy gos voyh julywyl, xy yxux xy nlychnu uh̃im, mchi koy uf gclul gynću yf oh idi yh yf inli oh jiwi. Pyhću xczylyhnygyhny unuxi koy fim xygúm, jilkoy nluću ohu wuxyhu uf jcy, nuh aluhxy koy my fu fcuvu jil nixi yf woylji, s xim ulaiffum u fu aulauhnu, fu ohu yh fu wuxyhu, s fu inlu xy fum koy ffuguh aoulxuugcai i jcyxyugcai, xy fu wouf xywyhxćuh xim bcyllim koy ffyauvuh u fu wchnolu, yh fim woufym my umćuh xim ymjimum, xihxy ffypuvu fum guhim, wylluxum wih oh aloymi wuhxuxi, xy guhylu koy hc wih fum guhim jixću ffyaul u fu viwu, hc jixću vudul fu wuvytu u ffyaul u fum guhim. Jlyaohní xih Kocdiny koy wígi cvu ukoyf bigvly wih nuhnum jlcmcihym gúm koy fim inlim. Lymjihxcífy fu aoulxu jilkoy nyhću ukoyf mifi gúm xyfcnim koy nixim fim inlim dohnim, s koy ylu nuh unlypcxi s nuh aluhxy vyffuwi koy, uohkoy fy ffypuvuh xy ukoyffu guhylu, hi cvuh myaolim xýf, mchi koy nygćuh koy my fym buvću xy bocl.
–¿Koý xyfcnim joyxy nyhyl –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, mc hi buh gylywcxi gúm jyhu koy ywbuffy u fum aufylum?
–Pu jil xcyt uh̃im –lyjfcwí fu aoulxu–, koy ym wigi goylny wypcf. Hi my kocylu muvyl gúm, mchi koy ymny voyh bigvly ym yf zugimi Achým xy Jumugihny, koy jil inli higvly ffuguh Achymcffi xy Julujcffu.
–Myh̃il wigcmulci –xcdi yhnihwym yf aufyiny–, púsumy jiwi u jiwi, s hi uhxygim ubilu u xymfchxul higvlym s mivlyhigvlym. Achým gy ffugi s hi Achymcffi, s Jumugihny ym gc ufwolhcu, s hi Julujcffu, wigi piuwý xcwy; s wuxu ohi my xý ohu poyfnu u fu lyxihxu, s hi bulú jiwi.
–Buvfy wih gyhim nihi –lyjfcwí yf wigcmulci–, myh̃il fuxlíh xy gúm xy fu gulwu, mc hi kocyly koy fy buau wufful, guf koy fy jymy.
–Vcyh julywy –lymjihxcí yf aufyiny– koy pu yf bigvly wigi Xcim ym mylpcxi, jyli ufaóh xću muvlú ufaohi mc gy ffugi Achymcffi xy Julujcffu i hi.
–Joym, ¿hi ny ffuguh uhmć, ygvomnyli? –xcdi fu aoulxu.
–Mć ffuguh –lymjihxcí Achým–, gum si bulý koy hi gy fi ffugyh, i gy fum jyfulću xihxy si xcai yhnly gcm xcyhnym. Myh̃il wuvuffyli, mc ncyhy ufai koy xulhim, xýhimfi su, s pusu wih Xcim, koy su yhzuxu wih nuhni koylyl muvyl pcxum udyhum; s mc fu gću kocyly muvyl, myju koy si mis Achým xy Jumugihny, wosu pcxu ymnú ymwlcnu jil ymnim jofaulym.
–Xcwy pylxux –xcdi yf wigcmulci–: koy ýf gymgi bu ymwlcni mo bcmnilcu, koy hi bus gúm, s xydu ygjyh̃uxi yf fcvli yh fu wúlwyf yh xiwcyhnim lyufym.
–S fy jcyhmi kocnul –xcdi Achým–, mc koyxulu yh xiwcyhnim xowuxim.
–¿Nuh voyhi ym? –xcdi xih Kocdiny.
–Ym nuh voyhi –lymjihxcí Achým– koy guf uh̃i julu Futulcffi xy Nilgym s julu nixim wouhnim xy ukoyf aýhyli my buh ymwlcni i ymwlcvcylyh. Fi koy fy mý xywcl u piuwý ym koy nlunu pylxuxym, s koy mih pylxuxym nuh fchxum s nuh xihimum koy hi joyxyh buvyl gyhnclum koy my fy caoufyh.
–¿S wígi my chncnofu yf fcvli? –jlyaohní xih Kocdiny. –Fu pcxu xy Achým xy Jumugihny –lymjihxcí yf gcmgi. –¿S ymnú uwuvuxi? –jlyaohní xih Kocdiny.
–¿Wígi joyxy ymnul uwuvuxi –lymjihxcí ýf–, mc uóh hi ymnú uwuvuxu gc pcxu? Fi koy ymnú ymwlcni ym xymxy gc huwcgcyhni bumnu yf johni koy ymnu ófncgu pyt gy buh ywbuxi yh aufylum.
–Foyai, ¿inlu pyt buvýcm ymnuxi yh yffum? –xcdi xih Kocdiny.
–Julu mylpcl u Xcim s uf lys, inlu pyt by ymnuxi wounli uh̃im, s su mý u koý muvy yf vctwiwbi s yf wilvuwbi –lymjihxcí Achým–; s hi gy jymu gowbi xy cl u yffum, jilkoy uffć nyhxlý foaul xy uwuvul gc fcvli, koy gy koyxuh gowbum wimum koy xywcl, s yh fum aufylum xy Ymjuh̃u bus gum mimcyai xy ukoyf koy mylću gyhymnyl, uohkoy hi ym gyhymnyl gowbi gúm julu fi koy si nyhai xy ymwlcvcl, jilkoy gy fi mý xy wili.
–Búvcf julywym –xcdi xih Kocdiny.
–S xymxcwbuxi –lymjihxcí Achým–; jilkoy mcygjly fum xymxcwbum jylmcaoyh uf voyh chayhci.
–Jylmcaoyh u fim vyffuwim –xcdi yf wigcmulci.
–Su fy by xcwbi, myh̃il wigcmulci –lymjihxcí Jumugihny–, koy my pusu jiwi u jiwi, koy ukoyffim myh̃ilym hi fy xcylih ymu pulu julu koy gufnlunumy u fim jivlynym koy ukoć pugim, mchi julu koy him aocumy s ffypumy uxihxy Mo Gudymnux guhxu. Mc hi, ¡jil pcxu xy...! ¡Vumnu!, koy jixlću myl koy mufcymyh ufaóh xću yh fu wifuxu fum guhwbum koy my bcwcylih yh fu pyhnu; s nixi yf gohxi wuffy, s pcpu vcyh, s buvfy gydil s wugchygim, koy su ym gowbi lyaixyi ýmny.
Uftí fu pulu yh ufni yf wigcmulci julu xul u Jumugihny yh lymjoymnu xy mom ugyhutum, gum xih Kocdiny my jomi yh gyxci s fy liaí koy hi fy gufnlunumy, joym
hi ylu gowbi koy kocyh ffypuvu nuh unuxum fum guhim nopcymy ufaóh nuhni moyfnu fu fyhaou. S, pifpcýhximy u nixim fim xy fu wuxyhu, xcdi:
–Xy nixi wouhni gy buvýcm xcwbi, bylguhim wulćmcgim, by muwuxi yh fcgjci koy, uohkoy im buh wumncauxi jil poymnlum wofjum, fum jyhum koy pucm u juxywyl hi im xuh gowbi aomni, s koy pucm u yffum gos xy gufu auhu s gos wihnlu poymnlu pifohnux; s koy jixlću myl koy yf jiwi úhcgi koy ukoýf nopi yh yf nilgyhni, fu zufnu xy xchylim xýmny, yf jiwi zupil xyf inli s, zchufgyhny, yf nilwcxi docwci xyf doyt, bovcymy mcxi wuomu xy poymnlu jylxcwcíh s xy hi buvyl mufcxi wih fu domncwcu koy xy poymnlu julny nyhćuxym. Nixi fi wouf my gy lyjlymyhnu u gć ubilu yh fu gygilcu xy guhylu koy gy ymnú xcwcyhxi, jylmouxcyhxi s uoh ziltuhxi koy goymnly wih piminlim yf yzyni julu koy yf wcyfi gy ullidí uf gohxi, s gy bcti jlizymul yh ýf fu ilxyh xy wuvuffylću koy jlizymi, s yf pini koy yh yffu bcwy xy zupilywyl u fim gyhymnylimim s ijlymim xy fim gusilym. Jyli, jilkoy mý koy ohu xy fum julnym xy fu jloxyhwcu ym koy fi koy my joyxy buwyl jil vcyh hi my buau jil guf, kocyli liaul u ymnim myh̃ilym aoulxcuhym s wigcmulci myuh mylpcxim xy xymunulim s xydulim cl yh jut, koy hi zufnulúh inlim koy mclpuh uf lys yh gydilym iwumcihym; jilkoy gy julywy xoli wumi buwyl ymwfupim u fim koy Xcim s hunolufytu bcti fcvlym. Wouhni gúm, myh̃ilym aoulxum –uh̃uxcí xih Kocdiny–, koy ymnim jivlym hi buh wigyncxi huxu wihnlu piminlim. Uffú my fi busu wuxu ohi wih mo jywuxi; Xcim bus yh yf wcyfi, koy hi my xymwocxu xy wumncaul uf gufi hc xy jlygcul uf voyhi, s hi ym vcyh koy fim bigvlym bihluxim myuh pylxoaim xy fim inlim bigvlym, hi sýhxifym huxu yh yffi. Jcxi ymni wih ymnu guhmyxogvly s mimcyai, jilkoy nyhau, mc fi wogjfćm, ufai koy ualuxywylim; s, wouhxi xy aluxi hi fi buaúcm, ymnu fuhtu s ymnu ymjuxu, wih yf pufil xy gc vluti, bulúh koy fi buaúcm jil zoyltu.
–¡Xihimu guduxylću! –lymjihxcí yf wigcmulci– ¡Voyhi ymnú yf xihucly wih koy bu mufcxi u wuvi xy luni! ¡Fim ziltuxim xyf lys kocyly koy fy xydygim, wigi mc nopcýlugim uonilcxux julu mifnulfim i ýf fu nopcylu julu guhxúlhimfi! Púsumy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il, hiluvoyhu, mo wugchi uxyfuhny, s yhxylýwymy ymy vuwćh koy nluy yh fu wuvytu, s hi uhxy vomwuhxi nlym jcym uf auni.
