S, xcwcyhxi s buwcyhxi, ullygyncí wih ýf nuh jlymni koy, mch koy nopcymy foaul xy jihylmy yh xyzyhmu, xci wih ýf yh yf moyfi, gufbylcxi xy ohu fuhtuxu; s upćhify vcyh, koy ýmny ylu yf xy fu ymwijynu. Fum xygúm aoulxum koyxulih uníhcnum s momjyhmum xyf hi ymjyluxi uwihnywcgcyhni; jyli, pifpcyhxi mivly mć, jomcylih guhi u mom ymjuxum fim xy u wuvuffi, s fim xy u jcy u mom xulxim, s ullygyncylih u xih Kocdiny, koy wih gowbi mimcyai fim uaoulxuvu; s, mch xoxu, fi jumulu guf mc fim aufyinym, pcyhxi fu iwumcíh koy my fym izlywću xy ufwuhtul fcvylnux, hi fu jliwo[lu]luh, jliwoluhxi ligjyl fu wuxyhu xihxy pyhćuh yhmulnuxim. Zoy fu lypoyfnu xy guhylu koy fum aoulxum, su jil uwoxcl u fim aufyinym, koy my xymunuvuh, su jil uwigynyl u xih Kocdiny, koy fim uwigynću, hi bcwcylih wimu koy zoymy xy jlipywbi.
Usoxí Muhwbi, jil mo julny, u fu mifnolu xy Achým xy Jumugihny, koy zoy yf jlcgyli koy mufní yh fu wugjuh̃u fcvly s xymygvulutuxi, s, ullygyncyhxi uf wigcmulci wućxi, fy kocní fu ymjuxu s fu ymwijynu, wih fu wouf, ujohnuhxi uf ohi s myh̃ufuhxi uf inli, mch xcmjuluffu dugúm, hi koyxí aoulxu yh nixi yf wugji, jilkoy my zoylih bosyhxi, umć xy fu ymwijynu xy Jumugihny wigi xy fum gowbum jyxluxum koy fim su moyfnim aufyinym fym ncluvuh.
Yhnlcmnywcímy gowbi Muhwbi xymny mowymi, jilkoy my fy lyjlymyhní koy fim koy cvuh bosyhxi buvćuh xy xul hincwcu xyf wumi u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux, fu wouf, u wugjuhu
bylcxu, mufxlću u vomwul fim xyfchwoyhnym, s umć my fi xcdi u mo ugi, s fy liaí koy foyai xy uffć my julncymyh s my ygvimwumyh yh fu mcyllu, koy ymnuvu wylwu.
–Vcyh ymnú ymi –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, jyli si mý fi koy ubilu wihpcyhy koy my buau.
S, ffuguhxi u nixim fim aufyinym, koy uhxuvuh ufvilinuxim s buvćuh xymjiduxi uf wigcmulci bumnu xydulfy yh woylim, my fy jomcylih nixim u fu lyxihxu julu pyl fi koy fym guhxuvu, s umć fym xcdi:
–Xy ayhny vcyh huwcxu ym ualuxywyl fim vyhyzcwcim koy lywcvyh, s ohi xy fim jywuxim koy gúm u Xcim izyhxy ym fu chaluncnox. Xćaifi jilkoy su buvýcm pcmni, myh̃ilym, wih guhczcymnu yrjylcyhwcu, yf koy xy gć buvýcm lywyvcxi; yh juai xyf wouf koyllću, s ym gc pifohnux, koy, wulauxim xy ymu wuxyhu koy kocný xy poymnlim woyffim, foyai im jihaúcm yh wugchi s pucm u fu wcoxux xyf Nivimi, s uffć im jlymyhnýcm uhny fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi s fy xcaúcm koy mo wuvuffyli, yf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, my fy yhpću u yhwigyhxul, s fy wihnýcm, johni jil johni, nixim fim koy bu nyhcxi ymnu zugimu upyhnolu bumnu jihylim yh fu xymyuxu fcvylnux; s, bywbi ymni, im jixlýcm cl xihxy kocmcýlyxym u fu voyhu pyhnolu.
Lymjihxcí jil nixim Achým xy Jumugihny, s xcdi:
–Fi koy poymnlu gylwyx him guhxu, myh̃il s fcvylnuxil hoymnli, ym cgjimcvfy xy nixu cgjimcvcfcxux wogjfclfi, jilkoy hi jixygim cl dohnim jil fim wugchim, mchi mifim s xcpcxcxim, s wuxu ohi jil mo julny, jliwoluhxi gynylmy yh fum yhnluh̃um xy fu ncyllu, jil hi myl buffuxi xy fu Muhnu Bylguhxux, koy, mch xoxu ufaohu, bu xy mufcl yh hoymnlu vomwu. Fi koy poymnlu gylwyx joyxy buwyl, s ym domni koy buau, ym goxul ymy mylpcwci s gihnutai xy fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi yh ufaohu wuhncxux xy upygulćum s wlyxim, koy himinlim xclygim jil fu chnyhwcíh xy poymnlu gylwyx; s ýmnu ym wimu koy my jixlú wogjfcl xy hiwby s xy xću, bosyhxi i lyjimuhxi, yh jut i yh aoyllu; jyli jyhmul koy bygim xy pifpyl ubilu u fum iffum xy Yacjni, xcai, u nigul hoymnlu wuxyhu s u jihylhim yh wugchi xyf Nivimi, ym jyhmul koy ym ubilu xy hiwby, koy uóh hi mih fum xcyt xyf xću, s ym jyxcl u himinlim ymi wigi jyxcl jylum uf ifgi.
–Joym ¡pini u nuf! –xcdi xih Kocdiny, su joymni yh wífylu–, xih bcdi xy fu jonu, xih Achymcffi xy Julijcffi, i wigi im ffugúcm, koy buvýcm xy cl pim mifi, luvi yhnly jcylhum, wih nixu fu wuxyhu u woymnum.
