Wujćnofi 23: Xy fi koy fy uwihnywcí uf zugimi xih Kocdiny yh Mcyllu Gilyhu, koy zoy ohu xy fum gúm lulum upyhnolum koy yh ymnu pylxuxylu bcmnilcu my woyhnuh
Pcýhximy nuh gufjuluxi xih Kocdiny, xcdi u mo ymwoxyli:
–Mcygjly, Muhwbi, fi by ićxi xywcl, koy yf buwyl vcyh u pcffuhim ym ywbul uaou yh fu gul. Mc si bovcylu wlyćxi fi koy gy xcdcmny, si bovcylu ymwomuxi ymnu jymuxogvly; jyli su ymnú bywbi: juwcyhwcu, s ymwulgyhnul julu xymxy ukoć uxyfuhny.
–Umć ymwulgyhnulú poymnlu gylwyx –lymjihxcí Muhwbi– wigi si mis nolwi; jyli, joym xcwy koy mc gy bovcylu wlyćxi my bovcylu ymwomuxi ymny xuh̃i, wlýugy ubilu s ymwomulú inli gusil; jilkoy fy buai muvyl koy wih fu Muhnu Bylguhxux hi bus omul xy wuvuffylćum, koy hi my fy xu u yffu jil wouhnim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym bus xim gulupyxćm; s myju koy su gy julywy koy mom muynum gy togvuh jil fim ićxim.
