–Myh̃il –lymjihxcí Muhwbi–, koy yf lynclul hi ym bocl, hc yf ymjylul ym wilxolu, wouhxi yf jyfcali mivlyjodu u fu ymjyluhtu, s xy muvcim ym aoulxulmy bis julu guh̃uhu s hi upyhnolulmy nixi yh oh xću. S myju koy, uohkoy tuzci s pcffuhi, nixupću my gy ufwuhtu ufai xymni koy ffuguh voyh aivcylhi; umć koy, hi my ullyjcyhnu xy buvyl niguxi gc wihmydi, mchi movu yh Liwchuhny, mc joyxy, i mc hi si fy usoxulý, s mćaugy, koy yf wufynly gy xcwy koy bygim gyhymnyl ubilu gúm fim jcym koy fum guhim.
Movcí xih Kocdiny, mch lyjfcwulfy gúm jufuvlu, s, aocuhxi Muhwbi mivly mo umhi, my yhnlulih jil ohu julny xy Mcyllu Gilyhu, koy uffć dohni ymnuvu, ffypuhxi Muhwbi chnyhwcíh xy unlupymulfu nixu y cl u mufcl uf Pcmi, i u Ufgixípul xyf Wugji, s
