–Foyai, ¿nugvcýh –xcdi Muhwbi– my fy yhncyhxy u poymnlu gylwyx xy nlipum?
–S gúm xy fi koy nó jcyhmum –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny–, s pylúmfi wouhxi ffypym ohu wulnu, ymwlcnu yh pylmi xy ullcvu uvudi, u gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi. Jilkoy kocyli koy myjum, Muhwbi, koy nixim i fim gúm wuvuffylim uhxuhnym xy fu yxux jumuxu yluh aluhxym nlipuxilym s aluhxym gómcwim; koy ymnum xim buvcfcxuxym, i aluwcum, jil gydil xywcl, mih uhyrum u fim yhugiluxim uhxuhnym. Pylxux ym koy fum wijfum xy fim jumuxim wuvuffylim ncyhyh gúm xy ymjćlcno koy xy jlcgil.
–Fyu gúm poymnlu gylwyx –xcdi Muhwbi–, koy su buffulú ufai koy him muncmzuau. Pifpcí fu bidu xih Kocdiny s xcdi:
