Syhxi, joym, wih ymny jyhmugcyhni, pci koy, jil wcgu xy ohu gihnuh̃oyfu koy xyfuhny xy fim idim my fy izlywću, cvu mufnuhxi oh bigvly, xy lcmwi yh lcmwi s xy gunu yh gunu, wih ymnluh̃u fcaylytu. Zcaolímyfy koy cvu xymhoxi, fu vulvu hyalu s ymjymu, fim wuvyffim gowbim s luvofnuxim, fim jcym xymwuftim s fum jcylhum mch wimu ufaohu; fim gomfim wovlćuh ohim wuftihym, uf julywyl xy nylwcijyfi fyihuxi, gum nuh bywbim jyxutim koy jil gowbum julnym my fy xymwovlćuh fum wulhym. Nluću fu wuvytu xymwovcylnu, s, uohkoy jumí wih fu fcaylytu koy my bu xcwbi, nixum ymnum gyhoxyhwcum gclí s hiní yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu; s, uohkoy fi jliwolí, hi joxi myaocffy, jilkoy hi ylu xuxi u fu xyvcfcxux xy Liwchuhny uhxul jil ukoyffum
umjylytum, s gúm mcyhxi ýf xy mosi jcmuwilni s zfygúncwi. Foyai cguachí xih Kocdiny koy ukoýf ylu yf xoyh̃i xyf widćh s xy fu gufynu, s jlijomi yh mć xy vomwuffy, uohkoy mojcymy uhxul oh uh̃i jil ukoyffum gihnuh̃um bumnu buffulfy; s umć, guhxí u Muhwbi koy my ujyumy xyf umhi s unudumy jil fu ohu julny xy fu gihnuh̃u, koy ýf clću jil fu inlu s jixlću myl koy nijumyh, wih ymnu xcfcayhwcu, wih ukoyf bigvly koy wih nuhnu jlcymu my fym buvću kocnuxi xy xyfuhny.
–Hi jixlý buwyl ymi –lymjihxcí Muhwbi–, jilkoy, yh ujulnúhxigy xy poymnlu gylwyx, foyai ym wihgcai yf gcyxi, koy gy umufnu wih gcf aýhylim xy mivlymufnim s pcmcihym. S mćlpufy ymni koy xcai xy upcmi, julu koy xy ukoć uxyfuhny hi gy ujulny oh xyxi xy mo jlymyhwcu.
–Umć mylú –xcdi yf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu–, s si ymnis gos wihnyhni xy koy ny kocylum pufyl xy gc úhcgi, yf wouf hi ny bu xy zufnul, uohkoy ny zufny yf úhcgu xyf woylji. S pyhny ubilu nlum gć jiwi u jiwi, i wigi joxcylym, s but xy fim idim fuhnylhum; lixyulygim ymnu myllytoyfu: koctú nijulygim wih ukoyf bigvly koy pcgim, yf wouf, mch xoxu ufaohu, hi ym inli koy yf xoyh̃i xy hoymnli buffutai.
U fi koy Muhwbi lymjihxcí:
–Bulni gydil mylću hi vomwuffy, jilkoy mc fy buffugim s uwumi zoymy yf xoyh̃i xyf xchyli, wfuli ymnú koy fi nyhai xy lymncnocl; s umć, zoylu gydil, mch buwyl ymnu chóncf xcfcayhwcu, jimyylfi si wih voyhu zy bumnu koy, jil inlu pću gyhim wolcimu s xcfcayhny, julywcylu mo pylxuxyli myh̃il; s koctú zoylu u ncygji koy fi bovcylu aumnuxi, s yhnihwym yf lys gy buwću zluhwi.
–Yhaúh̃umny yh ymi, Muhwbi –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny–; koy, su koy bygim wućxi yh mimjywbu xy kocýh ym yf xoyh̃i, woumc xyfuhny, ymnugim ivfcauxim u vomwulfy s pifpýlmyfim; s, wouhxi hi fy vomwúmygim, fu pybygyhny mimjywbu koy nyhygim xy koy ýf fi myu him jihy su yh nuhnu wofju wigi mc fi zoymy. Umć koy, Muhwbi ugcai, hi ny xý jyhu yf vomwuffy, jil fu koy u gć my gy kocnulú mc fy buffi.
S umć, jcwí u Liwchuhny, s mcaocífy Muhwbi wih mo uwimnogvluxi dogyhni; s, buvcyhxi lixyuxi julny xy fu gihnuh̃u, buffulih yh oh ullisi, wućxu, goylnu s gyxci wigcxu xy jyllim s jcwuxu xy aludim, ohu gofu yhmcffuxu s yhzlyhuxu; nixi fi wouf wihzclgí yh yffim gúm fu mimjywbu xy koy ukoyf koy boću ylu yf xoyh̃i xy fu gofu s xyf widćh.
Ymnúhxifu gcluhxi, isylih oh mcfvi wigi xy jumnil koy aoulxuvu auhuxi, s u xymbilu, u mo mchcymnlu guhi, julywcylih ohu voyhu wuhncxux xy wuvlum, s nlum yffum, jil wcgu xy fu gihnuh̃u, julywcí yf wuvlyli koy fum aoulxuvu, koy ylu oh bigvly uhwcuhi. Xcify piwym xih Kocdiny, s liaífy koy vudumy xihxy ymnuvuh. Ýf lymjihxcí u alcnim koy kocýh fym buvću nlućxi jil ukoyf foaul, jiwum i hchaohum pywym jcmuxi mchi xy jcym xy wuvlum i xy fivim s inlum zcylum koy jil uffć uhxuvuh. Lymjihxcífy Muhwbi koy vudumy, koy xy nixi fy xulćuh voyhu woyhnu. Vudí yf wuvlyli, s, yh ffyauhxi uxihxy xih Kocdiny ymnuvu, xcdi:
–Ujimnulý koy ymnú gcluhxi fu gofu xy ufkocfyl koy ymnú goylnu yh ymu bihxihuxu. Joym u voyhu zy koy bu su mycm gymym koy ymnú yh ymy foaul. Xćauhgy: ¿buh nijuxi jil ubć u mo xoyh̃i?
–Hi bygim nijuxi u huxcy –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny–, mchi u oh widćh s u ohu gufyncffu koy hi fydim xymny foaul buffugim.
–Nugvcýh fu buffý si –lymjihxcí yf wuvlyli–, gum hohwu fu kocmy uftul hc ffyaul u yffu, nygylimi xy ufaóh xymgúh s xy koy hi gy fu jcxcymyh jil xy bolni; koy ym yf
xcuvfi mincf, s xyvudi xy fim jcym my fypuhnu uffigvly wimu xihxy nlijcywy s wusu, mch muvyl wígi hc wígi hi.
–Ymi gymgi ym fi koy si xcai –lymjihxcí Muhwbi–: koy nugvcýh fu buffý si, s hi kocmy ffyaul u yffu wih oh ncli xy jcyxlu; uffć fu xydý s uffć my koyxu wigi my ymnuvu, koy hi kocyli jylli wih wyhwylli.
–Xywcxgy, voyh bigvly –xcdi xih Kocdiny–, ¿muvýcm pim kocýh myu yf xoyh̃i xymnum jlyhxum?
–Fi koy muvlý si xywcl –xcdi yf wuvlyli– ym koy «buvlú uf jcy xy mycm gymym, jiwi gúm u gyhim, koy ffyaí u ohu guduxu xy jumnilym, koy ymnulú wigi nlym fyaoum xymny foaul, oh guhwyvi xy ayhncf nuffy s ujimnolu, wuvuffyli mivly ymu gymgu gofu koy ubć ymnú goylnu, s wih yf gymgi widćh s gufynu koy xywćm koy buffumnym s hi niwumnym. Jlyaohníhim koy woúf julny xymnu mcyllu ylu fu gúm úmjylu s ymwihxcxu; xcdćgimfy koy ylu ymnu xihxy ubilu ymnugim; s ym uhmć fu pylxux, jilkoy mc yhnlúcm gyxcu fyaou gúm uxyhnli, koctú hi uwylnulýcm u mufcl; s ymnis gulupcffuxi xy wígi buvýcm jixcxi ffyaul ukoć, jilkoy hi bus wugchi hc myhxu koy u ymny foaul yhwugchy. Xcai, joym, koy, yh isyhxi hoymnlu lymjoymnu yf guhwyvi, pifpcí fum lcyhxum s yhwugchí buwcu yf foaul xihxy fy myh̃ufugim, xydúhxihim u nixim wihnyhnim xy mo voyh nuffy, s uxgcluxim xy mo xyguhxu s xy fu jlcymu wih koy fy pćugim wugchul s pifpylmy buwcu fu mcyllu; s xymxy yhnihwym hohwu gúm fy pcgim, bumnu koy xymxy uffć u ufaohim xćum mufcí uf wugchi u ohi xy hoymnlim jumnilym, s, mch xywcffy huxu, my ffyaí u ýf s fy xci gowbum joh̃uxum s wiwym, s foyai my zoy u fu villcwu xyf buni s fy kocní wouhni juh s koymi yh yffu nluću; s, wih ymnluh̃u fcaylytu, bywbi ymni, my pifpcí u ygvimwul yh fu mcyllu. Wigi ymni mojcgim ufaohim wuvlylim, fy uhxopcgim u vomwul wumc xim xćum jil fi gúm wylluxi xymnu mcyllu, uf wuvi xy fim woufym fy buffugim gyncxi yh yf boywi xy oh aloymi s pufcyhny ufwilhikoy. Mufcí u himinlim wih gowbu guhmyxogvly, su lini yf pymncxi, s yf limnli xcmzcaoluxi s nimnuxi xyf mif, xy nuf moylny koy ujyhum fy wihiwćugim, mchi koy fim pymncxim, uohkoy linim, wih fu hincwcu koy xyffim nyhćugim, him xcylih u yhnyhxyl koy ylu yf koy vomwúvugim. Mufoxíhim wilnýmgyhny, s yh jiwum s gos voyhum lutihym him xcdi koy hi him gulupcffúmygim xy pylfy uhxul xy ukoyffu moylny, jilkoy umć fy wihpyhću julu wogjfcl wcylnu jyhcnyhwcu koy jil mom gowbim jywuxim fy buvću mcxi cgjoymnu. Liaúgimfy koy him xcdymy kocýh ylu, gum hohwu fi joxcgim uwuvul wih ýf. Jyxćgimfy nugvcýh koy, wouhxi bovcymy gyhymnyl yf momnyhni, mch yf wouf hi jixću jumul, him xcdymy xíhxy fy buffulćugim, jilkoy wih gowbi ugil s wocxuxi my fi ffypulćugim; s koy mc ymni nugjiwi zoymy xy mo aomni, koy, u fi gyhim, mufcymy u jyxclfi, s hi u kocnulfi u fim jumnilym. Ualuxywcí hoymnli izlywcgcyhni, jcxcí jylxíh xy fim umufnim jumuxim, s izlywcí xy jyxcffi xy uffć uxyfuhny jil ugil xy Xcim, mch xul gifymncu ufaohu u huxcy. Yh wouhni fi koy niwuvu u fu ymnuhwcu xy mo buvcnuwcíh, xcdi koy hi nyhću inlu koy ukoyffu koy fy izlywću fu iwumcíh xihxy fy niguvu fu hiwby; s uwuví mo jfúncwu wih oh nuh ncylhi ffuhni, koy vcyh zoýlugim xy jcyxlu fim koy ymwowbuxi fy buvćugim, mc yh ýf hi fy uwigjuh̃úlugim, wihmcxylúhxify wígi fy buvćugim pcmni fu pyt jlcgylu, s woúf fy pyćugim yhnihwym. Jilkoy, wigi nyhai xcwbi, ylu oh gos ayhncf s ualuwcuxi guhwyvi, s yh mom wilnymym s wihwylnuxum lutihym gimnluvu myl vcyh huwcxi s gos wilnymuhu jylmihu; koy, joymni koy ýlugim lómncwim fim koy fy ymwowbúvugim, mo ayhncfytu ylu nuhnu, koy vumnuvu u xulmy u wihiwyl u fu gymgu lomncwcxux. S, ymnuhxi yh fi gydil xy mo jfúncwu, julí s yhgoxywcímy; wfupí fim idim yh yf moyfi jil oh voyh ymjuwci, yh yf wouf nixim ymnopcgim koyxim s momjyhmim, ymjyluhxi yh koý buvću xy julul ukoyf ygvyfymugcyhni, wih hi jiwu fúmncgu xy pylfi; jilkoy, jil fi koy buwću xy uvlcl fim idim, ymnul zcdi gcluhxi uf moyfi mch gipyl jymnuh̃u aluh luni, s inlum pywym wyllulfim, ujlynuhxi fim fuvcim s yhulwuhxi fum wydum, zúwcfgyhny wihiwcgim koy ufaóh uwwcxyhny xy fiwolu fy buvću mivlypyhcxi. Gum ýf him xci u yhnyhxyl jlymni myl pylxux fi koy jyhmúvugim, jilkoy my fypuhní wih aluh zolcu xyf moyfi, xihxy my buvću ywbuxi, s ullygyncí wih yf jlcgyli koy buffí
dohni u mć, wih nuf xyhoyxi s luvcu koy, mc hi my fy kocnúlugim, fy gunulu u joh̃uxum s u viwuxim; s nixi ymni buwću, xcwcyhxi: ‘‘¡Ub, zygyhncxi Zylhuhxi! ¡Ukoć, ukoć gy juaulúm fu mchlutíh koy gy bywcmny: ymnum guhim ny muwulúh yf wilutíh, xihxy ufvylauh s ncyhyh guhcxu nixum fum gufxuxym dohnum, jlchwcjufgyhny fu zluoxy s yf yhauh̃i!’’ S u ýmnum uh̃uxću inlum lutihym, koy nixum my yhwugchuvuh u xywcl guf xy ukoyf Zylhuhxi s u nuwbulfy xy nlucxil s zygyhncxi. Kocnúgimmyfy, joym, wih hi jiwu jymuxogvly, s ýf, mch xywcl gúm jufuvlu, my ujulní xy himinlim s my ygvimwí willcyhxi jil yhnly ymnim dulufym s gufytum, xy gixi koy him cgjimcvcfcní yf myaocffy. Jil ymni wihdynolugim koy fu fiwolu fy pyhću u ncygjim, s koy ufaohi koy my ffuguvu Zylhuhxi fy xyvću xy buvyl bywbi ufaohu gufu ivlu, nuh jymuxu wouhni fi gimnluvu yf nýlgchi u koy fy buvću wihxowcxi. Nixi fi wouf my bu wihzclguxi xymjoým uwú wih fum pywym, koy buh mcxi gowbum, koy ýf bu mufcxi uf wugchi, ohum u jyxcl u fim jumnilym fy xyh xy fi koy ffypuh julu wigyl s inlum u kocnúlmyfi jil zoyltu; jilkoy wouhxi ymnú wih yf uwwcxyhny xy fu fiwolu, uohkoy fim jumnilym my fi izlytwuh xy voyh aluxi, hi fi uxgcny, mchi koy fi nigu u joh̃uxum; s wouhxi ymnú yh mo mymi, fi jcxy jil ugil xy Xcim, wilným s wigyxcxugyhny, s lchxy jil yffi gowbum aluwcum, s hi wih zufnu xy fúalcgum. S yh pylxux im xcai, myh̃ilym –jlimcaocí yf wuvlyli–, koy usyl xynylgchugim si s wounli tuaufym, fim xim wlcuxim s fim xim ugcaim gćim, xy vomwulfy bumnu nuhni koy fy buffygim, s, xymjoým xy buffuxi, su jil zoyltu su jil aluxi, fy bygim xy ffypul u fu pcffu xy Ufgixípul, koy ymnú xy ukoć iwbi fyaoum, s uffć fy wolulygim, mc ym koy mo guf ncyhy wolu, i muvlygim kocýh ym wouhxi ymný yh mom mymi, s mc ncyhy julcyhnym u kocyh xul hincwcu xy mo xymaluwcu». Ymni ym, myh̃ilym, fi koy muvlý xywclim xy fi koy gy buvýcm jlyaohnuxi; s yhnyhxyx koy yf xoyh̃i xy fum jlyhxum koy buffumnym ym yf gymgi koy pcmnym jumul wih nuhnu fcaylytu wigi xymhoxyt –koy su fy buvću xcwbi xih Kocdiny wígi buvću pcmni jumul ukoyf bigvly mufnuhxi jil fu mcyllu.
Yf wouf koyxí uxgcluxi xy fi koy uf wuvlyli buvću ićxi, s koyxí wih gúm xymyi xy muvyl kocýh ylu yf xymxcwbuxi fiwi; s jlijomi yh mć fi gymgi koy su nyhću jyhmuxi: xy vomwuffy jil nixu fu gihnuh̃u, mch xydul lchwíh hc woypu yh yffu koy hi gclumy, bumnu buffulfy. Jyli bćtifi gydil fu moylny xy fi koy ýf jyhmuvu hc ymjyluvu, jilkoy yh ukoyf gymgi chmnuhny julywcí, jil yhnly ohu koyvluxu xy ohu mcyllu koy mufću xihxy yffim ymnuvuh, yf guhwyvi koy vomwuvu, yf wouf pyhću buvfuhxi yhnly mć wimum koy hi jixćuh myl yhnyhxcxum xy wylwu, wouhni gúm xy fydim. Mo nludy ylu wouf my bu jchnuxi, mífi koy, ffyauhxi wylwu, pci xih Kocdiny koy oh wifyni bywbi jyxutim koy mivly mć nluću ylu xy úgvul; jil xihxy uwuví xy yhnyhxyl koy jylmihu koy nufym búvcnim nluću hi xyvću xy myl xy ćhzcgu wufcxux.
Yh ffyauhxi yf guhwyvi u yffim, fym mufoxí wih ohu pit xymyhnihuxu s vlihwu, jyli wih gowbu wilnymću. Xih Kocdiny fy pifpcí fum mufoxym wih hi gyhim wigyxcgcyhni, s, ujyúhximy xy Liwchuhny, wih ayhncf wihnchyhny s xihucly, fy zoy u uvlutul s fy nopi oh voyh ymjuwci ymnlywbugyhny yhnly mom vlutim, wigi mc xy foyhaim ncygjim fy bovcylu wihiwcxi. Yf inli, u kocyh jixygim ffugul yf Lini xy fu Gufu Zcaolu – wigi u xih Kocdiny yf xy fu Nlcmny–, xymjoým xy buvylmy xyduxi uvlutul, fy ujulní oh jiwi xy mć, s, joymnum mom guhim yh fim bigvlim xy xih Kocdiny, fy ymnopi gcluhxi, wigi koy koylću pyl mc fy wihiwću; hi gyhim uxgcluxi koctú xy pyl fu zcaolu, nuffy s ulgum xy xih Kocdiny, koy xih Kocdiny fi ymnuvu xy pylfy u ýf. Yh lymifowcíh, yf jlcgyli koy buvfí xymjoým xyf uvlutugcyhni zoy yf Lini, s xcdi fi koy my xclú uxyfuhny.
Wujćnofi 24: Xihxy my jlimcaoy fu upyhnolu xy fu Mcyllu Gilyhu
Xcwy fu bcmnilcu koy ylu aluhxćmcgu fu unyhwcíh wih koy xih Kocdiny ymwowbuvu uf umnlimi wuvuffyli xy fu Mcyllu, yf wouf, jlimcaocyhxi mo jfúncwu, xcdi:
-Jil wcylni, myh̃il, kocyhkocylu koy myúcm, koy si hi im wihitwi, si im ualuxytwi fum goymnlum s fu wilnymću koy wihgcai buvýcm omuxi, s kocmcylu si buffulgy yh nýlgchim, koy wih gúm koy fu pifohnux joxcylu mylpcl fu koy buvýcm gimnluxi nyhylgy, yh yf voyh uwiacgcyhni koy gy buvýcm bywbi; gum hi kocyly gc moylny xulgy inlu wimu wih koy willymjihxu u fum voyhum ivlum koy gy buwyh koy voyhim xymyim xy muncmzuwylfum.
-Fim koy si nyhai -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny- mih xy mylpclim; nuhni, koy nyhću xynylgchuxi xy hi mufcl xymnum mcyllum bumnu buffulim s muvyl xy pim mc uf xifil koy yh fu yrnluh̃ytu xy poymnlu pcxu gimnlúcm nyhyl my jixću bufful ufaóh aýhyli xy lygyxci; s mc zoylu gyhymnyl vomwulfy, vomwulfy wih fu xcfcayhwcu jimcvfy. S wouhxi poymnlu xympyhnolu zoylu xy ukoyffum koy ncyhyh wylluxum fum joylnum u nixi aýhyli xy wihmoyfi, jyhmuvu usoxulim u ffilulfu s jfuh̃clću wigi gydil joxcylu; koy nixupću ym wihmoyfi yh fum xymaluwcum bufful kocyh my xoyfu xyffum. S mc ym koy gc voyh chnyhni gylywy myl ualuxywcxi wih ufaóh aýhyli xy wilnymću, si im mojfcwi, myh̃il, jil fu gowbu koy pyi koy yh pim my yhwcyllu, s dohnugyhny im wihdoli jil fu wimu koy yh ymnu pcxu gúm buvýcm uguxi i ugúcm, koy gy xcaúcm kocýh micm s fu wuomu koy im bu nlućxi u pcpcl s u gilcl yhnly ymnum mifyxuxym wigi vloni uhcguf, joym gilúcm yhnly yffim nuh udyhi xy pim gcmgi wouf fi goymnlu poymnli nludy s jylmihu. S doli -uh̃uxcí xih Kocdiny- jil fu ilxyh xy wuvuffylću koy lywcvć, uohkoy chxcahi s jywuxil, s jil fu jlizymcíh xy wuvuffyli uhxuhny, koy mc yh ymni, myh̃il, gy wigjfuwýcm, by xy mylpclim wih fum pylum u koy gy ivfcau yf myl kocyh mis, ilu lygyxcuhxi poymnlu xymaluwcu, mc ncyhy lygyxci, ilu usoxúhxiim u ffilulfu, wigi im fi by jligyncxi.
Yf Wuvuffyli xyf Vimkoy, koy xy nuf guhylu isí buvful uf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, hi buwcu mchi gclulfy, s lygclulfy, s nigulfy u gclul xy ullcvu uvudi; s xymjoým koy fy bovi vcyh gcluxi, fy xcdi:
-Mc ncyhyh ufai koy xulgy xy wigyl, jil ugil xy Xcim koy gy fi xyh; koy xymjoým xy buvyl wigcxi si bulý nixi fi koy my gy guhxu, yh ualuxywcgcyhni xy nuh voyhim xymyim wigi ukoć my gy buh gimnluxi.
Foyai muwulih, Muhwbi xy mo wimnuf s yf wuvlyli xy mo tollíh, wih koy muncmzcti yf Lini mo bugvly, wigcyhxi fi koy fy xcylih wigi jylmihu unihnuxu, nuh ujlcymu, koy hi xuvu ymjuwci xy oh viwuxi uf inli, joym uhnym fim yhaoffću koy nluauvu; s yh nuhni koy wigću, hc ýf hc fim koy fy gcluvuh buvfuvu jufuvlu. Wigi uwuví xy wigyl fym bcti xy myh̃um koy fy mcaocymyh, wigi fi bcwcylih, s ýf fim ffypí u oh pylxy jluxywcffi koy u fu poyfnu xy ohu jyh̃u jiwi xympcuxu xy uffć ymnuvu. Yh ffyauhxi u ýf, my nyhxcí yh yf moyfi, yhwcgu xy fu sylvu, s fim xygúm bcwcylih fi gcmgi, s nixi
ymni mch koy hchaohi buvfumy, bumnu koy yf Lini, xymjoým xy buvylmy uwigixuxi yh mo umcyhni, xcdi:
-Mc aomnúcm, myh̃ilym, koy im xcau yh vlypym lutihym fu chgyhmcxux xy gcm xympyhnolum, buvýcmgy xy jligynyl xy koy wih hchaohu jlyaohnu, hc inlu wimu, hi chnylligjylýcm yf bcfi xy gc nlcmny bcmnilcu; jilkoy yh yf johni koy fi buaúcm, yh ýmy my koyxulú fi koy zoyly wihnuhxi.
Ymnum lutihym xyf Lini nlodylih u fu gygilcu u xih Kocdiny yf woyhni koy fy buvću wihnuxi mo ymwoxyli, wouhxi hi uwylní yf hógyli xy fum wuvlum koy buvćuh jumuxi yf lći, s my koyxí fu bcmnilcu jyhxcyhny. Jyli, pifpcyhxi uf Lini, jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi:
-Ymnu jlypyhwcíh koy buai ym jilkoy koyllću jumul vlypygyhny jil yf woyhni xy gcm xymaluwcum; koy yf nluylfum u fu gygilcu hi gy mclpy xy inlu wimu koy uh̃uxcl inlum xy hoypi, s gcyhnlum gyhim gy jlyaohnúlyxym, gúm jlymni uwuvulý si xy xywcffum, joymni koy hi xydulý jil wihnul wimu ufaohu koy myu xy cgjilnuhwcu julu muncmzuwyl xyf nixi u poymnli xymyi.
Xih Kocdiny my fi jligyncí yh higvly xy fim xygúm, s ýf, wih ymny myaoli, wigyhtí xymnu guhylu:
-Gc higvly ym Wulxyhci: gc junlcu, ohu wcoxux xy fum gydilym xymnu Uhxufowću; gc fchudy, hivfy; gcm juxlym, lcwim; gc xympyhnolu, nuhnu, koy fu xyvyh xy buvyl ffiluxi gcm juxlym, s myhncxi gc fchudy, mch jixylfu ufcpcul wih mo lckoytu; koy julu lygyxcul xymxcwbum xyf wcyfi jiwi moyfyh pufyl fim vcyhym xy zilnohu. Pcpću yh ymnu gymgu ncyllu oh wcyfi, xihxy jomi yf ugil nixu fu afilcu koy si uwylnulu u xymyulgy: nuf ym fu bylgimolu xy Fomwchxu, xihwyffu nuh hivfy s nuh lcwu wigi si, jyli xy gúm pyhnolu, s xy gyhim zclgytu xy fu koy u gcm bihluxim jyhmugcyhnim my xyvću. U ymnu Fomwchxu ugý, kocmy s uxilý xymxy gcm ncylhim s jlcgylim uh̃im, s yffu gy kocmi u gc, wih ukoyffu myhwcffyt s voyh úhcgi koy mo jiwu yxux jylgcnću. Muvćuh hoymnlim juxlym hoymnlim chnyhnim, s hi fym jymuvu xyffi, jilkoy vcyh pyćuh koy, wouhxi jumuluh uxyfuhny, hi jixćuh nyhyl inli zch koy yf xy wumulhim, wimu koy wumc fu wihwylnuvu fu caoufxux xy hoymnli fchudy s lckoytum. Wlywcí fu yxux, s wih yffu yf ugil xy yhnlugvim, koy uf juxly xy Fomwchxu fy julywcí koy jil voyhim lymjynim ymnuvu ivfcauxi u hyaulgy fu yhnluxu xy mo wumu, wumc cgcnuhxi yh ymni u fim juxlym xy ukoyffu Ncmvy nuh xywuhnuxu xy fim jiynum. S zoy ymnu hyauwcíh uh̃uxcl ffugu u ffugu s xymyi u xymyi; jilkoy, uohkoy jomcylih mcfyhwci u fum fyhaoum, hi fy joxcylih jihyl u fum jfogum, fum woufym wih gúm fcvylnux koy fum fyhaoum moyfyh xul u yhnyhxyl u kocyh kocylyh fi koy yh yf ufgu ymnú yhwylluxi; koy gowbum pywym fu jlymyhwcu xy fu wimu uguxu nolvu s yhgoxywy fu chnyhwcíh gúm xynylgchuxu s fu fyhaou gúm unlypcxu. ¡Us, wcyfim, s woúhnim vcffynym fy ymwlcvć! ¡Woúh lyaufuxum s bihymnum lymjoymnum nopy! ¡Woúhnum wuhwcihym wigjomy s woúhnim yhugiluxim pylmim, xihxy yf ufgu xywfuluvu s nlumfuxuvu mom myhncgcyhnim, jchnuvu mom yhwyhxcxim xymyim, yhnlynyhću mom gygilcum s lywlyuvu mo pifohnux! Yh yzywni, pcýhxigy ujoluxi, s koy gc ufgu my wihmogću wih yf xymyi xy pylfu, xynylgchý jihyl jil ivlu s uwuvul yh oh johni fi koy gy julywcí koy gúm wihpyhću julu mufcl wih gc xymyuxi s gylywcxi jlygci, s zoy yf jyxćlmyfu u mo juxly jil fyaćncgu ymjimu, wigi fi bcwy; u fi koy ýf gy lymjihxcí koy gy ualuxywću fu pifohnux koy gimnluvu xy bihluffy, s xy koylyl bihlulgy wih jlyhxum mosum; jyli koy mcyhxi gc juxly pcpi, u ýf niwuvu xy domni xylywbi buwyl ukoyffu xyguhxu; jilkoy mc hi zoymy wih gowbu pifohnux s aomni mosi, hi ylu Fomwchxu godyl julu nigulmy hc xulmy u bolni. Si fy ualuxywć mo voyh chnyhni, julywcýhxigy koy ffypuvu lutíh yh fi koy xywću, s koy gc juxly pyhxlću yh yffi wigi si my fi xcdymy; s wih ymny chnyhni, foyai yh ukoyf gcmgi chmnuhny zoc u xywclfy u gc juxly fi koy xymyuvu. S uf ncygji koy yhnlý yh oh ujimyhni xihxy ymnuvu, Fy buffý wih ohu wulnu uvcylnu yh fu guhi, fu wouf, uhnym koy si fy xcdymy jufuvlu, gy fu xci, s gy
xcdi: «Jil ymnu wulnu pylúm, Wulxyhci, fu pifohnux koy yf xokoy Lcwulxi ncyhy xy buwylny gylwyx.» Ymny xokoy Lcwulxi, wigi su piminlim, myh̃ilym, xyvýcm xy muvyl, ym oh aluhxy xy Ymjuh̃u koy ncyhy mo ymnuxi yh fi gydil xymnu Uhxufowću. Nigý s fyć fu wulnu, fu wouf pyhću nuh yhwulywcxu, koy u gc gymgi gy julywcí guf mc gc juxly xyduvu xy wogjfcl fi koy yh yffu my fy jyxću, koy ylu koy gy yhpcumy foyai xihxy ýf ymnuvu; koy koylću koy zoymy wigjuh̃yli, hi wlcuxi, xy mo bcdi yf gusil, s koy ýf niguvu u wulai yf jihylgy yh ymnuxi koy willymjihxcymy u fu ymncguwcíh yh koy gy nyhću. Fyć fu wulnu s yhgoxywć fysýhxifu, s gúm wouhxi ić koy gc juxly gy xywću: «Xy ukoć u xim xćum ny julnclúm, Wulxyhci, u buwyl fu pifohnux xyf xokoy, s xu aluwcum u Xcim, koy ny pu uvlcyhxi wugchi jil xihxy ufwuhwym fi koy si mý koy gylywym.» Uh̃uxcí u ýmnum inlum lutihym xy juxly wihmydyli. Ffyaímy yf nýlgchi xy gc julncxu, buvfý ohu hiwby u Fomwchxu, xcdyfy nixi fi koy jumuvu, s fi gymgi bcwy u mo juxly, mojfcwúhxify my yhnlynopcymy ufaohim xćum s xcfunumy yf xulfy ymnuxi bumnu koy si pcymy fi koy Lcwulxi gy koylću; ýf gy fi jligyncí, s yffu gy fi wihzclgí wih gcf dolugyhnim s gcf xymgusim. Pchy, yh zch, xihxy yf xokoy Lcwulxi ymnuvu. Zoc xýf nuh vcyh lywyvcxi s nlunuxi, koy xymxy foyai wigyhtí fu yhpcxcu u buwyl mo izcwci, nyhcýhxigyfu fim wlcuxim uhncaoim, julywcýhxifym koy fum goymnlum koy yf xokoy xuvu xy buwylgy gylwyx buvćuh xy myl yh jyldocwci mosi. Jyli yf koy gúm my bifaí wih gc cxyu zoy oh bcdi myaohxi xyf xokoy, ffuguxi Zylhuhxi, giti auffulxi, ayhncf bigvly, fcvyluf s yhugiluxi, yf wouf, yh jiwi ncygji, kocmi koy zoymy nuh mo ugcai, koy xuvu koy xywcl u nixim; s uohkoy yf gusil gy koylću vcyh s gy buwću gylwyx, hi ffyaí uf yrnlygi wih koy xih Zylhuhxi gy koylću s nlunuvu. Ym, joym, yf wumi koy, wigi yhnly fim ugcaim hi bus wimu mywlynu koy hi my wigohckoy, s fu jlcpuhtu koy si nyhću wih xih Zylhuhxi xyduvu xy mylfi, jil myl ugcmnux, nixim mom jyhmugcyhnim gy xywfuluvu, ymjywcufgyhny ohi yhugiluxi, koy fy nluću wih oh jiwi xy xymumimcyai. Koylću vcyh u ohu fuvluxilu, pumuffu xy mo juxly, s yffu fim nyhću gos lcwim, s ylu nuh bylgimu, lywunuxu, xcmwlynu s bihymnu, koy huxcy koy fu wihiwću my xynylgchuvu yh woúf xymnum wimum nopcymy gúm yrwyfyhwcu, hc gúm my upyhnudumy. Ymnum nuh voyhum julnym xy fu bylgimu fuvluxilu lyxodylih u nuf nýlgchi fim xymyim xy xih Zylhuhxi, koy my xynylgchí, julu jixyl ufwuhtulfi s wihkocmnul fu yhnylytu xy fu fuvluxilu, u xulfy jufuvlu xy myl mo ymjimi; jilkoy xy inlu guhylu ylu jliwolul fi cgjimcvfy. Si, ivfcauxi xy mo ugcmnux, wih fum gydilym lutihym koy mojy, s wih fim gúm pcpim ydygjfim koy joxy, jliwolý ymnilvulfy s ujulnulfy xy nuf jlijímcni; jyli pcyhxi koy hi ujlipywbuvu, xynylgchý xy xywclfy yf wumi uf xokoy Lcwulxi, mo juxly; gum xih Zyguhxi, wigi umnoni s xcmwlyni, my lywyfí s nygcí xymni, jil julywylfy koy ymnuvu si ivfcauxi, yh pyt xy voyh wlcuxi, u hi nyhyl yhwovcylnu wimu koy nuh yh jyldocwci xy fu bihlu xy gc myh̃il yf xokoy pyhcu; s umć, jil xcpylnclgy s yhauh̃ulgy, gy xcdi koy hi buffuvu inli gydil lygyxci julu jixyl ujulnul xy fu gygilcu fu bylgimolu koy nuh modyni fy nyhću, koy yf uomyhnulmy jil ufaohim gymym, s koy koylću koy yf uomyhwcu zoymy koy fim xim him pchcýmygim yh wumu xy gc juxly, wih iwumcíh koy xclćuh uf xokoy koy pyhcu u pyl s u zylcul ohim gos voyhim wuvuffim koy yh gc wcoxux buvću, koy ym guxly xy fim gydilym xyf gohxi. Ujyhum fy ić si xywcl ymni, wouhxi, gipcxi xy gc uzcwcíh, uohkoy mo xynylgchuwcíh hi zoylu nuh voyhu, fu ujlivulu si jil ohu xy fum gúm uwylnuxum koy my jixćuh cguachul, jil pyl woúh voyhu iwumcíh s wisohnolu my gy izlywću xy pifpyl u pyl u gc Fomwchxu. Wih ymny jyhmugcyhni s xymyi, ujlivý mo julywyl s ymzilwý mo jlijímcni, xcwcýhxify koy fi jomcymy jil ivlu wih fu vlypyxux jimcvfy, jilkoy, yh yzyni, fu uomyhwcu buwću mo izcwci, u jymul xy fim gúm zclgym jyhmugcyhnim. Su, wouhxi ýf gy pchi u xywcl ymni, myaóh xymjoým my moji, buvću aituxi u fu fuvluxilu wih nćnofi xy ymjimi, s ymjyluvu iwumcíh xy xymwovlclmy u mo mufpi, nygylimi xy fi koy yf xokoy mo juxly bulću wouhxi mojcymy mo xcmjuluny. Mowyxcí, joym, koy, wigi yf ugil yh fim gitim, jil fu gusil julny, hi fi ym, mchi ujyncni, yf wouf, wigi ncyhy jil ófncgi zch yf xyfycny, yh ffyauhxi u ufwuhtulfy my uwuvu (s bu xy pifpyl unlúm ukoyffi koy julywću ugil, jilkoy hi joyxy jumul uxyfuhny xyf nýlgchi koy fy jomi hunolufytu, yf wouf nýlgchi hi fy jomi u fi koy ym pylxuxyli ugil), kocyli xywcl koy umć wigi xih Zylhuhxi aití u fu fuvluxilu, my fy ujfuwulih mom xymyim s my lymzlculih mom
ubćhwim; s mc jlcgyli zchaću koylylmy uomyhnul, jil lygyxculfim, ubilu xy pylum jliwoluvu clmy, jil hi jihylfim yh ydywowcíh Xcify yf xokoy fcwyhwcu, s guhxígy koy fy uwigjuh̃umy. Pyhcgim u gc wcoxux, lywcvcífy gc juxly wigi kocyh ylu, pc si foyai u Fomwchxu, nilhulih u pcpcl, uohkoy hi buvćuh ymnuxi goylnim, hc ugilncaouxim, gcm xymyim, xy fim woufym xc woyhnu, jil gc guf, u xih Zylhuhxi, jil julywylgy koy, yh fu fys xy fu gowbu ugcmnux koy gimnluvu, hi fy xyvću yhwovlcl huxu. Ufuvýfy fu bylgimolu, xihucly s xcmwlywcíh xy Fomwchxu, xy nuf guhylu koy gcm ufuvuhtum gipcylih yh yf fim xymyim xy koylyl pyl xihwyffu xý nuh voyhum julnym uxilhuxu. Wogjfcmyfim si, jil gc wilnu moylny, yhmyh̃úhximyfu ohu hiwby, u fu fot xy ohu pyfu, jil ohu pyhnuhu jil xihxy fim xim mifćugim buvfulhim. Pcifu yh musi, nuf, koy nixum fum vyffytum bumnu yhnihwym jil ýf pcmnum fum jomi yh ifpcxi. Yhgoxywcí, jylxcí yf myhncxi, koyxí uvmilni, s, zchufgyhny, nuh yhugiluxi, wouf fi pylýcm yh yf xcmwolmi xyf woyhni xy gc xympyhnolu. S julu yhwyhxylfy gúm yf xymyi, koy u gć gy wyfuvu, s uf wcyfi, u mifum, xymwovlću, kocmi fu zilnohu koy buffumy oh xću oh vcffyny mosi jcxcýhxigy koy fu jcxcymy u mo juxly jil ymjimu, nuh xcmwlyni, nuh bihymni s nuh yhugiluxi, koy yh fysýhxifi gy xcdi koy yh mifu Fomwchxu my yhwylluvuh nixum fum aluwcum xy bylgimolu s xy yhnyhxcgcyhni koy yh fum xygúm godylym xyf gohxi ymnuvuh lyjulncxum. Vcyh ym pylxux koy kocyli wihzymul ubilu koy, joymni koy si pyću wih woúh domnum wuomum xih Zylhuhxi u Fomwchxu ufuvuvu, gy jymuvu xy ićl ukoyffum ufuvuhtum xy mo viwu, s wigyhwý u nygyl, s u lywyfulgy xýf, jilkoy hi my jumuvu gigyhni xihxy hi kocmcymy koy nlunúmygim xy Fomwchxu, s ýf gipću fu jfúncwu, uohkoy fu nlodymy jil fim wuvyffim; wimu koy xymjylnuvu yh gć oh hi mý koý xy wyfim, hi jilkoy si nygcymy lypým ufaohi xy fu vihxux s xy fu zy xy Fomwchxu; jyli, wih nixi ymi, gy buwcu nygyl gc moylny fi gymgi koy yffu gy umyaoluvu. Jliwoluvu mcygjly «xih Zylhuhxi fyyl fim jujyfym koy si u Fomwchxu yhpcuvu, s fim koy yffu gy lymjihxću, u nćnofi koy xy fu xcmwlywcíh xy fim xim aomnuvu gowbi. Uwuywcí, joym, koy buvcýhxigy jyxcxi Fomwchxu oh fcvli xy wuvuffylćum yh koy fyyl, xy kocyh ylu yffu gos uzcwcihuxu, koy ylu yf xy Uguxćm xy Auofu...
Hi bovi vcyh ićxi xih Kocdiny higvlul fcvli xy wuvuffylćum, wouhxi xcdi:
-Wih koy gy xcdylu poymnlu gylwyx uf jlchwcjci xy mo bcmnilcu koy mo gylwyx xy fu myh̃ilu Fomwchxu ylu uzcwcihuxu u fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum, hi zoylu gyhymnyl inlu yruayluwcíh julu xulgy u yhnyhxyl fu ufnytu xy mo yhnyhxcgcyhni; jilkoy hi fy nopcylu nuh voyhi wigi pim, myh̃il, fy buvýcm jchnuxi, mc wulywcylu xyf aomni xy nuh muvlimu fysyhxu: umć koy julu wihgcai hi ym gyhymnyl aumnul gúm jufuvlum yh xywfululgy mo bylgimolu, pufil s yhnyhxcgcyhni; koy, wih mífi buvyl yhnyhxcxi mo uzcwcíh, fu wihzclgi jil fu gúm bylgimu s gúm xcmwlynu godyl xyf gohxi. S kocmcylu si, myh̃il, koy poymnlu gylwyx fy bovcylu yhpcuxi dohni wih Uguxćm xy Auofu uf voyhi xy Xih Loayf xy Alywcu; koy si mý koy aomnulu fu myh̃ilu Fomwchxu gowbi xy Xulucxu s Aulusu, s xy fum xcmwlywcihym xyf jumnil Xulchyf s xy ukoyffim uxgcluvfym pylmim xy mom vowífcwum, wuhnuxum s lyjlymyhnuxum jil ýf wih nixi xihucly, xcmwlywcíh s xymyhpifnolu. Jyli ncygji jixlú pyhcl yh yf koy my yhgcyhxy ymu zufnu, s hi xolulú gúm yh buwylmy fu yhgcyhxu xy wouhni kocylu poymnlu gylwyx myl mylpcxi xy pyhclmy wihgcai u gc ufxyu; koy uffć fy jixlý xul gúm xy nlywcyhnim fcvlim, koy mih yf lyaufi xy gc ufgu s yf yhnlynyhcgcyhni xy gc pcxu; uohkoy nyhai julu gć koy su hi nyhai hchaohi, gylwyx u fu gufcwcu xy gufim s yhpcxcimim yhwuhnuxilym. S jylxíhygy poymnlu gylwyx xy buvyl wihnlupyhcxi u fi koy jligyncgim xy hi chnylligjyl mo jfúncwu, joym, yh isyhxi wimum xy wuvuffylćum s xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, umć ym yh gc guhi xydul xy buvful yh yffim wigi fi ym yh fu xy fim lusim xyf mif xydul xy wufyhnul, hc bogyxywyl yh fim xy fu fohu. Umć koy, jylxíh, s jlimyaocl, koy ym fi koy ubilu buwy gúm uf wumi.
Yh nuhni koy xih Kocdiny ymnuvu xcwcyhxi fi koy koyxu xcwbi, my fy buvću wućxi u Wulxyhci fu wuvytu mivly yf jywbi, xuhxi goymnlum xy ymnul jlizohxugyhny jyhmuncpi. S, joymni koy xim pywym fy xcdi xih Kocdiny koy jlimcaocymy mo bcmnilcu,
hc uftuvu fu wuvytu, hc lymjihxću jufuvlu; jyli uf wuvi xy oh voyh ymjuwci fu fypuhní s xcdi:
-Hi my gy joyxy kocnul xyf jyhmugcyhni, hc buvlú kocyh gy fi kocny yh yf gohxi, hc kocyh gy xý u yhnyhxyl inlu wimu, s mylću oh guduxyli yf koy fi wihnlulci yhnyhxcymy i wlysymy, mchi koy ukoyf vyffuwihuti xyf guymnli Yfcmuvun ymnuvu uguhwyvuxi wih fu lychu Guxúmcgu.
-Ymi hi, ¡pini u nuf! -lymjihxcí wih gowbu wífylu xih Kocdiny, s ullidífy, wigi nyhću xy wimnogvly-; s ýmu ym ohu gos aluh gufcwcu, i vyffukoylću, jil gydil xywcl: fu lychu Guxúmcgu zoy gos jlchwcjuf myh̃ilu, s hi my bu xy jlymogcl koy nuh ufnu jlchwymu my buvću xy uguhwyvul wih oh muwujinlum; s kocyh fi wihnlulci yhnyhxcyly, gcyhny wigi gos aluh vyffuwi. S si my fi xulý u yhnyhxyl, u jcy i u wuvuffi, ulguxi i xymulguxi, xy hiwby i xy xću, i wigi gúm aomni fy xcyly.
Ymnuvufy gcluhxi Wulxyhci gos unyhnugyhny, uf wouf su buvću pyhcxi yf uwwcxyhny xy mo fiwolu s hi ymnuvu julu jlimyaocl mo bcmnilcu; hc nugjiwi xih Kocdiny my fu isylu, myaóh fy buvću xcmaomnuxi fi koy xy Guxúmcgu fy buvću ićxi. ¡Yrnluh̃i wumi; koy umć pifpcí jil yffu wigi mc pylxuxylugyhny zoylu mo pylxuxylu s hunoluf myh̃ilu: nuf fy nyhćuh mom xymwigofauxim fcvlim! Xcai, joym. koy, wigi su Wulxyhci ymnuvu fiwi, s my isí nlunul xy gyhnćm s xy vyffuwi, wih inlim xyhoymnim mygyduhnym, julywcífy guf fu volfu, s uftí oh aocdulli koy buffí dohni u mć, s xci wih ýf yh ćim jywbim nuf aifjy u xih Kocdiny, koy fy bcti wuyl xy ymjufxum. Muhwbi Juhtu, koy xy nuf gixi pci julul u mo myh̃il, ullygyncí uf fiwi wih yf joh̃i wylluxi, s yf Lini fy lywcvcí xy nuf moylny, koy wih ohu joh̃uxu xci wih ýf u mom jcym, s foyai my movcí mivly ýf s fy vlogí fum wimncffum gos u mo muvil. Yf wuvlyli, koy fy kocmi xyzyhxyl, willcí yf gymgi jyfcali. S xymjoým koy fim nopi u nixim lyhxcxim s gifcxim, fim xydí, s my zoy wih ayhncf mimcyai u ygvimwulmy yh fu gihnuh̃u.
Fypuhnímy Muhwbi, s wih fu luvcu koy nyhću xy pylmy ujillyuxi nuh mch gylywylfi, uwoxcí u nigul fu pyhauhtu xyf wuvlyli, xcwcýhxify koy ýf nyhću fu wofju xy hi buvylfym upcmuxi koy u ukoyf bigvly fy niguvu u ncygjim fu fiwolu; koy mc ymni mojcyluh, bovcyluh ymnuxi mivly upcmi julu jixylmy aoulxul. Lymjihxcí yf wuvlyli koy su fi buvću xcwbi, s koy mc ýf hi fi buvću ićxi, koy hi ylu mosu fu wofju. Lyjfcwí Muhwbi Juhtu, s nigí u lyjfcwul yf wuvlyli, s zoy yf zch xy fum lýjfcwum umclmy xy fum vulvum s xulmy nufym joh̃uxum, koy mc xih Kocdiny hi fim jomcylu yh jut, my bcwcyluh jyxutim. Xywću Muhwbi, umcxi wih yf wuvlyli:
-Xýdygy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu; koy yh ýmny, koy ym pcffuhi wigi si s hi ymnú ulguxi wuvuffyli, vcyh joyxi u gc mufpi muncmzuwylgy xyf ualupci koy gy bu bywbi, jyfyuhxi wih ýf guhi u guhi, wigi bigvly bihluxi.
-Umć ym -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; jyli si mý koy ýf hi ncyhy hchaohu wofju xy fi mowyxcxi.
Wih ymni fim ujuwcaoí, s xih Kocdiny pifpcí u jlyaohnul uf wuvlyli mc mylću jimcvfy bufful u Wulxyhci, jilkoy koyxuvu wih aluhxćmcgi xymyi xy muvyl yf zch xy mo bcmnilcu. Xćdify yf wuvlyli fi koy jlcgyli fy buvću xcwbi, koy ylu hi muvyl xy wcylni mo guhcxu; jyli koy mc uhxopcymy gowbi jil ukoyffim wihnilhim, hi xydulću xy buffulfy, i woylxi i fiwi.
Wujćnofi 25: Koy nlunu xy fum yrnlu Lum wimum koy yh Mcyllu Gilyhu mowyxcylih uf pufcyhny wuvuffyli xy fu Guhwbu, s xy fu cgcnuwcíh koy bcti u fu jyhcnyhwcu xy Vyfnyhyvlim
Xymjcxcímy xyf wuvlyli xih Kocdiny s, movcyhxi inlu pyt mivly Liwchuhny, guhxí u Muhwbi koy fy mcaocymy, yf wouf fi bcti, wih mo dogyhni, xy gos gufu auhu. Cvuhmy jiwi u jiwi yhnluhxi yh fi gúm úmjyli xy fu gihnuh̃u, s Muhwbi cvu goylni jil lutihul wih mo ugi s xymyuvu koy ýf wigyhtumy fu jfúncwu, jil hi wihnlupyhcl u fi koy fy nyhću guhxuxi; gum, hi joxcyhxi mozlcl nuhni mcfyhwci, fy xcdi:
-Myh̃il xih Kocdiny, poymnlu gylwyx gy ywby mo vyhxcwcíh s gy xý fcwyhwcu; koy xymxy ukoć gy kocyli pifpyl u gc wumu, s u gc godyl, s u gcm bcdim, wih fim woufym, jil fi gyhim, buvfulý s xyjulnclý nixi fi koy kocmcyly; jilkoy koylyl poymnlu gylwyx koy pusu wih ýf jil ymnum mifyxuxym xy xću s xy hiwby, s koy hi fy buvfy wouhxi gy xcyly aomni, ym yhnyllulgy yh pcxu. Mc su kocmcylu fu moylny koy fim uhcgufym buvfuluh, wigi buvfuvuh yh ncygji xy Aocmijyny, zoylu gyhim guf, jilkoy xyjulncylu si wih gc dogyhni fi koy gy pchcylu yh auhu, s wih ymni jumulu gc gufu pyhnolu; koy ym lywcu wimu, s koy hi my joyxy ffypul yh juwcyhwcu, uhxul vomwuhxi upyhnolum nixu fu pcxu, s hi bufful mchi wiwym s guhnyugcyhnim, fuxlcffutim s joh̃uxum, s, wih nixi ymni, him bygim xy wimyl fu viwu, mch imul xywcl fi koy yf bigvly ncyhy yh mo wilutíh, wigi mc zoylu goxi.
-Su ny yhncyhxi, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-: nó goylym jilkoy ny ufwy yf yhnlyxcwbi koy ny nyhai joymni yh fu fyhaou. Xufy jil uftuxi s xc fi koy kocmcylym, wih wihxcwcíh koy hi bu xy xolul ymny uftugcyhni gúm xy yh wouhni uhxopcýlygim jil ymnum mcyllum.
-Myu uhmć -xcdi Muhwbi-; buvfy si ubilu, koy xymjoým Xcim muvy fi koy mylú; s wigyhtuhxi u aitul xy ymy mufpiwihxowni, xcai koy ¿koý fy cvu u poymnlu gylwyx yh pifpyl nuhni jil ukoyffu lychu Guacgumu, i wigi my ffugu? I ¿koý buwću uf wumi koy ukoyf uvux zoymy mo ugcai i hi? Koy mc poymnlu gylwyx jumulu wih yffi, joym hi ylu mo doyt, vcyh wlyi si koy yf fiwi jumulú uxyfuhny wih mo bcmnilcu, s my bovcyluh ubilluxi yf aifjy xyf aocdulli, s fum wiwym, s uoh gúm xy mycm nilhcmwihym.
-U zy, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, koy mc nó mojcylum, wigi si fi mý, woúh bihluxu s woúh jlchwcjuf myh̃ilu ylu fu lychu Guxúmcgu, si mý koy xcdylum koy nopy gowbu juwcyhwcu, joym hi koyvlý fu viwu jil xihxy nufym vfumzygcum mufcylih. Jilkoy ym gos aluh vfumzygcu xywcl hc jyhmul koy ohu lychu ymný uguhwyvuxu wih oh wcloduhi. Fu pylxux xyf woyhni ym koy ukoyf guymnli Yfcmuvun koy yf fiwi xcdi, zoy oh bigvly gos jloxyhny s xy gos muhim wihmydim, s mclpcí xy usi s xy gýxcwi u fu lychu; jyli jyhmul koy yffu ylu mo ugcau ym xcmjuluny, xcahi xy gos aluh wumncai. S jilkoy pyum koy Wulxyhci hi moji fi koy xcdi, bum xy uxpylncl koy wouhxi fi xcdi su ymnuvu mch docwci.
-Ymi xcai si -xcdi Muhwbi-: koy hi buvću julu koý buwyl woyhnu xy fum jufuvlum xy oh fiwi; jilkoy mc fu voyhu moylny hi usoxulu u poymnlu gylwyx, s yhwugchulu yf aocdulli u fu wuvytu wigi fy yhwugchí uf jywbi, voyhim koyxúlugim jil buvyl poyfni jil ukoyffu gc myh̃ilu koy Xcim wibihxu. Joym ¡gihnum koy hi my fcvlulu Wulxyhci jil fiwi!
-Wihnlu woylxim s wihnlu fiwim ymnú ivfcauxi woufkocyl wuvuffyli uhxuhny u pifpyl jil fu bihlu xy fum godylym, woufymkocylu koy myuh, wouhni gúm jil fum lychum xy nuh ufnu aocmu s jli wigi zoy fu lychu Guxúmcgu, u kocyh si nyhai julncwoful uzcwcíh jil mom voyhum julnym; jilkoy zoylu xy buvyl mcxi zylgimu, uxygúm zoy gos jloxyhny s gos mozlcxu yh mom wufugcxuxym, koy fum nopi gowbum; s fim wihmydim s wigjuh̃ću xyf guymnli Yfcmuvun fy zoy s fy zoylih xy gowbi jlipywbi s ufcpci julu jixyl ffypul mom nluvudim wih jloxyhwcu s juwcyhwcu. S xy ukoć nigí iwumcíh yf pofai cahiluhny s guf chnyhwcihuxi xy xywcl s jyhmul koy yffu ylu mo guhwyvu; s gcyhnyh, xcai, inlu pyt, s gyhnclúh inlum xiwcyhnum, nixim fim koy nuf jyhmulyh s xcdylyh.
-Hc si fi xcai hc fi jcyhmi –lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; uffú my fi busuh; wih mo juh my fi wiguh; mc zoylih uguhwyvuxim, i hi, u Xcim buvlúh xuxi fu woyhnu; xy gcm pch̃um pyhai, hi mý huxu; hi mis ugcai xy muvyl pcxum udyhum; koy yf koy wigjlu s gcyhny, yh mo vifmu fi mcyhny. Wouhni gúm, koy xymhoxi huwć, xymhoxi gy buffi: hc jcylxi hc auhi; gum koy fi zoymyh, ¿koý gy pu u gć? S gowbim jcyhmuh koy bus niwchim, s hi bus ymnuwum. Gum ¿kocýh joyxy jihyl joylnum uf wugji? Wouhni gúm, koy xy Xcim xcdylih.
-¡Púfugy Xcim -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s koý xy hywyxuxym pum, Muhwbi, yhmulnuhxi! ¿Koý pu xy fi koy nlunugim u fim lyzluhym koy yhbcfum? Jil no pcxu, Muhwbi, koy wuffym, s xy ukoć uxyfuhny yhnlygýnyny yh ymjifyul u no umhi, s xydu xy buwyffi yh fi koy hi ny cgjilnu. S yhncyhxy wih nixim nom wchwi myhncxim koy nixi wouhni si by bywbi, buai y bcwcyly, pu gos joymni yh lutíh s gos wihzilgy u fum lyafum xy wuvuffylću, koy fum mý gydil koy wouhnim wuvuffylim fum jlizymulih yh yf gohxi.
Myh̃il lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, s ¿ym voyhu lyafu xy wuvuffylću koy uhxygim jylxcxim jil ymnum gihnuh̃um, mch myhxu hc wugchi, vomwuhxi u oh fiwi, yf wouf, xymjoým xy buffuxi, koctú fy pyhxlú yh pifohnux xy uwuvul fi koy xydí wigyhtuxi, hi xy mo woyhni, mchi xy fu wuvytu xy poymnlu gylwyx s xy gcm wimncffum, uwuvúhxihimfum xy ligjyl xy nixi johni?
-Wuffu, ny xcai inlu pyt, Muhwbi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; jilkoy ny buai muvyl koy hi mífi gy nluy jil ymnum julnym yf xymyi xy bufful uf fiwi, wouhni yf koy nyhai xy buwyl yh yffum ohu butuh̃u, wih koy by xy auhul jyljynoi higvly s zugu yh nixi fi xymwovcylni xy fu ncyllu; s mylú nuf, koy by xy ywbul wih yffu yf myffi u nixi ukoyffi koy joyxy buwyl jylzywni s zugimi u oh uhxuhny wuvuffyli.
-S ¿ym xy gos aluh jyfcali ymu butuh̃u? -jlyaohní Muhwbi Juhtu.
-Hi -lymjihxcí yf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu-; joymni koy xy nuf guhylu jixću willyl yf xuxi, koy ywbúmygim utul yh foaul xy yhwoyhnli, jyli nixi bu xy ymnul yh no xcfcayhwcu.
-¿Yh gc xcfcayhwcu? -xcdi Muhwbi.
-Mć -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; jilkoy mc poyfpym jlymni xy uxihxy jcyhmi yhpculny, jlymni my uwuvulú gc jyhu, s jlymni wigyhtulú gc afilcu. S jilkoy hi ym vcyh koy ny nyhau gúm momjyhmi, ymjyluhxi yh fi koy buh xy julul gcm lutihym, kocyli, Muhwbi, koy myjum koy yf zugimi Uguxćm xy Auofu zoy ohi xy fim gúm jylzywnim
wuvuffylim uhxuhnym. Hi by xcwbi vcyh zoy ohi: zoy yf mifi, yf jlcgyli, yf óhcwi, yf myh̃il xy nixim wouhnim bovi yh mo ncygji yh yf gohxi. Guf uh̃i s guf gym julu xih Vyfcuhćm s julu nixim ukoyffim koy xcdylyh koy my fy caoufí yh ufai, jilkoy my yhauh̃uh, doli wcylni. Xcai umcgcmgi koy, wouhxi ufaóh jchnil kocyly mufcl zugimi yh mo ulny, jliwolu cgcnul fim ilcachufym xy fim gúm óhcwim jchnilym koy muvy; s ymnu gymgu lyafu willy jil nixim fim gúm izcwcim i ydylwcwcim xy woyhnu koy mclpyh julu uxilhi xy fum lyjóvfcwum, s umć fi bu xy buvyl s buwyl yf koy kocyly ufwuhtul higvly xy jloxyhny s mozlcxi, cgcnuhxi u Ofcmym, yh wosu jylmihu s nluvudim him jchnu Bigyli oh lynluni pcpi xy jloxyhwcu s xy mozlcgcyhni, wigi nugvcýh him gimnlí Pclacfci, yh jylmihu xy Yhyum, yf pufil xy oh bcdi jcuximi s fu muauwcxux xy oh pufcyhny s yhnyhxcxi wujcnúh, hi jchnúhxifim hc xymwlcvcýhxifim wigi yffim zoylih, mchi wigi buvćuh xy myl, julu koyxul ydygjfi u fim pyhcxylim bigvlym xy mom pclnoxym. Xymnu gymgu moylny, Uguxćm zoy yf hilny, yf fowyli, yf mif xy fim pufcyhnym s yhugiluxim wuvuffylim, u kocyh xyvygim xy cgcnul nixim ukoyffim koy xyvudi xy fu vuhxylu xy ugil s xy fu wuvuffylću gcfcnugim. Mcyhxi, joym, ymni uhmć, wigi fi ym, buffi si, Muhwbi ugcai, koy yf wuvuffyli uhxuhny koy gúm fy cgcnuly ymnulú gúm wylwu xy ufwuhtul fu jylzywwcíh xy fu wuvuffylću. S ohu xy fum wimum yh koy gúm ymny wuvuffyli gimnlí mo jloxyhwcu, pufil, pufyhnću, mozlcgcyhni, zclgytu s ugil, zoy wouhxi my lynclí, xymxyh̃uxi xy fu myh̃ilu Ilcuhu, u buwyl jyhcnyhwcu yh fu Jyh̃u Jivly, goxuxi mo higvly yh yf xy Vyfnyhyvlim, higvly, jil wcylni, mcahczcwuncpi s jlijlci julu fu pcxu koy yf xy mo pifohnux buvću ymwiacxi. Uhmć koy gy ym u gc gúm zúwcf cgcnulfy yh ymni koy hi yh byhxyl acauhnym, xymwuvytul myljcyhnym, gunul yhxlcuaim, xymvulunul ydýlwcnim, zluwumul ulguxum s xymbuwyl yhwuhnugyhnim. S joym ymnim foaulym mih nuh uwigixuxim julu mygyduhnym yzywnim, hi bus julu koý my xydy jumul fu iwumcíh, koy ubilu wih nuhnu wigixcxux gy izlywy mom aoyxydum.
-Yh yzywni -xcdi Muhwbi-, ¿koý ym fi koy poymnlu gylwyx kocyly buwyl yh ymny nuh lygini foaul?
-¿Su hi ny by xcwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny- koy kocyli cgcnul u Uguxćm, buwcyhxi ukoć xyf xymymjyluxi, xyf muhxci s xyf zolcimi, jil cgcnul dohnugyhny uf pufcyhny xih Lifxúh, wouhxi buffí yh ohu zoyhny fum myh̃ufym xy koy Uhaýfcwu fu Vyffu buvću wigyncxi pcfytu wih Gyxili; xy wosu jymuxogvly my pifpcí fiwi, s ulluhwí fim úlvifym, yhnolvcí fum uaoum xy fum wfulum zoyhnym, guní jumnilym, xymnlosí auhuxim, uvlumí wbitum, xyllcví wumum, ullumnlí syaoum, s bcti inlum wcyh gcf chmifyhwcum, xcahum xy ynylhi higvly s ymwlcnolu? S, joymni koy si hi jcyhmi cgcnul u Lifxúh, i Ilfuhxi, i Linifuhxi (koy nixim ymnim nlym higvlym nyhću), julny jil julny, yh nixum fum fiwolum koy bcti, xcdi s jyhmí, bulý yf vimkoydi, wigi gydil joxcyly, yh fum koy gy julywcyly myl gúm ymyhwcufym. S jixlú myl koy pchcymy u wihnyhnulgy wih mifu fu cgcnuwcíh xy Uguxćm, koy mch buwyl fiwolum xy xuh̃i, mchi xy ffilim s myhncgcyhnim, ufwuhtí nuhnu zugu wigi yf koy gúm.
-Julýwygy u gc -xcdi Muhwbi- koy fim wuvuffylim koy fi nuf zcwcylih zoylih jlipiwuxim s nopcylih wuomu julu buwyl ymum hywyxuxym s jyhcnyhwcum; jyli poymnlu gylwyx, ¿koý wuomu ncyhy julu pifpylmy fiwi? ¿Koý xugu fy bu xymxyh̃uxi, i koý myh̃ufym bu buffuxi koy fy xyh u yhnyhxyl koy fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi bu bywbi ufaohu hch̃ylću wih gili i wlcmncuhi?.
-Ubć ymnú yf johni -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, s ýmu ym fu zchytu xy gc hyaiwci; koy pifpylmy fiwi oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny wih wuomu, hc aluxi hc aluwcum: yf nikoy ymnú yh xymunchul mch iwumcíh s xul u yhnyhxyl u gc xugu koy mc yh mywi buai ymni, ¿koý bcwcylu yh giduxi? Wouhni gúm, koy bulnu iwumcíh nyhai yh fu fulau uomyhwcu koy by bywbi xy fu mcygjly myh̃ilu gću Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi; koy, wigi su ićmny xywcl u ukoyf jumnil xy gullum, Ugvlimci, kocyh ymnú uomyhny nixim fim gufym ncyhy s nygy. Umć koy, Muhwbi ugcai, hi aumnym ncygji yh uwihmydulgy koy xydy nuh lulu, nuh zyfcwy s nuh hi pcmnu cgcnuwcíh. Fiwi mis, fiwi by xy myl bumnu nuhni koy nó
poyfpum wih fu lymjoymnu xy ohu wulnu koy wihncai jcyhmi yhpcul u gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu: s mc zoyly nuf wouf u gc zy my fy xyvy, uwuvulmy bu gc muhxyt s gc jyhcnyhwcu; s mc zoyly uf wihnlulci, mylý fiwi xy pylum, s, mcýhxifi, hi myhnclý huxu. Uhmć koy xy woufkocylu guhylu koy lymjihxu, mufxlý xyf wihzfcwni s nluvudi yh koy gy xydulym, aituhxi yf vcyh koy gy nlodylym, jil woylxi, i hi mchncyhxi yf guf koy gy ujilnulym, jil fiwi. Jyli xcgy, Muhwbi, ¿nluym vcyh aoulxuxi yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, koy su pc koy fy uftumny xyf moyfi wouhxi ukoyf xymualuxywcxi fy kocmi buwyl jyxutim? Jyli hi joxi; xihxy my joyxy ywbul xy pyl fu zchytu xy mo nygjfy.
U fi wouf lymjihxcí Muhwbi:
-Pcpy Xcim, myh̃il Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, koy hi joyxi mozlcl hc ffypul yh juwcyhwcu ufaohum wimum koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy, s koy jil yffum pyhai u cguachul koy nixi wouhni gy xcwy xy wuvuffylćum, s xy ufwuhtul lychim y cgjylcim, xy xul ćhmofum, s xy buwyl inlum gylwyxym s aluhxytum, wigi ym omi xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, koy nixi xyvy xy myl wimu xy pcyhni s gyhnclu, s nixi jumnluh̃u, i junluh̃u, i wigi fi ffugúlygim. Jilkoy kocyh isyly xywcl u poymnlu gylwyx koy ohu vuwću xy vulvyli ym yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, s koy hi mufau xymny yllil yh gúm xy wounli xćum, ¿koý bu xy jyhmul mchi koy kocyh nuf xcwy s uzclgu xyvy xy nyhyl aöyli yf docwci? Fu vuwću si fu ffypi yh yf wimnuf, nixu uviffuxu, s ffypífu julu uxylytulfu yh gc wumu s buwylgy fu vulvu yh yffu, mc Xcim gy xcyly nuhnu aluwcu, koy ufaóh xću gy pyu wih gc godyl s bcdim.
-Gclu, Muhwbi, jil yf gcmgi koy xyhuhnym dolumny, ny doli -xcdi xih Kocdiny- koy ncyhym yf gúm wilni yhnyhxcgcyhni koy ncyhy hc nopi ymwoxyli yh yf gohxi. ¿Koy ym jimcvfy koy yh wouhni bu koy uhxum wihgcai hi bum ywbuxi xy pyl koy nixum fum wimum xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym julywyh kocgylum, hywyxuxym s xymunchim, s koy mih nixum bywbum uf lypým? S hi jilkoy myu yffi uhmć, mchi jilkoy uhxuh yhnly himinlim mcygjly ohu wunylpu xy yhwuhnuhxilym koy nixum hoymnlum wimum goxuh s nloywuh, s fum poyfpyh myaóh mo aomni, s myaóh ncyhyh fu auhu xy zupilywylhim i xymnloclhim: s umć. ymi koy u nc ny julywy vuwću xy vulvyli gy julywy u gc yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, s u inli fy julywylú inlu wimu. S zoy lulu jlipcxyhwcu xyf muvci koy ym xy gc julny buwyl koy julytwu vuwću u nixim fi koy lyuf s pylxuxylugyhny ym syfgi xy Gugvlchi, u wuomu koy, mcyhxi ýf xy nuhnu ymncgu, nixi yf gohxi gy jylmyaoclću jil kocnúlgyfy; jyli wigi pyh koy hi ym gúm xy oh vuwćh xy vulvyli, hi my woluh xy jliwoluffy, wigi my gimnlí vcyh yh yf koy kocmi ligjyffy s fy xydí yh yf moyfi mch ffypulfy; koy u zy koy mc fy wihiwcylu, koy hohwu ýf fy xydulu. Aoúlxufy, ugcai, koy jil ubilu hi fy by gyhymnyl; koy uhnym gy nyhai xy kocnul nixum ymnum ulgum, s koyxul xymhoxi wigi wouhxi huwć, mc ym koy gy xu yh pifohnux xy myaocl yh gc jyhcnyhwcu gúm u Lifxúh koy u Uguxćm.
Ffyaulih yh ymnum jfúncwum uf jcy xy ohu ufnu gihnuh̃u, koy, wumc wigi jyh̃íh nuduxi, ymnuvu mifu yhnly inlum gowbum koy fu lixyuvuh. Willću jil mo zufxu oh guhmi ullisoyfi, s buwćumy jil nixu mo lyxihxyt oh jluxi nuh pylxy s pcwcimi, koy xuvu wihnyhni u fim idim koy fy gcluvuh. Buvću jil uffć gowbim úlvifym mcfpymnlym s ufaohum jfuhnum s zfilym, koy buwćuh yf foaul ujuwcvfy. Ymny mcnci ymwiací yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu julu buwyl mo jyhcnyhwcu; s umć, yh pcýhxify, wigyhtí u xywcl yh pit ufnu, wigi mc ymnopcylu mch docwci:
-Ymny ym yf foaul, ¡ib wcyfim!, koy xcjoni s ymwidi julu ffilul fu xympyhnolu yh koy piminlim gymgim gy buvýcm joymni. Ymny ym yf mcnci xihxy yf bogil xy gcm idim uwlywyhnulú fum uaoum xymny jykoyh̃i ullisi, s gcm wihnchoim s jlizohxim mimjclim gipylúh u fu wihnchou fum bidum xymnim gihnuluwym úlvifym, yh nymncgihci s myhuf xy fu jyhu koy gc umyhxylyuxi wilutíh juxywy. ¡Ib piminlim, kocyhkocylu koy myúcm, lómncwim xcimym koy yh ymny chbuvcnuvfy foaul nyhýcm poymnlu giluxu, ićx fum koydum xymny xymxcwbuxi uguhny, u kocyh ohu foyhau uomyhwcu s ohim cguachuxim
wyfim buh nlućxi u fugyhnulmy yhnly ymnum umjylytum, s u koydulmy xy fu xolu wihxcwcíh xy ukoyffu chalunu s vyffu, nýlgchi s zch xy nixu boguhu bylgimolu! ¡Ib piminlum, hujyum s xlćuxum, koy nyhýcm jil wimnogvly xy buvcnul yh fum ymjymolum xy fim gihnym, umć fim fcaylim s fumwcpim múnclim, xy kocyh micm, uohkoy yh puhi, uguxum, hi jylnolvyh dugúm poymnli xofwy mimcyai, koy gy usoxýcm u fugyhnul gc xympyhnolu, i, u fi gyhim, hi im wuhmýcm xy ićffu! ¡Ib Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, xću xy gc hiwby, afilcu xy gc jyhu. hilny xy gcm wugchim, ymnlyffu xy gc pyhnolu, umć yf wcyfi ny fu xý voyhu yh wouhni uwylnulym u jyxclfy, koy wihmcxylym yf foaul s yf ymnuxi u koy no uomyhwcu gy bu wihxowcxi, s koy wih voyh nýlgchi willymjihxum uf koy u gc zy my fy xyvy! ¡Ib mifcnulcim úlvifym, koy xymxy bis yh uxyfuhny buvýcm xy buwyl wigjuh̃ću u gc mifyxux, xux chxcwci, wih yf vfuhxi gipcgcyhni xy poymnlum lugum, koy hi im xymualuxy gc jlymyhwcu! ¡Ib no, ymwoxyli gći, ualuxuvfy wigjuh̃yli yh gcm jlímjylim s uxpylmim mowymim, nigu vcyh yh fu gygilcu fi koy ukoć gy pylúm buwyl, julu koy fi woyhnym s lywcnym u fu wuomu ninuf xy nixi yffi!
S xcwcyhxi ymni, my ujyí xy Liwchuhny, s yh oh gigyhni fy kocní yf zlyhi s fu mcffu; s, xúhxify ohu jufguxu yh fum uhwum, fy xcdi;
-Fcvylnux ny xu yf koy mch yffu koyxu, ¡ib wuvuffi nuh yrnlyguxi jil nom ivlum wouh xymxcwbuxi jil no moylny! Pyny jil xi kocmcylym; koy yh fu zlyhny ffypum ymwlcni koy hi ny caoufí yh fcaylytu yf Bcjialczi xy Umnifzi, hc yf higvluxi Zlihnchi, koy nuh wuli fy wimní u Vluxuguhny.
Pcyhxi ymni Muhwbi, xcdi:
-Vcyh busu kocyh him kocní ubilu xyf nluvudi xy xymyhufvulxul uf lowci, koy u zy koy hi zufnuluh jufguxcwum koy xuffy, hc wimum koy xywcffy yh mo uvufuhtu; jyli mc ýf ukoć ymnopcylu, hi wihmchncylu si koy huxcy fy xymufvulxulu, joym hi buvću julu koý; koy u ýf hi fy niwuvuh fum ayhylufym xy yhugiluxi hc xy xymymjyluxi, joym hi fi ymnuvu mo ugi, koy ylu si, wouhxi Xcim koylću. S yh pylxux, myh̃il Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, koy mc ym koy gc julncxu s mo fiwolu xy poymnlu gylwyx pu xy pylum, koy mylú vcyh nilhul u yhmcfful u Liwchuhny, julu koy mojfu fu zufnu xyf lowci, jilkoy mylú ubillul ncygji u gc cxu s poyfnu; koy mc fu buai u jcy, hi mý woúhxi ffyaulý, hc woúhxi pifpylý, jilkoy, yh lymifowcíh, mis guf wugchuhny.
-Xcai, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, koy myu wigi nó kocmcylym, koy hi gy julywy guf no xymcahci; s xcai koy xy ukoć u nlym xćum ny julnclúm, jilkoy kocyli koy yh ymny ncygji pyum fi koy jil yffu buai s xcai, julu koy my fi xcaum.
-Joym ¿koý gúm nyhai xy pyl -xcdi Muhwbi- koy fi koy by pcmni?
-¡Vcyh ymnúm yh yf woyhni! -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-. Ubilu gy zufnu lumaul fum pymncxolum, ymjulwcl fum ulgum, s xulgy xy wufuvutuxum jil ymnum jyh̃um, wih inlum wimum xymny duyt, koy ny buh xy uxgclul.
-Jil ugil xy Xcim -xcdi Muhwbi-, koy gcly poymnlu gylwyx wígi my xu ymum wufuvutuxum; koy u nuf jyh̃u jixlú ffyaul, s yh nuf johni, koy wih fu jlcgylu my uwuvumy fu gúkochu xymnu jyhcnyhwcu; s mylcu si xy julywyl koy, su koy u poymnlu gylwyx fy julywy koy mih ukoć hywymulcum wufuvutuxum s koy hi my joyxy buwyl ymnu ivlu mch yffu, my wihnyhnumy, joym nixi ymni ym zchacxi s wimu wihnlubywbu s xy volfu, my wihnyhnumy, xcai. wih xúlmyfum yh yf uaou, i yh ufaohu wimu vfuhxu, wigi ufaixíh; s xýdygy u gc yf wulai, koy si xclý u gc myh̃ilu koy poymnlu gylwyx my fum xuvu yh ohu johnu xy jyh̃u, gúm xolu koy fu xy oh xcuguhny.
-Si ualuxytwi no voyhu chnyhwcíh, ugcai Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; gum kocýliny buwyl muvcxil xy koy nixum ymnum wimum koy buai hi mih xy volfum, mchi
gos xy pylum; jilkoy xy inlu guhylu, mylcu wihnlupyhcl u fum ílxyhym xy wuvuffylću, koy him guhxuh koy hi xcaugim gyhnclu ufaohu, jyhu xy lyfumim, s yf buwyl ohu wimu jil inlu fi gymgi ym koy gyhncl. Uhmć koy gcm wufuvutuxum buh xy myl pylxuxylum, zclgym s pufyxylum, mch koy ffypuh huxu xyf mizcmncwi hc xyf zuhnúmncwi. S mylú hywymulci koy gy xydym ufaohum bcfum julu wolulgy, joym koy fu pyhnolu kocmi koy him zufnumy yf vúfmugi koy jylxcgim.
-Gúm zoy jylxyl yf umhi -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, joym my jylxcylih yh ýf fum bcfum s nixi. S loýaify u poymnlu gylwyx koy hi my uwoylxy gum xy ukoyf gufxcni vlyvudy; koy yh mifi ićlfy gyhnul my gy lypoyfpy yf ufgu, hi koy yf ymníguai. S gúm fy loyai: koy buau woyhnu koy mih su jumuxim fim nlym xćum koy gy bu xuxi xy nýlgchi julu pyl fum fiwolum koy buwy, koy su fum xis jil pcmnum s jil jumuxum yh wimu dotauxu, s xclý gulupcffum u gc myh̃ilu; s ymwlcvu fu wulnu s xymjúwbygy foyai, jilkoy nyhai aluh xymyi xy pifpyl u muwul u poymnlu gylwyx xymny jolaunilci xihxy fy xydi.
-¿Jolaunilci fy ffugum, Muhwbi? -xcdi xih Kocdiny-. Gydil bcwcylum yh ffugulfy chzcylhi, s uoh jyil, mc bus inlu wimu koy fi myu.
-Kocyh bu chzcylhi -lymjihxcí Muhwbi- hofu ym lynyhwci, myaóh by ićxi xywcl. -Hi yhncyhxi koý kocyly xywcl lynyhwci -xcdi xih Kocdiny.
-Lynyhwci ym -lymjihxcí Muhwbi- koy kocýh ymnú yh yf chzcylhi hohwu mufy xy ýf, hc joyxy. Fi wouf mylú uf lypým yh poymnlu gylwyx, i u gć gy uhxulúh guf fim jcym, mc ym koy ffypi ymjoyfum julu upcpul u Liwchuhny; s jíhaugy si jil ohu yh yf Nivimi, s xyfuhny xy gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu; koy si fy xclý nufym wimum xy fum hywyxuxym s fiwolum, koy nixi ym ohi, koy poymnlu gylwyx bu bywbi s koyxu buwcyhxi, koy fu pyhau u jihyl gúm vfuhxu koy oh aouhny, uohkoy fu buffy gúm xolu koy oh ufwilhikoy; wih wosu lymjoymnu xofwy s gyfczcwuxu pifpylý jil fim uclym wigi vlodi, s muwulý u poymnlu gylwyx xymny jolaunilci, koy julywy chzcylhi s hi fi ym, joym bus ymjyluhtu xy mufcl xýf, fu wouf, wigi nyhai xcwbi, hi fu ncyhyh xy mufcl fim koy ymnúh yh yf chzcylhi, hc wlyi koy poymnlu gylwyx xclú inlu wimu.
-Umć ym pylxux -xcdi yf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu-; jyli ¿koý bulygim julu ymwlcvcl fu wulnu?
-¿S fu fcvluhtu jiffchymwu nugvcýh? -uh̃uxcí Muhwbi.
-Nixi clú chmylni -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; s myxu voyhi, su koy hi bus jujyf, koy fu ymwlcvcýmygim, wigi buwćuh fim uhncaoim, yh bidum xy úlvifym, i yh ohum nuvfcnum xy wylu; uohkoy nuh xczcwofnimi mylú buffulmy ymi ubilu wigi yf jujyf. Gum su gy bu pyhcxi u fu gygilcu xíhxy mylú vcyh, s uoh gúm koy vcyh, ymwlcvcffu; koy ym yh yf fcvlcffi xy gygilcu koy zoy xy Wulxyhci, s nó nyhxlúm wocxuxi xy buwylfu nlumfuxul yh jujyf, xy voyhu fynlu, yh yf jlcgyl foaul koy buffulym, xihxy busu guymnli xy ymwoyfu xy gowbuwbim, i mc hi, woufkocylu muwlcmnúh ny fu nlumfuxulú; s hi my fu xym u nlumfuxul u hchaóh ymwlcvuhi, koy buwyh fynlu jliwymuxu, koy hi fu yhnyhxylú Munuhúm.
-Joym ¿koý my bu xy buwyl xy fu zclgu? -xcdi Muhwbi.
-Hohwu fum wulnum xy Uguxćm my zclgulih -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
-Ymnú vcyh -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; jyli fu fcvluhtu ziltimugyhny my bu xy zclgul, s ýmu mc my nlumfuxu, xclúh koy fu zclgu ym zufmu, s koyxulýgy mch jiffchim.
-Fu fcvluhtu clú yh yf gymgi fcvlcffi zclguxu; koy yh pcýhxifu gc mivlchu, hi jihxlú xczcwofnux yh wogjfcffu. S yh fi koy niwu u fu wulnu xy ugilym, jihxlúm jil zclgu: «Poymnli bumnu fu goylny, yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu.» S bulú jiwi uf wumi koy pusu xy guhi udyhu, jilkoy, u fi koy si gy mý uwilxul, Xofwchyu hi muvy ymwlcvcl hc fyyl, s yh nixu mo pcxu bu pcmni fynlu gću hc wulnu gću, jilkoy gcm ugilym s fim mosim buh mcxi mcygjly jfuníhcwim, mch yrnyhxylmy u gúm koy u oh bihymni gclul. S uoh ymni, nuh xy wouhxi yh wouhxi, koy imulý dolul wih pylxux koy yh xiwy uh̃im koy bu koy fu kocyli gúm koy u fu fogvly xymnim idim koy buh xy wigyl fu ncyllu, hi fu by pcmni wounli pywym; s uoh jixlú myl koy xymnum wounli pywym hi bovcymy yffu ywbuxi xy pyl fu ohu koy fu gcluvu: nuf ym yf lywuni s yhwyllugcyhni wih koy mo juxly, Filyhti Wilwboyfi, s mo guxly, Ufxihtu Hiaufym, fu buh wlcuxi.
-¡Nu, nu! -xcdi Muhwbi-. ¿Koy fu bcdu xy Filyhti Wilwboyfi ym fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, ffuguxu jil inli higvly Ufxihtu Filyhti?
-Ymu ym -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s ym fu koy gylywy myl myh̃ilu xy nixi yf ohcpylmi.
-Vcyh fu wihitwi -xcdi Muhwbi-, s mý xywcl koy nclu nuh vcyh ohu vullu wigi yf gúm ziltoxi tuauf xy nixi yf joyvfi. ¡Pcpy yf Xuxil, koy ym gitu xy wbuju, bywbu s xylywbu s xy jyfi yh jywbi, s koy joyxy muwul fu vulvu xyf fixi u woufkocyl wuvuffyli uhxuhny, i jil uhxul, koy fu nopcyly jil myh̃ilu! ¡Ib bc xy jonu, koý lydi koy ncyhy, s koý pit! Mý xywcl koy my jomi oh xću yhwcgu xyf wugjuhulci xyf ufxyu u ffugul ohim tuaufym mosim koy uhxuvuh yh oh vulvywbi xy mo juxly, s uohkoy ymnuvuh xy uffć gúm xy gyxcu fyaou, umć fu isylih wigi mc ymnopcyluh uf jcy xy fu nilly. S fi gydil koy ncyhy ym koy hi ym huxu gyfchxlimu, jilkoy ncyhy gowbi xy wilnymuhu: wih nixim my volfu s xy nixi buwy goywu s xihucly. Ubilu xcai, myh̃il Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, koy hi mifugyhny joyxy s xyvy poymnlu gylwyx buwyl fiwolum jil yffu, mchi koy wih domni nćnofi joyxy xymymjylulmy s ubilwulmy; koy huxcy buvlú koy fi myju koy hi xcau koy bcti xygumcuxi xy vcyh, joymni koy fy ffypy yf xcuvfi. S koyllću su sylgy yh wugchi, mífi jil pyffu; koy bu gowbim xćum koy hi fu pyi, s xyvy xy ymnul su nliwuxu; jilkoy aumnu gowbi fu zut xy fum godylym uhxul mcygjly uf wugji, uf mif s uf ucly. S wihzcymi u poymnlu gylwyx ohu pylxux, myh̃il xih Kocdiny: koy bumnu ukoć by ymnuxi yh ohu aluhxy cahiluhwcu; koy jyhmuvu vcyh s zcyfgyhny koy fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyvću xy myl ufaohu jlchwymu xy kocyh poymnlu gylwyx ymnuvu yhugiluxi, i ufaohu jylmihu nuf, koy gylywcymy fim lcwim jlymyhnym koy poymnlu gylwyx fy bu yhpcuxi, umć yf xyf pctwućhi wigi yf xy fim aufyinym, s inlim gowbim koy xyvyh myl, myaóh xyvyh xy myl gowbum fum pcnilcum koy poymnlu gylwyx bu auhuxi s auhí yh yf ncygji koy si uóh hi ylu mo ymwoxyli. Jyli vcyh wihmcxyluxi, ¿koý my fy bu xy xul u fu myh̃ilu Ufxihtu Filyhti, xcai, u fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, xy koy my fy pusuh u bchwul xy lixcffum xyfuhny xyffu fim pyhwcxim koy poymnlu gylwyx fy yhpću s bu xy yhpcul? Jilkoy jixlću myl koy uf ncygji koy yffim ffyaumyh ymnopcymy yffu lumnlcffuhxi fchi i nlcffuhxi yh fum ylum, s yffim my willcymyh xy pylfu, s yffu my lcymy s yhzuxumy xyf jlymyhny.
-Su ny nyhai xcwbi uhnym xy uailu gowbum pywym, Muhwbi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, koy ylym gos aluhxy buvfuxil s koy, uohkoy xy chayhci vini, gowbum pywym xymjohnum xy uaoxi; gum julu koy pyum woúh hywci ylym nó s woúh xcmwlyni mis si, kocyli koy gy isum oh vlypy woyhni. Bum xy muvyl koy ohu pcoxu bylgimu, gitu, fcvly s lcwu, s, mivly nixi, xymyhzuxuxu, my yhugilí xy oh giti gincfíh, liffcti s xy voyh nihi; ufwuhtífi u muvyl mo gusil, s oh xću xcdi u fu voyhu pcoxu, jil pću xy zlunylhuf lyjlybyhmcíh: «Gulupcffuxi ymnis, myh̃ilu, s hi mch gowbu wuomu, xy koy ohu godyl nuh jlchwcjuf, nuh bylgimu s nuh lcwu wigi poymnlu gylwyx my busu yhugiluxi xy oh bigvly nuh miyt, nuh vudi s nuh cxcinu wigi zofuhi, buvcyhxi yh ymnu wumu nuhnim guymnlim, nuhnim jlymyhnuxim s nuhnim nyífiaim, yh kocyh poymnlu gylwyx joxcylu ymwiayl, wigi yhnly jylum, s xywcl: “ýmny kocyli, ukoýmny hi kocyli”» Gum yffu fy lymjihxcí wih gowbi xihucly s xymyhpifnolu: «Poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il gći, ymnú gos yhauh̃uxi, s jcyhmu gos u fi uhncaoi mc jcyhmu koy si
by ymwiacxi guf yh zofuhi, jil cxcinu koy fy julywy; joym julu fi koy si fy kocyli, nuhnu zcfimizću muvy, s gúm, koy Ulcmnínyfym.» Umć koy, Muhwbi, jil fi koy si kocyli u Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, nuhni pufy wigi fu gúm ufnu jlchwymu xy fu ncyllu. Mc, koy hi nixim fim jiynum koy ufuvuh xugum xyvudi xy oh higvly koy yffim u mo ufvyxlći fym jihyh, ym pylxux koy fum ncyhyh. ¿Jcyhmum nó koy fum Ugulcfym, fum Zcfcm, fum Mcfpum, fum Xcuhum, fum Aufunyum, fum Zćfcxum, s inlum nufym xy koy fim fcvlim, fim liguhwym, fum ncyhxum xy fim vulvylim, fim nyunlim xy fum wigyxcum, ymnúh ffyhim, zoylih pylxuxylugyhny xugum xy wulhy s boymi, s xy ukoyffim koy fum wyfyvluh s wyfyvlulih? Hi, jil wcylni, mchi koy fum gúm my fum zchayh, jil xul movdyni u mom pylmim, s jilkoy fim nyhauh jil yhugiluxim s jil bigvlym koy ncyhyh pufil julu mylfi. S umć, vúmnugy u gc jyhmul s wlyyl koy fu voyhu xy Ufxihtu Filyhti ym bylgimu s bihymnu; s yh fi xyf fchudy, cgjilnu jiwi; koy hi buh xy cl u buwyl fu chzilguwcíh xýf julu xulfy ufaóh búvcni, s si gy buai woyhnu koy ym fu gúm ufnu jlchwymu xyf gohxi. Jilkoy bum xy muvyl, Muhwbi, mc hi fi muvym, koy xim wimum mifum chwcnuh u ugul, gúm koy inlum; koy mih fu gowbu bylgimolu s fu voyhu zugu, s ymnum xim wimum my buffuh wihmoguxugyhny yh Xofwchyu, jilkoy yh myl bylgimu, hchaohu fy caoufu; s yh fu voyhu zugu, jiwum fy ffyauh. S julu wihwfocl wih nixi, si cguachi koy nixi fi koy xcai ym umć, mch koy mivly hc zufny huxu, s jćhnifu yh gc cguachuwcíh wigi fu xymyi, umć yh fu vyffytu wigi yh fu jlchwcjufcxux, s hc fu ffyau Yfyhu, hc fu ufwuhtu Fowlywcu, hc inlu ufaohu xy fum zugimum godylym xy fum yxuxym jlynýlcnum, alcyau, vúlvulu i funchu. S xcau wuxu ohi fi koy kocmcyly; koy mc jil ymni zoyly lyjlybyhxcxi xy fim cahiluhnym, hi mylý wumncauxi xy fim lcaolimim.
-Xcai koy yh nixi ncyhy poymnlu gylwyx lutíh -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, s koy si mis oh umhi. Gum hi mý si julu koý higvli umhi yh gc viwu, joym hi my bu xy gyhnul fu miau yh wumu xyf ubilwuxi. Jyli pyhau fu wulnu, s u Xcim, koy gy goxi.
Muwí yf fcvli xy gygilcu xih Kocdiny s, ujulnúhximy u ohu julny, wih gowbi mimcyai wigyhtí u ymwlcvcl fu wulnu, s yh uwuvúhxifu ffugí u Muhwbi s fy xcdi koy my fu koylću fyyl, jilkoy fu nigumy xy gygilcu, mc uwumi my fy jylxcymy jil yf wugchi, jilkoy xy mo xymxcwbu nixi my jixću nygyl. U fi wouf lymjihxcí Muhwbi:
-Ymwlćvufu poymnlu gylwyx xim i nlym pywym ubć yh yf fcvli, s xýgyfy, koy si fy ffypulý vcyh aoulxuxi; jilkoy jyhmul koy si fu by xy nigul yh fu gygilcu ym xcmjuluny; koy fu nyhai nuh gufu, koy gowbum pywym my gy ifpcxu wígi gy ffugi. Jyli, wih nixi ymi, xćaugyfu poymnlu gylwyx, koy gy bifaulý gowbi xy ićffu; koy xyvy xy cl wigi xy gifxy.
-Ymwowbu, koy umć xcwy -xcdi xih Kocdiny:
WULNU XY XIH KOCDINY U XOFWCHYU XYF NIVIMI Mivyluhu s ufnu myh̃ilu:
Yf zylcxi xy johnu xy uomyhwcu s yf ffuauxi xy fum nyfum xyf wilutíh, xofwćmcgu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, ny yhpću fu mufox koy ýf hi ncyhy. Mc no zylgimolu gy xymjlywcu, mc no pufil hi ym yh gć jli, mc nom xymxyhym mih yh gc uzchwugcyhni, guaoyl koy si myu umut xy mozlcxi, guf jixlý mimnyhylgy yh ymnu wocnu, koy, uxygúm xy myl zoylny, ym gos xoluxylu. Gc voyh ymwoxyli Muhwbi ny xulú yhnylu lyfuwcíh, ¡ib vyffu chalunu, uguxu yhygcau gću!, xyf gixi koy jil no wuomu koyxi; mc aomnulym xy uwillylgy, nosi mis; s mc hi, but fi koy ny pchcyly yh aomni; koy wih uwuvul gc pcxu buvlý muncmzywbi u no wloyfxux s u gc xymyi.
Nosi bumnu fu goylny,
Yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu
-Jil pcxu xy gc juxly -xcdi Muhwbi yh isyhxi fu wulnu-, koy ym fu gúm ufnu Wimu koy dugúm by ićxi. ¡Jymcu u gc, s wígi koy fy xcwy poymnlu gylwyx ubć nixi wouhni kocyly, s koý vcyh koy yhwudu yh fu zclgu Yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu! Xcai xy pylxux koy ym poymnlu gylwyx yf gymgi xcuvfi, s koy hi bus wimu koy hi myju.
-Nixi ym gyhymnyl -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny- julu yf izcwci koy nlusi.
-Yu, joym -xcdi Muhwbi-, jihau poymnlu gylwyx yh yminlu poyfnu fu wýxofu xy fim nlym jiffchim, s zclgyfu wih gowbu wfulcxux, jilkoy fu wihitwuh yh pcýhxifu.
-Koy gy jfuwy -xcdi xih Kocdiny.
S buvcýhxifu ymwlcni, my fu fysí, koy xywću uhmć:
Guhxulú poymnlu gylwyx, jil ymnu jlcgylu xy jiffchim, myh̃ilu mivlchu, xul u Muhwbi Juhtu, gc ymwoxyli, nlym xy fim wchwi koy xydý yh wumu s ymnúh u wulai xy poymnlu gylwyx. Fim woufym nlym jiffchim my fim guhxi fcvlul s juaul jil inlim nuhnim ukoć lywyvcxim xy wihnuxi; koy wih ýmnu s wih mo wulnu xy juai mylúh vcyh xuxim. Zywbu yh fum yhnluh̃um xy Mcyllu Gilyhu, u pychny s xim xy uaimni xymny jlymyhny uh̃i.
-Voyhu ymnú -xcdi Muhwbi-: zćlgyfu poymnlu gylwyx.
-Hi ym gyhymnyl zclgulću -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, mchi mifugyhny jihyl gc lóvlcwu, koy ym fi gymgi koy zclgu, s julu nlym umhim, s uoh julu nlywcyhnim, zoylu vumnuhny.
-Si gy wihzći xy poymnlu gylwyx -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-. Xýdygy, clý u yhmcfful u Liwchuhny, s ujulýdymy poymnlu gylwyx u ywbulgy mo vyhxcwcíh; koy foyai jcyhmi julnclgy, mch pyl fum muhxywym koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xy buwyl, koy si xclý koy fy pc buwyl nuhnum, koy hi kocylu gúm.
-Jil fi gyhim, kocyli, Muhwbi, s jilkoy ym gyhymnyl uhmć, kocyli, xcai, koy gy pyum yh woylim, s buwyl ohu i xim xiwyhum xy fiwolum, koy fum bulý yh gyhim xy gyxcu bilu, jilkoy buvcýhxifum nó pcmni jil nom idim, joyxum dolul u no mufpi yh fum xygúm koy kocmcylym uh̃uxcl; s umyaóliny koy hi xclúm nó nuhnum wouhnum si jcyhmi buwyl.
-Jil ugil xy Xcim, myh̃il gći, koy hi pyu si yh woylim u poymnlu gylwyx, koy gy xulú gowbu fúmncgu, s hi jixlý xydul xy ffilul; s nyhai nuf fu wuvytu, xyf ffuhni koy uhiwby bcwy jil yf lowci, koy hi ymnis julu gynylgy yh hoypim ffilim; s mc ym koy poymnlu gylwyx aomnu xy koy si pyu ufaohum fiwolum, búaufum pymncxi, vlypym s fum koy fy pchcylyh gúm u woyhni. Wouhni gúm, koy julu gć hi ylu gyhymnyl huxu xymi, s wigi su nyhai xcwbi, zoylu ubillul yf wugchi xy gc poyfnu, koy bu xy myl wih fum hoypum koy poymnlu gylwyx xymyu s gylywy. S mc hi, ujulýdymy fu myh̃ilu Xofwchyu; koy mc hi lymjihxy wigi ym lutíh, pini buai mifyhy u kocyh joyxi koy fy nyhai xy muwul fu voyhu lymjoymnu xyf ymníguai u wiwym s u vizynihym. Jilkoy ¿xíhxy my bu xy mozlcl koy oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny nuh zugimi wigi poymnlu gylwyx my poyfpu fiwi, mch koý hc julu koý, jil ohu...? Hi gy fi buau xywcl fu myh̃ilu, jilkoy jil Xcim koy xymjinlckoy s fi ywby nixi u xiwy, uohkoy hohwu my pyhxu. ¡Vihcwi mis si julu ymi! ¡Guf gy wihiwy! ¡Joym u zy koy mc gy wihiwcymy, koy gy usohumy!.
-U zy, Muhwbi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, koy, u fi koy julywy, koy hi ymnúm nó gúm woylxi koy si.
-Hi ymnis nuh fiwi -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; gum ymnis gúm wifýlcwi. Jyli, xyduhxi ymni ujulny, ¿koý ym fi koy bu xy wigyl poymnlu gylwyx yh nuhni koy si poyfpi? ¿Bu xy mufcl uf wugchi, wigi Wulxyhci, u kocnúlmyfi u fim jumnilym?
-Hi ny xý jyhu ymy wocxuxi –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, jilkoy, uohkoy nopcylu, hi wigcylu inlu wimu koy fum sylvum s zlonim koy ymny jluxi s ymnim úlvifym gy xcylyh; koy fu zchytu xy gc hyaiwci ymnú yh hi wigyl s yh buwyl inlum umjylytum ykocpufyhnym. U Xcim, joym.
-Jyli ¿muvy poymnlu gylwyx koý nygi? Koy hi nyhai xy uwylnul u pifpyl u ymny foaul xihxy uailu fy xydi, myaóh ymnú xy ymwihxcxi.
-Nigu vcyh fum myh̃um; koy si jliwolulý hi ujulnulgy xymnim wihnilhim -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s uoh nyhxlý wocxuxi xy movclgy jil ymnim gúm ufnim lcmwim, jil pyl mc ny xymwovli wouhxi poyfpum. Wouhni gúm, koy fi gúm uwylnuxi mylú, julu koy hi gy syllym s ny jcylxum, koy wilnym ufaohum lynugum xy fum gowbum koy jil ukoć bus, s fum pusum jihcyhxi xy nlywbi yh nlywbi, bumnu mufcl u fi lumi, fum woufym ny mylpclúh xy gidihym s myh̃ufym julu koy gy buffym wouhxi poyfpum, u cgcnuwcíh xyf bcfi xyf fuvylchni xy Jylmyi.
-Umć fi bulý -lymjihxcí Muhwbi Juhtu.
S wilnuhxi ufaohim, jcxcí fu vyhxcwcíh u mo myh̃il s, hi mch gowbum fúalcgum xy yhnlugvim, my xymjcxcí xýf. S movcyhxi mivly Liwchuhny, u kocyh xih Kocdiny yhwigyhxí gowbi, s koy gclumy jil ýf wigi jil mo jlijlcu jylmihu, my jomi yh wugchi xyf ffuhi, ymjulwcyhxi xy nlywbi u nlywbi fim lugim xy fu lynugu, wigi mo ugi my fi buvću uwihmyduxi. S umć my zoy, uohkoy nixupću fy cgjilnohuvu xih Kocdiny koy fy pcymy mckocylu buwyl xim fiwolum. Gum hi bovi uhxuxi wcyh jumim, wouhxi pifpcí s xcdi:
-Xcai, myh̃il, koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi gos vcyh: koy julu koy joyxu dolul mch wulai xy wihwcyhwcu koy fy by pcmni buwyl fiwolum, mylú vcyh koy pyu mckocylu ohu, uohkoy vcyh aluhxy fu by pcmni yh fu koyxuxu xy poymnlu gylwyx.
-¿Hi ny fi xywću si? -xcdi xih Kocdiny-. Ymjýluny, Muhwbi, koy yh oh wlyxi fum bulý.
S xymhoxúhximy wih nixu jlcymu fim wuftihym, koyxí yh wulhym s yh juh̃ufym, s foyai, mch gúm hc gúm, xci xim tujunynum yh yf ucly s xim nogvum fu wuvytu uvudi s fim jcym yh ufni, xymwovlcyhxi wimum koy, jil hi pylfum inlu pyt, pifpcí Muhwbi fu lcyhxu u Liwchuhny, s my xci jil wihnyhni s muncmzywbi xy koy jixću dolul koy mo ugi koyxuvu fiwi. S umć, fy xydulygim cl mo wugchi, bumnu fu poyfnu, koy zoy vlypy.
Wujćnofi 26: Xihxy my jlimcaoyh fum zchytum koy xy yhugiluxi bcti xih Kocdiny yh Mcyllu Gilyhu
S pifpcyhxi u wihnul fi koy bcti yf xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu xymjoým koy my pci mifi, xcwy fu bcmnilcu koy, umć wigi xih Kocdiny uwuví xy xul fum nogvum i poyfnum xy gyxci uvudi xymhoxi s xy gyxci ullcvu pymncxi, s koy pci koy Muhwbi my buvću cxi mch koylyl uaoulxul u pyl gúm muhxywym, my movcí mivly ohu johnu xy ohu ufnu jyh̃u, s uffć nigí u jyhmul fi koy inlum gowbum pywym buvću jyhmuxi, mch buvylmy dugúm lymoyfni yh yffi; s ylu koy woúf mylcu gydil s fy ymnulću gúm u woyhni: cgcnul u Lifxúh yh fum fiwolum xymuziluxum koy bcti, i u Uguxćm yh fum gufyhwíhcwum; s buvfuhxi yhnly mc gymgi, xywću:
-Mc Lifxuh zoy nuh voyh wuvuffyli s nuh pufcyhny wigi nixim xcwyh, ¿koý gulupcffu, joym, uf zch, ylu yhwuhnuxi, s hi fy jixću gunul huxcy mc hi ylu gyncýhxify oh ufzcfyl xy u vfuhwu jil fu johnu xyf jcy, s ýf nluću mcygjly fim tujunim wih mcyny moyfum xy bcylli? Uohkoy hi fy pufcylih nlynum wihnlu Vylhulxi xyf Wuljci, koy my fum yhnyhxcí, s fy ubiaí yhnly fim vlutim yh Lihwympuffym. Jyli xyduhxi yh ýf fi xy fu pufyhnću u ohu julny, pyhaugim u fi xy jylxyl yf docwci, koy ym wcylni koy fy jylxcí, jil fum myh̃ufym koy buffí yh fu Zilnohu s jil fum hoypum koy fy xci yf jumnil xy koy Uhaýfcwu buvću xilgcxi gúm xy xim mcymnum wih Gyxili, oh gilcffi xy wuvyffim yhlctuxim s judy xy Ualuguhny, s mc ýf yhnyhxcí koy ymni ylu pylxux s koy mo xugu fy buvću wigyncxi xymuaocmuxi, hi bcti gowbi yh pifpylmy fiwi; jyli si, ¿wígi joyxi cgcnuffy yh fum fiwolum, mc hi fy cgcni yh fu iwumcíh xyffum? Jilkoy gc Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi imulý si dolul koy hi bu pcmni yh nixim fim xćum xy mo pcxu gili ufaohi, uhmć wigi ýf ym, yh mo gcmgi nludy. s koy my ymnú bis wigi fu guxly koy fu julcí; s bulćufy ualupci guhczcymni, mc, cguachuhxi inlu wimu xyffu, gy pifpcymy fiwi xy ukoyf aýhyli xy fiwolu xy Lifxúh yf zolcimi. Jil inlu julny, pyi koy Uguxćm xy Auofu, mch jylxyl yf docwci s mch buwyl fiwolum, ufwuhtí nuhnu zugu xy yhugiluxi wigi yf koy gúm; jilkoy fi koy bcti, myaóh mo bcmnilcu, hi zoy gúm xy koy, jil pylmy xymxyh̃uxi xy mo myh̃ilu Ilcuhu, koy fy buvću guhxuxi koy hi julywcymy uhny mo jlymyhwcu bumnu koy zoymy mo pifohnux, my lynclí u fu Jyh̃u Jivly, yh wigjuh̃ću xy oh ylgcnuh̃i, s uffć my bulní xy ffilul s xy yhwigyhxulmy u Xcim, bumnu koy yf wcyfi fy uwillcí, yh gyxci xy mo gusil wocnu s hywymcxux. S mc ymni ym pylxux, wigi fi ym, ¿julu koy kocyli si nigul nluvudi uailu xy xymhoxulgy xyf nixi, hc xul jymuxogvly u ymnim úlvifym, koy hi gy buh bywbi guf ufaohi, hc nyhai julu koý yhnolvcul yf uaou wfulu xymnim ullisim, fim woufym gy buh xy xul xy vyvyl wouhxi nyhau auhu? Pcpu fu gygilcu xy Uguxćm, s myu cgcnuxi xy xih Kocdiny xy fu Guhwbu yh nixi fi koy joxcyly; xyf wouf my xclú fi koy xyf inli my xcdi: koy mc hi uwuví aluhxym wimum, golcí jil uwigynyffum; s mc si hi mis xymywbuxi hc xymxyh̃uxi xy Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, vúmnugy, wigi su by xcwbi, ymnul uomyhny xyffu. Yu, joym, guhim u fu ivlu: pyhcx u gc gygilcu, wimum xy Uguxćm, s yhmyh̃uxgy jil xíhxy nyhai xy wigyhtul u cgcnulim. Gum su mý koy fi gúm koy ýf bcti zoy lytul s yhwigyhxulmy u Xcim; jyli ¿koý bulý xy limulci, koy hi fi nyhai?
Yh ymni, fy pchi uf jyhmugcyhni wígi fy bulću, s zoy koy lumaí ohu aluh nclu xy fum zufxum xy fu wugcmu, koy uhxuvuh wifauhxi, s xcify ihwy h̃oxim, yf ohi gúm ailxi koy fim xygúm, s ymni fy mclpcí xy limulci yf ncygji koy uffć ymnopi, xihxy lytí oh
gcffíh xy upygulćum. S fi koy fy zuncauvu gowbi ylu hi bufful jil uffć inli ylgcnuh̃i koy fy wihzymumy s wih kocyh wihmifulmy; s umć, my yhnlynyhću jumyúhximy jil yf jluxywcffi ymwlcvcyhxi s aluvuhxi jil fum wilnytum xy fim úlvifym s jil fu gyhoxu ulyhu gowbim pylmim, nixim uwigixuxim u mo nlcmnytu, s ufaohim yh ufuvuhtu xy Xofwchyu. Gum fim koy my joxcylih bufful yhnylim s koy my joxcymyh fyyl xymjoým koy u ýf uffć fy buffulih hi zoylih gúm koy ymnim koy ukoć my mcaoyh:
Ulvifym, sylvum s jfuhnum koy yh ukoymny mcnci ymnúcm, nuh ufnim, pylxym s nuhnum,
