Ffyaoý uf foaul xihxy ylu yhpcuxi; xc fum wulnum uf bylguhi xy xih Zylhuhxi; zoc vcyh lywyvcxi, jyli hi vcyh xymjuwbuxi, jilkoy gy guhxí uaoulxul, vcyh u gc xcmaomni, iwbi xćum, s yh julny xihxy yf xokoy mo juxly hi gy pcymy, jilkoy mo bylguhi fy ymwlcvću koy fy yhpcumy wcylni xchyli mch mo muvcxolću; s nixi zoy chpyhwcíh xyf zufmi xih Zylhuhxi, joym hi fy zufnuvuh u mo bylguhi xchylim julu xymjuwbulgy foyai. Ilxyh s guhxuni zoy ýmny koy gy jomi yh wihxcwcíh xy hi ivyxywylfy, jil julywylgy cgjimcvfy momnyhnul nuhnim xćum fu pcxu yh yf uomyhwcu xy Fomwchxu, s gum buvcýhxifu xyduxi wih fu nlcmnytu koy im by wihnuxi; jyli, wih nixi ymni, ivyxywć, wigi voyh wlcuxi, uohkoy pyću koy buvću xy myl u wimnu xy gc mufox. Jyli u fim wounli xćum koy uffć ffyaoý, ffyaí oh bigvly yh gc vomwu wih ohu wulnu, koy gy xci, koy yh yf mivlymwlcni wihiwć myl xy Fomwchxu, jilkoy fu fynlu xýf
ylu mosu. Uvlcfu, nygylimi s wih mivlymufni, wlysyhxi koy wimu aluhxy xyvću xy myl fu koy fu buvću gipcxi u ymwlcvclgy ymnuhxi uomyhny, joym jlymyhny jiwum pywym fi buwcu. Jlyaohnýfy uf bigvly, uhnym xy fyylfu, kocýh my fu buvću xuxi s yf ncygji koy buvću nulxuxi yh yf wugchi; xćdigy koy uwumi jumuhxi jil ohu wuffy xy fu wcoxux u fu bilu xy gyxcixću, ohu myh̃ilu gos bylgimu fy ffugí xymxy ohu pyhnuhu, fim idim ffyhim xy fúalcgum, s koy wih gowbu jlcymu fy xcdi: «-Bylguhi, mc micm wlcmncuhi, wigi julywýcm, jil ugil xy Xcim im loyai koy yhwugchýcm foyai foyai ymnu wulnu uf foaul s u fu jylmihu koy xcwy yf mivlymwlcni, koy nixi ym vcyh wihiwcxi, s yh yffi bulýcm oh aluh mylpcwci u hoymnli Myh̃il; s julu koy hi im zufny wigixcxux xy jixylfi buwyl, nigux fi koy pu yh ymny juh̃oyfi.» «-S xcwcyhxi ymni, gy ullidi jil fu pyhnuhu oh juh̃oyfi, xihxy pyhćuh unuxim wcyh lyufym s ymnu milncdu xy ili koy ukoć nlucai, wih ymu wulnu koy im by xuxi. S foyai, mch uaoulxul lymjoymnu gću my kocní xy fu pyhnuhu; uohkoy jlcgyli pci wígi si nigý fu wulnu s yf juh̃oyfi s, jil myh̃um, fy xcdy koy bulću fi koy gy guhxuvu. S umć, pcýhxigy nuh vcyh juauxi xyf nluvudi koy jixću nigul yh nluýlimfu, s wihiwcyhxi jil yf mivlymwlcni koy ýluxym pim u kocyh my yhpcuvu, jilkoy si, myh̃il, im wihitwi gos vcyh, s ivfcauxi umcgymgi xy fum fúalcgum xy ukoyffu bylgimu myh̃ilu, xynylgchý xy hi zculgy xy inlu jylmihu, mchi pyhcl si gymgi u xúlimfu, s yh xcyt s mycm bilum koy bu koy my gy xci, by bywbi yf wugchi, koy muvýcm koy ym xy xcyt s iwbi fyaoum.»
Yh nuhni koy yf ualuxywcxi s hoypi willyi ymni gy xywću, ymnuvu si wifauxi xy mom jufuvlum, nygvfúhxigy fum jcylhum, xy guhylu koy ujyhum jixću mimnyhylgy. Yh yzyni, uvlć fu wulnu s pc koy wihnyhću ymnum lunihym:
Fu jufuvlu koy xih Zylhuhxi im xci xy buvful u poymnli juxly julu koy buvfumy uf gći fu bu wogjfcxi gúm yh mo aomni koy yh poymnli jlipywbi. Muvyx, myh̃il, koy ýf gy bu jyxcxi jil ymjimu, s gc juxly, ffypuxi xy fu pyhnudu koy ýf jcyhmu koy xih Zylhuhxi im buwy, bu pyhcxi yh fi koy kocyly, wih nuhnum pylum, koy xy ukoć u xim xćum my bu xy buwyl yf xymjimilci; nuh mywlyni s nuh u mifum, koy mifi buh xy myl nymncaim fim wcyfim s ufaohu ayhny xy wumu. Wouf si koyxi, cguachufxi; mc im wogjfy pyhcl, pyfxi; s mc im kocyli vcyh i hi, yf mowymi xymny hyaiwci im fu xulú u yhnyhxyl. U Xcim jfyau koy ýmnu ffyaoy u poymnlum guhim uhnym koy fu gću my pyu yh wihxcwcíh xy dohnulmy wih fu xy kocyh guf muvy aoulxul fu zy koy jligyny.
Ymnum, yh mogu, zoylih fum lutihym koy fu wuxu wihnyhću, s fum koy gy bcwcylih jihyl foyai yh wugchi, mch ymjylul inlu lymjoymnu hc inlim xchylim; koy vcyh wfuli wihiwć yhnihwym koy hi fu wigjlu xy fim wuvuffim, mchi fu xy mo aomni, buvću gipcxi u xih Zylhuhxi u yhpculgy u mo bylguhi. Yf yhidi koy wihnlu xih Zyguhxi wihwyvć, dohni wih yf nygil xy jylxyl fu jlyhxu koy wih nuhnim uh̃im xy mylpcwcim s xymyim nyhću aluhdyuxu, gy jomcylih ufum, joym, wumc wigi yh poyfi, inli xću gy jomy yh gc foaul, uf johni s bilu koy wihpyhću julu cl u buvful u Fomwchxu. Yhnlý mywlyni s xydý ohu gofu yh koy pyhcu yh wumu xyf voyh bigvly koy gy buvću ffypuxi fu wuxu, s kocmi fu moylny koy yhnihwym fu nopcymy nuh voyhu, koy buffý u Fomwchxu joymnu u fu lydu, nymncai xy hoymnlim ugilym. Wihiwcígy Fomwchxu foyai, s wihiwćfu si; gum hi wigi xyvću yffu wihiwylgy, s si wihiwylfu. Jyli ¿kocýh bus yh yf gohxi koy my joyxu ufuvul koy bu jyhynluxi s muvcxi yf wihzomi jyhmugcyhni s wihxcwcíh goxuvfy xy ohu godyl? Hchaohi, jil wcylni. Xcai, joym, koy umć wigi Fomwchxu gy pci, gy xcdi:
-Wulxyhci, xy vixu ymnis pymncxu; su gy ymnúh uaoulxuhxi yh fu mufu xih Zyguhxi yf nlucxil s gc juxly yf wixcwcimi, wih inlim nymncaim, koy uhnym fi mylúh xy gc goylny koy xy gc xymjimilci. Hi ny nolvym, ugcai, mchi jliwolu buffuxy jlymyhny u ymny muwlczcwci, yf wouf mc hi joxcymy myl ymnilvuxi xy gcm lutihym, ohu xuau ffypi ymwihxcxu koy jixlú ymnilvul gúm xynylgchuxum zoyltum, xuhxi zch u gc pcxu s jlchwcjci u koy wihitwum fu pifohnux koy ny by nyhcxi s nyhai.
Si fy lymjihxć nolvuxi s ujlcymu, nygylimi hi gy zufnumy foaul julu lymjihxylfu:
-Buauh, myh̃ilu, nom ivlum pylxuxylum nom jufuvlum; koy mc nó ffypum xuau julu uwlyxcnulny, ukoć ffypi si ymjuxu julu xyzyhxylny wih yffu, i julu gunulgy mc fu moylny him zoyly wihnlulcu.
Hi wlyi koy joxi ićl nixum ymnum lutihym, jilkoy myhnć koy fu ffuguvuh ujlcymu, jilkoy yf xymjimuxi uaoulxuvu. Wyllímy wih ymni fu hiwby xy gc nlcmnytu; jómimygy yf mif xy gc ufyalću; koyxý mch fot yh fim idim s mch xcmwolmi yh yf yhnyhxcgcyhni. Hi uwyxuvu u yhnlul yh mo wumu, hc jixću gipylgy u julny ufaohu; jyli wihmcxyluhxi woúhni cgjilnuvu gc jlymyhwcu julu fi koy mowyxyl joxcymy yh ukoyf wumi, gy uhcgý fi gúm koy joxy s yhnlý yh mo wumu; s wigi su muvcu gos vcyh nixum mom yhnluxum s mufcxum, s gúm wih yf ufvilini koy xy mywlyni yh yffu uhxuvu, huxcy gy ywbí xy pyl; umć koy, mch myl pcmni, nopy foaul xy jihylgy yh yf boywi koy buwcu ohu pyhnuhu xy fu gymgu mufu, koy wih fum johnum s lygunym xy fim xim nujcwym my wovlću, jil yhnly fum woufym jixću si pyl, mch myl pcmni, nixi wouhni yh fu mufu my buwcu. ¿Kocýh joxcylu xywcl ubilu fim mivlymufnim koy gy xci yf wilutíh gcyhnlum uffć ymnopy, fim jyhmugcyhnim koy gy iwollcylih, fum wihmcxyluwcihym koy bcwy, koy zoylih nuhnum s nufym, koy hc my joyxyh xywcl, hc uoh ym vcyh koy my xcauh? Vumnu koy myjúcm koy yf xymjimuxi yhnlí yh fu mufu, mch inli uxilhi koy fim gymgim pymncxim ilxchulcim koy mifću. Nluću jil juxlchi u oh jlcgi bylguhi xy Fomwchxu, s yh nixu fu mufu hi buvću jylmihu xy zoylu, mchi fim wlcuxim xy wumu. Xy uffć u oh jiwi mufcí xy ohu lywugulu Fomwchxu, uwigjuh̃uxu xy mo guxly s xy xim xihwyffum mosum, nuh vcyh uxylytuxu s wigjoymnu wigi mo wufcxux s bylgimolu gylywćuh, s wigi kocyh ylu fu jylzywwcíh xy fu aufu s vctullću wilnymuhu. Hi gy xci foaul gc momjyhmcíh s ullivugcyhni julu koy gclumy s hinumy yh julncwoful fi koy nluću pymncxi: mífi joxy uxpylncl u fum wifilym, koy yluh yhwulhuxi s vfuhwi, s yh fum pcmfogvlym koy fum jcyxlum s disum xyf niwuxi s xy nixi yf pymncxi buwćuh, u nixi fi wouf my upyhnuduvu fu vyffytu mchaoful xy mom bylgimim s lovcim wuvyffim, nufym, koy, yh wigjynyhwcu xy fum jlywcimum jcyxlum s xy fum fowym xy wounli buwbum koy yh fu mufu ymnuvuh, fu mosu wih gúm lymjfuhxil u fim idim izlywćuh.
¡Ib gygilcu, yhygcau gixuf xy gc xymwuhmi! ¿Xy koý mclpy lyjlymyhnulgy ubilu fu chwigjuluvfy vyffytu xy ukoyffu uxiluxu yhygcau gću? ¿Hi mylú gydil, wloyf gygilcu, koy gy uwoylxym s lyjlymyhnym fi koy yhnihwym bcti, julu koy, gipcxi xy nuh guhczcymni ualupci jliwoly, su koy hi fu pyhauhtu, u fi gyhim, jylxyl fu pcxu? Hi im wuhmýcm, myh̃ilym, xy ićl ymnum xcalymcihym koy buai; koy hi ym gc jyhu xy ukoyffum koy joyxuh hc xyvuh wihnulmy mowchnugyhny s xy jumi, joym wuxu wclwohmnuhwcu mosu gy julywy u gć koy ym xcahu xy oh fulai xcmwolmi.
U ymni fy lymjihxcí yf wolu koy, hi mífi hi my wuhmuvuh xy ićlfy. mchi koy fym xuvu gowbi aomni fum gyhoxyhwcum koy wihnuvu, jil myl nufym, koy gylywćuh hi jumulmy yh mcfyhwci, s fu gymgu unyhwcíh koy fi jlchwcjuf xyf woyhni.
-Xcai, joym -jlimcaocí Wulxyhci-, koy ymnuhxi nixim yh fu mufu, yhnlí yf wolu xy fu jullikocu s, niguhxi u fim xim jil fu guhi julu buwyl fi koy yh nuf uwni my lykocyly, uf xywcl: «¿Koylýcm, myh̃ilu Fomwchxu, uf myh̃il xih Zylhuhxi, koy ymnú jlymyhny, jil poymnli fyacncgi ymjimi, wigi fi guhxu fu Muhnu Guxly Cafymcu?», si mukoý nixu fu wuvytu s woyffi xy yhnly fim nujcwym, s wih unyhnćmcgim ićxim s ufgu nolvuxu gy jomy u ymwowbul fi koy Fomwchxu lymjihxću, ymjyluhxi xy mo lymjoymnu fu myhnyhwcu xy gc goylny, i fu wihzclguwcíh xy gc pcxu. ¡Ib, kocýh my unlypcylu u mufcl yhnihwym, xcwcyhxi u piwym: «¡Ub, Fomwchxu, Fomwchxu! Gclu fi koy buwym; wihmcxylu fi koy gy xyvym; gclu koy ylym gću, s koy hi joyxym myl xy inli! Uxpcylny koy yf xywcl nó mc s yf uwuvúlmygy fu pcxu bu xy myl nixi u oh johni. ¡Ub, nlucxil xih Zylhuhxi, livuxil xy gc afilcu, goylny xy gc pcxu! ¿Koý kocylym? ¿Koý
jlynyhxym? Wihmcxylu koy hi joyxym wlcmncuhugyhny ffyaul uf zch xy nom xymyim, jilkoy Fomwchxu ym gc ymjimu, s si mis mo gulcxi.» ¡Ub fiwi xy gć! ¡Ubilu koy ymnis uomyhny s fydim xyf jyfcali xcai koy buvću xy buwyl fi koy hi bcwy! ¡Ubilu koy xydý livul gc wulu jlyhxu, gufxcai uf livuxil, xy kocyh joxcylu pyhaulgy mc nopcylu wilutíh julu yffi, wigi fy nyhai julu koydulgy! Yh zch, joym zoc yhnihwym wivulxy s hywci, hi ym gowbi koy goylu ubilu willcxi, ullyjyhncxi s fiwi.
