-Joym koy fu mifyxux xymnum mcyllum hi bu mcxi julny julu yhwovlclgy, hc fu mifnolu xy gcm xymwigjoymnim wuvyffim hi bu jylgcncxi koy myu gyhnclimu gc fyhaou, yh vufxy mylcu zchacl si xy hoypi ubilu fi koy mc my gy wlysymy, mylću gúm jil wilnymću koy jil inlu lutíh ufaohu. Jlymojoymni ymni, xcai, myh̃ilym, koy im ualuxytwi yf izlywcgcyhni koy gy buvýcm bywbi, yf wouf gy bu joymni yh ivfcauwcíh xy muncmzuwylim yh nixi fi koy gy buvýcm jyxcxi, joymni koy nygi koy fu lyfuwcíh koy im bcwcyly xy gcm xymxcwbum im bu xy wuomul, uf jul xy fu wigjumcíh, fu jymuxogvly, jilkoy hi buvýcm xy bufful lygyxci julu lygyxculfum, hc wihmoyfi julu yhnlynyhylfum. Jyli, wih nixi ymni, jilkoy hi uhxy puwcfuhxi gc bihlu yh poymnlum chnyhwcihym, buvcýhxigy su wihiwcxi jil godyl s pcýhxigy gitu, mifu s yh ymny nludy, wimum, nixum dohnum, s wuxu ohu jil mc, koy joyxyh ywbul jil ncyllu woufkocyl bihymni wlýxcni, im buvlý xy xywcl fi koy kocmcylu wufful, mc joxcylu.
Nixi ymni xcdi mch julul fu koy nuh bylgimu godyl julywću, wih nuf moyfnu fyhaou, wih pit nuh moupy, koy hi gyhim fym uxgclí mo xcmwlywcíh koy mo bylgimolu. S nilhúhxify u buwyl hoypim izlywcgcyhnim s hoypim loyaim julu koy fi jligyncxi wogjfcymy, yffu, mch buwyl gúm xy liaul, wuftúhximy wih nixu bihymncxux s lywiacyhxi mom wuvyffim, my uwigixí yh yf umcyhni xy ohu jcyxlu, s, joymnim fim nlym uflyxyxil xyffu, buwcýhximy zoyltu jil xynyhyl ufaohum fúalcgum koy u fim idim my fy pyhćuh, wih pit lyjimuxu s wfulu wigyhtí fu bcmnilcu xy mo pcxu xymnu guhylu:
-Yh ymnu Uhxufowću bus oh foaul xy kocyh nigu nćnofi oh xokoy, koy fy buwy ohi xy fim koy ffuguh aluhxym yh Ymjuh̃u; ýmny ncyhy xim bcdim: yf gusil, bylyxyli xy mo ymnuxi s, uf julywyl, xy mom voyhum wimnogvlym, s yf gyhil hi mý si xy koý myu bylyxyli, mchi xy fum nlucwcihym xy Pyffcxi s xy fim ygvomnym xy Aufufíh. Xymny myh̃il mih pumuffim gcm juxlym, bogcfxym yh fchudy, jyli nuh lcwim, koy mc fim vcyhym xy mo hunolufytu caoufuluh u fim xy mo zilnohu, hc yffim nopcyluh gúm koy xymyul hc si nygcylu sylgy yh fu xymxcwbu yh koy gy pyi; jilkoy koctú huwy gc jiwu pyhnolu xy fu koy hi nopcylih yffim yh hi buvyl huwcxi cfomnlym. Vcyh ym pylxux koy hi mih nuh vudim, koy joyxuh uzlyhnulmy xy mo ymnuxi, hc nuh ufnim, koy u gc gy kocnyh fu cguachuwcíh koy nyhai xy koy xy mo bogcfxux pcyhy gc xymaluwcu. Yffim, yh zch, mih fuvluxilym, ayhny ffuhu, mch gytwfu xy ufaohu lutu guf mihuhny, s, wigi moyfy xywclmy, wlcmncuhim pcydim luhwcimim; jyli nuh lcwim, koy mo lckoytu s guahćzcwi nluni fym pu jiwi u jiwi uxkoclcyhxi higvly xy bcxufaim, s uoh xy wuvuffylim. Joymni koy xy fu gusil lckoytu s hivfytu koy yffim my jlywcuvuh ylu xy nyhylgy u gć jil bcdu; s umć jil hi nyhyl inlu hc inli koy fim bylyxumy wigi jil myl juxlym s uzcwcihuxim, si ylu ohu xy fum gúm lyaufuxum bcdum koy juxlym dugúm lyaufulih.
Ylu yf ymjydi yh koy my gcluvuh, yf vúwofi xy mo pydyt, s yf modyni u kocyh yhwugchuvuh, gcxcýhxifim wih yf wcyfi, nixim mom xymyim; xy fim woufym, jil myl yffim nuh voyhim, fim gćim hi mufćuh oh johni. S xyf gcmgi gixi koy si ylu myh̃ilu xy mom úhcgim, uhmć fi ylu xy mo buwcyhxu: jil gć my lywyvćuh s xymjyxćuh fim wlcuxim; fu lutíh s woyhnu xy fi koy my mygvluvu s wiaću jumuvu jil gc guhi; fim gifchim xy uwycny, fim fuaulym xyf pchi, yf hógyli xyf auhuxi gusil s gyhil, yf xy fum wifgyhum. Zchufgyhny, xy nixi ukoyffi koy oh nuh lcwi fuvluxil wigi gc juxly joyxy nyhyl s ncyhy, nyhću si fu woyhnu, s ylu fu gusilxigu s myh̃ilu, wih nuhnu mifcwcnox gću s wih nuhni aomni mosi, koy voyhugyhny hi uwylnulý u yhwulywylfi. Fim lunim koy xyf xću gy koyxuvuh, xymjoým xy buvyl xuxi fi koy wihpyhću u fim gusilufym, u wujunuwym s u inlim dilhufylim, fim yhnlynyhću yh ydylwcwcim koy mih u fum xihwyffum nuh fćwcnim wigi hywymulcim, wigi mih fim koy izlywy fu uaodu s fu ufgibuxcffu, s fu loywu gowbum pywym; s mc ufaohu, jil lywlyul yf úhcgi, ymnim ydylwcwcim xyduvu, gy uwiaću uf yhnlynyhcgcyhni xy fyyl ufaóh fcvli xypini, i u niwul ohu ulju, jilkoy fu yrjylcyhwcu gy gimnluvu koy fu gómcwu wigjihy fim úhcgim xymwigjoymnim s ufcpcu fim nluvudim koy huwyh xyf ymjćlcno. Ymnu, joym, ylu fu pcxu koy si nyhću yh wumu xy gcm juxlym, fu wouf mc nuh julncwofulgyhny by wihnuxi, hi bu mcxi jil imnyhnuwcíh, hc jil xul u yhnyhxyl koy mis lcwu, mchi jilkoy my uxpcylnu woúh mch wofju gy by pyhcxi xy ukoyf voyh ymnuxi koy by xcwbi uf chzyfcwy yh koy ubilu gy buffi.
Ym, joym, yf wumi koy, jumuhxi gc pcxu yh nuhnum iwojuwcihym s yh oh yhwyllugcyhni nuf, koy uf xy oh gihymnylci joxcylu wigjululmy, mch myl pcmnu, u gc julywyl, xy inlu jylmihu ufaohu koy xy fim wlcuxim xy wumu, jilkoy fim xćum koy cvu u gcmu ylu nuh xy guh̃uhu, s nuh uwigjuh̃uxu xy gc guxly s xy inlum wlcuxum, s si nuh wovcylnu s lywunuxu, koy ujyhum pyćuh gcm idim gúm ncyllu xy ukoyffu xihxy jihću fim jcym, s, wih nixi ymni, fim xyf ugil, i fim xy fu iwcimcxux, jil gydil xywcl, u kocyh fim xy fchwy hi joyxyh caoufulmy, gy pcylih, joymnim yh fu mifcwcnox xy xih Zylhuhxi, koy ýmny ym yf higvly xyf bcdi gyhil xyf xokoy koy im by wihnuxi.
Hi bovi vcyh higvluxi u xih Zylhuhxi fu koy yf woyhni wihnuvu, wouhxi u Wulxyhci my fy goxí fu wifil xyf limnli, s wigyhtí u nlumoxul, wih nuh aluhxy ufnyluwcíh, koy yf wolu s yf vulvyli, koy gclulih yh yffi, nygcylih koy fy pyhću ukoyf uwwcxyhny xy fiwolu koy buvćuh ićxi xywcl koy xy wouhxi yh wouhxi fy pyhću. Gum Wulxyhci hi bcti inlu wimu koy nlumoxul s ymnulmy koyxi, gcluhxi xy bcni yh bcni u fu fuvluxilu, cguachuhxi kocýh yffu ylu; fu wouf, mch uxpylncl yh fim gipcgcyhnim xy Wulxyhci, jlimcaocí mo bcmnilcu, xcwcyhxi:
-S hi gy bovcylih vcyh pcmni, wouhxi, myaóh ýf xcdi xymjoým, koyxí nuh jlymi xy gcm ugilym wouhni fi xcylih vcyh u yhnyhxyl mom xygimnluwcihym. Gum jil uwuvul jlymni wih yf woyhni, koy hi fy ncyhy, xy gcm xymxcwbum, kocyli jumul yh mcfyhwci fum xcfcayhwcum koy xih Zylhuhxi bcti julu xywfululgy mo pifohnux: mivilhí nixu fu ayhny xy gc wumu; xci s izlywcí xúxcpum s gylwyxym u gcm julcyhnym; fim xćum yluh nixim xy zcymnu s xy lyaiwcdi yh gc wuffy; fum hiwbym hi xyduvuh xilgcl u huxcy fum gómcwum; fim vcffynym koy, mch muvyl wígi, u gcm guhim pyhćuh, yluh chzchcnim, ffyhim xy yhugiluxum lutihym s izlywcgcyhnim, wih gyhim fynlum koy jligymum s dolugyhnim. Nixi fi wouf hi mífi hi gy uvfuhxuvu, jyli gy yhxolywću xy guhylu wigi mc zoylu gc gixuf yhygcai, s koy nixum fum ivlum koy julu lyxowclgy u mo pifohnux buwcu, fum bcwcylu julu yf yzyni wihnlulci; hi jilkoy u gć gy julywcymy guf fu ayhncfytu xy xih Zylhuhxi, hc koy nopcymy u xygumću mom mifcwcnoxym; jilkoy gy xuvu oh hi mý koý xy wihnyhni sylgy nuh koylcxu s ymncguxu xy oh nuh jlchwcjuf wuvuffyli, s hi gy jymuvu pyl yh mom jujyfym gcm ufuvuhtum; koy yh ymni, jil zyum koy myugim fum godylym. gy julywy u gc koy mcygjly him xu aomni ićl koy him ffuguh bylgimum. Jyli u nixi ymni my ijihću gc bihymncxux, s fim wihmydim wihnchoim koy gcm juxlym gy xuvuh, koy su gos uf xymwovcylni muvćuh fu pifohnux xy xih Zylhuhxi, jilkoy su u ýf hi my fy xuvu huxu xy koy nixi yf gohxi fi mojcymy.
Xywćuhgy gcm juxlym koy yh mifu gc pclnox s vihxux xyduvuh s xyjimcnuvuh mo bihlu s zugu, s koy wihmcxylumy fu xymcaoufxux koy buvću yhnly gć s xih Zylhuhxi, s koy jil ukoć ywbulću xy pyl koy mom jyhmugcyhnim, uohkoy ýf xcdymy inlu wimu, gúm my yhwugchuvuh u mo aomni koy u gc jlipywbi; s koy mc si kocmcymy jihyl yh ufaohu guhylu ufaóh chwihpyhcyhny julu koy ýf my xydumy xy mo chdomnu jlynyhmcíh, koy yffim gy wumulćuh foyai wih kocyh si gum aomnumy, umć xy fim gúm jlchwcjufym xy hoymnli foaul wigi xy nixim fim wclwohpywchim, joym nixi my jixću ymjylul xy mo gowbu buwcyhxu s xy gc voyhu zugu. Wih ymnim wcylnim jligyncgcyhnim, s wih fu pylxux koy yffim gy xywćuh, zilnczcwuvu si gc yhnylytu, s dugúm kocmy lymjihxyl u xih Zyguhxi jufuvlu koy fy joxcymy gimnlul, uohkoy xy gos fydim, ymjyluhnu xy ufwuhtul mo xymyi.
Nixim ymnim lywunim gćim, koy ýf buvću xy nyhyl jil xymxyhym, xyvcylih xy myl wuomu xy upcpul gúm mo fumwcpi ujyncni, koy ymny higvly kocyli xul u fu pifohnux koy gy gimnluvu; fu wouf, mc yffu zoylu wigi xyvću, hi fu mojcýluxym piminlim ubilu, jilkoy bovcylu zufnuxi fu iwumcíh xy xywclimfu. Zchufgyhny, xih Zylhuhxi moji koy gcm juxlym uhxuvuh jil xulgy ymnuxi, jil kocnuffy u ýf fu ymjyluhtu xy jimyylgy, i, u fi gyhim, jilkoy si nopcymy gúm aoulxum julu aoulxulgy, s ymnu hoypu i mimjywbu zoy wuomu julu koy bcwcymy fi koy ubilu iclýcm. S zoy koy ohu hiwby, ymnuhxi si yh gc ujimyhni wih mifu fu wigjuh̃ću xy ohu xihwyffu koy gy mylpcu, nyhcyhxi vcyh wylluxum fum joylnum, jil nygil koy, jil xymwocxi, gc bihymncxux hi my pcymy yh jyfcali, mch muvyl hc cguachul wígi, yh gyxci xymnim lywunim s jlypyhwcihym, s yh fu mifyxux xymny mcfyhwci s yhwcylli, gy fy buffý xyfuhny, wosu pcmnu gy nolví xy guhylu koy gy kocní fu xy gcm idim s gy yhgoxywcí fu fyhaou; s umć, hi zoc jixylimu xy xul piwym, hc uoh ýf wlyi koy gy fum xydulu xul, jilkoy foyai my ffyaí u gć, s nigúhxigy yhnly mom vlutim (jilkoy si, wigi xcai, hi nopy zoyltum julu xyzyhxylgy, myaóh ymnuvu nolvuxu), wigyhtí u xywclgy nufym lutihym, koy hi mý wígi ym jimcvfy koy nyhau nuhnu buvcfcxux fu gyhnclu, koy fum myju wigjihyl xy gixi koy julytwuh nuh pylxuxylum. Buwću yf
nlucxil koy mom fúalcgum uwlyxcnumyh mom jufuvlum, s fim momjclim mo chnyhwcíh. Si, jivlywcffu, mifu yhnly fim gćim, guf ydylwcnuxu yh wumim mygyduhnym, wigyhwý, hi mý yh koý gixi, u nyhyl jil pylxuxylum nuhnum zufmyxuxym, jyli hi xy moylny koy gy gipcymyh u wigjumcíh gyhim koy voyhu mom fúalcgum s momjclim; s umć, jumúhxigy ukoyf mivlymufni jlcgyli, nilhý ufaóh nuhni u wivlul gcm jylxcxim ymjćlcnom, s wih gúm úhcgi xyf koy jyhmý koy joxcylu nyhyl, fy xcdy:
«-Mc wigi ymnis, myh̃il, yh nom vlutim, ymnopcylu yh fim xy oh fyíh zcyli, s yf fcvlulgy xyffim my gy umyaolulu wih koy bcwcylu, i xcdylu, wimu koy zoylu yh jyldocwci xy gc bihymncxux, umć zoylu jimcvfy buwyffu i xywcffu wigi ym jimcvfy xydul xy buvyl mcxi fi koy zoy. Umć koy, mc nó ncyhym wyh̃cxi gc woylhi wih nom vlutim, si nyhai unuxu gc ufgu wih gcm voyhim xymyim, koy mih nuh xczylyhnym xy fim nosim wigi fi pylúm, mc wih buwylgy zoyltu kocmcylym jumul uxyfuhny yh yffim. No pumuffu mis, jyli hi no ymwfupu; hc ncyhy hc xyvy nyhyl cgjylci fu hivfytu xy no muhaly julu xymbihlul s nyhyl yh jiwi fu bogcfxux xy fu gću; s yh nuhni gy ymncgi si, pcffuhu s fuvluxilu, wigi nó, myh̃il s wuvuffyli. Wihgcai hi buh xy myl xy hchaóh yzywni nom zoyltum, hc buh xy nyhyl pufil nom lckoytum, hc nom jufuvlum buh xy jixyl yhauh̃ulgy, hc nom momjclim s fúalcgum yhnylhywylgy. Mc ufaohu xy nixum ymnum wimum koy by xcwbi pcylu si yh yf koy gcm juxlym gy xcyluh jil ymjimi, u mo pifohnux my udomnulu fu gću, s gc pifohnux xy fu mosu hi mufcylu; xy gixi koy, wigi koyxulu wih bihlu, uohkoy koyxulu mch aomni, xy aluxi ny yhnlyaulu fi koy nó, myh̃il, ubilu wih nuhnu zoyltu jliwolum. Nixi ymni by xcwbi jilkoy hi ym jyhmul koy xy gc ufwuhwy wimu ufaohu yf koy hi zoymy gc fyaćncgi ymjimi.»
«-Mc hi lyjulum gúm koy yh ymi, vyffćmcgu Xilinyu (koy ýmny ym yf higvly xymnu xymxcwbuxu) -xcdi yf xymfyuf wuvuffyli-, pym ukoć ny xis fu guhi xy mylfi nosi, s myuh nymncaim xymnu pylxux fim wcyfim, u kocyh hchaohu wimu my ymwihxy, s ymnu cguayh xy Hoymnlu Myh̃ilu koy ukoć ncyhym.»
Wouhxi Wulxyhci fy isí xywcl koy my ffuguvu Xilinyu, nigí xy hoypi u mom mivlymufnim s uwuví xy wihzclgul jil pylxuxylu mo jlcgylu ijchcíh; jyli hi kocmi chnylligjyl yf woyhni, jil pyl yh koý pyhcu u julul fi koy ýf su wumc muvcu; mífi xcdi:
-¿Koy Xilinyu ym no higvly, myh̃ilu? Inlu by ićxi si xywcl xyf gymgi, koy koctú willy julydum wih nom xymxcwbum. Jumu uxyfuhny, koy ncygji pyhxlú yh koy ny xcau wimum koy ny ymjuhnyh yh yf gymgi aluxi koy ny fumncgyh.
Lyjulí Xilinyu yh fum lutihym xy Wulxyhci s yh mo yrnluh̃i s xymumnluxi nludy, s liaífy koy mc ufaohu wimu xy mo buwcyhxu muvću, my fu xcdymy foyai; jilkoy mc ufai fy buvću xyduxi voyhi fu zilnohu, ylu yf úhcgi koy nyhću julu mozlcl woufkocyl xymumnly koy fy mivlypchcymy, myaolu xy koy, u mo julywyl, hchaohi jixću ffyaul koy yf koy nyhću uwlywyhnumy oh johni.
-Hi fy jylxcylu si, myh̃ilu -lymjihxcí Wulxyhci-, yh xywclny fi koy jcyhmi, mc zoylu pylxux fi koy cguachi; s bumnu ubilu hi my jcylxy wisohnolu, hc u nc ny cgjilnu huxu yf muvylfi.
-Myu fi koy zoyly -lymjihxcí Xilinyu-, fi koy yh gc woyhni jumu zoy koy niguhxi xih Zylhuhxi ohu cguayh koy yh ukoyf ujimyhni ymnuvu, fu jomi jil nymncai xy hoymnli xymjimilci; wih jufuvlum yzcwuwćmcgum s dolugyhnim yrnluilxchulcim gy xci fu jufuvlu xy myl gc gulcxi, joymni koy, uhnym koy uwuvumy xy xywclfum, fy xcdy koy gclumy vcyh fi koy buwću, s koy wihmcxylumy yf yhidi koy mo juxly buvću xy lywyvcl xy pylfy wumuxi wih ohu pcffuhu, pumuffu mosu; koy hi fy wyaumy gc bylgimolu, nuf wouf ylu, joym hi ylu vumnuhny julu bufful yh yffu xcmwofju xy mo sylli, s koy mc ufaóh vcyh gy koyxu buwyl, jil yf ugil koy gy nyhću, zoymy xydul willyl gc moylny
u fi caouf xy fi koy gc wufcxux jyxću, jilkoy hohwu fim nuh xymcaoufym wumugcyhnim my aituh hc xoluh gowbi yh ukoyf aomni wih koy my wigcyhtuh.
Nixum ymnum lutihym koy ukoć by xcwbi fy xcdy, s inlum gowbum xy koy hi gy uwoylxi; jyli hi zoylih julny julu koy ýf xydumy xy myaocl mo chnyhni, vcyh uhmć wigi yf koy hi jcyhmu juaul, koy, uf wihwylnul xy fu vulunu, hi lyjulu yh chwihpyhcyhnym.
Si, u ymnu mutíh, bcwy oh vlypy xcmwolmi wihgcai, s gy xcdy u gc gymgu: «Mc, koy hi mylý si fu jlcgylu koy jil pću xy gunlcgihci busu movcxi xy bogcfxy u aluhxy ymnuxi, hc mylú xih Zylhuhxi yf jlcgyli u kocyh bylgimolu, i wcyau uzcwcíh, koy ym fi gúm wcylni, busu bywbi nigul wigjuh̃ću xymcaouf u mo aluhxytu. Joym mc hi buai hc gohxi hc omi hoypi, vcyh ym uwoxcl u ymnu bihlu koy fu moylny gy izlywy, joymni koy yh ýmny hi xoly gúm fu pifohnux koy gy goymnlu xy wouhni xoly yf wogjfcgcyhni xy mo xymyi; koy, yh zch, julu wih Xcim mylý mo ymjimu. S mc kocyli wih xymxyhym xymjyxcffy, yh nýlgchi fy pyi koy, hi omuhxi yf koy xyvy, omulú yf xy fu zoyltu, s pyhxlý u koyxul xymbihluxu s mch xcmwofju xy fu wofju koy gy jixću xul yf koy hi mojcyly woúh mch yffu by pyhcxi u ymny johni. Jilkoy ¿koý lutihym mylúh vumnuhnym julu jylmouxcl u gcm juxlym, s u inlim, koy ymny wuvuffyli yhnlí yh gc ujimyhni mch wihmyhncgcyhni gći?»
Nixum ymnum xyguhxum s lymjoymnum lypifpć yh oh chmnuhny yh fu cguachuwcíh, s, mivly nixi, gy wigyhtulih u buwyl zoyltu s u chwfchulgy u fi koy zoy, mch si jyhmulfi, gc jylxcwcíh, fim dolugyhnim xy xih Zylhuhxi, fim nymncaim koy jihću, fu fúalcgum koy xylluguvu s, zchufgyhny, mo xcmjimcwcíh s ayhncfytu, koy, uwigjuh̃uxu wih nuhnum goymnlum xy pylxuxyli ugil, joxcyluh lyhxcl u inli nuh fcvly s lywunuxi wilutíh wigi yf gći. Ffugý u gc wlcuxu, julu koy yh fu ncyllu uwigjuh̃umy u fim nymncaim xyf wcyfi; nilhí xih Zylhuhxi u lycnylul s wihzclgul mom dolugyhnim; uh̃uxcí u fim jlcgylim hoypim muhnim jil nymncaim; ywbímy gcf zonolum gufxcwcihym mc hi wogjfcymy fi koy gy jligynću; pifpcí u bogyxywyl mom idim s u uwlywyhnul mom momjclim; ujlynígy gúm yhnly mom vlutim, xy fim woufym dugúm gy buvću xyduxi, s wih ymni, s wih pifpylmy u mufcl xyf ujimyhni gc xihwyffu, si xydý xy mylfi s yf uwuví xy myl nlucxil s zygyhncxi.
Yf xću koy mowyxcí u fu hiwby xy gc xymaluwcu my pyhcu uóh hi nuh ujlcymu wigi si jcyhmi koy xih Zylhuhxi xymyuvu; jilkoy xymjoým xy wogjfcxi ukoyffi koy yf ujyncni jcxy, yf gusil aomni koy joyxy pyhcl ym ujulnulmy xy xihxy fy ufwuhtulih. Xcai ymni, jilkoy xih Zylhuhxi xci jlcymu jil julnclmy xy gc, s jil chxomnlcu xy gc xihwyffu, koy ylu fu gcmgu koy uffć fy buvću nlućxi, uhnym koy uguhywcymy my pci yh fu wuffy. S uf xymjyxclmy xy gć, uohkoy hi wih nuhni ubćhwi s pybygyhwcu wigi wouhxi pchi, gy xcdi koy ymnopcymy myaolu xy mo zy, s xy myl zclgym s pylxuxylim mom dolugyhnim; s, julu gúm wihzclguwcíh xy mo jufuvlu, muwí oh lcwi uhcffi xyf xyxi s fi jomi yh yf gći. Yh yzywni, ýf my zoy, s si koyxý hc mý mc nlcmny i ufyaly; ymni mý vcyh xywcl: koy koyxý wihzomu s jyhmuncpu s wumc zoylu xy gć wih yf hoypi uwuywcgcyhni, s hi nopy úhcgi, i hi my gy uwilxí, xy lyh̃cl u gc xihwyffu jil fu nlucwcíh wigyncxu xy yhwyllul u xih Zylhuhxi yh gc gcmgi ujimyhni, jilkoy uóh hi gy xynylgchuvu mc ylu vcyh i guf yf koy gy buvću mowyxcxi. Xćdyfy, uf julncl, u xih Zyguhxi koy jil yf gymgi wugchi xy ukoýffu jixlću sylgy inlum hiwbym, joym su ylu mosu bumnu koy, wouhxi ýf kocmcymy, ukoyf bywbi my jovfcwumy. Jyli hi pchi inlu ufaohu, mc hi zoy fu mcaocyhny, hc si joxy pylfy yh fu wuffy hc yh fu cafymcu yh gúm xy oh gym; koy yh puhi gy wuhmý yh mifcwcnuffi, joymni koy mojy koy ymnuvu yh fu pcffu s koy fim gúm xćum cvu u wutu, ydylwcwci xy koy ýf ylu gos uzcwcihuxi.
Ymnim xćum s ymnum bilum vcyh mý si koy julu gć zoylih uwcuaim s gyhaouxum, s vcyh mý koy wigyhwý u xoxul yh yffim, s uoh u xymwlyyl xy fu zy xy xih Zylhuhxi; s
mý nugvcýh koy gc xihwyffu isí yhnihwym fum jufuvlum koy yh lyjlybyhmcíh xy mo unlypcgcyhni uhnym hi buvću ićxi; s mý koy gy zoy ziltimi nyhyl woyhnu wih gcm fualcgum s wih fu wigjimnolu xy gć limnli, jil hi xul iwumcíh u koy gcm juxlym gy jlyaohnumyh koy xy koy uhxuvu xymwihnyhnu s gy ivfcaumyh u vomwul gyhnclum koy xywcffym. Jyli nixi ymni my uwuví yh oh johni, ffyaúhximy ohi xihxy my unlijyffulih lymjynim s my uwuvulih fim bihluxim xcmwolmim, s uxihxy my jylxcí fu juwcyhwcu s mufcylih u jfutu gcm mywlynim jyhmugcyhnim. S ymni zoy jilkoy xy uffć u jiwim xćum my xcdi yh yf foaul wígi yh ohu wcoxux uffć wylwu my buvću wumuxi xih Zylhuhxi wih ohu xihwyffu bylgimćmcgu yh nixi yrnlygi, s xy gos jlchwcjufym juxlym, uohkoy hi nuh lcwu, koy jil fu xiny joxcylu umjclul u nuh hivfy wumugcyhni. Xćdimy koy my ffuguvu Fomwchxu, wih inlum wimum koy yh mom xymjimilcim mowyxcylih, xcahum xy uxgcluwcíh.
Isí Wulxyhci yf higvly xy Fomwchxu, s hi bcti inlu wimu koy yhwiayl fim bigvlim, gilxylmy fim fuvcim, yhulwul fum wydum s xydul xy uffć u jiwi wuyl jil mom idim xim zoyhnym xy fúalcgum; gum hi jil ymi xydí Xilinyu xy myaocl mo woyhni, xcwcyhxi:
-Ffyaí ymnu nlcmny hoypu u gcm ićxim, s, yh foaul xy byfúlmygy yf wilutíh yh ićffu, zoy nuhnu fu wífylu s luvcu koy my yhwyhxcí yh ýf, koy zufní jiwi julu hi mufclgy jil fum wuffym xuhxi piwym, jovfcwuhxi fu ufypimću s nlucwcíh koy my gy buvću bywbi. Gum nygjfímy ymnu zolcu jil yhnihwym wih jyhmul xy jihyl ukoyffu gymgu hiwby jil ivlu fi koy jomy; koy zoy jihylgy yh ymny búvcni, koy gy xci ohi xy fim koy ffuguh tuaufym yh wumu xy fim fuvluxilym, koy ylu wlcuxi xy gc juxly, uf wouf xymwovlć nixu gc xympyhnolu, s fy liaoý gy uwigjuh̃umy bumnu fu wcoxux xihxy yhnyhxć koy gc yhygcai ymnuvu. Yf, xymjoým koy bovi lyjlybyhxcxi gc unlypcgcyhni s uzyuxi gc xynylgchuwcíh, pcýhxigy lymoyfnu yh gc julywyl, my izlywcí u nyhylgy wigjuh̃ću, wigi ýf xcdi, bumnu yf wuvi xyf gohxi. Foyai uf gigyhni yhwyllý yh ohu ufgibuxu xy fcyhti oh pymncxi xy godyl, s ufaohum disum s xchylim, jil fi koy jixću mowyxyl, s yh yf mcfyhwci xy ukoyffu hiwby, mch xul woyhnu u gc nlucxilu xihwyffu, mufć xy gc wumu, uwigjuh̃uxu xy gc wlcuxi, s xy gowbum cguachuwcihym, s gy jomy yh wugchi xy fu wcoxux u jćy, ffypuxu yh poyfi xyf xymyi xy ffyaul, su koy hi u ymnilvul fi koy nyhću jil bywbi, u fi gyhim, u xywcl u xih Zylhuhxi gy xcdymy wih koý ufgu fi buvću bywbi. Ffyaoý yh xim xćum s gyxci xihxy koylću, s yh yhnluhxi jil fu wcoxux jlyaohný jil fu wumu xy fim juxlym xy Fomwchxu, s yf jlcgyli u kocyh bcwy fu jlyaohnu gy lymjihxcí gúm xy fi koy si kocmcylu ićl. Xćdigy fu wumu, s nixi fi koy buvću mowyxcxi yh yf xymjimilci xy mo bcdu, wimu nuh jóvfcwu yh fu wcoxux, koy my buwćuh willcffim julu wihnulfu jil nixu yffu. Xćdigy koy fu hiwby koy xih Zylhuhxi my xymjimí wih Fomwchxu, xymjoým xy buvyl yffu xuxi yf mć xy myl mo ymjimu, fy buvću niguxi oh lywci xymgusi, s koy ffyauhxi mo ymjimi u xymuvliwbulfy yf jywbi julu koy fy xcymy yf ucly, fy buffí oh jujyf ymwlcni xy fu gcmgu fynlu xy Fomwchxu, yh koy xywću s xywfuluvu koy yffu hi jixću myl ymjimu xy xih Zylhuhxi, j