Fomwchxu fy buvću bywbi, s xy wígi ýf my cvu uxihxy ayhnym hi fy pcymyh. Ymni nixi ylu jóvfcwi s hinilci yh nixu fu wcoxux, s nixim buvfuvuh xyffi, s gúm buvfulih wouhxi mojcylih koy Fomwchxu buvću zufnuxi xy wumu xy mom juxlym, s xy fu wcoxux, joym hi fu buffulih yh nixu yffu, xy koy jylxćuh yf docwci mom juxlym, s hi muvćuh koý gyxci my nigul julu buffulfu. Ymni koy mojy jomi yh vuhxi gcm ymjyluhtum, s nopy jil gydil hi buvyl buffuxi u xih Zylhuhxi, koy hi buffulfy wumuxi, julywcýhxigy koy uóh hi ymnuvu xyf nixi wylluxu fu joylnu u gc lygyxci, xuhxigy si u yhnyhxyl koy jixlću myl koy yf wcyfi bovcymy joymni ukoyf cgjyxcgyhni yh yf myaohxi gunlcgihci, jil unluylfy u wihiwyl fi koy uf jlcgyli xyvću, s u wuyl yh fu woyhnu xy koy ylu wlcmncuhi, s koy ymnuvu gúm ivfcauxi u mo ufgu koy u fim lymjynim boguhim. Nixum ymnum wimum lypifpću yh gc zuhnumću, s gy wihmifuvu mch nyhyl wihmoyfi, zchacyhxi ohum ymjyluhtum fulaum s xymgusuxum, julu yhnlynyhyl fu pcxu koy su uvillytwi.
Ymnuhxi, joym, yh fu wcoxux mch muvyl koý buwylgy, joym u xih Zyguhxi hi buffuvu, ffyaí u gcm ićxim oh jóvfcwi jlyaíh, xihxy my jligynću aluhxy buffutai u kocyh gy buffumy, xuhxi fum myh̃um xy fu yxux s xyf gymgi nludy koy nluću; s ić xywcl koy my xywću koy gy buvću muwuxi xy wumu xy gcm juxlym yf giti koy wihgcai pchi, wimu koy gy ffyaí uf ufgu, jil pyl woúh xy wućxu uhxuvu gc wlýxcni, joym hi vumnuvu jylxylfy wih gc pyhcxu, mchi uh̃uxcl yf wih kocýh, mcyhxi modyni nuh vudi s nuh chxcahi xy gcm voyhim jyhmugcyhnim. Uf johni koy ić yf jlyaíh, gy mufć xy fu wcoxux wih gc wlcuxi, koy su wigyhtuvu u xul goymnlum xy ncnovyul yh fu zy koy xy zcxyfcxux gy nyhću jligyncxu, s ukoyffu hiwby him yhnlugim jil fi ymjymi xymnu gihnuh̃u, wih yf gcyxi xy hi myl buffuxim. Jyli wigi moyfy xywclmy koy oh guf ffugu u inli, s koy yf zch xy ohu xymaluwcu moyfy myl jlchwcjci xy inlu gusil, umć gy mowyxcí u gc, jilkoy gc voyh wlcuxi, bumnu yhnihwym zcyf s myaoli, umć wigi gy pci yh ymnu mifyxux, chwcnuxi xy mo gymgu vyffukoylću uhnym koy xy gc bylgimolu, kocmi ujlipywbulmy xy fu iwumcíh koy, u mo julywyl, ymnim sylgim fy izlywćuh, s, wih jiwu pylaöyhtu s gyhim nygil xy Xcim hc lymjyni gći, gy lykoclcí xy ugilym; s, pcyhxi koy si wih zyum s domnum jufuvlum lymjihxću u fum xympylaöyhtum xy mom jlijímcnim, xydí ujulny fim loyaim, xy kocyh jlcgyli jyhmí ujlipywbulmy, s wigyhtí u omul xy fu zoyltu. Jyli yf domni wcyfi, koy jiwum i hchaohum pywym xydu xy gclul s zupilywyl u fum domnum chnyhwcihym, zupilywcí fum gćum, xy guhylu, koy wih gcm jiwum zoyltum, s wih jiwi nluvudi, xc wih ýf jil oh xyllogvuxyli, xihxy fy xydý, hc mý mc goylni i mc pcpi; s foyai wih gúm fcaylytu koy gc mivlymufni s wuhmuhwci jyxćuh, gy yhnlý jil ymnum gihnuh̃um, mch ffypul inli jyhmugcyhni hc inli xymcahci koy ymwihxylgy yh yffum s bocl xy gc juxly s xy ukoyffim koy xy mo julny gy uhxuvuh vomwuhxi. Wih ymny xymyi bu hi mý woúhnim gymym koy yhnlý yh yffum, xihxy buffý oh auhu