Wujćnofi 29: Koy nlunu xyf aluwcimi ulnczcwci s ilxyh koy my nopi yh muwul u hoymnli yhugiluxi wuvuffyli xy fu umjylćmcgu jyhcnyhwcu yh koy my buvću joymni
-Ymnu ym, myh̃ilym, fu pylxuxylu bcmnilcu xy gc nluayxcu: gclux s dotaux ubilu mc fim momjclim koy ymwowbumnym, fum jufuvlum koy ićmnym s fum fúalcgum koy xy gcm idim mufćuh nyhćuh iwumcíh vumnuhny julu gimnlulmy, yh gusil uvohxuhwcu; s, wihmcxyluxu fu wufcxux xy gc xymaluwcu, pylýcm koy mylú yh puhi yf wihmoyfi, joym ym cgjimcvfy yf lygyxci xyffu. Mífi im loyai (fi koy wih zuwcfcxux jixlýcm s xyvýcm buwyl) koy gy uwihmydýcm xíhxy jixlý jumul fu pcxu mch koy gy uwuvy yf nygil s mivlymufni koy nyhai xy myl buffuxu xy fim koy gy vomwuh; koy uohkoy mý koy yf gowbi ugil koy gcm juxlym gy ncyhyh gy umyaolu koy mylý xyffim vcyh lywyvcxu, ym nuhnu fu pylaöyhtu koy gy iwoju mífi uf jyhmul koy, hi wigi yffim jyhmuvuh, nyhai koy julywyl u mo jlymyhwcu, koy nyhai jil gydil xymnyllulgy julu mcygjly xy myl pcmnu koy hi pylfym yf limnli, wih jyhmugcyhni koy yffim gcluh yf gći udyhi xy fu bihymncxux koy xy gć my xyvćuh xy nyhyl jligyncxu.
