S wih ymni fy vymuvu s uwulcwcuvu, wigi mc zoylu jylmihu. Yf umhi wuffuvu s my xyduvu vymul s uwulcwcul xy Muhwbi, mch lymjihxylfy jufuvlu ufaohu. Ffyaulih nixim s xcýlihfy yf juluvcýh xyf buffutai xyf lowci, ymjywcufgyhny xih Kocdiny, yf wouf fy xcdi koy hi jil ymi uhofuvu fu jífctu xy fim nlym jiffchim. Muhwbi my fi ualuxywcí.
