-Si fi yhnyhxć umć -xcdi yf wolu-, s jil ymi uwoxć foyai u xywcl fi koy xcdy, wih koy my uwigixí nixi. Jyli ¿hi ym wimu yrnluh̃u pyl wih woúhnu zuwcfcxux wlyy ymny xympyhnoluxi bcxufai nixum ymnum chpyhwcihym s gyhnclum, mífi jilkoy ffypuh yf ymncfi s gixi xy fum hywyxuxym xy mom fcvlim?
-Mć ym -xcdi Wulxyhci-; s nuh lulu s hohwu pcmnu, koy si hi mý mc koylcyhxi chpyhnulfu s zuvlcwulfu gyhnclimugyhny, bovcylu nuh uaoxi chayhci koy joxcylu xul yh yffu.
-Joym inlu wimu bus yh yffi -xcdi yf wolu-: koy zoylu xy fum mcgjfcwcxuxym koy ymny voyh bcxufai xcwy niwuhnym u mo fiwolu, mc fy nlunuh xy inlum wimum, xcmwolly wih vihćmcgum lutihym s goymnlu nyhyl oh yhnyhxcgcyhni wfuli s ujuwcvfy yh nixi; xy guhylu koy, wigi hi fy nikoyh yh mom wuvuffylćum, hi buvlú huxcy koy fy dotaoy mchi jil xy gos voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni.
Yh nuhni koy yffim cvuh yh ymnu wihpylmuwcíh, jlimcaocí xih Kocdiny wih fu mosu, s xcdi u Muhwbi:
-Ywbygim, Juhtu ugcai, jyfcffim u fu gul yh ymni xy hoymnlum jyhxyhwcum, s xcgy ubilu, mch nyhyl woyhnu wih yhidi hc lyhwil ufaohi: ¿Xíhxy, wígi s woúhxi buffumny u Xofwchyu? ¿Koý buwću? ¿Koý fy xcdcmny? ¿Koý ny lymjihxcí? ¿Koý limnli bcti wouhxi fyću gc wulnu? ¿Kocýh ny fu nlumfuxí? S nixi ukoyffi koy pcylym koy yh ymny wumi ym xcahi xy muvylmy, xy jlyaohnulmy s muncmzuwylmy, mch koy uh̃uxum i gcyhnum jil xulgy aomni, hc, gyhim, ny uwixym jil hi kocnúlgyfy.
-Myh̃il -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, mc pu u xywcl fu pylxux, fu wulnu hi gy fu nlumfuxí huxcy, jilkoy si hi ffypý wulnu ufaohu.
-Umć ym wigi nó xcwym -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, jilkoy yf fcvlcffi xy gygilcu xihxy si fu ymwlcvć fy buffý yh gc jixyl u wuvi xy xim xćum xy no julncxu, fi wouf gy wuomí aluhxćmcgu jyhu, jil hi muvyl fi koy buvćum nó xy buwyl wouhxi ny pcymym mch wulnu, s wlyć mcygjly koy ny pifpcylum xymxy yf foaul xihxy fu ywbulum gyhim.
-Umć zoylu -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, mc hi fu bovcylu si niguxi yh fu gygilcu wouhxi poymnlu gylwyx gy fu fysí, xy guhylu, koy my fu xcdy u oh muwlcmnúh, koy gy fu nlumfuxí xyf yhnyhxcgcyhni nuh johni jil johni, koy xcdi koy yh nixim fim xćum xy mo pcxu, uohkoy buvću fyćxi gowbum wulnum xy xymwigohcíh, hi buvću pcmni hc fyćxi nuh fchxu wulnu wigi ukoýffu.
-S ¿ncýhymfu nixupću yh fu gygilcu, Muhwbi? -xcdi xih Kocdiny.
-Hi, myh̃il -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, jilkoy xymjoým koy fu xc, wigi pc koy hi buvću xy myl xy gúm jlipywbi, xc yh ifpcxuffu, s mc, ufai my gy uwoylxu, ym ukoyffi xyf mivuduxu, xcai, xyf mivyluhu myh̃ilu, s fi ófncgi: Poymnli bumnu fu goylny, yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu. S yh gyxci xymnum xim wimum fy jomy gúm xy nlymwcyhnum ufgum, s pcxum, s idim gćim.
Wujćnofi 30: Koy nlunu xy fu xcmwlywcíh xy fu bylgimu Xilinyu, wih inlum wimum xy gowbi aomni s jumuncygji
Hi bovi vcyh uwuvuxi yf wolu, wouhxi Muhwbi xcdi:
-Joym gću zy, myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi, yf koy bcti ymu zutuh̃u zoy gc ugi, s hi jilkoy si hi fy xcdy uhnym s fy upcmý koy gclumy fi koy buwću, koy ylu jywuxi xulfym fcvylnux, jilkoy nixim cvuh uffć jil aluhxćmcgim vyffuwim.
-Guduxyli -xcdi u ymnu mutíh xih Kocdiny-, u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym hi fym niwu hc unuh̃y upylcaoul mc fim uzfcacxim, yhwuxyhuxim s ijlymim koy yhwoyhnluh jil fim wugchim puh xy ukoyffu guhylu i ymnúh yh ukoyffu uhaomncu, jil mom wofjum, i jil mom xymaluwcum; mífi fy niwu usoxulfym wigi u gyhymnylimim, jihcyhxi fim idim yh mom jyhum, s hi yh mom vyffukoylćum. Si nijý oh limulci s mulnu xy ayhny gibćhu s xymxcwbuxu, s bcwy wih yffim fi koy gc lyfcacíh gy jcxy, s fi xygúm uffú my upyhau; s u kocyh guf fy bu julywcxi, mufpi fu muhnu xcahcxux xyf myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi s mo bihluxu jylmihu, xcai koy muvy jiwi xy uwbukoy xy wuvuffylću, s koy gcyhny wigi oh bcxyjonu s guf huwcxi; s ymni fy bulý wihiwyl wih gc ymjuxu, xihxy gúm fulaugyhny my wihncyhy.
S ymni xcdi uzclgúhximy yh fim ymnlcvim s wufúhximy yf gillcíh; jilkoy fu vuwću xy vulvyli, koy u mo woyhnu ylu yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, ffypuvu wifauxu xyf ultíh xyfuhnyli, bumnu uxivulću xyf guf nlunugcyhni koy fu bcwcylih fim aufyinym.
Xilinyu, koy ylu xcmwlynu s xy aluh xihucly, wigi kocyh su muvću yf gyhaouxi bogil xy xih Kocdiny s koy nixim buwćuh volfu xýf, mchi Muhwbi Juhtu, hi kocmi myl julu gyhim, s pcýhxify nuh yhiduxi, fy xcdi:
-Myh̃il wuvuffyli, gcýgvlymyfy u fu poymnlu gylwyx yf xih koy gy ncyhy jligyncxi, s koy, wihzilgy u ýf, hi joyxy yhnlygynylmy yh inlu upyhnolu, jil olayhny koy myu; mimcyaoy poymnlu gylwyx yf jywbi, koy mc yf myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi mojcylu koy jil ymy chpcwni vluti buvćuh mcxi fcvluxim fim aufyinym, ýf my xcylu nlym johnim yh fu viwu, s uoh my gilxcylu nlym pywym fu fyhaou, uhnym koy buvyl xcwbi jufuvlu koy yh xymjywbi xy poymnlu gylwyx lyxohxulu.
-Ymi doli si vcyh -xcdi yf wolu-, s uoh gy bovcylu kocnuxi oh vcainy.
-Si wuffulý, myh̃ilu gću -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s lyjlcgclý fu domnu wífylu koy su yh gc jywbi my buvću fypuhnuxi, s clý kocyni s juwćzcwi bumnu nuhni koy im wogjfu yf xih jligyncxi; jyli, yh juai xymny voyh xymyi, im mojfcwi gy xcaúcm, mc hi im buwy xy guf, woúf ym fu poymnlu wocnu, s woúhnum, kocýhym s woúfym mih fum jylmihum xy kocyh im nyhai xy xul xyvcxu, muncmzywbu s yhnylu pyhauhtu.
-Ymi bulý si xy auhu -lymjihxcí Xilinyu-, mc ym koy hi im yhzuxu ićl fúmncgum s xymaluwcum.
-Hi yhzuxulú, myh̃ilu gću -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny. U fi koy lymjihxcí Xilinyu:
-Joym umć ym, ymnýhgy poymnlum gylwyxym unyhnim.
Hi bovi yffu xcwbi ymni, wouhxi Wulxyhci s yf vulvyli my fy jomcylih uf fuxi, xymyimim xy pyl wígi zchaću mo bcmnilcu fu xcmwlynu Xilinyu, s fi gcmgi bcti Muhwbi, koy nuh yhauh̃uxi cvu wih yffu wigi mo ugi. S yffu, xymjoým xy buvylmy joymni vcyh yh fu mcffu s jlypyhćximy wih nimyl s buwyl inlim uxyguhym, wih gowbi xihucly wigyhtí u xywcl xymnu guhylu:
-Jlcgylugyhny, kocyli koy poymnlum gylwyxym myjuh, myh̃ilym gćim, koy u gc gy ffuguh...
S xynópimy ukoć oh jiwi jilkoy my fy ifpcxí yf higvly koy yf wolu fy buvću joymni; jyli ýf uwoxcí uf lygyxci, jilkoy yhnyhxcí yh fi koy lyjuluvu, s xcdi:
-Hi ym gulupcffu, myh̃ilu gću, koy fu poymnlu aluhxytu my nolvy s ygjuwby wihnuhxi mom xympyhnolum; koy yffum moyfyh myl nufym, koy gowbum pywym kocnuh fu gygilcu u fim koy gufnlunuh, xy nuf guhylu, koy uoh xy mom gymgim higvlym hi my fym uwoylxu, wigi buh bywbi wih poymnlu aluh myh̃ilću, koy my bu ifpcxuxi koy my ffugu fu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu, fyaćncgu bylyxylu xyf aluh lychi Gcwigcwíh; s wih ymny ujohnugcyhni joyxy fu poymnlu aluhxytu lyxowcl ubilu zúwcfgyhny u mo fumncguxu gygilcu nixi ukoyffi koy wihnul kocmcyly.
-Umć ym fu pylxux -lymjihxcí fu xihwyffu-, s xymxy ukoć uxyfuhny wlyi koy hi mylú gyhymnyl ujohnulgy huxu; koy si mufxlý u voyh joyxi wih gc pylxuxylu bcmnilcu. Fu wouf ym koy yf lys gc juxly, koy my ffuguvu Nchuwlci yf Muvcxil, zoy gos xiwni yh ymni koy ffuguh yf ulny gúacwu, s ufwuhtí jil mo wcyhwcu koy gc guxly, koy my ffuguvu fu lychu Dulugcffu, buvću xy gilcl jlcgyli koy ýf, s koy xy uffć u jiwi ncygji ýf nugvcýh buvću xy jumul xymnu pcxu s si buvću xy koyxul boýlzuhu xy juxly s guxly. Jyli xywću ýf koy hi fy zuncauvu nuhni ymni wouhni fy jihću yh wihzomcíh muvyl jil wimu gos wcylnu koy oh xymwigohuf acauhny, myh̃il xy ohu aluhxy ćhmofu, koy wumc ufchxu wih hoymnli lychi, ffuguxi Juhxuzcfuhxi xy fu Zimwu Pcmnu (jilkoy ym wimu upylcaouxu koy, uohkoy ncyhy fim idim yh mo foaul s xylywbim, mcygjly gclu uf lypým, wigi mc zoymy vctwi, s ymni fi buwy ýf xy gufcahi s jil jihyl gcyxi s ymjuhni u fim koy gclu), xcai koy moji koy ymny acauhny, yh muvcyhxi gc ilzuhxux, buvću xy jumul wih aluh jixylći mivly gc lychi, s gy fi buvću xy kocnul nixi, mch xydulgy ohu jykoyh̃u ufxyu xihxy gy lywiacymy; jyli koy jixću yrwomul nixu ymnu lonchu s xymaluwcu mc si gy kocmcymy wumul wih ýf; gum, u fi koy ýf yhnyhxću, dugúm jyhmuvu koy gy pyhxlću u gc yh pifohnux xy buwyl nuh xymcaouf wumugcyhni; s xcdi yh ymni fu jolu pylxux, jilkoy dugúm gy bu jumuxi jil yf jyhmugcyhni wumulgy wih ukoyf acauhny, jyli hc wih inli ufaohi, jil aluhxy s xymuziluxi koy zoymy. Xcdi nugvcýh gc juxly koy xymjoým koy ýf zoymy goylni s pcymy si koy Juhxuzcfuhxi wigyhtuvu u jumul mivly gc lychi, koy hi uaoulxumy u jihylgy yh xyzyhmu, jilkoy mylcu xymnloclgy, mchi koy fcvlygyhny fy xydumy xymygvulutuxi yf lychi, mc koylću yrwomul fu goylny s ninuf xymnlocwcíh xy gcm voyhim s fyufym pumuffim, jilkoy hi buvću xy myl jimcvfy xyzyhxylgy xy fu yhxcuvfuxu zoyltu xyf acauhny; mchi koy foyai, wih ufaohim xy fim gćim, gy jomcymy yh wugchi xy fum Ymjuh̃um, xihxy buffulću yf lygyxci xy gcm gufym buffuhxi u oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny, wosu zugu yh ymny ncygji my yrnyhxylću jil nixi ymny lychi; yf wouf my buvću xy ffugul, mc guf hi gy uwoylxi, xih Utiny i xih Acainy.
-Xih Kocdiny xclću, myh̃ilu -xcdi u ymnu mutíh Muhwbi Juhtu-, i, jil inli higvly, yf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu.
-Umć ym fu pylxux -xcdi Xilinyu-. Xcdi gúm: koy buvću xy myl ufni xy woylji, mywi xy limnli, s koy yh yf fuxi xylywbi, xyvudi xyf bigvli ctkocylxi, i jil uffć dohni, buvću xy nyhyl oh fohul julxi wih wcylnim wuvyffim u guhylu xy wylxum.
Yh isyhxi ymni xih Kocdiny, xcdi u mo ymwoxyli:
-Nyh ukoć, Muhwbi, bcdi, usóxugy u xymhoxul, koy kocyli pyl mc mis yf wuvuffyli koy ukoyf muvci lys xydí jlizynctuxi.
-Joym ¿julu koý kocyly poymnlu gylwyx xymhoxulmy? -xcdi Xilinyu.
-Julu pyl mc nyhai ymy fohul koy poymnli juxly xcdi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
-Hi bus julu koý xymhoxulmy -xcdi Muhwbi-; koy si mý koy ncyhy poymnlu gylwyx oh fohul xymum myh̃um yh fu gcnux xyf ymjchuti, koy ym myh̃uf xy myl bigvly zoylny.
-Ymi vumnu -xcdi Xilinyu-; jilkoy wih fim ugcaim hi my bu xy gclul yh jiwum wimum s koy ymný yh yf bigvli, i koy ymný yh yf ymjchuti, cgjilnu jiwi: vumnu koy busu fohul, s ymný xihxy ymnopcyly, joym nixi ym ohu gymgu wulhy; s, mch xoxu, uwylní gc voyh juxly yh nixi, s si by uwylnuxi yh yhwigyhxulgy uf myh̃il xih Kocdiny; koy ýf ym jil kocyh gc juxly xcdi, joym fum myh̃ufym xyf limnli pcyhyh wih fum xy fu voyhu zugu koy ymny wuvuffyli ncyhy, hi mífi yh Ymjuh̃u, jyli yh nixu fu Guhwbu, joym ujyhum gy bovy xymygvulwuxi yh Imohu, wouhxi ić xywcl nuhnum butuh̃um mosum, koy foyai gy xci yf ufgu koy ylu yf gymgi koy pyhću u vomwul.
-Joym ¿wígi my xymygvulwí poymnlu gylwyx yh Imohu, myh̃ilu gću -jlyaohní xih Kocdiny-, mc hi ym joylni xy gul?
Gum uhnym koy Xilinyu lymjihxcymy, nigí yf wolu fu guhi, s xcdi:
-Xyvy xy koylyl xywcl fu myh̃ilu jlchwymu koy xymjoým koy xymygvulwí yh Gúfuau, fu jlcgylu julny xihxy isí hoypum xy poymnlu gylwyx zoy yh Imohu.
-Ymi kocmy xywcl -xcdi Xilinyu.
-S ymni ffypu wugchi -xcdi yf wolu-; s jlimcau poymnlu Gudymnux uxyfuhny.
-Hi bus koy jlimyaocl -lymjihxcí Xilinyu-, mchi koy, zchufgyhny, gc moylny bu mcxi nuh voyhu yh bufful uf myh̃il xih Kocdiny, koy su gy woyhni s nyhai jil lychu s myh̃ilu xy nixi gc lychi, joym ýf, jil mo wilnymću s guahczcwyhwcu, gy bu jligyncxi yf xih xy clmy wihgcai xihxykocylu koy si fy ffypuly, koy hi mylú u inlu julny koy u jihylfy xyfuhny xy Juhxuzcfuhxi xy fu Zimwu Pcmnu, julu koy fy guny, s gy lymncnosu fi koy nuh wihnlu lutíh gy ncyhy omoljuxi; koy nixi ymni bu xy mowyxyl u jyxcl xy viwu, joym umć fi xydí jlizynctuxi Nchuwlci yf Muvcxil, gc voyh juxly; yf wouf nugvcýh xydí xcwbi, s ymwlcni yh fynlum wufxyum i alcyaum, koy si hi fum mý fyyl, koy mc ymny wuvuffyli xy fu jlizywću, xymjoým xy buvyl xyaiffuxi uf acauhny, kocmcymy wumulmy wihgcai, koy si gy inilaulmy foyai mch lýjfcwu ufaohu jil mo fyaćncgu ymjimu, s fy xcymy fu jimymcíh xy gc lychi, dohni wih fu xy gc jylmihu.
-¿Koý ny julywy, Muhwbi ugcai? -xcdi u ymny johni xih Kocdiny-. ¿Hi isym fi koy jumu? ¿Hi ny fi xcdy si? Gclu mc nyhygim su lychi koy guhxul s lychu wih kocyh wumul .
-¡Ymi doli si -xcdi Muhwbi- julu yf joni koy hi my wumuly yh uvlcyhxi yf authuncwi uf myh̃il Juhxubcfuxi! Joym ¡gihnu koy ym gufu fu lychu! ¡Umć my gy poyfpuh fum jofaum xy fu wugu!
S xcwcyhxi ymni, xci xim tujunynum yh yf ucly, wih goymnlum xy aluhxćmcgi wihnyhni, s foyai zoy u nigul fum lcyhxum xy fu goću xy Xilinyu, s buwcýhxifu xynyhyl, my bchwí xy lixcffum uhny yffu, mojfcwúhxify fy xcymy fum guhim julu vymúlmyfum, yh myh̃uf koy fu lywcvću jil mo lychu s myh̃ilu. ¿Kocýh hi buvću xy lyćl xy fim wclwohmnuhnym, pcyhxi fu fiwolu xyf ugi s fu mcgjfcwcxux xyf wlcuxi? Yh yzywni, Xilinyu my fum xci, s fy jligyncí xy buwylfy aluh myh̃il yh mo lychi, wouhxi yf wcyfi fy bcwcymy nuhni vcyh, koy my fi xydumy wivlul s aitul. Ualuxywcímyfi Muhwbi wih nufym jufuvlum, koy lyhipí fu lcmu yh nixim.
-Ymnu, myh̃ilym -jlimcaocí Xilinyu-, ym gc bcmnilcu; mífi lymnu jil xywclim koy xy wouhnu ayhny xy uwigjuh̃ugcyhni mukoý xy gc lychi hi gy bu koyxuxi mchi mífi ymny voyh vulvuxi ymwoxyli, jilkoy nixim my uhyaulih yh ohu aluh villumwu koy nopcgim u pcmnu xyf joylni, s ýf s si mufcgim yh xim nuvfum u ncyllu, wigi jil gcfuali; s umć, ym nixi gcfuali s gcmnylci yf xcmwolmi xy gc pcxu, wigi fi buvlýcm hinuxi. S mc yh ufaohu wimu by uhxuxi xygumcuxu, i hi nuh uwylnuxu wigi xyvcylu, ywbux fu wofju u fi koy yf myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi xcdi uf jlchwcjci xy gc woyhni: koy fim nluvudim wihnchoim s yrnluilxchulcim kocnuh fu gygilcu uf koy fim juxywy.
-Ymu hi gy kocnulúh u gc, ¡ib ufnu s pufylimu myh̃ilu! -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, wouhnim si jumuly yh mylpclim, jil aluhxym s hi pcmnim koy myuh; s umć, xy hoypi wihzclgi yf xih koy im by jligyncxi s doli xy cl wih pim uf wuvi xyf gohxi, bumnu sylgy wih yf zcyli yhygcai poymnli, u kocyh jcyhmi, wih fu usoxu xy Xcim s xy gc vluti, nudul fu wuvytu mivylvcu wih fim zcfim xymnu... hi kocyli xywcl voyhu ymjuxu, gylwyx u Achým xy Jumugihny, koy gy ffypí fu gću.
Ymni xcdi yhnly xcyhnym, s jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi:
