-Nixi pu vcyh bumnu uailu -xcdi xih Kocdiny-. Jyli xcgy: ¿koý disu zoy fu koy ny xci uf xymjyxclny, jil fum hoypum koy xy gć fy ffypumny? Jilkoy ym omuxu s uhncaou wimnogvly yhnly fim wuvuffylim s xugum uhxuhnym xul u fim ymwoxylim, xihwyffum i yhuhim koy fym ffypuh hoypum, xy mom xugum u yffim, u yffum xy mom uhxuhnym, ufaohu lcwu disu yh ufvlcwcum, yh ualuxywcgcyhni xy mo lywuxi.
-Vcyh joyxy ymi myl umć, s si fu nyhai jil voyhu omuhtu; jyli ymi xyvcí xy myl yh fim ncygjim jumuxim; koy ubilu mífi my xyvy xy uwimnogvlul u xul oh jyxuti xy juh s koymi, koy ymni zoy fi koy gy xci gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, jil fum vulxum xy oh willuf, wouhxi xyffu gy xymjyxć: s uoh jil gúm myh̃um, ylu yf koymi ipydohi.
-Ym fcvyluf yh yrnlygi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; s mc hi ny xci disu xy ili, mch xoxu xyvcí xy myl jilkoy hi fu nyhxlću uffć u fu guhi julu xúlnyfu; jyli voyhum mih guhaum xymjoým xy Jumwou: si fu pylý, s my muncmzulú nixi. ¿Muvym xy koý ymnis gulupcffuxi, Muhwbi? Xy koy gy julywy koy zocmny s pyhcmny jil fim uclym, joym jiwi gúm xy nlym xćum bum nulxuxi yh cl s pyhcl xymxy ukoć uf Nivimi, buvcyhxi xy ukoć uffú gúm xy nlychnu fyaoum; jil fi wouf gy xis u yhnyhxyl koy ukoyf muvci
hcaliguhny koy ncyhy woyhnu wih gcm wimum s ym gc ugcai (jilkoy jil zoyltu fy bus, s fy bu xy buvyl, mi jyhu koy si hi mylću voyh wuvuffyli uhxuhny), xcai koy ýmny nuf ny xyvcí xy usoxul u wugchul, mch koy nó fi mchncymym; koy bus muvci xymnim koy wiay u oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny xolgcyhxi yh mo wugu, s mch muvyl wígi i yh koý guhylu, uguhywy inli xću gúm xy gcf fyaoum xy xihxy uhiwbywcí. S mc hi zoymy jil ymni, hi my jixlćuh miwillyl yh mom jyfcalim fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ohim u inlim, wigi my miwillyh u wuxu jumi; koy uwuywy ymnul ohi jyfyuhxi yh fum mcyllum xy Ulgyhcu wih ufaóh yhxlcuai, i wih ufaóh zcyli pymncaci, i wih inli wuvuffyli, xihxy ffypu fi jyil xy fu vunuffu s ymnú su u johni xy goylny, s wouhxi hi im gy wuni, umigu jil uwoffú, yhwcgu xy ohu hovy, i mivly oh wulli xy zoyai, inli wuvuffyli ugcai mosi, koy jiwi uhnym my buffuvu yh Chaufunyllu, koy fy zupilywy s fcvlu xy fu goylny, s u fu hiwby my buffu yh mo jimuxu, wyhuhxi gos u mo muvil; s moyfy buvyl xy fu ohu u fu inlu julny xim i nlym gcf fyaoum. S nixi ymni my buwy jil chxomnlcu s muvcxolću xymnim muvcim yhwuhnuxilym koy ncyhyh wocxuxi xymnim pufylimim wuvuffylim. Umć koy, ugcai Muhwbi, hi my gy buwy xczcwofnimi wlyyl koy yh nuh vlypy ncygji busum cxi s pyhcxi xymxy ymny foaul uf xyf Nivimi, joym, wigi nyhai xcwbi, ufaóh muvci ugcai ny xyvcí xy ffypul yh pifuhxcffum, mch koy nó fi mchncymym.
-Umć mylcu -xcdi Muhwbi-; jilkoy u voyhu zy koy uhxuvu Liwchuhny wigi mc zoylu umhi xy acnuhi wih utiaoy yh fim ićxim.
-S ¡wígi mc ffypuvu utiaoy! -xcdi xih Kocdiny-. S uoh ohu fyacíh xy xygihcim, koy ym ayhny koy wugchu s buwy wugchul, mch wuhmulmy, nixi ukoyffi koy my fym uhnidu. Jyli, xyduhxi ymni ujulny, ¿koý ny julywy u nc koy xyvi si xy buwyl ubilu wylwu xy fi koy gc myh̃ilu gy guhxu koy fu pusu u pyl? Koy, uohkoy si pyi koy ymnis ivfcauxi u wogjfcl mo guhxugcyhni, pýigy nugvcýh cgjimcvcfcnuxi xyf xih koy by jligyncxi u fu jlchwymu koy wih piminlim pcyhy, s zoýltugy fu fys xy wuvuffylću u wogjfcl gc jufuvlu uhnym koy gc aomni. Jil ohu julny, gy uwimu s zuncau yf xymyi xy pyl u gc myh̃ilu; jil inlu, gy chwcnu s ffugu fu jligyncxu zy, s fu afilcu koy by xy ufwuhtul yh ymnu ygjlymu. Jyli fi koy jcyhmi buwyl mylú wugchul ujlcymu s ffyaul jlymni xihxy ymnú ymny acauhny, s yh ffyauhxi, fy wilnulý fu wuvytu, s jihxlý u fu jlchwymu juwćzcwugyhny yh mo ymnuxi, s uf johni xulý fu poyfnu u pyl u fu fot koy gcm myhncxim ufogvlu, u fu wouf xulý nufym xcmwofjum, koy yffu pyhau u nyhyl jil voyhu gc nulxuhtu, joym pylú koy nixi lyxohxu yh uogyhni xy mo afilcu s zugu, joym wouhnu si by ufwuhtuxi, ufwuhti s ufwuhtulý jil fum ulgum yh ymnu pcxu, nixu gy pcyhy xyf zupil koy yffu gy xu s xy myl si mosi.
-¡Us -xcdi Muhwbi-, s wígi ymnú poymnlu gylwyx fumncguxi xy ymim wumwim! Joym xcaugy, myh̃il: ¿jcyhmu poymnlu gylwyx wugchul ymny wugchi yh vufxy, s xydul jumul s jylxyl oh nuh lcwi s nuh jlchwcjuf wumugcyhni wigi ymny, xihxy fy xuh yh xiny oh lychi, koy u voyhu pylxux koy by ićxi xywcl koy ncyhy gúm xy pychny gcf fyaoum xy wihnilhi, s koy ym uvohxuhnćmcgi xy nixum fum wimum koy mih hywymulcum julu yf momnyhni xy fu pcxu boguhu, s koy ym gusil koy Jilnoauf s koy Wumncffu dohnim? Wuffy, jil ugil xy Xcim, s nyhau pylaöyhtu xy fi koy bu xcwbi, s nigy gc wihmydi, s jylxíhygy, s wúmymy foyai yh yf jlcgyl foaul koy busu wolu; s mc hi, ubć ymnú hoymnli fcwyhwcuxi, koy fi bulú xy jylfum. S uxpcylnu koy su nyhai yxux julu xul wihmydim, s koy ýmny koy fy xis fy pcyhy xy gifxy, s koy gúm pufy júduli yh guhi koy vocnly pifuhxi, jilkoy kocyh vcyh ncyhy s guf ymwiay, jil vcyh koy my yhidu hi my pyhau.
-Gclu, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; mc yf wihmydi koy gy xum xy koy gy wumy ym jilkoy myu foyai lys yh gunuhxi uf acauhny, s nyhau wígixi julu buwylny gylwyxym s xulny fi jligyncxi, búainy muvyl koy mch wumulgy jixlý wogjfcl no xymyi gos zúwcfgyhny; jilkoy si muwulý xy uxubufu, uhnym xy yhnlul yh fu vunuffu, koy, mufcyhxi pyhwyxil xyffu, su koy hi gy wumy, gy buh xy xul ohu julny xyf lychi, julu koy fu joyxu xul u kocyh si kocmcyly; s yh xúhxigyfu, ¿u kocýh kocylym nó koy fu xý mchi u nc?
-Ymi ymnú wfuli -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; jyli gcly poymnlu gylwyx koy fu ymwidu buwcu fu gulchu, jilkoy, mc hi gy wihnyhnuly fu pcpcyhxu, joyxu ygvulwul gcm hyalim pumuffim s buwyl xyffim fi koy su by xcwbi. S poymnlu gylwyx hi my woly xy cl jil uailu u pyl u gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, mchi púsumy u gunul uf acauhny, s wihwfosugim ymny hyaiwci; koy jil Xcim koy my gy umcyhnu koy bu xy myl xy gowbu bihlu s xy gowbi jlipywbi.
-Xćainy, Muhwbi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, koy ymnúm yh fi wcylni, s koy buvlý xy nigul no wihmydi yh wouhni yf cl uhnym wih fu jlchwymu koy u pyl u Xofwchyu. S upcminy koy hi xcaum huxu u huxcy, hc u fim koy wih himinlim pcyhyh, xy fi koy ukoć bygim xyjulncxi s nlunuxi; koy joym Xofwchyu ym nuh lywunuxu, koy hi kocyly koy my myjuh mom jyhmugcyhnim, hi mylú vcyh koy si, hc inli jil gc, fim xymwovlu.
-Joym mc ymi ym umć -xcdi Muhwbi-, ¿wígi buwy poymnlu gylwyx koy nixim fim koy pyhwy jil mo vluti my pusuh u jlymyhnul uhny gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu, mcyhxi ymni zclgu xy mo higvly koy fu kocyly vcyh s koy ym mo yhugiluxi? S mcyhxi ziltimi koy fim koy zoylyh my buh xy cl u bchwul xy zchidim uhny mo jlymyhwcu, s xywcl koy puh xy julny xy poymnlu gylwyx u xuffy fu ivyxcyhwcu, ¿wígi my joyxyh yhwovlcl fim jyhmugcyhnim xy yhnlugvim?
-¡Ib, koý hywci s koý mcgjfy ylym! –xcdi xih Kocdiny-. ¿Nó hi pym, Muhwbi, koy ymi nixi lyxohxu yh mo gusil yhmuftugcyhni? Jilkoy bum xy muvyl koy yh ymny hoymnli ymncfi xy wuvuffylću ym aluh bihlu nyhyl ohu xugu gowbim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym koy fu mclpuh, mch koy my yrncyhxuh gúm mom jyhmugcyhnim koy u mylpcffu jil mífi myl yffu kocyh ym, mch ymjylul inli jlygci xy mom gowbim s voyhim xymyim mchi koy yffu my wihnyhny xy uwynulfim jil mom wuvuffylim.
-Wih ymu guhylu xy ugil -xcdi Muhwbi- by ićxi si jlyxcwul koy my bu xy ugul u Hoymnli Myh̃il, jil mc mífi, mch koy him goypu ymjyluhtu xy afilcu i nygil xy jyhu. Uohkoy si fy koyllću ugul s mylpcl jil fi koy joxcymy.
-¡Púfuny yf xcuvfi jil pcffuhi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s koý xy xcmwlywcihym xcwym u fum pywym! Hi julywy mchi koy bum ymnoxcuxi.
-Joym u zy gću koy hi mý fyyl –lymjihxcí Muhwbi.
Yh ymni fym xci piwym guymy Hcwifúm koy ymjylumyh oh jiwi; koy koylćuh xynyhylmy u vyvyl yh ohu zihnywcffu koy uffć ymnuvu. Xynópimy xih Kocdiny, wih hi jiwi aomni xy Muhwbi, koy su ymnuvu wuhmuxi xy gyhncl nuhni s nygću hi fy wiacymy mo ugi u jufuvlum; jilkoy, joymni koy ýf muvcu koy Xofwchyu ylu ohu fuvluxilu xyf Nivimi, hi fu buvću pcmni yh nixu mo pcxu.
Buvćumy yh ymny ncygji pymncxi Wulxyhci fim pymncxim koy Xilinyu nluću wouhxi fu buffulih, koy uohkoy hi yluh gos voyhim, buwćuh gowbu pyhnudu u fim koy xyduvu. Ujyúlihmy dohni u fu zoyhny, s wih fi koy yf wolu my uwigixí yh fu pyhnu muncmzcwcylih, uohkoy jiwi, fu gowbu bugvly koy nixim nlućuh.
Ymnuhxi yh ymni, uwylní u jumul jil uffć oh gowbuwbi koy cvu xy wugchi, yf wouf, jihcýhximy u gclul wih gowbu unyhwcíh u fim koy yh fu zoyhny ymnuvuh, xy uffć u jiwi ullygyncí u xih Kocdiny s, uvlutúhxify jil fum jcylhum, wigyhtí u ffilul gos xy jlijímcni, xcwcyhxi:
-¡Us, myh̃il gći! ¿Hi gy wihiwy poymnlu gylwyx? Joym gćlygy vcyh; koy si mis ukoyf giti Uhxlým koy kocní poymnlu gylwyx xy fu yhwchu xihxy ymnuvu unuxi.
Lywihiwcífy xih Kocdiny, s umcýhxify jil fu guhi, my pifpcí u fim koy uffć ymnuvuh, s xcdi:
-Jilkoy pyuh poymnlum gylwyxym woúh xy cgjilnuhwcu ym buvyl wuvuffylim uhxuhnym yh yf gohxi, koy xymzuauh fim noylnim s ualupcim koy yh ýf my buwyh jil fim chmifyhnym s gufim bigvlym koy yh ýf pcpyh, myjuh poymnlum gylwyxym koy fim xćum jumuxim, jumuhxi si jil oh vimkoy, ić ohim alcnim s ohum piwym gos fumncgimum, wigi xy jylmihu uzfcacxu s gyhymnylimu; uwoxć foyai, ffypuxi xy gc ivfcauwcíh, buwcu fu julny xihxy gy julywcí koy fum fugyhnuvfym piwym mihuvuh, s buffý unuxi u ohu yhwchu u ymny gowbuwbi koy ubilu ymnú xyfuhny, xy fi koy gy boyfai yh yf ufgu, jilkoy mylú nymncai koy hi gy xydulú gyhncl yh huxu. Xcai koy ymnuvu unuxi u fu yhwchu, xymhoxi xyf gyxci woylhi ullcvu, s ymnúvufy uvlcyhxi u utinym wih fum lcyhxum xy ohu syaou oh pcffuhi, koy xymjoým mojy koy ylu ugi mosi; s umć wigi si fy pc fy jlyaohný fu wuomu xy nuh unlit pujofugcyhni; lymjihxcí yf tuzci koy fy utinuvu jilkoy ylu mo wlcuxi, s koy wcylnim xymwocxim koy nyhću huwćuh gúm xy fuxlíh koy xy mcgjfy; u fi wouf ymny hch̃i xcdi: «Myh̃il, hi gy utinu mchi jilkoy fy jcxi gc mufulci.» Yf ugi lyjfcwí hi mý koý ulyhaum s xcmwofjum, fum woufym, uohkoy xy gć zoylih ićxum, hi zoylih uxgcncxum. Yh lymifowcíh, si fy bcwy xymunul, s nigý dolugyhni uf pcffuhi xy koy fy ffypulću wihmcai s fy juaulću oh lyuf mivly inli, s uoh muboguxim. ¿Hi ym pylxux nixi ymni, bcdi Uhxlým? ¿Hi hinumny wih woúhni cgjylci my fi guhxý, s wih woúhnu bogcfxux jligyncí xy buwyl nixi wouhni si fy cgjomy s hinczckoý s kocmy? Lymjihxy; hi ny nolvym hc xoxym yh huxu; xc fi koy jumí u ymnim myh̃ilym, jilkoy my pyu s wihmcxyly myl xyf jlipywbi koy xcai buvyl wuvuffylim uhxuhnym jil fim wugchim.
-Nixi fi koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi ym gowbu pylxux -lymjihxcí yf gowbuwbi-; jyli yf zch xyf hyaiwci mowyxcí gos uf lypým xy fi koy poymnlu gylwyx my cguachu.
-¿Wígi uf lypým? -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-.Foyai ¿hi ny juaí yf pcffuhi?
-Hi mífi hi gy juaí -lymjihxcí yf gowbuwbi-, jyli umć wigi poymnlu gylwyx nlumjomi xyf vimkoy s koyxugim mifim, gy pifpcí u unul u fu gymgu yhwchu s gy xci xy hoypi nuhnim utinym, koy koyxý bywbi oh Muh Vulnifigý xymiffuxi; s u wuxu utiny koy gy xuvu, gy xywću oh xihucly s wbozynu uwylwu xy buwyl volfu xy poymnlu gylwyx, koy, u hi myhncl si nuhni xifil, gy lcylu xy fi koy xywću. Yh yzywni, ýf gy julí nuf, koy bumnu ubilu by ymnuxi wolúhxigy yh oh bimjcnuf xyf guf koy yf guf pcffuhi yhnihwym gy bcti. Xy nixi fi wouf ncyhy poymnlu gylwyx fu wofju; jilkoy mc my zoylu mo wugchi uxyfuhny s hi pchcylu xihxy hi fy ffuguvuh, hc my yhnlygyncylu yh hyaiwcim udyhim, gc ugi my wihnyhnulu wih xulgy ohu i xim xiwyhum xy utinym, s foyai gy mifnulu s juaulu wouhni gy xyvću. Gum wigi poymnlu gylwyx fy xymbihlí nuh mch jlijímcni, s fy xcdi nuhnum pcffuhćum, yhwyhxcímyfy fu wífylu, s wigi hi fi joxi pyhaul yh poymnlu gylwyx, wouhxi my pci mifi xymwulaí mivly gć yf hovfuxi, xy gixi, koy gy julywy koy hi mylý gúm bigvly yh nixu gc pcxu.
-Yf xuh̃i ymnopi -xcdi xih Kocdiny- yh clgy si xy uffć, koy hi gy buvću xy cl bumnu xydulny juauxi; jilkoy vcyh xyvću si xy muvyl, jil foyhaum yrjylcyhwcum, koy hi bus pcffuhi koy aoulxy jufuvlu koy xcyly, mc ýf pyy koy hi fy ymnú vcyh aoulxuffu. Jyli su ny uwoylxum, Uhxlým, koy si dolý koy mc hi ny juauvu, koy buvću xy cl u vomwulfy, s koy fy buvću xy bufful, uohkoy my ymwihxcymy yh yf pcyhnly xy fu vuffyhu.
-Umć ym fu pylxux -xcdi Uhxlým-; jyli hi ujlipywbí huxu. -Ubilu pylúm mc ujlipywbu -xcdi xih Kocdiny.
S xcwcyhxi ymni, my fypuhní gos ujlcymu s guhxí u Muhwbi koy yhzlyhumy u Liwchuhny, koy ymnuvu juwcyhxi yh nuhni koy yffim wigćuh.
Jlyaohnífy Xilinyu koý ylu fi koy buwyl koylću. Yf fy lymjihxcí koy koylću cl u vomwul uf pcffuhi s wumncauffy xy nuh guf nýlgchi, s buwyl juauxi u Uhxlým bumnu yf ófncgi gulupyxć, u xymjywbi s jymul xy wouhnim pcffuhim bovcymy yh yf gohxi; u fi koy yffu lymjihxcí koy uxpclncymy koy hi jixću, wihzilgy uf xih jligyncxi, yhnlygynylmy yh hchaohu ygjlymu bumnu uwuvul fu mosu; s koy joym ymni muvću ýf gydil koy inli ufaohi, koy mimyaumy yf jywbi bumnu fu poyfnu xy mo lychi.
-Umć ym pylxux -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-,s ym ziltimi koy Uhxlým nyhau juwcyhwcu bumnu fu poyfnu, wigi pim, myh̃ilu, xywćm; koy si fy nilhi u dolul s u jligynyl xy hoypi xy hi julul bumnu buwylfy pyhauxi s juauxi.
-Hi gy wlyi xymim dolugyhnim -xcdi Uhxlým-; gúm kocmcylu nyhyl uailu wih koy ffyaul u Mypcffu koy nixum fum pyhauhtum xyf gohxi: xýgy, mc ncyhy ubć, ufai koy wigu s ffypy, s koýxymy wih Xcim mo gylwyx s nixim fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, koy nuh vcyh uhxuhnym myuh yffim julu wihmcai wigi fi buh mcxi julu wihgcai.
Muwí xy mo lyjoymni Muhwbi oh jyxuti xy juh s inli xy koymi, s xúhximyfi uf giti, fy xcdi:
-Nigu, bylguhi Uhxlým, koy u nixim him ufwuhtu julny xy poymnlu xymaluwcu. -Joym ¿koý julny im ufwuhtu u pim? -jlyaohní Uhxlým.
-Ymnu julny xy koymi s juh koy im xis -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, koy Xcim muvy mc gy bu xy buwyl zufnu i hi; jilkoy im buai muvyl, ugcai, koy fim ymwoxylim xy fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ymnugim modynim u gowbu bugvly s u gufu pyhnolu, s uoh u inlum wimum koy my mcyhnyh gydil koy my xcwyh.
Uhxlým umcí xy mo juh s koymi s, pcyhxi koy huxcy fy xuvu inlu wimu, uvudí mo wuvytu s nigí yf wugchi yh fum guhim, wigi moyfy xywclmy. Vcyh ym pylxux koy, uf julnclmy, xcdi u xih Kocdiny:
-Jil ugil xy Xcim, myh̃il wuvuffyli uhxuhny, koy mc inlu pyt gy yhwihnluly, uohkoy pyu koy gy buwyh jyxutim, hi gy miwillu hc usoxy, mchi xýdygy wih gc xymaluwcu; koy hi mylú nuhnu, koy hi myu gusil fu koy gy pyhxlú xy mo usoxu xy poymnlu gylwyx, u kocyh Xcim gufxcau, s u nixim wouhnim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym buh huwcxi yh yf gohxi.
Cvumy u fypuhnul xih Kocdiny julu wumncauffy; gum ýf my jomi u willyl xy gixi koy hchaohi my unlypcí u myaocffy. Koyxí willcxćmcgi xih Kocdiny xyf woyhni xy Uhxlým, s zoy gyhymnyl koy fim xygúm nopcymyh gowbu woyhnu wih hi lyćlmy, jil hi uwuvuffy xy willyl xyf nixi.
Wujćnofi 32: Koy nlunu xy fi koy mowyxcí yh fu pyhnu u nixu fu wouxlcffu xy xih Kocdiny
Uwuvímy fu voyhu wigcxu, yhmcffulih foyai s, mch koy fym mowyxcymy wimu xcahu xy wihnul, ffyaulih inli xću u fu pyhnu, ymjuhni s umigvli xy Muhwbi Juhtu; s uohkoy ýf kocmcylu hi yhnlul yh yffu, hi fi joxi bocl. Fu pyhnylu, pyhnyli, mo bcdu s Gulcnilhym, koy pcylih pyhcl u xih Kocdiny s u Muhwbi, fym mufcylih u lywyvcl wih goymnlum xy gowbu ufyalću, s ýf fum lywcvcí wih alupy wihnchyhny s ujfuomi; s xcdifym koy fy uxylytumyh inli gydil fywbi koy fu pyt jumuxu; u fi wouf fy lymjihxcí fu boýmjyxu koy wigi fu juaumy gydil koy fu inlu pyt, koy yffu my fu xulću xy jlćhwcjym. Xih Kocdiny xcdi koy mć bulću, s umć, fy uxylytulih ohi lutihuvfy yh yf gcmgi wuluguhwbíh xy gullum, s ýf my uwimní foyai, jilkoy pyhću gos koyvluhnuxi s zufni xy docwci.
Hi my bovi vcyh yhwylluxi wouhxi fu boýmjyxu ullygyncí uf vulvyli, s umcýhxify xy fu vulvu, xcdi:
-Julu gc muhncaouxu koy hi my bu uóh xy ujlipywbul gúm xy gc luvi julu mo vulvu, s koy gy bu xy pifpyl gc wifu; koy uhxu fi xy gc gulcxi jil ymim moyfim, koy ym pylaöyhtu; xcai, yf jychy, koy mifću si wifaul xy gc voyhu wifu.
Hi my fu koylću xul yf vulvyli, uohkoy yffu gúm ncluvu, bumnu koy yf fcwyhwcuxi fy xcdi koy my fu xcymy; koy su hi ylu gyhymnyl gúm omul xy ukoyffu chxomnlcu, mchi koy my xymwovlcymy s gimnlumy yh mo gcmgu zilgu, s xcdymy u xih Kocdiny koy wouhxi fy xymjidulih fim fuxlihym aufyinym my buvću pyhcxi u ukoyffu pyhnu bosyhxi; s koy mc jlyaohnumy jil yf ymwoxyli xy fu jlchwymu, fy xclćuh koy yffu fy buvću yhpcuxi uxyfuhny u xul upcmi u fim xy mo lychi wígi yffu cvu s ffypuvu wihmcai yf fcvylnuxil xy nixim. Wih ymni xci xy voyhu auhu fu wifu u fu pyhnylu yf vulvyli, s umcgcmgi fy pifpcylih nixim fim uxbylyhnym koy buvću jlymnuxi julu fu fcvylnux xy xih Kocdiny. Ymjuhnúlihmy nixim fim xy fu pyhnu xy fu bylgimolu xy Xilinyu, s uoh xyf voyh nuffy xyf tuauf Wulxyhci. Bcti yf wolu koy fym uxylytumyh xy wigyl xy fi koy yh fu pyhnu bovcymy, s yf boýmjyx, wih ymjyluhtu xy gydil juau, wih xcfcayhwcu fym uxylytí ohu lutihuvfy wigcxu; s u nixi ymni xilgću xih Kocdiny, s zoylih xy julywyl xy hi xymjylnuffy, jilkoy gúm jlipywbi fy bulću jil yhnihwym yf xilgcl koy yf wigyl. Nlunulih mivly wigcxu, ymnuhxi xyfuhny yf pyhnyli, mo godyl, mo bcdu, Gulcnilhym s nixim fim jumudylim, xy fu yrnluh̃u fiwolu xy xih Kocdiny s xyf gixi koy fy buvćuh buffuxi. Fu boýmjyxu fym wihní fi koy wih ýf s wih yf bullcyli fym buvću uwihnywcxi, s gcluhxi mc uwumi ymnuvu uffć Muhwbi, wigi hi fy pcymy, wihní nixi fi xy mo guhnyugcyhni, xy koy hi jiwi aomni lywcvcylih. S wigi yf wolu xcdymy koy fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum koy xih Kocdiny buvću fyćxi fy buvćuh poyfni yf docwci, xcdi yf pyhnyli:
-Hi mý si wígi joyxy myl ymi; koy yh pylxux koy, u fi koy si yhncyhxi, hi bus gydil fynluxi yh yf gohxi, s koy nyhai ubć xim i nlym xyffim, wih inlim jujyfym, koy pylxuxylugyhny gy buh xuxi fu pcxu, hi mífi u gć, mchi u inlim gowbim;
jilkoy wouhxi ym ncygji xy fu mcyau, my lywiayh ukoć fum zcymnum gowbim myauxilym, s mcygjly bus ufaohi koy muvy fyyl, yf wouf wiay ohi xymnim fcvlim yh fum guhim, s lixyúgihim xýf gúm xy nlychnu, s ymnúgimfy ymwowbuhxi wih nuhni aomni, koy him kocnu gcf wuhum; u fi gyhim, xy gć mý xywcl koy wouhxi isí xywcl ukoyffim zolcvohxim s nyllcvfym aifjym koy fim wuvuffylim jyauh, koy gy nigu auhu xy buwyl inli nuhni, s koy koyllću ymnul isýhxifim hiwbym s xćum.
-S si hc gúm hc gyhim -xcdi fu pyhnylu-; jilkoy hohwu nyhai voyh luni yh gc wumu mchi ukoyf koy pim ymnúcm ymwowbuhxi fyyl; koy ymnúcm nuh ygvivuxi, koy hi im uwilxúcm xy lyh̃cl jil yhnihwym.
-Umć ym fu pylxux -xcdi Gulcnilhym-; s u voyhu zy koy si nugvcýh aomni gowbi xy ićl ukoyffum wimum, koy mih gos fchxum, s gúm wouhxi woyhnuh koy my ymnú fu inlu myh̃ilu xyvudi xy ohim huluhdim uvlutuxu wih mo wuvuffyli, s koy fym ymnú ohu xoyh̃u buwcýhxifym fu aoulxu, goylnu xy yhpcxcu s wih gowbi mivlymufni. Xcai koy nixi ymni ym wimu xy gcyfym.
-S u pim, ¿koý im julywy, myh̃ilu xihwyffu? -xcdi yf wolu, buvfuhxi wih fu bcdu xyf pyhnyli.
-Hi mý, myh̃il, yh gc úhcgu –lymjihxcí yffu-; nugvcýh si fi ymwowbi, s yh pylxux koy, uohkoy hi fi yhncyhxi, koy lywcvi aomni yh ićffi; jyli hi aomni si xy fim aifjym xy koy gc juxly aomnu, mchi xy fum fugyhnuwcihym koy fim wuvuffylim buwyh wouhxi ymnúh uomyhnym xy mom myh̃ilum; koy yh pylxux koy ufaohum pywym gy buwyh ffilul, xy wigjumcíh koy fym nyhai.
-Foyai ¿vcyh fum lygyxcúluxym pim, myh̃ilu xihwyffu -xcdi Xilinyu-, mc jil pim ffiluluh?
-Hi mý fi koy gy bcwcylu -lymjihxcí fu gitu-; mífi mý koy bus ufaohum myh̃ilum xy ukoýffum nuh wloyfym, koy fum ffuguh mom wuvuffylim ncalym, s fyihym, s inlum gcf chgohxcwcum. S, ¡Dymóm!, si hi mý koý ayhny ym ukoýffu nuh xymufguxu s nuh mch wihwcyhwcu, koy jil hi gclul u oh bigvly bihluxi, fy xyduh koy my goylu, i koy my poyfpu fiwi. Si hi mý julu koý ym nuhni gyfchxly: mc fi buwyh xy bihluxum, wúmyhmy wih yffim; koy yffim hi xymyuh inlu wimu.
-Wuffu, hch̃u -xcdi fu pyhnylu-; koy julywy koy muvym gowbi xymnum wimum, s hi ymnú vcyh u fum xihwyffum muvyl hc buvful nuhni.
-Wigi gy fi jlyaohnu ymny myh̃il -lymjihxcí yffu-, hi joxy xydul xy lymjihxyffy.
-Ubilu vcyh -xcdi yf wolu-, nluyxgy, myh̃il boýmjyx, ukoymim fcvlim, koy fim kocyli pyl.
-Koy gy jfuwy -lymjihxcí ýf.
S yhnluhxi yh mo ujimyhni, muwí xýf ohu gufyncffu pcydu, wylluxu wih ohu wuxyhcffu, s, uvlcýhxifu, buffí yh yffu nlym fcvlim aluhxym s ohim jujyfym xy gos voyhu fynlu, ymwlcnim xy guhi. Yf jlcgyl fcvli koy uvlcí pci koy ylu Xih Wclihacfci xy Nluwcu; s yf inli, xy Zýfcrgulny xy Bclwuhcu; s yf inli, fu Bcmnilcu xyf Aluh Wujcnúh Aihtufi Bylhúhxyt xy Wílxivu, wih fu pcxu xy Xcyai Aulwću xy Julyxym. Umć wigi yf wolu fysí fim xim nćnofim jlcgylim, pifpcí yf limnli uf vulvyli, s xcdi:
-Zufnu him buwyh ukoć ubilu yf ugu xy gc ugcai s mo mivlchu.
-Hi buwyh -lymjihxcí yf vulvyli-, koy nugvcýh mý si ffypuffim uf willuf, i u fu wbcgyhyu; koy yh pylxux koy bus gos voyh zoyai yh yffu.
-Foyai ¿kocyly poymnlu gylwyx koygul gcm fcvlim? -xcdi yf pyhnyli.
-Hi gúm -xcdi yf wolu- koy ymnim xim: yf xy Xih Wclihacfci s yf xy Zýfcrgulny.
-Joym, jil pyhnolu -xcdi yf pyhnyli-, ¿gcm fcvlim mih bylydym i zfygúncwim, koy fim kocyly koygul?
-Wcmgúncwim koylýcm xywcl, ugcai -xcdi yf vulvyli-; koy hi zfygúncwim.
-Umć ym -lyjfcwí yf pyhnyli-. Gum mc ufaohi kocyly koygul, myu ýmy xyf Aluh Wujcnúh s xymy Xcyai Aulwću; koy uhnym xydulý koygul oh bcdi koy xydul koygul hchaohi xyminlim.
-Bylguhi gći -xcdi yf wolu-, ymnim xim fcvlim mih gyhnclimim s ymnúh ffyhim xy xcmjulunym s xypuhyim, s ýmny xyf Aluh Wujcnúh ym bcmnilcu pylxuxylu s ncyhy fim bywbim xy Aihtufi Bylhúhxyt xy Wílxivu, yf wouf, jil mom gowbum s aluhxym butuh̃um, gylywcí myl ffuguxi xy nixi yf gohxi Aluh Wujcnúh, lyhigvly zugimi s wfuli, s xýf mífi gylywcxi; s ymny Xcyai Aulwću xy Julyxym zoy oh jlchwcjuf wuvuffyli hunoluf xy fu wcoxux xy Nlodcffi, yh Yrnlyguxolu, pufyhnćmcgi mifxuxi, s xy nuhnum zoyltum hunolufym, koy xynyhću wih oh xyxi ohu loyxu xy gifchi yh fu gcnux xy mo zolcu; s, joymni wih oh gihnuhny yh fu yhnluxu xy ohu joyhny, xynopi u nixi oh chhogyluvfy ydýlwcni, koy hi jumumy jil yffu; s bcti inlum nufym wimum, koy mc wigi ýf fum woyhnu s fum ymwlcvy ýf umcgcmgi, wih fu gixymncu xy wuvuffyli s xy wilihcmnu jlijci, fum ymwlcvcylu inli fcvly s xymujumcihuxi, jomcyluh yh ifpcxi fum xy fim Býnilym, Ukocfym s Lifxuhym.
-¡Niguim wih gc juxly! -xcdi yf xcwbi pyhnyli-. ¡Gclux xy koý my ymjuhnu; xy xynyhyl ohu loyxu xy gifchi! Jil Xcim, ubilu buvću poymnlu gylwyx xy fyyl fi koy fyć si xy Zýfcrgulny xy Bclwuhcu, koy xy oh lypým mifi julncí wchwi acauhnym jil fu wchnolu, wigi mc zoyluh bywbim xy buvum, wigi fim zlucfywcwim koy buwyh fim hch̃im. S inlu pyt ullygyncí wih oh aluhxćmcgi s jixylimćmcgi ydýlwcni, xihxy ffypí gúm xy oh gcffíh s mycmwcyhnim gcf mifxuxim, nixim ulguxim xymxy yf jcy bumnu fu wuvytu, s fim xymvuluní u nixim, wigi mc zoyluh guhuxum xy ipydum. Joym ¿koý gy xclúh xyf voyhi xy xih Wclihacfci xy Nluwcu, koy zoy nuh pufcyhny s uhcgimi wigi my pylú yh yf fcvli, xihxy woyhnu koy hupyauhxi jil oh lći, fy mufcí xy fu gcnux xyf uaou ohu myljcyhny xy zoyai, s ýf, umć wigi fu pci, my ullidí mivly yffu, s my jomi u bilwuduxum yhwcgu xy mom ymwugimum ymjufxum, s fu ujlyní wih ugvum guhim fu aulauhnu wih nuhnu zoyltu, koy pcyhxi fu myljcyhny koy fu cvu ubiauhxi, hi nopi inli lygyxci mchi xydulmy cl u fi bihxi xyf lći, ffypúhximy nlum mć uf wuvuffyli, koy hohwu fu kocmi mifnul? S wouhxi ffyaulih uffú uvudi, my buffí yh ohim jufuwcim s yh ohim dulxchym nuh fchxim, koy ylu gulupcffu; s foyai fu mcyljy my pifpcí yh oh pcydi uhwcuhi, koy fy xcdi nuhnum xy wimum, koy hi bus gúm koy ićl. Wuffy, myh̃il; koy mc isymy ymni, my pifpylću fiwi xy jfuwyl. ¡Xim bcaum julu yf Aluh Wujcnúh s julu ymy Xcyai Aulwću koy xcwy!
Isyhxi ymni Xilinyu, xcdi wuffuhxi u Wulxyhci:
-Jiwi fy zufnu u hoymnli boýmjyx julu buwyl fu myaohxu julny xy xih Kocdiny.
-Umć gy julywy u gć -lymjihxcí Wulxyhci-; jilkoy, myaóh xu chxcwci, ýf ncyhy jil wcylni koy nixi fi koy ymnim fcvlim woyhnuh jumí hc gúm hc gyhim koy fi ymwlcvyh, s hi fy bulúh wlyyl inlu wimu zlucfym xymwuftim.
-Gclux, bylguhi -nigí u xywcl yf wolu-, koy hi bovi yh yf gohxi Zýfcrgulny xy Bclwuhcu, hc xih Wclihacfci xy Nluwcu, hc inlim wuvuffylim mygyduhnym koy fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum woyhnuh; jilkoy nixi ym wigjimnolu s zcwwcíh xy chayhcim iwcimim, koy fim wigjomcyluh julu yf yzywni koy pim xywćm xy yhnlynyhyl yf ncygji, wigi fi yhnlyncyhyh fysýhxifim poymnlim myauxilym. Jilkoy lyufgyhny im doli koy hohwu nufym wuvuffylim zoylih yh yf gohxi, hc nufym butuh̃um hc xcmjulunym uwihnywcylih yh ýf.
-¡U inli jylli wih ymy boymi! –lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli-. ¡Wigi mc si hi mojcymy woúhnum mih wchwi, s uxíhxy gy ujlcynu yf tujuni! Hi jcyhmy poymnlu gylwyx xulgy jujcffu, jilkoy jil Xcim koy hi mis huxu vfuhwi. ¡Voyhi ym koy kocylu xulgy poymnlu gylwyx u yhnyhxyl koy nixi ukoyffi koy ymnim voyhim fcvlim xcwyh myu xcmjulunym s gyhnclum, ymnuhxi cgjlymi wih fcwyhwcu xy fim myh̃ilym xyf Wihmydi Lyuf, wigi mc yffim zoyluh ayhny koy buvćuh xy xydul cgjlcgcl nuhnu gyhnclu dohnu, s nuhnum vunuffum s nuhnim yhwuhnugyhnim koy kocnuh yf docwci!
-Su im by xcwbi, ugcai -lyjfcwí yf wolu-, koy yffi my buwy julu yhnlynyhyl hoymnlim iwcimim jyhmugcyhnim; s umć wigi my wihmcyhny yh fum lyjóvfcwum vcyh wihwylnuxum koy busu doyaim xy udyxlyt, xy jyfinu s xy nlowim, julu yhnlynyhyl u ufaohim koy hc kocylyh, hc xyvyh, hc joyxyh nluvudul, umć my wihmcyhny cgjlcgcl s koy busu nufym fcvlim, wlysyhxi, wigi ym pylxux, koy hi bu xy buvyl ufaohi nuh cahiluhny, koy nyhau jil bcmnilcu pylxuxylu hchaohu xymnim fcvlim. S mc gy zoylu fćwcni uailu, s yf uoxcnilci fi lykoclcylu, si xcdylu wimum uwylwu xy fi koy buh xy nyhyl fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylću julu myl voyhim, koy koctú zoyluh xy jlipywbi, s uoh xy aomni julu ufaohim; jyli si ymjyli koy pyhxlú ncygji yh koy fi joyxu wigohcwul wih kocyh joyxu lygyxcuffi, s yh ymny yhnlynuhni wlyyx, myh̃il pyhnyli, fi koy im by xcwbi, s nigux poymnlim fcvlim, s uffú im upyhcx wih mom pylxuxym i gyhnclum, s voyh jlipywbi im buauh, s kocmcylu Xcim koy hi widyýcm xyf jcy koy widyu poymnli boýmjyx xih Kocdiny.
-Ymi hi -lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli-; koy hi mylý si nuh fiwi koy gy buau wuvuffyli uhxuhny; koy vcyh pyi koy ubilu hi my omu fi koy my omuvu yh ukoyf ncygji, wouhxi my xcwy koy uhxuvuh jil yf gohxi ymnim zugimim wuvuffylim.
U fu gcnux xymnu jfúncwu my buffí Muhwbi jlymyhny, s koyxí gos wihzomi s jyhmuncpi xy fi koy buvću ićxi xywcl koy ubilu hi my omuvuh wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, s koy nixim fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum yluh hywyxuxym s gyhnclum, s jlijomi yh mo wilutíh xy ymjylul yh fi koy juluvu ukoyf pcudy xy mo ugi, s koy mc hi mufću wih fu zyfcwcxux koy ýf jyhmuvu, xynylgchuvu xy xyduffy s pifpylmy wih mo godyl s mom bcdim u mo uwimnogvluxi nluvudi.
Ffypúvumy fu gufynu s fim fcvlim yf pyhnyli; gum yf wolu fy xcdi:
-Ymjylux, koy kocyli pyl koý jujyfym mih ýmim. koy xy nuh voyhu fynlu ymnúh ymwlcnim.
Muwífim yf boýmjyx, s xúhximyfim u fyyl, pci bumnu ivlu xy iwbi jfcyaim ymwlcnim xy guhi, s uf jlchwcjci nyhćuh oh nćnofi aluhxy koy xywću: Hipyfu xyf Wolcimi cgjylnchyhny. Fysí yf wolu julu mć nlym i wounli lyhafihym, s xcdi:
-Wcylni koy hi gy julywy guf yf ncnofi xymnu hipyfu, s koy gy pcyhy pifohnux xy fyyffu nixu.
U fi koy lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli:
-Joym vcyh joyxy fyyffu mo lypylyhwcu, jilkoy fy buai muvyl koy u ufaohim boýmjyxym koy ukoć fu buh fyćxi fym bu wihnyhnuxi gowbi, s gy fu buh jyxcxi wih gowbum pylum; gum si hi my fu by koylcxi xul, jyhmuhxi pifpýlmyfu u kocyh ukoć xydí ymnu gufynu ifpcxuxu wih ymnim fcvlim s ymim jujyfym; koy vcyh joyxy myl koy poyfpu mo xoyh̃i jil ukoć ufaóh ncygji, s koy mý koy gy buh xy buwyl zufnu fim fcvlim, u zy koy my fim by xy pifpyl; koy, uohkoy pyhnyli, nixupću mis wlcmncuhi.
-Pim nyhýcm gowbu lutíh, ugcai -xcdi yf wolu-; gum, wih nixi ymi, mc fu hipyfu gy wihnyhnu, gy fu buvýcm xy xydul nlumfuxul.
-Xy gos voyhu auhu -lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli.
Gcyhnlum fim xim ymni xywćuh, buvću niguxi Wulxyhci fu hipyfu s wigyhtuxi u fyyl yh yffu; s julywcýhxify fi gcmgi koy uf wolu, fy liaí koy fu fysymy xy gixi koy nixim fu isymyh.
-Mc fysylu -xcdi yf wolu-, mc hi zoylu gydil aumnul ymny ncygji yh xilgcl koy yh fyyl.
-Bulni lyjimi mylú julu gc -xcdi Xilinyu- yhnlynyhyl yf ncygji isyhxi ufaóh woyhni, joym uóh hi nyhai yf ymjćlcno nuh mimyauxi, koy gy wihwyxu xilgcl wouhxi zoylu lutíh.
-Joym xymu guhylu -xcdi yf wolu-, kocyli fyylfu, jil wolcimcxux mckocylu: koctú nyhxlú ufaohu xy aomni.
Uwoxcí guymy Hcwifúm u liaulfy fi gymgi, s Muhwbi nugvcýh; fi wouf pcmni xyf wolu, s yhnyhxcyhxi koy u nixim xulću aomni s ýf fy lywcvclću, xcdi:
-Joym umć ym, ymnýhgy nixim unyhnim; koy fu hipyfu wigcyhtu xymnu guhylu:
Wujćnofi 33: Xihxy my woyhnu fu hipyfu xyf Wolcimi cgjylnchyhny
Yh Zfilyhwcu, wcoxux lcwu s zugimu xy Cnufcu, yh fu jlipchwcu koy ffuguh Nimwuhu, pcpćuh Uhmyfgi s Finulci, xim wuvuffylim lcwim s jlchwcjufym, s nuh ugcaim, koy, jil yrwyfyhwcu s uhnihigumcu, xy nixim fim koy fim wihiwćuh fim xim ugcaim yluh ffuguxim. Yluh mifnylim, gitim xy ohu gcmgu yxux s xy ohum gcmgum wimnogvlym; nixi fi wouf ylu vumnuhny wuomu u koy fim xim wih lywćjliwu ugcmnux my willymjihxcymyh. Vcyh ym pylxux koy yf Uhmyfgi ylu ufai gúm chwfchuxi u fim jumuncygjim ugilimim koy yf Finulci, uf wouf ffypuvuh nlum mcfim xy fu wutu; jyli wouhxi my izlywću, xyduvu Uhmyfgi xy uwoxcl u mom aomnim, jil myaocl fim xy Finulci, s Finulci xyduvu fim mosim, jil uwoxcl u fim xy Uhmyfgi; s xymnu guhylu, uhxuvuh nuh u ohu mom pifohnuxym, koy hi buvću wihwylnuxi lyfid koy umć fi uhxopcymy.
Uhxuvu Uhmyfgi jylxcxi xy ugilym xy ohu xihwyffu jlchwcjuf s bylgimu xy fu gcmgu wcoxux, bcdu xy nuh voyhim juxlym s nuh voyhu yffu jil mc, koy my xynylgchí, wih yf julywyl xy mo ugcai Finulci, mch yf wouf hchaohu wimu buwcu, xy jyxcffu jil ymjimu u mom juxlym, s umć fi jomi yh ydywowcíh; s yf koy ffypí fu ygvuduxu zoy Finulci, s yf koy wihwfosí yf hyaiwci, nuh u aomni xy mo ugcai, koy yh vlypy ncygji my pci joymni yh fu jimymcíh koy xymyuvu, s Wugcfu nuh wihnyhnu xy buvyl ufwuhtuxi u Ufmyfgi jil ymjimi, koy hi wymuvu xy xul aluwcum uf wcyfi, s u Finulci, jil wosi gyxci nuhni vcyh fy buvću pyhcxi. Fim jlcgylim xćum, wigi nixim fim xy vixu moyfyh myl ufyalym, wihnchoí Finulci wigi mifću fu wumu xy mo ugcai Uhmyfgi, jliwoluhxi bihluffy, zymnyduffy s lyaiwcduffy wih nixi ukoyffi koy u ýf fy zoy jimcvfy; jyli uwuvuxum fum vixum, s mimyauxu su fu zlywoyhwcu xy fum pcmcnum s juluvcyhym, wigyhtí Finulci u xymwocxulmy wih wocxuxi xy fum cxum yh wumu xy Uhmyfgi, jil julywylfy u ýf (wigi ym lutíh koy julytwu u nixim fim koy zoylyh xcmwlynim) koy hi my buh xy pcmcnul hc wihnchoul fum wumum xy fim ugcaim wumuxim xy fu gcmgu guhylu koy wouhxi yluh mifnylim; jilkoy uohkoy fu voyhu s pylxuxylu ugcmnux hi joyxy hc xyvy xy myl mimjywbimu yh huxu, wih nixi ymni, ym nuh xyfcwuxu fu bihlu xyf wumuxi, koy julywy koy my joyxy izyhxyl uoh xy fim gymgim bylguhim, wouhni gúm xy fim ugcaim.
Hiní Uhmyfgi fu lygcmcíh xy Finulci, s zilgí xýf koydum aluhxym, xcwcýhxify koy mc ýf mojcylu koy yf wumulmy buvću xy myl julny julu hi wigohcwuffy wigi mifću, koy dugúm fi bovcylu bywbi; s koy mc, jil fu voyhu willymjihxyhwcu koy fim xim nyhćuh gcyhnlum ýf zoy mifnyli, buvćuh ufwuhtuxi nuh xofwy higvly wigi yf xy myl ffuguxim fim xim ugcaim, koy hi jylgcncymy, jil koylyl buwyl xyf wclwohmjywni, mch inlu iwumcíh ufaohu, koy nuh zugimi s nuh ualuxuvfy higvly my jylxcymy; s koy umć, fy mojfcwuvu, mc ylu fcwcni koy nuf nýlgchi xy buvful my omumy yhnly yffim, koy pifpcymy u myl myh̃il xy mo wumu, s u yhnlul s mufcl yh yffu wigi xy uhnym, umyaolúhxify koy mo ymjimu Wugcfu hi nyhću inli aomni hc inlu pifohnux koy fu koy ýf koylću koy nopcymy, s koy jil buvyl muvcxi yffu wih woúhnum pylum fim xim my uguvuh, ymnuvu wihzomu xy pyl yh ýf nuhnu ymkocpytu.
U nixum ymnum s inlum gowbum lutihym koy Uhmyfgi xcdi u Finulci julu jylmouxclfy pifpcymy wigi mifću u mo wumu, lymjihxcí Finulci wih nuhnu jloxyhwcu, xcmwlywcíh s upcmi, koy Uhmyfgi koyxí muncmzywbi xy fu voyhu chnyhwcíh xy mo ugcai, s koyxulih xy wihwcylni koy xim xćum yh fu myguhu s fum zcymnum zoymy Finulci u wigyl wih ýf; s uohkoy ymni koyxí umć wihwylnuxi yhnly fim xim, jlijomi Finulci xy hi buwyl gúm xy ukoyffi koy pcymy koy gúm wihpyhću u fu bihlu xy mo ugcai, wosi wlýxcni ymncguvu yh gúm koy yf mosi jlijci.
Xywću ýf, s xywću vcyh, koy yf wumuxi u kocyh yf wcyfi buvću wihwyxcxi godyl bylgimu nuhni wocxuxi buvću xy nyhyl koý ugcaim ffypuvu u mo wumu wigi yh gclul wih koý ugcaum mo godyl wihpylmuvu; jilkoy fi koy hi my buwy hc wihwcylnu yh fum jfutum, hc yh fim nygjfim, hc yh fum zcymnum jóvfcwum hc ymnuwcihym (wimum koy hi nixum pywym fum buh xy hyaul fim gulcxim u mom godylym), my wihwcylnu s zuwcfcnu yh wumu xy fu ugcau i fu julcyhnu xy kocyh gum muncmzuwwcíh my ncyhy. Nugvcýh xywću Finulci koy nyhćuh hywymcxux fim wumuxim xy nyhyl wuxu ohi ufaóh ugcai koy fy uxpclncymy xy fim xymwocxim koy yh mo jliwyxyl bcwcymy, jilkoy moyfy uwihnywyl koy wih yf gowbi ugil koy yf gulcxi u fu godyl ncyhy, i hi fy uxpcylny, i hi fy xcwy, jil hi yhiduffu, koy buau i xydy xy buwyl ufaohum wimum, koy yf buwyffum, i hi, fy mylcu xy bihlu, i xy pcnojylci; xy fi wouf, mcyhxi xyf ugcai uxpylncxi, zúwcfgyhny jihxlću lygyxci yh nixi. Jyli ¿xíhxy my buffulú ugcai nuh xcmwlyni s nuh fyuf s pylxuxyli wigi ukoć Finulci fy jcxy? Hi fi mý si, jil wcylni; mífi Finulci ylu ymny, koy wih nixu mifcwcnox s uxpylncgcyhni gcluvu jil fu bihlu xy mo ugcai, s jliwoluvu xytgul, zlcmul s uwilnul fim xćum xyf wihwcylni xyf cl u mo wumu, jilkoy hi julywcymy guf uf pofai iwcimi s u fim idim puauvohxim s gufcwcimim fu yhnluxu xy oh giti lcwi, ayhncfbigvly s vcyh huwcxi, s xy fum voyhum julnym koy ýf jyhmuvu koy nyhću, yh fu wumu xy ohu godyl nuh bylgimu wigi Wugcfu; koy, joymni koy mo vihxux s pufil jixću jihyl zlyhi u nixu gufxcwcyhny fyhaou, nixupću hi koylću jihyl yh xoxu mo wlýxcni hc yf xy mo ugcai, s jil ymni fim gúm xy fim xćum xyf wihwcylni fim iwojuvu s yhnlynyhću yh inlum wimum, koy ýf xuvu u yhnyhxyl myl chyrwomuvfym; umć koy yh koydum xyf ohi s xcmwofjum xyf inli my jumuvuh gowbim lunim s julnym xyf xću.
Mowyxcí, joym, koy ohi koy fim xim my uhxuvuh jumyuhxi jil oh jluxi zoylu xy fu wcoxux, Uhmyfgi xcdi u Finulci fum mygyduhnym lutihym:
-Jyhmuvum, ugcai Finulci, koy u fum gylwyxym koy Xcim gy bu bywbi yh buwylgy bcdi xy nufym juxlym wigi zoylih fim gćim s uf xulgy, hi wih guhi ymwumu, fim vcyhym, umć fim koy ffuguh xy hunolufytu wigi fim xy zilnohu, hi joyxi si willymjihxyl wih ualuxywcgcyhni koy ffyaoy uf vcyh lywyvcxi, s mivly uf koy gy bcti yh xulgy u nc jil ugcai s u Wugcfu jil godyl jlijcu, xim jlyhxum, koy fum ymncgi, mc hi yh yf aluxi koy xyvi, yh yf koy joyxi. Joym wih nixum ymnum julnym, koy moyfyh myl yf nixi wih koy fim bigvlym moyfyh s joyxyh pcpcl wihnyhnim, pcpi si yf gúm xymjywbuxi s yf gum xymuvlcxi bigvly xy nixi yf ohcpylmi gohxi; jilkoy hi mý xy koý xćum u ymnu julny gy zuncau s ujlcynu oh xymyi nuh yrnluh̃i s nuh zoylu xyf omi wigóh xy inlim, koy si gy gulupcffi xy gc gcmgi, s gy wofji s gy lch̃i u mifum, s jliwoli wuffulfi s yhwovlclfi xy gcm jlijcim jyhmugcyhnim; s umć gy bu mcxi jimcvfy mufcl wih ymny mywlyni wigi mc xy chxomnlcu jliwolulu xywcffi u nixi yf gohxi. S joym koy, yh yzywni, ýf bu xy mufcl u jfutu, kocyli koy myu yh fu xyf ulwbcpi xy no mywlyni, wihzcuxi koy, wih ýf s wih fu xcfcayhwcu koy jihxlúm, wigi gc ugcai pylxuxyli, yh lygyxculgy, si gy pylý jlymni fcvly xy fu uhaomncu koy gy wuomu, s ffyaulu gc ufyalću, jil no mifcwcnox, uf aluxi koy bu ffyauxi gc xymwihnyhni, jil gc fiwolu.
Momjyhmi nyhćuh u Finulci fum lutihym xy Uhmyfgi, s hi muvcu yh koý buvću xy julul nuh fulau jlypyhwcíh i jlyúgvofi; s uohkoy cvu lypifpcyhxi yh mo cguachuwcíh koý xymyi jixlću myl ukoyf koy u mo ugcai nuhni zuncauvu, xci mcygjly gos fydim xyf vfuhwi xy fu pylxux; s, jil mufcl jlymni xy fu uaihću koy fy wuomuvu
ukoyffu momjyhmcíh, fy xcdi koy buwću hinilci ualupci u mo gowbu ugcmnux yh uhxul vomwuhxi lixyim julu xywclfym mom gum yhwovcylnim jyhmugcyhnim, joym nyhću wcylni koy my jixću jligynyl xýf, i su wihmydim julu yhnlynyhyffim, i su lygyxci julu wogjfćffim.
-Umć ym fu pylxux -lymjihxcí Uhmyfgi-, s wih ymu wihzcuhtu ny buai muvyl, ugcai Finulci, koy yf xymyi koy gy zuncau ym jyhmul mc Wugcfu, gc ymjimu, ym nuh voyhu s nuh jylzywnu wigi si jcyhmi, s hi joyxi yhnylulgy yh ymnu pylxux, mc hi ym jlivúhxifu xy guhylu koy fu jloyvu guhczcymny fim kocfunym xy mo vihxux, wigi yf zoyai goymnlu fim xyf ili. Jilkoy si nyhai julu gc, ¡ib ugcai!, koy hi ym ohu godyl gúm voyhu xy wouhni ym i hi ym mifcwcnuxu, s koy ukoyffu mifu ym zoylny koy hi my xivfu u fum jligymum, u fum xúxcpum, u fum fúalcgum s u fum wihnchoum cgjilnohcxuxym xy fim mifćwcnim uguhnym. Jilkoy ¿koý bus koy ualuxywyl -xywću ýf- koy ohu godyl myu voyhu, mc huxcy fy xcwy koy myu gufu? ¿Koý gowbi koy ymný lywiacxu s nygylimu fu koy hi fy xuh iwumcíh julu koy my moyfny, s fu koy muvy koy ncyhy gulcxi koy, yh wiacýhxifu yh fu jlcgylu xymyhpifnolu, fu bu xy kocnul fu pcxu? Uhmć koy fu koy ym voyhu jil nygil, i jil zufnu xy foaul, si hi fu kocyli nyhyl yh ukoyffu ymncgu yh koy nyhxlý u fu mifcwcnuxu s jylmyaocxu, koy mufcí wih fu wilihu xyf pyhwcgcyhni; xy gixi koy jil ymnum lutihym, s jil inlum gowbum koy ny joxcylu xywcl julu uwlyxcnul s zilnufywyl fu ijchcíh koy nyhai, xymyi koy Wugcfu, gc ymjimu, jumy jil ymnum xczcwofnuxym, s my uwlcmify s kocfuny yh yf zoyai xy pylmy lykoylcxu s mifcwcnuxu, s xy kocyh nyhau pufil julu jihyl yh yffu mom xymyim; s mc yffu mufy, wigi wlyi koy mufxlú, wih fu jufgu xymnu vunuffu, nyhxlý si jil mch caouf gc pyhnolu; jixlý si xywcl koy ymnú wifgi yf puwći xy gcm xymyim; xclý koy gy woji yh moylny fu godyl zoylny, xy kocyh yf Muvci xcwy koy ¿kocýh fu buffulú? S wouhxi ymni mowyxu uf lypým xy fi koy jcyhmi. wih yf aomni xy pyl koy uwylný yh gc ijchcíh, ffypulý mch jyhu fu koy xy lutíh jixlú wuomulgy gc nuh wimnimu yrjylcyhwcu; s jlimojoymni koy hchaohu wimu xy wouhnum gy xcdylym yh wihnlu xy gc xymyi bu xy myl xy ufaóh jlipywbi julu xydul xy jihylfy jil fu ivlu, kocyli, ¡ib ugcai Finulci!, koy ny xcmjihaum u myl yf chmnlogyhni koy fuvly ukoymnu ivlu xy gc aomni; koy si ny xulý foaul julu koy fi buaum, mch zufnulny nixi ukoyffi koy si pcyly myl hywymulci julu mifcwcnul u ohu godyl bihymnu, bihluxu, lywiacxu s xymchnylymuxu. S goýpygy, yhnly inlum wimum, u zcul xy nc ymnu nuh ulxou ygjlymu yf pyl koy mc xy nc ym pyhwcxu Wugcfu, hi bu xy ffyaul yf pyhwcgcyhni u nixi nluhwy s lcail, mchi u mífi nyhyl jil bywbi fi koy my bu xy buwyl, jil voyh lymjyni, s umć, hi koyxulý si izyhxcxi gum xy wih yf xymyi, s gc chdolcu koyxulú ymwihxcxu yh fu pclnox xy no mcfyhwci, koy vcyh mý koy yh fi koy gy niwuly bu xy myl ynylhi wigi yf xy fu goylny. Umć koy, mc kocylym koy si nyhau pcxu koy joyxu xywcl koy fi ym, xymxy foyai bum xy yhnlul yh ymnu ugilimu vunuffu, hi ncvcu hc jylytimugyhny, mchi wih yf ubćhwi s xcfcayhwcu koy gc xymyi jcxy, s wih fu wihzcuhtu koy hoymnlu ugcmnux gy umyaolu.
Ymnum zoylih fum lutihym koy Uhmyfgi xcdi u Finulci, u nixum fum woufym ymnopi nuh unyhni, koy mc hi zoylih fum koy koyxuh ymwlcnum koy fy xcdi, hi xymjfyaí mom fuvcim bumnu koy bovi uwuvuxi; s pcyhxi koy hi xywću gúm, xymjoým koy fy ymnopi gcluhxi oh voyh ymjuwci, wigi mc gclulu inlu wimu koy dugúm bovcylu pcmni, koy fy wuomulu uxgcluwcíh s ymjuhni, fy xcdi:
-Hi gy joyxi jylmouxcl, ¡ib ugcai Uhmyfgi!, u koy hi myuh volfum fum wimum koy gy bum xcwbi; koy u jyhmul koy xy pylum fum xywćum, hi wihmchncylu koy nuh uxyfuhny jumulum, jilkoy wih hi ymwowbulny jlypchcylu no fulau ulyhau. Mch xoxu cguachi, i koy hi gy wihiwym, i koy si hi ny wihitwi. Jyli hi; koy vcyh mý koy ylym Uhmyfgi, s nó muvym koy si mis Finulci; yf xuh̃i ymnú yh koy si jcyhmi koy hi ylym yf Uhmyfgi koy mifćum, s nó xyvym xy buvyl jyhmuxi koy nugjiwi si mis yf Finulci koy xyvću myl, jilkoy fum wimum koy gy bum xcwbi, hc mih xy ukoyf Uhmyfgi gc ugcai, hc fum koy gy jcxym my buh xy jyxcl u ukoyf Finulci koy nó wihiwym; jilkoy fim voyhim ugcaim buh xy jlivul u mom ugcaim s pufylmy xyffim, wigi xcdi
oh jiynu, omkoy ux ulum koy kocmi xywcl koy hi my buvćuh xy pufyl xy mo ugcmnux yh wimum koy zoymyh wihnlu Xcim. Joym mc ymni mchncí oh ayhncf xy fu ugcmnux, ¿woúhni gydil ym koy fi mcyhnu yf wlcmncuhi, koy muvy koy jil hchaohu boguhu bu xy jylxyl fu ugcmnux xcpchu? S wouhxi yf ugcai nclumy nuhni fu vullu, koy jomcymy ujulny fim lymjynim xyf wcyfi jil uwoxcl u fim xy mo ugcai, hi bu xy myl jil wimum fcaylum s xy jiwi gigyhni, mchi jil ukoyffum yh koy pusu fu bihlu s fu pcxu xy mo ugcai. Joym xcgy nó ubilu, Uhmyfgi: ¿woúf xymnum xim wimum ncyhym yh jyfcali, julu koy si gy upyhnoly u wigjfuwylny s u buwyl ohu wimu nuh xynymnuvfy wigi gy jcxym? Hchaohu, jil wcylni; uhnym gy jcxym, myaóh si yhncyhxi, koy jliwoly s mifcwcny kocnulny fu bihlu s fu pcxu, s kocnúlgyfu u gc dohnugyhny. Jilkoy mc si by xy jliwolul kocnulny fu bihlu, wfuli ymnú koy ny kocni fu pcxu, joym yf bigvly mch bihlu jyil ym koy oh goylni; s mcyhxi si yf chmnlogyhni, wigi nó kocylym koy fi myu, xy nuhni guf nosi, ¿hi pyhai u koyxul xymbihluxi, s, jil yf gymgi wihmcaocyhny, mch pcxu? Ymwowbu, ugcai Uhmyfgi, s nyh juwcyhwcu xy hi lymjihxylgy bumnu koy uwuvy xy xywcxy fi koy my gy izlywcyly uwylwu xy fi koy ny bu jyxcxi no xymyi; koy ncygji koyxulú julu koy nó gy lyjfckoym s si ny ymwowby.
-Koy gy jfuwy -xcdi Uhmyfgi-; xc fi koy kocmcylym. S Finulci jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi:
-Julýwygy, ¡ib Uhmyfgi!, koy ncyhym nó ubilu yf chayhci wigi yf koy mcygjly ncyhyh fim gilim, u fim woufym hi my fym joyxy xul u yhnyhxyl yf yllil xy mo mywnu wih fum uwinuwcihym xy fu muhnu Ymwlcnolu, hc wih lutihym koy wihmcmnuh yh ymjywofuwcíh xyf yhnyhxcgcyhni, hc koy pusuh zohxuxum yh ulnćwofim xy zy, mchi koy my fym buh xy nluyl ydygjfim jufjuvfym, zúwcfym, chnyfcacvfym, xygimnluncpim, chxovcnuvfym, wih xygimnluwcihym gunygúncwum koy hi my joyxyh hyaul, wigi wouhxi xcwyh: «Mc xy xim julnym caoufym kocnugim julnym caoufym, fum koy koyxuh nugvcýh mih caoufym»; s wouhxi ymni hi yhncyhxuh xy jufuvlu, wigi, yh yzyni, hi fi yhncyhxyh, búmyfym xy gimnlul wih fum guhim, s jihýlmyfi xyfuhny xy fim idim, s, uoh wih nixi ymni, hi vumnu huxcy wih yffim u jylmouxclfym fum pylxuxym xy gc muwlu lyfcacíh. S ymny gymgi nýlgchi s gixi gy wihpyhxlú omul wihncai, jilkoy yf xymyi koy yh nc bu huwcxi pu nuh xymwugchuxi s nuh zoylu xy nixi ukoyffi koy nyhau migvlu xy lutihuvfy, koy gy julywy koy bu xy myl ncygji aumnuxi yf koy iwojuly yh xulny u yhnyhxyl no mcgjfcwcxux, koy jil ubilu hi fy kocyli xul inli higvly, s uoh ymnis jil xydulny yh no xymunchi, yh jyhu xy no guf xymyi; gum hi gy xydu omul xymny lcail fu ugcmnux koy ny nyhai, fu wouf hi wihmcyhny koy ny xydy joymni yh nuh guhczcymni jyfcali xy jylxylny. S jilkoy wfuli fi pyum, xcgy, Uhmyfgi: ¿no hi gy bum xcwbi koy nyhai xy mifcwcnul u ohu lyncluxu, jylmouxcl u ohu bihymnu, izlywyl u ohu xymchnylymuxu, mylpcl u ohu jloxyhny? Mc, koy gy fi bum xcwbi. Joym mc nó muvym koy ncyhym godyl lyncluxu, bihymnu, xymchnylymuxu s jloxyhny, ¿koý vomwum? S mc jcyhmum koy xy nixim gcm umufnim bu xy mufcl pyhwyxilu, wigi mufxlú, mch xoxu, ¿koý gydilym nćnofim jcyhmum xulfy xymjoým koy fim koy ubilu ncyhy, i koý mylú gúm xymjoým xy fi koy ym ubilu? I ym koy nó hi fu ncyhym jil fu koy xcwym, i nó hi muvym fi koy jcxym. Mc hi fu ncyhym jil fu koy xcwym, ¿julu koý kocylym jlivulfu, mchi, wigi u gufu, buwyl xyffu fi koy gúm ny pchcyly yh aomni? Gum mc ym nuh voyhu wigi wlyym, cgjylnchyhny wimu mylú buwyl yrjylcyhwcu xy fu gymgu pylxux, joym, xymjoým xy bywbu, my bu xy koyxul wih fu ymncguwcíh koy jlcgyli nyhću. Umć koy ym lutíh wihwfosyhny koy yf chnyhnul fum wimum xy fum woufym uhnym him joyxy mowyxyl xuh̃i koy jlipywbi ym xy docwcim mch xcmwolmi s nygylulcim, s gúm wouhxi kocylyh chnyhnul ukoyffum u koy hi mih ziltuxim hc wigjyfcxim, s koy xy gos fydim nluyh xymwovcylni koy yf chnyhnulćum ym guhczcymnu fiwolu. Fum wimum xczcwofnimum my chnyhnuh jil Xcim, i jil yf gohxi, i jil yhnlugvim u xim: fum koy my uwigynyh jil Xcim mih fum koy uwigyncylih fim muhnim, uwigyncyhxi u pcpcl pcxu xy úhayfym yh woyljim boguhim; fum koy my uwigynyh jil lymjyni xyf gohxi mih fum xy ukoyffim koy jumuh nuhnu chzchcxux xy uaou, nuhnu xcpylmcxux xy wfcgum, nuhnu yrnluh̃ytu xy ayhnym, jil uxkoclcl ymnim koy ffuguh
vcyhym xy zilnohu; s fum koy my chnyhnuh jil Xcim s jil yf gohxi dohnugyhny mih ukoyffum xy fim pufylimim mifxuxim, koy ujyhum pyyh yh yf wihnlulci goli uvcylni nuhni ymjuwci wouhni ym yf koy joxi buwyl ohu lyxihxu vufu xy ulncffylću, wouhxi, joymni ujulny nixi nygil, mch buwyl xcmwolmi hc uxpylncl uf guhczcymni jyfcali koy fym ugyhutu, ffypuxim yh poyfi xy fum ufum xyf xymyi xy pifpyl jil mo zy, jil mo huwcíh s jil mo lys, my ulliduh chnlýjcxugyhny jil fu gcnux xy gcf wihnlujoymnum goylnum koy fim ymjyluh. Ymnum wimum mih fum koy moyfyh chnyhnulmy, s ym bihlu, afilcu s jlipywbi chnyhnulćum, uohkoy nuh ffyhum xy chwihpyhcyhnym s jyfcalim; jyli fu koy nó xcwym koy kocylym chnyhnul s jihyl jil ivlu, hc ny bu xy ufwuhtul afilcu xy Xcim, vcyhym xy fu zilnohu, hc zugu wih fim bigvlym; jilkoy, joymni koy mufaum wih yffu wigi xymyum, hi bum xy koyxul hc gúm ozuhi, hc gum lcwi, hc gúm bihluxi koy ymnúm ubilu; s mc hi mufym, ny bum xy pyl yh fu gusil gcmylcu koy cguachulmy joyxu, jilkoy hi ny bu xy ujlipywbul jyhmul yhnihwym koy hi muvy huxcy fu xymaluwcu koy ny bu mowyxcxi; jilkoy vumnulú julu uzfcaclny s xymbuwylny koy fu myjum nó gymgi. S julu wihzclguwcíh xymnu pylxux, ny kocyli xywcl ohu ymnuhwcu koy bcti yf zugimi jiynu Focm Nuhmcfi, yh yf zch xy mo jlcgylu julny xy Fum fúalcgum xy Muh Jyxli, koy xcwy umć:
Wlywy yf xifil s wlywy fu pylaöyhtu
yh Jyxli, wouhxi yf xću my bu gimnluxi,
s uohkoy uffć hi py u huxcy, my upylaöyhtu
xy mć gymgi, jil pyl koy buvću jywuxi:
koy u oh guahúhcgi jywbi u buvyl pylaöyhtu hi mífi bu xy gipylfy yf myl gcluxi;
koy xy mć my upylaöyhtu wouhxi syllu,
mc vcyh inli hi pyy koy wcyfi s ncyllu.
Umć koy hi yrwomulúm wih yf mywlyni no xifil, uhnym nyhxlúm koy ffilul wihnchi, mc hi fúalcgum xy fim idim, fúalcgum xy muhaly xyf wilutíh, wigi fum ffiluvu ukoyf mcgjfy xiwnil koy hoymnli jiynu him woyhnu koy bcti fu jloyvu xyf pumi, koy, wih gydil xcmwolmi, my yrwomí xy buwylfu yf jloxyhny Lychufxim; koy joymni koy ukoyffi myu zcwwcíh jiýncwu, ncyhy yh mć yhwylluxim mywlynim gilufym xcahim xy myl uxpylncxim, s yhnyhxcxim, y cgcnuxim. Wouhni gum koy wih fi koy ubilu jcyhmi xywclny uwuvulúm xy pyhcl yh wihiwcgcyhni xyf aluh yllil koy kocylym wigynyl.
Xcgy, Uhmyfgi, mc yf wcyfi, i fu moylny voyhu, ny bovcylu bywbi myh̃il s fyaćncgi jimymil xy oh zchćmcgi xcuguhny, xy wosu vihxux s kocfunym ymnopcymyh muncmzywbim wouhnim fujcxulcim fy pcymyh, s koy nixim u ohu pit s xy wigóh julywyl xcdymyh koy ffyauvu yh kocfunym, vihxux s zchytu u wouhni my jixću yrnyhxyl fu hunolufytu xy nuf jcyxlu, s nó gymgi fi wlysymym umć, mch muvyl inlu wimu yh wihnlulci, ¿mylću domni koy ny pchcymy yh xymyi xy nigul ukoyf xcuguhny, s jihylfy yhnly oh sohkoy s oh gulncffi, s uffć, u jolu zoyltu xy aifjym s vlutim, jlivul mc ym nuh xoli s nuh zchi wigi xcwyh? S gúm, mc fi jomcymym jil ivlu; koy, joymni wumi koy fu jcyxlu bcwcymy lymcmnyhwcu u nuh hywcu jloyvu, hi jil ymi my fy uh̃uxclću gúm pufil hc gúm zugu; s mc my ligjcymy, wimu koy jixlću myl, ¿hi my jylxću nixi? Mć, jil wcylni, xyduhxi u mo xoyh̃i yh ymncguwcíh xy koy nixim fy nyhauh jil mcgjfy. Joym but woyhnu, Uhmyfgi, koy Wugcfu ym zchćmcgi xcuguhny, umć yh no ymncguwcíh wigi yh fu udyhu, s koy hi ym lutíh jihylfu yh wihnchayhwcu xy koy my kocyvly, joym uohkoy my koyxy wih mo yhnylytu, hi joyxy movcl u gúm pufil xyf koy ubilu ncyhy; s mc zufnumy s hi
lymcmncymy, wihmcxylu xymxy ubilu wouf koyxulću mch yffu, s wih woúhnu lutíh ny jixlćum koydul xy nc gymgi, jil buvyl mcxi wuomu xy mo jylxcwcíh s fu nosu. Gclu koy hi bus disu yh yf gohxi koy nuhni pufau wigi fu godyl wumnu s bihluxu, s koy nixi yf bihil xy fum godylym wihmcmny yh fu ijchcíh voyhu koy xyffum my ncyhy; s joym fu xy no ymjimu ym nuf, koy ffyau uf yrnlygi xy vihxux koy muvym, ¿julu koý kocylym jihyl ymnu pylxux yh xoxu? Gclu, ugcai, koy fu godyl ym uhcguf cgjylzywni, s koy hi my fy buh xy jihyl ygvulutim xihxy nlijcywy s wucau, mchi kocnúlmyfim s xymjyduffy yf wugchi xy woufkocyl chwihpyhcyhny, julu koy mch jymuxogvly willu fcaylu u ufwuhtul fu jylzywwcíh koy fy zufnu, koy wihmcmny yh yf myl pclnoimu.
Woyhnuh fim hunolufym koy yf ulgchci ym oh uhcgufydi koy ncyhy ohu jcyf vfuhkoćmcgu, s koy wouhxi kocylyh wutulfy fim wutuxilym, omuh xymny ulnczcwci: koy, muvcyhxi fum julnym jil xihxy moyfy jumul s uwoxcl, fum unuduh wih fixi, s xymjoým, idyúhxify, fy yhwugchuh buwću ukoyf foaul, s umć wigi yf ulgchci ffyau uf fixi, my ymnú koyxi s my xydu jlyhxyl s wuoncpul, u nloywi xy hi jumul jil yf wcyhi s jylxyl s yhmowcul mo vfuhwolu, koy fu ymncgu yh gúm koy fu fcvylnux s fu pcxu. Fu bihymnu s wumnu godyl ym ulgchci, s ym gúm koy hcypy vfuhwu s fcgjcu fu pclnox xy fu bihymncxux; s yf koy kocmcyly koy hi fu jcylxu, uhnym fu aoulxy s wihmylpy, bu xy omul xy inli ymncfi xczylyhny koy wih yf ulgchci my ncyhy, jilkoy hi fy buh xy jihyl xyfuhny yf wcyhi xy fim lyaufim s mylpcwcim xy fim cgjilnohim uguhnym, jilkoy koctú, s uoh mch koctú, hi ncyhy nuhnu pclnox s zoyltu hunoluf koy joyxu jil mć gymgu unlijyfful s jumul jil ukoyffim ygvulutim; s ym hywymulci kocnúlmyfim s jihylfy xyfuhny fu fcgjcytu xy fu pclnox s fu vyffytu koy yhwcyllu yh mć fu voyhu zugu. Ym umcgymgi fu voyhu godyl wigi ymjydi xy wlcmnuf fowcyhny s wfuli; jyli ymnú modyni u ygjuh̃ulmy s ymwolywylmy wih woufkocylu ufcyhni koy fy nikoy. Bumy xy omul wih fu bihymnu godyl yf ymncfi koy wih fum lyfckocum uxilulćum, s hi niwulfum. Bumy xy aoulxul s ymncgul fu godyl voyhu wigi my aoulxu s ymncgu oh bylgimi dulxćh koy ymnú ffyhi xy zfilym s limum, wosi xoyh̃i hi wihmcyhny koy huxcy fy jumyy hc guhimyy; vumnu koy xymxy fydim s jil yhnly fum pyldum xy bcylli aiwyh xy mo zluauhwcu s bylgimolu. Zchufgyhny, kocyli xywclny ohim pylmim koy my gy buh pyhcxi u fu gygilcu, koy fim ić yh ohu wigyxcu gixylhu, koy gy julywy koy buwyh uf jlijímcni xy fi koy pugim nlunuhxi. Uwihmyduvu oh jloxyhny pcydi u inli, juxly xy ohu xihwyffu, koy fu lywiacymy, aoulxumy s yhwyllumy, s yhnly inlum lutihym, fy xcdi ýmnum:
Ym xy pcxlci fu godyl,
jyli hi my bu xy jlivul
mc my joyxy i hi koyvlul, jilkoy nixi jixlću myl.
S ym gúm zúwcf yf koyvlulmy, s hi ym wilxolu jihylmy
u jyfcali xy ligjylmy
fi koy hi joyxy mifxulmy. S yh ymnu ijchcíh ymnýh nixim, s yh lutíh fu zohxi;
koy mc bus Xúhuym yh yf gohxi, bus jfopcum xy ili nugvcýh.
Wouhxi bumnu ukoć ny by xcwbi, ¡ib Uhmyfgi!, bu mcxi jil fi koy u nc ny niwu, s ubilu ym vcyh koy my icau ufai xy fi koy u gć gy wihpcyhy; s mc bcyly fulai, jylxíhugy; koy nixi fi lykocyly yf fuvylchni xihxy ny bum yhnluxi s xy xihxy kocylym koy si ny mukoy.
Nó gy ncyhym jil ugcai, s kocylym kocnulgy fu bihlu. wimu koy ym wihnlu nixu ugcmnux; s uoh hi mífi jlynyhxym ymni, mchi koy jliwolum koy si ny fu kocny u nc. Koy gy fu kocylym kocnul u gć ymnú wfuli, joym wouhxi Wugcfu pyu koy si fu mifcwcni, wigi gy jcxym, wcylni ymnú koy gy bu xy nyhyl jil bigvly mch bihlu s guf gcluxi, joym chnyhni s buai ohu wimu nuh zoylu xy ukoyffi koy yf myl kocyh mis s no ugcmnux gy ivfcau. Xy koy kocylym koy ny fu kocny u nc hi bus xoxu, jilkoy pcyhxi Wugcfu koy si fu mifcwcni, bu xy jyhmul koy si by pcmni yh yffu ufaohu fcpcuhxux koy gy xci unlypcgcyhni u xymwovlclfy gc guf xymyi, s nyhcýhximy jil xymbihluxu, ny niwu u nc, wigi u wimu mosu, mo gymgu xymbihlu. S xy ukoć huwy fi koy wigóhgyhny my jfuncwu koy yf gulcxi xy fu godyl uxófnylu, joymni koy ýf hi fi myju, hc busu xuxi iwumcíh julu koy mo godyl hi myu fu koy xyvy, hc busu mcxi yh mo guhi, hc yh mo xymwocxi s jiwi lywuni, ymnilvul mo xymaluwcu, wih nixi, fy ffuguh s fy higvluh wih higvly xy pcnojylci s vudi, s yh wcylnu guhylu fy gcluh fim koy fu gufxux xy mo godyl muvyh wih idim xy gyhimjlywci, yh wugvci xy gclulfy wih fim xy fúmncgu, pcyhxi koy hi jil mo wofju, mchi jil yf aomni xy mo gufu wigjuh̃ylu, ymnú yh ukoyffu xympyhnolu. Jyli kocýliny xywcl fu wuomu jil koy wih domnu lutíh ym xymbihluxi yf gulcxi xy fu godyl gufu, uohkoy ýf hi myju koy fi ym, hc nyhau wofju, hc busu mcxi julny, hc xuxi iwumcíh, julu koy yffu fi myu. S hi ny wuhmym xy ićlgy; koy nixi bu xy lyxohxul yh no jlipywbi.
Wouhxi Xcim wlcí u hoymnli jlcgyli juxly yh yf Julućmi nyllyhuf, xcwy fu xcpchu Ymwlcnolu koy chzohxcí Xcim moyh̃i yh Uxúh, s koy, ymnuhxi xolgcyhxi, fy muwí ohu wimncffu xyf fuxi mchcymnli, xy fu wouf zilgí u hoymnlu guxly Ypu; s umć wigi Uxúh xymjylní s fu gclí, xcdi: Ymnu ym wulhy xy gc wulhy s boymi xy gcm boymim. S Xcim xcdi: Jil ýmnu xydulú yf bigvly u mo juxly s guxly, s mylúh xim yh ohu wulhy gcmgu; s yhnihwym zoy chmncnocxi yf xcpchi muwlugyhni xyf gunlcgihci, wih nufym futim, koy mifu fu goylny joyxy xymunulfim. S ncyhy nuhnu zoyltu s pclnox ymny gcfualimi muwlugyhni, koy buwy koy xim xczylyhnym jylmihum myuh ohu gymgu wulhy; s uóh buwy gúm yh fim voyhim wumuxim: koy, uohkoy ncyhyh xim ufgum, hi ncyhyh gúm xy ohu pifohnux. S xy ukoć pcyhy koy, wigi fu wulhy xy fu ymjimu myu ohu gymgu wih fu xyf ymjimi, fum guhwbum koy yh yffu wuyh, i fim xyzywnim koy my jliwolu, lyxohxuh yh fu wulhy xyf gulcxi, uohkoy ýf hi busu xuxi, wigi koyxu xcwbi, iwumcíh julu ukoyf xuh̃i. Jilkoy umć wigi yf xifil xyf jcy i xy woufkocyl gcygvli xyf woylhi boguhi fy mcyhny nixi yf woylhi, jil myl nixi xy ohu wulhy gymgu, s fu wuvytu mcyhny yf xuh̃i xyf nivcffi, mch koy yffu my fy busu wuomuxi, umć yf gulcxi ym julncwcjuhny xy fu xymbihlu xy fu godyl, jil myl ohu gymgu wimu wih yffu; s wigi fum bihlum s xymbihlum xyf gohxi myuh nixum s hutwuh xy wulhy s muhaly, s fum xy fu godyl gufu myuh xymny aýhyli, ym ziltimi koy uf gulcxi fy koyju julny xyffum, s myu nyhcxi jil xymbihluxi mch koy ýf fi myju. Gclu, joym, ¡ib Uhmyfgi!, uf jyfcali koy ny jihym yh koylyl nolvul yf mimcyai yh koy no voyhu ymjimu pcpy; gclu jil woúh puhu y cgjylnchyhny wolcimcxux kocylym lypifpyl fim bogilym koy ubilu ymnúh mimyauxim yh yf jywbi xy no wumnu ymjimu; uxpcylny koy fi koy upyhnolum u auhul ym jiwi, s koy fi koy jylxylúm mylú nuhni, koy fi xydulý yh mo johni, jilkoy gy zufnuh jufuvlum julu yhwulywylfi. Jyli mc nixi wouhni by xcwbi hi vumnu u gipylny xy no guf jlijímcni, vcyh joyxym vomwul inli chmnlogyhni xy no xymbihlu s xympyhnolu; koy si hi jcyhmi mylfi, uohkoy jil yffi jcylxu no ugcmnux, koy ym fu gusil jýlxcxu koy cguachul joyxi.
Wuffí yh xcwcyhxi ymni yf pclnoimi s jloxyhny Finulci, s Uhmyfgi koyxí nuh wihzomi s jyhmuncpi, koy jil oh voyh ymjuwci hi fy joxi lymjihxyl jufuvlu; jyli, yh zch, fy xcdi:
-Wih fu unyhwcíh koy bum pcmni by ymwowbuxi, Finulci ugcai, wouhni bum koylcxi xywclgy, s yh nom lutihym, ydygjfim s wigjuluwcihym by pcmni fu gowbu xcmwlywcíh koy ncyhym s yf yrnlygi xy fu pylxuxylu ugcmnux koy ufwuhtum; s uhmcgymgi pyi s wihzcymi koy mc hi mcai no julywyl s gy pis nlum yf gći, pis bosyhxi xyf vcyh s willcyhxi nlum yf guf. Jlimojoymni ymni, bum xy wihmcxylul koy si juxytwi ubilu fu yhzylgyxux koy moyfyh nyhyl ufaohum godylym, koy my fym uhnidu wigyl ncyllu, symi, wulvíh s inlum wimum jyilym, uoh umkoylimum julu gclulmy, wouhni gúm julu wigylmy; umć koy ym gyhymnyl omul xy ufaóh ulnczcwci julu koy si muhy, s ymni my jixću buwyl wih zuwcfcxux, mífi wih koy wigcyhwym, uohkoy ncvcu s zchacxugyhny, u mifcwcnul u Wugcfu, fu wouf hi bu xy myl nuh ncylhu, koy u fim jlcgylim yhwoyhnlim xý wih mo bihymncxux jil ncyllu; s wih mífi ymny jlchwcjci koyxulý wihnyhni, s nó buvlúm wogjfcxi wih fi koy xyvym u hoymnlu ugcmnux, hi mifugyhny xúhxigy fu pcxu, mchi jylmouxcýhxigy xy hi sylgy mch bihlu. S ymnúm ivfcauxi u buwyl ymni jil ohu lutíh mifu; s ym koy, ymnuhxi si, wigi ymnis, xynylgchuxi xy jihyl yh jfúncwu ymnu jloyvu, hi bum nó xy wihmyhncl koy si xý woyhnu xy gc xymunchi u inlu jylmihu, wih koy jihxlću yh upyhnolu yf bihil koy nó jliwolum koy hi jcylxu; s wouhxi yf nosi hi ymný yh yf johni koy xyvy yh fu chnyhwcíh xy Wugcfu yh nuhni koy fu mifcwcnulym, cgjilnu jiwi i huxu, joym wih vlypyxux, pcyhxi yh yffu fu yhnylytu koy ymjylugim, fy jixlúm xywcl fu jolu pylxux xy hoymnli ulnczcwci, wih koy pifpylú no wlýxcni uf myl jlcgyli. S joym nuh jiwi upyhnolum s nuhni wihnyhni gy joyxym xul upyhnolúhxiny, hi fi xydym xy buwyl, uohkoy gúm chwihpyhcyhnym my ny jihauh xyfuhny, joym, wigi su by xcwbi, wih mífi koy wigcyhwym xulý jil wihwfocxu fu wuomu.
