Umć wigi moyfy xywclmy koy julywy guf yf ydýlwcni mch mo ayhyluf s yf wumncffi mch mo wumnyffuhi, xcai si koy julywy gos jyil fu godyl wumuxu s gitu mch mo gulcxi, wouhxi domnćmcgum iwumcihym hi fi cgjcxyh. Si gy buffi nuh guf mch pim, s nuh cgjimcvcfcnuxu xy hi jixyl mozlcl ymnu uomyhwcu, koy mc jlymni hi pyhćm, gy buvlý xy cl u yhnlynyhyl yh wumu xy gcm juxlym, uohkoy xydy mch aoulxu fu poymnlu; jilkoy fu koy gy xydumnym, mc ym koy koyxí wih nuf nćnofi, wlyi koy gclu gúm jil mo aomni koy jil fi koy u pim im niwu; s joym micm xcmwlyni, hi nyhai gúm koy xywclim, hc uoh ym vcyh koy gúm im xcau.
Ymnu wulnu lywcvcí Uhmyfgi, s yhnyhxcí jil yffu koy Finulci buvću su wigyhtuxi fu ygjlymu, s koy Wugcfu xyvću xy buvyl willymjihxcxi wigi ýf xymyuvu; s, ufyaly mivlyguhylu xy nufym hoypum, lymjihxcí u Wugcfu, xy jufuvlu, koy hi bcwcymy goxugcyhni xy mo wumu yh gixi hchaohi, jilkoy ýf pifpylću wih gowbu vlypyxux. Uxgcluxu koyxí Wugcfu xy fu lymjoymnu xy Uhmyfgi, koy fu jomi yh gúm wihzomcíh koy jlcgyli, jilkoy hc my unlypću u ymnul yh mo wumu, hc gyhim clmy u fu xy mom juxlym; jilkoy yh fu koyxuxu, willću jyfcali mo bihymncxux; s yh fu cxu, cvu wihnlu yf guhxugcyhni xy mo ymjimi. Yh zch, my lymifpcí yh fi koy fy ymnopi jyil, koy zoy yh yf koyxulmy, wih xynylgchuwcíh xy hi bocl fu jlymyhwcu xy Finulci, jil hi xul koy xywcl u mom wlcuxim, s su fy jymuvu xy buvyl ymwlcni fi koy ymwlcvcí u mo ymjimi, nygylimu xy koy hi jyhmumy koy Finulci buvću pcmni yh yffu ufaohu xymyhpifnolu koy fy bovcymy gipcxi u hi aoulxuffy yf xywili koy xyvću. Jyli, zcuxu yh mo vihxux, my zcí yh Xcim s yh mo voyh jyhmugcyhni, wih koy jyhmuvu lymcmncl wuffuhxi u nixi ukoyffi koy Finulci xywclfy kocmcymy, mch xul gúm woyhnu u mo gulcxi, jil hi jihylfy yh ufaohu jyhxyhwcu s nluvudi; s uoh uhxuvu vomwuhxi guhylu wigi xcmwofjul u Finulci wih Uhmyfgi, wouhxi fy jlyaohnumy fu iwumcíh koy fy buvću gipcxi u ymwlcvclfy ukoyf jujyf.
Wih ymnim jyhmugcyhnim, gúm bihluxim koy uwylnuxim hc jlipywbimim, ymnopi inli xću ymwowbuhxi u Finulci, yf wouf wulaí fu guhi xy guhylu koy wigyhtí u ncnovyul fu zclgytu xy Wugcfu, s mo bihymncxux nopi bulni koy buwyl yh uwoxcl u fim idim, julu koy hi xcymyh goymnlum xy ufaohu ugilimu wigjumcíh koy fum fúalcgum s fum lutihym xy Finulci yh mo jywbi buvćuh xymjylnuxi. Nixi ymni hinuvu Finulci, s nixi fy yhwyhxću. Zchufgyhny, u ýf fy julywcí koy ylu gyhymnyl, yh yf ymjuwci s foaul koy xuvu fu uomyhwcu xy Uhmyfgi, ujlynul yf wylwi u ukoyffu zilnufytu, s umć, uwigyncí u mo jlymohwcíh wih fum ufuvuhtum xy mo bylgimolu, jilkoy hi bus wimu koy gúm jlymni lchxu s uffuhy fum yhwumncffuxum nillym xy fu puhcxux xy fum bylgimum koy fu gymgu puhcxux, joymnu yh fum fyhaoum xy fu uxofuwcíh. Yh yzywni, ýf, wih nixu xcfcayhwcu, gchí fu liwu xy mo yhnylytu, wih nufym jylnlywbim, koy uohkoy Wugcfu zoylu nixu xy vlihwy, pchcylu uf moyfi. Ffilí, liaí, izlywcí, uxofí, jilzcí s zchací Finulci wih nuhnim myhncgcyhnim, wih goymnlum xy nuhnum pylum, koy xci uf nlupým wih yf lywuni xy Wugcfu s pchi u nlcohzul xy fi koy gyhim my jyhmuvu s gum xymyuvu.
Lchxcímy Wugcfu; Wugcfu my lchxcí; jyli ¿koý gowbi, mc fu ugcmnux xy Finulci hi koyxí yh jcy? Ydygjfi wfuli koy him goymnlu koy mífi my pyhwy fu jumcíh ugilimu
wih bocffu, s koy huxcy my bu xy jihyl u vluti wih nuh jixylimi yhygcai, jilkoy ym gyhymnyl zoyltum xcpchum julu pyhwyl fum mosum boguhum. Mífi moji Fyihyfu fu zfukoytu xy mo myh̃ilu, jilkoy hi my fu joxcylih yhwovlcl fim xim gufim ugcaim s hoypim uguhnym. Hi kocmi Finulci xywcl u Wugcfu fu jlynyhmcíh xy Uhmyfgi, hc koy ýf fy buvću xuxi foaul julu ffyaul u ukoyf johni, jilkoy hi nopcymy yh gyhim mo ugil, s jyhmumy koy umć, uwumi s mch jyhmul, s hi xy jlijímcni, fu buvću mifcwcnuxi.
Pifpcí xy uffć u jiwim xćum Uhmyfgi u mo wumu, s hi ywbí xy pyl fi koy zufnuvu yh yffu, koy ylu fi koy yh gyhim nyhću s gúm ymncguvu. Zoymy foyai u pyl u Finulci, s buffífy yh mo wumu; uvlutúlihmy fim xim, s yf ohi jlyaohní jil fum hoypum xy mo pcxu, i xy mo goylny.
-Fum hoypum koy ny jixlý xul, ¡ib ugcai Uhmyfgi! -xcdi Finulci-, mih xy koy ncyhym ohu godyl koy xcahugyhny joyxy myl ydygjfi s wilihu xy nixum fum godylym voyhum. Fum jufuvlum koy fy by xcwbi my fum bu ffypuxi yf ucly; fim izlywcgcyhnim my buh nyhcxi yh jiwi; fum xúxcpum hi my buh uxgcncxi; xy ufaohum fúalcgum zchacxum gćum my bu bywbi volfu hinuvfy. Yh lymifowcíh, umć wigi Wugcfu ym wczlu xy nixu vyffytu, ym ulwbcpi xihxy umcmny fu bihymncxux s pcpy yf wigyxcgcyhni s yf lywuni, s nixum fum pclnoxym koy joyxyh buwyl fiuvfy s vcyh uzilnohuxu u ohu bihluxu godyl. Poyfpy u nigul nom xchylim, ugcai, koy ukoć fim nyhai, mch buvyl nyhcxi hywymcxux xy niwul u yffim; koy fu yhnylytu xy Wugcfu hi my lchxy u wimum nuh vudum wigi mih xúxcpum hc jligymum. Wihnýhnuny, Uhmyfgi, s hi kocylum buwyl gúm jloyvum xy fum bywbum; s, joym u jcy yhdoni bum jumuxi yf gul xy fum xczcwofnuxym s mimjywbum koy xy fum godylym moyfyh s joyxyh nyhylmy, hi kocylum yhnlul xy hoypi yh yf jlizohxi jcýfuai xy hoypim chwihpyhcyhnym, hc kocylum buwyl yrjylcyhwcu wih inli jcfini xy fu vihxux s zilnufytu xyf hupći koy yf wcyfi ny xci yh moylny julu koy yh ýf jumumym fu gul xymny gohxi; mchi but woyhnu koy ymnúm su yh myaoli joylni, s uzýlluny wih fum úhwilum xy fu voyhu wihmcxyluwcíh, s xýduny ymnul bumnu koy ny pyhauh u jyxcl fu xyoxu koy hi bus bcxufaoću boguhu koy xy juaulfu my yrwomy.
Wihnyhnćmcgi koyxí Uhmyfgi xy fum lutihym xy Finulci, s umć my fum wlysí wigi mc zoyluh xcwbum jil ufaóh ilúwofi; jyli, wih nixi ymi, fy liaí koy hi xydumy fu ygjlymu, uohkoy hi zoymy gúm xy jil wolcimcxux s yhnlynyhcgcyhni; uohkoy hi my ujlipywbumy xy uffć uxyfuhny xy nuh ubchwuxum xcfcayhwcum wigi bumnu yhnihwym; s koy mífi koylću koy fy ymwlcvcymy ufaohim pylmim yh mo ufuvuhtu, xyvudi xyf higvly xy Wfilc, jilkoy ýf fy xulću u yhnyhxyl u Wugcfu koy uhxuvu yhugiluxi xy ohu xugu, u kocyh fy buvću joymni ukoyf higvly, jil jixyl wyfyvlulfu wih yf xywili koy u mo bihymncxux my fy xyvću; s koy, wouhxi Finulci hi kocmcylu nigul nluvudi xy ymwlcvcl fim pylmim, koy ýf fim bulću.
-Hi mylú gyhymnyl ymi -xcdi Finulci--; joym hi gy mih nuh yhygcaum fum gomum koy ufaohim lunim xyf uh̃i gy pcmcnyh. Xcfy nó u Wugcfu fi koy bum xcwbi xyf zchacgcyhni xy gcm ugilym; koy fim pylmim si fim bulý, mc hi nuh voyhim wigi yf modyni gylywy, mylúh, jil fi gyhim, fim gydilym koy si joxcyly.
Koyxulih xymny uwoylxi yf cgjylnchyhny s yf nlucxil ugcai; s, poyfni Uhmyfgi u mo wumu, jlyaohní u Wugcfu fi koy yffu su my gulupcffuvu koy hi my fi bovcymy jlyaohnuxi, koy zoy koy fy xcdymy fu iwumcíh jil koy fy buvću ymwlcni yf jujyf koy fy yhpcí. Wugcfu fy lymjihxcí koy fy buvću julywcxi koy Finulci fu gcluvu oh jiwi gúm xymyhpoyfnugyhny koy wouhxi ýf ymnuvu yh wumu; jyli koy su ymnuvu xymyhauh̃uxu s wlyću koy buvću mcxi cguachuwcíh mosu, jilkoy su Finulci boću xy pyffu s xy ymnul wih yffu u mifum.
Xćdify Uhmyfgi koy vcyh jixću ymnul myaolu xy ukoyffu mimjywbu, jilkoy ýf muvću koy Finulci uhxuvu yhugiluxi xy ohu xihwyffu jlchwcjuf xy fu wcoxux, u kocyh ýf wyfyvluvu xyvudi xyf higvly xy Wfilc, s koy, uohkoy hi fi ymnopcylu, hi buvću koy
nygyl xy fu pylxux xy Finulci s xy fu gowbu ugcmnux xy yhnlugvim. S, u hi ymnul upcmuxu Wugcfu xy Finulci xy koy yluh zchacxim ukoyffim ugilym xy Wfilc, s koy ýf my fi buvću xcwbi u Uhmyfgi jil jixyl iwojulmy ufaohim lunim yh fum gcmgum ufuvuhtum xy Wugcfu, yffu, mch xoxu, wusylu yh fu xymymjyluxu lyx xy fim wyfim; gum jil ymnul su uxpylncxu, jumí ukoyf mivlymufni mch jymuxogvly.
Inli xću, ymnuhxi fim nlym mivly gymu, liaí Uhmyfgi u Finulci xcdymy ufaohu wimu xy fum koy buvću wigjoymni u mo uguxu Wfilc; koy, joym Wugcfu hi fu: wihiwću, myaolugyhny jixću xywcl fi koy kocmcymy.
-Uohkoy fu wihiwcylu -lymjihxcí Finulci-, hi yhwovlcylu si huxu; jilkoy wouhxi ufaóh uguhny fiu u mo xugu xy bylgimu s fu hinu xy wloyf, hchaóh ujlivci buwy u mo voyh wlýxcni; jyli, myu fi koy zoyly, fi koy mý xywcl, koy usyl bcwy oh mihyni u fu chaluncnox xymnu Wfilc, koy xcwy uhmć:
MIHYNI
Yh yf mcfyhwci xy fu hiwby, wouhxi
iwoju yf xofwy moyh̃i u fim gilnufym,
fu jivly woyhnu xy gcm lcwim gufym
ymnis uf wcyfi s u gc Wfilc xuhxi.
S uf ncygji wouhxi yf mif my pu gimnluhxi jil fum limuxum joylnum ilcyhnufym,
wih momjclim s uwyhnim xymcaoufym
