S xcwcyhxi ymnum lutihym, wih ohu chwlyćvfy zoyltu s fcaylytu ullygyncí u Finulci wih fu xuau xymyhpuchuxu, wih nufym goymnlum xy koylyl yhwfupúlmyfu yh yf jywbi, koy wumc ýf ymnopi yh xoxu mc ukoyffum xygimnluwcihym yluh zufmum i pylxuxylum, jilkoy fy zoy ziltimi pufylmy xy mo chxomnlcu s xy mo zoyltu julu ymnilvul koy Wugcfu hi fy xcymy. Fu wouf nuh pcpugyhny zchaću ukoyf yrnluh̃i ygvomny s zyufxux, koy, jil xuffy wifil xy pylxux, fu kocmi gunctul wih mo gcmgu muhaly; jilkoy, pcyhxi koy hi jixću buvyl u Finulci, i zchacyhxi koy hi jixću, xcdi:
-Joym fu moylny hi kocyly muncmzuwyl xyf nixi gc nuh domni xymyi, u fi gyhim, hi mylú nuh jixylimu, koy, yh julny, gy kocny koy hi fy muncmzuau.
S buwcyhxi zoyltu julu mifnul fu guhi xy fu xuau, koy Finulci fu nyhću umcxu, fu muwí, s aocuhxi mo johnu jil julny koy joxcymy bylcl hi jlizohxugyhny, my fu yhnlí s ymwihxcí jil gúm ullcvu xy fu cmfcffu xyf fuxi ctkocylxi, dohni uf bigvli, s foyai my xydí wuyl yh yf moyfi, wigi xymgusuxu.
Ymnuvuh Fyihyfu s Finulci momjyhmim s uníhcnim xy nuf mowymi, s nixupću xoxuvuh xy fu pylxux xy ukoyf bywbi, pcyhxi u Wugcfu nyhxcxu yh ncyllu s vuh̃uxu yh mo muhaly. Uwoxcí Finulci wih gowbu jlymnytu, xymjupilcxi s mch ufcyhni, u muwul fu xuau, s yh pyl fu jykoyh̃u bylcxu, mufcí xyf nygil koy bumnu yhnihwym nyhću, s xy hoypi my uxgclí xy fu muauwcxux, jloxyhwcu s gowbu xcmwlywcíh xy fu bylgimu Wugcfu; s, jil uwoxcl wih fi koy u ýf fy niwuvu, wigyhtí u buwyl ohu fulau s nlcmny fugyhnuwcíh mivly yf woylhi xy Wugcfu, wilhi mc ymnopcylu xczohnu, ywbúhximy gowbum gufxcwcihym, hi mífi u ýf, mchi uf koy buvću mcxi wuomu xy buvyffy joymni yh ukoyf nýlgchi. S wigi muvću koy fy ymwowbuvu mo ugcai Uhmyfgi, xywću wimum koy yf koy fy isylu fy nopcylu gowbu gúm fúmncgu koy u Wugcfu, uohkoy jil goylnu fu dotaulu. Fyihyfu fu nigí yh vlutim s fu jomi yh yf fywbi, mojfcwuhxi u Finulci zoymy u vomwul kocyh mywlynugyhny u Wugcfu wolumy; jyxćufy umcgcmgi wihmydi s julywyl xy fi koy xclćuh u Uhmyfgi xy ukoyffu bylcxu xy mo myh̃ilu, mc uwumi pchcymy uhnym koy ymnopcymy muhu. Yf lymjihxcí koy xcdymyh fi koy kocmcymyh; koy ýf hi ymnuvu julu xul wihmydi koy xy jlipywbi zoymy; mífi fy xcdi koy jliwolumy nigulfy fu muhaly, jilkoy ýf my cvu uxihxy ayhnym hi fy pcymyh. S wih goymnlum xy gowbi xifil s myhncgcyhni, my mufcí xy wumu; s wouhxi my pci mifi s yh julny xihxy huxcy fy pyću, hi wymuvu xy buwylmy wlowym, gulupcffúhximy xy fu chxomnlcu xy Wugcfu s xy fim uxyguhym nuh jlijlcim xy Fyihyfu. Wihmcxyluvu woúh yhnyluxi buvću xy koyxul Uhmyfgi xy koy nyhću jil godyl u ohu myaohxu Jilwcu, s xymyuvu pylmy wih ýf julu wyfyvlul fim xim fu gyhnclu s fu pylxux gúm xcmcgofuxu koy dugúm joxcylu cguachulmy.
Fyihyfu nigí, wigi my bu xcwbi, fu muhaly u mo myh̃ilu, koy hi ylu gúm xy ukoyffi koy vumní julu uwlyxcnul mo ygvomny, s fupuhxi wih oh jiwi xy pchi fu bylcxu, my fu uní fi gydil koy moji, xcwcyhxi nufym lutihym yh nuhni koy fu woluvu, koy uohkoy hi bovcyluh jlywyxcxi inlum, vumnuluh u buwyl wlyyl u Uhmyfgi koy nyhću yh Wugcfu oh mcgofuwli xy fu bihymncxux. Dohnúlihmy u fum jufuvlum xy Fyihyfu inlum xy Wugcfu, ffugúhximy wivulxy s xy jiwi úhcgi, joym fy buvću zufnuxi uf ncygji koy zoylu gúm hywymulci nyhylfy, julu kocnulmy fu pcxu, koy nuh uvillywcxu nyhću. Jyxću wihmydi u mo xihwyffu mc xulću, i hi, nixi ukoyf mowymi u mo koylcxi ymjimi; fu wouf fy xcdi koy hi my fi xcdymy, jilkoy fy jihxlću yh ivfcauwcíh xy pyhaulmy xy Finulci, fi wouf hi jixlću myl mch gowbi lcymai mosi, s koy fu voyhu godyl ymnuvu ivfcauxu u hi xul iwumcíh u mo gulcxi u koy lch̃ymy, mchi u kocnuffy nixum ukoyffum koy fy zoymy jimcvfy. Lymjihxcí Wugcfu koy fy julywću gos vcyh mo julywyl, s koy yffu fy myaoclću; jyli koy yh nixi wumi wihpyhću vomwul koý xywcl u Uhmyfgi xy fu wuomu xy ukoyffu bylcxu, koy ýf hi jixlću xydul xy pyl; u fi koy Fyihyfu lymjihxću koy yffu, hc uoh volfuhxi, hi muvću gyhncl.
-Joym si, bylguhu -lyjfcwí Wugcfu-, ¿koý nyhai xy muvyl, koy hi gy unlypylý u zildul hc momnyhnul ohu gyhnclu, mc gy zoymy yh yffi fu pcxu? S mc ym koy hi bygim xy muvyl xul mufcxu u ymni, gydil mylú xywclfy fu pylxux xymhoxu, koy hi koy him ufwuhwy yh gyhnclimu woyhnu.
-Hi nyhaum jyhu, myh̃ilu: xy ukoć u guh̃uhu -lymjihxcí Fyihyfu- si jyhmulý koý fy xcaugim, s koctú koy jil myl fu bylcxu xihxy ym, fu jixlúm yhwovlcl mch koy ýf fu pyu, s yf wcyfi mylú mylpcxi xy zupilywyl u hoymnlim nuh domnim s nuh bihluxim jyhmugcyhnim. Mimcýauny, myh̃ilu gću, s jliwolu mimyaul no ufnyluwcíh, jilkoy gc myh̃il hi ny buffy mivlymufnuxu, s fi xygúm xýdufi u gc wulai, s uf xy Xcim, koy mcygjly uwoxy u fim voyhim xymyim.
Unyhnćmcgi buvću ymnuxi Uhmyfgi u ymwowbul s u pyl lyjlymyhnul fu nluayxcu xy fu goylny xy mo bihlu; fu wouf wih nuh yrnluh̃im s yzcwuwym uzywnim fu lyjlymyhnulih fim jylmihudym xyffu, koy julywcí koy my buvćuh nluhmzilguxi yh fu gcmgu pylxux xy fi koy zchaćuh. Xymyuvu gowbi fu hiwby, s yf nyhyl foaul julu mufcl xy mo wumu, s cl u pylmy wih mo voyh ugcai Finulci, wihalunofúhximy wih ýf xy fu gulaulcnu jlywcimu koy buvću buffuxi yh yf xymyhauh̃i xy fu vihxux xy mo ymjimu. Nopcylih wocxuxi fum xim xy xulfy foaul s wigixcxux u koy mufcymy, s ýf, mch jylxyffu, mufcí, s foyai zoy u vomwul u Finulci; yf wouf buffuxi, hi my joyxy voyhugyhny wihnul fim uvlutim koy fy xci, fum wimum koy xy mo wihnyhni fy xcdi, fum ufuvuhtum koy xci u Wugcfu. Nixi fi wouf ymwowbí Finulci mch jixyl xul goymnlum xy ufaohu ufyalću, jilkoy my fy lyjlymyhnuvu u fu gygilcu woúh yhauh̃uxi ymnuvu mo ugcai, s woúh chdomnugyhny ýf fy ualupcuvu; s uohkoy Uhmyfgi pyću koy Finulci hi my ufyaluvu, wlyću myl fu wuomu jil buvyl xyduxi u Wugcfu bylcxu s buvyl ýf mcxi fu wuomu; s umć, yhnly inlum lutihym, fy xcdi koy hi nopcymy jyhu xyf mowymi xy Wugcfu, jilkoy, mch xoxu, fu bylcxu ylu fcaylu, joym koyxuvuh xy wihwcylni xy yhwovlclmyfu u ýf, s koy, myaóh ymni, hi buvću xy koý nygyl, mchi koy xy uffć uxyfuhny my aitumy s ufyalumy wih ýf, joym jil mo chxomnlcu s gyxci ýf my pyću fypuhnuxi u fu gúm ufnu zyfcwcxux koy uwylnulu u xymyulmy, s koylću koy hi zoymyh inlim mom yhnlynyhcgcyhnim koy yf buwyl pylmim yh ufuvuhtu xy Wugcfu, koy fu bcwcymyh ynylhu yh fu gygilcu xy fim mcafim pyhcxylim. Finulci ufuví mo voyhu xynylgchuwcíh s xcdi koy ýf, jil mo julny, usoxulću u fypuhnul nuh cfomnly yxczcwci.
Wih ymni koyxí Uhmyfgi yf bigvly gúm muvlimugyhny yhauh̃uxi koy joxi buvyl yh yf gohxi: ýf gcmgi ffypuvu jil fu guhi u mo wumu, wlysyhxi koy ffypuvu yf chmnlogyhni xy mo afilcu, nixu fu jylxcwcíh xy mo zugu. Lywyvćufy Wugcfu wih limnli, uf julywyl, nilwcxi, uohkoy wih ufgu lcmoyh̃u. Xolí ymny yhauh̃i ufaohim xćum, bumnu koy uf wuvi xy jiwim gymym pifpcí Zilnohu mo loyxu, s mufcí u jfutu fu gufxux wih nuhni ulnczcwci bumnu uffć wovcylnu, s u Uhmyfgi fy wimní fu pcxu mo cgjylnchyhny wolcimcxux.
Wujćnofi 35: Koy nlunu xy fu vlupu s xymwigohuf vunuffu koy xih Kocdiny nopi wih ohim woylim xy pchi nchni, s my xu zch u fu hipyfu xyf wolcimi cgjylnchyhny
Jiwi gúm koyxuvu jil fyyl xy fu hipyfu, wouhxi xyf wuluguhwbíh xihxy lyjimuvu xih Kocdiny mufcí Muhwbi Juhtu nixi ufvilinuxi, xcwcyhxi u piwym:
-Uwoxcx, myh̃ilym, jlymni s miwillyx u gc myh̃il, koy uhxu yhpoyfni yh fu gúm lyh̃cxu s nluvuxu vunuffu koy gcm idim buh pcmni. ¡Pcpy Xcim, koy bu xuxi ohu wowbcffuxu uf acauhny yhygcai xy fu myh̃ilu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu, koy fy bu nuduxi fu wuvytu wylwyh u wylwyh wigi mc zoylu oh huvi!
-¿Koý xywćm, bylguhi? -xcdi yf wolu, xyduhxi xy fyyl fi koy xy fu hipyfu koyxuvu-. ¿Ymnúcm yh pim, Muhwbi? ¿Wígi xcuvfim joyxy myl ymi koy xywćm, ymnuhxi yf acauhny xim gcf fyaoum xy ukoć?
Yh ymni, isylih oh aluh locxi yh yf ujimyhni, s koy xih Kocdiny xywću u piwym:
-¡Nyhny, fuxlíh, gufuhxlćh, ziffíh; koy ukoć ny nyhai, s hi ny bu xy pufyl no wcgcnullu!
S julywću koy xuvu aluhxym wowbcffuxum jil fum julyxym. S xcdi Muhwbi:
-Hi ncyhyh koy jululmy u ymwowbul, mchi yhnlyh u xymjulncl fu jyfyu, i u usoxul u gc ugi; uohkoy su hi mylú gyhymnyl, jilkoy, mch xoxu ufaohu, yf acauhny ymnú su goylni, s xuhxi woyhnu u Xcim xy mo jumuxu s gufu pcxu; koy si pc willyl fu muhaly jil yf moyfi, s fu wuvytu wilnuxu s wućxu u oh fuxi, koy ym nuguh̃u wigi oh aluh woyli xy pchi.
-Koy gy gunyh -xcdi u ymnu mutíh yf pyhnyli- mc xih Kocdiny i xih xcuvfi hi bu xuxi ufaohu wowbcffuxu yh ufaohi xy fim woylim xy pchi nchni koy u mo wuvywylu ymnuvuh ffyhim, s yf pchi xylluguxi xyvy xy myl fi koy fy julywy muhaly u ymny voyh bigvly.
S wih ymni yhnlí yh yf ujimyhni, s nixim nlum ýf, s buffulih u xih Kocdiny yh yf gúm yrnluh̃i nludy xyf gohxi. Ymnuvu yh wugcmu, fu wouf hi ylu nuh wogjfcxu, koy jil xyfuhny fy uwuvumy xy wovlcl fim gomfim, s jil xynlúm nyhću mycm xyxim gyhim; fum jcylhum yluh gos fulaum s zfuwum, ffyhum xy pyffi s hi huxu fcgjcum; nyhću yh fu wuvytu oh vihyncffi wifiluxi alumcyhni, koy ylu xyf pyhnyli; yh yf vluti ctkocylxi nyhću lypoyfnu fu guhnu xy fu wugu, wih kocyh nyhću idylctu Muhwbi, s ýf my muvću vcyh yf jilkoý, s yh fu xylywbu, xymyhpuchuxu fu ymjuxu, wih fu wouf xuvu wowbcffuxum u nixum julnym, xcwcyhxi jufuvlum wigi mc pylxuxylugyhny ymnopcylu jyfyuhxi wih ufaóh acauhny. S ym fi voyhi koy hi nyhću fim idim uvcylnim, jilkoy ymnuvu xolgcyhxi s mih̃uhxi koy ymnuvu yh vunuffu wih yf acauhny; koy zoy nuh chnyhmu fu cguachuwcíh xy fu upyhnolu koy cvu u zyhywyl, koy fy bcti mih̃ul koy su buvću ffyauxi uf lychi xy Gcwigcwíh, s koy su ymnuvu yh fu jyfyu wih mo yhygcai; s
buvću xuxi nuhnum wowbcffuxum yh fim woylim, wlysyhxi koy fum xuvu yh yf acauhny, koy nixi yf ujimyhni ymnuvu ffyhi xy pchi. Fi wouf pcmni jil yf pyhnyli, nigí nuhni yhidi, koy ullygyncí wih xih Kocdiny, s u joh̃i wylluxi fy wigyhtí u xul nuhnim aifjym, koy mc Wulxyhci s yf wolu hi my fy kocnuluh, ýf uwuvulu fu aoyllu xyf acauhny; s, wih nixi ukoyffi, hi xymjylnuvu yf jivly wuvuffyli, bumnu koy yf vulvyli nlodi oh aluh wufxyli xy uaou zlću xyf jiti, s my fy ywbí jil nixi yf woylji xy aifjy, wih fi wouf xymjylní xih Kocdiny; gum hi wih nuhni uwoylxi, koy ywbumy xy pyl xy fu guhylu koy ymnuvu. Xilinyu, koy pci woúh wilnu s mincfgyhny ymnuvu pymncxi, hi kocmi yhnlul u pyl fu vunuffu xy mo usoxuxil s xy mo wihnlulci.
Uhxuvu Muhwbi vomwuhxi fu wuvytu xyf acauhny jil nixi yf moyfi, s wigi hi fu buffuvu, xcdi:
-Su si mý koy nixi fi xymnu wumu ym yhwuhnugyhni; koy fu inlu pyt yh ymny gymgi foaul xihxy ubilu gy buffi, gy xcylih gowbim gidcwihym s jillutim, mch muvyl kocýh gy fim xuvu, s hohwu joxy pyl u huxcy; s ubilu hi julywy jil ukoć ymnu wuvytu, koy pc wilnul jil gcm gcmgćmcgim idim, s fu muhaly willću xyf woylhi wigi xy ohu zoyhny.
-¿Koý muhaly hc koý zoyhny xcwym, yhygcai xy Xcim s xy mom muhnim? -xcdi yf pyhnyli-. ¿Hi pym, fuxlíh, koy fu muhaly s fu zoyhny hi ym inlu wimu koy ymnim woylim koy ukoć ymnúh biluxuxim s yf pchi nchni koy huxu yh ymny ujimyhni, koy huxuhxi pyu si yf ufgu, yh fim chzcylhim, xy kocyh fim biluxí?
-Hi mý huxu -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-: mífi mý koy pyhxlý u myl nuh xymxcwbuxi, koy, jil hi bufful ymnu wuvytu, my gy bu xy xymbuwyl gc wihxuxi wigi fu muf yh yf uaou.
S ymnuvu jyil Muhwbi xymjcylni koy mo ugi xolgcyhxi: nuf fy nyhćuh fum jligymum koy mo ugi fy buvću bywbi. Yf pyhnyli my xymymjyluvu xy pyl fu zfygu xyf ymwoxyli s yf gufyzcwci xyf myh̃il, s doluvu koy hi buvću xy myl wigi fu pyt jumuxu, koy my fy zoylih mch juaul, s koy ubilu hi fy buvćuh xy pufyl fim jlypcfyacim xy mo wuvuffylću julu xydul xy juaul fi ohi s fi inli, uoh bumnu fi koy joxcymyh wimnul fum vinuhum koy my buvćuh xy ywbul u fim linim woylim.
Nyhću yf wolu xy fum guhim u xih Kocdiny, yf wouf, wlysyhxi koy su buvću uwuvuxi fu upyhnolu, s koy my buffuvu xyfuhny xy fu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu, my bchwí xy lixcffum xyfuhny xyf wolu, xcwcyhxi:
-Vcyh joyxy fu poymnlu aluhxytu, ufnu s zugimu myh̃ilu, pcpcl, xy bis gúm, myaolu koy fy joyxu buwyl guf ymnu guf huwcxu wlcunolu; s si nugvcýh, xy bis gúm, mis kocni xy fu jufuvlu koy im xc, joym, wih yf usoxu xyf ufni Xcim s wih yf zupil xy ukoyffu jil kocyh si pcpi s lymjcli, nuh vcyh fu by wogjfcxi.
-¿Hi fi xcdy si? -xcdi isyhxi ymni Muhwbi-. Mc koy hi ymnuvu si villuwbi, ¡gclux mc ncyhy joymni su yh muf gc ugi uf acauhny! ¡Wcylnim mih fim nilim, gc wihxuxi ymnú xy gifxy!
¿Kocýh hi buvću xy lyćl wih fim xcmjulunym xy fim xim, ugi s giti? Nixim lyćuh mchi yf pyhnyli, koy my xuvu u Munuhúm; jyli, yh zch, nuhni bcwcylih yf vulvyli, Wulxyhci s yf wolu, koy, wih hi jiwi nluvudi, xcylih wih xih Kocdiny yh fu wugu, yf wouf my koyxí xilgcxi, wih goymnlum xy aluhxćmcgi wuhmuhwci. Xydúlihfy xilgcl, s mufcýlihmy uf jilnuf xy fu pyhnu u wihmiful u Muhwbi Juhtu xy hi buvyl buffuxi fu wuvytu xyf acauhny; uohkoy gúm nopcylih koy buwyl yh ujfuwul uf pyhnyli, koy ymnuvu xymymjyluxi jil fu lyjyhnchu goylny xy mom woylim. S fu pyhnylu xywću yh pit s yh alcni:
-Yh guf johni s yh bilu gyhaouxu yhnlí yh gc wumu ymny wuvuffyli uhxuhny, koy hohwu gcm idim fy bovcyluh pcmni, koy nuh wuli gy woymnu. Fu pyt jumuxu my zoy wih yf wimni xy ohu hiwby, xy wyhu, wugu, judu s wyvuxu, julu ýf s julu mo ymwoxyli, s oh liwćh s oh dogyhni, xcwcyhxi koy ylu wuvuffyli upyhnolyli, koy gufu pyhnolu fy xý Xcim, u ýf s u wouhnim upyhnolylim bus yh yf gohxi, s koy jil ymni hi ymnuvu ivfcauxi u juaul huxu, koy umć ymnuvu ymwlcni yh fim uluhwyfym xy fu wuvuffylću uhxuhnymwu; s ubilu, jil mo lymjyni, pchi ymninli myh̃il s gy ffypí gc wifu, s búgyfu poyfni wih gúm xy xim woulncffim xy xuh̃i, nixu jyfuxu, koy hi joyxy mylpcl julu fi koy fu kocyly gc gulcxi; s jil zch s lyguny xy nixi, ligjylgy gcm woylim s xyllugulgy gc pchi, koy xylluguxu fy pyu si mo muhaly. ¡Joym hi my jcyhmy; koy jil fim boymim xy gc juxly s jil yf mcafi xy gc guxly, mc hi gy fi buh xy juaul oh woulni mivly inli, i hi gy ffugulću si wigi gy ffugi, hc mylcu bcdu xy kocyh mis!
Ymnum s inlum lutihym nufym xywću fu pyhnylu wih aluhxy yhidi, s usoxúvufu mo voyhu wlcuxu Gulcnilhym. Fu bcdu wuffuvu, s xy wouhxi yh wouhxi my mihlyću. Yf wolu fi mimyaí nixi, jligyncyhxi xy muncmzuwylfym mo jýlxcxu fi gydil koy joxcymy, umć xy fim woylim wigi xyf pchi, s jlchwcjufgyhny xyf gyhimwuvi xy fu wifu, xy kocyh nuhnu woyhnu buwćuh. Xilinyu wihmifí u Muhwbi Juhtu xcwcýhxify koy wuxu s wouhxi koy julywcymy buvyl mcxi pylxux koy mo ugi bovcymy xymwuvytuxi uf acauhny, fy jligynću, yh pcýhximy juwćzcwu yh mo lychi, xy xulfy yf gydil wihxuxi koy yh ýf bovcymy. Wihmifímy wih ymni Muhwbi, s umyaolí u fu jlchwymu koy nopcymy jil wcylni koy ýf buvću pcmni fu wuvytu xyf acauhny, s koy, jil gúm myh̃um, nyhću ohu vulvu koy fy ffyauvu u fu wchnolu; s koy mc hi julywću, ylu jilkoy nixi wouhni yh ukoyffu wumu jumuvu ylu jil pću xy yhwuhnugyhni, wigi ýf fi buvću jlivuxi inlu pyt koy buvću jimuxi yh yffu. Xilinyu xcdi koy umć fi wlyću, s koy hi nopcymy jyhu; koy nixi my bulću vcyh s mowyxylću u jyxcl xy viwu.
Mimyauxim nixim, yf wolu kocmi uwuvul xy fyyl fu hipyfu, jilkoy pci koy zufnuvu jiwi. Wulxyhci, Xilinyu s nixim fim xygúm fy liaulih fu uwuvumy. Yf, koy u nixim kocmi xul aomni, s jil yf koy ýf nyhću xy fyylfu, jlimcaocí yf woyhni, koy umć xywću:
Mowyxcí, joym, koy, jil fu muncmzuwcíh koy Uhmyfgi nyhcu xy fu vihxux xy Wugcfu, pcpću ohu pcxu wihnyhnu s xymwocxuxu, s Wugcfu, xy chxomnlcu, buwcu guf limnli u Finulci, jilkoy Uhmyfgi yhnyhxcymy uf lypým xy fu pifohnux koy fy nyhću; s julu gum wihzclguwcíh xy mo bywbi, jcxcí fcwyhwcu Finulci julu hi pyhcl u mo wumu, joym wfulugyhny my gimnluvu fu jymuxogvly koy wih mo pcmnu Wugcfu lywyvću; gum yf yhauh̃uxi Uhmyfgi fy xcdi koy yh hchaohu guhylu nuf bcwcymy; s xymnu guhylu, jil gcf guhylum ylu Uhmyfgi yf zuvlcwuxil xy mo xymbihlu, wlysyhxi koy fi ylu xy mo aomni.
Yh ymni, yf koy nyhću Fyihyfu xy pylmy woufczcwuxu yh mom ugilym ffyaí u nuhni, koy, mch gclul u inlu wimu, my cvu nlum ýf u moyfnu lcyhxu, zcuxu yh koy mo myh̃ilu fu yhwovlću, s uoh fu uxpylnću xyf gixi koy wih jiwi lywyfi joxcymy jihylfy yh ydywowcíh. Yh zch, ohu hiwby mchncí Uhmyfgi jumim yh yf ujimyhni xy Fyihyfu, s koylcyhxi yhnlul u pyl kocýh fim xuvu, mchncí koy fy xynyhćuh fu joyxu, wimu koy fy jomi gum pifohnux xy uvlclfu; s nuhnu zoyltu bcti, koy fu uvlcí, s yhnlí xyhnli u ncygji koy pci koy oh bigvly mufnuvu jil fu pyhnuhu u fu wuffy; s uwoxcyhxi wih jlymnytu u ufwuhtulfy i wihiwylfy, hi joxi wihmyaocl fi ohi hc fi inli, jilkoy Fyihyfu my uvluti wih ýf, xcwcýhxify:
-Mimcýauny, myh̃il gći, s hi ny ufvilinym, hc mcaum uf koy xy ukoć mufní: ym wimu gću, s nuhni, koy ym gc ymjimi.
Hi fi kocmi wlyyl Uhmyfgi; uhnym, wcyai xy yhidi, muwí fu xuau s kocmi bylcl u Fyihyfu, xcwcýhxify koy fy xcdymy fu pylxux; mc hi, koy fu gunulću. Yffu, wih yf gcyxi, mch muvyl fi koy my xywću, fy xcdi:
-Hi gy gunym, myh̃il, koy si ny xclý wimum xy gúm cgjilnuhwcu xy fum koy joyxym cguachul.
-Xcfum foyai -xcdi Uhmyfgi-; mc hi, goylnu ylym.
-Jil ubilu mylú cgjimcvfy -xcdi Fyihyfu-, myaóh ymnis xy nolvuxu; xýdugy bumnu guh̃uhu, koy yhnihwym muvlúm xy gcfi koy ny bu xy uxgclul; s ymnú myaoli koy yf koy mufní jil ymnu pyhnuhu ym oh guhwyvi xy ymnu wcoxux, koy gy bu xuxi fu guhi xy myl gc ymjimi.
Mimyaimy wih ymni Uhmyfgi s kocmi uaoulxul yf nýlgchi koy my fy jyxću, jilkoy hi jyhmuvu ićl wimu koy wihnlu Wugcfu zoymy, jil ymnul xy mo vihxux nuh muncmzywbi s myaoli; s umć, my mufcí xyf ujimyhni s xydi yhwylluxu yh yf u Fyihyfu, xcwcýhxify koy xy uffć hi mufxlću bumnu koy fy xcdymy fi koy nyhću koy xywclfy.
Zoy foyai u pyl u Wugcfu s u xywclfy, wigi fy xcdi, nixi ukoyffi koy wih mo xihwyffu fy buvću jumuxi, s fu jufuvlu koy fy buvću xuxi xy xywclfy aluhxym wimum s xy cgjilnuhwcu. Mc my nolví Wugcfu i hi, hi bus julu koý xywclfi; jilkoy zoy nuhni yf nygil koy wivlí wlysyhxi pylxuxylugyhny, s ylu xy wlyyl, koy Fyihyfu buvću xy xywcl u Uhmyfgi nixi fi koy muvću xy mo jiwu zy, koy hi nopi úhcgi julu ymjylul mc mo mimjywbu mufću zufmu i hi, s ukoyffu gymgu hiwby, wouhxi fy julywcí koy Uhmyfgi xilgću, dohní fum gydilym disum koy nyhću, s ufaohim xchylim, s, mch myl xy huxcy myhncxu, mufcí xy wumu s my zoy u fu xy Finulci, u kocyh wihní fi koy jumuvu s fy jcxcí koy fu jomcymy yh wivli, i koy my uomyhnumyh fim xim xihxy xy Uhmyfgi joxcymyh ymnul myaolim. Fu wihzomcíh yh koy Wugcfu jomi u Finulci zoy nuf koy hi fy muvcu lymjihxyl jufuvlu, hc gyhim muvcu lymifpylmy yh fi koy bulću. Yh zch, uwilxí xy ffypul u Wugcfu u oh gihymnylci, yh kocyh ylu jlcilu ohu mo bylguhu. Wihmchncí Wugcfu yh yffi, s wih fu jlymnytu koy yf wumi jyxću fu ffypí Finulci s fu xydí yh yf gihymnylci, s ýf uhmcgymgi my uomyhní foyai xy fu wcoxux, mch xul julny u huxcy xy mo uomyhwcu.
Wouhxi uguhywcí, mch ywbul xy pyl Uhmyfgi koy Wugcfu zufnuvu xy mo fuxi, wih yf xymyi koy nyhću xy muvyl fi koy Fyihyfu koylću xywclfy, my fypuhní s zoy uxihxy fu buvću xyduxi yhwylluxu. Uvlcí s yhnlí yh yf ujimyhni, jyli hi buffí yh ýf u Fyihyfu; mífi buffí joymnum ohum múvuhum uh̃oxuxum u fu pyhnuhu, chxcwci s myh̃uf koy jil uffć my buvću xymwifauxi y cxi. Pifpcí foyai gos nlcmny u xywćlmyfi u Wugcfu, s, hi buffúhxifu yh fu wugu hc yh nixu fu wumu, koyxí umigvluxi. Jlyaohní u fim wlcuxim xy wumu jil yffu; jyli huxcy fy moji xul lutíh xy fi koy jyxću.
Uwylní uwumi, uhxuhxi u vomwul u Wugcfu, koy pci mom wizlym uvcylnim s koy xyffim zufnuvuh fum gúm xy mom disum, s wih ymni uwuví xy wuyl yh fu woyhnu xy mo xymaluwcu, s yh koy hi ylu Fyihyfu fu wuomu xy mo xympyhnolu; s uhmć wigi ymnuvu, mch uwuvulmy xy pymncl, nlcmny s jyhmuncpi, zoy u xul woyhnu xy mo xymxcwbu u mo ugcai Finulci. Gum wouhxi hi fy buffí, s mom wlcuxim fy xcdylih koy ukoyffu hiwby buvću zufnuxi xy wumu, s buvću ffypuxi wihmcai nixim fim xchylim koy nyhću, jyhmí jylxyl yf docwci. S julu uwuvul xy wihwfocl wih nixi, pifpcýhximy u mo wumu, hi buffi yh yffu hchaohi xy wouhnim wlcuxim hc wlcuxum nyhću, mchi fu wumu xymcylnu s mifu.
Hi muvcu koy jyhmul, koý xywcl, hc koý buwyl, s jiwi u jiwi my fy cvu pifpcyhxi yf docwci. Wihnygjfúvumy s gclúvumy yh oh chmnuhny mch godyl, mch ugcai s mch wlcuxim, xymugjuluxi, u mo julywyl, xyf wcyfi koy fy wovlću, s mivly nixi mch bihlu, jilkoy yh fu zufnu xy Wugcfu pci mo jylxcwcíh.
Lymifpcímy, yh zch, u wuvi xy ohu aluh jcytu, xy clmy u fu ufxyu xy mo ugcai, xihxy buvću ymnuxi wouhxi xci foaul u koy my gukochumy nixu ukoyffu xympyhnolu. Wyllí fum joyxum xy mo wumu, movcí u wuvuffi, s wih xymgusuxi ufcyhni my jomi yh wugchi; s ujyhum bovi uhxuxi fu gcnux, wouhxi, uwimuxi xy mom jyhmugcyhnim, fy zoy ziltimi ujyulmy s ullyhxul mo wuvuffi u oh úlvif, u wosi nlihwi my xydí wuyl, xuhxi ncylhim s xifilimim momjclim, s uffć my ymnopi bumnu wumc koy uhiwbywću; s u ukoyffu bilu pci koy pyhću oh bigvly u wuvuffi xy fu wcoxux, s, xymjoým xy buvylfy mufoxuxi, fy jlyaohní koý hoypum buvću yh Zfilyhwcu. Yf wcoxuxuhi lymjihxcí:
-Fum gúm yrnluh̃um koy gowbim xćum bu my buh ićxi yh yffu; jilkoy my xcwy jóvfcwugyhny koy Finulci, ukoyf aluhxy ugcai xy Uhmyfgi yf lcwi, koy pcpću u Muh Douh, my ffypí ymnu hiwby u Wugcfu, godyl xy Uhmyfgi, yf wouf nugjiwi julywy. Nixi ymni bu xcwbi ohu wlcuxu xy Wugcfu, koy uhiwby fu buffí yf aivylhuxil xymwifaúhximy wih ohu múvuhu jil fum pyhnuhum xy fu wumu xy Uhmyfgi. Yh yzyni, hi mý johnoufgyhny wígi jumí yf hyaiwci; mífi mý koy nixu fu wcoxux ymnú uxgcluxu xymny mowymi, jilkoy hi my jixću ymjylul nuf bywbi xy fu gowbu s zugcfcul ugcmnux xy fim xim, koy xcwyh koy ylu nuhnu, koy fim ffuguvuh fim xim ugcaim.
-¿Múvymy, jil pyhnolu -xcdi Uhmyfgi-, yf wugchi koy ffypuh Finulci s Wugcfu?
-Hc jil jcyhmi -xcdi yf wcoxuxuhi-, joymni koy yf aivylhuxil bu omuxi xy gowbu xcfcayhwcu yh vomwulfim.
-U Xcim pucm, myh̃il -xcdi Uhmyfgi.
-Wih ýf koyxýcm -lymjihxcí yf wcoxuxuhi, s zoymy.
Wih nuh xymxcwbuxum hoypum wumc ffyaí u nýlgchim Uhmyfgi, hi mífi xy jylxyl yf docwci, mchi xy uwuvul fu pcxu. Fypuhnímy wigi joxi, s ffyaí u wumu xy mo ugcai, koy uóh hi muvcu mo xymaluwcu; gum wigi fy pci ffyaul ugulcffi, wihmogcxi s mywi, yhnyhxcí koy xy ufaóh alupy guf pyhcu zuncauxi. Jcxcí foyai Uhmyfgi koy fy uwimnumyh, s koy fy xcymyh uxylyti xy ymwlcvcl. Bćtimy umć, s xydúlihfy uwimnuxi s mifi, jilkoy ýf umć fi kocmi, s uoh koy fy wyllumyh fu joyxu. Pcýhximy, joym, mifi, wigyhtí u wulaul nuhni fu cguachuwcíh xy mo xympyhnolu, koy wfulugyhny wihiwcí koy my fy cvu uwuvuhxi fu pcxu; s umć, ilxyhí xy xydul hincwcu xy fu wuomu xy mo yrnluh̃u goylny; s wigyhtuhxi u ymwlcvcl, uhnym koy uwuvumy xy jihyl nixi fi koy koyxu, fy zufní yf ufcyhni s xydí fu pcxu yh fum guhim xyf xifil koy fy wuomí mo wolcimcxux cgjylnchyhny.
Pcyhxi yf myh̃il xy fu wumu koy ylu su nulxy s koy Uhmyfgi hi ffuguvu, uwilxí xy yhnlul u muvyl mc jumuvu uxyfuhny mo chxcmjimcwcíh, s buffífy nyhxcxi viwu uvudi, fu gcnux xyf woylhi yh fu wugu s fu inlu gcnux mivly yf vozyny, mivly yf wouf ymnuvu, wih yf jujyf ymwlcni s uvcylni, s ýf nyhću uóh fu jfogu yh fu guhi. Ffyaímy yf boýmjyx u ýf, buvcýhxify ffuguxi jlcgyli; s, nluvúhxify jil fu guhi, pcyhxi koy hi fy lymjihxću, s buffúhxify zlći, pci koy ymnuvu goylni. Uxgclímy s wihaidímy yh aluh guhylu, s ffugí u fu ayhny xy wumu julu koy pcymyh fu xymaluwcu u Uhmyfgi mowyxcxu, s, zchufgyhny, fysí yf jujyf, koy wihiwcí koy xy mo gymgu guhi ymnuvu ymwlcni, yf wouf wihnyhću ymnum lutihym:
Oh hywci y cgjylnchyhny xymyi gy kocní fu pcxu. Mc fum hoypum xy gc goylny ffyaulyh u fim ićxim xy Wugcfu, myju koy si fu jylxihi, jilkoy hi ymnuvu yffu ivfcauxu u buwyl gcfualim, hc si nyhću hywymcxux xy koylyl koy yffu fim bcwcymy; s joym si zoc yf zuvlcwuxil xy gc xymbihlu, hi bus julu koý...
Bumnu ukoć ymwlcvcí Uhmyfgi, jil xihxy my ywbí xy pyl koy yh ukoyf johni, mch jixyl uwuvul fu lutíh, my fy uwuví fu pcxu. Inli xću xci upcmi mo ugcai u fim julcyhnym xy Uhmyfgi xy mo goylny, fim woufym su muvćuh mo xymaluwcu, s yf gihymnylci xihxy Wugcfu ymnuvu, wumc yh yf nýlgchi xy uwigjuh̃ul u mo ymjimi yh ukoyf ziltimi pcudy, hi jil fum hoypum xyf goylni ymjimi, gum jil fum koy moji xyf uomyhny ugcai. Xćwymy koy, uohkoy my pci pcoxu, hi kocmi mufcl xyf gihymnylci, hc, gyhim, buwyl jlizymcíh xy gihdu, bumnu koy, hi xy uffć u gowbim xćum, fy pchcylih hoypum koy Finulci buvću goylni yh ohu vunuffu koy yh ukoyf ncygji xci gihmcol xy Fuonlyw uf Aluh Wujcnúh Aihtufi Zylhúhxyt xy Wílxivu yh yf lychi xy Hújifym, xihxy buvću cxi u julul yf nulxy ullyjyhncxi ugcai; fi wouf muvcxi jil Wugcfu, bcti jlizymcíh, s uwuví yh vlypym xćum fu pcxu, u fum lcaolimum guhim xy nlcmnytum s gyfuhwifćum. Ymny zoy yf zch koy nopcylih nixim, huwcxi xy oh nuh xymunchuxi jlchwcjci.
-Vcyh -xcdi yf wolu- gy julywy ymnu hipyfu; jyli hi gy joyxi jylmouxcl koy ymni myu pylxux; s mc ym zchacxi, zchací guf yf uonil, jilkoy hi my joyxy cguachul koy busu gulcxi nuh hywci, koy kocylu buwyl nuh wimnimu yrjylcyhwcu wigi Uhmyfgi. Mc ymny wumi my jomcylu yhnly oh aufúh s ohu xugu, joxcýlumy ffypul; jyli yhnly gulcxi s godyl, ufai ncyhy xyf cgjimcvfy; s yh fi koy niwu uf gixi xy wihnulfi, hi gy xymwihnyhnu.
Wujćnofi 36: Koy nlunu xy inlim lulim mowymim koy yh fu pyhnu mowyxcylih
Ymnuhxi yh ymni, yf pyhnyli, koy ymnuvu u fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, xcdi:
-Ymnu koy pcyhy ym ohu bylgimu nliju xy boýmjyxym; mc yffim juluh ukoć, auoxyugom nyhygim.
-¿Koý aymny ym? -xcdi Wulxyhci.
-Wounli bigvlym -lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli- pcyhyh u wuvuffi, u fu dchynu, wih fuhtum s uxulaum, s nixim wih uhnczuwym hyalim; s dohni wih yffim pcyhy ohu godyl pymncxu xy vfuhwi, yh oh mcffíh, uhmcgymgi wovcylni yf limnli, s inlim xim gitim xy u jcy.
-¿Pcyhyh gos wylwu? -jlyaohní yf wolu.
Nuh wylwu -lymjihxcí yf pyhnyli-, koy su ffyauh.
Isyhxi ymni Xilinyu, my wovlcí yf limnli, s Wulxyhci my yhnlí yh yf ujimyhni xy xih Kocdiny; s wumc hi buvćuh nyhcxi foaul julu ymni, wouhxi yhnlulih yh fu pyhnu nixim fim koy yf pyhnyli buvću xcwbi; s ujyúhximy fim wounli xy u wuvuffi, koy xy gos ayhncf nuffy s xcmjimcwcíh yluh, zoylih u ujyul u fu godyl koy yh yf mcffíh pyhcu; s, nigúhxifu ohi xyffim yh mom vlutim, fu myhní yh ohu mcffu koy ymnuvu u fu yhnluxu xyf ujimyhni xihxy Wulxyhci my buvću ymwihxcxi. Yh nixi ymny ncygji, hc yffu hc yffim my buvćuh kocnuxi fim uhnczuwym, hc buvfuxi jufuvlu ufaohu; mífi koy uf myhnulmy fu godyl yh fu mcffu, xci oh jlizohxi momjcli, s xydí wuyl fim vlutim, wigi jylmihu yhzylgu s xymgusuxu. Fim gitim xy u jcy ffypulih fim wuvuffim u fu wuvuffylctu.
Pcyhxi ymni yf wolu, xymyimi xy muvyl koý ayhny ylu ukoyffu koy wih nuf nludy s nuf mcfyhwci ymnuvu, my zoy xihxy ymnuvuh fim gitim, s u ohi xy yffim fy jlyaohní fi koy su xymyuvu; yf wouf fy lymjihxcí:
-Julxcyt, myh̃il, si hi muvlý xywclim koý ayhny myu ýmnu; mífi mý koy goymnlu myl gos jlchwcjuf, ymjywcufgyhny ukoyf koy ffyai u nigul yh mom vlutim u ukoyffu myh̃ilu koy buvýcm pcmni; s ymni xćaifi jilkoy nixim fim xygúm fy ncyhyh lymjyni, s hi my buwy inlu wimu gum xy fu koy ýf ilxyhu s guhxu.
-S fu myh̃ilu ¿kocýh ym? -jlyaohní yf wolu.
-Nugjiwi muvlý xywcl ymi -lymjihxcí yf giti-; jilkoy yh nixi yf wugchi hi fu by pcmni yf limnli; momjclul mc fu by ićxi gowbum pywym s xul ohim aygcxim, koy julywy koy wih wuxu ohi xyffim kocyly xul yf ufgu. S hi ym xy gulupcfful koy hi myjugim gúm xy fi buvygim xcwbi, jilkoy gc wigjuh̃yli s si hi bu gúm xy xim xćum koy fim uwigjuh̃ugim; jilkoy, buvcýhxifim yhwihnluxi yh yf wugchi, him liaulih s
jylmouxcylih koy pchcýmygim wih yffim bumnu yf Uhxufowću, izlywcýhximy u juaúlhimfi gos vcyh.
-S ¿buvýcm ićxi higvlul u ufaohi xyffim? -jlyaohní yf wolu.
-Hi, jil wcylni -lymjihxcí yf giti-, jilkoy nixim wugchuh wih nuhni mcfyhwci, koy ym gulupcffu; jilkoy hi my isy yhnly yffim inlu wimu koy fim momjclim s miffitim xy fu jivly myh̃ilu, koy him goypyh u fúmncgu; s mch xoxu nyhygim wlyćxi koy yffu pu ziltuxu xihxy kocylu koy pu; s, myaóh my joyxy wifyacl jil mo búvcni, yffu ym gihdu, i pu u mylfi, koy ym fi gúm wcylni, s koctú jilkoy hi fy xyvy xy huwyl xy pifohnux yf gihdći, pu nlcmny, wigi julywy.
-Nixi jixlću myl -xcdi yf wolu.
S xydúhxifim, my pifpcí uxihxy ymnuvu Xilinyu; fu wouf, wigi buvću ićxi momjclul u fu ygvituxu, gipcxu xy hunoluf wigjumcíh, my ffyaí u yffu s fy xcdi:
-¿Koý guf myhnćm, myh̃ilu gću? Gclux mc ym ufaohi xy kocyh fum godylym moyfyh nyhyl omi s yrjylcyhwcu xy wolulfy; koy xy gc julny im izlytwi ohu voyhu pifohnux xy mylpclim.
U nixi ymni wuffuvu fu fumncguxu myh̃ilu; s uohkoy Xilinyu nilhi wih gusilym izlywcgcyhnim, nixupću my ymnuvu yh mo mcfyhwci, bumnu koy ffyaí yf wuvuffyli ygvituxi koy xcdi yf giti koy fim xygúm ivyxywćuh, s xcdi u Xilinyu:
-Hi im wuhmýcm, myh̃ilu, yh izlywyl huxu u ymu godyl, jilkoy ncyhy jil wimnogvly xy hi ualuxywyl wimu koy jil yffu my buwy, hc jliwolýcm koy im lymjihxu, mc hi koylýcm ićl ufaohu gyhnclu xy mo viwu.
-Dugúm fu xcdy -xcdi u ymnu mutíh fu koy bumnu uffć buvću ymnuxi wuffuhxi-; uhnym jil myl nuh pylxuxylu s nuh mch nlutum gyhnclimum gy pyi ubilu yh nuhnu xympyhnolu; s xymni pim gymgi kocyli koy myúcm yf nymncai, joym gc jolu pylxux im buwy u pim myl zufmi s gyhnclimi.
Isí ymnum lutihym Wulxyhci vcyh wfulu s xcmnchnugyhny, wigi kocyh ymnuvu nuh dohni xy kocyh fum xywću, koy mifu fu joylnu xyf ujimyhni xy xih Kocdiny ymnuvu yh gyxci; s umć wigi fum isí, xuhxi ohu aluh pit xcdi:
¡Púfaugy Xcim! ¿Koý ym ymni koy icai? ¿Koý pit ym ymnu koy bu ffyauxi u gcm ićxim?
Pifpcí fu wuvytu u ymnim alcnim ukoyffu myh̃ilu, nixu mivlymufnuxu, s hi pcyhxi kocýh fim xuvu, my fypuhní yh jcy s zoymy u yhnlul yh yf ujimyhni; fi wouf pcmni jil yf wuvuffyli, fu xynopi, mch xydulfu gipyl oh jumi. U yffu, wih fu nolvuwcíh s xymumimcyai, my fy wusi yf nuzynúh wih koy nluću wovcylni yf limnli, s xymwovlcí ohu bylgimolu chwigjuluvfy s oh limnli gcfualimi, uohkoy xymwifilcxi s umigvluxi, jilkoy wih fim idim uhxuvu lixyuhxi nixim fim foaulym xihxy ufwuhtuvu wih fu pcmnu, wih nuhni ubćhwi, koy julywću jylmihu zoylu xy docwci; wosum myh̃ufym, mch muvyl jil koy fum buwcu, jomcylih aluh fúmncgu yh Xilinyu s yh wouhnim fu gcluvuh. Nyhćufu yf wuvuffyli zoylnygyhny umcxu jil fum ymjufxum, s jil ymnul nuh iwojuxi yh nyhylfu, hi joxi uwoxcl u uftulmy yf ygviti, koy my fy wuću, wigi, yh yzyni, my fy wusí xyf nixi; s uftuhxi fim idim Xilinyu, koy uvlutuxu wih fu myh̃ilu ymnuvu, pci koy yf koy uvlutuxu uhmcgymgi fu nyhću ylu mo ymjimi xih Zylhuhxi; s ujyhum fy bovi wihiwcxi, wouhxi ulliduhxi xy fi ćhncgi xy mom yhnluh̃um oh foyhai s
nlcmnćmcgi ¡us!, my xydí wuyl xy ymjufxum xymgusuxu; s u hi buffulmy uffć dohni yf vulvyli, koy fu lywiací yh fim vlutim, yffu xcylu wihmcai yh yf moyfi.
Uwoxcí foyai yf wolu u kocnulfy yf ygviti, julu ywbulfy uaou yh yf limnli, s umć wigi fu xymwovlcí, fu wihiwcí xih Zylhuhxi, koy ylu yf koy ymnuvu uvlutuxi wih fu inlu, s koyxí wigi goylni yh pylfu; jyli hi jilkoy xydumy, wih nixi ymni, xy nyhyl u Fomwchxu, koy ylu fu koy jliwoluvu mifnulmy xy mom vlutim; fu wouf buvću wihiwcxi yh yf momjcli u Wulxyhci, s ýf fu buvću wihiwcxi u yffu. Isí umcgymgi Wulxyhci yf ¡us! koy xci Xilinyu wouhxi my wusí xymgusuxu, s, wlysyhxi koy ylu mo Fomwchxu, mufcí xyf ujimyhni xymjupilcxi, s fi jlcgyli koy pci zoy u xih Zylhuhxi, koy nyhću uvlutuxi u Fomwchxu. Nugvcýh xih Zylhuhxi wihiwcí foyai u Wulxyhci; s nixim nlym, Fomwchxu, Wulxyhci s Xilinyu, koyxulih goxim s momjyhmim, wumc mch muvyl fi koy fym buvću uwihnywcxi.
Wuffuvuh nixim s gclúvuhmy nixim, Xilinyu u xih Zylhuhxi, xih Zylhuhxi u Wulxyhci, Wulxyhci u Fomwchxu, s Fomwchxu u Wulxyhci. Gum kocyh jlcgyli ligjcí yf mcfyhwci zoy Fomwchxu, buvfuhxi u xih Zylhuhxi xymnu guhylu:
-Xyduxgy, myh̃il xih Zylhuhxi, jil fi koy xyvýcm u myl kocyh micm, su koy jil inli lymjyni hi fi buaúcm, xyduxgy ffyaul uf goli xy kocyh si mis syxlu, uf ullcgi xy kocýh hi gy buh jixcxi ujulnul poymnlum cgjilnohuwcihym, poymnlum ugyhutum, poymnlum jligymum hc poymnlum xúxcpum. Hinux wígi yf wcyfi, jil xymomuxim s u himinlim yhwovcylnim wugchim gy bu joymni u gc pylxuxyli ymjimi xyfuhny; s vcyh muvýcm jil gcf wimnimum yrjylcyhwcum koy mifu fu goylny zoylu vumnuhny julu villulfy xy gc gygilcu. Myuh, joym, julny nuh wfulim xymyhauh̃im julu koy pifpúcm, su koy hi jixúcm buwyl inlu wimu, yf ugil yh luvcu, fu pifohnux yh xymjywbi, s uwuvuxgy wih ýf fu pcxu, koy wigi si fu lchxu xyfuhny xy gc voyh ymjimi, fu xulý jil vcyh ygjfyuxu: koctú wih gc goylny koyxulú muncmzywbi xy fu zy koy fy guhnopy bumnu yf ófncgi nluhwy xy fu pcxu.
Buvću yh ymny yhnlynuhni poyfni Xilinyu yh mć, s buvću ymnuxi ymwowbuhxi nixum fum lutihym koy Fomwchxu xcdi, jil fum woufym pchi yh wihiwcgcyhni xy kocýh yffu ylu; s pcyhxi koy xih Zylhuhxi uóh hi fu xyduvu xy fim vlutim, hc lymjihxću u mom lutihym, ymziltúhximy fi gúm koy joxi, my fypuhní s my zoy u bchwul xy lixcffum u mom jcym, s xylluguhxi gowbu wuhncxux xy bylgimum s fumncgylum fúalcgum, umć fy wigyhtí u xywcl:
-Mc su hi ym, myh̃il gći, koy fim lusim xymny mif koy yh nom vlutim ywfcjmuxi ncyhym ny kocnuh s izomwuh fim xy nom idim, su buvlúm ywbuxi xy pyl koy fu koy u nom jcym ymnú ullixcffuxu ym fu mch pyhnolu, bumnu koy nó kocylum, s fu xymxcwbuxu Xilinyu. Si mis ukoyffu fuvluxilu bogcfxy u kocyh nó, jil no vihxux i jil no aomni, kocmcmny fypuhnul u fu ufnytu xy jixyl ffugulmy nosu; mis fu koy, yhwylluxu yh fim fćgcnym xy fu bihymncxux, pcpcí pcxu wihnyhnu bumnu koy, u fum piwym xy nom cgjilnohcxuxym, s, uf julywyl, domnim s ugilimim myhncgcyhnim, uvlcí fum joylnum xy mo lywuni s ny yhnlyaí fum ffupym xy mo fcvylnux, xúxcpu xy nc nuh guf ualuxywcxu, wouf fi goymnlu vcyh wfuli buvyl mcxi ziltimi buffulgy yh yf foaul xihxy gy buffum, s pylny si u nc xy fu guhylu koy ny pyi. Jyli, wih nixi ymni, hi koyllću koy wusymy yh no cguachuwcíh jyhmul koy by pyhcxi ukoć wih jumim xy gc xymbihlu, buvcýhxigy nlućxi mífi fim xyf xifil s myhncgcyhni xy sylgy xy nc ifpcxuxu. Nó kocmcmny koy si zoymy nosu, s kocmćmnyfi xy guhylu koy, uohkoy ubilu kocylum koy hi fi myu, hi mylú jimcvfy koy nó xydym xy myl gći. Gclu, myh̃il gći, koy joyxy myl lywigjyhmu u fu bylgimolu s hivfytu jil kocyh gy xydum fu chwigjuluvfy pifohnux koy ny nyhai. Nó hi joyxym myl xy fu bylgimu Fomwchxu, jilkoy ylym gći, hc yffu joyxy myl nosu, jilkoy ym xy Wulxyhci; s gúm zúwcf ny mylú, mc yh yffi gclum, lyxowcl no pifohnux u koylyl u kocyh ny uxilu, koy hi yhwugchul fu koy ny uvillywy u koy vcyh ny kocylu. Nó mifcwcnumny gc xymwocxi; nó liaumny u gc yhnylytu; nó hi cahilumny gc wufcxux; nó
muvym vcyh xy fu guhylu koy gy yhnlyaoý u nixu no pifohnux: hi ny koyxu foaul hc uwiacxu xy ffugulny u yhauh̃i. S mc ymni ym umć, wigi fi ym, s nó ylym nuh wlcmncuhi wigi wuvuffyli, ¿jil koý jil nuhnim lixyim xcfunum xy buwylgy pyhnolimu yh fim zchym, wigi gy bcwcmny yh fim jlchwcjcim? S mc hi gy kocylym jil fu koy mis, koy mis no pylxuxylu s fyaćncgu ymjimu, kocýlygy, u fi gyhim, s uxgćnygy jil no ymwfupu; koy wigi si ymný yh no jixyl, gy nyhxlý jil xcwbimu s vcyh uzilnohuxu. Hi jylgcnum, wih xydulgy s xymugjululgy, koy my buauh s dohnyh willcffim yh gc xymbihlu; hi xym nuh gufu pydyt u gcm juxlym, joym hi fi gylywyh fim fyufym mylpcwcim koy, wigi voyhim pumuffim, u fim nosim mcygjly buh bywbi. S mc ny julywy koy bum xy uhckocful no muhaly jil gytwfulfu wih fu gću, wihmcxylu koy jiwum i hchaohu hivfytu bus yh yf gohxi koy hi busu willcxi jil ymny wugchi, s koy fu koy my nigu xy fum godylym hi ym fu koy buwy uf wumi yh fum cfomnlym xymwyhxyhwcum, wouhni gúm, koy fu pylxuxylu hivfytu wihmcmny yh fu pclnox, s mc ýmnu u nc ny zufnu hyaúhxigy fi koy nuh domnugyhny gy xyvym, si koyxulý wih gúm pyhnudum xy hivfy koy fum koy nó ncyhym. Yh zch, myh̃il, fi koy ófncgugyhny ny xcai ym koy, kocylum i hi kocylum, si mis no ymjimu: nymncaim mih nom jufuvlum, koy hi buh hc xyvyh myl gyhnclimum, mc su ym koy ny jlywcum xy ukoyffi jil koy gy xymjlywcum; nymncai mylú fu zclgu koy bcwcmny, s nymncai yf wcyfi, u kocyh nó ffugumny jil nymncai xy fi koy gy jligynćum. S wouhxi nixi ymni zufny, no gcmgu wihwcyhwcu hi bu xy zufnul xy xul piwym wuffuhxi yh gcnux xy nom ufyalćum, pifpcyhxi jil ymnu pylxux koy ny by xcwbi, s nolvuhxi nom gydilym aomnim s wihnyhnim.
Ymnum s inlum lutihym xcdi fu fumncguxu Xilinyu, wih nuhni myhncgcyhni s fúalcgum, koy fim gcmgim koy uwigjuh̃uvuh u xih Zylhuhxi, s wouhnim jlymyhnym ymnuvuh, fu uwigjuh̃ulih yh yffum. Ymwowbífu xih Zylhuhxi mch lyjfcwuffy jufuvlu, bumnu koy yffu xci zch u fum mosum, s jlchwcjci u nuhnim miffitim s momjclim, koy vcyh buvću xy myl wilutíh xy vlihwy yf koy wih goymnlum xy nuhni xifil hi my yhnylhywcylu. Gclúhxifu ymnuvu Fomwchxu, hi gyhim fumncguxu xy mo myhncgcyhni koy uxgcluxu xy mo gowbu xcmwlywcíh s bylgimolu; s uohkoy kocmcylu ffyaulmy u yffu s xywclfy ufaohum jufuvlum xy wihmoyfi, hi fu xyduvuh fim vlutim xy xih Zyguhxi, koy ujlynuxu fu nyhćuh. Yf wouf, ffyhi xy wihzomcíh s ymjuhni, uf wuvi xy oh voyh ymjuwci koy unyhnugyhny ymnopi gcluhxi u Xilinyu, uvlcí fim vlutim s, xyduhxi fcvly u Fomwchxu, xcdi:
-Pyhwcmny, bylgimu Xilinyu, pyhwcmny; jilkoy hi ym jimcvfy nyhyl úhcgi julu hyaul nuhnum pylxuxym dohnum.
Wih yf xymgusi koy Fomwchxu buvću nyhcxi, umć wigi fu xydí xih Zyguhxi cvu u wuyl yh yf moyfi; gúm buffúhximy Wulxyhci uffć dohni, koy u fum ymjufxum xy xih Zyguhxi my buvću joymni jilkoy hi fy wihiwcymy, jimjoymni nixi nygil s upyhnoluhxi u nixi lcymai, uwoxcí u mimnyhyl u Fomwchxu, s, wiacýhxifu yhnly mom vlutim, fy xcdi:
-Mc yf jcuximi wcyfi aomnu s kocyly koy su nyhaum ufaóh xymwuhmi, fyuf, zclgy s bylgimu myh̃ilu gću, yh hchaohu julny wlyi si koy fy nyhxlúm gúm myaoli koy yh ymnim vlutim koy ubilu ny lywcvyh, s inli ncygji ny lywcvcylih, wouhxi fu zilnohu kocmi koy joxcymy ffugulny gću.
U ymnum lutihym jomi Fomwchxu yh Wulxyhci fim idim, s buvcyhxi wigyhtuxi u wihiwylfy, jlcgyli jil fu pit, s umyaolúhximy koy ýf ylu wih fu pcmnu, wumc zoylu xy myhncxi s mch nyhyl woyhnu u hchaóh bihymni lymjyni, fy ywbí fim vlutim uf woyffi s, dohnuhxi mo limnli wih yf xy Wulxyhci, fy xcdi:
-Pim mć, myh̃il gći, micm yf pylxuxyli xoyh̃i xymnu poymnlu wujncpu, uohkoy gum fi cgjcxu fu wihnlulcu moylny, s uohkoy gúm ugyhutum fy buauh u ymnu pcxu koy yh fu poymnlu my momnyhnu.
Yrnluh̃i ymjywnúwofi zoy ýmny julu xih Zyguhxi s julu nixim fim wclwohmnuhnym, uxgclúhximy xy nuh hi pcmni mowymi. Julywcífy u Xilinyu koy xih Zylhuhxi buvću jylxcxi fu wifil xyf limnli, s koy buwcu uxygúh xy koylyl pyhaulmy xy Wulxyhci, jilkoy fy pci yhwugchul fu guhi u jihyffu yh fu ymjuxu; s umć wigi fi jyhmí, wih hi pcmnu jlymnytu my uvlutí wih ýf jil fum lixcffum, vymúhximyfum s nyhcýhxify ujlynuxi, koy hi fy xyduvu gipyl, s, mch wymul oh johni xy mom fúalcgum, fy xywću:
-¿Koý ym fi koy jcyhmum buwyl, óhcwi lyzoaci gći, yh ymny nuh cgjyhmuxi nluhwy? Nó ncyhym u nom jcym u no ymjimu, s fu koy kocylym koy fi myu ymnú yh fim vlutim xy mo gulcxi. Gclu mc ny ymnulú vcyh, i ny mylú jimcvfy xymbuwyl fi koy yf wcyfi bu bywbi, i mc ny wihpyhxlú koylyl fypuhnul u caouful u nc gcmgi u fu koy, jimjoymni nixi chwihpyhcyhny, wihzclguxu yh mo pylxux s zclgytu, xyfuhny xy nom idim ncyhy fim mosim, vuh̃uxim xy fcwil ugilimi yf limnli s jywbi xy mo pylxuxyli ymjimi. Jil kocyh Xcim ym ny loyai, s jil kocyh nó ylym ny mojfcwi, koy ymny nuh hinilci xymyhauh̃i hi mífi hi uwlywcyhny no clu, mchi koy fu gyhaöy yh nuf guhylu, koy wih kocynox s mimcyai jylgcnum koy ymnim xim uguhnym fy nyhauh mch cgjyxcgyhni nosi nixi yf ncygji koy yf wcyfi kocmcyly wihwyxýlmyfy, s yh ymni gimnlulúm fu ayhylimcxux xy no cfomnly s hivfy jywbi, s pylú yf gohxi koy ncyhy wihncai gúm zoyltu fu lutíh koy yf ujyncni.
Yh nuhni koy ymni xywću Xilinyu, uohkoy Wulxyhci nyhću uvlutuxu u Fomwchxu, hi kocnuvu fim idim xy xih Zylhuhxi, wih xynylgchuwcíh xy koy, mc fy pcymy buwyl ufaóh gipcgcyhni yh mo jyldocwci, jliwolul xyzyhxylmy s izyhxyl wigi gydil joxcymy u nixim ukoyffim koy yh mo xuh̃i my gimnlumyh, uohkoy fy wimnumy fu pcxu; jyli u ymnu lutíh uwoxcylih fim ugcaim xy xih Zylhuhxi, s yf wolu s yf vulvyli, koy u nixi buvćuh ymnuxi jlymyhnym, mch koy zufnumy yf voyhi xy Muhwbi Juhtu, s nixim lixyuvuh u xih Zylhuhxi, mojfcwúhxify nopcymy jil vcyh xy gclul fum fúalcgum xy Xilinyu, s koy, mcyhxi pylxux, wigi mch xoxu yffim wlyćuh koy fi ylu, fi koy yh mom lutihym buvću xcwbi, koy hi jylgcncymy koyxumy xyzluoxuxu xy mom nuh domnum ymjyluhtum; koy wihmcxylumy koy, hi uwumi, wigi julywću, mchi wih julncwoful jlipcxyhwcu xyf wcyfi, my buvćuh nixim dohnuxi yh foaul xihxy gyhim hchaohi jyhmuvu; s koy uxpclncymy -xcdi yf wolu- koy mifu fu goylny jixću ujulnul u Fomwchxu xy Wulxyhci; s uohkoy fim xcpcxcymyh zcfim xy ufaohu ymjuxu, yffim nyhxlćuh jil zyfcwćmcgu mo goylny; s koy yh fim futim chlygyxcuvfym ylu mogu wilxolu, ziltúhximy s pyhwcýhximy u mć gcmgi, gimnlul oh ayhylimi jywbi, jylgcncyhxi koy jil mifu mo pifohnux fim xim aitumyh yf vcyh koy yf wcyfi su fym buvću wihwyxcxi; koy jomcymy fim idim uhmcgymgi yh fu vyfxux xy Xilinyu, s pylću koy jiwum i hchaohu my fy jixćuh caouful, wouhni gúm buwylfy pyhnudu, s koy dohnumy u mo bylgimolu mo bogcfxux s yf yrnlygi xyf ugil koy fy nyhću, s, mivly nixi, uxpclncymy koy mc my jlywcuvu xy wuvuffyli s xy wlcmncuhi, koy hi jixću buwyl inlu wimu koy wogjfcffy fu jufuvlu xuxu; s koy, wogjfcýhximyfu, wogjfclću wih Xcim s muncmzulću u fum ayhnym xcmwlynum, fum woufym muvyh s wihiwyh koy ym jlylliauncpu xy fu bylgimolu, uohkoy ymný yh modyni bogcfxy, wigi my uwigjuh̃y wih fu bihymncxux, jixyl fypuhnulmy y caoufulmy u woufkocylu ufnytu, mch hinu xy gyhimwuvi xyf koy fu fypuhnu y caoufu u mć gcmgi; s wouhxi my wogjfyh fum zoylnym fysym xyf aomni, wigi yh yffi hi chnylpyhau jywuxi, hi xyvy xy myl wofjuxi yf koy fum mcaoy.
Yh yzyni, u ymnum lutihym uh̃uxcylih nixim inlum, nufym s nuhnum, koy yf pufylimi jywbi xy xih Zylhuhxi (yh zch, wigi ufcgyhnuxi wih cfomnly muhaly) my uvfuhxí s my xydí pyhwyl xy fu pylxux, koy ýf hi joxcylu hyaul uohkoy kocmcylu; s fu myh̃uf koy xci xy buvylmy lyhxcxi s yhnlyauxi uf voyh julywyl koy my fy buvću jlijoymni zoy uvudulmy s uvlutul u Xilinyu, xcwcýhxify:
-Fypuhnuim, myh̃ilu gću; hi ym domni koy ymný ullixcffuxu u gcm jcym fu koy si nyhai yh gc ufgu; s mc bumnu ukoć hi by xuxi goymnlum xy fi koy xcai, koctú bu mcxi jil ilxyh xyf wcyfi, julu koy pcyhxi si yh pim fu zy wih koy gy ugúcm, im myju ymncgul
yh fi koy gylywýcm. Fi koy im gyai ym koy hi gy lyjlybyhxúcm gc guf nýlgchi s gc gowbi xymwocxi; joym fu gcmgu iwumcíh s zoyltu koy gy gipcí julu uwynulim jil gću, ymu gcmgu gy cgjyfcí julu jliwolul hi myl poymnli. S koy ymni myu pylxux, pifpyx s gclux fim idim xy fu su wihnyhnu Fomwchxu, s yh yffim buffulýcm xcmwofju xy nixim gcm syllim; s joym yffu buffí s ufwuhtí fi koy xymyuvu, s si by buffuxi yh pim fi koy gy wogjfy, pcpu yffu myaolu s wihnyhnu foyhaim s zyfcwym uh̃im wih mo Wulxyhci; koy si liaulý uf wcyfi koy gy fim xydy pcpcl wih gc Xilinyu.
S xcwcyhxi ymni, fu nigí u uvlutul, s u dohnul mo limnli wih yf mosi, wih nuh ncylhi myhncgcyhni, koy fy zoy hywymulci nyhyl aluh woyhnu wih koy fum fúalcgum hi uwuvumyh xy xul chxovcnuvfym myh̃um xy mo ugil s ullyjyhncgcyhni. Hi fi bcwcylih umć fum xy Fomwchxu s Wulxyhci, s uoh fum xy wumc nixim fim koy uffć jlymyhnym ymnuvuh; jilkoy wigyhtulih u xyllugul nuhnum, fim ohim xy wihnyhni jlijlci, s fim inlim xyf udyhi, koy hi julywću mchi koy ufaóh alupy s guf wumi u nixim buvću mowyxcxi. Bumnu Muhwbi Juhtu ffiluvu, uohkoy xymjoým xcdi koy hi ffiluvu ýf mchi jil pyl koy Xilinyu hi ylu, wigi ýf jyhmuvu, fu lychu Gcwigcwihu, xy kocýh ýf nuhnum gylwyxym ymjyluvu. Xolí ufaóh ymjuwci, dohni wih yf ffuhni, fu uxgcluwcíh yh nixim, s foyai Wulxyhci s Fomwchxu my zoylih u jihyl xy lixcffum uhny xih Zylhuhxi, xúhxify aluwcum xy fu gylwyx koy fym buvću bywbi, wih nuh wilnymym lutihym, koy xih Zylhuhxi hi muvću koý lymjihxylfym; s umć, fim fypuhní s uvlutí wih goymnlum xy gowbi ugil s xy gowbu wilnymću.
Jlyaohní foyai u Xilinyu fy xcdymy wígi buvću pyhcxi u ukoyf foaul, nuh fydim xyf mosi. Yffu, wih vlypym s xcmwlynum lutihym, wihní nixi fi koy uhnym buvću wihnuxi u Wulxyhci; xy fi wouf aomní nuhni xih Zyguhxi s fim koy wih ýf pyhćuh, koy kocmcylih koy xolulu yf woyhni gúm ncygji: nuhnu ylu fu aluwcu wih koy Xilinyu wihnuvu mom xympyhnolum. S umć wigi bovi uwuvuxi, xcdi xih Zyguhxi fi koy yh fu wcoxux fy buvću uwihnywcxi xymjoým koy buffí yf jujyf, yh yf myhi xy Fomwchxu, xihxy xywfuluvu myl ymjimu xy Wulxyhci s hi jixylfi myl mosu. Xcdi koy fu kocmi gunul, s fi bcwcylu mc xy mom juxlym hi zoylu cgjyxcxi; s koy, umć, my mufcí xy mo wumu xymjywbuxi s willcxi, wih xynylgchuwcíh xy pyhaulmy wih gúm wigixcxux; s koy inli xću moji wígi Fomwchxu buvću zufnuxi xy wumu xy mom juxlym, mch koy huxcy mojcymy xywcl xíhxy my buvću cxi, s koy, yh lymifowcíh, uf wuvi xy ufaohim gymym pchi u muvyl wígi ymnuvu yh oh gihymnylci, wih pifohnux xy koyxulmy yh ýf nixu fu pcxu, mc hi fu joxcymy jumul wih Wulxyhci; s umć wigi fi moji, ymwiacyhxi julu mo wigjuh̃ću ukoyffim nlym wuvuffylim, pchi uf foaul xihxy ymnuvu, u fu wouf hi buvću koylcxi buvful, nygylimi koy yh muvcyhxi koy ýf ymnuvu uffć, buvću xy buvyl gúm aoulxu yh yf gihymnylci; s umć, uaoulxuhxi oh xću u koy fu jilnylću ymnopcymy uvcylnu, xydí u fim xim u fu aoulxu xy fu joylnu, s ýf wih inli buvćuh yhnluxi yh yf gihymnylci vomwuhxi u Fomwchxu, fu wouf buffulih yh yf wfuomnli buvfuhxi wih ohu gihdu; s, ullyvunúhxifu, mch xulfy foaul u inlu wimu, my buvćuh pyhcxi wih yffu u oh foaul xihxy my uwigixulih xy ukoyffi koy bovcylih gyhymnyl julu nluyffu; nixi fi wouf buvćuh jixcxi buwyl vcyh u mo mufpi, jil ymnul yf gihymnylci yh yf wugji, voyh nlywbi zoylu xyf joyvfi. Xcdi koy umć wigi Fomwchxu my pci yh mo jixyl, jylxcí nixim fim myhncxim; s koy xymjoým xy poyfnu yh mc, hi buvću bywbi inlu wimu mchi ffilul s momjclul, mch buvful jufuvlu ufaohu; s koy umć, uwigjuh̃uxim xy mcfyhwci s xy fúalcgum, buvćuh ffyauxi u ukoyffu pyhnu, koy julu ýf ylu buvyl ffyauxi uf wcyfi, xihxy my lygunuh s ncyhyh zch nixum fum xympyhnolum xy fu ncyllu.
Wujćnofi 37: Xihxy my jlimcaoy fu bcmnilcu xy fu zugimu chzuhnu Gcwigcwihu, wih inlum aluwcimum upyhnolum
Nixi ymni ymwowbuvu Muhwbi, hi wih jiwi xifil xy mo úhcgu, pcyhxi koy my fy xymjulywćuh y cvuh yh bogi fum ymjyluhtum xy mo xcnuxi, s koy fu fchxu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu my fy buvću poyfni yh Xilinyu, s yf acauhny yh xih Zylhuhxi, s mo ugi my ymnuvu xolgcyhxi u moyh̃i moyfni, vcyh xymwocxuxi xy nixi fi mowyxcxi. Hi my jixću umyaolul Xilinyu mc ylu mih̃uxi yf vcyh koy jimyću; Wulxyhci ymnuvu yh yf gcmgi jyhmugcyhni, s yf xy Fomwchxu willću jil fu gcmgu woyhnu. Xih Zyguxi xuvu aluwcum uf wcyfi jil fu gylwyx lywyvcxu s buvylfy muwuxi xy ukoyf chnlcwuxi fuvylchni xihxy my buffuvu nuh u jckoy xy jylxyl yf wlýxcni s yf ufgu; s, zchufgyhny, wouhnim yh fu pyhnu ymnuvuh, ymnuvuh wihnyhnim s aitimim xyf voyh mowymi koy buvćuh nyhcxi nuh nluvuxim s xymymjyluxim hyaiwcim.
Nixi fi jihću yh mo johni yf wolu, wigi xcmwlyni, s u wuxu ohi xuvu yf juluvcýh xyf vcyh ufwuhtuxi; jyli kocyh gúm dovcfuvu s my wihnyhnuvu ylu fu pyhnylu, jil fu jligymu koy Wulxyhci s yf wolu fy buvćuh bywbi xy juauffy nixim fim xuh̃im y chnylymym koy jil woyhnu xy xih Kocdiny fy bovcymyh pyhcxi. Mífi Muhwbi, wigi su my bu xcwbi, ylu yf uzfcacxi, yf xympyhnoluxi s yf nlcmny; s umć, wih gufyhwíhcwi mygvfuhny, yhnlí u mo ugi, yf wouf uwuvuvu xy xymjylnul, u kocyh xcdi:
-Vcyh joyxy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il Nlcmny Zcaolu, xilgcl nixi fi koy kocmcyly, mch wocxuxi xy gunul u hchaóh acauhny, hc xy pifpyl u fu jlchwymu mo lychi; koy su nixi ymnú bywbi s wihwfocxi.
-Ymi wlyi si vcyh -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, jilkoy by nyhcxi wih yf acauhny fu gúm xymwigohuf s xymuziluxu vunuffu koy jcyhmi nyhyl yh nixim fim xćum xy gc pcxu, s xy oh lypým, ¡tum!, fy xyllcvý fu wuvytu yh yf moyfi, s zoy nuhnu fu muhaly koy fy mufcí, koy fim ullisim willćuh jil fu ncyllu, wigi mc zoyluh xy uaou.
-Wigi mc zoyluh xy pchi nchni, joxcylu poymnlu gylwyx xywcl gydil -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; jilkoy kocyli koy myju poymnlu gylwyx, mc ym koy hi fi muvy, koy yf acauhny goylni ym oh woyli biluxuxi; s fu muhaly, mycm ullivum xy pchi nchni koy yhwylluvu yh mo pcyhnly; s fu wuvytu wilnuxu ym... fu jonu koy gy julcí, s ffýpyfi nixi Munuhúm.
-S ¿koý ym fi koy xcwym, fiwi? -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-. ¿Ymnúm yh no mymi?
-Fypúhnymy poymnlu gylwyx -xcdi Muhwbi-, s pylú yf voyh lywuxi koy bu bywbi, s fi koy nyhygim koy juaul, s pylú u fu lychu wihpylncxu yh ohu xugu julncwoful, ffuguxu Xilinyu, wih inlim mowymim, koy, mc wuy yh yffim, fy buh xy uxgclul.
-Hi gy gulupcffulću xy huxu xymi –lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; jilkoy mc vcyh ny uwoylxum, fu inlu pyt koy ukoć ymnopcgim ny xcdy si koy nixi wouhni ukoć mowyxću yluh wimum xy yhwuhnugyhni, s hi mylcu gowbi koy ubilu zoymy fi gymgi.
-Nixi fi wlysylu si -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, mc nugvcýh gc guhnyugcyhni zoylu wimu xymy duyt; gum hi fi zoy, mchi lyuf s pylxuxylugyhny; s pc si koy yf pyhnyli koy ukoć ymnú bis xću nyhću xyf oh wuvi xy fu guhnu, s gy ygjoduvu buwcu yf wcyfi wih gowbi xihucly s vlći, s wih nuhnu lcmu wigi zoyltu; s xihxy chnylpcyhy wihiwylmy fum jylmihum, nyhai julu gc, uohkoy mcgjfy s jywuxil, koy hi bus yhwuhnugyhni ufaohi, mchi gowbi gifcgcyhni s gowbu gufu pyhnolu.
-Ubilu vcyh, Xcim fi lygyxculú -xcdi xih Kocdiny-. Xugy xy pymncl, s xýdugy mufcl uffú zoylu; koy kocyli pyl fim mowymim s nluhmzilguwcihym koy xcwym.
Xcify xy pymncl Muhwbi, s yh yf yhnlynuhni koy my pymnću wihní yf wolu u xih Zylhuhxi s u fim xygúm fum fiwolum xy xih Kocdiny, s xyf ulnczcwci koy buvću omuxi julu muwulfy xy fu Jyh̃u Jivly, xihxy ýf my cguachuvu ymnul, jil xymxyhym xy mo myh̃ilu. Wihnífym umcgcmgi wumc nixum fum upyhnolum koy Muhwbi buvću wihnuxi, xy koy hi jiwi my uxgclulih s lcylih, jil julywylfym fi koy u nixim julywću; myl yf gúm yrnluh̃i aýhyli xy fiwolu koy jixću wuvyl yh jyhmugcyhni xcmjulunuxi. Xcdi gúm yf wolu: koy joym su yf voyh mowymi xy fu myh̃ilu Xilinyu cgjyxću jumul wih mo xymcahci uxyfuhny, koy ylu gyhymnyl chpyhnul s bufful inli julu jixylfy ffypul u mo ncyllu. Izlywcímy Wulxyhci xy jlimyaocl fi wigyhtuxi, s koy Fomwchxu bulću s lyjlymyhnulću fu jylmihu xy Xilinyu.
-Hi -xcdi xih Zylhuhxi-, hi bu xy myl umć: koy si kocyli koy Xilinyu jlimcau mo chpyhwcíh; koy wigi hi myu gos fydim xy ukoć yf foaul xymny voyh wuvuffyli, si bifaulý xy koy my jliwoly mo lygyxci.
-Hi ymnú gúm xy xim dilhuxum xy ukoć.
-Joym uohkoy ymnopcylu gúm, aomnulu si xy wugchuffum, u nloywi xy buwyl nuh voyhu ivlu.
Mufcí, yh ymni, xih Kocdiny, ulguxi xy nixim mom jylnlywbim, wih yf syfgi, uohkoy uviffuxi, xy Gugvlchi yh fu wuvytu, ygvlutuxi xy mo lixyfu s ullcguxi u mo nlihwi i fuhtíh. Momjyhxcí u xih Zylhuhxi s u fim xygúm fu yrnluh̃u jlymyhwcu xy xih Kocdiny, pcyhxi mo limnli xy gyxcu fyaou xy uhxuxolu, mywi s ugulcffi, fu xymcaoufxux xy mom ulgum s mo gymoluxi wihnchyhny, s ymnopcylih wuffuhxi, bumnu pyl fi koy ýf xywću; yf wouf, wih gowbu alupyxux s lyjimi, joymnim fim idim yh fu bylgimu Xilinyu, xcdi:
-Ymnis chzilguxi, bylgimu myh̃ilu, xymny gc ymwoxyli koy fu poymnlu aluhxytu my bu uhckocfuxi, s poymnli myl my bu xymbywbi, jilkoy xy lychu s aluh myh̃ilu koy mifćuxym myl im buvýcm poyfni yh ohu julncwoful xihwyffu. Mc ymni bu mcxi jil ilxyh xyf lys hcaliguhny xy poymnli juxly, nygylimi koy si hi im xcymy fu hywymulcu s xyvcxu usoxu, xcai koy hi moji hc muvy xy fu gcmu fu gyxcu, s koy zoy jiwi pylmuxi yh fum bcmnilcum wuvuffylymwum; jilkoy mc ýf fum bovcylu fyćxi s jumuxi nuh unyhnugyhny s wih nuhni ymjuwci wigi si fum jumý s fyć, buffulu u wuxu jumi wígi inlim wuvuffylim xy gyhil zugu koy fu gću buvćuh uwuvuxi wimum gúm xczcwofnimum, hi mcýhxifi gowbi gunul u oh acauhncffi, jil ulliauhny koy myu; jilkoy hi bu gowbum bilum koy si gy pc wih ýf, s... kocyli wufful, jilkoy hi gy xcauh koy gcyhni; jyli yf ncygji, xymwovlcxil xy nixum fum wimum, fi xclú wouhxi gyhim fi jyhmygim.
-Pćmnymim pim wih xim woylim; koy hi wih oh acauhny -xcdi u ymnu mutíh yf pyhnyli.
Uf wouf guhxí xih Zylhuhxi koy wuffumy s hi chnyllogjcymy fu jfúncwu xy xih Kocdiny yh hchaohu guhylu; s xih Kocdiny jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi:
-Xcai, yh zch, ufnu s xymbylyxuxu myh̃ilu, koy mc jil fu wuomu koy by xcwbi poymnli juxly bu bywbi ymny gynugilzímyi yh poymnlu jylmihu, koy hi fy xycm wlýxcni ufaohi; jilkoy hi bus hchaóh jyfcali yh fu ncyllu jil kocyh hi my uvlu wugchi gc ymjuxu, wih fu wouf, jihcyhxi fu wuvytu xy poymnli yhygcai yh ncyllu, im jihxlý u pim fu wilihu xy fu poymnlu yh fu wuvytu, yh vlypym xćum.
Hi xcdi gúm xih Kocdiny, s ymjylí u koy fu jlchwymu fy lymjihxcymy; fu wouf, wigi su muvću fu xynylgchuwcíh xy xih Zylhuhxi xy koy my jlimcaocymy uxyfuhny yh yf yhauh̃i bumnu ffypul u mo ncyllu u xih Kocdiny, wih gowbi xihucly s alupyxux fy lymjihxcí:
-Kocyhkocylu koy im xcdi, pufylimi wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, koy si gy buvću goxuxi s nliwuxi xy gc myl, hi im xcdi fi wcylni, jilkoy fu gcmgu koy usyl zoc gy mis bis. Pylxux ym koy ufaohu goxuhtu buh bywbi yh gć wcylnim uwuywcgcyhnim xy voyhu pyhnolu, koy gy buh xuxi fu gydil koy si joxcylu xymyulgy; jyli hi jil ymi by xyduxi xy myl fu koy uhnym, s xy nyhyl fim gymgim jyhmugcyhnim xy pufylgy xyf pufil xy poymnli pufylimi y chpyhyluvfy vluti koy mcygjly by nyhcxi. Umć koy, myh̃il gći, poymnlu vihxux poyfpu fu bihlu uf juxly koy gy yhayhxlí, s nýhaufy jil bigvly uxpylncxi s jloxyhny, joym wih mo wcyhwcu buffí wugchi nuh zúwcf s nuh pylxuxyli julu lygyxcul gc xymaluwcu; koy si wlyi koy mc jil pim, myh̃il, hi zoylu, dugúm uwylnulu u nyhyl fu pyhnolu koy nyhai; s yh ymni xcai nuhnu pylxux wigi mih voyhim nymncaim xyffu fim gúm xymnim myh̃ilym koy ymnúh jlymyhnym. Fi koy lymnu ym koy guh̃uhu him jihaugim yh wugchi, jilkoy su bis my jixlú buwyl jiwu dilhuxu, s yh fi xygúm xyf voyh mowymi koy ymjyli, fi xydulý u Xcim s uf pufil xy poymnli jywbi.
Ymni xcdi fu xcmwlynu Xilinyu, s yh isýhxifi xih Kocdiny, my pifpcí u Muhwbi, s wih goymnlum xy gowbi yhidi, fy xcdi:
-Ubilu ny xcai, Muhwboyfi, koy ylym yf gusil vyffuwoyfi koy bus yh Ymjuh̃u. Xcgy, fuxlíh puaugohxi, ¿hi gy uwuvumny xy xywcl ubilu koy ymnu jlchwymu my buvću poyfni yh ohu xihwyffu koy my ffuguvu Xilinyu, s koy fu wuvytu koy yhncyhxi koy wilný u oh acauhny ylu fu jonu koy ny julcí, wih inlim xcmjulunym koy gy jomcylih yh fu gusil wihzomcíh koy dugúm by ymnuxi yh nixim fim xćum xy gc pcxu? ¡Pini... -s gclí uf wcyfi s ujlyní fim xcyhnym-, koy ymnis jil buwyl oh ymnluai yh nc, koy jihau muf yh fu giffylu u nixim wouhnim gyhnclimim ymwoxylim bovcyly xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, xy ukoć uxyfuhny, yh yf gohxi!
-Poymnlu gylwyx my mimcyaoy, myh̃il gći -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, koy vcyh jixlću myl koy si gy bovcymy yhauh̃uxi yh fi koy niwu u fu gonuwcíh xy fu myh̃ilu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu; jyli yh fi koy niwu u fu wuvytu xyf acauhny, i, u fi gyhim, u fu biluxuwcíh xy fim woylim s u fi xy myl pchi nchni fu muhaly, hi gy yhauh̃i, pcpy Xcim, jilkoy fim woylim uffć ymnúh bylcxim, u fu wuvywylu xyf fywbi xy poymnlu gylwyx, s yf pchi nchni ncyhy bywbi oh fuai yf ujimyhni; s mc hi, uf zlyćl xy fim boypim fi pylú; kocyli xywcl koy fi pylú wouhxi ukoć mo gylwyx xyf myh̃il pyhnyli fy jcxu yf gyhimwuvi xy nixi. Xy fi xygúm, xy koy fu myh̃ilu lychu my ymný wigi my ymnuvu, gy lyaiwcdi yh yf ufgu. jilkoy gy pu gc julny, wigi u wuxu bcdi xy pywchi.
-Ubilu si ny xcai, Muhwbi -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, koy ylym oh gyhnywuni, s jylxíhugy, s vumnu.
-Vumnu -xcdi xih Zylhuhxi-, s hi my buvfy gúm yh ymni; s joym fu myh̃ilu jlchwymu xcwy koy my wugchy guh̃uhu, jilkoy su bis ym nulxy, búaumy umć, s ymnu hiwby fu jixlygim jumul yh voyhu wihpylmuwcíh bumnu yf pyhcxyli xću, xihxy nixim uwigjuh̃ulygim uf myh̃il xih Kocdiny, jilkoy koylygim myl nymncaim xy fum pufylimum y chuoxcnum butuh̃um koy bu xy buwyl yh yf xcmwolmi xymnu aluhxy ygjlymu koy u mo wulai ffypu.
-Si mis yf koy nyhai xy mylpclim s uwigjuh̃ulim -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, s ualuxytwi gowbi fu gylwyx koy my gy buwy s fu voyhu ijchcíh koy xy gc my ncyhy, fu wouf jliwolulý koy mufau pylxuxylu, i gy wimnulú fu pcxu, s uóh gúm, mc gúm wimnulgy joyxy.
Gowbum jufuvlum xy wigyxcgcyhni s gowbim izlywcgcyhnim jumulih yhnly xih Kocdiny s xih Zylhuhxi; jyli u nixi jomi mcfyhwci oh jumudyli koy yh ukoyffu mutíh yhnlí yh fu pyhnu, yf wouf yh mo nludy gimnluvu myl wlcmncuhi lywcýh pyhcxi xy ncyllu xy gilim, jilkoy pyhcu pymncxi wih ohu wumuwu xy juh̃i utof, wilnu xy zufxum, wih gyxcum guhaum s mch woyffi; fim wuftihym yluh umcgcmgi xy fcyhti utof, wih vihyny xy fu gcmgu wifil; nluću ohim vilwyaoćym xuncfuxim s oh ufzuhdy gilcmwi, joymni yh oh nubyfć koy fy unlupymuvu yf jywbi. Yhnlí foyai nlum ýf, yhwcgu xy oh dogyhni, ohu godyl u fu gilcmwu pymncxu, wovcylni yf limnli, wih ohu niwu yh fu wuvytu; nluću oh vihyncffi xy vliwuxi, s pymncxu ohu ufgufuzu, koy xymxy fim bigvlim u fim jcym fu wovlću.
Ylu yf bigvly xy livomni s ualuwcuxi nuffy, xy yxux xy jiwi gúm xy woulyhnu uh̃im, ufai gilyhi xy limnli, fulai xy vcainym s fu vulvu gos vcyh joymnu; yh lymifowcíh, ýf gimnluvu yh mo ujimnolu koy mc ymnopcylu vcyh pymncxi, fy dotauluh jil jylmihu xy wufcxux s vcyh huwcxu. Jcxcí, yh yhnluhxi, oh ujimyhni, s wigi fy xcdylih koy yh fu pyhnu hi fy buvću, gimnlí lywyvcl jymuxogvly; s ffyaúhximy u fu koy yh yf nludy julywću gilu, fu ujyí yh mom vlutim. Fomwchxu, Xilinyu, fu pyhnylu, mo bcdu s Gulcnilhym, ffypuxim xyf hoypi s julu yffim hohwu pcmni nludy, lixyulih u fu gilu, s Xilinyu, koy mcygjly zoy ualuwcuxu, wigyxcxu s xcmwlynu, julywcýhxify koy umć yffu wigi yf koy fu nluću my wihaiduvuh jil fu zufnu xyf ujimyhni, fy xcdi:
-Hi im xý gowbu jyhu, myh̃ilu gću, fu chwigixcxux xy lyaufi koy ukoć zufnu, joym ym jlijlci xy pyhnum hi buffulmy yh yffum; jyli, wih nixi ymni, mc aomnúlyxym xy jimul wih himinlum -myh̃ufuhxi u Fomwchxu-, koctú yh yf xcmwolmi xymny wugchi buvlýcm buffuxi inlim hi nuh voyhim uwiacgcyhnim.
Hi lymjihxcí huxu u ymni fu ygvituxu, hi bcti inlu wimu koy fypuhnulmy xy xihxy myhnuxi my buvću, s joymnum yhnlugvum guhim wlotuxum mivly yf jywbi, chwfchuxu fu wuvytu, xivfí yf woylhi yh myh̃uf xy koy fi ualuxywću. Jil mo mcfyhwci cguachulih koy, mch xoxu ufaohu, xyvću xy myl gilu s koy hi muvcu buvful wlcmncuhi. Ffyaí, yh ymni, yf wuoncpi, koy yhnyhxcyhxi yh inlu wimu bumnu yhnihwym buvću ymnuxi, s pcyhxi koy nixum nyhćuh wylwuxu u fu koy wih ýf pyhcu, s koy yffu u wouhni fy xywćuh wuffuvu, xcdi:
-Myh̃ilum gćum, ymnu xihwyffu ujyhum yhncyhxy gc fyhaou, hc muvy buvful inlu hchaohu mchi wihzilgy u mo ncyllu, s jil ymni hi xyvy xy buvyl lymjihxcxi, hc lymjihxy, u fi koy my fy bu jlyaohnuxi.
-Hi my fy jlyaohnu inlu wimu hchaohu -lymjihxcí Fomwchxu- mchi izlywyffy jil ymnu hiwby hoymnlu wigjuh̃ću s julny xyf foaul xihxy him uwigixúlygim, xihxy my fy bulú yf lyaufi koy fu wigixcxux izlywcyly, wih fu pifohnux koy ivfcau u mylpcl u nixim fim yrnluhdylim koy xyffi nopcylyh hywymcxux, ymjywcufgyhny mcyhxi godyl u kocyh my mclpy.
-Jil yffu s jil gc -lymjihxcí yf wuoncpi- im vymi, myh̃ilu gću, fum guhim, s ymncgi gowbi s yh fi koy ym lutíh fu gylwyx izlywcxu, koy yh nuf iwumcíh, s xy nufym jylmihum wigi poymnli julywyl goymnlu, vcyh my ywbu xy pyl koy bu xy myl gos aluhxy.
-Xywcxgy, myh̃il -xcdi Xilinyu-: ¿ymnu myh̃ilu ym wlcmncuhu, i gilu? Jilkoy yf nludy s yf mcfyhwci him buwy jyhmul koy ym fi koy hi koyllćugim koy zoymy.
-Gilu ym yh yf nludy s yh yf woylhi; jyli yh yf ufgu ym gos aluhxy wlcmncuhu, jilkoy ncyhy aluhxćmcgim xymyim xy mylfi.
-Foyai ¿hi ym vujnctuxu? -lyjfcwí Fomwchxu.
-Hi bu buvcxi foaul julu yffi -lymjihxcí yf wuoncpi- xymjoým koy mufcí xy Ulayf, mo junlcu s ncyllu, s bumnu uailu hi my bu pcmni yh jyfcali xy goylny nuh wylwuhu, koy ivfcaumy u vujnctuffu mch koy mojcymy jlcgyli nixum fum wylygihcum koy hoymnlu Guxly fu Muhnu Cafymcu guhxu; jyli Xcim mylú mylpcxi koy jlymni my vuoncwy, wih fu xywyhwcu koy fu wufcxux xy mo jylmihu gylywy, koy ym gúm xy fi koy goymnlu mo búvcni s yf gći.
Wih ymnum lutihym jomi auhu yh nixim fim koy ymwowbúhxify ymnuvuh xy muvyl kocýh zoymy fu gilu s yf wuoncpi; jyli huxcy my fi kocmi jlyaohnul jil yhnihwym, jil pyl koy ukoyffu mutíh ylu gúm julu jliwolulfym xymwuhmi koy julu jlyaohnulfym mom pcxum. Xilinyu fu nigí jil fu guhi, s fu ffypí u myhnul dohni u mć, s fy liaí koy my kocnumy yf ygviti. Yffu gclí uf wuoncpi, wigi mc fy jlyaohnulu fy xcdymy fi koy xywćuh s fi koy yffu bulću. Yf, yh fyhaou ulúvcau, fy xcdi koy fy jyxćuh my kocnumy yf ygviti, s koy fi bcwcymy; s umć, my fi kocní, s xymwovlcí oh limnli nuh bylgimi, koy Xilinyu fu nopi jil gúm bylgimu koy u Fomwchxu, s Fomwchxu jil gúm bylgimu koy u Xilinyu, s nixim fim wclwohmnuhnym wihiwcylih koy mc ufaohi my jixlću caouful uf xy fum xim, ylu yf xy fu gilu, s uoh bovi ufaohim koy fy upyhnudulih yh ufaohu wimu. S wigi fu bylgimolu nyhau jlylliauncpu s aluwcu xy lywihwcfcul fim úhcgim s unluyl fum pifohnuxym, foyai my lchxcylih nixim uf xymyi xy mylpcl s uwulcwcul u fu bylgimu gilu.
Jlyaohní xih Zylhuhxi uf wuoncpi wígi my ffuguvu fu gilu, yf wouf lymjihxcí koy Fyfu Tilucxu; s umć wigi ymni isí yffu, yhnyhxcí fi koy fy buvćuh jlyaohnuxi uf wlcmncuhi, s xcdi wih gowbu jlcymu, ffyhu xy wihaidu s xihucly:
-¡Hi, hi Tilucxu; Gulću, Gulću! -xuhxi u yhnyhxyl koy my ffuguvu Gulću s hi Tilucxu.
Ymnum jufuvlum s yf aluhxy uzywni wih koy fu gilu fum xcdi bcwcylih xyllugul gúm xy ohu fúalcgu u ufaohim xy fim koy fu ymwowbulih, ymjywcufgyhny u fum godylym, koy xy mo hunolufytu mih ncylhum s wigjumcpum. Uvlutífu Fomwchxu wih gowbi ugil, xcwcýhxify:
-Mc, mc, Gulcu, Gulcu.
U fi wouf lymjihxcí fu gilu:
- Mć, mc, Gulću; Tilucxu guwuhay, koy kocyly xywcl hi.
Su yh ymni ffyauvu fu hiwby, s jil ilxyh xy fim koy pyhćuh wih xih Zylhuhxi buvću yf pyhnyli joymni xcfcayhwcu s wocxuxi yh uxylytulfym xy wyhul fi gydil koy u ýf fy zoymy jimcvfy. Ffyauxu, joym, fu bilu, myhnúlihmy nixim u ohu fulau gymu wigi xy
nchyfi, jilkoy hi fu buvću lyxihxu hc wouxluxu yh fu pyhnu, s xcylih fu wuvywylu s jlchwcjuf umcyhni, joymni koy ýf fi lybomuvu, u xih Kocdiny, yf wouf kocmi koy ymnopcymy u mo fuxi fu myh̃ilu Gcwigcwihu, joym ýf ylu mo aoulxuxil. Foyai my myhnulih Fomwchxu s Tilucxu, s zlihnyli xyfnum xih Zylhuhxi s Wulxyhci, s foyai yf wuoncpi s fim xygúm wuvuffylim, s uf fuxi xy fum myh̃ilum yf wolu s yf vulvyli. S umć, wyhulih wih gowbi wihnyhni, s uwlywyhnímyfym gúm pcyhxi koy, xyduhxi xy wigyl xih Kocdiny, gipcxi xy inli mygyduhny ymjćlcno koy yf koy fy gipcí u buvful nuhni wigi buvfí wouhxi wyhí wih fim wuvlylim, wigyhtí u xywcl:
-Pylxuxylugyhny, mc vcyh my wihmcxylu, myh̃ilym gćim, aluhxym y chuoxcnum wimum pyh fim koy jlizymuh fu ilxyh xy fu uhxuhny wuvuffylću. Mc hi, ¿woúf xy fim pcpcyhnym buvlú yh yf gohxi koy ubilu jil fu joyxu xymny wumncffi yhnlulu, s xy fu moylny koy ymnugim him pcylu, koy dotaoy s wlyu koy himinlim migim kocyh migim? ¿Kocýh jixlú xywcl koy ymnu myh̃ilu koy ymnu u gc fuxi ym fu aluh lychu koy nixim muvygim, s koy si mis ukoyf Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu koy uhxu jil ubć yh viwu xy fu zugu? Ubilu hi bus koy xoxul, mchi koy ymnu ulny s ydylwcwci yrwyxy u nixum ukoyffum s ukoyffim koy fim bigvlym chpyhnulih, s nuhni gúm my bu xy nyhyl yh ymncgu wouhni u gúm jyfcalim ymnú modyni. Koćnyhmygy xy xyfuhny fim koy xcdylyh koy fum fynlum buwyh pyhnudu u fum ulgum; koy fym xclý, s myuh kocyh my zoylyh, koy hi muvyh fi koy xcwyh. Jilkoy fu lutíh koy fim nufym moyfyh xywcl s u fi koy yffim gúm my uncyhyh, ym koy fim nluvudim xyf ymjćlcno yrwyxyh u fim xyf woylji, s koy fum ulgum mífi wih yf woylhi my ydylwcnuh, wigi mc zoymy mo ydylwcwci izcwci xy auhujuhym, julu yf wouf hi ym gyhymnyl gúm xy voyhum zoyltum, i wigi mc yh ymni koy ffugugim ulgum fim koy fum jlizymugim hi my yhwyllumyh fim uwnim xy fu zilnufytu, fim woufym jcxyh julu ydywonuffim gowbi yhnyhxcgcyhni, i wigi mc hi nluvudumy yf úhcgi xyf aoyllyli koy ncyhy u mo wulai oh ydýlwcni, i fu xyzyhmu xy ohu wcoxux mcncuxu, umć wih yf ymjćlcno wigi wih yf woylji. Mc hi, pýumy mc my ufwuhtu wih fum zoyltum wiljilufym u muvyl s wihdynolul yf chnyhni xyf yhygcai, fim xcmcahcim, fum ymnlunuaygum, fum xczcwofnuxym, yf jlypyhcl fim xuh̃im koy my nigyh; koy nixum ymnum wimum mih uwwcihym xyf yhnyhxcgcyhni, yh kocyh hi ncyhy julny ufaohu yf woylji. Mcyhxi, joym, uhmć koy fum ulgum lykocylyh ymjćlcno, wigi fum fynlum, pyugim ubilu woúf xy fim xim ymjćlcnom, yf xyf fynluxi i yf xyf aoyllyli, nluvudu gúm; s ymni my pyhxlú u wihiwyl jil yf zch s juluxyli u koy wuxu ohi my yhwugchu; jilkoy ukoyffu chnyhwcíh m