wuh̃ihym xy ulncffylću my umymnuh xy fu julny wihnlulcu, koy hi xcmnuh xy mo woylji ohu fuhtu, s pcyhxi koy uf jlcgyl xymwocxi xy fim jcym clću u pcmcnul fim jlizohxim myhim xy Hyjnohi, s, wih nixi ymni, wih chnlýjcxi wilutíh, ffypuxi xy fu bihlu koy fy chwcnu, my jihy u myl vfuhwi xy nuhnu ulwuvowylću, s jliwolu jumul jil nuh ymnlywbi jumi uf vudyf wihnlulci. S fi koy gúm ym xy uxgclul, koy ujyhum ohi bu wućxi xihxy hi my jixlú fypuhnul bumnu fu zch xyf gohxi, wouhxi inli iwoju mo gymgi foaul; s mc ýmny nugvcýh wuy yh yf gul, koy wigi u yhygcai fy uaoulxu, inli s inli fy mowyxy mch xul ncygji uf ncygji xy mom goylnym: pufyhnću s unlypcgcyhni yf gusil koy my joyxy bufful yh nixim fim nluhwym xy fu aoyllu.
¡Vcyh busuh ukoyffim vyhxcnim mcafim koy wulywcylih xy fu ymjuhnuvfy zolcu xy ukoymnim yhxygihcuxim chmnlogyhnim xy fu ulncffylću¡ u wosi chpyhnil nyhai julu gć koy yh yf chzcylhi my fy ymnú xuhxi yf jlygci xy mo xcuvífcwu chpyhwcíh, wih fu wouf xci wuomu koy oh chzugy s wivulxy vluti kocny fu pcxu u oh pufylimi wuvuffyli, s koy, mch muvyl wígi i jil xíhxy, yh fu gcnux xyf wiludy s vlći koy yhwcyhxy s uhcgu u fim pufcyhnym jywbim, ffyau ohu xymguhxuxu vufu, xcmjuluxu xy kocyh koctú bosí s my ymjuhní xyf lymjfuhxil koy bcti yf zoyai uf xcmjulul xy fu gufxcnu
