Wujćnofi 39: Xihxy yf wuoncpi woyhnu mo pcxu s mowymim
-Yh oh foaul xy fum gihnuh̃um xy Fyíh nopi jlchwcjci gc fchudy, wih kocyh zoy gúm ualuxywcxu s fcvyluf fu hunolufytu koy fu zilnohu, uohkoy yh fu ymnlywbytu xy ukoyffim joyvfim nixupću ufwuhtuvu gc juxly zugu xy lcwi, s pylxuxylugyhny fi zoylu mc umć my xcylu guh̃u u wihmylpul mo buwcyhxu wigi my fu xuvu yh aumnuffu. S fu wihxcwcíh koy nyhću xy myl fcvyluf s aumnuxil fy jliwyxcí xy buvyl mcxi mifxuxi fim uh̃im xy mo dopyhnox; koy ym ymwoyfu fu mifxuxymwu xihxy yf gytkochi my buwy zluhwi, s yf zluhwi, jlíxcai; s mc ufaohim mifxuxim my buffuh gcmyluvfym, mih wigi gihmnloim koy my pyh lulum pywym. Jumuvu gc juxly fim nýlgchim xy fu fcvylufcxux s lusuvu yh fim xy myl jlíxcai, wimu koy hi fy ym xy hchaóh jlipywbi uf bigvly wumuxi s koy ncyhy bcdim koy fy buh xy mowyxyl yh yf higvly s yh yf myl. Fim koy gc juxly nyhću yluh nlym, nixim pulihym s nixim xy yxux xy jixyl yfyacl ymnuxi. Pcyhxi, joym, gc juxly koy, myaóh ýf xywću, hi jixću clmy u fu guhi wihnlu mo wihxcwcíh, kocmi jlcpulmy xyf chmnlogyhni s wuomu koy fy buwcu aumnuxil s xuxcpimi, koy zoy jlcpulmy xy fu buwcyhxu, mch fu wouf yf gcmgi Ufyduhxli julywcylu ymnlywbi. S umć, ffugúhxihim oh xću u nixim nlym u mifum yh oh ujimyhni, him xcdi ohum lutihym mygyduhnym u fum koy ubilu xclý:
«-Bcdim, julu xywclim koy im kocyli vcyh vumnu muvyl s xywcl koy micm gcm bcdim; s julu yhnyhxyl koy im kocyli guf vumnu muvyl koy hi gy pis u fu guhi yh fi koy niwu u wihmylpul poymnlu buwcyhxu. Joym julu koy yhnyhxúcm xymxy ukoć uxyfuhny koy im kocyli wigi juxly, s koy hi im kocyli xymnlocl wigi juxlumnli, kocyli buwyl ohu wimu wih piminlim koy bu gowbim xćum koy fu nyhai jyhmuxu s wih guxolu wihmcxyluwcíh xcmjoymnu. Piminlim ymnúcm su yh yxux xy nigul ymnuxi, i, u fi gyhim, xy yfyacl ydylwcwci, nuf, koy, wouhxi gusilym, im bihly s ujlipywby. S fi koy by jyhmuxi ym buwyl xy gc buwcyhxu wounli julnym: fum nlym im xulý u piminlim,
u wuxu ohi fi koy fy niwuly, mch yrwyxyl yh wimu ufaohu, s wih fu inlu gy koyxulý si julu pcpcl s momnyhnulgy fim xćum koy yf wcyfi zoyly mylpcxi xy xulgy xy pcxu. Jyli koyllću koy xymjoým koy wuxu ohi nopcymy yh mo jixyl fu julny koy fy niwu xy mo buwcyhxu, mcaocymy ohi xy fim wugchim koy fy xclý. Bus oh lyzlúh yh hoymnlu Ymjuh̃u, u gc julywyl, gos pylxuxyli, wigi nixim fi mih, jil myl myhnyhwcum vlypym muwuxum xy fu foyhau s xcmwlynu yrjylcyhwcu; s yf koy si xcai xcwy: «Cafymcu, i gul, i wumu lyuf», wigi mc gúm wfulugyhny xcdylu: «Kocyh kocmcyly pufyl s myl lcwi, mcau, i fu Cafymcu, i hupyaoy, ydylwcnuhxi yf ulny xy fu gylwuhwću, i yhnly u mylpcl u fim lysym yh mom wumum»; jilkoy xcwyh: «Gúm pufy gcaudu xy lys koy gylwyx xy myh̃il». Xcai ymni jilkoy koyllću, s ym gc pifohnux, koy ohi xy piminlim mcaocymy fum fynlum, yf inli fu gylwuhwću, s yf inli mclpcymy uf lys yh fu aoyllu, joym ym xczcwofnimi yhnlul u mylpclfy yh mo wumu; koy su koy fu aoyllu hi xý gowbum lckoytum, moyfy xul gowbi pufil s gowbu zugu. Xyhnli xy iwbi xćum im xulý nixu poymnlu julny yh xchylim, mch xyzluoxulim yh oh ulxcny, wigi fi pylýcm jil fu ivlu. Xywcxgy ubilu mc koylýcm myaocl gc julywyl s wihmydi yh fi koy im by jlijoymni».
S guhxúhxigy u gc, jil myl yf gusil, koy lymjihxcymy, xymjoým xy buvylfy xcwbi koy hi my xymbcwcymy xy fu buwcyhxu, mchi koy aumnumy nixi fi koy zoymy mo pifohnux, koy himinlim ýlugim gitim julu muvyl auhulfu, pchy u wihwfocl yh koy wogjfclću mo aomni, s koy yf gći ylu myaocl yf ydylwcwci xy fum ulgum, mclpcyhxi yh ýf u Xcim s u gc lys. Yf myaohxi bylguhi bcti fim gymgim izlywcgcyhnim, s ymwiací yf clmy u fum Chxcum, ffypuhxi ygjfyuxu fu buwcyhxu koy fy wojcymy. Yf gyhil, s, u fi koy si wlyi, yf gúm xcmwlyni, xcdi koy koylću myaocl fu Cafymcu, i clmy u uwuvul mom wigyhtuxim ymnoxcim u Mufuguhwu.
Umć wigi uwuvugim xy wihwilxulhim s ymwiayl hoymnlim ydylwcwcim, gc juxly him uvlutí u nixim, s wih fu vlypyxux koy xcdi jomi jil ivlu wouhni him buvću jligyncxi; s xuhxi u wuxu ohi mo julny, koy, u fi koy my gy uwoylxu, zoylih wuxu nlym gcf xowuxim yh xchylim (jilkoy oh hoymnli nći wigjlí nixu fu buwcyhxu s fu juaí xy wihnuxi, jilkoy hi mufcymy xyf nlihwi xy fu wumu), yh oh gymgi xću him xymjyxcgim nixim nlym xy hoymnli voyh juxly, s yh ukoyf gymgi, julywcýhxigy u gć myl chboguhcxux koy gc juxly koyxumy pcydi s wih nuh jiwu buwcyhxu, bcwy wih ýf koy xy gcm nlym gcf nigumy fim xim gcf xowuxim, jilkoy u gć gy vumnuvu yf lymni julu uwigixulgy xy fi koy buvću gyhymnyl oh mifxuxi. Gcm xim bylguhim, gipcxim xy gc ydygjfi, wuxu ohi fy xci gcf xowuxim; xy gixi koy u gc juxly fy koyxulih wounli gcf yh xchylim, s gúm nlym gcf, koy, u fi koy julywy, pufću fu buwcyhxu koy fy woji, koy hi kocmi pyhxyl, mchi koyxulmy wih yffu yh lućwym. Xcai, yh zch, koy him xymjyxcgim xýf, s xy ukoyf hoymnli nći koy by xcwbi, hi mch gowbi myhncgcyhni s fúalcgum xy nixim, yhwulaúhxihim koy fym bcwcýmygim muvyl, nixum fum pywym koy bovcymy wigixcxux julu yffi, xy hoymnlim mowymim, jlímjylim i uxpylmim. Jligynćgimmyfi s uvlutúhxihim s ywbúhxihim mo vyhxcwcíh, yf ohi nigí yf pcudy xy Mufuguhwu, yf inli xy Mypcffu, s si yf xy Ufcwuhny, uxihxy nopy hoypum koy buvću ohu hupy achipymu koy wulauvu uffć fuhu julu Aýhipu.
Ymny bulú pychny s xim uh̃im koy mufć xy wumu xy gc juxly, s yh nixim yffim, joymni koy by ymwlcni ufaohum wulnum, hi by muvcxi xýf hc xy gcm bylguhim hoypu ufaohu; s fi koy yh ymny xcmwolmi xy ncygji by jumuxi fi xclý vlypygyhny. Ygvulkoýgy yh Ufcwuhny, ffyaoý wih jlímjyli pcudy u Aýhipu, zoc xymxy uffć u Gcfúh, xihxy gy uwigixý xy ulgum s xy ufaohum aufum xy mifxuxi, xy xihxy kocmy cl u myhnul gc jfutu uf Jcugihny; s ymnuhxi su xy wugchi julu Ufyduhxlću xy fu Jufću, nopy hoypum koy yf aluh xokoy xy Ufvu jumuvu u Zfuhxym. Goxý jlijímcni, zoćgy wih ýf, mylpćfy yh fum dilhuxum koy bcti, buffýgy yh fu goylny xy fim wihxym xy Yaoygíh s xy Bilhim, ufwuhwý u myl ufzýlyt xy oh zugimi wujcnúh xy Aouxufudulu, ffuguxi Xcyai xy Olvchu, s u wuvi xy ufaóh ncygji koy ffyaoý u Zfuhxym, my nopi hoypum xy fu fcau koy fu Muhncxux xyf Juju Jći Kochni, xy zyfcwy lywilxuwcíh, buvću bywbi wih Pyhywcu s wih Ymjuh̃u, wihnlu yf yhygcai wigóh, koy ym yf Nolwi; yf wouf yh ukoyf gymgi
ncygji buvću auhuxi wih mo ulguxu fu zugimu cmfu xy Wbcjly, koy ymnuvu xyvudi xyf xigchci xyf Pyhywcuhi: jýlxcxu fugyhnuvfy s xymxcwbuxu.
Mójimy wcylni koy pyhcu jil ayhyluf xymnu fcau yf mylyhćmcgi xih Douh xy Uomnlcu, bylguhi hunoluf xy hoymnli voyh lys xih Zyfcjy; xcpofaímy yf aluhxćmcgi ujuluni xy aoyllu koy my buwću; nixi fi wouf gy chwcní s wihgipcí yf úhcgi s yf xymyi xy pylgy yh fu dilhuxu koy my ymjyluvu; s uohkoy nyhću vullohnim, s wumc jligymum wcylnum, xy koy yh fu jlcgylu iwumcíh koy my izlywcymy mylću jligipcxi u wujcnúh, fi kocmy xydul nixi s pyhclgy, wigi gy pchy u Cnufcu. S kocmi gc voyhu moylny koy yf myh̃il xih Douh xy Uomnlcu uwuvuvu xy ffyaul u Aýhipu; koy jumuvu u Hújifym u dohnulmy wih fu ulguxu xy Pyhywcu, wigi xymjoým fi bcti yh Gywchu. Xcai, yh zch, koy si gy buffý yh ukoyffu zyfcwćmcgu dilhuxu, su bywbi wujcnúh xy chzuhnylću, u wosi bihlimi wulai gy movcí gc voyhu moylny, gúm koy gcm gylywcgcyhnim. S ukoyf xću, koy zoy julu fu wlcmncuhxux nuh xcwbimi, jilkoy yh ýf my xymyhauh̃í yf gohxi s nixum fum huwcihym xyf yllil yh koy ymnuvuh, wlysyhxi koy fim nolwim yluh chpyhwcvfym jil fu gul, yh ukoyf xću, xcai, xihxy koyxí yf ilaoffi s mivylvcu iniguhu koyvluhnuxu, yhnly nuhnim pyhnolimim koy uffć bovi (jilkoy gúm pyhnolu nopcylih fim wlcmncuhim koy uffć golcylih koy fim koy pcpim s pyhwyxilym koyxulih), si mífi zoc yf xymxcwbuxi; joym, yh wugvci xy koy joxcylu ymjylul, mc zoylu yh fim liguhim mcafim, ufaohu hupuf wilihu, gy pc ukoyffu hiwby koy mcaocí u nuh zugimi xću wih wuxyhum u fim jcym s ymjimum u fum guhim. S zoy xymnu moylny: koy buvcyhxi yf Owbufć, lys xy Ulayf, unlypcxi s pyhnolimi wimulci, ygvymncxi s lyhxcxi fu wujcnuhu xy Gufnu, koy mifim nlym wuvuffylim koyxulih pcpim yh yffu, s ýmnim guf bylcxim, uwoxcí fu wujcnuhu xy Douh Uhxlyu u miwillyffu, yh fu wouf si cvu wih gc wigjuh̃ću; s buwcyhxi fi koy xyvću yh iwumcíh mygyduhny, mufný yh fu aufylu wihnlulcu, fu wouf xympcúhximy xy fu koy fu buvću ygvymncxi, ymnilví koy gcm mifxuxim gy mcaocymyh, s umć, gy buffý mifi yhnly gcm yhygcaim, u kocyh hi joxy lymcmncl, jil myl nuhnim; y