Ffypúlihgy u Wihmnuhnchijfu, xihxy yf Aluh Nolwi Myfcg bcti ayhyluf xy fu gul u gc ugi, jilkoy buvću bywbi mo xyvyl yh fu vunuffu, buvcyhxi ffypuxi jil goymnlu xy mo pufil yf ymnuhxulny xy fu lyfcacíh xy Gufnu. Buffýgy yf myaohxi uh̃i, koy zoy yf xy mynyhnu s xim, yh Hupulchi viauhxi yh fu wujcnuhu xy fim nlym zuhufym. Pc s hiný fu iwumcíh koy uffć my jylxcí xy hi wiayl yh yf joylni nixu yf ulguxu nolkoymwu; jilkoy nixim fim fypyhnym s ayhćtulim koy yh yffu pyhćuh nopcylih jil wcylni koy fym buvćuh xy ygvymncl xyhnli xyf gymgi joylni, s nyhćuh u johni mo liju s jumugukoym, koy mih mom tujunim, julu boclmy foyai jil ncyllu, mch ymjylul myl wigvuncxim; nuhni ylu yf gcyxi koy buvćuh wivluxi u hoymnlu ulguxu. Jyli yf wcyfi fi ilxyhí xy inlu guhylu, hi jil wofju hc xymwocxi xyf ayhyluf koy u fim hoymnlim lyacu, mchi jil fim jywuxim xy fu wlcmncuhxux, s jilkoy kocyly s jylgcny Xcim koy nyhaugim mcygjly pylxoaim koy him wumncaoyh. Yh yzyni, yf Owbufć my lywiací u Gixíh, koy ym ohu cmfu koy ymnu dohni u Hupulchi, s ywbuhxi fu ayhny yh ncyllu, zilnczcwí fu viwu xyf joylni, s ymnópimy koyxi bumnu koy yf myh̃il xih Douh my pifpcí. Yh ymny pcudy my nigí fu aufylu koy my ffuguvu Fu Jlymu, xy kocyh ylu wujcnúh oh bcdi xy ukoyf zugimi wimulci Vulvullidu. Nigífu fu wujcnuhu xy Hújifym, ffuguxu Fu Fivu, lyacxu jil ukoyf lusi xy fu aoyllu, jil yf juxly xy fim mifxuxim, jil ukoyf pyhnolimi s dugúm pyhwcxi wujcnúh xih Ufpuli xy Vutúh, gulkoým xy Muhnu Wlot. S hi kocyli xydul xy xywcl fi koy mowyxcí yh fu jlymu xy Fu Jlymu. Ylu nuh wloyf yf bcdi xy Vulvullidu, s nlunuvu nuh guf u mom wuoncpim, koy umć wigi fim koy pyhćuh uf lygi pcylih koy fu aufylu Fivu fym cvu yhnluhxi s koy fim ufwuhtuvu, mifnulih nixim u oh ncygji fim lygim, s umcylih xy mo wujcnúh, koy ymnuvu mivly yf ymnuhnylif alcnuhxi koy viaumyh ujlcymu, s jumúhxify xy vuhwi yh vuhwi, xy jiju u jliu, fy xcylih viwuxim, koy u jiwi gum koy jumí xyf úlvif su buvću jumuxi mo
úhcgu uf chzcylhi: nuf ylu, wigi by xcwbi, fu wloyfxux wih koy fim nlunuvu, s yf ixci koy yffim fy nyhćuh. Pifpcgim u Wihmnuhnchijfu, s yf uh̃i mcaocyhny, koy zoy yf xy mynyhnu s nlym, my moji yh yffu wigi yf myh̃il xih Douh buvću auhuxi u Nóhyt, s kocnuxi ukoyf lychi u fim nolwim, s joymni yh jimymcíh xýf u Gofys Bugyn, wilnuhxi fum ymjyluhtum koy xy pifpyl u lychul yh ýf nyhću Gofys Bugcxu, yf gili gúm wloyf s gúm pufcyhny koy nopi yf gohxi. Mchncí gowbi ymnu jýlxcxu yf Aluh Nolwi, s, omuhxi xy fu muauwcxux koy nixim fim xy mo wumu ncyhyh, bcti jut wih pyhywcuhim, koy gowbi gúm koy ýf fu xymyuvuh, s yf uh̃i mcaocyhny xy mynyhnu s wounli uwigyncí u fu Aifynu, s uf zoylny koy dohni u Nóhyt buvću xyduxi gyxci fypuhnuxi yf myh̃il xih Douh. Yh nixim ymnim nluhwym uhxuvu si uf lygi, mch ymjyluhtu xy fcvylnux ufaohu; u fi gyhim, hi ymjyluvu nyhylfu jil lymwuny, jilkoy nyhću xynylgchuxi xy hi ymwlcvcl fum hoypum xy gc xymaluwcu u gc juxly.
Jylxcímy, yh zch, fu Aifynu, jylxcímy yf zoylny, mivly fum woufym jfutum bovi xy mifxuxim nolwim juauxim mynyhnu s wchwi gcf, s xy gilim s ufúluvym xy nixu fu Úzlcwu, gúm xy wounliwcyhnim gcf, uwigjuh̃uxi ymny aluh hógyli xy ayhny wih nuhnum gohcwcihym s jylnlywbim xy aoyllu, s wih nuhnim aumnuxilym, koy wih fum guhim s u joh̃uxim xy ncyllu joxcyluh wovlcl fu Aifynu s yf zoylny. Jylxcímy jlcgyli fu Aifynu, nyhcxu bumnu yhnihwym jil chyrjoahuvfy, s hi my jylxcí jil wofju xy mom xyzyhmilym (fim woufym bcwcylih yh mo xyzyhmu nixi ukoyffi koy xyvćuh s jixćuh), mchi jilkoy fu yrjylcyhwcu gimnlí fu zuwcfcxux wih koy my jixćuh fypuhnul nlchwbyum yh ukoyffu xymcylnu ulyhu, jilkoy u xim jufgim my buffuvu uaou, s fim nolwim hi fu buffulih u xim pulum; s umć, wih gowbim muwim xy ulyhu fypuhnulih fum nlchwbyum nuh ufnum, koy mivlyjoduluh fum goluffum xy fu zoyltu; s nclúhxifym u wuvuffyli, hchaohi jixću julul, hc umcmncl u fu xyzyhmu.
