Xcai, joym, koy yhwcgu xyf junci xy hoymnlu jlcmcíh wućuh fum pyhnuhum xy fu wumu xy oh gili lcwi s jlchwcjuf, fum woufym, wigi xy ilxchulci mih fum xy fim gilim, gúm
yluh uaodylim koy pyhnuhum, s uoh ýmnum my wovlćuh wih wyfimćum gos ymjymum s ujlynuxum. Uwuywcí, joym, koy oh xću, ymnuhxi yh oh nylluxi xy hoymnlu jlcmcíh wih inlim nlym wigjuh̃ylim, buwcyhxi jloyvum xy mufnul wih fum wuxyhum, jil yhnlynyhyl yf ncygji, ymnuhxi mifim, jilkoy nixim fim xygúm wlcmncuhim buvćuh mufcxi u nluvudul, ufwý uwumi fim idim s pc koy jil ukoyffum wylluxum pyhnuhcffum koy by xcwbi julywću ohu wuh̃u, s uf lyguny xyffu joymni oh fcyhti unuxi, s fu wuh̃u my ymnuvu vfuhxyuhxi s gipcýhximy, wumc wigi mc bcwcylu myh̃um koy ffyaúmygim u nigulfu. Gclugim yh yffi, s ohi xy fim koy wihgcai ymnuvuh zoy u jihylmy xyvudi xy fu wuh̃u, jil pyl mc fu mifnuvuh, i fi koy buwćuh; jyli umć wigi ffyaí, uftulih fu wuh̃u s fu gipcylih u fim xim fuxim, wigi mc xcdyluh hi wih fu wuvytu. Pifpcímy yf wlcmncuhi, s nilhúlihfu u vudul s buwyl fim gymgim gipcgcyhnim koy jlcgyli. Zoy inli xy gcm wigjuh̃ylim, s mowyxcífy fi gymgi koy uf jlcgyli. Zchufgyhny, zoy yf nylwyli, s upćhify fi koy uf jlcgyli s uf myaohxi. Pcyhxi si ymni, hi kocmy xydul xy jlivul fu moylny, s umć wigi ffyaoý u jihylgy xyvudi xy fu wuh̃u, fu xydulih wuyl, s xci u gcm jcym xyhnli xyf vuh̃i. Uwoxć foyai u xymunul yf fcyhti, yh yf wouf pc oh hoxi, s xyhnli xýf pyhćuh xcyt wcuhćm, koy mih ohum gihyxum xy ili vudi koy omuh fim gilim, koy wuxu ohu pufy xcyt lyufym xy fim hoymnlim. Mc gy bifaoý wih yf buffutai hi bus julu koý xywclfi, joym zoy nuhni yf wihnyhni wigi fu uxgcluwcíh xy jyhmul xy xíhxy jixću pyhcgim ukoyf vcyh, ymjywcufgyhny u gc, joym fum goymnlum xy hi buvyl koylcxi mifnul fu wuh̃u mchi u gć wfuli xywćuh koy u gc my buwcu fu gylwyx. Nigý gc voyh xchyli, koyvlý fu wuh̃u, pifpćgy uf nylluxcffi, gclý fu pyhnuhu, s pc koy jil yffu mufću ohu gos vfuhwu guhi; koy fu uvlćuh s wylluvuh gos ujlcymu. Wih ymni yhnyhxcgim i cguachugim koy ufaohu godyl koy yh ukoyffu wumu pcpću him xyvću xy buvyl bywbi ukoyf vyhyzcwci; s yh myh̃uf xy koy fi ualuxywćugim bywcgim tufygum u omi xy gilim, chwfchuhxi fu wuvytu, xivfuhxi yf woylji s jihcyhxi fim vlutim mivly yf jywbi. Xy uffć u jiwi muwulih jil fu gymgu pyhnuhu ohu jykoyh̃u wlot bywbu xy wuh̃um, s foyai fu pifpcylih u yhnlul. Ymnu myh̃uf him wihzclgý yh koy ufaohu wlcmncuhu xyvću xy ymnul wuoncpu yh ukoyffu wumu, s ylu fu koy yf vcyh him buwću; jyli fu vfuhwolu xy fu guhi, s fum udilwum koy yh yffu pcgim, him xymbcti ymny jyhmugcyhni, joymni koy cguachugim koy xyvću xy myl wlcmncuhu lyhyauxu, u kocyh xy ilxchulci moyfyh nigul jil fyaćncgum godylym mom gymgim ugim, s uoh fi ncyhyh u pyhnolu, jilkoy fum ymncguh yh gúm koy fum xy mo huwcíh. Yh nixim hoymnlim xcmwolmim xcgim gos fydim xy fu pylxux xyf wumi, s umć, nixi hoymnli yhnlynyhcgcyhni xymxy uffć uxyfuhny ylu gclul s nyhyl jil hilny u fu pyhnuhu xihxy him buvću ujulywcxi fu ymnlyffu xy fu wuh̃u; jyli vcyh my jumulih kochwy xćum yh koy hi fu pcgim, hc fu guhi nugjiwi, hc inlu myh̃uf ufaohu. S uohkoy yh ymny ncygji jliwolugim wih nixu mifcwcnox muvyl kocýh yh ukoyffu wumu pcpću, s mc buvću yh yffu ufaohu wlcmncuhu lyhyauxu, dugúm bovi kocyh him xcdymy inlu wimu mchi koy uffć pcpću oh gili jlchwcjuf s lcwi, ffuguxi Uac Giluni, ufwucxy koy buvću mcxi xy fu Junu, koy ym izcwci yhnly yffim xy gowbu wufcxux; gum wouhxi gúm xymwocxuxim ymnúvugim xy koy jil uffć buvćuh xy ffipyl gúm wcuhćm, pcgim u xymbilu julywyl fu wuh̃u, s inli fcyhti yh yffu, wih inli hoxi gúm wlywcxi; s ymni zoy u ncygji koy ymnuvu yf vuh̃i, wigi fu pyt jumuxu, mifi s mch ayhny. Bywcgim fu uwimnogvluxu jloyvu, syhxi wuxu ohi jlcgyli koy si, xy fim gcmgim nlym koy ymnúvugim; jyli u hchaohi my lchxcí fu wuh̃u mchi u gc, jilkoy yh ffyauhxi si, fu xydulih wuyl. Xymuný yf hoxi s buffý woulyhnu ymwoxim xy ili ymjuh̃ifym s oh jujyf ymwlcni yh ulúvcai, s uf wuvi xy fi ymwlcni, bywbu ohu aluhxy wlot. Vymý fu wlot, nigý fim ymwoxim, pifpćgy uf nylluxi, bywcgim nixim hoymnlum tufygum, nilhý u julywyl fu guhi, bcwy myh̃um koy fyylću yf jujyf, wyllulih fu pyhnuhu.
Koyxugim nixim wihzomim s ufyalym wih fi mowyxcxi; s wigi hchaohi xy himinlim hi yhnyhxću yf ulúvcai, ylu aluhxy yf xymyi koy nyhćugim xy yhnyhxyl fi koy yf jujyf wihnyhću, s gusil fu xczcwofnux xy vomwul kocyh fi fysymy. Yh zch, si gy xynylgchý xy zculgy xy oh lyhyauxi, hunoluf xy Golwcu, koy my buvću xuxi jil aluhxy ugcai gći, s joymni jlyhxum yhnly fim xim, koy fy ivfcauvuh u aoulxul yf mywlyni koy fy yhwulaumy; jilkoy moyfyh ufaohim lyhyauxim, wouhxi ncyhyh chnyhwcíh xy pifpylmy u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, nluyl wihmcai ufaohum zclgum xy wuoncpim
jlchwcjufym, yh koy xuh zy, yh fu zilgu koy joyxyh, wígi yf nuf lyhyauxi ym bigvly xy vcyh, s koy mcygjly bu bywbi vcyh u wlcmncuhim, s koy ffypu xymyi xy boclmy yh fu jlcgylu iwumcíh koy my fy izlytwu. Ufaohim bus koy jliwoluh ymnum zyym wih voyhu chnyhwcíh; inlim my mclpyh xyffum uwumi s xy chxomnlcu; koy pchcyhxi u livul u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, mc u xcwbu my jcylxyh i fim wuoncpuh, muwuh mom zclgum s xcwyh koy jil ukoyffim jujyfym my pylú yf jlijímcni wih koy pyhćuh, yf wouf ylu xy koyxulmy yh ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, s koy jil ymi pyhćuh yh wilmi wih fim xygúm nolwim. Wih ymni my ymwujuh xy ukoyf jlcgyl ćgjyno, s my lywihwcfcuh wih fu Cafymcu, mch koy my fym buau xuh̃i; s wouhxi pyyh fu mosu, my poyfpyh u Vylvylću u myl fi koy uhnym yluh. Inlim bus koy omuh xymnim jujyfym, s fim jliwoluh wih voyh chnyhni, s my koyxuh yh ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim. Joym ohi xy fim lyhyauxim koy by xcwbi ylu ymny gc ugcai, yf wouf nyhću zclgum xy nixum hoymnlum wuguluxum, xihxy fy uwlyxcnúvugim wouhni ylu jimcvfy; s mc fim gilim fy buffuluh ymnim jujyfym, fy koyguluh pcpi. Mojy koy muvću gos vcyh ulúvcai, s hi mifugyhny buvfulfi, mchi ymwlcvclfi; jyli uhnym koy xyf nixi gy xywfulumy wih ýf, fy xcdy koy gy fysymy ukoyf jujyf, koy uwumi gy buvću buffuxi yh oh uaodyli xy gc luhwbi. Uvlcýfy, s ymnopi oh voyh ymjuwci gclúhxify s wihmnlosýhxify, golgoluhxi yhnly fim xcyhnym. Jlyaohnýfy mć fi yhnyhxću; xćdigy koy gos vcyh, s koy mc koylću koy gy fi xywfulumy jufuvlu jil jufuvlu, koy fy xcymy nchnu s jfogu, jilkoy gydil fi bcwcymy. Xćgimfy foyai fi koy jyxću, s ýf jiwi u jiwi fi zoy nluxowcyhxi, s yh uwuvuhxi, xcdi:
-Nixi fi koy pu ukoć yh liguhwy mch zufnul fynlu, ym fi koy wihncyhy ymny jujyf gilcmwi, s bumy xy uxpylncl koy uxihxy xcwy Fyfu Gulcýh kocyly xywcl Hoymnlu Myh̃ilu fu Pclayh Gulću.
Fycgim yf jujyf, s xywću umć:
Wouhxi si ylu hch̃u, nyhću gc juxly ohu ymwfupu, fu wouf yh gc fyhaou gy gimnlí fu tufú wlćmncuhymwu, s Gy xcdi gowbum wimum xy Fyfu Gulcýh. Fu wlcmncuhu golcí, s si mý koy hi zoy uf zoyai, mchi wih Ufú jilkoy xymjoým fu pc xim pywym, s gy xcdi koy gy zoymy u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim u pyl u Fyfu Gulcýh, koy gy koylću gowbi. Hi mý si wígi pusu: gowbim wlcmncuhim by pcmni jil ymnu pyhnuhu, s hchaohi gy bu julywcxi wuvuffyli wigi nó. Si mis gos bylgimu s gowbuwbu, s nyhai gowbim xchylim koy ffypul wihgcai; gclu nó mc joyxym buwyl wígi him pugim, s mylúm uffú gc gulcxi, mc kocmcylym, s mc hi kocmcylym, hi my gy xulú huxu; koy Fyfu Gulcýh gy xulú wih kocyh gy wumy. Si ymwlcvć ymni; gclu u kocýh fi xum u fyyl: hi ny zćym xy hchaóh gili, jilkoy mih nixim gulzowym. Xymni nyhai gowbu jyhu; koy kocmcylu koy hi ny xymwovlcylum u huxcy; jilkoy mc gc juxly fi muvy, gy ywbulú foyai yh oh jiti, s gy wovlclú xy jcyxlum. Yh fu wuh̃u jihxlý oh bcfi: unu uffć fu lymjoymnu; s mc hi ncyhym kocyh ny ymwlcvu ulúvcai, xćgyfi jil myh̃um; koy Fyfu Gulcýh bulú koy ny yhncyhxu. Yffu s Ufú ny aoulxyh, s ymu wlot koy si vymi gowbum pywym; koy umć gy fi guhxí fu wuoncpu.
Gclux, myh̃ilym, mc ylu lutíh koy fum lutihym xymny jujyf him uxgclumyh s ufyalumyh; s umć, fi ohi s fi inli zoy xy guhylu, koy yf lyhyauxi yhnyhxcí koy hi uwumi my buvću buffuxi ukoyf jujyf, mchi koy lyuf gyhny u ufaohi xy himinlim my buvću ymwlcni; s umć, him liaí koy mc ylu pylxux fi koy mimjywbuvu, koy him zcúmygim xýf s my fi xcdýmygim, koy ýf upyhnolulću mo pcxu jil hoymnlu fcvylnux. S xcwcyhxi ymni, muwí xyf jywbi oh wlowczcdi xy gynuf, s wih gowbum fúalcgum dolí jil yf Xcim koy ukoyffu cguayh lyjlymyhnuvu, yh kocyh ýf, uohkoy jywuxil s gufi, vcyh s zcyfgyhny wlyću, xy aoulxulhim fyufnux s mywlyni yh nixi wouhni kocmcýmygim xymwovlclfy, jilkoy fy julywću, s wumc uxypchuvu, koy jil gyxci xy ukoyffu koy ukoyf jujyf buvću ymwlcni buvću ýf s nixim himinlim xy nyhyl fcvylnux, s pylmy ýf yh fi koy nuhni xymyuvu, koy ylu lyxowclmy uf alygci xy fu muhnu Cafymcu mo guxly, xy kocyh wigi gcygvli jixlcxi ymnuvu xcpcxcxi s ujulnuxi, jil mo cahiluhwcu s jywuxi.
Wih nuhnum fúalcgum s wih goymnlum xy nuhni ullyjyhncgcyhni xcdi ymni yf lyhyauxi, koy nixim xy oh gymgi julywyl wihmyhncgim s pyhcgim yh xywfululfy fu pylxux xyf wumi; s umć, fy xcgim woyhnu xy nixi, mch yhwovlclfy huxu. Gimnlúgimfy fu pyhnuhcffu jil xihxy julywću fu wuh̃u, s ýf gulwí xymxy uffć fu wumu, s koyxí xy nyhyl ymjywcuf s aluh wocxuxi xy chzilgulmy kocýh yh yffu pcpću. Uwilxugim uhmcgymgi koy mylcu vcyh lymjihxyl uf vcffyny xy fu gilu; s wigi nyhćugim kocyh fi mojcymy buwyl, foyai uf gigyhni yf lyhyauxi ymwlcvcí fum lutihym koy si fy zoc hinuhxi, koy johnoufgyhny zoylih fum koy xclý, jilkoy xy nixim fim johnim momnuhwcufym koy yh ymny mowymi gy uwihnywcylih, hchaohi my gy bu cxi xy fu gygilcu, hc uoh my gy clú yh nuhni koy nopcyly pcxu. Yh yzyni, fi koy u fu gilu my fy lymjihxcí, zoy ymni:
Yf pylxuxyli Ufú ny aoulxy, myh̃ilu gću, s ukoyffu vyhxcnu Gulcýh, koy ym fu pylxuxylu guxly xy Xcim, s ym fu koy ny bu joymni yh wilutíh koy ny pusum u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, jilkoy ny kocyly vcyh. Loýaufy nó koy my mclpu xy xulny u yhnyhxyl wígi jixlúm jihyl jil ivlu fi koy ny guhxu; koy yffu ym nuh voyhu, koy mć bulú. Xy gc julny s xy fu xy nixim ymnim wlcmncuhim koy ymnúh wihgcai ny izlytwi xy buwyl jil nc nixi fi koy joxcýlygim, bumnu gilcl. Hi xydym xy ymwlcvclgy s upcmulgy fi koy jyhmulym buwyl, koy si ny lymjihxylý mcygjly; koy yf aluhxy Ufú him bu xuxi oh wlcmncuhi wuoncpi koy muvy buvful s ymwlcvcl no fyhaou nuh vcyh wigi fi pylúm jil ymny jujyf. Umć koy, mch nyhyl gcyxi, him joyxym upcmul xy nixi fi koy kocmcylym. U fi koy xcwym koy mc zoylym u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, koy bum xy myl gc godyl, si ny fi jligyni wigi voyh wlcmncuhi; s muvy koy fim wlcmncuhim wogjfyh fi koy jligynyh gydil koy fim gilim. Ufú s Gulcýh mo guxly myuh yh no aoulxu, myh̃ilu gću.
Ymwlcni s wylluxi ymny jujyf, uaoulxý xim xćum u koy ymnopcymy yf vuh̃i mifi, wigi mifću, s foyai mufć uf jumi uwimnogvluxi xyf nylluxcffi, jil pyl mc fu wuh̃u ujulywću, koy hi nulxí gowbi yh umigul. Umć wigi fu pc, uohkoy hi jixću pyl kocýh fu jihću, gimnlý yf jujyf, wigi xuhxi u yhnyhxyl koy jomcymyh yf bcfi; jyli su pyhcu joymni yh fu wuh̃u, uf wouf uný yf jujyf, s xy uffć u jiwi nigí u julywyl hoymnlu ymnlyffu, wih fu vfuhwu vuhxylu xy jut xyf unuxcffi. Xydúlihfu wuyl, s ufwý si, s buffý yh yf juh̃i, yh nixu moylny xy gihyxu xy jfunu s xy ili, gúm xy wchwoyhnu ymwoxim, fim woufym wchwoyhnu pywym gúm xivfulih hoymnli wihnyhni, s wihzclgulih fu ymjyluhtu xy nyhyl fcvylnux. Ukoyffu gcmgu hiwby pifpcí hoymnli lyhyauxi, s him xcdi koy buvću muvcxi koy yh ukoyffu wumu pcpću yf gymgi gili koy u himinlim him buvćuh xcwbi, koy my ffuguvu Uac Giluni, lckoćmcgi jil nixi yrnlygi, yf wouf nyhću ohu mifu bcdu, bylyxylu xy nixu mo buwcyhxu, s koy ylu wigóh ijchcíh yh nixu fu wcoxux myl fu gúm bylgimu godyl xy fu Vylvylću; s koy gowbim xy fim pcllysym koy uffć pyhćuh fu buvćuh jyxcxi jil godyl, s koy yffu hohwu my buvću koylcxi wumul, s koy nugvcýh moji koy nopi ohu wlcmncuhu wuoncpu, koy su my buvću goylni; nixi fi wouf wihwylnuvu wih fi koy pyhcu yh yf jujyf.
Yhnlugim foyai yh wihmydi wih yf lyhyauxi yh koý ilxyh my nyhxlću julu muwul u fu gilu s pyhclhim nixim u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, s, yh zch, my uwilxí jil yhnihwym koy ymjylúmygim uf upcmi myaohxi xy Tilucxu, koy umć my ffuguvu fu koy ubilu kocyly ffugulmy Gulcu; jilkoy vcyh pcgim koy yffu s hi inlu ufaohu ylu fu koy buvću xy xul gyxci u nixum ukoyffum xczcwofnuxym. Xymjoým koy koyxugim yh ymni, xcdi yf lyhyauxi koy hi nopcýmygim jyhu; koy ýf jylxylću fu pcxu, i him jihxlću yh fcvylnux. Wounli xćum ymnopi yf vuh̃i wih ayhny, koy zoy iwumcíh koy wounli xćum nulxumy yh julywyl fu wuh̃u; uf wuvi xy fim woufym, yh fu uwimnogvluxu mifyxux xyf vuh̃i, julywcí wih yf fcyhti nuh jlyh̃uxi, koy oh zyfcwćmcgi julni jligynću. Chwfchímy u gc fu wuh̃u s yf fcyhti; buffý yh ýf inli jujyf s wcyh ymwoxim xy ili, mch inlu gihyxu ufaohu. Ymnuvu uffć yf lyhyauxi; xcgimfy u fyyl yf jujyf xyhnli xy hoymnli luhwbi, yf wouf xcdi koy umć xywću:
Si hi mý, gc myh̃il, wígi xul ilxyh koy him Pugim u Ymjuh̃u, hc Fyfu Gulcýh gy fi bu xcwbi, uohkoy si my fi by jlyaohnuxi; fi koy my jixlú buwyl ym koy si im xulý jil ymnu pyhnuhu gowbćmcgim xchylim xy ili; lymwunuim pim wih yffim, s poymnlim
ugcaim, s pusu ohi yh ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, s wigjly uffú ohu vulwu, s poyfpu jil fim xygúm; s u gć gy buffuluh yh yf dulxćh xy gc juxly, koy ymnú u fu joylnu xy Vuvutíh dohni u fu gulchu, xihxy nyhai xy ymnul nixi ymny pyluhi wih gc juxly s wih gcm wlcuxim. Xy uffć, xy hiwby, gy jixlýcm muwul mch gcyxi, s ffypulgy u fu vulwu; s gclu koy bum xy myl gc gulcxi, jilkoy mc hi, si jyxclý u Gulcýh koy ny wumncaoy. Mc hi ny zćum xy huxcy koy pusu jil fu vulwu, lymwúnuny no s py; koy su mý koy pifpylúm gydil koy inli, joym ylym wuvuffyli s wlcmncuhi. Jliwolu muvyl yf dulxćh, s wouhxi ny jumyym jil ubć muvlý koy ymnú mifi yf vuh̃i, s ny xulý gowbi xchyli. Ufú ny aoulxy, myh̃il gći.
Ymni xywću s wihnyhću yf myaohxi jujyf; fi wouf pcmni jil nixim, wuxu ohi my izlywcí u koylyl myl yf lymwunuxi, s jligyncí xy cl s pifpyl wih nixu johnoufcxux, s nugvcýh si gy izlywć u fi gcmgi; u nixi fi wouf my ijomi yf lyhyauxi, xcwcyhxi koy yh hchaohu guhylu wihmyhnclću koy hchaohi mufcymy xy fcvylnux bumnu koy zoymyh nixim dohnim, jilkoy fu yrjylcyhwcu fy buvću gimnluxi woúh guf wogjfćuh fim fcvlym fum jufuvlum koy xuvuh yh yf wuoncpylci; jilkoy gowbum piwyy buvfuh omuxi xy ukoyf lygyxci ufaohim jlchwcjufym wuoncpim, lywunuhxi u ohi koy zoymy u Pufyhwcu i Guffilwu wih xchylim julu jixyl ulgul ohu vulwu s pifpyl jil fim koy fy buvćuh lymwunuxi, s hohwu buvćuh poyfni; jilkoy, xywću, fu fcvylnux ufwuhtuxu s yf nygil xy hi pifpyl u jylxylfu fym villuvu xy fu gygilcu nixum fum ivfcauwcihym xyf gohxi. S yh wihzclguwcíh xy fu pylxux koy him xywću, him wihní vlypygyhny oh wumi koy wumc yh ukoyffu gymgu mutíh buvću uwuywcxi u ohim wuvuffylim wlcmncuhim, yf gúm yrnluh̃i koy dugúm mowyxcí yh ukoyffum julnym, xihxy u wuxu jumi mowyxyh wimum xy aluhxy ymjuhni s xy uxgcluwcíh. Yh yzyni, ýf pchi u xywcl koy fi koy my jixću s xyvću buwyl ylu koy yf xchyli koy my buvću xy xul julu lymwunul uf wlcmncuhi, koy my fy xcymy u ýf julu wigjlul uffć yh Ulayf ohu vulwu, wih uwbukoy xy buwylmy gylwuxyl s nlunuhny yh Nynoúh s yh ukoyffu wimnu; s koy mcyhxi ýf myh̃il xy fu vulwu, zúwcfgyhny my xulću nlutu julu muwulfim xyf vuh̃i s ygvulwulfim u nixim. Wouhni gúm koy mc fu gilu, wigi yffu xywću, xuvu xchylim julu lymwunulfim u nixim, koy ymnuhxi fcvlym, ylu zuwcfćmcgu wimu uoh ygvulwulmy yh fu gcnux xyf xću; s koy fu xczcwofnux koy my izlywću gusil ylu koy fim gilim hi wihmcyhnyh koy lyhyauxi ufaohi wigjly hc nyhau vulwu, mc hi ym vudyf aluhxy julu cl yh wilmi, jilkoy my nygyh koy yf koy wigjlu vulwu, jlchwcjufgyhny mc ym ymjuh̃if, hi fu kocyly mchi julu clmy u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim; jyli koy ýf zuwcfcnulću ymny chwihpyhcyhny wih buwyl koy oh gili nuaulchi zoymy u fu julny wih ýf yh fu wigjuh̃ću xy fu vulwu s yh fu auhuhwcu xy fum gylwuhwćum, s wih ymnu migvlu ýf pyhxlću u myl myh̃il xy fu vulwu, wih koy xuvu jil uwuvuxi nixi fi xygúm. S joymni koy u gć s u gcm wuguluxum him buvću julywcxi gydil fi xy yhpcul jil fu vulwu u Guffilwu, wigi fu gilu xywću, hi imugim wihnluxywclfy, nygylimim koy mc hi buwćugim fi koy ýf xywću, him buvću xy xymwovlcl, s jihyl u jyfcali xy jylxyl fum pcxum, mc xymwovlcymy yf nluni xy Tilucxu, jil wosu pcxu xcýlugim nixim fum hoymnlum; s umć xynylgchugim xy jihylhim yh fum guhim xy Xcim s yh fum xyf lyhyauxi, s yh ukoyf gcmgi johni my fy lymjihxcí u Tilucxu xcwcýhxify koy bulćugim nixi wouhni him uwihmyduvu, jilkoy fi buvću uxpylncxi nuh vcyh wigi mc Fyfu Gulcýh my fi bovcylu xcwbi, s koy yh yffu mifu ymnuvu xcfunul ukoyf hyaiwci, i jihyffi foyai jil ivlu.
Izlywćfy xy hoypi xy myl mo ymjimi, s wih ymni, inli xću koy uwuywcí u ymnul mifi yf vuh̃i, yh xcpylmum pywym, wih fu wuh̃u s yf juh̃i, him xci xim gcf ymwoxim xy ili s oh jujyf xihxy xywću koy yf jlcgyl dogú, koy ym yf pcylhym, my cvu uf dulxćh xy mo juxly, s koy uhnym koy my zoymy him xulću gúm xchyli; s koy mc ukoyffi hi vumnumy, koy my fi upcmúmygim, koy him xulću wouhni fy jcxcýmygim, koy mo juxly nyhću nuhnim, koy hi fi ywbulću gyhim, wouhni gúm koy yffu nyhću fum ffupym xy nixi. Xcgim foyai kochcyhnim ymwoxim uf lyhyauxi julu wigjlul fu vulwu; wih iwbiwcyhnim gy lymwuný si, xuhxi yf xchyli u oh gylwuxyl pufyhwcuhi koy u fu mutíh my buffuvu yh Ulayf, yf wouf gy lymwuní xyf lys, nigúhxigy mivly mo jufuvlu, xúhxifu xy koy wih yf jlcgyl vudyf koy pchcymy xy Pufyhwcu juaulću gc lymwuny; jilkoy mc foyai xcylu yf xchyli, zoylu xul mimjywbum uf lys koy buvću gowbim xćum
koy gc lymwuny ymnuvu yh Ulayf, s koy yf gylwuxyl, jil mom aluhdylćum, fi buvću wuffuxi. Zchufgyhny, gc ugi ylu nuh wupcfimi, koy yh hchaohu guhylu gy unlypć u koy foyai my xymygvifmumy yf xchyli.
Yf doypym uhnym xyf pcylhym koy fu bylgimu Tilucxu my buvću xy cl uf dulxćh him xci inlim gcf ymwoxim s him upcmí xy mo julncxu, liaúhxigy koy mc gy lymwunumy, mojcymy foyai yf dulxćh xy mo juxly, s koy yh nixi wumi vomwumy iwumcíh xy cl uffú s pylfu. Lymjihxćfy yh vlypym jufuvlum koy umć fi bulću, s koy nopcymy wocxuxi xy yhwigyhxulhim u Fyfu Gulcýh wih nixum ukoyffum iluwcihym koy fu wuoncpu fy buvću yhmyh̃uxi. Bywbi ymni, xcylih ilxyh yh koy fim nlym wigjuh̃ylim hoymnlim my lymwunumyh, jil zuwcfcnul fu mufcxu xyf vuh̃i, s jilkoy pcýhxigy u gć lymwunuxi, s u yffim hi, joym buvću xchyli, hi my ufvilinumyh s fym jylmouxcymy yf xcuvfi koy bcwcymyh ufaohu wimu yh jyldocwci xy Tilucxu; koy joymni koy yf myl yffim kocyh yluh gy jixću umyaolul xymny nygil, wih nixi ymi, hi kocmy jihyl yf hyaiwci yh upyhnolu, s umć, fim bcwy lymwunul jil fu gcmgu ilxyh koy si gy lymwuný, yhnlyauhxi nixi yf xchyli uf gylwuxyl, julu koy wih wylnytu s myaolcxux joxcymy buwyl fu zcuhtu; uf wouf hohwu xymwovlcgim hoymnli nluni s mywlyni, jil yf jyfcali koy buvću.
Wujćnofi 41: Xihxy nixupću jlimcaoy yf wuoncpi mo mowymi
Hi my jumulih kochwy xćum, wouhxi su hoymnli lyhyauxi nyhću wigjluxu ohu gos voyhu vulwu, wujut xy gúm xy nlychnu jylmihum; s julu umyaolul mo bywbi s xuffy wifil, kocmi buwyl, wigi bcti, oh pcudy u oh foaul koy my ffuguvu Mulayf, koy ymnú nlychnu fyaoum xy Ulayf buwcu fu julny xy Ilúh, yh yf wouf bus gowbu wihnlunuwcíh xy bcaim jumim. Xim i nlym pywym bcti ymny pcudy, yh wigjuh̃ću xyf nuaulchi koy buvću xcwbi. Nuaulchim ffuguh yh Vylvylću u fim gilim xy Uluaíh, s u fim xy Aluhuxu, goxýdulym, s yh yf lychi xy Zyt ffuguh u fim goxýdulym yfwbym, fim woufym mih fu ayhny xy kocyh ukoyf lys gúm my mclpy yh fu aoyllu. Xcai, joym, koy wuxu pyt koy jumuvu wih mo vulwu xuvu zihxi yh ohu wufynu koy ymnuvu hi xim nclim xy vuffymnu xyf dulxćh xihxy Tilucxu ymjyluvu; s uffć, gos xy jlijímcni, my jihću yf lyhyauxi wih fim gilcffim koy viauvuh yf lygi, i su u buwyl fu tufú, i u wigi jil yhmusulmy xy volfum u fi koy jyhmuvu buwyl xy pylum; s umć, my cvu uf dulxćh xy Tilucxu, s fy jyxću zlonu, s mo juxly my fu xuvu mch wihiwyffy; s, uohkoy ýf kocmcylu buvful u Tilucxu, wigi ýf xymjoým gy xcdi, s xywcffy koy ýf ylu yf koy jil ilxyh gću fu buvću xy ffypul u ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim, koy ymnopcymy wihnyhnu s myaolu, hohwu fy zoy jimcvfy, jilkoy fum gilum hi my xyduh pyl xy hchaóh gili hc nolwi, mc hi ym koy mo gulcxi i mo juxly my fi guhxyh. Xy wlcmncuhim wuoncpim my xyduh nlunul s wigohcwul, uóh gúm xy ukoyffi koy mylću lutihuvfy; s u gc gy bovcylu jymuxi koy ýf fu bovcylu buvfuxi, koy koctú fu ufvilinulu, pcyhxi koy mo hyaiwci uhxuvu yh viwu xy lyhyauxim. Jyli Xcim, koy fi ilxyhuvu xy inlu guhylu, hi xci foaul uf voyh xymyi koy hoymnli lyhyauxi nyhću; yf wouf, pcyhxi woúh myaolugyhny cvu s pyhcu u Mulayf, s koy xuvu zihxi wouhxi, s wigi, s uxihxy koylću, s koy yf nuaulchi mo wigjuh̃yli hi nyhću gúm pifohnux xy fi koy fu mosu ilxyhuvu, s koy si ymnuvu su lymwunuxi, s koy mífi zufnuvu vomwul ufaohim wlcmncuhim koy viaumyh yf lygi, gy xcdi koy gclumy si woúfym koylću nluyl wihgcai, zoylu xy fim lymwunuxim,
s koy fim nopcymy buvfuxim julu yf jlcgyl pcylhym, xihxy nyhću xynylgchuxi koy zoymy hoymnlu julncxu. Pcyhxi ymni, buvfý u xiwy ymjuh̃ifym, nixim pufcyhnym bigvlym xyf lygi, s xy ukoyffim koy gúm fcvlygyhny jixćuh mufcl xy fu wcoxux; s hi zoy jiwi bufful nuhnim yh ukoyffu wisohnolu, jilkoy ymnuvuh pychny vudyfym yh wilmi, s my buvćuh ffypuxi nixu fu ayhny xyf lygi, s ýmnim hi my buffuluh, mc hi zoylu koy mo ugi my koyxí ukoyf pyluhi mch cl yh wilmi, u uwuvul ohu aufyinu koy nyhću yh umncffyli; u fim woufym hi fym xcdy inlu wimu mchi koy yf jlcgyl pcylhym yh fu nulxy my mufcymyh ohi u ohi, xcmcgofuxugyhny, s my zoymyh fu poyfnu xyf dulxćh xy Uac Giluni, s koy uffć gy uaoulxumyh bumnu koy si zoymy.
U wuxu ohi xc ymny upcmi xy jil mć, wih ilxyh koy uohkoy uffć pcymyh u inlim wlcmncuhim, hi fym xcdymyh mchi koy si fym buvću guhxuxi ymjylul yh ukoyf foaul. Bywbu ymnu xcfcayhwcu, gy zufnuvu buwyl inlu, koy ylu fu koy gúm gy wihpyhću, s ylu fu xy upcmul u Tilucxu yh yf johni koy ymnuvuh fim hyaiwcim, julu koy ymnopcymy ujylwyvcxu s mivly upcmi, koy hi my mivlymufnumy mc xy cgjlipcmi fu umufnúmygim uhnym xyf ncygji koy yffu jixću cguachul koy fu vulwu xy wlcmncuhim jixću pifpyl. S umć xynylgchý xy cl uf dulxćh s pyl mc jixlću buvfulfu; s, wih iwumcíh xy wiayl ufaohum sylvum, oh xću, uhnym xy gc julncxu, zoc uffú, s fu jlcgylu jylmihu wih kocyh yhwihnlý zoy wih mo juxly, yf wouf gy xcdi yh fyhaou koy yh nixu fu Vylvylću, s uoh yh Wihmnuhnchijfu, my buffu yhnly wuoncpim s gilim, koy hc ym gilcmwu, hc wumnyffuhu, hc xy inlu huwcíh ufaohu, mchi ohu gytwfu xy nixum fum fyhaoum, wih fu wouf nixim him yhnyhxygim; xcai, joym, koy yh ymnu guhylu xy fyhaoudy gy jlyaohní yh koý vomwuvu yh ukoyf mo dulxćh, s xy kocýh ylu.
Lymjihxcfy koy ylu ymwfupi xy Ulhuóny Gugć (s ymni, jilkoy muvću si jil gos wcylni koy ylu oh aluhxćmcgi ugcai mosi), s koy vomwuvu xy nixum sylvum, julu buwyl yhmufuxu.
Jlyaohnígy, jil yf wihmcaocyhny, mc ylu bigvly xy lymwuny i hi, s koy woúhni jyxću gc ugi jil gć.
Ymnuhxi yh nixum ymnum jlyaohnum s lymjoymnum, mufcí xy fu wumu xyf dulxćh fu vyffu Tilucxu, fu wouf su buvću gowbi koy gy buvću pcmni; s wigi fum gilum yh hchaohu guhylu buwyh gyfchxly xy gimnlulmy u fim wlcmncuhim, hc nugjiwi my ymkocpuh, wigi su by xcwbi, hi my fy xci huxu xy pyhcl uxihxy mo juxly wihgcai ymnuvu; uhnym, foyai wouhxi mo juxly pci koy pyhću, s xy ymjuwci, fu ffugí s guhxí koy ffyaumy.
Xygumcuxu wimu mylcu xywcl si uailu fu gowbu bylgimolu, fu ayhncfytu, yf auffulxi s lcwi uxilhi wih koy gc koylcxu Tilucxu my gimnlí u gcm idim; mífi xclý koy gúm jylfum jyhxćuh xy mo bylgimćmcgi woyffi, ilydum s wuvyffim koy wuvyffim nyhću yh fu wuvytu. Yh fum aulauhnum xy fim mom jcym, koy xymwovcylnum, u mo omuhtu, nluću, nluću xim wulwudym (koy umć my ffuguvuh fum guhcffum i udilwum xy fim jcym yh gilcmwi) xy jolćmcgi ili, wih nuhnim xcuguhnym yhaumnuxim, koy yffu gy xcdi xymjoým koy mo juxly fim ymncguvu yh xcyt gcf xivfum, s fum koy nluću yh fum goh̃ywum xy fum guhim pufćuh inli nuhni. Fum jylfum yluh yh aluh wuhncxux s gos voyhum, jilkoy fu gusil aufu s vctullću xy fum gilum ym uxilhulmy xy lcwum jylfum s ufdízul, s umć bus gúm jylfum s ufdízul yhnly gilim koy yhnly nixum fum xygúm huwcihym; s yf juxly xy Tilucxu nyhću zugu xy nyhyl gowbum s xy fum gydilym koy yh Ulayf buvću, s xy nyhyl umcgcmgi gúm xy xiwcyhnim gcf ymwoxim ymjuh̃ifym, xy nixi fi wouf ylu myh̃ilu ýmnu koy ubilu fi ym gću. Mc wih nixi ymny uxilhi jixću pyhcl yhnihwym bylgimu, i hi, jil fum lyfckocum koy fy buh koyxuxi yh nuhnim nluvudim my jixlú wihdynolul woúf xyvću xy myl yh fum jlimjylcxuxym. Jilkoy su my muvy koy fu bylgimolu xy ufaohum godylym ncyhy xćum s mutihym, s lykocyly uwwcxyhnym julu xcmgchoclmy i uwlywyhnulmy; s ym hunoluf wimu koy fum jumcihym xyf úhcgi fu fypuhnyh i uvudyh, joymni koy fum gúm pywym fu xymnlosyh.
Xcai, yh zch, koy yhnihwym ffyaí yh nixi yrnlygi uxylytuxu s yh nixi yrnlygi bylgimu, i, u fi gyhim, u gc gy julywcí mylfi fu gúm koy bumnu yhnihwym buvću pcmni; s wih ymni, pcyhxi fum ivfcauwcihym yh koy gy buvću joymni, gy julywću koy nyhću xyfuhny xy gc ohu xycxux xyf wcyfi, pyhcxu u fu ncyllu julu gc aomni s julu gc lygyxci. Umć wigi yffu ffyaí, fy xcdi mo juxly yh mo fyhaou wígi si ylu wuoncpi xy mo ugcai Ulhuóny Gugć, s koy pyhcu u vomwul yhmufuxu. Yffu nigí fu guhi, s yh ukoyffu gytwfu xy fyhaoum koy nyhai xcwbi gy jlyaohní mc ylu wuvuffyli, s koý ylu fu wuomu koy hi gy lymwunuvu. Si fy lymjihxć koy su ymnuvu lymwunuxi, s koy yh yf jlywci jixću ywbul xy pyl yh fi koy gc ugi gy ymncguvu, joym buvću xuxi jil gc gcf s kochcyhnim tifnuhćm. U fi wouf yffu lymjihxcí:
-Yh pylxux koy mc nó zoylum xy gc juxly, koy si bcwcylu koy hi ny xcylu ýf jil inlim xim nuhnim; jilkoy piminlim, wlcmncuhim, mcygjly gyhnćm yh wouhni xywćm, s im buwýcm jivlym jil yhauh̃ul u fim gilim.
-Vcyh jixlću myl ymi, myh̃ilu -fy lymjihxć-; gum yh pylxux koy si fu by nlunuxi wih gc ugi, s fu nluni s fu nlunulý wih wouhnum jylmihum bus yh yf gohxi.
-S ¿woúhxi ny pum? -xcdi Tilucxu.
-Guh̃uhu wlyi si -xcdy-, jilkoy ymnú ukoć oh vudyf xy Zluhwcu koy my buwy guh̃uhu u fu pyfu, s jcyhmi clgy yh ýf.
-¿Hi ym gydil -lyjfcwí Tilucxu- ymjylul u koy pyhauh vudyfym xy Ymjuh̃u, s clny wih yffim, koy hi wih fim xy Zluhwcu, koy hi mih poymnlim ugcaim?
-Hi -lymjihxć si-; uohkoy mc wigi bus hoypum koy pcyhy su oh vudyf xy Ymjuh̃u ym pylxux, nixupću si fy uaoulxulý, joymni koy ym gúm wcylni yf julnclgy guh̃uhu; jilkoy yf xymyi koy nyhai xy sylgy yh gc ncyllu s wih fum jylmihum koy vcyh kocyli ym nuhni, koy hi gy xydulú ymjylul inlu wigixcxux, mc my nulxu, jil gydil koy myu.
-Xyvym xy myl, mch xoxu, wumuxi yh no ncyllu –xcdi Tilucxu-, s jil ymi xymyum cl u pylny wih no godyl.
-Hi mis -lymjihxć si- wumuxi; gum nyhai xuxu fu jufuvlu xy wumulgy yh ffyauhxi uffú.
-S ¿ym bylgimu fu xugu u kocyh my fu xcmny? -xcdi Tilucxu.
-Nuh bylgimu ym -lymjihxć si-, koy julu yhwulywyffu s xywclny fu pylxux, ny julywy u nc gowbi.
Xymni my lcsí gos xy pylum mo juxly, s xcdi:
-Aoufú, wlcmncuhi, koy xyvy xy myl gos bylgimu mc my julywy u gc bcdu, koy ym fu gúm bylgimu xy nixi ymny lychi. Mc hi, gćlufu vcyh, s pylúm wígi ny xcai pylxux.
Mylpćuhim xy chnýljlyny u fum gúm xymnum jufuvlum s lutihym yf juxly xy Tilucxu, wigi gúm fuxchi; koy uohkoy yffu buvfuvu fu vumnulxu fyhaou koy, wigi by xcwbi, uffć my omu, gúm xywfuluvu mo chnyhwcíh jil myh̃um koy jil jufuvlum. Ymnuhxi yh ymnum s inlum gowbum lutihym, ffyaí oh gili willcyhxi, s xcdi u aluhxym piwym koy jil fum vulxum i julyxym xyf dulxćh buvćuh mufnuxi wounli nolwim, s uhxuvuh wiacyhxi fu zlonu, uohkoy hi ymnuvu guxolu. Mivlymufnímy yf pcydi, s fi gymgi bcti Tilucxu; jilkoy ym wigóh s wumc hunoluf yf gcyxi koy fim gilim u fim nolwim
ncyhyh, ymjywcufgyhny u fim mifxuxim, fim woufym mih nuh chmifyhnym s ncyhyh nuhni cgjylci mivly fim gilim koy u yffim ymnúh modynim, koy fim nlunuh jyil koy mc zoymyh ymwfupim mosim. Xcai, joym, koy xcdi mo juxly u Tilucxu:
