Ymnuvu fu vyffćmcgu Tilucxu uaoulxúhxihim u ohu pyhnuhu, s umć wigi mchncí ayhny, jlyaohní wih pit vudu mc ýlugim hctuluhc, wigi mc xcdylu i jlyaohnulu mc ýlugim wlcmncuhim. Si fy lymjihxć koy mc, s koy vudumy. Wouhxi yffu gy wihiwcí, hi my xynopi oh johni; jilkoy, mch lymjihxylgy jufuvlu, vudí yh oh chmnuhny, uvlcí fu joylnu, s gimnlímy u nixim nuh bylgimu s lcwugyhny pymncxu, koy hi fi uwcylni u
