-Joym mylú gyhymnyl xymjylnuffy -lyjfcwí yf lyhyauxi-, s ffypúlhimfy wih himinlim, s nixi ukoyffi koy ncyhy xy pufil ymny bylgimi dulxćh.
-Hi -xcdi yffu-; u gc juxly hi my bu xy niwul yh hchaóh gixi, s yh ymnu wumu hi bus inlu wimu koy fi koy si ffypi, koy ym nuhni, koy vcyh buvlú julu koy nixim koyxýcm lcwim s wihnyhnim, s ymjylulim oh jiwi s fi pylýcm.
