Yh xcwcyhxi ymni, wigyhtí u ffilul nuh ugulaugyhny, koy u nixim him gipcí u wigjumcíh, s ziltí u Tilucxu koy fy gclumy; fu wouf, pcýhxify ffilul, umć my yhnylhywcí, koy my fypuhní xy gcm jcym s zoy u uvlutul u mo juxly s, dohnuhxi mo limnli wih yf mosi, wigyhtulih fim xim nuh ncylhi ffuhni, koy gowbim xy fim koy uffć ćvugim fy uwigjuh̃ugim yh ýf. Jyli wouhxi mo juxly fu pci uxilhuxu xy zcymnu s wih nuhnum disum mivly mć, fy xcdi yh mo fyhaou:
-¿Koý ym ymni, bcdu, koy usyl uf uhiwbywyl, uhnym koy him mowyxcymy ymnu nyllcvfy xymaluwcu yh koy him pygim, ny pc wih nom ilxchulcim s wumylim pymncxim, s uailu, mch koy busum nyhcxi ncygji xy pymnclny, s mch buvylny xuxi ufaohu hoypu ufyaly xy mifyhctuffu wih uxilhulny s jofclny, ny pyi wigjoymnu wih fim gydilym pymncxim koy si mojy s joxy xulny wouhxi him zoy fu pyhnolu gúm zupiluvfy? Lymjíhxygy u ymni, koy gy ncyhy gúm momjyhmi s uxgcluxi koy fu gcmgu xymaluwcu yh koy gy buffi.
Nixi fi koy yf gili xywću u mo bcdu him fi xywfuluvu yf lyhyauxi, s yffu hi fy lymjihxću jufuvlu. Jyli wouhxi ýf pci u oh fuxi xy fu vulwu yf wizlywcffi xihxy yffu mifću nyhyl mom disum, yf wouf muvću ýf vcyh koy fy buvću xyduxi yh Ulayf, s hi nlućxify uf dulxćh, koyxí gúm wihzomi, s jlyaohnífy koy wígi ukoyf wizly buvću
pyhcxi u hoymnlum guhim, s koý ylu fi koy pyhću xyhnli. U fi wouf yf lyhyauxi, mch uaoulxul koy Tilucxu fy lymjihxcymy, fy lymjihxcí:
-Hi ny wuhmym, myh̃il, yh jlyaohnul u Tilucxu no bcdu nuhnum wimum, jilkoy wih ohu koy si ny lymjihxu ny muncmzulý u nixum, s umć, kocyli koy myjum koy yffu ym wlcmncuhu, s ym fu koy bu mcxi fu fcgu xy hoymnlum wuxyhum s fu fcvylnux xy hoymnli wuoncpylci. Yffu pu ukoć xy mo pifohnux, nuh wihnyhnu, u fi koy si cguachi, xy pylmy yh ymny ymnuxi, wigi yf koy mufy xy fum nchcyvfum u fu fot, xy fu goylny u fu pcxu s xy fu jyhu u fu afilcu.
-¿Ym pylxux fi koy ýmny xcwy, bcdu? -xcdi yf gili. -Umć ym -lymjihxcí Tilucxu.
-¿Koy, yh yzyni -lyjfcwí yf pcydi-, nó ylym wlcmncuhu, s fu koy bu joymni u mo juxly yh jixyl xy mom yhygcaim?
U fi wouf lymjihxcí Tilucxu:
-Fu koy ym wlcmncuhu, si mis; jyli hi fu koy ny bu joymni yh ymny johni; jilkoy hohwu gc xymyi my yrnyhxcí u xydulny hc u buwylny guf, mchi u buwylgy u gć vcyh.
-S ¿koý vcyh ym yf koy ny bum bywbi, bcdu?
-Ymi -lymjihxcí yffu- jlyaóhnumyfi nó u Fyfu Gulcýh; koy yffu ny fi muvlú xywcl gydil koy hi si.
Ujyhum bovi ićxi ymni yf gili, wouhxi, wih ohu chwlyćvfy jlymnytu, my ullidí xy wuvytu yh fu gul, xihxy mch hchaohu xoxu my ubiaulu, mc yf pymncxi fulai s ygvulutimi koy nluću hi fy yhnlynopcylu oh jiwi mivly yf uaou. Xci piwym Tilucxu koy fy muwumyh, s umć, uwoxcgim foyai nixim, s, umcýhxify xy fu ufgufuzu, fy muwugim gyxci ubiauxi s mch myhncxi; xy koy lywcvcí nuhnu jyhu Tilucxu, koy, wigi mc zoylu su goylni buwću mivly ýf oh ncylhi s xifilimi ffuhni. Pifpcgimfy viwu uvudi; pifpcí gowbu uaou; nigí yh mc uf wuvi xy xim bilum, yh fum woufym, buvcýhximy nliwuxi yf pcyhni, him wihpchi pifpyl buwcu ncyllu, s buwyl zoyltu xy lygim, jil hi ygvymncl yh yffu; gum kocmi hoymnlu voyhu moylny koy ffyaugim u ohu wuću koy my buwy uf fuxi xy oh jykoyh̃i jligihnilci i wuvi koy xy fim gilim ym ffuguxi yf xy fu Wuvu Logću, koy yh hoymnlu fyhaou kocyly xywcl fu gufu godyl wlcmncuhu; s ym nluxcwcíh yhnly fim gilim koy yh ukoyf foaul ymnú yhnylluxu fu Wupu, jil kocyh my jylxcí Ymjuh̃u. jilkoy wupu yh mo fyhaou kocyly xywcl godyl gufu, s logću, wlcmncuhu; s uoh ncyhyh jil guf uaöyli ffyaul uffć u xul zihxi wouhxi fu hywymcxux fym zoyltu u yffi, jilkoy hohwu fy xuh mch yffu; joymni koy julu himinlim hi zoy uvlcai xy gufu godyl, mchi joylni myaoli xy hoymnli lygyxci, myaóh uhxuvu ufnyluxu fu gul. Jomcgim hoymnlum wyhnchyfum yh ncyllu, s hi xydugim dugúm fim lygim xy fu guhi; wigcgim xy fi koy yf lyhyauxi buvću jlipyćxi, s liaugim u Xcim s u Hoymnlu Myh̃ilu, xy nixi hoymnli wilutíh, koy him usoxumy s zupilywcymy julu koy zyfcwygyhny xcýmygim zch u nuh xcwbimi jlchwcjci. Xcimy ilxyh, u mojfcwuwcíh xy Tilucxu, wigi ywbúmygim yh ncyllu u mo juxly s u nixim fim xygúm gilim koy uffć unuxim pyhćuh, jilkoy hi fy vumnuvu yf úhcgi, hc fi jixćuh mozlcl mom vfuhxum yhnluh̃um, pyl xyfuhny xy mom idim unuxi u mo juxly s u ukoyffim xy mo ncyllu jlymim. Jligynćgimfy xy buwylfi umć uf ncygji xy fu julncxu, joym hi willću jyfcali yf xyduffim yh ukoyf foaul, koy ylu xymjivfuxi. Hi zoylih nuh puhum hoymnlum iluwcihym, koy hi zoymyh ićxum xyf wcyfi; koy, yh hoymnli zupil, foyai pifpcí yf pcyhni nluhkocfi yf gul, wihpcxúhxihim u koy nilhúmygim ufyalym u jlimyaocl hoymnli wigyhtuxi pcudy. Pcyhxi ymni, xymunugim u fim gilim, s ohi u ohi fim
jomcgim yh ncyllu, xy fi koy yffim my koyxulih uxgcluxim; jyli ffyauhxi u xymygvulwul uf juxly xy Tilucxu, koy su ymnuvu yh nixi mo uwoylxi, xcdi:
-¿Jil koý jyhmúcm, wlcmncuhim, koy ymnu gufu bygvlu boyfau xy koy gy xycm fcvylnux? ¿Jyhmúcm koy ym jil jcyxux koy xy gc ncyhy? Hi, jil wcylni, mchi koy fi buwy jil yf ymnilvi koy fy xulú gc jlymyhwcu wouhxi kocylu jihyl yh ydywowcíh mom gufim xymyim; hc jyhmýcm koy fu bu gipcxi u goxul lyfcacíh yhnyhxyl yffu koy fu poymnlu u fu hoymnlu my upyhnudu, mchi yf muvyl koy yh poymnlu ncyllu my omu fu xymbihymncxux gúm fcvlygyhny koy yh fu hoymnlu.
S pifpcýhximy u Tilucxu, nyhcýhxify si s inli wlcmncuhi xy yhnlugvim vlutim umcxi, jilkoy ufaóh xymunchi hi bcwcymy, fy xcdi:
-¡Ib chzugy gitu s guf uwihmyduxu gowbuwbu! ¿Uxíhxy pum, wcyau s xymunchuxu, yh jixyl xymnim jyllim, hunolufym yhygcaim hoymnlim? ¡Gufxcnu myu fu bilu yh koy si ny yhayhxlý, s gufxcnim myuh fim lyaufim s xyfycnym yh koy ny by wlcuxi!
Jyli pcyhxi si koy ffypuvu nýlgchi xy hi uwuvul nuh jlymni, xc jlcymu u jihyffy yh ncyllu, s xymxy uffć, u piwym, jlimcaocí yh mom gufxcwcihym s fugyhnim, liauhxi u Gubigu liaumy u Ufú koy him xymnlosymy, wihzohxcymy s uwuvumy; s wouhxi, jil buvylhim bywbi u fu pyfu, hi jixcgim ićl mom jufuvlum, pcgim mom ivlum, koy yluh ulluhwulmy fum vulvum, gymulmy fim wuvyffim s ullumnlulmy jil yf moyfi; gum ohu pyt ymziltí fu pit xy nuf guhylu, koy jixcgim yhnyhxyl koy xywću:
-Poyfpy, uguxu bcdu, poyfpy u ncyllu, koy nixi ny fi jylxihi; yhnlyau u ymim bigvlym ymy xchyli, koy su ym mosi, s poyfpy u wihmiful u ymny nlcmny juxly nosi, koy yh ymnu xymcylnu ulyhu xydulú fu pcxu, mc nó fy xydum.
Nixi fi wouf ymwowbuvu Tilucxu, s nixi fi myhnću s ffiluvu, s hi moji xywclfy hc lymjihxyffy jufuvlu, mchi:
-¡Jfyau u Ufú, juxly gći, koy Fyfu Gulcýh, koy bu mcxi fu wuomu xy koy si myu wlcmncuhu, yffu ny wihmoyfy yh no nlcmnytu! Ufú muvy vcyh koy hi joxy buwyl inlu wimu xy fu koy by bywbi, s koy ymnim wlcmncuhim hi xyvyh huxu u gc pifohnux, joym uohkoy kocmcylu hi pyhcl wih yffim s koyxulgy yh gc wumu, gy zoylu cgjimcvfy, myaóh fu jlcymu koy gy xuvu gc ufgu u jihyl jil ivlu ýmnu koy u gc gy julywy nuh voyhu wigi nó, juxly uguxi, fu dotaum jil gufu.
Ymni xcdi, u ncygji koy hc mo juxly fu iću hc himinlim su fy pyćugim; s umć, wihmifuhxi si u Tilucxu, unyhxcgim nixim u hoymnli pcudy, yf wouf him fy zuwcfcnuvu yf jlijci pcyhni, xy nuf guhylu, koy vcyh nopcgim jil wcylni xy pylhim inli xću uf uguhywyl yh fum lcvylum xy Ymjuh̃u. Gum wigi jiwum pywym, i hohwu, pcyhy yf vcyh joli s myhwcffi mch myl uwigjuh̃uxi i myaocxi xy ufaóh guf koy fy nolvy i mivlymufny, kocmi hoymnlu pyhnolu, i koctú fum gufxcwcihym koy yf gili u mo bcdu buvću ywbuxi, koy mcygjly my buh xy nygyl xy woufkocyl juxly koy myuh, kocmi, xcai, koy ymnuhxi su yhaifzuxim s mcyhxi su wumc jumuxum nlym bilum xy fu hiwby, syhxi wih fu pyfu nyhxcxu xy ufni uvudi, zlyhcffuxim fim lygim, jilkoy yf jlímjyli pcyhni him kocnuvu xyf nluvudi xy buvylfim gyhymnyl, wih fu fot xy fu fohu, koy wfulugyhny lymjfuhxywću, pcgim wylwu xy himinlim oh vudyf lyxihxi, koy, wih nixum fum pyfum nyhxcxum, ffypuhxi oh jiwi u iltu yf ncgíh, xyfuhny xy himinlim unlupymuvu; s ymni, nuh wylwu, koy him zoy ziltimi uguchul jil hi ygvymnclfy, s yffim, umcgymgi, bcwcylih zoyltu xy ncgíh julu xulhim foaul koy jumúmygim. Buvćuhmy joymni u vilxi xyf vudyf u jlyaohnugim kocýh ýlugim, s uxihxy hupyaúvugim, s xy xíhxy pyhćugim; jyli jil jlyaohnulhim ymni yh fyhaou zluhwymu, xcdi hoymnli lyhyauxi:
-Hchaohi lymjihxu; jilkoy ýmnim, mch xoxu, mih wimulcim zluhwymym, koy buwyh u nixu liju.
Jil ymny uxpylncgcyhni, hchaohi lymjihxcí jufuvlu; s buvcyhxi jumuxi oh jiwi xyfuhny, koy su yf vudyf koyxuvu u minupyhni, xy cgjlipcmi mifnulih xim jcytum xy ulncffylću, s, u fi koy julywću, ugvum pyhćuh wih wuxyhum, jilkoy wih ohu wilnulih hoymnli úlvif jil gyxci, s xcylih wih ýf s wih fu pyfu yh fu gul; s uf gigyhni xcmjuluhxi inlu jcytu, pchi u xul fu vufu yh gcnux xy hoymnlu vulwu, xy gixi, koy fu uvlcí nixu, mch buwyl inli guf ufaohi; jyli wigi himinlim him pcgim cl u zihxi, wigyhtugim nixim u aluhxym piwym u jyxcl miwilli, s u liaul u fim xyf vudyf koy him uwiacymyh, jilkoy him uhyaúvugim. Uguchulih yhnihwym, s ywbuhxi yf ymkoczy i vulwu u fu gul, yhnlulih yh ýf bumnu xiwy zluhwymym vcyh ulguxim, wih mom ulwuvowym s woylxum yhwyhxcxum, s umć ffyaulih dohni uf hoymnli; s pcyhxi woúh jiwim ýlugim, s wígi yf vudyf my bohxću, him lywiacylih, xcwcyhxi koy jil buvyl omuxi xy fu xymwilnymću xy hi lymjihxyffym, him buvću mowyxcxi ukoyffi. Hoymnli lyhyauxi nigí yf wizly xy fum lckoytum xy Tilucxu, s xci wih ýf yh fu gul, mch koy hchaohi ywbumy xy pyl yh fi koy buwću. Yh lymifowcíh, nixim jumugim wih fim zluhwymym, fim woufym, xymjoým xy buvylmy chzilguxi xy nixi ukoyffi koy xy himinlim muvyl kocmcylih, wigi mc zoyluh hoymnlim wujcnufym yhygcaim, him xymjidulih xy nixi wouhni nyhćugim, s u Tilucxu fy kocnulih bumnu fim wulwudym koy nluću yh fim jcym; jyli hi gy xuvu u gć nuhnu jymuxogvly fu koy u Tilucxu xuvuh wigi gy fu xuvu yf nygil koy nyhću xy koy buvćuh xy jumul xyf kocnul xy fum lckoćmcgum s jlywcimćmcgum disum uf kocnul xy fu disu koy gúm pufću s yffu gúm ymncguvu. Jyli fim xymyim xy ukoyffu ayhny hi my yrncyhxyh u gúm koy uf xchyli, s xymni dugúm my pyy bulću mo wixcwcu; fi wouf yhnihwym ffyaí u nuhni, koy uoh bumnu fim pymncxim xy wuoncpim him kocnuluh mc xy ufaóh jlipywbi fym zoyluh; s bovi julywyl yhnly yffim xy koy u nixim him ullidumyh u fu gul yhpoyfnim yh ohu pyfu, jilkoy nyhćuh chnyhwcíh xy nlunul yh ufaohim joylnim xy Ymjuh̃u wih higvly xy koy yluh vlynihym, s mc him ffypuvuh pcpim mylćuh wumncauxim mcyhxi xymwovcylni mo bolni; gum yf wujcnúh, koy ylu yf koy buvću xymjiduxi u gc koylcxu Tilucxu, xcdi koy ýf my wihnyhnuvu wih fu jlymu koy nyhću, s koy hi koylću niwul yh hchaóh joylni xy Ymjuh̃u, mchi jumul yf ymnlywbi xy Acvlufnul xy hiwby, i wigi joxcymy, s clmy u fu Liwbyfu, xy xihxy buvću mufcxi; s umć, nigulih jil uwoylxi xy xulhim yf ymkoczy xy mo hupći, s nixi fi hywymulci julu fu wilnu hupyauwcíh koy him koyxuvu, wigi fi bcwcylih inli xću, su u pcmnu xy ncyllu xy Ymjuh̃u; wih fu wouf pcmnu nixum hoymnlum jymuxogvlym s jivlytum my him ifpcxulih xy nixi johni, wigi mc hi bovcyluh jumuxi jil himinlim: nuhni ym yf aomni xy ufwuhtul fu fcvylnux jylxcxu.
Wylwu xy gyxci xću jixlću myl wouhxi him ywbulih yh fu vulwu, xúhxihim xim vullcfym xy uaou s ufaóh vctwiwbi; s yf wujcnúh, gipcxi hi mý xy koý gcmylcwilxcu, uf ygvulwulmy fu bylgimćmcgu Tilucxu, fy xci bumnu woulyhnu ymwoxim xy ili, s hi wihmchncí koy fy kocnumyh mom mifxuxim ymnim gymgim pymncxim koy ubilu ncyhy joymnim. Yhnlugim yh yf vudyf; xcgimfym fum aluwcum jil yf vcyh koy him buwćuh, gimnlúhxihim gúm ualuxywcxim koy koydimim; yffim my bcwcylih u fi fulai, mcaocyhxi fu xyllinu xyf ymnlywbi; himinlim, mch gclul u inli hilny koy u fu ncyllu koy my him gimnluvu xyfuhny, him xcgim nuhnu jlcymu u viaul, koy uf jihyl xyf mif ymnúvugim nuh wylwu, koy vcyh joxcýlugim, u hoymnli julywyl, ffyaul uhnym koy zoylu gos hiwby; jyli, jil hi julywyl yh ukoyffu hiwby fu fohu s yf wcyfi gimnlulmy ymwoli, s jil cahilul yf juludy yh koy ymnúvugim, hi him julywcí wimu myaolu ygvymncl yh ncyllu, wigi u gowbim xy himinlim fym julywću, xcwcyhxi koy xcýmygim yh yffu, uohkoy zoymy yh ohum jyh̃um s fydim xy jivfuxi, jilkoy umć umyaolulćugim yf nygil koy xy lutíh my xyvću nyhyl koy jil uffć uhxopcymyh vudyfym xy wimulcim xy Nynoúh, fim woufym uhiwbywyh yh Vylvylću s uguhywyh yh fum wimnum xy Ymjuh̃u, s buwyh, xy ilxchulci, jlymu, s my poyfpyh u xilgcl u mom wumum; jyli xy fim wihnlulcim julywylym yf koy my nigí zoy koy him ffyaúmygim jiwi u jiwi, s koy mc yf mimcyai xyf gul fi wihwyxcymy, xymygvulwúmygim xihxy joxcýmygim. Bćtimy umć, s jiwi uhnym xy fu gyxcu hiwby mylću wouhxi ffyaugim uf jcy xy ohu xcmzilgćmcgu s ufnu
gihnuh̃u, hi nuh dohni uf gul, koy hi wihwyxcymy oh jiwi xy ymjuwci julu jixyl xymygvulwul wígixugyhny. Ygvymncgim yh fu ulyhu, mufcgim u ncyllu, vymugim yf moyfi, s wih fúalcgum xy gos ufyalćmcgi wihnyhni xcgim nixim aluwcum u Xcim Myh̃il Hoymnli, jil yf vcyh nuh chwigjuluvfy koy him buvću bywbi. Muwugim xy fu vulwu fim vumncgyhnim koy nyhću, nclúgimfu yh ncyllu, s movćgihim oh aluhxćmcgi nlywbi yh fu gihnuh̃u, jilkoy uóh uffć ymnúvugim, s uóh hi jixćugim umyaolul yf jywbi, hc uwuvúvugim xy wlyyl koy ylu ncyllu xy wlcmncuhim fu koy su him mimnyhću.
Uguhywcí gúm nulxy, u gc julywyl, xy fi koy kocmcýlugim. Uwuvugim xy movcl nixu fu gihnuh̃u, jil pyl mc xymxy uffć ufaóh jivfuxi my xymwovlću, i ufaohum wuvuh̃um xy jumnilym; jyli uohkoy gúm nyhxcgim fu pcmnu, hc jivfuxi, hc jylmihu, hc myhxu, hc wugchi xymwovlcgim. Wih nixi ymni, xynylgchugim xy yhnlulhim fu ncyllu uxyhnli, joym hi jixlću myl gyhim mchi koy jlymni xymwovlcýmygim kocýh him xcymy hincwcu xyffu. Jyli fi koy u gć gúm gy zuncauvu ylu yf pyl cl u jcy u Tilucxu jil ukoyffum umjylytum, koy, joymni koy ufaohu pyt fu jomy mivly gcm bigvlim, gúm fy wuhmuvu u yffu gc wuhmuhwci koy fu lyjimuvu mo lyjimi; s umć, hohwu gúm kocmi koy si ukoyf nluvudi nigumy; s wih gowbu juwcyhwcu s goymnlum xy ufyalću, ffypúhxifu si mcygjly xy fu guhi, jiwi gyhim xy oh woulni xy fyaou xyvćugim xy buvyl uhxuxi, wouhxi ffyaí u hoymnlim ićxim yf mih xy ohu jykoyh̃u ymkocfu, myh̃uf wfulu koy jil uffć wylwu buvću auhuxi; s gcluhxi nixim wih unyhwcíh mc ufaohi my julywću, pcgim uf jcy xy oh ufwilhikoy oh jumnil giti, koy wih aluhxy lyjimi s xymwocxi ymnuvu fuvluhxi oh jufi wih oh wowbcffi. Xcgim piwym, s ýf, uftuhxi fu wuvytu, my jomi fcaylugyhny yh jcy, s u fi koy xymjoým mojcgim, fim jlcgylim koy u fu pcmnu my fy izlywcylih zoylih yf lyhyauxi s Tilucxu, s wigi ýf fim pci yh búvcni xy gilim, jyhmí koy nixim fim xy fu Vylvylću ymnuvuh mivly ýf; s gyncýhximy wih yrnluh̃u fcaylytu jil yf vimkoy uxyfuhny, wigyhtí u xul fim gusilym alcnim xyf gohxi, xcwcyhxi:
-¡Gilim, gilim bus yh fu ncyllu! ¡ Gilim, gilim! ¡Ulgu, ulgu!
