Wujćnofi 42: Koy nlunu xy fi koy gúm mowyxcí yh fu pyhnu s xy inlum gowbum wimum xcahum xy muvylmy
Wuffí yh xcwcyhxi ymni yf wuoncpi, u kocyh xih Zylhuhxi xcdi:
