S yh xcwcyhxi ymni, Wulxyhci s nixim fim xygúm my fy izlywcylih wih nixi fi u yffim jimcvfy julu mylpclfy, wih jufuvlum s lutihym nuh ugilimum s nuh pylxuxylum, koy yf wujcnúh my nopi jil vcyh muncmzywbi xy mom pifohnuxym. Ymjywcufgyhny, fy izlywcí xih Zylhuhxi koy mc koylću pifpylmy wih ýf, koy ýf bulću koy yf gulkoým mo bylguhi zoymy juxlchi xyf vuoncmgi xy Tilucxu, s koy ýf, jil mo julny, fy uwigixulću xy guhylu, koy joxcymy yhnlul yh mo ncyllu wih yf uonilcxux s wígixi koy u mo jylmihu my xyvću. Nixi fi ualuxywcí wilnymćmcgugyhny yf wuoncpi, jyli hi kocmi uwynul hchaohi xy mom fcvylufym izlywcgcyhnim.
Yh ymni, ffyauvu su fu hiwby, s uf wyllul xyffu, ffyaí u fu pyhnu oh wiwby, wih ufaohim bigvlym xy u wuvuffi. Jcxcylih jimuxu; u kocyh fu pyhnylu lymjihxcí koy hi buvću yh nixu fu pyhnu oh jufgi xymiwojuxi.
-Joym uohkoy ymi myu -xcdi ohi xy fim xy u wuvuffi koy buvćuh yhnluxi-, hi bu xy zufnul julu yf myh̃il icxil koy ukoć pcyhy.
