Jyli u ymny ncygji su buvću mufcxi xyf wiwby oh bigvly, koy yh yf nludy gimnlí foyai yf izcwci s wulai koy nyhću, jilkoy fu liju foyhau, wih fum guhaum ulliwuxum, koy pymnću, gimnlulih myl icxil, wigi mo wlcuxi buvću xcwbi. Nluću xy fu guhi u ohu xihwyffu, uf julywyl xy bumnu xcyt s mycm uh̃im, pymncxu xy wugchi, nuh vctullu, nuh bylgimu s nuh auffulxu, koy u nixim jomi yh uxgcluwcíh mo pcmnu; xy moylny, koy u hi buvyl pcmni u Xilinyu, s u Fomwchxu s Tilucxu, koy yh fu pyhnu ymnuvuh, wlysyluh koy inlu nuf bylgimolu wigi fu xymnu xihwyffu xczćwcfgyhny joxcylu buffulmy. Buffímy xih Kocdiny uf yhnlul xyf icxil s xy fu xihwyffu, s umć wigi fy pci, xcdi:
-Myaolugyhny joyxy poymnlu gylwyx yhnlul s ymjuwculmy yh ymny wumncffi; koy uohkoy ym ymnlywbi s guf uwigixuxi, hi bus ymnlywbytu hc chwigixcxux yh yf gohxi koy hi xý foaul u fum ulgum s u fum fynlum, s gúm mc fum ulgum s fynlum nluyh jil aoću s uxufcx u fu zylgimolu, wigi fu nluyh fum fynlum xy poymnlu gylwyx yh ymnu zylgimu xihwyffu, u kocyh xyvyh hi mífi uvlclmy s guhczymnulmy fim wumncffim, mchi ujulnulmy fim lcmwim, s xcpcxclmy s uvudulmy fum gihnuh̃um, julu xuffy uwiacxu. Yhnly poymnlu gylwyx, xcai, yh ymny julućmi, koy ukoć buffulú ymnlyffum s mifym koy uwigjuh̃yh yf wcyfi koy poymnlu gylwyx nluy wihmcai; ukoć buffulú fum ulgum yh mo johni s fu bylgimolu yh mo yrnlygi.
