-Xýdymygy u gc yf buwyl ymu yrjylcyhwcu -xcdi yf wolu-; wouhni gúm koy hi bus jyhmul mchi koy pim, myh̃il wujcnúh, mylýcm gos vcyh lywyvcxi; jilkoy yf pufil s jloxyhwcu koy yh mo voyh julywyl xymwovly poymnli bylguhi hi xu chxcwcim xy myl ulliauhny hc xymwihiwcxi, hc koy hi bu xy muvyl jihyl fim wumim xy fu zilnohu yh mo johni.
