-Ffugúvumy -lymjihxcí yf wolu- Los Jýlyt xy Pcyxgu, s ylu hunoluf xy oh foaul xy fum gihnuh̃um xy Fyíh; yf wouf gy wihní oh wumi koy u mo juxly wih mom bylguhim fy buvću mowyxcxi, koy, u hi wihnúlgyfi oh bigvly nuh pylxuxyli wigi ýf, fi nopcylu jil wihmydu xy ukoyffum koy fum pcydum woyhnuh yf chpcylhi uf zoyai. Jilkoy gy xcdi koy mo juxly buvću xcpcxcxi mo buwcyhxu yhnly nlym bcdim koy nyhću, s fym buvću xuxi wcylnim wihmydim, gydilym koy fim xy Wuníh. S mý si xywcl koy yf koy ýf ymwiací xy pyhcl u fu aoyllu fy buvću mowyxcxi nuh vcyh, koy yh jiwim uh̃im, jil mo pufil s ymzoylti, mch inli vluti koy yf xy mo gowbu pclnox, movcí u myl wujcnúh xy chzuhnylću, s u pylmy yh wugchi s jlyxcwugyhni xy myl jlymni guymnly xy wugji. Jyli zoyfy fu zilnohu wihnlulcu, joym xihxy fu joxcylu ymjylul s nyhyl voyhu, uffć fu jylxcí, wih jylxyl fu fcvylnux yh fu zyfcwćmcgu dilhuxu xihxy nuhnim fu wivlulih, koy zoy yh fu vunuffu xy Fyjuhni. Si fu jylxć yh fu Aifynu, s xymjoým, jil xczylyhnym mowymim, him buffugim wuguluxum yh Wihmnuhnchijfu. Xymxy uffć pchi u Ulayf, xihxy mý koy fy mowyxcí ohi xy fim gúm yrnluh̃im wumim koy yh yf gohxi buh mowyxcxi.
