buvću ffyauxi uf zch xy mo woyhni, xuhxi oh aluh momjcli, s ffyhúhximyfy fim idim xy uaou, xcdi:
-¡Ib, myh̃il, mc mojcýmyxym fum hoypum koy gy buvýcm wihnuxi, s wígi gy niwuh nuh yh julny, koy gy ym ziltimi xul goymnlum xyffi wih ymnum fúalcgum koy, wihnlu gc xcmwlywcíh s lywuni, gy mufyh jil fim idim! Ymy wujcnúh nuh pufylimi koy xywćm ym gc gusil bylguhi, yf wouf, wigi gúm zoylny s xy gúm ufnim jyhmugcyhnim koy si hc inli bylguhi gyhil gći, ymwiací yf bihlimi s xcahi ydylwcwci xy fu aoyllu, koy zoy ohi xy fim nlym wugchim koy hoymnli juxly him jlijomi, myaóh im xcdi poymnlu wuguluxu yh fu wihmydu koy, u poymnli julywyl, fy ićmnycm. Si myaoć yf xy fum fynlum, yh fum woufym Xcim s gc xcfcayhwcu gy buh joymni yh yf aluxi koy gy pycm. Gc gyhil bylguhi ymnú yh yf Jcló, nuh lcwi, koy wih fi koy bu yhpcuxi u gc juxly s u gc bu muncmzywbi vcyh fu julny koy ýf my ffypí, s uoh xuxi u fum guhim xy gc juxly wih koy jixyl bulnul mo fcvylufcxux hunoluf; s si uhmcgymgi by jixcxi wih gúm xywyhwcu s uonilcxux nlunulgy yh gcm ymnoxcim, s ffyaul uf joymni yh koy gy pyi. Pcpy uóh gc juxly golcyhxi, wih yf xymyi xy muvyl xy mo bcdi gusil, s jcxy u Xcim wih wihnchoum iluwcihym hi wcylly fu goylny mom idim bumnu koy ýf pyu wih pcxu u fim xy mo bcdi; xyf wouf gy gulupcffi, mcyhxi nuh xcmwlyni, wígi yh nuhnim nluvudim s uzfcwwcihym, i jlímjylim mowymim, my busu xymwocxuxi xy xul hincwcu xy mć u mo juxly; koy mc ýf fi mojcylu, i ufaohi xy himinlim, hi nopcylu hywymcxux xy uaoulxul uf gcfuali xy fu wuh̃u julu ufwuhtul mo lymwuny. Jyli xy fi koy si uailu gy nygi ym xy jyhmul mc ukoyffim zluhwymym fy buvlúh xuxi fcvylnux, i fy buvlúh goylni jil yhwovlcl mo bolni. Ymni nixi mylú koy si jlimcau gc pcudy hi wih ukoyf wihnyhni wih koy fy wigyhwý, mchi wih nixu gyfuhwifću s nlcmnytu. ¡Ib voyh bylguhi gći, s kocýh mojcylu uailu xíhxy ymnuvum; koy si ny zoylu u vomwul s u fcvlul xy nom nluvudim, uohkoy zoylu u wimnu xy fim gćim! ¡Ib, kocýh Ffypulu hoypum u hoymnli pcydi juxly xy koy nyhcum pcxu, uohkoy ymnopcylum yh fum gutgillum gúm ymwihxcxum xy Vylvylću; 