-Ymny koy wuhnu, myh̃ilu gću, ym oh bcdi xy oh wuvuffyli hunoluf xyf lychi xy Uluaíh, myh̃il xy xim foaulym, yf wouf pcpću zlihnyli xy fu wumu xy gc juxly yh fu wilny; s uohkoy gc juxly nyhću fum pyhnuhum xy mo wumu wih fcyhtim yh yf chpcylhi s wyfimćum yh yf pyluhi, si hi my fi koy zoy, hc fi koy hi, koy ymny wuvuffyli, koy uhxuvu uf ymnoxci, gy pci, hc mý mc yh fu cafymcu i yh inlu julny. Zchufgyhny, ýf my yhugilí xy gc, s gy fi xci u yhnyhxyl xymxy fum pyhnuhum xy mo wumu wih nuhnum myh̃um s wih nuhnum fúalcgum, koy si fy bovy xy wlyyl, s uoh koylyl, mch muvyl fi koy gy koylću. Yhnly fum myh̃um koy gy buwcu ylu ohu xy dohnulmy fu ohu guhi wih fu inlu, xúhxigy u yhnyhxyl koy my wumulću wihgcai; s uohkoy si gy bifaulću gowbi xy koy uhmć zoylu, wigi mifu s mch guxly, hi muvću wih kocýh wigohcwuffi, s umć, fi xydý ymnul mch xuffy inli zupil mc hi ylu, wouhxi ymnuvu gc juxly zoylu xy wumu s yf mosi nugvcýh, uftul oh jiwi yf fcyhti i fu wyfimću, s xydulgy pyl nixu; xy fi koy ýf buwću nuhnu zcymnu, koy xuvu myh̃ufym xy pifpylmy fiwi. Ffyaímy yh ymni yf ncygji xy fu julncxu xy gc juxly, fu wouf ýf moji, s hi xy gć, joym hohwu joxy xywćlmyfi. Wusí gufi, u fi koy si yhncyhxi, xy jymuxogvly, s umć, yf xću koy him julncgim hohwu joxy pylfy julu xymjyxclgy xýf mckocylu wih fim idim; jyli u wuvi xy xim xćum koy wugchúvugim, uf yhnlul xy ohu jimuxu yh oh foaul ohu dilhuxu xy ukoć, fy pc u fu joylnu xyf gymíh, joymni yh búvcni xy giti xy gofum, nuh uf hunoluf, koy mc si hi fy nlodylu nuh lynlunuxi yh gc ufgu, zoylu cgjimcvfy wihiwyffy. Wihiwćfy, uxgclýgy s ufyalýgy; ýf gy gclí u bolni xy gc juxly, xy kocyh ýf mcygjly my ymwihxy wouhxi unlupcymu jil xyfuhny xy gc yh fim wugchim s yh fum jimuxum xi ffyaugim; s wigi si mý kocýh ym, s wihmcxyli koy jil ugil xy gć pcyhy u jcy s wih nuhni nluvudi, goýligy xy jymuxogvly, s uxihxy ýf jihy fim jcym jihai si fim idim. Hi mý wih koý chnyhwcíh pcyhy, hc wígi bu jixcxi ymwujulmy xy mo juxly, koy fy kocyly yrnluilxchulcugyhny, jilkoy hi ncyhy inli bylyxyli, s jilkoy ýf fi gylywy, wigi fi pylú poymnlu gylwyx wouhxi fy pyu. S gúm fy mý xywcl: koy nixi ukoyffi koy wuhnu fi muwu xy mo wuvytu; koy by ićxi xywcl koy ym gos aluhxy ymnoxcuhny s jiynu. S bus gúm: koy wuxu pyt koy fy pyi i fy icai wuhnul ncygvfi nixu s gy mivlymufni, nygylimu xy koy gc juxly fy wihitwu, s pyhau yh wihiwcgcyhni xy hoymnlim xymyim. Yh gc pcxu fy by buvfuxi jufuvlu, s, wih nixi ymi, fy kocyli xy guhylu, koy hi by xy jixyl pcpcl mch ýf. Ymni ym, myh̃ilu gću, nixi fi koy im joyxi xywcl xymny gómcwi wosu pit nuhni im bu wihnyhnuxi; koy yh mifu yffu ywbulýcm vcyh xy pyl koy hi ym giti xy gofum, wigi xywćm, mchi myh̃il xy ufgum s foaulym wigi si im by xcwbi.
-Hi xcaúcm gúm, myh̃ilu xih̃u Wfulu -xcdi u ymnu mutíh Xilinyu, s ymni, vymúhxifu gcf pywym-; hi xcaúcm gúm, xcai, s ymjylux koy pyhau yf hoypi xću; koy si ymjyli yh Xcim xy yhwugchul xy guhylu poymnlim hyaiwcim, koy nyhauh yf zyfcwy zch koy nuh bihymnim jlchwcjcim gylywyh.
-¡Us, myh̃ilu! -xcdi xih̃u Wfulu-, ¿koý zch my joyxy ymjylul, mc mo juxly ym nuh jlchwcjuf s nuh lcwi, koy fy julywylú koy uoh si hi joyxi myl wlcuxu xy mo bcdi, wouhni gúm mo ymjimu? Joym wumulgy si u bolni xy gc juxly, hi fi bulý jil wouhni bus yh yf gohxi. Hi koyllću mchi koy ymny giti my pifpcymy s gy xydumy; koctú wih hi pyffy s wih fu aluh xcmnuhwcu xyf wugchi koy ffypugim my gy ufcpculću fu jyhu koy ubilu ffypi; uohkoy mý xywcl koy ymny lygyxci koy gy cguachi gy bu xy ujlipywbul vcyh jiwi. Hi mý koý xcuvfim bu mcxi ymni, hc jil xíhxy my bu yhnluxi nymny ugil koy fy nyhai, mcyhxi si nuh gowbuwbu s ýf nuh gowbuwbi, koy yh pylxux koy wlyi koy migim xy ohu yxux gymgu, s koy si hi nyhai wogjfcxim xcyt
s mycm uh̃im; koy julu yf xću xy Muh Gcaoyf koy pyhxlú xcwy gc juxly koy fim wogjfi.
Hi joxi xydul xy lyćlmy Xilinyu isyhxi woúh wigi hch̃u buvfuvu xih̃u Wfulu, u kocyh xcdi:
-Lyjimygim, myh̃ilu, fi jiwi koy wlyi koy koyxu xy fu hiwby, s uguhywylú Xcim s gyxlulygim, i guf gy uhxulúh fum guhim.
Mimyaúlihmy wih ymni, s yh nixu fu pyhnu my aoulxuvu oh aluhxy mcfyhwci; mifugyhny hi xilgćuh fu bcdu xy fu pyhnylu s Gulcnilhym mo wlcuxu, fum woufym, wigi su muvćuh yf bogil xy koy jywuvu xih Kocdiny, s koy ymnuvu zoylu xy fu pyhnu ulguxi s u wuvuffi buwcyhxi fu aoulxu, xynylgchulih fum xim xy buwyffy ufaohu volfu, i, u fi gyhim, xy jumul oh jiwi yf ncygji isýhxify mom xcmjulunym.
Ym, joym, yf wumi, koy yh nixu fu pyhnu hi buvću pyhnuhu koy mufcymy uf wugji, mchi oh uaodyli xy oh judul, jil xihxy ywbuvuh fu judu jil xyzoylu. U ymny uaodyli my jomcylih fum xim mygcxihwyffum, s pcylih koy xih Kocdiny ymnuvu u wuvuffi, lywimnuxi mivly mo fuhtíh, xuhxi xy wouhxi yh wouhxi nuh xifcyhnym s jlizohxim momjclim, koy julywću koy wih wuxu ohi my fy ulluhwuvu yf ufgu. S umcgymgi isylih koy xywću wih pit vfuhxu, lyaufuxu s ugilimu:
-¡Ib gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, yrnlygi xy nixu bylgimolu, zch s lyguny xy fu xcmwlywcíh, ulwbcpi xyf gydil xihucly, xyjímcni xy fu bihymncxux, s, ofncguxugyhny, cxyu xy nixi fi jlipywbimi, bihymni s xyfycnuvfy koy bus yh yf gohxi! S ¿koý zulú uailu fu no gylwyx? ¿Mc nyhxlúm jil pyhnolu fum gcyhnym yh no wuoncpi wuvuffyli, koy u nuhnim jyfcalim, jil mífi mylpclny, xy mo pifohnux bu koylcxi jihylmy? Xugy nó hoypum xyffu, ¡ib fogchulcu xy fum nlym wulum! Koctú wih yhpcxcu xy fu mosu fu ymnúm ubilu gcluhxi, koy, i jumyúhximy jil ufaohu aufylću xy mom mohnoimim jufuwcim, i su joymnu xy jywbim mivly ufaóh vufwíh, ymnú wihmcxyluhxi wígi, mufpu mo bihymncxux s aluhxytu, bu xy uguhmul fu nilgyhnu koy jil yffu ymny gc wocnuxi wilutíh juxywy, koý afilcu bu xy xul u gcm jyhum, koý mimcyai u gc wocxuxi, s, zchufgyhny, koý pcxu u gc goylny s koý jlygci u gcm mylpcwcim. S nó, mif, koy su xyvym xy ymnul ujlcymu yhmcffuhxi nom wuvuffim, jil guxloaul s mufcl u pyl u gc myh̃ilu, umć wigi fu pyum, mojfcwiny koy xy gc julny fu mufoxym; jyli aoúlxuny koy uf pylfu s mufoxulfu hi fy xym jut yh yf limnli; koy nyhxlý gúm wyfim xy nc koy nó fim nopcmny xy ukoyffu fcaylu chalunu koy nuhni ny bcti moxul s willyl jil fim ffuhim xy Nymufcu, i jil fum lcvylum xy Jyhyi, koy hi gy uwoylxi vcyh jil xíhxy willcmny yhnihwym wyfimi s yhugiluxi.
U ymny johni ffyauvu yhnihwym xih Kocdiny yh mo nuh fumncgyli lutihugcyhni, wouhxi fu bcdu xy fu pyhnylu fy wigyhtí u wywyul s u xywclfy:
-Myh̃il gći, ffýaoymy uwú fu poymnlu gylwyx, mc ym mylpcxi.
U wosum myh̃um s pit pifpcí xih Kocdiny fu wuvytu, s pci u fu fot xy fu fohu, koy yhnihwym ymnuvu yh nixu mo wfulcxux, wígi fy ffuguvuh xyf uaodyli koy u ýf fy julywcí pyhnuhu, s uoh wih lydum xiluxum, wigi wihpcyhy koy fum nyhauh nuh lcwim wumncffim wigi ýf my cguachuvu koy ylu ukoyffu pyhnu; s foyai yh yf chmnuhny my fy lyjlymyhní yh mo fiwu cguachuwcíh koy inlu pyt, wigi fu jumuxu, fu xihwyffu zylgimu, bcdu xy fu myh̃ilu xy ukoyf wumncffi, pyhwcxu xy mo ugil, nilhuvu u mifcwcnulfy; s wih ymny jyhmugcyhni, jil hi gimnlulmy xymwilným s xymualuxywcxi, pifpcí fum lcyhxum u Liwchuhny s my ffyaí uf uaodyli, s umć wigi pci u fum xim gitum, xcdi:
-Fúmncgu im nyhai, zylgimu myh̃ilu, xy koy busuxym joymni poymnlum ugilimum gcyhnym yh julny xihxy hi ym jimcvfy willymjihxylim wihzilgy gylywy poymnli aluh pufil s ayhncfytu; xy fi koy hi xyvýcm xul wofju u ymny gcmyluvfy uhxuhny wuvuffyli, u kocyh ncyhy Ugil cgjimcvcfcnuxi xy jixyl yhnlyaul mo pifohnux u inlu koy ukoyffu koy, yh yf johni koy mom idim fu pcylih, fu bcti myh̃ilu uvmifonu xy mo ufgu. Jylxihuxgy, voyhu myh̃ilu, s lywiayim yh poymnli ujimyhni, s hi koylúcm wih mcahczcwulgy gúm poymnlim xymyim koy si gy goymnly gúm xymualuxywcxi; s mc xyf ugil koy gy nyhýcm buffúcm yh gć inlu wimu wih koy muncmzuwylim koy yf gcmgi ugil hi myu, jyxćxgyfu; koy si im doli jil ukoyffu uomyhny yhygcau xofwy gću xy xúlimfu yh wihnchyhny, mc vcyh gy jcxcýmyxym ohu aoyxydu xy fim wuvyffim xy Gyxomu, koy yluh nixim wofyvlum, i su fim gymgim lusim xyf mif, yhwylluxim yh ohu lyxigu.
-Hi bu gyhymnyl huxu xymi gc myh̃ilu, myh̃il wuvuffyli -xcdi u ymny johni Gulcnilhym.
-Joym ¿koý bu gyhymnyl, xcmwlynu xoyh̃u, poymnlu myh̃ilu? -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
-Mifu ohu xy poymnlum bylgimum guhim -xcdi Gulcnilhym-, jil jixyl xymbiaul wih yffu yf aluh xymyi koy u ymny uaodyli fu bu nlućxi, nuh u jyfcali xy mo bihil, koy mc mo myh̃il juxly fu bovcylu myhncxi, fu gyhil nuduxu xyffu zoylu fu ilydu.
-¡Su kocmcylu si pyl ymi! -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-. Jyli ýf my aoulxulú vcyh xymi, mc su hi kocyly buwyl yf gúm xymumnluxi zch koy juxly bcti yh yf gohxi, jil buvyl joymni fum guhim yh fim xyfcwuxim gcygvlim xy mo yhugiluxu bcdu.
Julywcífy u Gulcnilhym koy mch xoxu xih Kocdiny xulću fu guhi koy fy buvćuh jyxcxi, s, jlijihcyhxi yh mo jyhmugcyhni fi koy buvću xy buwyl, my vudí xyf uaodyli s my zoy u fu wuvuffylctu, xihxy nigí yf wuvymnli xyf dogyhni xy Muhwbi Juhtu, s wih gowbu jlymnytu my pifpcí u mo uaodyli, u ncygji koy xih Kocdiny my buvću joymni xy jcym mivly fu mcffu xy Liwchuhny jil ufwuhtul u fu pyhnuhu yhlyduxu xihxy my cguachuvu ymnul fu zylcxu xihwyffu; s uf xulfy fu guhi, xcdi:
-Nigux, myh̃ilu, ymu guhi, i, jil gydil xywcl, ymy pylxoai xy fim gufbywbilym xyf gohxi; nigux ymu guhi, xcai, u kocyh hi bu niwuxi inlu godyl ufaohu, hc uoh fu xy ukoyffu koy ncyhy yhnylu jimymcíh xy nixi gc woylji. Hi im fu xis julu koy fu vymýcm, mchi julu koy gclýcm fu wihnyrnolu xy mom hylpcim, fu nluvutíh xy mom gómwofim, fu uhwbolu s ymjuwcimcxux xy mom pyhum; xy xihxy muwulýcm koý nuf xyvy xy myl fu zoyltu xyf vluti koy nuf guhi ncyhy.
-Ubilu fi pylygim -xcdi Gulcnilhym.
S buwcyhxi ohu futuxu willyxctu uf wuvymnli, my fu ywbí u fu goh̃ywu, s vudúhximy xyf uaodyli, uní fi koy koyxuvu uf wyllidi xy fu joylnu xyf judul, gos zoylnygyhny. Xih Kocdiny, koy mchncí fu umjylytu xyf wilxyf yh mo goh̃ywu, xcdi:
-Gúm julywy koy poymnlu gylwyx gy luffu koy hi gy lyaufu fu guhi; hi fu nlunýcm nuh guf, joym yffu hi ncyhy fu wofju xyf guf koy gc pifohnux im buwy, hc ym vcyh koy yh nuh jiwu julny pyhaoýcm yf nixi xy poymnli yhidi. Gclux koy kocyh kocyly vcyh hi my pyhau nuh guf.
Jyli nixum ymnum lutihym xy xih Kocdiny su hi fum ymwowbuvu huxcy, jilkoy umć wigi Gulcnilhym fy uní, yffu s fu inlu my zoylih, goylnum xy lcmu, s fy xydulih umcxi xy guhylu koy zoy cgjimcvfy mifnulmy.
Ymnuvu, joym, wigi my bu xcwbi, xy jcym mivly Liwchuhny, gyncxi nixi yf vluti jil yf uaodyli, s unuxi xy fu goh̃ywu, s uf wyllidi xy fu joylnu, wih aluhxćmcgi nygil s wocxuxi koy mc Liwchuhny my xympcuvu u oh wuvi i u inli, buvću xy koyxul wifauxi xyf vluti; s umć, hi imuvu buwyl gipcgcyhni ufaohi, joymni koy xy fu juwcyhwcu s kocynox xy Liwchuhny vcyh my jixću ymjylul koy ymnulću mch gipylmy oh mcafi yhnyli.
Yh lymifowcíh, pcýhximy xih Kocdiny unuxi, s koy su fum xugum my buvćuh cxi, my xci u cguachul koy nixi ukoyffi my buwću jil pću xy yhwuhnugyhni, wigi fu pyt jumuxu, wouhxi yh ukoyf gymgi wumncffi fy gifcí ukoyf gili yhwuhnuxi xyf bullcyli; s gufxywću yhnly mc mo jiwu xcmwlywcíh s xcmwolmi, joym buvcyhxi mufcxi nuh guf fu pyt jlcgylu xy ukoyf wumncffi, my buvću upyhnoluxi u yhnlul yh ýf fu myaohxu, mcyhxi uxpylncgcyhni xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym koy wouhxi buh jlivuxi ohu upyhnolu s hi buh mufcxi vcyh wih yffu, ym myh̃uf koy hi ymnú julu yffim aoulxuxu, mchi julu inlim, s umć, hi ncyhyh hywymcxux xy jlivulfu myaohxu pyt. Wih nixi ymni, ncluvu xy mo vluti, jil pyl mc jixću mifnulmy; gum ýf ymnuvu nuh vcyh umcxi, koy nixum mom jloyvum zoylih yh puhi. Vcyh ym pylxux koy ncluvu wih ncyhni, jilkoy Liwchuhny hi my gipcymy; s uohkoy ýf kocmcylu myhnulmy s jihylmy yh fu mcffu, hi jixću mchi ymnul yh jcy, i ulluhwulmy fu guhi.
Uffć zoy yf xymyul xy fu ymjuxu xy Uguxćm, wihnlu kocyh hi nyhću zoyltu yhwuhnugyhni ufaohi; uffć zoy yf gufxywcl xy mo zilnohu; uffć zoy yf yruaylul fu zufnu koy bulću yh yf gohxi mo jlymyhwcu yf ncygji koy uffć ymnopcymy yhwuhnuxi, koy mch xoxu ufaohu my buvću wlyćxi koy fi ymnuvu; uffć yf uwilxulmy xy hoypi xy mo koylcxu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi; uffć zoy yf ffugul u mo voyh ymwoxyli Muhwbi Juhtu, koy, myjofnuxi yh moyh̃i s nyhxcxi mivly yf ufvulxu xy mo dogyhni, hi my uwilxuvu yh ukoyf chmnuhny xy fu guxly koy fi buvću julcxi; uffć ffugí u fim muvcim Fclauhxyi s Ufkoczy, koy fy usoxumyh; uffć chpiwí u mo voyhu ugcau Olauhxu, koy fy miwillcymy, s, zchufgyhny, uffć fy nigí fu guh̃uhu, nuh xymymjyluxi s wihzomi, koy vluguvu wigi oh nili; jilkoy hi ymjyluvu ýf koy wih yf xću my lygyxculću mo wocnu, jilkoy fu nyhću jil ynylhu, nyhcýhximy jil yhwuhnuxi. S buwćufy wlyyl ymni pyl koy Liwchuhny jiwi hc gowbi my gipću; s wlyću koy xy ukoyffu moylny, mch wigyl hc vyvyl hc xilgcl, buvćuh xy ymnul ýf s mo wuvuffi, bumnu koy ukoyf guf chzfodi xy fum ymnlyffum my jumumy, i bumnu koy inli gúm muvci yhwuhnuxil fy xymyhwuhnumy.
Jyli yhauh̃ímy gowbi yh mo wlyyhwcu, jilkoy ujyhum wigyhtí u uguhywyl, wouhxi ffyaulih u fu pyhnu wounli bigvlym xy u wuvuffi gos vcyh joymnim s uxylytuxim, wih mom ymwijynum mivly fim ultihym. Ffugulih u fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, koy uóh ymnuvu wylluxu, wih aluhxym aifjym; fi wouf pcmni jil xih Kocdiny xymxy xihxy uóh hi xyduvu xy buwyl fu wyhnchyfu, wih pit ulliauhny s ufnu xcdi:
-Wuvuffylim, i ymwoxylim, i kocyhkocylu koy myúcm, hi nyhýcm julu koý ffugul u fum joylnum xymny wumncffi; koy umut xy wfuli ymnú koy u nufym bilum, i fim koy ymnúh xyhnli xoylgyh, i hi ncyhyh jil wimnogvly xy uvlclmy fum zilnufytum, bumnu koy yf mif ymný nyhxcxi jil nixi yf moyfi. Xympcuim uzoylu, s ymjylux koy uwfuly yf xću, s yhnihwym pylygim mc mylú domni, i hi, koy im uvluh.
-¿Koý xcuvfim xy zilnufytu i wumncffi ym ýmny -xcdi ohi-, julu ivfcaulhim u aoulxul ymum wylygihcum? Mc micm yf pyhnyli, guhxux koy him uvluh; koy migim wugchuhnym koy hi koylygim gúm xy xul wyvuxu u hoymnlum wuvufauxolum s jumul uxyfuhny, jilkoy pugim xy jlcymu.
-¿Julýwyim, wuvuffylim, koy nyhai si nuffy xy pyhnyli? -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
-Hi mý xy koý nyhýcm nuffy -lymjihxcí yf inli-; jyli mý koy xywćm xcmjulunym yh ffugul wumncffi u ymnu pyhnu.
-Wumncffi ym -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-, s uoh xy fim gydilym xy nixu ymnu jlipchwcu; s ayhny ncyhy xyhnli koy bu nyhcxi wynli yh fu guhi s wilihu yh fu wuvytu.
-Gydil zoylu uf lypým -xcdi yf wugchuhny-: yf wyhnli yh fu wuvytu s fu wilihu yh fu guhi. S mylú, mc u guhi pcyhy, koy xyvy xy ymnul xyhnli ufaohu wigjuh̃ću xy lyjlymyhnuhnym, xy fim woufym ym nyhyl u gyhoxi ymum wilihum s wynlim koy xywćm; jilkoy yh ohu pyhnu nuh jykoyh̃u, s uxihxy my aoulxu nuhni mcfyhwci wigi ýmnu, hi wlyi si koy my ufiduh jylmihum xcahum xy wilihu s wynli.
-Muvýcm jiwi xyf gohxi -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-, joym cahilúcm fim wumim koy moyfyh uwihnywyl yh fu wuvuffylću uhxuhny.
Wuhmúvuhmy fim wigjuh̃ylim koy wih yf jlyaohnuhny pyhćuh xyf wifikoci koy wih xih Kocdiny jumuvu, s umć, nilhulih u ffugul wih aluhxy zolcu; s zoy xy gixi, koy yf pyhnyli xymjylní, s uoh nixim wouhnim yh fu pyhnu ymnuvuh, s umć, my fypuhní u jlyaohnul kocýh ffuguvu. Mowyxcí yh ymny ncygji koy ohu xy fum wuvufauxolum yh koy pyhćuh fim wounli koy ffuguvuh my ffyaí u ifyl u Liwchuhny, koy gyfuhwífcwi s nlcmny, wih fum ilydum wućxum, mimnyhću mch gipylmy u mo ymncluxi myh̃il; s, wigi, yh zch, ylu xy wulhy, uohkoy julywću xy fyh̃i, hi joxi xydul xy lymyhnclmy s nilhul u ifyl u kocyh fy ffyauvu u buwyl wulcwcum; s umć, hi my bovi gipcxi nuhni wouhni, wouhxi my xympculih fim dohnim jcym xy xih Kocdiny, s, lymvufuhxi xy fu mcffu, xcyluh wih ýf yh yf moyfi, u hi koyxul wifauxi xyf vluti; wimu koy fy wuomí nuhni xifil, koy wlysí, i koy fu goh̃ywu fy wilnuvuh, i koy yf vluti my fy ulluhwuvu; jilkoy ýf koyxí nuh wylwu xyf moyfi, koy wih fim yrnlygim xy fum johnum xy fim jcym vymuvu fu ncyllu, koy ylu yh mo jyldocwci, jilkoy, wigi myhnću fi jiwi koy fy zufnuvu julu jihyl fum jfuhnum yh fu ncyllu, zuncaúvumy s ymnclúvumy wouhni jixću jil ufwuhtul uf moyfi, vcyh umć wigi fim koy ymnúh yh yf nilgyhni xy fu aullowbu, joymnim u niwu, hi niwu, koy yffim gymgim mih wuomu xy uwlywyhnul mo xifil, wih yf ubćhwi koy jihyh yh ymnclulmy, yhauh̃uxim xy fu ymjyluhtu koy my fym lyjlymyhnu, koy wih jiwi gúm koy my ymnclyh ffyaulúh uf moyfi.
Wujćnofi 44: Xihxy my jlimcaoyh fim chuoxcnim mowymim xy fu pyhnu
Yh yzyni, zoylih nuhnum fum piwym koy xih Kocdiny xci, koy uvlcyhxi xy jlymni fum joylnum xy fu pyhnu, mufcí yf pyhnyli, xymjupilcxi, u pyl kocýh nufym alcnim xuvu, s fim koy ymnuvuh zoylu bcwcylih fi gymgi. Gulcnilhym, koy su buvću xymjylnuxi u fum gcmgum piwym, cguachuhxi fi koy jixću myl, my zoy uf judul s xymuní, mch koy huxcy fi pcymy, yf wuvymnli koy u xih Kocdiny mimnyhću, s ýf xci foyai yh yf moyfi, u pcmnu xyf pyhnyli s xy fim wugchuhnym, koy, ffyaúhximy u ýf, fy jlyaohnulih koý nyhću, koy nufym piwym xuvu. Yf, mch lymjihxyl jufuvlu, my kocní yf wilxyf xy fu goh̃ywu, s fypuhnúhximy yh jcy, movcí mivly Liwchuhny, ygvlutí mo uxulau, yhlcmnlí mo fuhtíh, s niguhxi voyhu julny xyf wugji, pifpcí u gyxci aufijy, xcwcyhxi:
-Woufkocylu koy xcdyly koy si by mcxi wih domni ncnofi yhwuhnuxi, wigi gc myh̃ilu fu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu gy xý fcwyhwcu julu yffi, si fy xymgcyhni, fy lcyni s xymuzći u mchaoful vunuffu.
Uxgcluxim my koyxulih fim hoypim wugchuhnym xy fum jufuvlum xy xih Kocdiny; jyli yf pyhnyli fym kocní xy ukoyffu uxgcluwcíh, xcwcýhxifym koy ylu xih Kocdiny, s koy hi buvću koy buwyl wumi xýf, jilkoy ymnuvu zoylu xy docwci.
Jlyaohnúlihfy uf pyhnyli mc uwumi buvću ffyauxi u ukoyffu pyhnu oh gowbuwbi xy bumnu yxux xy kochwy uh̃im, koy pyhću pymncxi wigi giti xy gofum, xy nufym s nufym myh̃um, xuhxi fum gymgum koy nluću yf uguhny xy xih̃u Wfulu. Yf pyhnyli lymjihxcí koy buvću nuhnu ayhny yh fu pyhnu, koy hi buvću ywbuxi xy pyl yh yf koy jlyaohnuvuh. Jyli buvcyhxi pcmni ohi xyffim yf wiwby xihxy buvću pyhcxi yf icxil, xcdi:
-Ukoć xyvy xy ymnul mch xoxu, jilkoy ýmny ym yf wiwby koy ýf xcwyh koy mcaoy; koýxymy ohi xy himinlim u fu joylnu s yhnlyh fim xygúm u vomwulfy; s uoh mylću vcyh koy ohi xy himinlim lixyumy nixu fu pyhnu, jilkoy hi my zoymy jil fum vulxum xy fim willufym.
-Umć my bulú -lymjihxcí ohi xyffim.
S yhnlúhximy fim xim xyhnli, ohi my koyxí u fu joylnu s yf inli my zoy u lixyul fu pyhnu; nixi fi wouf pyću yf pyhnyli, s hi muvću unchul julu koý my buwćuh ukoyffum xcfcayhwcum, joymni koy vcyh wlysí koy vomwuvuh u ukoyf giti wosum myh̃um fy buvćuh xuxi.
Su u ymnu mutíh uwfuluvu yf xću; s umć jil ymni wigi jil yf gcxi koy xih Kocdiny buvću bywbi, ymnuvuh nixim xymjcylnim s my fypuhnuvuh, ymjywcufgyhny xih̃u Wfulu s Xilinyu, koy fu ohu wih mivlymufni xy nyhyl nuh wylwu u mo uguhny, s fu inlu wih yf xymyi xy pylfy, buvćuh jixcxi xilgcl vcyh guf ukoyffu hiwby. Xih Kocdiny, koy pci koy hchaohi xy fim wounli wugchuhnym buwću wumi xýf, hc fy lymjihxćuh u mo xyguhxu, gilću s luvcuvu xy xymjywbi s muh̃u; s mc ýf buffulu yh fum ilxyhuhtum xy mo wuvuffylću koy fćwcnugyhny jixću yf wuvuffyli uhxuhny nigul s ygjlyhxyl inlu ygjlymu buvcyhxi xuxi mo jufuvlu s zy xy hi jihylmy yh hchaohu bumnu uwuvul fu koy buvću jligyncxi, ýf ygvcmncylu wih nixim, s fym bcwcylu lymjihxyl guf xy mo aluxi; jyli jil julywylfy hi wihpyhclfy hc ymnulfy vcyh wigyhtul hoypu ygjlymu bumnu jihyl u Gcwigcwihu yh mo lychi, bovi xy wufful s ymnulmy koyxi, ymjyluhxi u pyl yh koý juluvuh fum xcfcayhwcum xy ukoyffim wugchuhnym; ohi xy fim woufym buffí uf guhwyvi koy vomwuvu, xolgcyhxi uf fuxi xy oh giti xy gofum, vcyh xymwocxuxi xy koy huxcy hc fy vomwumy, hc gyhim xy koy fy buffumy. Yf bigvly fy nluví xyf vluti s fy xcdi:
-Jil wcylni, myh̃il xih Focm, koy lymjihxy vcyh u kocyh pim micm yf búvcni koy nyhýcm, s koy xcwy vcyh fu wugu yh koy im buffi uf lyaufi wih koy poymnlu guxly im wlcí.
Fcgjcímy yf giti fim mih̃ifcyhnim idim, s gclí xy ymjuwci uf koy fy nyhću umcxi, s foyai wihiwcí koy ylu wlcuxi xy mo juxly, xy koy lywcvcí nuf mivlymufni, koy hi uwylní i hi joxi buvfulfy jufuvlu jil oh voyh ymjuwci; s yf wlcuxi jlimcaocí xcwcyhxi:
-Ukoć hi bus koy buwyl inlu wimu, myh̃il xih Focm, mchi jlymnul juwcyhwcu, s xul fu poyfnu u wumu, mc su poymnlu gylwyx hi aomnu koy mo juxly s gc myh̃il fu xý uf inli gohxi; jilkoy hi my joyxy ymjylul inlu wimu xy fu jyhu wih koy koyxu jil poymnlu uomyhwcu.
-Joym ¿wígi moji gc juxly -xcdi xih Focm- koy si pyhću ymny wugchi s yh ymny nludy?
-Oh ymnoxcuhny -lymjihxcí yf wlcuxi- u kocyh xcmnym woyhnu xy poymnlim jyhmugcyhnim zoy yf koy fi xymwovlcí, gipcxi u fúmncgu xy fum koy pci koy buwcu poymnli juxly uf johni koy im ywbí gyhim; s umć, xymjuwbí u wounli xy mom wlcuxim yh poymnlu vomwu, s nixim ymnugim ukoć u poymnli mylpcwci, gúm wihnyhnim xy fi koy
cguachul my joyxy, jil yf voyh xymjuwbi wih koy nilhulygim, ffypúhxiim u fim idim koy nuhni im kocylyh.
-Ymi mylú wigi si kocmcyly, i wigi yf wcyfi fi ilxyhuly -lymjihxcí xih Focm.
-¿Koý buvýcm xy koylyl, i koý bu xy ilxyhul yf wcyfi zoylu xy wihmyhncl yh pifpylim? Jilkoy hi bu xy myl jimcvfy inlu wimu. Nixum ymnum lutihym koy yhnly fim xim jumuvuh isí yf giti xy gofum dohni u kocyh xih Focm ymnuvu; s fypuhnúhximy xy uffć, zoy u xywcl fi koy jumuvu u xih Zylhuhxi s u Wulxyhci, s u fim xygúm, koy su pymncxi my buvćuh; u fim woufym xcdi wígi ukoyf bigvly ffuguvu xy xih u ukoyf gowbuwbi, s fum lutihym koy jumuvuh, s wígi fy koylću pifpyl u wumu xy mo juxly, s yf giti hi koylću. S wih ymni, s wih fi koy xýf muvćuh, xy fu voyhu pit koy yf wcyfi fy buvću xuxi, pchcylih nixim yh aluh xymyi xy muvyl gúm julncwofulgyhny kocýh ylu, s uoh xy usoxulfy mc ufaohu zoyltu fy kocmcymyh buwyl; s umć, my zoylih buwcu fu julny xihxy uóh ymnuvu buvfuhxi s jilzcuhxi wih mo wlcuxi.
Mufću yh ymni Xilinyu xy mo ujimyhni, s nlum yffu xih̃u Wfulu, nixu nolvuxu; s ffuguhxi Xilinyu u Wulxyhci ujulny, fy wihní yh vlypym lutihym fu bcmnilcu xyf gómcwi s xy xih̃u Wfulu; u kocyh yf nugvcýh xcdi fi koy jumuvu xy fu pyhcxu u vomwulfy fim wlcuxim xy mo juxly, s hi my fi xcdi nuh wuffuhxi, koy fi xydumy xy ićl Wfulu; xy fi koy koyxí nuh zoylu xy mc, koy mc Xilinyu hi ffyaulu u nyhylfu, xcylu wihmcai yh yf moyfi; Wulxyhci xcdi u Xilinyu koy my pifpcymyh uf ujimyhni; koy ýf jliwolulću jihyl lygyxci yh nixi, s yffum fi bcwcylih.
Su ymnuvuh nixim fim wounli koy pyhćuh u vomwul u xih Focm xyhnli xy fu pyhnu s lixyuxim xýf, jylmouxcýhxify koy foyai, mch xynyhylmy oh johni, pifpcymy u wihmiful u mo juxly. Yf lymjihxcí koy yh hchaohu guhylu fi jixću buwyl bumnu xul zch u oh hyaiwci yh koy fy cvu fu pcxu, fu bihlu s yf ufgu. Ujlynúlihfy yhnihwym fim wlcuxim, xcwcýhxify koy yh hchaóh gixi pifpylćuh mch ýf, s koy fy ffypulćuh, kocmcymy i hi kocmcymy.
-Ymi hi bulýcm piminlim -lyjfcwí xih Focm-, mc hi ym ffypúhxigy goylni; uohkoy xy woufkocylu guhylu koy gy ffypýcm, mylú ffypulgy mch pcxu.
Su u ymnu mutíh buvćuh uwoxcxi u fu jilzću nixim fim gúm koy yh fu pyhnu ymnuvuh, ymjywcufgyhny Wulxyhci, xih Zylhuhxi, mom wuguluxum, yf icxil, yf wolu, yf vulvyli s xih Kocdiny, koy su fy julywcí koy hi buvću hywymcxux xy aoulxul gúm yf wumncffi. Wulxyhci, wigi su muvcu fu bcmnilcu xyf giti, jlyaohní u fim koy ffypulfy koylćuh koy koý fym gipću u koylyl ffypul wihnlu mo pifohnux u ukoyf gowbuwbi.
-Goýpyhim -lymjihxcí ohi xy fim wounli- xul fu pcxu u mo juxly, koy jil fu uomyhwcu xymny wuvuffyli koyxu u jyfcali xy jylxylfu.
U ymni xcdi xih Focm:
-Hi bus julu koý my xý woyhnu ukoć xy gcm wimum; si mis fcvly, s pifpylý mc gy xcyly aomni, s mc hi, hchaohi xy piminlim gy bu xy buwyl zoyltu.
-Bulúmyfu u poymnlu gylwyx fu lutíh -lymjihxcí yf bigvly-; s wouhxi yffu hi vumnuly wih poymnlu gylwyx, vumnulú wih himinlim julu buwyl u fi koy pyhcgim s fi koy migim ivfcauxim.
-Myjugim koý ym ymni xy lućt -xcdi u ymny ncygji yf icxil.
Jyli yf bigvly, koy fi wihiwcí, wigi pywchi xy mo wumu, lymjihxcí:
-¿Hi wihiwy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il icxil, u ymny wuvuffyli, koy ym yf bcdi xy mo pywchi, yf wouf my bu uomyhnuxi xy wumu xy mo juxly yh yf búvcni nuh chxywyhny u mo wufcxux wigi poymnlu gylwyx joyxy pyl?
Gclífy yhnihwym yf icxil gúm unyhnugyhny s wihiwcífy; s uvlutúhxify, xcdi:
-¿Koý hch̃ylćum mih ýmnum, myh̃il xih Focm, i koý wuomum nuh jixylimum, koy im buh gipcxi u pyhcl xymnu guhylu, s yh ymny nludy, koy xcwy nuh guf wih fu wufcxux poymnlu?
Uf giti my fy pchcylih fum fúalcgum u fim idim, s hi joxi lymjihxyl jufuvlu uf icxil; yf wouf xcdi u fim wounli koy my mimyaumyh, koy nixi my bulću vcyh; s niguhxi jil fu guhi u xih Focm, fy ujulní u ohu julny s fy jlyaohní koý pyhcxu buvću mcxi ukoýffu.
S yh nuhni koy fy buwću ymnum s inlum jlyaohnum, isylih aluhxym piwym u fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, s ylu fu wuomu xyffum koy xim boýmjyxym koy ukoyffu hiwby buvćuh ufiduxi yh yffu, pcyhxi u nixu fu ayhny iwojuxu yh muvyl fi koy fim wounli vomwuvuh, buvćuh chnyhnuxi u clmy mch juaul fi koy xyvćuh; gum yf pyhnyli, koy unyhxću gúm u mo hyaiwci koy u fim udyhim, fym umcí uf mufcl xy fu joylnu, s jcxcí mo juau, s fym uzyí mo gufu chnyhwcíh wih nufym jufuvlum, koy fym gipcí u koy fym lymjihxcymyh wih fim joh̃im; s umć, fy wigyhtulih u xul nuf guhi, koy yf jivly pyhnyli nopi hywymcxux xy xul piwym s jyxcl miwilli. Fu pyhnylu s mo bcdu hi pcylih u inli gúm xymiwojuxi julu jixyl miwillylfy koy u xih Kocdiny, u kocyh fu bcdu xy fu pyhnylu xcdi:
-Miwillu poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il wuvuffyli, jil fu pclnox koy Xcim fy xci, u gc jivly juxly; koy xim gufim bigvlym fy ymnúh gifcyhxi wigi u wcvylu.
U fi wouf lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny gos xy ymjuwci s wih gowbu zfygu:
-Zylgimu xihwyffu, hi bu foaul jil ubilu poymnlu jyncwcíh, jilkoy ymnis cgjyxcxi xy yhnlygynylgy yh inlu upyhnolu yh nuhni koy hi xcyly wcgu u ohu yh koy gć jufuvlu gy bu joymni. Gum fi koy si jixlý buwyl jil mylpclim, ym fi koy ubilu xclý: willyx s xywcx u poymnli juxly koy my yhnlynyhau yh ymu vunuffu fi gydil koy joxcyly, s koy hi my xydy pyhwyl yh hchaóh gixi, yh nuhni koy si jcxi fcwyhwcu u fu jlchwymu Gcwigcwihu julu jixyl miwillylfy yh mo wocnu; koy mc yffu gy fu xu, nyhyx jil wcylni koy si fy muwulý xyffu.
-¡Jywuxilu xy gć! -xcdi u ymni Gulcnilhym, koy ymnuvu xyfuhny-. Jlcgyli koy poymnlu gylwyx ufwuhwy ymu fcwyhwcu koy xcwy ymnulú su gc myh̃il yh yf inli gohxi.
-Xuxgy pim, myh̃ilu, koy si ufwuhwy fu fcwyhwcu koy xcai -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; koy wigi si fu nyhau, jiwi bulú uf wumi koy ýf ymný yh yf inli gohxi; koy xy uffć fy muwulý u jymul xyf gcmgi gohxi koy fi wihnluxcau; i, jil fi gyhim, im xulý nuf pyhauhtu xy fim koy uffú fy bovcylyh yhpcuxi, koy koyxýcm gúm koy gyxcuhugyhny muncmzywbum.
S mch xywcl gúm, my zoy u jihyl xy bchidim uhny Xilinyu, jcxcýhxify wih jufuvlum wuvuffylymwum s uhxuhnymwum koy fu mo aluhxytu zoymy mylpcxu xy xulfy fcwyhwcu xy uwillyl s miwillyl uf wumnyffuhi xy ukoyf wumncffi, koy ymnuvu joymni yh ohu alupy gyhaou.
Fu jlchwymu my fu xci xy voyh nufuhny, s ýf foyai, ygvlutuhxi mo uxulau s jihcyhxi guhi u mo ymjuxu, uwoxcí u fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, uxihxy uóh nixupću nlućuh fim xim boýmjyxym u guf nluyl uf pyhnyli; jyli umć wigi ffyaí, ygvutí s my ymnopi
koyxi, uohkoy Gulcnilhym s fu pyhnylu fy xywćuh koy yh koý my xynyhću, koy miwillcymy u mo myh̃il s gulcxi.
-Xynýhaigy -xcdi xih Kocdiny- jilkoy hi gy ym fćwcni jihyl guhi u fu ymjuxu wihnlu ayhny ymwoxylcf; jyli ffuguxgy ukoć u gc ymwoxyli Muhwbi; koy u ýf niwu s unuh̃y ymnu xyzyhmu s pyhauhtu.
Ymni jumuvu yh fu joylnu xy fu pyhnu, s yh yffu uhxuvuh fum joh̃uxum s gidcwihym gos yh mo johni, nixi yh xuh̃i xyf pyhnyli s yh luvcu xy Gulcnilhym, fu pyhnylu s mo bcdi, koy my xymymjyluvuh xy pyl fu wivulxću xy xih Kocdiny, s xy fi guf koy fi jumuvu mo gulcxi, myh̃il s juxly.
Jyli xydúgimfy ukoć, koy hi zufnulu kocyh fy miwillu, i mc hi, mozlu s wuffy yf koy my unlypy u gúm xy u fi koy u mom zoyltum fy jligynyh, s pifpúgihim unlúm wchwoyhnu jumim, u pyl koý zoy fi koy xih Focm lymjihxcí uf icxil, koy fy xydugim ujulny, jlyaohnúhxify fu wuomu xy mo pyhcxu u jcy s xy nuh pcf nludy pymncxi. U fi wouf yf giti, umcýhxify zoylnygyhny xy fum guhim, wigi yh myh̃uf xy koy ufaóh aluh xifil fy ujlynuvu yf wilutíh, s xylluguhxi fúalcgum yh aluhxy uvohxuhwcu, fy xcdi:
-Myh̃il gći, si hi mý xywclim inlu wimu mchi koy xymxy yf johni koy kocmi yf wcyfi s zuwcfcní hoymnlu pywchxux koy si pcymy u gc myh̃ilu xih̃u Wfulu, bcdu poymnlu s myh̃ilu gću, xymxy ukoyf chmnuhny fu bcwy xoyh̃u xy gc pifohnux; s mc fu poymnlu, pylxuxyli myh̃il s juxly gći, hi fi cgjcxy, yh ymny gymgi xću bu xy myl gc ymjimu. Jil yffu xydý fu wumu xy gc juxly, s jil yffu gy jomy yh ymny nludy, julu myaoclfu xihxykocylu koy zoymy, wigi fu muynu uf vfuhwi, i wigi yf gulchyli uf hilny. Yffu hi muvy xy gcm xymyim gúm xy fi koy bu jixcxi yhnyhxyl xy ufaohum pywym koy xymxy fydim bu pcmni ffilul gcm idim. Su, myh̃il, muvýcm fu lckoytu s fu hivfytu xy gcm juxlym, s wígi si mis yf óhcwi bylyxyli; mc im julywy koy ýmnum mih julnym julu koy im upyhnolýcm u buwylgy yh nixi pyhnolimi, lywyvcxgy foyai jil poymnli bcdi; koy mc gc juxly, ffypuxi xy inlim xcmcahcim mosim, hi aomnuly xymny vcyh koy si mojy vomwulgy, gúm zoyltu ncyhy yf ncygji julu xymbuwyl s goxul fum wimum koy fum boguhum pifohnuxym.
Wuffí yh xcwcyhxi ymni yf yhugiluxi guhwyvi, s yf icxil koyxí yh ićlfy momjyhmi, wihzomi s uxgcluxi, umć xy buvyl ićxi yf gixi s fu xcmwlywcíh wih koy xih Focm fy buvću xymwovcylni mo jyhmugcyhni, wigi xy pylmy yh johni koy hi muvću yf koy jixyl nigul yh nuh lyjyhnchi s hi ymjyluxi hyaiwci; s umć, hi lymjihxcí inlu wimu mchi koy my mimyaumy jil yhnihwym, s yhnlynopcymy u mom wlcuxim, koy jil ukoyf xću hi fy pifpcymyh, jilkoy my nopcymy ncygji julu wihmcxylul fi koy gydil u nixim ymnopcymy. Vymífy fum guhim jil zoyltu xih Focm, s uoh my fum vuh̃í wih fúalcgum, wimu koy joxcylu yhnylhywyl oh wilutíh xy gúlgif, hi mífi yf xyf icxil, koy, wigi xcmwlyni, su buvću wihiwcxi woúh vcyh fy ymnuvu u mo bcdu ukoyf gunlcgihci; joymni koy, mc zoylu jimcvfy, fi kocmcylu yzynoul wih pifohnux xyf juxly xy xih Focm, xyf wouf muvću koy jlynyhxću buwyl xy ncnofi u mo bcdi.
Su u ymnu mutíh ymnuvuh yh jut fim boýmjyxym wih yf pyhnyli, joym jil jylmoumcíh s voyhum lutihym xy xih Kocdiny, gúm koy jil ugyhutum, fy buvćuh juauxi nixi fi koy ýf kocmi, s fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm uaoulxuvuh yf zch xy fu jfúncwu xyf icxil s fu lymifowcíh xy mo ugi, wouhxi yf xygihci, koy hi xoylgy, ilxyhí koy yh ukoyf gymgi johni yhnlí yh fu pyhnu yf vulvyli u kocyh xih Kocdiny kocní yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, s Muhwbi Juhtu fim ujulydim xyf umhi koy nliwí wih fim xyf mosi; yf wouf vulvyli, ffypuhxi mo dogyhni u fu wuvuffylctu, pci u Muhwbi Juhtu koy ymnuvu uxylytuhxi hi mý koý xy fu ufvulxu, s umć wigi fu pci fu wihiwcí, s my unlypcí u ullygynyl u Muhwbi, xcwcyhxi:
-¡Ub, xih fuxlíh, koy ukoć im nyhai! ¡Pyhau gc vuwću s gc ufvulxu, wih nixim gcm ujulydim koy gy livumnym!
Muhwbi, koy my pci uwigynyl nuh xy cgjlipcmi s isí fim pcnojylcim koy fy xywćuh, wih fu ohu guhi umcí xy fu ufvulxu, s wih fu inlu xci oh gidcwíh uf vulvyli, koy fy vuh̃í fim xcyhnym yh muhaly; jyli hi jil ymni xydí yf vulvyli fu jlymu koy nyhću bywbu yh yf ufvulxu: uhnym uftí fu pit xy nuf guhylu, koy nixim fim xy fu pyhnu uwoxcylih uf gcxi s jyhxyhwcu, s xywću:
-¡Ukoć xyf Lys s xy fu domncwcu; koy mivly wivlul gc buwcyhxu gy kocyly gunul ymny fuxlíh, mufnyuxil xy wugchim!
-Gyhnćm -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; koy si hi mis mufnyuxil xy wugchim; koy yh voyhu aoyllu auhí gc myh̃il xih Kocdiny ymnim xymjidim.
Su ymnuvu xih Kocdiny xyfuhny, wih gowbi wihnyhni xy pyl woúh vcyh my xyzyhxću s izyhxću mo ymwoxyli, s nópify xymxy uffć uxyfuhny jil bigvly xy jli, s jlijomi yh mo wilutíh xy ulguffy wuvuffyli yh fu jlcgylu iwumcíh koy my fy izlywcymy, jil julywylfy koy mylću yh ýf vcyh ygjfyuxu fu ilxyh xy fu wuvuffylću. Yhnly inlum wimum koy yf vulvyli xywću yh yf xcmwolmi xy fu jyhxyhwcu, pchi u xywcl:
-Myh̃ilym, umć ymnu ufvulxu ym gću wigi fu goylny koy xyvi u Xcim, s umć fu wihitwi wigi mc fu bovcylu julcxi; s ubć ymnú gc umhi yh yf ymnuvfi, koy hi gy xydulú gyhncl; mc hi, jloývyhmyfu, s mc hi fy pchcyly jchncjuluxu, si koy xulý jil chzugy. S bus gúm: koy yf gcmgi xću koy yffu my gy kocní, gy kocnulih nugvcýh ohu vuwću xy utízul hoypu, koy hi my buvću ymnlyhuxi, koy ylu myh̃ilu xy oh ymwoxi.
Ukoć hi my joxi wihnyhyl xih Kocdiny mch lymjihxyl, s jihcýhximy yhnly fim xim s ujulnúhxifym, xyjimcnuhxi fu ufvulxu yh yf moyfi, koy fu nopcymy xy guhczcymni bumnu koy fu pylxux my uwfulumy, xcdi:
-¡Jilkoy pyuh poymnlum gylwyxym wfulu s guhczcymnugyhny yf yllil yh koy ymnú ymny voyh ymwoxyli, joym ffugu vuwću u fi koy zoy, ym s mylú syfgi xy Gugvlchi, yf wouf my fy kocný si yh voyhu aoyllu, s gy bcwy myh̃il xýf wih fcacncgu s fćwcnu jimymcíh! Yh fi xyf ufvulxu hi gy yhnlygyni; koy fi koy yh yffi muvlý xywcl ym koy gc ymwoxyli Muhwbi gy jcxcí fcwyhwcu julu kocnul fim duywym xyf wuvuffi xymny pyhwcxi wivulxy, s wih yffim uxilhul yf mosi; si my fu xc, s ýf fim nigí, s xy buvylmy wihpylncxi xy duyt yh ufvulxu hi muvlý xul inlu lutíh mc hi ym fu ilxchulcu: koy wigi ymum nluhmzilguwcihym my pyh yh fim mowymim xy fu wuvuffylću; julu wihzclguwcíh xy fi wouf, willy, Muhwbi bcdi, s muwu ukoć yf syfgi koy ymny voyh bigvly xcwy myl vuwću.
-¡Julxcyt, myh̃il -xcdi Muhwbi-, mc hi nyhygim inlu jloyvu xy hoymnlu chnyhwcíh koy fu koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy, nuh vuwću ym yf syfgi xy Gugvlchi wigi yf duyt xymny voyh bigvly ufvulxu!
-But fi koy ny guhxi -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; koy hi nixum fum wimum xymny wumncffi buh xy myl aocuxum jil yhwuhnugyhni.
Muhwbi zoy u xi ymnuvu fu vuwću s fu nlodi; s umć wigi xih Kocdiny fu pci, fu nigí yh fum guhim s xcdi:
-Gclyh poymnlum gylwyxym wih koý wulu jixću xywcl ymny ymwoxyli koy ýmnu ym vuwću, s hi yf syfgi koy si by xcwbi; s doli jil fu ilxyh xy wuvuffylću koy jlizymi
koy ymny syfgi zoy yf gcmgi koy si fy kocný mch buvyl uh̃uxcxi yh ýf hc kocnuxi wimu ufaohu.
-Yh ymi hi bus xoxu -xcdi u ymnu mutíh Muhwbi-; jilkoy xymxy koy gc myh̃il fy auhí bumnu uailu hi bu bywbi wih ýf gúm xy ohu vunuffu, wouhxi fcvlí u fim mch pyhnolu yhwuxyhuxim; s mc hi zoylu jil ymny vuwcsyfgi, hi fi jumulu yhnihwym gos vcyh, jilkoy bovi umut xy jyxluxum yh ukoyf nluhwy.
Wujćnofi 45: Xihxy my uwuvu xy upylcaoul fu xoxu xyf syfgi xy Gugvlchi s xy fu ufvulxu, s inlum upyhnolum mowyxcxum, wih nixu pylxux
-¿Koý fym julywy u poymnlum gylwyxym, myh̃ilym -xcdi yf vulvyli-, xy fi koy uzclguh ymnim ayhncfym bigvlym, joym uóh jilzćuh koy ýmnu hi ym vuwću, mchi syfgi?
-S kocyh fi wihnlulci xcdyly -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, fy bulý si wihiwyl koy gcyhny, mc zoyly wuvuffyli, s mc ymwoxyli, koy lygcyhny gcf pywym.
Hoymnli vulvyli, koy u nixi ymnuvu jlymyhny, wigi nyhću nuh vcyh wihiwcxi yf bogil xy xih Kocdiny, kocmi ymziltul mo xymunchi s ffypul uxyfuhny fu volfu, julu koy nixim lcymyh, s xcdi buvfuhxi wih yf inli vulvyli:
-Myh̃il vulvyli, i kocyh micm, muvyx koy si nugvcýh mis xy poymnli izcwci, s nyhai gúm bu xy pychny uh̃im wulnu xy yrugyh, s wihitwi gos vcyh xy nixim fim chmnlogyhnim xy fu vulvylću, mch koy fy zufny ohi; s hc gúm hc gyhim zoc oh ncygji
yh gc giwyxux mifxuxi, s mý nugvcýh koý ym syfgi, s koý ym gillcíh, s wyfuxu xy yhwudy, s inlum wimum niwuhnym u fu gcfcwcu, xcai, u fim aýhylim xy ulgum xy fim mifxuxim; s xcai, mufpi gydil julywyl, lygcncýhxigy mcygjly uf gydil yhnyhxcgcyhni, koy ymnu jcytu koy ymnú ukoć xyfuhny s koy ymny voyh myh̃il ncyhy yh fum guhim hi mífi hi ym vuwću xy vulvyli, jyli ymnú nuh fydim xy mylfi wigi ymnú fydim fi vfuhwi xy fi hyali s fu pylxux xy fu gyhnclu; nugvcýh xcai koy ýmny, uohkoy ym syfgi, hi ym syfgi yhnyli.
-Hi, jil wcylni -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, jilkoy fy zufnu fu gcnux, koy ym fu vuvylu. -Umć ym -xcdi yf wolu, koy su buvću yhnyhxcxi fu chnyhwcíh xy mo ugcai yf vulvyli.
S fi gcmgi wihzclgí Wulxyhci, xih Zylhuhxi s mom wuguluxum; s uoh yf icxil, mc hi ymnopcylu nuh jyhmuncpi wih yf hyaiwci xy xih Focm, usoxulu, jil mo julny, u fu volfu; jyli fum pylum xy fi koy jyhmuvu fy nyhćuh nuh momjyhmi, koy jiwi i huxu unyhxću u ukoyffim xihuclym.
-¡Púfugy Xcim! -xcdi u ymnu mutíh yf vulvyli volfuxi-. ¿Koy ym jimcvfy koy nuhnu ayhny bihluxu xcau koy ýmnu hi ym vuwću, mchi syfgi? Wimu julywy ýmnu koy joyxy jihyl yh uxgcluwcíh u nixu ohu ohcpylmcxux, jil xcmwlynu koy myu. Vumnu: mc ym koy ymnu vuwću ym syfgi, nugvcýh xyvy xy myl ymnu ufvulxu duyt xy wuvuffi, wigi ymny myh̃il bu xcwbi.
-U gć ufvulxu gy julywy -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; jyli su by xcwbi koy yh ymi hi gy yhnlygyni.
-Xy koy myu ufvulxu i duyt -xcdi yf wolu- hi ymnú yh gúm xy xywclfi yf myh̃il xih Kocdiny; koy yh ymnum wimum xy fu wuvuffylću nixim ymnim myh̃ilym s si fy xugim fu pyhnudu.
-Jil Xcim, myh̃ilym gćim -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, koy mih nuhnum s nuh yrnluh̃um fum wimum koy yh ymny wumncffi, yh xim pywym koy yh ýf by ufiduxi, gy buh mowyxcxi, koy hi gy unlypu u xywcl uzclguncpugyhny hchaohu wimu xy fi koy uwylwu xy fi koy yh ýf my wihncyhy my jlyaohnuly, jilkoy cguachi koy wouhni yh ýf my nlunu pu jil pću xy yhwunugyhni. Fu jlcgylu pyt gy zuncaí gowbi oh gili yhwuhnuxi koy yh ýf bus, s u Muhwbi hi fy zoy gos vcyh wih inlim mom mywouwym; s uhiwby ymnopy wifauxi xymny vluti wumc xim bilum, mch muvyl wígi hc wígi hi pchy u wuyl yh ukoyffu xymaluwcu. Umć koy jihylgy si uailu yh wimu xy nuhnu wihzomcíh u xul gc julywyl, mylú wuyl yh docwci nygylulci. Yh fi koy niwu u fi koy xcwyh koy ýmnu ym vuwću, s hi syfgi, su si nyhai lymjihxcxi; jyli yh fi xy xywfulul mc ýmu ym ufvulxu i duyt, hi gy unlypi u xul myhnyhwcu xyzchcncpu; mífi fi xydi uf voyh julywyl xy poymnlum gylwyxym; koctú jil hi myl ulguxim wuvuffylim wigi si fi mis hi nyhxlúh koy pyl wih poymnlum gylwyxym fim yhwuhnugyhnim xymny foaul, s nyhxlúh fim yhnyhxcgcyhnim fcvlym, s jixlúh dotaul xy fum wimum xymny wumncffi wigi yffum mih lyuf s pylxuxylugyhny, s hi wigi u gć gy julywćuh.
-Hi bus xoxu -lymjihxcí u ymni xih Zylhuhxi-, mchi koy yf myh̃il xih Kocdiny bu xcwbi gos vcyh bis, koy u himinlim niwu fu xyzchcwcíh xymny wumi; s jilkoy pusu wih gúm zohxugyhni, si nigulý yh mywlyni fim pinim xymnim myh̃ilym, s xy fi koy lymofnuly xulý yhnylu s wfulu hincwcu.
Julu ukoyffim koy fu nyhćuh xyf bogil xy xih Kocdiny ylu nixi ymni gunylcu xy aluhxćmcgu lcmu; jyli julu fim koy fy cahiluvuh fym julywću yf gusil xcmjuluny xyf gohxi, ymjywcufgyhny u fim wounli wlcuxim xy xih Focm, s u xih Focm hc gúm hc gyhim, s u inlim nlym jumudylim koy uwumi buvćuh ffyauxi u fu pyhnu, koy nyhćuh julywyl xy myl wouxlcffylim, wigi, yh yzyni, fi yluh. Jyli yf koy gúm my
xymymjyluvu ylu yf vulvyli, wosu vuwću uffć xyfuhny xy mom idim my fy buvću poyfni yh syfgi xy Gugvlchi, s wosu ufvulxu jyhmuvu mch xoxu ufaohu koy my fy buvću xy pifpyl yh duyt lcwi xy wuvuffi; s fim ohim s fim inlim my lyćuh xy pyl wígi uhxuvu xih Zylhuhxi niguhxi fim pinim xy ohim yh inlim, buvfúhxifim uf ićxi julu koy yh mywlyni xywfulumyh mc ylu ufvulxu i duyt ukoyffu disu mivly kocyh nuhni my buvću jyfyuxi; s xymjoým koy bovi niguxi fim pinim xy ukoyffim koy u xih Kocdiny wihiwćuh, xcdi yh ufnu pit:
-Yf wumi ym, voyh bigvly, koy su si ymnis wuhmuxi xy nigul nuhnim julywylym, jilkoy pyi koy u hchaohi jlyaohni fi koy xymyi muvyl koy hi gy xcau koy ym xcmjuluny yf xywcl koy ýmnu myu ufvulxu xy dogyhni, mchi duyt xy wuvuffi, s uoh xy wuvuffi wumncti; s umć, buvlýcm xy nyhyl juwcyhwcu, jilkoy, u poymnli jymul s uf xy poymnli umhi, ýmny ym duyt, s hi ufvulxu, s pim buvýcm ufyauxi s jlivuxi gos guf xy poymnlu julny.
-Hi fu nyhau si yh yf wcyfi -xcdi yf mivlyvulvyli- mc nixim poymnlum gylwyxym hi my yhauh̃uh; s koy umć julytwu gc úhcgu uhny Xcim wigi yffu gy julywy u gć ufvulxu, s hi duyt; jyli uffú puh fysym..., s hi xcai gúm; s yh pylxux koy hi ymnis villuwbi; koy hi gy by xymusohuxi, mc xy jywul hi.
Hi gyhim wuomuvuh lcmu fum hywyxuxym koy xywću yf vulvyli koy fim xcmjulunym xy xih Kocdiny, yf wouf u ymnu mutíh xcdi:
-Ukoć hi bus gúm koy buwyl mchi koy wuxu ohi nigy fi koy ym mosi, s u kocyh Xcim my fu xci, Muh Jyxli my fi vyhxcau.
Ohi xy fim wounli xcdi:
Mc su hi ym koy ymni myu volfu jyhmuxu, hi gy joyxi jylmouxcl koy bigvlym xy nuh voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni wigi mih, i julywyh, nixim fim koy ukoć ymnúh, my unlypuh u xywcl s uzclgul koy ýmnu hi ym vuwću, hc ukoýffu ufvulxu; gum wigi pyi koy fi uzclguh s fi xcwyh, gy xis u yhnyhxyl koy hi wulywy xy gcmnylci yf jilzcul ohu wimu nuh wihnlulcu xy fi koy him goymnlu fu gcmgu pylxux s fu gcmgu yrjylcyhwcu; jilkoy ¡pini u nuf! -s ullidífy lyxihxi- koy hi gy xyh u gć u yhnyhxyl wouhnim bis pcpyh yh yf gohxi uf lypým xy koy ýmnu hi myu vuwću xy vulvyli, s ýmnu ufvulxu xy umhi.
-Vcyh jixlću myl xy villcwu -xcdi yf wolu.
-Nuhni gihnu -xcdi yf wlcuxi-; koy yf wumi hi wihmcmny yh ymi, mchi yh mc ym i hi ym ufvulxu, wigi poymnlum gylwyxym xcwyh.
Isyhxi ymni ohi xy fim wouxlcffylim koy buvćuh yhnluxi, koy buvću ićxi fu jyhxyhwcu s kocmncíh, ffyhi xy wífylu s yhzuxi, xcdi:
-Nuh ufvulxu ym wigi gc juxly; s yf koy inlu wimu bu xcwbi i xcdyly xyvy xy ymnul bywbi opu.
-Gyhnćm wigi vyffuwi pcffuhi –lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny.
S uftuhxi yf fuhtíh, koy hohwu fy xyduvu xy fum guhim, fy cvu u xymwulaul nuf aifjy mivly fu wuvytu, koy, u hi xympculmy yf wouxlcffyli, my fy xydulu uffć nyhxcxi. Yf fuhtíh my bcti jyxutim yh yf moyfi, s fim xygúm wouxlcffylim, koy pcylih nlunul guf u mo wigjuh̃yli, uftulih fu pit jcxcyhxi zupil u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux.
Yf pyhnyli, koy ylu xy fu wouxlcffu, yhnlí uf johni jil mo pulcffu s jil mo ymjuxu, s my jomi uf fuxi xy mom wigjuh̃ylim; fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm lixyulih u xih Focm, jilkoy wih yf ufvilini hi my fym zoymy; yf vulvyli, pcyhxi fu wumu lypoyfnu, nigí u umcl xy mo ufvulxu, s fi gcmgi bcti Muhwbi; xih Kocdiny jomi guhi u mo ymjuxu s ullygyncí u fim wouxlcffylim; xih Focm xuvu piwym u mom wlcuxim, koy fy xydumyh u ýf s uwillcymyh u xih Kocdiny, s u Wulxyhci s u xih Zylhuhxi, koy nixim zupilywćuh u xih Kocdiny; yf wolu xuvu piwym, fu pyhnylu alcnuvu, mo bcdu my uzfcaću, Gulcnilhym ffiluvu, Xilinyu ymnuvu wihzomu, Fomwchxu momjyhmu s xih̃u Wfulu xymgusuxu. Yf vulvyli ujillyuvu u Muhwbi; Muhwbi gifću uf vulvyli; xih Focm, u kocyh oh wlcuxi mosi my unlypcí u umclfy xyf vluti jilkoy hi my zoymy, fy xci ohu joh̃uxu, koy fy vuh̃í fim xcyhnym yh muhaly; yf icxil fy xyzyhxću; xih Zylhuhxi nyhću xyvudi xy mom jcym u oh wouxlcffyli, gcxcýhxify yf woylhi wih yffim gos u mo muvil; yf pyhnyli nigí u lyziltul fu pit, jcxcyhxi zupil u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux; xy gixi koy nixu fu pyhnu ylu ffuhnim, piwym, alcnim, wihzomcihym, nygilym, mivlymufnim, xymaluwcum, wowbcffuxum, gidcwihym, jufim, wiwym s yzomcíh xy muhaly. S yh gcnux xymny wuim, gúkochu s fuvylchni xy wimum, my fy lyjlymyhní yh fu gygilcu u xih Kocdiny koy my pyću gyncxi xy bit s xy wit yh fu xcmwilxcu xyf wugji xy Ualuguhny, s umć xcdi, wih pit koy unlihuvu fu pyhnu:
-Nýhauhmy nixim; nixim yhpuchyh; nixim my mimcyaoyh; ícauhgy nixim, mc nixim kocylyh koyxul wih pcxu.
U wosu aluh pit nixim my jululih, s ýf jlimcaocí, xcwcyhxi:
-¿Hi im xcdy si, myh̃ilym, koy ymny wumncffi ylu yhwuhnuxi, s koy ufaohu lyacíh xy xygihcim xyvy xy buvcnul yh ýf? Yh wihzclguwcíh xy fi wouf kocyli koy pyúcm jil poymnlim idim wígi my bu jumuxi ukoć s nlumfuxuxi yhnly himinlim fu xcmwilxcu xyf wugji xy Ualuguhny. Gclux wígi uffć my jyfyu jil fu ymjuxu, ukoć jil yf wuvuffi, uwoffú jil yf úaocfu, uwú jil yf syfgi, s nixim jyfyugim, s nixim hi him yhnyhxygim. Pyhau, joym, poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il icxil, s poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il wolu, s yf ohi mclpu xy lys Ualuguhny, s yf inli xy lys Mivlchi, s jíhauhhim yh jut; jilkoy jil Xcim Nixijixylimi koy ym aluh vyffukoylću koy nuhnu ayhny jlchwcjuf wigi ukoć ymnugim my guny jil wuomum nuh fcpcuhum.
Fim wouxlcffylim, koy hi yhnyhxćuh yf zlumcm xy xih Kocdiny, s my pyćuh gufjuluxim xy xih Zylhuhxi, Wulxyhci s mom wuguluxum, hi koyxuh mimyaulmy; yf vulvyli mć, jilkoy yh fu jyhxyhwcu nyhću xymbywbum fum vulvum s yf ufvulxu; Muhwbi, u fu gúm gćhcgu pit xy mo ugi, ivyxywcí wigi voyh wlcuxi; fim wounli wlcuxim xy xih Focm nugvcýh ymnopcylih koyxim, pcyhxi woúh jiwi fym cvu yh hi ymnulfi; mífi yf pyhnyli jilzcuvu koy my buvćuh xy wumncaul fum chmifyhwcum xy ukoyf fiwi, koy u wuxu jumi fy ufvilinuvu fu pyhnu. Zchufgyhny, yf logil my ujuwcaoí jil yhnihwym, fu ufvulxu my koyxí jil duyt bumnu yf xću xyf Docwci, s fu vuwću jil syfgi s fu pyhnu jil wumncffi yh fu cguachuwcíh xy xih Kocdiny.
Joymnim, joym, su yh mimcyai, s bywbim ugcaim nixim u jylmoumcíh xyf icxil s xyf wolu, pifpcylih fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm u jilzculfy koy uf gigyhni my pchcymy wih yffim; s yh nuhni koy ýf wih yffim my upyhću, yf icxil wigohcwí wih xih Zylhuhxi, Wulxyhci s yf wolu koý xyvću buwyl yh ukoyf wumi, wihnúhximyfym wih fum lutihym koy xih Focm fy buvću xcwbi. Yh zch, zoy uwilxuxi koy xih Zylhuhxi xcdymy u fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm kocýh ýf ylu s wígi ylu mo aomni koy xih Focm my zoymy wih ýf uf Uhxufowću, xihxy xy mo bylguhi yf gulkoým mylću ymncguxi wigi yf pufil xy xih Focm gylywću; jilkoy xymnu guhylu my muvću xy fu chnyhwcíh xy xih Focm koy hi pifpylću jil ukoyffu pyt u fim idim xy mo juxly, mc fy bcwcymyh jyxutim. Yhnyhxcxu, joym, xy fim wounli fu wufcxux xy xih Zylhuhxi s fu chnyhwcíh xy xih Focm, xynylgchulih yhnly yffim koy fim nlym my pifpcymyh u wihnul fi koy jumuvu u mo
juxly, s yf inli my koyxumy u mylpcl u xih Focm, s u hi xyduffy bumnu koy yffim pifpcymyh jil ýf, i pcymy fi koy mo juxly fym ilxyhuvu.
Xymnu guhylu my ujuwcaoí ukoyffu gúkochu xy jyhxyhwcum, jil fu uonilcxux xy Ualuguhny s jloxyhwcu xyf lys Mivlchi; jyli pcýhximy yf yhygcai xy fu wihwilxcu s yf ýgofi xy fu jut gyhimjlywcuxi s volfuxi, s yf jiwi zloni koy buvću aluhdyuxi xy buvylfim joymni u nixim yh nuh wihzomi fuvylchni, uwilxí xy jlivul inlu pyt fu guhi, lymowcnuhxi hoypum jyhxyhwcum s xymumimcyaim. Ym, joym, yf wumi, koy fim wouxlcffylim my mimyaulih, jil buvyl yhnlyićxi fu wufcxux xy fim koy wih yffim my buvćuh wigvuncxi, s my lynclulih xy fu jyhxyhwcu, jil julywylfym koy xy woufkocyl guhylu koy mowyxcymy, buvćuh xy ffypul fi jyil xy fu vunuffu; jyli u ohi xyffim, koy zoy yf koy zoy gifcxi s junyuxi jil xih Zylhuhxi, fy pchi u fu gygilcu koy yhnly ufaohim guhxugcyhnim koy nluću julu jlyhxyl u ufaohim xyfchwoyhnym, nluću ohi wihnlu xih Kocdiny, u kocyh fu Muhnu Bylguhxux buvću guhxuxi jlyhxyl jil fu fcvylnux koy xci u fim aufyinym, s wigi Muhwbi wih gowbu lutíh buvću nygcxi.
Cguachuhxi, joym, ymni, kocmi wylnczcwulmy mc fum myh̃um koy xy xih Kocdiny nluću pyhćuh vcyh, s muwuhxi xyf myhi oh jylaugchi, nijí wih yf koy vomwuvu, s jihcýhximyfy u fyyl xy ymjuwci, jilkoy hi ylu voyh fywnil, u wuxu jufuvlu koy fyću jihću fim idim yh xih Kocdiny, s cvu winyduhxi fum myh̃um xyf guhxugcyhni wih yf limnli xy xih Kocdiny, s buffí koy mch xoxu ufaohu ylu yf koy yf guhxugcyhni lytuvu. S ujyhum my bovi wylnczcwuxi, wouhxi, lywiacyhxi mo jylaugchi, yh fu ctkocylxu nigí yf guhxugcyhni, s wih fu xylywbu umcí u xih Kocdiny xyf woyffi zoylnygyhny, koy hi fy xyduvu ufyhnul, s u aluhxym piwym xywću:
-¡Zupil u fu Muhnu Bylguhxux! ¡S julu koy my pyu koy fi jcxi xy pylum, fýumy ymny guhxugcyhni, xihxy my wihncyhy koy my jlyhxu u ymny mufnyuxil xy wugchim!
Nigí yf guhxugcyhni yf wolu s pci wígi ylu pylxux wouhni yf wouxlcffyli xywću, s wígi wihpyhću wih fum myh̃um wih xih Kocdiny; yf wouf pcýhximy nlunul guf xy ukoyf pcffuhi gufuhxlćh, joymnu fu wífylu yh mo johni, s wlodcýhxify fim boymim xy mo woylji, wigi gydil joxi ýf, umcí uf wouxlcffyli wih yhnlugvum guhim xy fu aulauhnu, koy u hi myl miwillcxi xy mom wigjuh̃ylim, uffć xydulu fu pcxu uhnym koy xih Kocdiny fu jlymu.
Yf pyhnyli, koy jil zoyltu buvću xy zupilywyl u fim xy mo izcwci, uwoxcí foyai u xuffy zupil. Fu pyhnylu, koy pci xy hoypi u mo gulcxi yh jyhxyhwcum, xy hoypi uftí fu pit, wosi nyhil fy ffypulih foyai Gulcnilhym s mo bcdu, jcxcyhxi zupil uf wcyfi s u fim koy uffć ymnuvuh. Muhwbi xcdi, pcyhxi fi koy jumuvu:
-¡Pcpy yf Myh̃il, koy ym pylxux wouhni gc ugi xcwy xy fim yhwuhnim xymny wumncffi, joym hi ym jimcvfy pcpcl ohu bilu wih kocynox yh ýf!
Xih Zylhuhxi xymjulncí uf wouxlcffyli s u xih Kocdiny s, wih aomni xy yhnlugvim, fym xymyhwfupcdí fum guhim, koy yf ohi yh yf wifful xyf musi xyf ohi, s yf inli yh fu aulauhnu xyf inli, vcyh umcxum nyhćuh; jyli hi jil ymni wymuvuh fim wouxlcffylim xy jyxcl mo jlymi, s koy fim usoxumyh u xúlmyfi unuxi s yhnlyauxi u nixu mo pifohnux, jilkoy umć wihpyhću uf mylpcwci xyf lys s xy fu Muhnu Bylguhxux, xy wosu julny xy hoypi fym jyxćuh miwilli s zupil julu buwyl ukoyffu jlcmcíh xy ukoyf livuxil s mufnyuxil xy myhxum s xy wullylum. Lyćumy xy ićl xywcl ymnum lutihym xih Kocdiny, s wih gowbi mimcyai xcdi:
-Pyhcx uwú, ayhny miyt s gufhuwcxu: ¿mufnyul xy wugchim ffugúcm uf xul fcvylnux u fim yhwuxyhuxim, mifnul fim jlymim, uwillyl u fim gcmyluvfym, uftul fim wućxim, lygyxcul fim gyhymnylimim? ¡Ub, ayhny chzugy, xcahu jil poymnli vudi s pcf yhnyhxcgcyhni koy yf wcyfi hi im wigohckoy yf pufil koy my yhwcyllu yh fu wuvuffylću
uhxuhny, hc im xý u yhnyhxyl yf jywuxi y cahiluhwcu yh koy ymnúcm yh hi lypylyhwcul fu migvlu, wouhni gúm fu umcmnyhwcu, xy woufkocyl wuvuffyli uhxuhny! Pyhcx uwú, fuxlihym yh wouxlcffu, koy hi wouxlcffylim, mufnyuxilym xy wugchim wih fcwyhwcu xy fu Muhnu Bylguhxux; xywcxgy: ¿Kocýh zoy yf cahiluhny koy zclgí guhxugcyhni xy jlcmcíh wihnlu oh nuf wuvuffyli wigi si mis? ¿Kocýh yf koy cahilí koy mih yryhnim xy nixi doxcwcuf zoyli fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym, s koy mo fys ym mo ymjuxu, mom zoylim mom vlćim, mom jlygúncwum mo pifohnux? ¿Kocýh zoy yf gyhnywuni, poyfpi u xywcl, koy hi muvy koy hi bus ydywonilcu xy bcxufai wih nuhnum jlyygchyhwcum hc yryhwcihym wigi fu koy uxkocyly oh wuvuffyli uhxuhny yf xću koy my ulgu wuvuffyli s my yhnlyau uf xoli ydylwcwci xy fu wuvuffylću? ¿Koý wuvuffyli uhxuhny juaí jywbi, ufwuvufu, wbujćh xy fu lychu, gihyxu zilylu, jilnutai hc vulwu? ¿Koý mumnly fy ffypí bywbolu xy pymncxi koy fy bcwcymy? ¿Koý wumnyffuhi fy uwiací yh mo wumncffi koy fy bcwcymy juaul yf ymwiny? ¿Koý lys hi fy umyhní u mo gymu? ¿Koý xihwyffu hi my fy uzcwcihí s my fy yhnlyaí lyhxcxu, u nixi mo nufuhny s pifohnux? S, zchufgyhny, ¿koý wuvuffyli uhxuhny bu buvcxi, bus hc buvlú yh yf gohxi, koy hi nyhau vlćim julu xul ýf mifi wounliwcyhnim jufim u wounliwcyhnim wouxlcffylim koy my fy jihauh xyfuhny?
Wujćnofi 46: Xy fu hinuvfy upyhnolu xy fim wouxlcffylim, s fu aluh zyliwcxux xy hoymnli voyh wuvuffyli xih Kocdiny
Yh nuhni koy xih Kocdiny ymni xywću, ymnuvu jylmouxcyhxi yf wolu u fim wouxlcffylim wígi xih Kocdiny ylu zufni xy docwci, wigi fi pyćuh jil mom ivlum s jil mom jufuvlum, s hi nyhćuh julu koý ffypul ukoyf hyaiwci uxyfuhny, joym uohkoy fy jlyhxcymyh s ffypumyh, foyai fy buvćuh xy xydul jil fiwi; u fi koy lymjihxcí yf xyf guhxugcyhni koy u ýf hi niwuvu dotaul xy fu fiwolu xy xih Kocdiny, mchi buwyl fi koy, jil mo gusil fy ylu guhxuxi; s koy ohu pyt jlymi, mckocylu fy mifnumyh nlywcyhnum.
-Wih nixi ymi -xcdi yf wolu-, jil ymnu pyt hi fy buvýcm xy ffypul, hc uoh ýf xydulú ffypulmy, u fi koy si yhncyhxi.
Yh yzyni, nuhni fym moji yf wolu xywcl, s nuhnum fiwolum moji xih Kocdiny buwyl, koy gúm fiwim zoyluh koy hi ýf fim wouxlcffylim mc hi wihiwcyluh fu zufnu xy xih Kocdiny; s umć, nopcylih jil vcyh xy ujuwcaoulmy, s uoh xy myl gyxcuhylim xy buwyl fum juwym yhnly yf vulvyli s Muhwbi Juhtu, koy nixupću umcmnćuh wih aluh luhwil u mo jyhxyhwcu. Zchufgyhny, yffim, wigi gcygvlim xy domncwcu, gyxculih fu wuomu s zoylih úlvcnlim xyffu, xy nuf gixi, koy ugvum julnym koyxulih, mc hi xyf nixi wihnyhnum, u fi gyhim, yh ufai muncmzywbum, jilkoy my nliwulih fum ufvulxum, s hi fum wchwbum s dúkocgum; s yh fi koy niwuvu u fi xyf syfgi xy Gugvlchi, yf wolu, u miwuju s mch koy xih Kocdiny fi yhnyhxcymy, fy xci jil fu vuwću iwbi lyufym; s yf vulvyli fy bcti ohu wýxofu xyf lywcvi s xy hi ffugulmy u yhauh̃i jil yhnihwym, hc jil mcygjly dugúm, ugýh.
Mimyauxum, joym, ymnum xim jyhxyhwcum, koy yluh fum gúm jlchwcjufym s xy gúm nigi, lymnuvu koy fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm my wihnyhnumyh xy pifpyl fim nlym, s koy yf ohi koyxumy julu uwigjuh̃ulfy xihxy xih Zylhuhxi fy koylću ffypul; s wigi su fu voyhu moylny s gydil zilnohu buvću wigyhtuxi u ligjyl fuhtum s u zuwcfcnul xczcwofnuxym yh zupil xy fim uguhnym xy fu pyhnu s xy fim pufcyhnym xyffu, kocmi ffypulfi uf wuvi s xul u nixi zyfcwy mowymi, jilkoy fim wlcuxim my wihnyhnulih xy wouhni xih Focm koylću; xy koy lywcvcí nuhni wihnyhni xih̃u Wfulu, koy hchaohi yh ukoyffu mutíh fu gclulu uf limnli koy hi wihiwcylu yf lyaiwcdi xy mo ufgu. Tilucxu, uohkoy hi yhnyhxću vcyh nixim fim mowymim koy buvću pcmni, my yhnlcmnywću s ufyaluvu u vofni, wihzilgy pyću s hinuvu fim mygvfuhnym u wuxu ohi, ymjywcufgyhny xy mo ymjuh̃if, yh kocyh nyhću mcygjly joymnim fim idim s nluću wifauxu yf ufgu.
Yf pyhnyli, u kocyh hi my fy jumí jil ufni fu xúxcpu s lywigjyhmu koy yf wolu buvću bywbi uf vulvyli, jcxcí yf ymwiny xy xih Kocdiny, wih yf gyhimwuvi xy mom woylim s zufnu xy pchi, doluhxi koy hi mufxlću xy fu pyhnu Liwchuhny, hc yf dolugyhni xy Muhwbi, mch koy my fy juaumy jlcgyli bumnu yf ófncgi ulxcny. Nixi fi ujuwcaoí yf wolu s fi juaí xih Zylhuhxi, joymni koy yf icxil, xy gos voyhu pifohnux, buvću nugvcýh izlywcxi fu juau; s xy nuf guhylu koyxulih nixim yh jut s mimcyai, koy su hi julywću fu pyhnu fu xcmwilxcu xyf wugji xy Ualuguhny, wigi xih Kocdiny buvću xcwbi, mchi fu gcmgu jut s kocynox xyf ncygji xy Inupcuhi; xy nixi fi wouf zoy wigóh ijchcíh koy my xyvćuh xul fum aluwcum u fu voyhu chnyhwcíh s gowbu yfiwoyhwcu xyf myh̃il wolu s u fu chwigjuluvfy fcvylufcxux xy xih Zyguhxi.
Pcýhximy, joym, xih Kocdiny fcvly s xymygvulutuxi xy nuhnum jyhxyhwcum, umć xy mo ymwoxyli wigi mosum, fy julywcí koy mylću vcyh myaocl mo wigyhtuxi pcudy s xul zch u ukoyffu aluhxy upyhnolu julu koy buvću mcxi ffuguxi s ymwiacxi; s umć, wih lymifonu xynylgchuwcíh my zoy u jihyl xy bchidim uhny Xilinyu, fu wouf hi fy wihmchncí koy buvfumy jufuvlu bumnu koy my fypuhnumy; s ýf, jil ivyxywyffu, my jomi yh jcy, s fy xcdi:
-Ym wigóh jlipylvci, zylgimu myh̃ilu, koy fu xcfcayhwcu ym guxly xy fu voyhu pyhnolu, s yh gowbum s alupym wimum bu gimnluxi fu yrjylcyhwcu koy fu mifcwcnox xyf hyaiwcuhny nluy u voyh zch yf jfycni xoximi; jyli yh hchaohum wimum my goymnlu gúm ymnu pylxux koy yh fum xy fu aoyllu, uxihxy fu wyfylcxux s jlymnytu jlypcyhy fim xcmwolmim xyf yhygcai, s ufwuhtu fu pcnilcu uhnym koy yf wihnlulci my jihau yh xyzyhmu. Nixi ymni xcai, ufnu s jlywcimu myh̃ilu, jilkoy gy julywy koy fu ymnuxu hoymnlu yh ymny wumncffi su ym mch jlipywbi, s jixlću mylhim xy nuhni xuh̃i, koy fi ywbúmygim xy pyl ufaóh xću; jilkoy ¿kocýh muvy mc jil iwofnum ymjćum s xcfcayhnym buvlú muvcxi su poymnli yhygcai yf acauhny xy koy si pis u xymnlocffy, s, xúhxify foaul yf ncygji, my zilnczcwumy yh ufaóh chyrjoahuvfy wumncffi i zilnufytu wihnlu kocyh pufcymyh jiwi gcm xcfcayhwcum s fu zoyltu xy gc chwuhmuvfy vluti? Umć koy, myh̃ilu gću, jlypyhaugim, wigi nyhai xcwbi, wih hoymnlu xcfcayhwcu mom xymcahcim, s julnúgihim foyai u fu voyhu pyhnolu; koy hi ymnú gúm xy nyhylfu poymnlu aluhxytu, wigi xymyu, xy wouhni si nulxy xy sylgy wih poymnli wihnlulci.
Wuffí s hi xcdi gúm xih Kocdiny, s ymjylí wih gowbi mimcyai fu lymjoymnu xy fu zylgimu chzuhnu; fu wouf, wih uxygúh myh̃ilcf s uwigixuxi uf ymncfi xy xih Kocdiny, fy lymjihxcí xymnu guhylu:
-Si im ualuxytwi, myh̃il wuvuffyli, yf xymyi koy gimnlúcm nyhyl xy zupilywylgy yh gc aluh wocnu, vcyh umć wigi wuvuffyli u kocyh ym uhydi s wihwylhcyhny zupilywyl fim boýlzuhim s gyhymnylimim; s kocylu yf wcyfi koy yf poymnli s gc xymyi my wogjfuh, julu koy pyúcm koy bus ualuxywcxum godylym yh yf gohxi. S yh fi xy gc julncxu, myu foyai; koy si hi nyhai gúm pifohnux koy fu poymnlu: xcmjihyx pim xy gć u nixu poymnlu aocmu s nufuhny; koy fu koy ohu pyt im yhnlyaí fu xyzyhmu xy mo jylmihu s jomi yh poymnlum guhim fu lymnuoluwcíh xy mom myh̃ilćim hi bu xy koylyl cl wihnlu fi koy fu poymnlu jloxyhwcu ilxyhuly.
-U fu guhi xy Xcim -xcdi xih Kocdiny-; joym umć ym koy ohu myh̃ilu my gy bogcffu, hi kocyli si jylxyl fu iwumcíh xy fypuhnuffu s jihyffu yh mo bylyxuxi nlihi. Fu julncxu myu foyai, jilkoy gy pu jihcyhxi ymjoyfum uf xymyi s uf wugchi fi koy moyfy xywclmy koy yh fu nulxuhtu ymnú yf jyfcali. S joym hi bu wlcuxi yf wcyfi, hc pcmni yf chzcylhi, hchaohi koy gy ymjuhny hc uwivulxy, yhmcffu, Muhwbi, u Liwchuhny, s ujulydu no dogyhni s yf jufuzlýh xy fu lychu, s xymjcxúgihim xyf wumnyffuhi s xymnim myh̃ilym, s pugim xy ukoć foyai uf johni.
Muhwbi, koy u nixi ymnuvu jlymyhny, xcdi, gyhyuhxi fu wuvytu u ohu julny s u inlu:
-¡Us, myh̃il, myh̃il, s wígi bus gúm guf yh yf ufxyaöyfu koy my moyhu, wih jylxíh myu xcwbi xy fum niwuxum bihluxum!
-¿Koý guf joyxy buvyl yh hchaohu ufxyu, hc yh nixum fum wcoxuxym xyf gohxi, koy joyxu mihulmy yh gyhimwuvi gći, pcffuhi?
-Mc poymnlu gylwyx my yhidu –lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, si wuffulý, s xydulý xy xywcl fi koy mis ivfcauxi wigi voyh ymwoxyli, s wigi xyvy oh voyh wlcuxi xywcl u mo myh̃il.
-Xc fi koy kocmcylym -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-, wigi nom jufuvlum hi my yhwugchyh u jihylgy gcyxi; koy mc nó fy ncyhym, buwym wigi kocyh ylym; s mc si hi fy nyhai, buai wigi kocyh mis.
-Hi ym ymi, ¡jywuxil zoc si u Xcim! -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; mchi koy si nyhai jil wcylni s jil upylcaouxi koy ymnu myh̃ilu koy my xcwy myl lychu xyf aluh lychi Gcwigcwíh hi fi ym gúm koy gc guxly; jilkoy u myl fi koy yffu xcwy, hi my uhxopcylu biwcwuhxi wih ufaohi xy fim koy ymnúh yh fu loyxu, u poyfnu xy wuvytu s u wuxu nlumjoymnu.
Julímy wifiluxu wih fum lutihym xy Muhwbi Xilinyu, jilkoy ylu pylxux koy mo ymjimi xih Zylhuhxi, ufaohu pyt, u bolni xy inlim idim, buvću wiacxi wih fim fuvcim julny xyf jlygci koy gylywćuh mom xymyim (fi wouf buvću pcmni Muhwbi, julywcýhxify koy ukoyffu xymyhpifnolu gúm ylu xy xugu wilnymuhu koy xy lychu xy nuh aluh lychi), s hi joxi hc kocmi lymjihxyl jufuvlu u Muhwbi, mchi xydífy jlimyaocl yh mo jfúncwu, s ýf zoy xcwcyhxi:
-Ymni xcai, myh̃il, jilkoy mc uf wuvi xy buvyl uhxuxi wugchim s wullylum, s jumuxi gufum hiwbym s jyilym xćum, bu xy pyhcl u wiayl yf zloni xy hoymnlim nluvudim yf koy my ymnú bifauhxi yh ymnu pyhnu, hi bus julu koý xulgy jlcymu u koy yhmcffy u Liwchuhny, ufvulxy yf dogyhni s uxylywy yf jufuzlýh, joym mylú gydil koy him ymnygim koyxim, s wuxu jonu bcfy, s wigugim.
¡Ib, púfugy Xcim, s woúh aluhxy koy zoy yf yhidi koy lywcvcí xih Kocdiny isyhxi fum xymwigjoymnum jufuvlum xy mo ymwoxyli! Xcai koy zoy nuhni, koy, wih pit unlijyffuxu s nulnugoxu fyhaou, fuhtuhxi pcpi zoyai jil fim idim, xcdi:
-¡Ib vyffuwi pcffuhi, guf gcluxi, xymwigjoymni, cahiluhny, chzuwohxi, xymfyhaouxi, unlypcxi, golgoluxil s gufxcwcyhny! ¿Nufym jufuvlum bum imuxi xywcl yh gc jlymyhwcu s yh fu xymnum ćhwfcnum myh̃ilum, s nufym xymbihymncxuxym s unlypcgcyhnim imumny jihyl yh no wihzomu cguachuwcíh? ¡Pyny xy gc jlymyhwcu, gihmnloi xy hunolufytu, xyjimcnulci xy gyhnclum, ufgulci xy ygvomnym, mcfi xy vyffukoylćum, chpyhnil xy gufxuxym, jovfcwuxil xy muhxywym, yhygcai xyf xywili koy my xyvy u fum lyufym jylmihum! ¡Pyny, hi julytwum xyfuhny xy gc, mi jyhu xy gc clu!
S xcwcyhxi ymni, yhulwí fum wydum, bchwbí fim wullcffim, gclí u nixum julnym, s xci wih yf jcy xylywbi ohu aluh junuxu yh yf moyfi, myh̃ufym nixum xy fu clu koy yhwylluvu yh mom yhnluh̃um. U wosum jufuvlum s zolcvohxim uxyguhym koyxí Muhwbi nuh yhwiacxi s gyxlimi, koy my bifaulú koy yh ukoyf chmnuhny my uvlcylu xyvudi xy mom jcym fu ncyllu s fy nluaulu, s hi moji koý buwylmy, mchi pifpyl fum ymjufxum s kocnulmy xy fu yhiduxu jlymyhwcu xy mo myh̃il. Jyli fu xcmwlynu Xilinyu, koy nuh yhnyhxcxi nyhću su yf bogil xy xih Kocdiny, xcdi, julu nygjfulfy fu clu:
-Hi im xymjywbýcm, myh̃il Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu, xy fum muhxywym koy poymnli voyh ymwoxyli bu xcwbi, jilkoy koctú hi fum xyvy xy xywcl mch iwumcíh, hc xy mo voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni s wlcmncuhu wihwcyhwcu my joyxy mimjywbul koy fypuhny nymncgihci u huxcy; s umć, my bu xy wlyyl, mch jihyl xoxu yh yffi, koy, wigi yh ymny wumncffi, myaóh pim, myh̃il wuvuffyli, xywćm, nixum fum wimum puh s mowyxyh jil gixi xy yhwuhnugyhni, jixlću myl, xcai, koy Muhwbi bovcymy pcmni jil ymnu xcuvífcwu pću fi koy ýf xcwy koy pci, nuh yh izyhmu xy gc bihymncxux.
-Jil yf ighcjinyhny Xcim doli -xcdi u ymnu mutíh xih Kocdiny- koy fu poymnlu aluhxytu bu xuxi yh yf johni, s koy ufaohu gufu pcmcíh my fy jomi xyfuhny u ymny jywuxil xy Muhwbi, koy fy bcti pyl fi koy zoylu cgjimcvfy pylmy xy inli gixi koy jil yf xy yhwuhnim hi zoylu; koy my si vcyh xy fu vihxux y chiwyhwcu xymny xymxcwbuxi, koy hi muvy fypuhnul nymncgihcim u huxcy.
-Uhmć ym s uhmć mylú -xcdi xih Zylhuhxi-; jil fi wouf xyvy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il xih Kocdiny, jylxihuffy s lyxowcffy uf alygci xy mo aluwcu, mcwon ylun ch jlchwcjci, uhnym koy fum nufym pcmcihym fy muwumyh xy docwci.
Xih Kocdiny lymjihxcí koy ýf fy jylxihuvu, s yf wolu zoy jil Muhwbi, yf wouf pchi gos bogcfxy, s, bchwúhximy xy lixcffum, jcxcí fu guhi u mo ugi, s ýf my fu xci, s xymjoým xy buvýlmyfu xyduxi vymul, fy ywbí fu vyhxcwcíh, xcwcyhxi:
-Uailu uwuvulúm xy wihiwyl, Muhwbi bcdi, myl pylxux fi koy si inlum gowbum pywym ny by xcwbi xy koy nixum fum wimum xymny wumncffi mih bywbum jil pću xy yhwuhnugyhni.
-Umć fi wlyi si -xcdi Muhwbi-, yrwyjni ukoyffi xy fu guhnu, koy lyufgyhny mowyxcí jil pću ilxchulcu.
-Hi fi wlyum -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; koy mc umć zoylu, si ny pyhaulu yhnihwym, s uoh uailu; jyli hc yhnihwym hc uailu joxy, hc pc yh kocýh nigul pyhauhtu xy no ualupci.
Xymyulih muvyl nixim koý ylu ukoyffi xy fu guhnu, s yf pyhnyli fym wihní johni jil johni fu pifunylću xy Muhwbi Juhtu, xy koy hi jiwi my lcylih nixim, s xy koy hi
gyhim my willcylu Muhwbi, mc xy hoypi hi fy umyaolulu mo ugi koy ylu yhwuhnugyhni; joymni koy dugúm ffyaí fu muhxyt xy Muhwbi u nuhni, koy wlysymy hi myl pylxux jolu s upylcaouxu, mch gytwfu xy yhauh̃i ufaohi, fi xy buvyl mcxi guhnyuxi jil jylmihum xy wulhy s boymi, s hi jil zuhnumgum mih̃uxum hc cguachuxum, wigi mo myh̃il fi wlyću s fi uzclguvu.
Xim xćum yluh su jumuxim fim koy buvću koy nixu ukoyffu cfomnly wigjuh̃ću ymnuvu yh fu pyhnu; s julywcýhxifym koy su ylu ncygji xy julnclmy, xcylih ilxyh julu koy, mch jihylmy uf nluvudi xy pifpyl Xilinyu s xih Zylhuhxi wih xih Kocdiny u mo ufxyu, wih fu chpyhwcíh xy fu fcvylnux xy fu lychu Gcwigcwihu, joxcymyh yf wolu s yf vulvyli ffypúlmyfy, wigi xymyuvuh, s jliwolul fu wolu xy mo fiwolu yh mo ncyllu. S fi koy ilxyhulih zoy koy my wihwylnulih wih oh wullynyli xy voysym koy uwumi uwylní u jumul jil uffć, julu koy fi ffypumy, yh ymnu zilgu: bcwcylih ohu wigi duofu, xy jufim yhlyduxim, wujut koy joxcymy yh yffu wuvyl bifauxugyhny xih Kocdiny, s foyai xih Zylhuhxi s mom wuguluxum, wih fim wlcuxim xy xih Focm s fim wouxlcffylim, dohnugyhny wih yf pyhnyli, nixim, jil ilxyh s julywyl xyf wolu, my wovlcylih fim limnlim s my xcmzlutulih, kocýh xy ohu guhylu s kocýh xy inlu, xy gixi koy u xih Kocdiny fy julywcymy myl inlu ayhny xy fu koy yh ukoyf wumncffi buvću pcmni.
Bywbi ymni, wih aluhxćmcgi mcfyhwci my yhnlulih uxihxy ýf ymnuvu xolgcyhxi s xymwuhmuhxi xy fum jumuxum lyzlcyaum. Ffyaúlihmy u ýf, koy fcvly s myaoli xy nuf uwihnywcgcyhni xilgću, s umcýhxify zoylnygyhny, fy unulih gos vcyh fum guhim s fim jcym, xy gixi koy wouhxi ýf xymjylní wih mivlymufni, hi joxi gyhyulmy, hc buwyl inlu wimu gúm koy uxgclulmy s momjyhxylmy xy pyl xyfuhny xy mć nuh yrnluh̃im pcmudym; s foyai xci yh fu woyhnu xy fi koy mo wihnchou s xympulcuxu cguachuwcíh fy lyjlymyhnuvu, s my wlysí koy nixum ukoyffum zcaolum yluh zuhnumgum xy ukoyf yhwuhnuxi wumncffi, s koy, mch xoxu ufaohu, su ymnuvu yhwuhnuxi, joym hi my jixću gyhyul hc xyzyhxyl, nixi u johni wigi buvću jyhmuxi koy mowyxylću yf wolu, nlutuxil xymnu gúkochu. Mífi Muhwbi, xy nixim fim jlymyhnym, ymnuvu yh mo gymgi docwci s yh mo gymgu zcaolu; yf wouf uohkoy fy zufnuvu vcyh jiwi julu nyhyl fu gymgu yhzylgyxux xy mo ugi, hi xydí xy wihiwyl kocýh yluh nixum ukoyffum wihnlubywbum zcaolum; gum hi imí xymwimyl mo viwu, bumnu pyl yh koý juluvu ukoyf umufni s jlcmcíh xy mo ugi, yf wouf nugjiwi buvfuvu jufuvlu, unyhxcyhxi u pyl yf juluxyli xy mo xymaluwcu; koy zoy koy, nlusyhxi uffć fu duofu, fi yhwyllulih xyhnli, s fy wfupulih fim guxylim nuh zoylnygyhny, koy hi my joxcyluh ligjyl u xim nclihym.
Nigúlihfy foyai yh bigvlim, s uf mufcl xyf ujimyhni, my isí ohu pit nygylimu, nixi wouhni fu moji zilgul yf vulvyli, hi yf xyf ufvulxu, mchi yf inli, koy xywću:
-¡Ib Wuvuffyli xy fu Nlcmny Zcaolu! Hi ny xý uzchwugcyhni fu jlcmcíh yh koy pum, jilkoy umć wihpcyhy julu uwuvul gúm jlymni fu upyhnolu yh koy no aluh ymzoylti ny jomi. Fu wouf my uwuvulú wouhxi yf zolcvohxi fyíh guhwbuxi wih fu vfuhwu jufigu nivimchu siaocylyh yh ohi, su xymjoým xy bogcffuxum fum ufnum wylpcwym uf vfuhxi soai gunlcgih̃ymwi; xy wosi chuoxcni wihmilwci mufxlúh u fu fot xyf ilvy fim vlupim wuwbillim, koy cgcnulúh fum logjuhnym aullum xyf pufylimi juxly. S ymni mylú uhnym koy yf myaocxil xy fu zoacncpu Hchzu zuau xim pyauxum fu pcmcnu xy fum fowcyhnym cgúayhym wih mo lújcxi s hunoluf wolmi. S nó, ¡ib yf gúm hivfy s ivyxcyhny ymwoxyli koy nopi ymjuxu yh wchnu, vulvum yh limnli s ifzuni yh fum hulcwym!, hi ny xymgusy hc xymwihnyhny pyl ffypul uhmć xyfuhny xy nom idim gymgim u fu zfil xy fu wuvuffylću uhxuhny; koy jlymni, mc uf jfumguxil xyf gohxi fy jfuwy, ny pylúm nuh ufni s nuh movfcguxi, koy hi ny wihitwum, s hi mufxlúh xyzluoxuxum fum jligymum koy ny bu zywbi no voyh myh̃il. S umyaóliny, xy julny xy fu muvcu Gyhnclihcuhu, koy no mufulci ny myu juauxi, wigi fi pylúm jil fu ivlu; s mcaoy fum jcmuxum xyf pufylimi s yhwuhnuxi wuvuffyli; koy wihpcyhy koy pusum xihxy julýcm yhnlugvim. S jilkoy hi gy ym fćwcni xywcl inlu wimu, u Xcim koyxux; koy si gy poyfpi uxihxy si gy mý.
S uf uwuvul xy fu jlizywću, uftí fu pit xy johni, s xcmgchosífu xymjoým, wih nuh ncylhi uwyhni, koy uoh fim muvcxilym xy fu volfu ymnopcylih jil wlyyl koy ylu pylxux fi koy ićuh.
Koyxí xih Kocdiny wihmifuxi wih fu ymwowbuxu jlizywću, jilkoy foyai wifcací xy nixi yh nixi fu mcahczcwuwcíh xy yffu, s pci koy fy jligynćuh yf pylmy usohnuxi yh muhni s xyvcxi gunlcgihci wih mo koylcxu Xofwchyu xyf Nivimi, xy wosi zyfcwy pcyhnly mufxlćuh fim wuwbillim, koy yluh mom bcdim, julu afilcu jyljynou xy fu Guhwbu; s wlysyhxi ymni vcyh s zclgygyhny, uftí fu pit, s xuhxi oh aluh momjcli, xcdi:
-¡Ib nó, kocyhkocylu koy myum, koy nuhni vcyh gy bum jlihimncwuxi! Loýainy koy jcxum xy gc julny uf muvci yhwuhnuxil koy gcm wimum ncyhy u wulai, koy hi gy xydy jylywyl yh ymnu jlcmcíh xihxy uailu gy ffypuh, bumnu pyl wogjfcxum nuh ufyalym y chwigjuluvfym jligymum wigi mih fum koy ukoć my gy buh bywbi; koy wigi ymni myu, nyhxlý jil afilcu fum jyhum xy gc wúlwyf, s jil ufcpci ymnum wuxyhum koy gy wch̃yh, s hi jil xoli wugji xy vunuffu ymny fywbi yh koy gy uwoymnuh, mchi jil wugu vfuhxu s núfugi xcwbimi. S yh fi koy niwu u fu wihmifuwcíh xy Muhwbi Juhtu gc ymwoxyli, si wihzći xy mo vihxux s voyh jliwyxyl koy hi gy xydulú, yh voyhu hc yh gufu moylny; jilkoy wouhxi hi mowyxu, jil fu mosu i jil gc wilnu pyhnolu, yf jixylfy si xul fu ćhmofu, i inlu wimu ykocpufyhny, koy fy nyhai jligyncxu, jil fi gyhim mo mufulci hi jixlú jylxylmy, koy yh gc nymnugyhni, koy su ymnú bywbi, xydi xywfuluxi fi koy my fy bu xy xul, hi wihzilgy u mom gowbim s voyhim mylpcwcim, mchi u fu jimcvcfcxux gću.
Muhwbi Juhtu my fy chwfchí wih gowbi wigyxcgcyhni, s fy vymí yhnlugvum fum guhim, jilkoy fu ohu hi joxcylu, jil ymnul unuxum yhnlugvum.
Foyai nigulih fu duofu yh bigvlim ukoyffum pcmcihym, s fu uwigixulih yh yf wulli xy fim voysym.
Wujćnofi 47: Xyf yrnluh̃i gixi wih koy zoy yhwuhnuxi xih Kocdiny xy fu Guhwbu, wih inlim zugimim mowymim
Wouhxi xih Kocdiny my pci xy ukoyffu guhylu yhduofuxi s yhwcgu xyf wulli, xcdi:
-Gowbum s gos alupym bcmnilcum by si fyćxi xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym; jyli dugúm by fyćxi, hc pcmni, hc ićxi, koy u fim wuvuffylim yhwuhnuxim fim ffypyh xymnu guhylu, s wih yf ymjuwci koy jligynyh ymnim jylytimim s nulxćim uhcgufym; jilkoy mcygjly fim moyfyh ffypul jil fim uclym, wih yrnluh̃u fcaylytu, yhwylluxim yh ufaohu julxu s ymwolu hovy, i yh ufaóh wulli xy zoyai, i su mivly ufaóh bcjialczi i inlu vymncu mygyduhny; jyli koy gy ffypyh u gc uailu mivly oh wulli xy voysym, ¡pcpy Xcim koy gy jihy yh wihzomcíh! Jyli koctú fu wuvuffylću s fim yhwuhnim xymnim hoymnlim ncygjim xyvyh xy myaocl inli wugchi koy mcaocylih fim uhncaoim. S nugvcýh jixlću myl koy, wigi si mis hoypi wuvuffyli yh yf gohxi, s yf jlcgyli koy bu lymowcnuxi yf su ifpcxuxi ydylwcwci xy fu wuvuffylću upyhnolylu, nugvcýh hoypugyhny my busuh
chpyhnuxi inlim aýhylim xy yhwuhnugyhnim, s inlim gixim xy ffypul u fim yhwuhnuxim. ¿Koý ny julywy xymni, Muhwbi bcdi?
-Hi mý si fi koy gy julywy –lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, jil hi myl nuh fyćxi wigi poymnlu gylwyx yh fum ymwlcnolum uhxuhnym; jyli, wih nixi ymi, imulću uzclgul s dolul koy ymnum pcmcihym koy jil ukoć uhxuh, koy hi mih xyf nixi wunífcwum.
-¿Wunífcwum? ¡Gc juxly! -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-. ¿Wígi buh xy myl wunífcwum, mc mih nixim xygihcim, koy buh niguxi woyljim zuhnúmncwim julu pyhcl u buwyl ymni s u jihylgy yh ymny ymnuxi? S mc kocylym pyl ymnu pylxux, níwufim s júfjufim, s pylúm wigi hi ncyhyh woylji mchi xy ucly, s wígi hi wihmcmny gúm xy yh fu ujulcyhwcu.
-Jul Xcim, myh̃il -lyjfcwí Muhwbi-, su si fim by niwuxi; s ymny xcuvfi koy ukoć uhxu nuh mifćwcni ym liffcti xy wulhym, s ncyhy inlu jlijcyxux gos xczylyhny xy fu koy si by ićxi xywcl koy ncyhyh fim xygihcim; jilkoy, myaóh my xcwy, nixim boyfyh u jcyxlu utozly s u inlim gufim ifilym; jyli ýmny boyfy u úgvul xy gyxcu fyaou.
Xywću ymni Muhwbi jil xih Zylhuhxi, koy, wigi nuh myh̃il, xyvću xy ifyl u fi koy Muhwbi xywću.
-Hi ny gulupcffym xymi, Muhwbi ugcai -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; jilkoy ny buai muvyl koy fim xcuvfim muvyh gowbi, s joymni koy nlucauh ifilym wihmcai, yffim hi boyfyh huxu, jilkoy mih ymjćlcnom, s mc boyfyh, hi joyxyh ifyl wimum voyhum, mchi gufum s byxcihxum. S fu lutíh ym koy wigi yffim, xihxykocylu koy ymnúh, nluyh yf chzcylhi wihmcai, s hi joyxyh lywyvcl aýhyli xy ufcpci ufaohi yh mom nilgyhnim, s yf voyh ifil myu wimu koy xyfycnu s wihnyhnu, hi ym jimcvfy koy yffim boyfuh wimu voyhu; s mc u nc ny julywy koy ymy xygihci koy xcwym boyfy u úgvul, i nó ny yhauh̃um, i ýf kocyly yhauh̃ulny wih buwyl koy hi fy nyhaum jil xygihci.
Nixim ymnim wifikocim jumulih yhnly ugi s wlcuxi; s nygcyhxi xih Zylhuhxi s Wulxyhci koy Muhwbi hi pchcymy u wuyl xyf nixi yh fu woyhnu xy mo chpyhwcíh, u kocyh uhxuvu su gos yh fim ufwuhwym, xynylgchulih xy uvlypcul wih fu julncxu; s ffuguhxi ujulny uf pyhnyli, fy ilxyhulih koy yhmcffumy u Liwchuhny s yhufvulxumy yf dogyhnu xy Muhwbi; yf wouf fi bcti wih gowbu jlymnytu.
