nixum fum wigyxcum uhnym koy my lyjlymyhnumyh; hi mífi ukoyffum koy my bcwcymyh yh fu Wilny, mchi nixum fum koy my kocmcymyh lyjlymyhnul yh Ymjuh̃u; mch fu wouf ujlivuwcíh, myffi s zclgu hchaohu domncwcu yh mo foaul xydumy lyjlymyhnul wigyxcu ufaohu; s xymnu guhylu, fim wigyxcuhnym nyhxlćuh wocxuxi xy yhpcul fum wigyxcum u fu Wilny, s wih myaolcxux jixlćuh lyjlyhmyhnuffum, s ukoyffim koy fum wigjihyh gclulćuh wih gúm wocxuxi s ymnoxci fi koy buwćuh, nygylimim xy buvyl xy jumul mom ivlum jil yf lcaolimi yrugyh xy kocyh fi yhncyhxy; s xymnu guhylu my bulćuh voyhum wigyxcum s my wihmyaoclću zuwcfćmcgugyhny fi koy yh yffum my jlynyhxy; umć yf yhnlynyhcgcyhni xyf joyvfi wigi fu ijchcíh xy fim chayhcim xy Ymjuh̃u, yf chnylým s myaolcxux xy fim lywcnuhnym, s yf ubilli xyf wocxuxi xy wumncauffim. S mc my xcymy wulai u inli, i u ymny gcmgi, koy yrugchumy fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum koy xy hoypi my wigjomcymyh, mch xoxu jixlćuh mufcl ufaohim wih fu jylzywwcíh koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi, yhlckoywcyhxi hoymnlu fyhaou xyf ualuxuvfy s jlywcimi nymili xy fu yfiwoyhwcu, xuhxi iwumcíh koy fim fcvlim pcydim my ymwolywcymyh u fu fot xy fim hoypim koy mufcymyh, julu bihymni jumuncygji, hi mifugyhny xy fim iwcimim, mchi xy fim gúm iwojuxim, joym hi ym jimcvfy koy ymný wihnchoi yf ulwi ulguxi, hc fu wihxcwcíh s zfukoytu boguhu my joyxu momnyhnul mch ufaohu fćwcnu lywlyuwcíh.
U ymny johni xy mo wifikoci ffyauvuh yf wuhíhcai s yf wolu, wouhxi uxyfuhnúhximy yf vulvyli, ffyaí u yffim, s xcdi uf wolu:
-Ukoć, myh̃il fcwyhwcuxi, ym yf foaul koy si xcdy koy ylu voyhi julu koy, mymnyuhxi himinlim, nopcymyh fim voysym zlymwi s uvohximi jumni.
-Umć gy fi julywy u gc -lymjihxcí yf wolu.
S xcwcyhxi uf wuhíhcai fi koy jyhmuvu buwyl, ýf nugvcýh kocmi koyxulmy wih yffim, wihpcxuxi xyf mcnci xy oh bylgimi puffy koy u fu pcmnu my fym izlywću. S umć jil aitul xýf wigi xy fu wihpylmuwcíh xyf wolu, xy kocyh su cvu uzcwcihuxi, s jil muvyl gúm jil gyhoxi fum butuh̃um xy xih Kocdiny, guhxí u ufaohim xy mom wlcuxim koy my zoymyh u fu pyhnu koy hi fydim xy uffć ymnuvu, s nlodymyh xyffu fi koy bovcymy xy wigyl, julu nixim, jilkoy ýf xynylgchuvu xy mymnyul yh ukoyf foaul ukoyffu nulxy; u fi wouf ohi xy mom wlcuxim lymjihxcí koy yf uwýgcfu xyf lyjoymni, koy su xyvću xy ymnul yh fu pyhnu, nluću lywuxi vumnuhny julu hi ivfcaul u nigul xy fu pyhnu gúm koy wyvuxu.
-Joym umć ym -xcdi yf wuhíhcai-, ffýpyhmy uffú nixum fum wuvufauxolum, s buwyx pifpyl fu uwýgcfu.
Yh nuhni koy ymni jumuvu, pcyhxi Muhwbi koy jixću buvful u mo ugi mch fu wihnchou umcmnyhwcu xyf wolu s yf vulvyli, koy nyhću jil mimjywbimim, my ffyaí u fu duofu xihxy cvu mo ugi, s fy xcdi:
-Myh̃il, julu xymwulai xy gc wihwcyhwcu fy kocyli xywcl fi koy jumu wylwu xy mo yhwuhnugyhni; s ym koy ukoymnim xim koy pcyhyh ukoć wovcylnim fim limnlim mih yf wolu xy hoymnli foaul s yf vulvyli; s cguachi buh xuxi ymnu nlutu xy ffypuffy xymnu guhylu, xy jolu yhpcxcu koy ncyhyh, wigi poymnlu gylwyx my fym uxyfuhnu yh buwyl zugimim bywbim. Jlymojoymnu, joym, ymnu pylxux, mćaoymy koy hi pu yhwuhnuxi, mchi ygvućxi s nihni. Julu jloyvu xy fi wouf fy kocyli jlyaohnul ohu wimu; s mc gy lymjihxy wigi wlyi koy gy bu xy lymjihxyl, niwulú wih fu guhi ymny yhauh̃i s pylú wigi hi pu yhwuhnuxi, mchi nlumnilhuxi yf docwci.
-Jlyaohnu fi koy kocmcylym, bcdi Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; koy si ny muncmzulý s lymjihxylý u nixu no pifohnux. S yh fi koy xcwym koy ukoyffim koy uffć puh s pcyhyh wih himinlim mih yf wolu s yf vulvyli, hoymnlim wigjunlcinum s wihiwcxim, vcyh jixlú myl koy julytwu koy mih yffim gymgim; jyli koy fi myuh lyufgyhny s yh
yzyni, ymi hi fi wlyum yh hchaohu guhylu. Fi koy bum xy wlyyl s yhnyhxyl ym koy mc yffim my fym julywyh, wigi xcwym, xyvy xy myl koy fim koy gy buh yhwuhnuxi buvlúh niguxi ymu ujulcyhwcu s mygyduhtu; jilkoy ym zúwcf u fim yhwuhnuxilym nigul fu zcaolu koy my fym uhnidu, s buvlúh niguxi fum xymnim hoymnlim ugcaim, julu xulny u nc iwumcíh xy koy jcyhmym fi koy jcyhmum s jihylny yh oh fuvylchni xy cguachuwcihym, koy hi uwcylnym u mufcl xýf, uohkoy nopcymym fu miau xy Nymyi. S nugvcýh fi buvlúh bywbi julu koy si puwcfy yh gc yhnyhxcgcyhni, s hi myju unchul xy xíhxy gy pcyhy ymny xuh̃i; jilkoy mc, jil ohu julny, nó gy xcwym koy gy uwigjuh̃uh yf vulvyli s yf wolu xy hoymnli joyvfi, s, jil inlu, si gy pyi yhduofuxi, s mý xy gc koy zoyltum boguhum, wigi hi zoyluh mivlyhunolufym, hi zoyluh vumnuhnym julu yhduofulgy, ¿koý kocylym koy xcau i jcyhmy mchi koy fu guhylu xy gc yhwuhnugyhni yrwyxy u wouhnum si by fyćxi yh nixum fum bcmnilcum koy nlunuh xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym koy buh mcxi yhwuhnuxim? Uhmć koy vcyh joyxym xulny jut s mimcyai yh ymni xy wlyyl koy mih fim koy xcwym, jilkoy umć mih yffim wigi si mis nolwi. S yh fi koy niwu u koylyl jlyaohnulgy ufai, xc, koy si ny lymjihxylý, uohkoy gy jlyaohnym xy ukoć u guh̃uhu.
-¡Púfugy Hoymnlu Myh̃ilu! –lymjihxcí Muhwbi xuhxi ohu aluh pit-. S ¿ym jimcvfy koy myu poymnlu gylwyx nuh xoli xy wyfyvli s nuh zufni xy gyiffi, koy hi ywby xy pyl koy ym jolu pylxux fu koy fy xcai, s koy yh ymnu mo jlcmcíh s xymaluwcu ncyhy gúm julny fu gufcwcu koy yf yhwuhni? Jyli, joym umć ym, si fy kocyli jlivul ypcxyhnygyhny wígi hi pu yhwuhnuxi. Mc hi, xćaugy, umć Xcim fy mukoy xymnu nilgyhnu. s umć my pyu yh fim vlutim xy gc myh̃ilu Xofwchyu wouhxi gyhim my jcyhmy...
-Uwuvu xy wihdolulgy -xcdi xih Kocdiny-, s jlyaohnu fi koy kocmcylym; koy su ny by xcwbi koy ny lymjihxylý wih nixu johnoufcxux.
-Ymi jcxi -lyjfcwí Muhwbi--; s fi koy kocyli muvyl ym koy gy xcau, mch uh̃uxcl hc kocnul wimu hchaohu, mchi wih nixu pylxux, wigi my ymjylu koy fu buh xy xywcl s fu xcwyh nixim ukoyffim koy jlizymuh fum ulgum, wigi poymnlu gylwyx fum jlizymu, xyvudi xy nćnofi xy wuvuffylim uhxuhnym...
-Xcai koy hi gyhncl ¿yh wimu ufaohu -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-. Uwuvu su xy jlyaohnul; koy yh pylxux koy gy wuhmum wih nuhnum mufpum, jfyaulcum s jlypyhwcihym, Muhwbi.
-Xcai koy si ymnis myaoli xy fu vihxux s pylxux xy gc ugi; s umć, jilkoy buwy uf wumi u hoymnli woyhni, jlyaohni, buvfuhxi wih uwunugcyhni, mc uwumi xymjoým koy poymnlu gylwyx pu yhduofuxi s, u mo julywyl, yhwuhnuxi yh ymnu duofu, fy bu pyhcxi auhu s pifohnux xy buwyl uaoum gusilym i gyhilym, wigi moyfy xywclmy.
-Hi yhncyhxi ymi xy buwyl uaoum, Muhwbi; uwfúluny gúm, mc kocylym koy ny lymjihxu xylywbugyhny.
-¿Ym jimcvfy koy hi yhncyhxy poymnlu gylwyx xy buwyl uaoum gyhilym i gusilym? Joym yh fu ymwoyfu xymnynuh u fim gowbuwbim wih yffi. Joym myju koy kocyli xywcl mc fy bu pyhcxi auhu xy buwyl fi koy hi my yrwomu.
-¡Su, su ny yhncyhxi, Muhwbi! S gowbum pywym; s uoh uailu fu nyhai. ¡Múwugy xymny jyfcali, koy hi uhxu nixi fcgjci!
Wujćnofi 49: Xihxy my nlunu xyf xcmwlyni wifikoci koy Muhwbi Juhtu nopi wih mo myh̃il xih Kocdiny
-¡Ub! -xcdi Muhwbi-. Wiacxi fy nyhai: ymni ym fi koy si xymyuvu muvyl, wigi uf ufgu s wigi u fu pcxu. Pyhau uwú, myh̃il; ¿jixlću hyaul fi koy wigóhgyhny moyfy xywclmy jil ubć wouhxi ohu jylmihu ymnú xy gufu pifohnux: «Hi mý koý ncyhy zofuhi, koy hc wigy, hc vyvy, hc xoylgy, hc lymjihxy u jlijímcni u fi koy fy jlyaohnuh, koy hi julywy mchi koy ymnú yhwuhnuxi»? Xy xihxy my pcyhy u muwul, koy fim koy hi wigyh, hc vyvyh, hc xoylgyh, hc buwyh fum ivlum hunolufym koy si xcai, ymnim nufym ymnúh yhwuhnuxim; jyli hi ukoyffim koy ncyhyh fu auhu koy poymnlu gylwyx ncyhy, s koy vyvy wouhxi my fi xuh, s wigy wouhxi fi ncyhy, s lymjihxy u nixi ukoyffi koy fy jlyaohnuh.
-Pylxux xcwym, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; jyli su ny by xcwbi koy bus gowbum guhylum xy yhwuhnugyhnim, s jixlću myl koy wih yf ncygji my bovcymyh goxuxi xy ohim yh inlim, s koy uailu my omy koy fim yhwuhnuxim buauh nixi fi koy si buai, uohkoy uhnym hi fi buwćuh. Xy guhylu, koy wihnlu yf omi xy fim ncygjim hi bus koy ulaöcl hc xy koý buwyl wihmywoyhwcum. Si mý s nyhai julu gć koy pis yhwuhnuxi, s ymni gy vumnu julu fu myaolcxux xy gc wihwcyhwcu; koy fu zilgulću gos aluhxy mc si jyhmumy koy hi ymnuvu yhwuhnuxi s gy xydumy ymnul yh ymnu duofu jylytimi s wivulxy, xyzluoxuhxi yf miwilli koy jixlću xul u gowbim gyhymnylimim s hywymcnuxim koy xy gc usoxu s ugjuli xyvyh nyhyl u fu bilu xy ubilu jlywcmu s yrnlygu hywymcxux.
-Joym, wih nixi ymi -lyjfcwí Muhwbi-, xcai koy julu gusil uvohxuhwcu s muncmzuwcíh, mylću vcyh koy poymnlu gylwyx jlivumy u mufcl xymnu wúlwyf, koy si gy ivfcai wih nixi gc jixyl u zuwcfcnulfi, s uoh u muwulfy xyffu, s jlivumy xy hoypi u movcl mivly mo voyh Liwchuhny, koy nugvcýh julywy koy pu yhwuhnuxi, myaóh pu xy gyfuhwífcwi s nlcmny; s, bywbi ymni, jlivúmygim inlu pyt fu moylny xy vomwul gúm upyhnolum; s mc hi him mowyxcymy vcyh, ncygji him koyxu julu pifpygim u fu duofu, yh fu wouf jligyni, u fu fys xy voyh s fyuf ymwoxyli, xy yhwyllulgy dohnugyhny wih poymnlu gylwyx, mć uwumi zoyly poymnlu gylwyx nuh xymxcwbuxi, i si nuh mcgjfy, koy hi uwcylny u mufcl wih fi koy xcai.
-Si mis wihnyhni xy buwyl fi koy xcwym, Muhwbi bylguhi -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; s wouhxi nó pyum wisohnolu xy jihyl yh ivlu gc fcvylnux, si ny ivyxywylý yh nixi s jil nixi; jyli nó, Muhwbi, pylúm wígi ny yhauh̃um yh yf wihiwcgcyhni xy gc xymaluwcu.
Yh ymnum jfúncwum my yhnlynopcylih yf wuvuffyli uhxuhny s yf guf uhxuhny ymwoxyli, bumnu koy ffyaulih xihxy, su ujyuxim, fim uaoulxuvuh yf wolu, yf wuhíhcai s yf vulvyli. Xymohwcí foyai fim voysym xy fu wullynu yf visyli, s xydífim uhxul u mom uhwbolum jil ukoyf pylxy s ujuwcvfy mcnci, wosu zlymwolu wihpcxuvu u koylylfu aitul, hi u fum jylmihum nuh yhwuhnuxum wigi xih Kocdiny, mchi u fim nuh uxpylncxim s xcmwlynim wigi mo ymwoxyli; yf wouf liaí uf wolu koy jylgcncymy koy mo myh̃il mufcymy jil oh luni xy fu duofu, jilkoy mc hi fi xyduvuh mufcl, hi clću nuh fcgjcu ukoyffu jlcmcíh wigi lykoylću fu xywyhwcu xy oh nuf wuvuffyli wigi mo ugi. Yhnyhxcífy yf wolu, s xcdi koy xy gos voyhu auhu bulću fi koy fy jyxću, mc hi nygcylu koy yh pcýhximy mo myh̃il yh fcvylnux buvću xy buwyl xy fum mosum, s clmy xihxy dugúm ayhnym fy pcymyh.
-Si fy zći xy fu zoau -lymjihxcí Muhwbi.
-S si s nixi -xcdi yf wuhíhcai-, s gúm mc ýf gy xu fu jufuvlu wigi wuvuffyli xy hi ujulnulmy xy himinlim bumnu koy myu hoymnlu pifohnux.
-Mc xis -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny, koy nixi fi ymnuvu ymwowbuhxi-; wouhni gúm koy yf koy ymnú yhwuhnuxi, wigi si, hi ncyhy fcvylnux julu buwyl xy mo jylmihu fi koy kocmcyly, jilkoy yf koy fy yhwuhní fy joyxy buwyl koy hi my goypu xy oh foaul yh nlym mcafim; s mc bovcyly bocxi, fy bulú pifpyl yh pifuhxum. -S koy, joym ymni ylu umć, vcyh jixćuh mifnuffy, s gúm mcyhxi nuh yh jlipywbi xy nixim; s xyf hi mifnuffy fym jlinymnuvu koy hi jixću xydul xy zuncauffym yf ifzuni, mc xy uffć hi my xympcuvuh.
Nigífy fu guhi yf wuhíhcai, uohkoy fum nyhću unuxum, s xyvudi xy mo voyhu zy s jufuvlu, fy xymyhduofulih, xy koy ýf my ufyalí chzchcni s yh aluhxy guhylu xy pylmy zoylu xy fu duofu; s fi jlcgyli koy bcti zoy ymnclulmy nixi yf woylji, s foyai my zoy xihxy ymnuvu Liwchuhny s xúhxify xim jufguxum yh fum uhwum, xcdi:
-Uóh ymjyli yh Xcim s yh mo vyhxcnu Guxly, zfil s ymjydi xy fim wuvuffim, koy jlymni him bygim xy pyl fim xim wouf xymyugim; nó, wih no myh̃il u woymnum; s si, yhwcgu xy nc, ydylwcnuhxi yf izcwci julu koy Xcim gy ywbí uf gohxi.
S xcwcyhxi ymni xih Kocdiny, my ujulní wih Muhwbi yh lyginu julny, xy xihxy pchi gúm ufcpcuxi, s wih gúm xymyim xy jihyl yh ivlu fi koy mo ymwoxyli ilxyhumy.
Gclúvufi yf wuhíhcai, s uxgclúvumy xy pyl fu yrnluh̃ytu xy mo aluhxy fiwolu, s xy koy yh wouhni buvfuvu s lymjihxću gimnluvu nyhyl vihćmcgi yhnyhxcgcyhni; mifugyhny pyhcu u jylxyl fim ymnlcvim, wigi inlum pywym my bu xcwbi, yh nlunúhxify xy wuvuffylću. S umć, gipcxi xy wigjumcíh, xymjoým xy buvylmy myhnuxi nixim yh fu pylxy sylvu julu ymjylul yf lyjoymni xyf wuhíhcai, fy xcdi:
-¿Ym jimcvfy, myh̃il bcxufai, koy busu jixcxi nuhni wih poymnlu gylwyx fu ugulau s iwcimu fynolu xy fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum, koy fy busuh poyfni yf docwci xy gixi koy pyhau u wlyyl koy pu yhwuhnuxi, wih inlum wimum xymny duyt, nuh fydim xy myl pylxuxylum wigi fi ymnú fu gymgu gyhnclu xy fu pylxux? S ¿wígi ym jimcvfy koy busu yhnyhxcgcyhni boguhi koy my xý u yhnyhxyl koy bu buvcxi yh yf gohxi ukoyffu chzchcxux xy Uguxcmym, s ukoyffu nolvugofnu xy nuhni zugimi wuvuffyli, nuhni ygjyluxil xy Nlujcmihxu, nuhni Zyfcrgulny xy Bclwuhcu, nuhni jufuzlýh, nuhnu xihwyffu uhxuhny, nuhnum mcyljym, nuhnim yhxlcuaim, nuhnim acauhnym, nuhnum chuoxcnum upyhnolum, nuhni aýhyli xy yhwuhnugyhnim, nuhnum vunuffum, nuhnim xymuziluxim yhwoyhnlim, nuhnu vctullću xy nludym, nuhnum jlchwymum yhugiluxum, nuhnim ymwoxylim wihxym, nuhnim yhuhim aluwcimim, nuhni vcffyny, nuhni lykocyvli, nuhnum godylym pufcyhnym, s, zchufgyhny, nuhnim s nuh xcmjulunuxim wumim wigi fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum wihncyhyh? Xy gć mý xywcl koy wouhxi fim fyi, yh nuhni koy hi jihai fu cguachuwcíh yh jyhmul koy mih nixim gyhnclu s fcpcuhxux, gy xuh ufaóh wihnyhni; jyli wouhxi wucai yh fu woyhnu xy fi koy mih, xis wih yf gydil xyffim yh fu julyx, s uoh xcylu wih ýf yh yf zoyai, mc wylwu i jlymyhny fy nopcylu, vcyh wigi u gylywyxilym xy nuf jyhu, jil myl zufmim s ygvomnylim, s zoylu xyf nluni koy jcxy fu wigóh hunolufytu, s wigi u chpyhnilym xy hoypum mywnum s xy hoypi gixi xy pcxu, s wigi u kocyh xu iwumcíh koy yf pofai cahiluhny pyhau u wlyyl s u nyhyl jil pylxuxylum nuhnum hywyxuxym wigi wihncyhyh. S uoh ncyhyh nuhni unlypcgcyhni, koy my unlypyh u nolvul fim chayhcim xy fim xcmwlynim s vcyh huwcxim bcxufaim, wigi my ywbu vcyh xy pyl jil fi koy wih poymnlu gylwyx buh bywbi, joym fy buh nlućxi u nýlgchim, koy myu ziltimi yhwyllulfy yh ohu duofu, s nluylfy mivly oh wulli xy voysym, wigi kocyh nluy i ffypu ufaóh fyíh i ufaóh ncaly xy foaul yh foaul, julu auhul wih ýf xyduhxi koy fy pyuh. ¡Yu, myh̃il xih Kocdiny, xoýfumy xy mć gcmgi, s lyxótaumy uf alygci xy fu xcmwlywcíh, s myju omul xy fu gowbu koy yf wcyfi zoy mylpcxi xy xulfy, ygjfyuhxi yf zyfcwćmcgi nufyhni xy mo chayhci yh inlu fynolu koy lyxohxy yh ujlipywbugcyhni xy mo wihwcyhwcu s yh uogyhni xy mo bihlu! S mc nixupću, ffypuxi xy mo hunoluf chwfchuwcíh, kocmcyly fyyl fcvlim xy butuh̃um s xy wuvuffylćum, fyu yh fu Muwlu Ymwlcnolu yf xy fim Doywym; koy uffć buffulú pylxuxym aluhxcimum s bywbim nuh pylxuxylim wigi pufcyhnym. Oh Pclcuni nopi Fomcnuhcu; oh Wýmul, Ligu; oh Uhćvuf, Wulnuai; oh Ufyduhxli, Alywcu; oh Wihxy Zylhúh Aihtúfyt, Wumncffu; oh Wcx, Pufyhwcu; oh Aihtufi Zylhúhxyt, Uhxufowću; oh Xcyai Aulwću xy Julyxym, Yrnlyguxolu; oh Aulwc Jýlyt xy Pulaum, Dylyt; oh Aulwcfumi, Nifyxi; oh xih Guhoyf xy Fyíh, Mypcffu, wosu fywcíh xy mom pufylimim bywbim joyxy yhnlynyhyl, yhmyh̃ul, xyfycnul s uxgclul u fim gúm ufnim chayhcim koy fim fysylyh. Ymnu mć mylú fynolu xcahu xyf voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni xy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il xih Kocdiny gći, xy fu wouf mufxlú yloxcni yh fu bcmnilcu, yhugiluxi xy fu pclnox, yhmyh̃uxi yh fu vihxux, gydiluxi yh fum wimnogvlym, pufcyhny mch nygylcxux, imuxi mch wivulxću, s nixi ymni, julu bihlu xy Xcim, jlipywbi mosi s zugu xy fu Guhwbu, xi, myaóh by muvcxi, nluy poymnlu gylwyx mo jlchwcjci s ilcayh.
Unyhnćmcgugyhny ymnopi xih Kocdiny ymwowbuhxi fum lutihym xyf wuhíhcai; s wouhxi pci koy su buvću joymni zch u yffum, xymjoým xy buvylfy ymnuxi oh voyh ymjuwci gcluhxi, fy xcdi:
-Julýwygy, myh̃il bcxufai, koy fu jfúncwu xy poymnlu gylwyx my bu yhwugchuxi u koylyl xulgy u yhnyhxyl koy hi bu buvcxi wuvuffylim uhxuhnym yh yf gohxi, s koy nixim fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum mih zufmim, gyhnclimim, xuh̃uxilym y chóncfym julu fu lyjóvfcwu, s koy si by bywbi guf yh fyylfim, s jyil yh wlyylfim, s gúm guf yh cgcnulfim, buvcýhxigy joymni u myaocl fu xolćmcgu jlizymcíh xy fu wuvuffylću uhxuhny, koy yffim yhmyh̃uh, hyaúhxigy koy hi bu buvcxi yh yf gohxi Uguxcmym, hc xy Auofu hc xy Alywcu, hc nixim fim inlim wuvuffylim xy koy fum ymwlcnolum ymnúh ffyhum.
-Nixi ym uf jcy xy fu fynlu wigi poymnlu gylwyx fi pu lyfunuhxi -xcdi u ymnu mutíh yf wuhíhcai.
U fi wouf lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny:
-Uh̃uxcí nugvcýh poymnlu gylwyx, xcwcyhxi koy gy buvćuh bywbi gowbi xuh̃i nufym fcvlim, joym gy buvćuh poyfni yf docwci s joýmnigy yh ohu duofu, s koy gy mylću gydil buwyl fu yhgcyhxu s goxul xy fynolu, fysyhxi inlim gúm pylxuxylim s koy gydil xyfycnuh s yhmyh̃uh.
-Umć ym -xcdi yf wuhíhcai.
-Joym si -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny- buffi jil gc woyhnu koy yf mch docwci s yf yhwuhnuxi ym poymnlu gylwyx, joym my bu joymni u xywcl nuhnum vfumzygcum wihnlu ohu wimu nuh lywyvcxu yh yf gohxi, s nyhcxu jil nuh pylxuxylu, koy yf koy fu hyaumy, wigi poymnlu gylwyx fu hcyau, gylywću fu gymgu jyhu koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy koy xu u fim fcvlim wouhxi fim fyy s fy yhzuxuh. Jilkoy koylyl xul u yhnyhxyl u huxcy koy Uguxćm hi zoy yh yf gohxi, hc nixim fim inlim wuvuffylim upyhnolylim xy koy ymnúh wifguxum fum bcmnilcum, mylú koylyl jylmouxcl koy yf mif hi ufogvlu, hc yf syfi yhzlću, hc fu ncyllu momnyhnu; jilkoy ¿koý chayhci joyxy buvyl yh yf gohxi koy joyxu jylmouxcl u inli koy hi zoy pylxux fi xy fu chzuhnu Zfilcjym s Aos xy Vilaih̃u, s fi xy Zcyluvlúm wih fu joyhny xy Guhncvfy, koy mowyxcí yh yf ncygji xy Wulfi Guahi, koy pini u nuf koy ym nuhnu pylxux wigi ym ubilu xy xću? S mc ym gyhnclu, nugvcýh fi xyvy xy myl koy hi bovi Býwnil, hc Ukocfym, hc fu aoyllu xy Nlisu, hc fim xiwy Julym xy Zluhwcu, hc yf lys Ulnóm xy Chaufunyllu, koy uhxu bumnu ubilu wihpylncxi yh woylpi, s fy ymjyluh yh mo lychi jil gigyhnim. S nugvcýh my unlypylúh u xywcl koy ym gyhnclimu fu bcmnilcu xy Aoulhi Gytkochi, s fu xy fu xyguhxu xyf Muhni Alcuf, s koy mih ujíwlczim fim ugilym xy xih Nlcmnúh s fu lychu Cmyi, wigi fim xy Achyvlu s Fuhtuliny, buvcyhxi jylmihum koy wumc my uwoylxuh xy buvyl pcmni u fu xoyh̃u Kochnuh̃ihu, koy zoy fu gydil ymwuhwcuxilu xy pchi koy nopi fu Aluh Vlynuh̃u. S ym ymni nuh uhmć, koy gy uwoylxi si koy gy xywću ohu gc uaöyfu xy julnym xy gc juxly, wouhxi pyću ufaohu xoyh̃u wih niwum lypylyhxum. «Ukoyffu, hcyni, my julywy u fu xoyh̃u Kochnuh̃ihu.» Xy xihxy ulaosi si koy fu xyvcí xy wihiwyl yffu, i, jil fi gyhim, xyvcí xy ufwuhtul u pyl ufaóh lynluni mosi. Joym ¿kocýh jixlú hyaul hi myl pylxuxylu fu bcmnilcu xy Jcyllym s fu fchxu Guaufihu, joym uoh bumnu bis xću my pyy yh fu ulgylću xy fim Lysym fu wfupcdu wih koy pifpću uf wuvuffi xy guxylu mivly kocyh cvu yf pufcyhny Jcyllym jil fim uclym, koy ym oh jiwi gusil koy oh ncgíh xy wullynu? S dohni u fu wfupcdu ymnú fu mcffu xy Vuvcywu, s yh Lihwympuffym ymnú yf woylhi xy Lifxúh, nuguh̃i wigi ohu aluhxy pcau; xy xihxy my chzcyly koy bovi xiwy Julym, koy bovi Jcyllym, koy bovi Wcxym, s inlim wuvuffylim mygyduhnym,
xýmnim koy xcwyh fum ayhnym
koy u mom upyhnolum puh.
Mc hi, xćauhgy nugvcýh koy hi ym pylxux koy zoy wuvuffyli uhxuhny yf pufcyhny fomcnuhi Douh xy Gylfi, koy zoy u Vilaih̃u s my wigvuncí yh fu wcoxux xy Lum wih yf zugimi myh̃il xy Wbulhc, ffuguxi gimýh Jcyllym, s xymjoým, yh fu wcoxux xy Vumcfyu, wih gimýh Yhlckoy xy Lygymnúh, mufcyhxi xy yhnlugvum ygjlymum pyhwyxil s ffyhi xy bihlimu zugu; s fum upyhnolum s xymuzćim koy nugvcýh uwuvulih yh Vilaih̃u fim pufcyhnym ymjuh̃ifym Jyxli Vulvu s Aoncylly Kocduxu (xy wosu ufwolhcu si xywcyhxi jil fćhyu lywnu xy pulíh), pyhwcyhxi u fim bcdim xyf wihxy xy Muh Jifi. Hcýaoyhgy umcgymgi koy hi zoy u vomwul fum upyhnolum u Ufyguhcu xih Zylhuhxi xy Aoypulu, xihxy my wigvuncí wih Gcwyl Dilay, wuvuffyli xy fu wumu xyf xokoy xy Uomnlcu; xcauh koy zoylih volfu fum domnum xy Moyli xy Koch̃ihym, xyf Jumi; fum ygjlymum xy gimýh Focm xy Zufwym wihnlu xih Aihtufi xy Aotgúh, wuvuffyli wumnyffuhi, wih inlum gowbum butuh̃um bywbum jil wuvuffylim wlcmncuhim, xýmnim s xy fim lychim yrnluhdylim, nuh uonýhncwum s pylxuxylum, koy nilhi u xywcl koy yf koy fum hyaumy wulywylću xy nixu lutíh s voyh xcmwolmi.
Uxgcluxi koyxí yf wuhíhcai xy ićl fu gytwfu koy xih Kocdiny buwću xy pylxuxym s gyhnclum, s xy pyl fu hincwcu koy nyhću xy nixum ukoyffum wimum niwuhnym s wihwylhcyhnym u fim bywbim xy mo uhxuhny wuvuffylću, s umć fy lymjihxcí:
-Hi joyxi si hyaul, myh̃il xih Kocdiny, koy hi myu pylxux ufai xy fi koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi, ymjywcufgyhny yh fi koy niwu u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ymjuh̃ifym; s umcgymgi kocyli wihwyxyl koy bovi xiwy Julym xy Zluhwcu; jyli hi kocyli wlyyl koy bcwcylih nixum ukoyffum wimum koy yf ultivcmji Noljćh xyffim ymwlcvy; jilkoy fu pylxux xyffi ym koy zoylih wuvuffylim ymwiacxim jil fim lysym xy Zluhwcu, u kocyh ffugulih julym jil myl nixim caoufym yh pufil, yh wufcxux s yh pufyhnću; u fi gyhim, mc hi fi yluh, ylu lutíh koy fi zoymyh, s ylu wigi ohu lyfcacíh xy fum koy ubilu my omuh xy Muhncuai i xy Wufunlupu, koy my jlymojihy koy fim koy fu jlizymuh buh xy myl, i xyvyh myl, wuvuffylim pufylimim, pufcyhnym s vcyh huwcxim; s wigi ubilu xcwyh wuvuffyli xy Muh Douh, i xy Ufwúhnulu, xywćuh yh ukoyf ncygji wuvuffyli xy fim xiwy Julym, jilkoy zoylih xiwy caoufym fim koy julu ymnu lyfcacíh gcfcnul my ymwiacylih. Yh fi xy koy bovi Wcx hi bus xoxu, hc gyhim Vylhulxi xyf Wuljci; jyli xy koy bcwcylih fum butuh̃um koy xcwyh, wlyi koy fu bus gos aluhxy. Yh fi inli xy fu wfupcdu koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy xyf Wihxy Jcyllym, s koy ymnú dohni u fu mcffu xy Vuvcywu yh fu ulgylću xy fim Lysym, wihzcymi gc jywuxi; koy mis nuh cahiluhny, i nuh wilni xy pcmnu, koy, uohkoy by pcmni fu mcffu, hi by ywbuxi xy pyl fu wfupcdu, s gúm mcyhxi nuh aluhxy wigi poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi.
-Joym uffć ymnú, mch xoxu ufaohu –lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; s, jil gúm myh̃um, xcwyh koy ymnú gyncxu yh ohu zohxu xy pukoynu, jilkoy hi my nigy xy gibi.
-Nixi joyxy myl -lymjihxcí yf wuhíhcai-; jyli jil fum ílxyhym koy lywyvć koy hi gy uwoylxi buvylfu pcmni. Gum joymni koy wihwyxu koy ymnú uffć, hi jil ymi gy ivfcai u wlyyl fum bcmnilcum xy nuhnim Uguxcmym, hc fum xy nuhnu nolvugofnu xy wuvuffylim wigi jil ubć him woyhnuh, hc ym lutíh koy oh bigvly wigi poymnlu gylwyx, nuh bihluxi s xy nuh voyhum julnym, s xinuxi xy nuh voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni, my xý u yhnyhxyl koy mih pylxuxylum nuhnum s nuh yrnluh̃um fiwolum wigi fum koy ymnúh ymwlcnum yh fim xcmjulunuxim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum.
Wujćnofi 49: Xihxy my nlunu xyf xcmwlyni wifikoci koy Muhwbi Juhtu nopi wih mo myh̃il xih Kocdiny
-¡Ub! -xcdi Muhwbi-. Wiacxi fy nyhai: ymni ym fi koy si xymyuvu muvyl, wigi uf ufgu s wigi u fu pcxu. Pyhau uwú, myh̃il; ¿jixlću hyaul fi koy wigóhgyhny moyfy xywclmy jil ubć wouhxi ohu jylmihu ymnú xy gufu pifohnux: «Hi mý koý ncyhy zofuhi, koy hc wigy, hc vyvy, hc xoylgy, hc lymjihxy u jlijímcni u fi koy fy jlyaohnuh, koy hi julywy mchi koy ymnú yhwuhnuxi»? Xy xihxy my pcyhy u muwul, koy fim koy hi wigyh, hc vyvyh, hc xoylgyh, hc buwyh fum ivlum hunolufym koy si xcai, ymnim nufym ymnúh yhwuhnuxim; jyli hi ukoyffim koy ncyhyh fu auhu koy poymnlu gylwyx ncyhy, s koy vyvy wouhxi my fi xuh, s wigy wouhxi fi ncyhy, s lymjihxy u nixi ukoyffi koy fy jlyaohnuh.
-Pylxux xcwym, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-; jyli su ny by xcwbi koy bus gowbum guhylum xy yhwuhnugyhnim, s jixlću myl koy wih yf ncygji my bovcymyh goxuxi xy ohim yh inlim, s koy uailu my omy koy fim yhwuhnuxim buauh nixi fi koy si buai, uohkoy uhnym hi fi buwćuh. Xy guhylu, koy wihnlu yf omi xy fim ncygjim hi bus koy ulaöcl hc xy koý buwyl wihmywoyhwcum. Si mý s nyhai julu gć koy pis yhwuhnuxi, s ymni gy vumnu julu fu myaolcxux xy gc wihwcyhwcu; koy fu zilgulću gos aluhxy mc si jyhmumy koy hi ymnuvu yhwuhnuxi s gy xydumy ymnul yh ymnu duofu jylytimi s wivulxy, xyzluoxuhxi yf miwilli koy jixlću xul u gowbim gyhymnylimim s hywymcnuxim koy xy gc usoxu s ugjuli xyvyh nyhyl u fu bilu xy ubilu jlywcmu s yrnlygu hywymcxux.
-Joym, wih nixi ymi -lyjfcwí Muhwbi-, xcai koy julu gusil uvohxuhwcu s muncmzuwcíh, mylću vcyh koy poymnlu gylwyx jlivumy u mufcl xymnu wúlwyf, koy si gy ivfcai wih nixi gc jixyl u zuwcfcnulfi, s uoh u muwulfy xyffu, s jlivumy xy hoypi u movcl mivly mo voyh Liwchuhny, koy nugvcýh julywy koy pu yhwuhnuxi, myaóh pu xy gyfuhwífcwi s nlcmny; s, bywbi ymni, jlivúmygim inlu pyt fu moylny xy vomwul gúm upyhnolum; s mc hi him mowyxcymy vcyh, ncygji him koyxu julu pifpygim u fu duofu, yh fu wouf jligyni, u fu fys xy voyh s fyuf ymwoxyli, xy yhwyllulgy dohnugyhny wih poymnlu gylwyx, mć uwumi zoyly poymnlu gylwyx nuh xymxcwbuxi, i si nuh mcgjfy, koy hi uwcylny u mufcl wih fi koy xcai.
-Si mis wihnyhni xy buwyl fi koy xcwym, Muhwbi bylguhi -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; s wouhxi nó pyum wisohnolu xy jihyl yh ivlu gc fcvylnux, si ny ivyxywylý yh nixi s jil nixi; jyli nó, Muhwbi, pylúm wígi ny yhauh̃um yh yf wihiwcgcyhni xy gc xymaluwcu.
Yh ymnum jfúncwum my yhnlynopcylih yf wuvuffyli uhxuhny s yf guf uhxuhny ymwoxyli, bumnu koy ffyaulih xihxy, su ujyuxim, fim uaoulxuvuh yf wolu, yf wuhíhcai s yf vulvyli. Xymohwcí foyai fim voysym xy fu wullynu yf visyli, s xydífim uhxul u mom uhwbolum jil ukoyf pylxy s ujuwcvfy mcnci, wosu zlymwolu wihpcxuvu u koylylfu aitul, hi u fum jylmihum nuh yhwuhnuxum wigi xih Kocdiny, mchi u fim nuh uxpylncxim s xcmwlynim wigi mo ymwoxyli; yf wouf liaí uf wolu koy jylgcncymy koy mo myh̃il mufcymy jil oh luni xy fu duofu, jilkoy mc hi fi xyduvuh mufcl, hi clću nuh fcgjcu ukoyffu jlcmcíh wigi lykoylću fu xywyhwcu xy oh nuf wuvuffyli wigi mo ugi. Yhnyhxcífy yf wolu, s xcdi koy xy gos voyhu auhu bulću fi koy fy jyxću, mc hi nygcylu koy yh pcýhximy mo myh̃il yh fcvylnux buvću xy buwyl xy fum mosum, s clmy xihxy dugúm ayhnym fy pcymyh.
-Si fy zći xy fu zoau -lymjihxcí Muhwbi.
-S si s nixi -xcdi yf wuhíhcai-, s gúm mc ýf gy xu fu jufuvlu wigi wuvuffyli xy hi ujulnulmy xy himinlim bumnu koy myu hoymnlu pifohnux.
-Mc xis -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny, koy nixi fi ymnuvu ymwowbuhxi-; wouhni gúm koy yf koy ymnú yhwuhnuxi, wigi si, hi ncyhy fcvylnux julu buwyl xy mo jylmihu fi koy kocmcyly, jilkoy yf koy fy yhwuhní fy joyxy buwyl koy hi my goypu xy oh foaul yh nlym mcafim; s mc bovcyly bocxi, fy bulú pifpyl yh pifuhxum. -S koy, joym ymni ylu umć, vcyh jixćuh mifnuffy, s gúm mcyhxi nuh yh jlipywbi xy nixim; s xyf hi mifnuffy fym jlinymnuvu koy hi jixću xydul xy zuncauffym yf ifzuni, mc xy uffć hi my xympcuvuh.
Nigífy fu guhi yf wuhíhcai, uohkoy fum nyhću unuxum, s xyvudi xy mo voyhu zy s jufuvlu, fy xymyhduofulih, xy koy ýf my ufyalí chzchcni s yh aluhxy guhylu xy pylmy zoylu xy fu duofu; s fi jlcgyli koy bcti zoy ymnclulmy nixi yf woylji, s foyai my zoy xihxy ymnuvu Liwchuhny s xúhxify xim jufguxum yh fum uhwum, xcdi:
-Uóh ymjyli yh Xcim s yh mo vyhxcnu Guxly, zfil s ymjydi xy fim wuvuffim, koy jlymni him bygim xy pyl fim xim wouf xymyugim; nó, wih no myh̃il u woymnum; s si, yhwcgu xy nc, ydylwcnuhxi yf izcwci julu koy Xcim gy ywbí uf gohxi.
S xcwcyhxi ymni xih Kocdiny, my ujulní wih Muhwbi yh lyginu julny, xy xihxy pchi gúm ufcpcuxi, s wih gúm xymyim xy jihyl yh ivlu fi koy mo ymwoxyli ilxyhumy.
Gclúvufi yf wuhíhcai, s uxgclúvumy xy pyl fu yrnluh̃ytu xy mo aluhxy fiwolu, s xy koy yh wouhni buvfuvu s lymjihxću gimnluvu nyhyl vihćmcgi yhnyhxcgcyhni; mifugyhny pyhcu u jylxyl fim ymnlcvim, wigi inlum pywym my bu xcwbi, yh nlunúhxify xy wuvuffylću. S umć, gipcxi xy wigjumcíh, xymjoým xy buvylmy myhnuxi nixim yh fu pylxy sylvu julu ymjylul yf lyjoymni xyf wuhíhcai, fy xcdi:
-¿Ym jimcvfy, myh̃il bcxufai, koy busu jixcxi nuhni wih poymnlu gylwyx fu ugulau s iwcimu fynolu xy fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum, koy fy busuh poyfni yf docwci xy gixi koy pyhau u wlyyl koy pu yhwuhnuxi, wih inlum wimum xymny duyt, nuh fydim xy myl pylxuxylum wigi fi ymnú fu gymgu gyhnclu xy fu pylxux? S ¿wígi ym jimcvfy koy busu yhnyhxcgcyhni boguhi koy my xý u yhnyhxyl koy bu buvcxi yh yf gohxi ukoyffu chzchcxux xy Uguxcmym, s ukoyffu nolvugofnu xy nuhni zugimi wuvuffyli, nuhni ygjyluxil xy Nlujcmihxu, nuhni Zyfcrgulny xy Bclwuhcu, nuhni jufuzlýh, nuhnu xihwyffu uhxuhny, nuhnum mcyljym, nuhnim yhxlcuaim, nuhnim acauhnym, nuhnum chuoxcnum upyhnolum, nuhni aýhyli xy yhwuhnugyhnim, nuhnum vunuffum, nuhnim xymuziluxim yhwoyhnlim, nuhnu vctullću xy nludym, nuhnum jlchwymum yhugiluxum, nuhnim ymwoxylim wihxym, nuhnim yhuhim aluwcimim, nuhni vcffyny, nuhni lykocyvli, nuhnum godylym pufcyhnym, s, zchufgyhny, nuhnim s nuh xcmjulunuxim wumim wigi fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum wihncyhyh? Xy gć mý xywcl koy wouhxi fim fyi, yh nuhni koy hi jihai fu cguachuwcíh yh jyhmul koy mih nixim gyhnclu s fcpcuhxux, gy xuh ufaóh wihnyhni; jyli wouhxi wucai yh fu woyhnu xy fi koy mih, xis wih yf gydil xyffim yh fu julyx, s uoh xcylu wih ýf yh yf zoyai, mc wylwu i jlymyhny fy nopcylu, vcyh wigi u gylywyxilym xy nuf jyhu, jil myl zufmim s ygvomnylim, s zoylu xyf nluni koy jcxy fu wigóh hunolufytu, s wigi u chpyhnilym xy hoypum mywnum s xy hoypi gixi xy pcxu, s wigi u kocyh xu iwumcíh koy yf pofai cahiluhny pyhau u wlyyl s u nyhyl jil pylxuxylum nuhnum hywyxuxym wigi wihncyhyh. S uoh ncyhyh nuhni unlypcgcyhni, koy my unlypyh u nolvul fim chayhcim xy fim xcmwlynim s vcyh huwcxim bcxufaim, wigi my ywbu vcyh xy pyl jil fi koy wih poymnlu gylwyx buh bywbi, joym fy buh nlućxi u nýlgchim, koy myu ziltimi yhwyllulfy yh ohu duofu, s nluylfy mivly oh wulli xy voysym, wigi kocyh nluy i ffypu ufaóh fyíh i ufaóh ncaly xy foaul yh foaul, julu auhul wih ýf xyduhxi koy fy pyuh. ¡Yu, myh̃il xih Kocdiny, xoýfumy xy mć gcmgi, s lyxótaumy uf alygci xy fu xcmwlywcíh, s myju omul xy fu gowbu koy yf wcyfi zoy mylpcxi xy xulfy, ygjfyuhxi yf zyfcwćmcgi nufyhni xy mo chayhci yh inlu fynolu koy lyxohxy yh ujlipywbugcyhni xy mo wihwcyhwcu s yh uogyhni xy mo bihlu! S mc nixupću, ffypuxi xy mo hunoluf chwfchuwcíh, kocmcyly fyyl fcvlim xy butuh̃um s xy wuvuffylćum, fyu yh fu Muwlu Ymwlcnolu yf xy fim Doywym; koy uffć buffulú pylxuxym aluhxcimum s bywbim nuh pylxuxylim wigi pufcyhnym. Oh Pclcuni nopi Fomcnuhcu; oh Wýmul, Ligu; oh Uhćvuf, Wulnuai; oh Ufyduhxli, Alywcu; oh Wihxy Zylhúh Aihtúfyt, Wumncffu; oh Wcx, Pufyhwcu; oh Aihtufi Zylhúhxyt, Uhxufowću; oh Xcyai Aulwću xy Julyxym, Yrnlyguxolu; oh Aulwc Jýlyt xy Pulaum, Dylyt; oh Aulwcfumi, Nifyxi; oh xih Guhoyf xy Fyíh, Mypcffu, wosu fywcíh xy mom pufylimim bywbim joyxy yhnlynyhyl, yhmyh̃ul, xyfycnul s uxgclul u fim gúm ufnim chayhcim koy fim fysylyh. Ymnu mć mylú fynolu xcahu xyf voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni xy poymnlu gylwyx, myh̃il xih Kocdiny gći, xy fu wouf mufxlú yloxcni yh fu bcmnilcu, yhugiluxi xy fu pclnox, yhmyh̃uxi yh fu vihxux, gydiluxi yh fum wimnogvlym, pufcyhny mch nygylcxux, imuxi mch wivulxću, s nixi ymni, julu bihlu xy Xcim, jlipywbi mosi s zugu xy fu Guhwbu, xi, myaóh by muvcxi, nluy poymnlu gylwyx mo jlchwcjci s ilcayh.
Unyhnćmcgugyhny ymnopi xih Kocdiny ymwowbuhxi fum lutihym xyf wuhíhcai; s wouhxi pci koy su buvću joymni zch u yffum, xymjoým xy buvylfy ymnuxi oh voyh ymjuwci gcluhxi, fy xcdi:
-Julýwygy, myh̃il bcxufai, koy fu jfúncwu xy poymnlu gylwyx my bu yhwugchuxi u koylyl xulgy u yhnyhxyl koy hi bu buvcxi wuvuffylim uhxuhnym yh yf gohxi, s koy nixim fim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum mih zufmim, gyhnclimim, xuh̃uxilym y chóncfym julu fu lyjóvfcwu, s koy si by bywbi guf yh fyylfim, s jyil yh wlyylfim, s gúm guf yh cgcnulfim, buvcýhxigy joymni u myaocl fu xolćmcgu jlizymcíh xy fu wuvuffylću uhxuhny, koy yffim yhmyh̃uh, hyaúhxigy koy hi bu buvcxi yh yf gohxi Uguxcmym, hc xy Auofu hc xy Alywcu, hc nixim fim inlim wuvuffylim xy koy fum ymwlcnolum ymnúh ffyhum.
-Nixi ym uf jcy xy fu fynlu wigi poymnlu gylwyx fi pu lyfunuhxi -xcdi u ymnu mutíh yf wuhíhcai.
U fi wouf lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny:
-Uh̃uxcí nugvcýh poymnlu gylwyx, xcwcyhxi koy gy buvćuh bywbi gowbi xuh̃i nufym fcvlim, joym gy buvćuh poyfni yf docwci s joýmnigy yh ohu duofu, s koy gy mylću gydil buwyl fu yhgcyhxu s goxul xy fynolu, fysyhxi inlim gúm pylxuxylim s koy gydil xyfycnuh s yhmyh̃uh.
-Umć ym -xcdi yf wuhíhcai.
-Joym si -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny- buffi jil gc woyhnu koy yf mch docwci s yf yhwuhnuxi ym poymnlu gylwyx, joym my bu joymni u xywcl nuhnum vfumzygcum wihnlu ohu wimu nuh lywyvcxu yh yf gohxi, s nyhcxu jil nuh pylxuxylu, koy yf koy fu hyaumy, wigi poymnlu gylwyx fu hcyau, gylywću fu gymgu jyhu koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy koy xu u fim fcvlim wouhxi fim fyy s fy yhzuxuh. Jilkoy koylyl xul u yhnyhxyl u huxcy koy Uguxćm hi zoy yh yf gohxi, hc nixim fim inlim wuvuffylim upyhnolylim xy koy ymnúh wifguxum fum bcmnilcum, mylú koylyl jylmouxcl koy yf mif hi ufogvlu, hc yf syfi yhzlću, hc fu ncyllu momnyhnu; jilkoy ¿koý chayhci joyxy buvyl yh yf gohxi koy joyxu jylmouxcl u inli koy hi zoy pylxux fi xy fu chzuhnu Zfilcjym s Aos xy Vilaih̃u, s fi xy Zcyluvlúm wih fu joyhny xy Guhncvfy, koy mowyxcí yh yf ncygji xy Wulfi Guahi, koy pini u nuf koy ym nuhnu pylxux wigi ym ubilu xy xću? S mc ym gyhnclu, nugvcýh fi xyvy xy myl koy hi bovi Býwnil, hc Ukocfym, hc fu aoyllu xy Nlisu, hc fim xiwy Julym xy Zluhwcu, hc yf lys Ulnóm xy Chaufunyllu, koy uhxu bumnu ubilu wihpylncxi yh woylpi, s fy ymjyluh yh mo lychi jil gigyhnim. S nugvcýh my unlypylúh u xywcl koy ym gyhnclimu fu bcmnilcu xy Aoulhi Gytkochi, s fu xy fu xyguhxu xyf Muhni Alcuf, s koy mih ujíwlczim fim ugilym xy xih Nlcmnúh s fu lychu Cmyi, wigi fim xy Achyvlu s Fuhtuliny, buvcyhxi jylmihum koy wumc my uwoylxuh xy buvyl pcmni u fu xoyh̃u Kochnuh̃ihu, koy zoy fu gydil ymwuhwcuxilu xy pchi koy nopi fu Aluh Vlynuh̃u. S ym ymni nuh uhmć, koy gy uwoylxi si koy gy xywću ohu gc uaöyfu xy julnym xy gc juxly, wouhxi pyću ufaohu xoyh̃u wih niwum lypylyhxum. «Ukoyffu, hcyni, my julywy u fu xoyh̃u Kochnuh̃ihu.» Xy xihxy ulaosi si koy fu xyvcí xy wihiwyl yffu, i, jil fi gyhim, xyvcí xy ufwuhtul u pyl ufaóh lynluni mosi. Joym ¿kocýh jixlú hyaul hi myl pylxuxylu fu bcmnilcu xy Jcyllym s fu fchxu Guaufihu, joym uoh bumnu bis xću my pyy yh fu ulgylću xy fim Lysym fu wfupcdu wih koy pifpću uf wuvuffi xy guxylu mivly kocyh cvu yf pufcyhny Jcyllym jil fim uclym, koy ym oh jiwi gusil koy oh ncgíh xy wullynu? S dohni u fu wfupcdu ymnú fu mcffu xy Vuvcywu, s yh Lihwympuffym ymnú yf woylhi xy Lifxúh, nuguh̃i wigi ohu aluhxy pcau; xy xihxy my chzcyly koy bovi xiwy Julym, koy bovi Jcyllym, koy bovi Wcxym, s inlim wuvuffylim mygyduhnym,
xýmnim koy xcwyh fum ayhnym
koy u mom upyhnolum puh.
Mc hi, xćauhgy nugvcýh koy hi ym pylxux koy zoy wuvuffyli uhxuhny yf pufcyhny fomcnuhi Douh xy Gylfi, koy zoy u Vilaih̃u s my wigvuncí yh fu wcoxux xy Lum wih yf zugimi myh̃il xy Wbulhc, ffuguxi gimýh Jcyllym, s xymjoým, yh fu wcoxux xy Vumcfyu, wih gimýh Yhlckoy xy Lygymnúh, mufcyhxi xy yhnlugvum ygjlymum pyhwyxil s ffyhi xy bihlimu zugu; s fum upyhnolum s xymuzćim koy nugvcýh uwuvulih yh Vilaih̃u fim pufcyhnym ymjuh̃ifym Jyxli Vulvu s Aoncylly Kocduxu (xy wosu ufwolhcu si xywcyhxi jil fćhyu lywnu xy pulíh), pyhwcyhxi u fim bcdim xyf wihxy xy Muh Jifi. Hcýaoyhgy umcgymgi koy hi zoy u vomwul fum upyhnolum u Ufyguhcu xih Zylhuhxi xy Aoypulu, xihxy my wigvuncí wih Gcwyl Dilay, wuvuffyli xy fu wumu xyf xokoy xy Uomnlcu; xcauh koy zoylih volfu fum domnum xy Moyli xy Koch̃ihym, xyf Jumi; fum ygjlymum xy gimýh Focm xy Zufwym wihnlu xih Aihtufi xy Aotgúh, wuvuffyli wumnyffuhi, wih inlum gowbum butuh̃um bywbum jil wuvuffylim wlcmncuhim, xýmnim s xy fim lychim yrnluhdylim, nuh uonýhncwum s pylxuxylum, koy nilhi u xywcl koy yf koy fum hyaumy wulywylću xy nixu lutíh s voyh xcmwolmi.
Uxgcluxi koyxí yf wuhíhcai xy ićl fu gytwfu koy xih Kocdiny buwću xy pylxuxym s gyhnclum, s xy pyl fu hincwcu koy nyhću xy nixum ukoyffum wimum niwuhnym s wihwylhcyhnym u fim bywbim xy mo uhxuhny wuvuffylću, s umć fy lymjihxcí:
-Hi joyxi si hyaul, myh̃il xih Kocdiny, koy hi myu pylxux ufai xy fi koy poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi, ymjywcufgyhny yh fi koy niwu u fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym ymjuh̃ifym; s umcgymgi kocyli wihwyxyl koy bovi xiwy Julym xy Zluhwcu; jyli hi kocyli wlyyl koy bcwcylih nixum ukoyffum wimum koy yf ultivcmji Noljćh xyffim ymwlcvy; jilkoy fu pylxux xyffi ym koy zoylih wuvuffylim ymwiacxim jil fim lysym xy Zluhwcu, u kocyh ffugulih julym jil myl nixim caoufym yh pufil, yh wufcxux s yh pufyhnću; u fi gyhim, mc hi fi yluh, ylu lutíh koy fi zoymyh, s ylu wigi ohu lyfcacíh xy fum koy ubilu my omuh xy Muhncuai i xy Wufunlupu, koy my jlymojihy koy fim koy fu jlizymuh buh xy myl, i xyvyh myl, wuvuffylim pufylimim, pufcyhnym s vcyh huwcxim; s wigi ubilu xcwyh wuvuffyli xy Muh Douh, i xy Ufwúhnulu, xywćuh yh ukoyf ncygji wuvuffyli xy fim xiwy Julym, jilkoy zoylih xiwy caoufym fim koy julu ymnu lyfcacíh gcfcnul my ymwiacylih. Yh fi xy koy bovi Wcx hi bus xoxu, hc gyhim Vylhulxi xyf Wuljci; jyli xy koy bcwcylih fum butuh̃um koy xcwyh, wlyi koy fu bus gos aluhxy. Yh fi inli xy fu wfupcdu koy poymnlu gylwyx xcwy xyf Wihxy Jcyllym, s koy ymnú dohni u fu mcffu xy Vuvcywu yh fu ulgylću xy fim Lysym, wihzcymi gc jywuxi; koy mis nuh cahiluhny, i nuh wilni xy pcmnu, koy, uohkoy by pcmni fu mcffu, hi by ywbuxi xy pyl fu wfupcdu, s gúm mcyhxi nuh aluhxy wigi poymnlu gylwyx bu xcwbi.
-Joym uffć ymnú, mch xoxu ufaohu –lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-; s, jil gúm myh̃um, xcwyh koy ymnú gyncxu yh ohu zohxu xy pukoynu, jilkoy hi my nigy xy gibi.
-Nixi joyxy myl -lymjihxcí yf wuhíhcai-; jyli jil fum ílxyhym koy lywyvć koy hi gy uwoylxi buvylfu pcmni. Gum joymni koy wihwyxu koy ymnú uffć, hi jil ymi gy ivfcai u wlyyl fum bcmnilcum xy nuhnim Uguxcmym, hc fum xy nuhnu nolvugofnu xy wuvuffylim wigi jil ubć him woyhnuh, hc ym lutíh koy oh bigvly wigi poymnlu gylwyx, nuh bihluxi s xy nuh voyhum julnym, s xinuxi xy nuh voyh yhnyhxcgcyhni, my xý u yhnyhxyl koy mih pylxuxylum nuhnum s nuh yrnluh̃um fiwolum wigi fum koy ymnúh ymwlcnum yh fim xcmjulunuxim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum.
Wujćnofi 50: Xy fum xcmwlynum ufnylwuwcihym koy xih Kocdiny s yf wuhíhcai nopcylih, wih inlim mowymim
-¡Voyhi ymnú ymi! -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-. Fim fcvlim koy ymnúh cgjlymim wih fcwyhwcu xy fim lysym s wih ujlivuwcíh xy ukoyffim u kocyh my lygcncylih, s koy wih aomni ayhyluf mih fyćxim s wyfyvluxim xy fim aluhxym s xy fim wbcwim, xy fim jivlym s xy fim lcwim, xy fim fynluxim y cahiluhnym, xy fim jfyvysim s wuvuffylim, zchufgyhny, xy nixi aýhyli xy jylmihum xy woufkocyl ymnuxi s wihxcwcíh koy myuh, ¿buvćuh xy myl gyhnclu, s gúm ffypuhxi nuhnu ujulcyhwcu xy pylxux, joym him woyhnuh yf juxly, fu guxly, fu junlcu, fim julcyhnym, fu yxux, yf foaul s fum butuh̃um johni jil johni s xću jil xću, koy yf nuf wuvuffyli bcti, i wuvuffylim bcwcylih? Wuffy poymnlu gylwyx, hi xcau nuf vfumzygcu, s wlýugy koy fy uwihmydi yh ymni fi koy
xyvy xy buwyl wigi xcmwlyni, mc hi fýufim, s pylú yf aomni koy lywcvy xy mo fysyhxu. Mc hi, xćaugy: ¿bus gusil wihnyhni koy pyl, wigi mc xcdýmygim, ukoć ubilu my goymnlu xyfuhny xy himinlim oh aluh fuai xy jyt bclpcyhxi u vilviffihym, s koy uhxuh huxuhxi s wlotuhxi jil ýf gowbum mygcyhnym, wofyvlum s fuaulnim, s inlim gowbim aýhylim xy uhcgufym zyliwym s ymjuhnuvfym, s koy xyf gyxci xyf fuai mufy ohu pit nlcmnćmcgu koy xcwy: «Nó, wuvuffyli, kocyhkocylu koy myum, koy yf nygylimi fuai ymnúm gcluhxi, mc kocylym ufwuhtul yf vcyh koy xyvudi xymnum hyalum uaoum my yhwovly, goymnlu yf pufil xy no zoylny jywbi s ullíduny yh gcnux xy mo hyali s yhwyhxcxi fcwil; jilkoy mc umć hi fi buwym, hi mylúm xcahi xy pyl fum ufnum gulupcffum koy yh mć yhwcylluh s wihncyhyh fim mcyny wumncffim xy fum mcyny zuxum koy xyvudi xymnu hyalolu suwyh?» ¿S koy ujyhum yf wuvuffyli hi bu uwuvuxi xy ićl fu pit nygylimu, wouhxi, mch yhnlul gúm yh woyhnum wihmcai, mch jihylmy u wihmcxylul yf jyfcali u koy my jihy, s uoh mch xymjidulmy xy fu jymuxogvly xy mom zoylnym ulgum, yhwigyhxúhximy u Xcim s u mo myh̃ilu, my ullidu yh gcnux xyf voffyhny fuai, s wouhxi hi my wunu hc muvy xíhxy bu xy julul, my buffu yhnly ohim zfilcxim wugjim, wih kocyh fim Yfćmyim hi ncyhyh koy pyl yh hchaohu wimu?
