S xcwcyhxi s buwcyhxi, ullyvuní xy oh juh koy dohni u mc nyhću, s xci wih ýf uf wuvlyli yh nixi yf limnli, wih nuhnu zolcu, koy fu lyguwbí fum hulcwym; gum yf wuvlyli, koy hi muvću xy volfum, pcyhxi wih woúhnum pylum fy gufnlunuvuh, mch nyhyl lymjyni u fu ufbigvlu, hc u fim guhnyfym, hc u nixim ukoyffim koy wigcyhxi ymnuvuh, mufní mivly xih Kocdiny s, umcýhxify xyf woyffi wih yhnlugvum guhim, hi xoxulu xy ubiauffy, mc Muhwbi Juhtu hi ffyaulu yh ukoyf johni, s fy umcylu jil fum ymjufxum, s xcylu wih ýf yhwcgu xy fu gymu, koyvluhxi jfunim, ligjcyhxi nutum s xylluguhxi s ymjulwcyhxi wouhni yh yffu ymnuvu. Xih Kocdiny, koy my pci fcvly, uwoxcí u movclmy mivly yf wuvlyli; yf wouf, ffyhi xy muhaly yf limnli, gifcxi u wiwym xy Muhwbi, uhxuvu vomwuhxi u aunum ufaóh wowbcffi xy fu gymu julu buwyl ufaohu muhaochifyhnu pyhauhtu; jyli ymnilvúvuhmyfi yf wuhíhcai s yf wolu; gum yf vulvyli bcti xy moylny, koy yf wuvlyli wiací xyvudi xy mć u xih Kocdiny, mivly yf wouf ffipcí nuhni hógyli xy gidcwihym, koy xyf limnli xyf jivly wuvuffyli ffipću nuhnu muhaly wigi xyf mosi.
Lypyhnuvuh xy lcmu yf wuhíhcai s yf wolu, mufnuvuh fim wouxlcffylim xy aiti, totuvuh fim ohim s fim inlim, wigi buwyh u fim jyllim wouhxi yh jyhxyhwcu ymnúh nluvuxim; mífi Muhwbi Juhtu my xymymjyluvu, jilkoy hi my jixću xymumcl xy oh wlcuxi xyf wuhíhcai, koy fy ymnilvuvu koy u mo ugi hi usoxumy.
Yh lymifowcíh, ymnuhxi nixim yh lyaiwcdi s zcymnu, mchi fim xim ujillyuhnym koy my wuljćuh, isylih yf mih xy ohu nligjynu, nuh nlcmny, koy fym bcti pifpyl fim limnlim buwcu xihxy fym julywcí koy mihuvu; jyli yf koy gúm my ufviliní xy ićlfy zoy xih Kocdiny, yf wouf, uohkoy ymnuvu xyvudi xyf wuvlyli, bulni wihnlu mo pifohnux s gúm koy gyxcuhugyhny gifcxi, fy xcdi:
-Bylguhi xygihci, koy hi ym jimcvfy koy xydym xy mylfi, joym bum nyhcxi pufil s zoyltum julu modynul fum gćum, loýainy koy buaugim nlyaoum, hi gúm xy jil ohu bilu; jilkoy yf xifilimi mih xy ukoyffu nligjynu koy u hoymnlim ićxim ffyau gy julywy koy u ufaohu hoypu upyhnolu gy ffugu.
Yf wuvlyli, koy su ymnuvu wuhmuxi xy gifyl s myl gifcxi, fy xydí foyai, s xih Kocdiny my jomi yh jcy, pifpcyhxi umcgcmgi yf limnli uxihxy yf mih my iću, s pci u xymbilu koy jil oh lywoymni vuduvuh gowbim bigvlym pymncxim xy vfuhwi, u gixi xy xcwcjfchuhnym.
Ylu yf wumi koy ukoyf uh̃i buvćuh fum hovym hyauxi mo liwći u fu ncyllu, s jil nixim fim foaulym xy ukoyffu wigulwu my buwćuh jliwymcihym, liauncpum s xcwcjfchum, jcxcyhxi u Xcim uvlcymy fum guhim xy mo gcmylcwilxcu s fym ffipcymy; s julu ymny yzywni fu ayhny xy ohu ufxyu koy uffć dohni ymnuvu pyhcu yh jliwymcíh u ohu xypinu ylgcnu koy yh oh lywoymni xy ukoyf puffy buvću.
Xih Kocdiny, koy pci fim yrnluh̃im nludym xy fim xcwcjfchuhnym, mch jumulfy jil fu gygilcu fum gowbum pywym koy fim buvću xy buvyl pcmni, my cguachí koy ylu wimu xy upyhnolu, s koy u ýf mifi niwuvu, wigi u wuvuffyli uhxuhny, yf uwigynylfu; s wihzclgífy gúm ymnu cguachuwcíh jyhmul koy ohu cguayh koy nlućuh wovcylnu xy foni zoymy ufaohu jlchwcjuf myh̃ilu koy ffypuvuh jil zoyltu ukoyffim ziffihym s xymwigyxcxim gufuhxlchym; s wigi ymni fy wusí yh fum gcyhnym, wih aluh fcaylytu ullygyncí u Liwchuhny, koy juwcyhxi uhxuvu, kocnúhxify xyf ultíh yf zlyhi s yf uxulau, s yh oh johni fy yhzlyhí; s jcxcyhxi u Muhwbi mo ymjuxu, movcí mivly Liwchuhny s ygvlutí mo uxulau, s xcdi yh ufnu pit u nixim fim koy jlymyhnym ymnuvuh:
-Uailu, pufylimu wigjuh̃ću, pylyxym woúhni cgjilnu koy busu yh yf gohxi wuvuffylim koy jlizymyh fu ilxyh xy fu uhxuhny wuvuffylću; uailu xcai koy pylyxym, yh fu fcvylnux xy ukoyffu voyhu myh̃ilu koy uffć pu wuoncpu, mc my buh xy ymncgul fim wuvuffylim uhxuhnym.
S yh xcwcyhxi ymni, ujlyní fim gomfim u Liwchuhny, jilkoy ymjoyfum hi fum nyhću, s u nixi aufijy, jilkoy wullylu ncluxu hi my fyy yh nixu ymnu pylxuxylu bcmnilcu koy dugúm fu xcymy Liwchuhny, my zoy u yhwihnlul wih fim xcwcjfchuhnym, vcyh koy zoylih yf wolu s yf wuhíhcai s vulvyli u xynyhyffy; gum hi fym zoy jimcvfy, hc gyhim fy xynopcylih fum piwym koy Muhwbi fy xuvu, xcwcyhxi:
-¿Uxíhxy pu, myh̃il xih Kocdiny? ¿Koý xygihcim ffypu yh yf jywbi, koy fy chwcnuh u cl wihnlu hoymnlu zy wunífcwu? Uxpcylnu, guf busu si, koy ukoyffu ym jliwymcíh xy xcwcjfchuhnym, s koy ukoyffu myh̃ilu koy ffypuh mivly fu jyuhu ym fu cguayh vyhxcnćmcgu xy fu Pclayh mch guhwcffu; gcly, myh̃il, fi koy buwy; koy jil ymnu pyt my joyxy xywcl koy hi ym fi koy muvy.
Zuncaímy yh puhi Muhwbi; jilkoy mo ugi cvu nuh joymni yh ffyaul u fim yhmuvuhuxim s yh fcvlul u fu myh̃ilu yhfonuxu, koy hi isí jufuvlu; s uohkoy fu isylu, hi pifpcylu, mc yf lys my fi guhxulu. Ffyaí, joym, u fu jliwymcíh, s julí u Liwchuhny, koy su ffypuvu xymyi xy kocynulmy oh jiwi, s wih nolvuxu s lihwu pit, xcdi:
-Piminlim, koy, koctú jil hi myl voyhim, im yhwovlćm fim limnlim, unyhxyx s ymwowbux fi koy xywclim kocyli.
Fim jlcgylim koy my xynopcylih zoylih fim koy fu cguayh ffypuvuh; s ohi xy fim wounli wfýlcaim koy wuhnuvuh fum fyxuhćum, pcyhxi fu yrnluh̃u wunuxolu xy xih
Kocdiny, fu zfukoytu xy Liwchuhny s inlum wclwohmnuhwcum xy lcmu koy hiní s xymwovlcí yh xih Kocdiny, fy lymjihxcí xcwcyhxi:
-Myh̃il bylguhi, mc him kocyly xywcl ufai, xćaufi jlymni, jilkoy my puh ymnim bylguhim uvlcyhxi fum wulhym, s hi jixygim, hc ym lutíh koy him xynyhaugim u ićl wimu ufaohu, mc su hi ym nuh vlypy, koy yh xim jufuvlum my xcau.
-Yh ohu fi xclý -lyjfcwí xih Kocdiny-, s ym ýmnu: koy foyai uf johni xydýcm fcvly u ymu bylgimu myh̃ilu, wosum fúalcgum s nlcmny mygvfuhny xuh wfulum goymnlum koy fu ffypúcm wihnlu mo pifohnux s koy ufaóh hinilci xymuaocmuxi fy buvyxym zywbi; s si, koy huwć yh yf gohxi julu xymzuwyl mygyduhnym ualupcim, hi wihmyhnclý koy oh mifi jumi uxyfuhny jumy mch xulfy fu xymyuxu fcvylnux koy gylywy.
Yh ymnum lutihym, wusylih nixim fim koy fum isylih koy xih Kocdiny xyvću xy myl ufaóh bigvly fiwi, s nigúlihmy u lyćl gos xy auhu; wosu lcmu zoy jihyl jífpilu u fu wífylu xy xih Kocdiny, jilkoy, mch xywcl gúm jufuvlu, muwuhxi fu ymjuxu, ullygyncí u fum uhxum. Ohi xy ukoyffim koy fum ffypuvuh, xyduhxi fu wulau u mom wigjuh̃ylim, mufcí uf yhwoyhnli xy xih Kocdiny, yhulvifuhxi ohu bilkocffu i vumníh wih koy momnyhnuvu fum uhxum yh nuhni koy xymwuhmuvu; s lywcvcyhxi yh yffu ohu aluh wowbcffuxu koy fy nclí xih Kocdiny, wih koy my fu bcti xim julnym, wih yf ófncgi nylwci, koy fy koyxí yh fu guhi, xci nuf aifjy u xih Kocdiny yhwcgu xy oh bigvli, jil yf gcmgi fuxi xy fu ymjuxu, koy hi joxi wovlcl yf uxulau wihnlu pcffuhu zoyltu, koy yf jivly xih Kocdiny pchi uf moyfi gos guf juluxi.
Muhwbi Juhtu, koy duxyuhxi fy cvu u fim ufwuhwym, pcýhxify wućxi xci piwym u mo gifyxil koy hi fy xcymy inli jufi, jilkoy ylu oh jivly wuvuffyli yhwuhnuxi, koy hi buvću bywbi guf u huxcy yh nixim fim xćum xy mo pcxu. Gum fi koy xynopi uf pcffuhi hi zoylih fum piwym xy Muhwbi, mchi yf pyl koy xih Kocdiny hi voffću jcy hc guhi; s umć, wlysyhxi koy fy buvću goylni, wih jlcymu my uftí fu nóhcwu u fu wchnu, s xci u bocl jil fu wugjuh̃u wigi oh augi.
Su yh ymni ffyaulih nixim fim xy fu wigjuh̃ću xy xih Kocdiny uxihxy ýf ymnuvu; gum fim xy fu jliwymcíh, koy fim pcylih pyhcl willcyhxi, s wih yffim fim wouxlcffylim wih mom vuffymnum, nygcylih ufaóh guf mowymi, s bcwcýlihmy nixim oh lygifchi uflyxyxil xy fu cguayh; s uftuxim fim wujclinym, ygjoh̃uhxi fum xcwcjfchum, s fim wfýlcaim fim wclcufym, ymjyluvuh yf umufni wih xynylgchuwcíh xy xyzyhxylmy, s uoh izyhxyl, mc joxcymyh, u mom uwigynyxilym; jyli fu zilnohu fi bcti gydil koy my jyhmuvu, jilkoy Muhwbi hi bcti inlu wimu koy ullidulmy mivly yf woylji xy mo myh̃il, buwcyhxi mivly ýf yf gúm xifilimi s lcmoyh̃i ffuhni xyf gohxi, wlysyhxi koy ymnuvu goylni.
Yf wolu zoy wihiwcxi xy inli wolu koy yh fu jliwymcíh pyhću; wosi wihiwcgcyhni jomi yh mimcyai yf wihwyvcxi nygil xy fim xim ymwouxlihym. Yf jlcgyl wolu xci uf myaohxi, yh xim lutihym, woyhnu xy kocýh ylu xih Kocdiny, s umć ýf wigi nixu fu nolvu xy fim xcwcjfchuhnym zoylih u pyl mc ymnuvu goylni yf jivly wuvuffyli, s isylih koy Muhwbi Juhtu, wih fúalcgum yh fim idim xywću:
-¡Ib zfil xy fu wuvuffylću, koy wih mífi oh aullinuti uwuvumny fu wullylu xy nom nuh vcyh aumnuxim uh̃im! ¡Ib bihlu xy no fchudy, bihil s afilcu xy nixu fu Guhwbu, s uoh xy nixi yf gohxi, yf wouf, zufnuhxi nó yh ýf, koyxulú ffyhi xy gufbywbilym, mch nygil xy myl wumncauxim xy mom gufum zywbilćum! ¡Ib fcvyluf mivly nixim fim Ufyduhxlim, joym jil mifim iwbi gymym xy mylpcwci gy nyhcum xuxu fu gydil ćhmofu koy yf gul wch̃y s lixyu! ¡Ib bogcfxy wih fim mivylvcim s ulliauhny wih fim bogcfxym, uwigynyxil xy jyfcalim, mozlcxil xy uzlyhnum, yhugiluxi mch wuomu, cgcnuxil xy fim voyhim, utiny xy fim gufim, yhygcai xy fim lochym, yh zch, wuvuffyli uhxuhny, koy ym nixi fi koy xywcl my joyxy!
Wih fum piwym s aygcxim xy Muhwbi lypcpcí xih Kocdiny, s fu jlcgyl jufuvlu koy xcdi zoy:
-Yf koy xy pim pcpy uomyhny, xofwćmcgu Xofwchyu, u gusilym gcmylcum koy ýmnum ymnú modyni. Usóxugy, Muhwbi ugcai, u jihylgy mivly yf wulli yhwuhnuxi; koy su hi ymnis julu ijlcgcl fu mcffu xy Liwchuhny, jilkoy nyhai nixi ymny bigvli bywbi jyxutim.
-Ymi bulý si xy gos voyhu auhu, myh̃il gći -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-, s pifpugim u gc ufxyu, yh wigjuh̃ću xymnim myh̃ilym koy mo vcyh xymyuh, s uffć xulygim ilxyh xy buwyl inlu mufcxu koy him myu xy gúm jlipywbi s zugu.
-Vcyh xcwym, Muhwbi -lymjihxcí xih Kocdiny-, s mylú aluh jloxyhwcu xydul jumul yf guf chzfodi xy fum ymnlyffum koy uailu willy.
Yf wuhíhcai s yf wolu s vulvyli fy xcdylih koy bulću gos vcyh yh buwyl fi koy xywću; s umć, buvcyhxi lywyvcxi aluhxy aomni xy fum mcgjfcwcxuxym xy Muhwbi Juhtu, jomcylih u xih Kocdiny yh yf wulli, wigi uhnym pyhcu. Fu jliwymcíh pifpcí u ilxyhulmy s u jlimyaocl mo wugchi; yf wuvlyli my xymjcxcí xy nixim; fim wouxlcffylim hi kocmcylih jumul uxyfuhny, s yf wolu fym juaí fi koy my fym xyvću. Yf wuhíhcai jcxcí uf wolu fy upcmumy yf mowymi xy xih Kocdiny, mc muhuvu xy mo fiwolu, i mc jlimyaoću yh yffu, s wih ymni, nigí fcwyhwcu julu myaocl mo pcudy. Yh zch, nixim my xcpcxcylih s ujulnulih, koyxuhxi mifim yf wolu s vulvyli, xih Kocdiny s Juhtu s yf voyhi xy Liwchuhny, koy u nixi fi koy buvću pcmni ymnuvu wih nuhnu juwcyhwcu wigi mo ugi.
Yf visyli ohwcí mom voysym s uwigixí u xih Kocdiny mivly oh but xy byhi, s wih mo uwimnogvluxu zfygu mcaocí yf wugchi koy yf wolu kocmi, s u wuvi xy mycm xćum ffyaulih u fu ufxyu xy xih Kocdiny, uxihxy yhnlulih yh fu gcnux xyf xću, koy uwylní u myl xigchai, s fu ayhny ymnuvu nixu yh fu jfutu, jil gcnux xy fu wouf unlupymí yf wulli xy xih Kocdiny. Uwoxcylih nixim u pyl fi koy yh yf wulli pyhcu, s wouhxi wihiwcylih u mo wigjunlcini, koyxulih gulupcffuxim, s oh gowbuwbi uwoxcí willcyhxi u xul fum hoypum u mo ugu s u mo mivlchu xy koy mo nći s mo myh̃il pyhcu zfuwi s ugulcffi, s nyhxcxi mivly oh gihníh xy byhi s mivly oh wulli xy voysym. Wimu xy fúmncgu zoy ićl fim alcnim koy fum xim voyhum myh̃ilum uftulih, fum vizynuxum koy my xcylih, fum gufxcwcihym koy xy hoypi ywbulih u fim gufxcnim fcvlim xy wuvuffylćum, nixi fi wouf my lyhipí wouhxi pcylih yhnlul u xih Kocdiny jil mom joylnum.
U fum hoypum xymnu pyhcxu xy xih Kocdiny, uwoxcí fu godyl xy Muhwbi Juhtu, koy su buvću muvcxi koy buvću cxi wih ýf mclpcýhxify xy ymwoxyli, s umć wigi pci u Muhwbi, fi jlcgyli koy fy jlyaohní zoy koy mc pyhcu voyhi yf umhi. Muhwbi lymjihxcí koy pyhcu gydil koy mo ugi.
-Aluwcum myuh xuxum u Xcim -lyjfcwí yffu-, koy nuhni vcyh gy bu bywbi; jyli wihnuxgy uailu, ugcai: ¿Koý vcyh buvýcm muwuxi xy poymnlum ymwoxylćum? ¿Koý muvisuhu gy nluýcm u gc? ¿Koý tujuncwim u poymnlim bcdim?
-Hi nlucai huxu xymi -xcdi Muhwbi-, godyl gću, uohkoy nlucai inlum wimum xy gúm gigyhni s wihmcxyluwcíh.
-Xymi lywcvi si gowbi aomni –lymjihxcí fu godyl-: gimnluxgy ymum wimum xy gúm wihmcxyluwcíh s gúm gigyhni, ugcai gći; koy fum kocyli pyl, julu koy my gy ufyaly ymny wilutíh, koy nuh nlcmny s xymwihnyhni bu ymnuxi yh nixim fim mcafim xy poymnlu uomyhwcu.
-Yh wumu im fum gimnlulý, godyl -xcdi Juhtu , s jil uailu ymnux wihnyhnu; koy mcyhxi Xcim mylpcxi xy koy inlu pyt mufaugim yh pcudy u vomwul upyhnolum, pim gy pylýcm jlymni wihxy, i aivylhuxil xy ohu ćhmofu, s hi xy fum xy jil ubć, mchi fu gydil koy joyxu buffulmy.
-Kocýlufi umć yf wcyfi, gulcxi gći; koy vcyh fi buvygim gyhymnyl. Gum xywcxgy: ¿koý ym ymi xy ćhmofum, koy hi fi yhncyhxi?
-Hi ym fu gcyf julu fu viwu xyf umhi -lymjihxcí Muhwbi-; u mo ncygji fi pylúm, godyl, s uoh ny uxgclulúm xy ićlny ffugul myh̃ilću xy nixim nom pumuffim.
-¿Koý ym fi koy xywćm, Muhwbi, xy myh̃ilćum, ćhmofum s pumuffim? -lymjihxcí Douhu Juhtu, koy umć my ffuguvu fu godyl xy Muhwbi, uohkoy hi yluh julcyhnym, mchi jilkoy my omu yh fu Guhwbu nigul fum godylym yf ujyffcxi xy mom gulcxim.
